Comment: Held up in midfield or just worse around home bend, ran on to assert authority closing stages.
Broke well holding narrowing advantage 3-wide, strode forward to obtain rails run coming out of back straight, fought on under pressure, only to be collared close to home.
Ridden for cover after beginning from the one gate, travelling one-back on rails around the bend, kept on well but failed to quicken when asked over 200 metres out.
Ridden along in rear of midfield, shuffled backward before home bend, in last few into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Niggled along to keep with up leaders early, hampered and lost position 1000 metres out, remained in midfield around the bend and into the straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Slightly slow out, settled just worse than midfield on rails, gained a little bit closer around home bend, found nothing in straight.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, trailed the field around home bend and shifted widest turning for home, kept on well in the run home.
Settled in last few, saved ground turning in, made no impression in straight.
Jumped best from a poor draw, gradually settled just better than midfield and wide without cover, slightly closer up turning in but soon dropped out.
Prominent to straight, soon dropped out. (Bled)
Settled in second position on the fence after handing up the lead near the 1200m. Kicked clear early in the straight and withstood late challenge.
Settled behind midfield, 3 wide with cover. Ran on well particularly over the final 100M.
Made its run from third last position after being 1 off with cover. Closed off gamely.
Stalked the leaders on the fence. Stayed on reasonably in the home stretch to figure in the frame.
When wide early, was allowed to stroll forward and took up leading duties after the 1200m, 1 off. Failed to quicken and was one paced in the run to the line.
Eventually got cover near the 1200m, settling in 3rd position. Was a beaten horse approaching the 200m.
Race just ahead of midfield, 1 off with cover. Just plugged away in the straight.
Settled back in the field, close to the rail, had cover. Peeled out approaching the home turn and came widest in the straight, plodded to the line.
Ridden along early landing in about midfield position, had the fence with cover. Struggled in the straight.
Posted 3 deep without cover for the major part of the trip, settling behind the speed. Never a factor.
Settled at the rear, 3 deep with cover. Shifted wide on straightening, failed to close off and weakened easily over the latter stages.
Prominent, settled 2Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow pace, finished off nicely to get 2nd.
Rolled forward, then settled 1L off the leader with cover, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well until inside 100M weakened.
Camped handy, settled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Settled worse than midfield 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slow sectionals, dashed well.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, kept on one pace to the line.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, one paced home.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow sectionals, weakened 300M.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader, hung out rounding the Home turn, never looked likely.
Always at rear, no progress.
Missed the jump, never a factor.
Started OK, trapped 3 wide no cover midfield, shaken up on turn, hard-driven & responded with strong run to lead late.
Fair break, camped rail behind midfield, not clear run in stretch, forced to wait until daylight at 200m, ran home fast to snatch 2nd last stride.
Fast start, crossed to lead on rail 1600m, headed 1400m & switched 1 off in 3rd, 3 deep & shaken up 400m, led 300m, headed 50m, no extra.
Slow break, raced at tail, closed to 2nd last on rail 900m, switched out & driven 300m, closed off for good late gains.
Smart break, sat 2nd no cover outside leader, led on bridle 380m, soon driven for pressure, found little when asked, headed 300m, boxed on one pace.
Broke OK, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 3 wide 600m, driven turning in, stayed on soundly centre track.
Broke OK, raced 1 off with cover midfield, driven home turn, plugged on same speed.
Rousted at break, rolled wide to lead 1400m & crossed to rail, under pressure & headed 380m, weakened in run.
Fast break, tracked 1 back on rail, niggled 1000m, driven turning in, found little & tapered.
Tardy break, raced 2nd last, over-raced 1500m, to tail 1 off 900m, wide final turn, driven 400m but outpaced & never a factor.
Smart start, tracked pace 1 off with cover, switched out & shaken up 400m, quickened to lead 280m & kicked clear.
Taken behind from wide gate, settled 1 off with cover near rear, 5L down & driven wide 430m, closed off strongly to grab 2nd late.
Taken behind to slot rail near rear, switched out on turn & shaken up 400m, quickened in pursuit & ran on to edge duel for 3rd.
Missed break & bustled to settle midfield 1 off with cover, driven turning in, switched out 250m, battled soundly to wire, just missed frame.
Slow start & bustled, raced rail in rear, 7L last & ridden 430m, switched centre track, stayed on for solid gains.
Good break, settled rail midfield at 850m, switched out turning in, ran on evenly under strong drive.
Broke well, tracked pace 3 wide with cover, wide into stretch, driven 350m, outpaced & plugged on same speed.
Sharp break, tracked 1 back on rail, ridden 430m, switched 1 off 300m, found little in weak run home.
Speed to dispute lead 3 wide no cover, vied for lead turning in & ridden 400m, headed 280m & no extra, plugged on tamely until tapered out.
Broke OK, driven initially, posted 3 wide with cover midfield, driven wider into stretch, found nothing & eased when beaten.
Fast break to dispute lead 1 off, neck & neck for lead into stretch & driven 400m, headed 280m & faded out.
Broke well, rousted to dispute lead on rail, under pressure & found wanting 400m, weakened thereafter.
Eased back, 6Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M, drifted away 200M to score.
Eased back, 8Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Settled in midfield, 4.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made ground 400M, run ended 150M, ran on for 3rd.
Bumped start, 6Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden to keep up in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace 3 wide, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to take the rail and led by 1L at good pace, hung on until 200M, out of fuel.
Midfield, 6Ls off the good pace, raced keenly 800M, allowed to stride forward around the field in 4 wide, joined the lead 400M, but soon flattened 250M.
Pushed early, 2.5Ls off the good pace on the fence, held up 300M to 100M, not tested.
Hard ridden to obtain the box seat, pace good, reduced 250M.
At rear, 10Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on fairly.
Pressed forward, 1L off the good pace 2 wide, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the good pace 2 wide, weakened 250M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 10Ls off the good pace, made some ground 250M, no room 100M.
At back, 9Ls off the good pace along the fence, no dash, lack room 100M.
Lost right front plate soon after start, no early pace settling towards rear along rail. Saved ground turn, no clear run till 200m, ran on strongly when clear.
Ridden along early, settling 2-back, one-off back stretch. Boxed in around turn, no clear run till 300m, shot through to lead 200m, run down near line.
Ridden along early but trapped 4-wide without cover from 900m. Covered extra ground turn, wide in straight, kept battling to line.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling, cutting to rail 1200m. Headed around turn, retook lead 400m, collared 200m, kept on till swamped final 50m.
Hard ridden from outside draw but cross in and trapped 3-wide without cover. Rolled forward entering straight and kept on one-paced.
Outpaced early, dropped to rear away from fence. Last into turn, taken very wide in straight, kept on steadily.
Began awkwardly and bumped. Ridden to obtain forward position but crowded for room 1500m and later steadied, losing position around turn. Switched out wide in straight and kept on one-paced.
Outpaced and given early remainders to stay with field at the rear. Saved ground turn, unable to get run in straight till 200m when shifted out. Kept on steadily.
Ridden along behind midfield, crowded for room 1500m, steadied 1200m. Took off from 700m, made ground till 200m, then one-paced.
Began OK and pressed forward to sit one-back, one-off on settling. Rolled forward on entering straight, looked chance 200m, flattened.
Not pressured, sitting behind midfield along rail back stretch. Made ground early in straight to be closest at 200m before tiring.
Outpaced early, then steadied 1500m dropping to rear. Steadied 1200m, taken wide entering straight, kept on one-paced.
Hard ridden from wide draw to sit outside leader on settling. Took over lead around turn in one-off position, gave ground quickly after entering straight.
Pressed forward along rail, taking box seat 1200m when outside runners crossed in. Gave ground quickly soon after entering straight.
Began well, travelled comfortably in 4th 3-4Ls behind leader, cruised to the lead 200M out, kept on strongly to the line, won unextended.
Waited with in 6th place, ran on well to chase eventual winner over final 300M but always held.
Settled near the rear along the fence, ran on well from an unpromising position to claim 3rd close home.
Held up towards the rear, into clear 300M, made good initial progress, one paced final 100M.
Sent forward, allowed an easy lead upfront, kept on same pace when driven out 300M, headed 200M out, faded to 5th.
Always prominent behind leader, ran on same pace in straight, out of contention 200M.
Held up in mid-division, had every chance turning in, outdashed over final 200M.
Restrained at the rear, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, briefly responded to riding early straight, no extra passing 200M.
Tracked leader in a slowly run race, lacked further response entering 300M, dropped away to last.
Began OK, ridden forward to sit behind and between leaders 800m. Forged to front 400m, battled strongly to line while making contact with runner up several times final 200m.
Began well, led on settling, joined 400m out, shifted out 200m, battled while making contact with winner several times final 200, just failed.
Fractious in gate, slow to jump then crowded. Picked up speed to sit behind leaders 600m, had to switch in 200m to get clear running, finished off nicely. (See Racing Incidents)
Dislodged rider before start. Began well, staying close to leading pack. Raced tightly and taken in 200m, kept on steadily.
Began awkwardly, ridden along while edging closer to outer fence. Checked 700m, kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Jumped best and led initially before settling outside leader from 800m. Joined by third runner at 400m, crossed 300m, kept on one-paced.
Began OK, mustered to sit just behind leaders before course proper. One paced under hard riding from 400m.
Jumped fairly, outpaced and soon at rear along outer fence. One-paced while drifting in under pressure from 400m.
Began fairly, ridden along while shifting to outer fence. Under pressure from 400m, shifted out 150m and finished off with head on side.
Began well, ridden along behind pacemakers to 600m when lost position. Found little under hard riding from 400m.
Jumped OK then tightened for room dropping to last. Cut to outer fence and kept on one-paced, running past tired horses.
Jumped with field, ridden along to look a chance approaching 400m before tiring and giving ground gradually.
Began well but no pace dropping to rear at 800m. Pressed forward approaching course proper before tiring from 300m.
Began fairly, raced on own down centre track. Gave ground gradually after reaching course proper.
Jumped well, sat 2 wide with cover, 2-3 lengths back, ridden after turning in, kicked clear final 200M to score a strong win.
Began well from wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, kept on well in straight but unable to match winner final furlong.
Off slowly, settled 4-5 lengths back on rail, 2 wide turning in, no much room until 200M, finished off nicely late.
Away well, sat 1-2 lengths back on rail, travelled well throughout, kept on steadily for 4th.
Slightly slow out, recovered to take the 2nd position, 2 wide with no cover, ridden after turning in, stayed on fairly in straight.
Jumped well, settled 3 lengths back on rail, kept to inside after turn, not much clear running early in straight but finished evenly when clear.
Slowly away, sat 5-6 lengths back on rail, in traffic most of the straight, never got a real crack at them. (See racing incidents)
Began nicely from the widest draw, kept 4 wide with no cover until 800M, 3 wide with cover thereafter, made little progress in straight.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover, 5-6 lengths back, taken wider in straight, made some progress thereafter but never threatened.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, under pressure before turning in, failed to close off.
Taken back from wide draw, raced at rear throughout, taken well back and widest turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Slightly slow out, raced 2-3 wide with cover in midfield, ridden after turning in, failed to respond in straight.
Broke nicely, unable to slot in and raced 3 wide without cover, 2-3 lengths back, weakened after turning in when hard run took toll.
Drifted back from gate 12, raced at rear throughout, never a factor.
Moderately away, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover in the early stages, found cover near 800M, taken wider turning, let down on a strong finish and won comfortably.
Jumped nicely, raced on rails behind midfield, 5-6 lengths back, in traffic early in straight, finished off strongly when clear final 150M.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover, 5-6 lengths back, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to take 3rd.
Slowly out, recovered quickly to sit 3 lengths back on rail, came 2 wide at 800M, eased into clear turning, finished off well to make frame.
Began well, settled in 1 out 1 back spot, ideal run in mid-section, made run turning, ran on fairly in straight but peaked at 200M.
Jumped well, took the lead easily, travelled nicely throughout, ridden after turning in, headed 150M, stayed on fairly thereafter.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide in midfield 4 lengths back, hampered 600M, no clear running early in straight, ran on fairly when clear.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail for the majority of the race, ridden after turning in, made some progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Off slowly, raced 7 lengths behind the leader on rail, no clear running early in straight, ran on steadily but unable to factor in finish.
Average to begin, settled 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, swung wider turning in, weakened 200M when condition gave out.
Taken back from wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear throughout, taken wide in straight, made no real progress.
Began well, raced outside the leader in 2nd, travelled comfortably throughout, failed to respond in straight.
Jumped nicely, sat behind the leader on rail, 1-2 lengths back, travelled well, showed little response in straight.
Began fairly from wide draw, positioned 3 wide with cover at the back of the field, taken widest in straight, made no progress.

Comment: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Ridden along early, settled just off the pace from the 800 metres, quickened well to take command 200 metres out, won readily.
Close up early, soon dropped back to over 2L off the speed in midfield, renewed effort inside final 250 metres but unable to match pace of winner.
Never far off near stands rails, ran home one-paced.
Slowly away, trailed the field early stages, commenced move inside final 200 metres, improving when checked on stands rails 200 metres out, never recovered.
Outpaced early, ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Broke well, niggled along in midfield early stages, faded under pressure from halfway out.
Jumped fairly, settled around midfield near the centre of the track, yielded ground closing stages.
Made running to about 300 metres, soon overhauled.
Jumped fairly, travelled behind midfield off the rails, found nothing. (Bled)
Made its run from back in the field, 2 wide with cover. Rounded the home bend widest and closed off strongly to take control of the race near the 50M.
Did some work early to cross and lead in the early stages before handing up & taking a sit near the 1100M on the rails. Regained the lead at the 400m, finished off well.
Missed the start but managed to progress forward and race midfield, on the fence with cover. Finished off gamely along the inside.
Raced prominently on the rails with cover. Had no luck in running, finished off soundly to make the frame. (See incident report)
Settled in 5th position, 1 off with cover. Maintained a reasonable gallop down the running.
Travelled worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Kept on steadily the in the run home.
Camped behind midfield the fence with cover. Stayed towards the inside in the final stretch, was one paced.
Taken back from a wide gate and settled in last position close to the rail. Came wide in the straight, passed tiring runners.
Settled 4th from the rear, 3 deep with cover. Shifted out with one wider in the straight, was dour in the run to the line.
Raced in 3rd position, 1 off no cover. Was under pressure at the entrance to the straight, failed to respond and was gone at the 250m.
Settled at the rear of the field on the paint with cover. Never looked likely and was spent force after the furlong.
Posted 3 deep without cover near the 1100m, settling close to midfield. Struggled in the straight.
Rolled forward and took up the lead along the paint after the 1100m. Was a beaten horse early in the straight and gave ground easily passing the 300m.
Showed good early pace to share the lead, battled on strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Sent forward to share the lead, battled on strongly over the concluding stages with the winner, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Travelled prominent, kept on one pace to the line without any threats to the first two when asked 300M.
Showed early paced along the outer rails, then dropped to 3.5Ls behind the main group near the course proper, dashed strongly 300M to get 4th.
Showed good early pace to share the lead along the stands side, kept on well to the line.
Rolled forward to share the lead in the middle of the track, under pressure near the course proper, kept on one pace to the line without any serious threats.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls behind the leader, made some ground in the middle of the track.
Niggled along to settle in a prominent position, under pressure near the course proper, soon weakened thereafter.
At rear, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader, ran on fairly.
Sent forward to race in the middle of the track, under pressure near the course proper, kept on one pace until 200M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader, never ran on.
Never looked competitive.
Showed some early pace to settle midfield, under pressure near the course proper, flattened 300M.
Never a factor.
Sharp start, tracked pace 1 off with cover, progress on turn 500m, driven & switched out 350m, grinding run to lead 100m, drew clear.
Smart break, outpaced & drifted back to rail behind midfield, driven 550m & switched out on turn, steady advance to snag 2nd close home.
Slow start, driven wide to settle handy 3 wide no cover, rolled to press lead home turn, led 250m, all out & headed 100m, boxed on.
Driven at break, mustered wide to lead 800m, crossed to rail approaching 600m, headed 250m, battled on same speed.
Slow start, raced rear 1 off with cover, 7L last turning in, shaken up 350m, closed off for fair inroads.
Broke well to sit 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven home turn, plugged on same pace.
Awkward start, taken behind to race 3 wide in rear, switched very wide & driven final turn, stayed on past beaten rivals.
Sharp break, settled 1 off with cover 2nd, every chance turning in but found little under pressure & faded in run.
Tardy break, raced rail in rear rank, driven home turn, outpaced in tame stretch run.
Slow start, driven to race midfield 3 wide with cover, driven wide home turn, found little & tapered in tepid stretch run.
Broke OK, taken back to rear & caught 4 wide no cover, hard-ridden 500m, widest into stretch, struggled in run home.
Fast break & rousted to lead on rail, headed 800m, checked off heels above 600m & hung out on turn, lost ground, faded markedly turning in.
Taken back, raced 3 wide near tail, 6L back & very wide into stretch, reeling run mid-track, led 75m & drew away.
Speed to lead, headed 1300m & tracked 1 off no cover 2nd, ridden turning in, boxed on to overhaul long-time leader late but no match for winner.
Rousted at break to race 3 wide with cover midfield, driven a touch 900m, switched out & ridden 400m, stayed on soundly to snatch 3rd.
Driven to lead 1300m, soon to rail, extended 1L clear 800m, ridden 400m & kicked on, tied up 150m & headed 75m, no extra.
Sharp start, taken back to slot 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven wide into stretch, closed soundly centre track.
Sluggish start, rousted to rail behind midfield, ridden into stretch, stayed on gradually for solid inroads.
Dropped in at start, settled rail near tail, ridden 430m, switched out 300m, stayed on for solid gains.
Broke OK, raced 1 off with cover fore of midfield, ridden home turn, boxed on evenly to wire.
Smart start, sat 1 back on rail 3rd, shaken up 430m, found little & plugged on moderately.
Broke OK, sat rail midfield, driven 400m, plugged on one pace until tapered closing stages.
Smart start, 4 wide no cover until slotted 3 wide midfield 900m, wide home turn, outpaced & tapered to wire.
Moderate break, raced 1 off with cover towards rear, ridden into stretch, found little in weak run to wire.
Broke OK, rolled on to sit handy but caught 3 wide no cover, ridden 400m, found nothing & folded tamely.
Taken behind at start, soon slightly detached at tail, very wide into stretch, never a factor.
Settled 3Ls off the slow pace along the fence, dashed well 300M to score.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the slow pace, just held ground for 3rd.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, favoured by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, just held ground when clear.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Eased at start, 8.5Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow tempo.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 400M, little dash 200M.
Settled just off the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on until 250M emptied.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground.
At rear, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, little dash 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased at start, took rail at back, 6Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide no cover throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, no progress.
At back, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Began awkwardly, mustered to sit 3-back the fence. Shuffled back turn when pace slacked, switched out 400m to get run, pushed through to lead 200m, held off challengers. Substantial blood in trachea.
Began OK, pressed forward along fence but over raced 1200m when crossed, settling in box seat. Blocked for run entering straight but finished off nicely when clear from 250m.
Began awkwardly but pressed forward to lead on settling. Slowed pace turn, kicked 400m, joined at 200m, kept battling to line.
Fractious in gate, bumped and unbalanced start. Ridden along back stretch settling one-off, one-back at 1200m. Raced tight around turn when looking for run, kept on steadily in straight.
Jumped fairly, not pressured and held 3-wide at rear. Raced tightly turn, taken very wide into straight, finished off OK.
Pressed forward, settling on hind quarters of leader at 1200m. Battled on early in straight before flattened final strides.
Outpaced and soon detached from field. Took closer order turn, very wide into straight, ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Crowded out start, dropping to midfield on settling. Boxed in at turn, switched out kept on fairly final 400m under hard riding.
Allowed to find feet while crossing to rail soon after start. Saved ground turn but found nothing under hard riding in straight.
Ridden along from wide draw and trapped wide in midfield without cover from 1200m. Rolled forward turn, third into straight, gave ground from 300m.
Sent forward from wide barrier, crossed to the lead with ease, set slow pace to straight, opened up 2Ls lead mid-straight, kept on well and managed to hold off late challenge of 2nd.
Never far off from leaders, travelled strongly throughout, shifted out to clear 300M, had 2Ls to make up on leader passing 200M, closed off soundly, just held.
Strode forward, travelled comfortably behind the leader, had every chance turning in but was outsprinted by first two over final 200M.
Assumed a 2-wide spot close up to pace, kept on steadily turning home but offered little threat to first 2 inside 200M.
Began fairly, attempted to improve position along the inside but was checked 1100M, dropped back to a spot behind midfield, responded briefly turning in before fading 100M out.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, stayed on fairly inside 300M, not reached leaders.
Raced keenly behind midfield, held up for clear running early straight but didn't offer much when clear run presented 250M from home.
Held up 3-wide towards the rear down the back straight, strode closer to pace when left with no cover from 1000M, not quickened turning in, soon weakened out of contention.
Switched off to last, 5-6Ls off the pace in middle stages, turned wide 600M, no real progress down outside of track.
Began awkwardly, ended up near the rear 5Ls away from leader, found nothing under pressure, never a factor.
Dropped back from wide barrier but unable to slot in, caught 3-wide throughout, soon beaten passing 350M.
Crowded out start dropping to last. Waited at rear, saved ground turn, peeled out entering straight, ran on strongly to win in last stride.
Began fairly, allowed to stride own pace at rear away from fence. Taken 5-wide entering straight, surged forward to lead 100m, caught on post.
Began OK, ridden along between horses to settle 3-back, one-off at turn. Shifted out 800m when close on heels. Threw out challenge entering straight, kept on strongly to line.
Fractious in gate, slow but pressed forward between horses to grab box seat at turn. Rolled forward entering straight, hit front 200m, no extra closing stages.
Began fairly, mustered along fence to sit behind midfield on settling. Rolled forward entering straight, looked chance 200m, flattened. Lame left front leg.
Ridden along early, crossing to rail 2-back from leader. Made ground early in straight before turning one-paced final 200m.
Pressed forward 3-wide to sit behind leading pair without cover. Shaken up entering straight, looked chance 200m before running on empty.
Began OK, ridden along but wide back stretch, taken out and bumped 800m dropping to near last. Ran past tired horses final 200m.
Pressed forward to sit outside leader on settling. Travelled strongly around turn and early in straight before tiring final 100m.
Outpaced and soon detached from field. Last into home stretch and ran past beaten horses.
Hard ridden from jump to lead on settling. First into straight, collared 300m, kept battling before flattened 100m.
Pressed forward from outside draw, taking turn 4-wide without cover. Gave ground quickly in straight and eased final 200m.
Began smartly, raced 1 length behind the leader on the stands rail, travelled well throughout, hit the front near 300M and scored by 3/4 length.
Raced behind midfield close to the stands rail, improved from 400M, finished off strongly to take 2nd.
Slowly away, nearest to the grandstand rail, just behind midfield, finished off well to get 3rd.
Travelled in midfield down the centre of the track, with cover, ran home strongly to make the frame.
Showed early speed, raced in the middle of the track 1-2 lengths back with no cover, weakened in the concluding stages.
Tracked the speed, raced closer to the middle of the track 2 lengths back, made no progress and weakened in the final furlong.
Shared the lead throughout, near to the stands rail, hampered 400M, weakened thereafter.
Showed good speed to take the lead, difficult to settle when under pressure after 400M, weakened thereafter.
Raced behind midfield throughout, closer to the middle of the track, no response to riding in the final furlong.
Began awkwardly from gate 1, raced at rear nearer to the middle of the track, made no impression final 400M.
Began well, raced behind lead, 2 away from the stands rail, no response to vigorous riding final 300M and dropped away tamely. (See racing incidents)
Raced at rear throughout, never competitive.

Never far off on rails, saved ground turning in, fought on under pressure to hit the front over 100 metres out.
Jumped moderately, settled in last few, ran on well.
Broke well, attempted to make all but could find no extra and swamped over 100 metres out.
Slightly slow out, driven to midfield, hampered and lost position past 1000 metre bend, dropped towards rear leaving the Rock, saved ground turning in, finished off race well.
Jumped fairly, prominent when hampered and lost position passing 1000 metres, remained in midfield on rails to straight, ran on without threatening.
Jumped fairly, settled wide and just worse than midfield, took closer order around the Rock, kept on same pace in straight.
Slowly away, remained well behind to straight, finished off race nicely. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped well, settled in midfield, lost position passing the Rock, baulked early in straight, kept on to the line.
Well back, went widest into straight, kept on same pace.
Jumped fairly, gradually improved to 1L 2nd one off the rails, remained similar into straight, hung in early and soon faded.
Jumped fairly, settled in forward of midfield, checked when beaten 250 metres out.
Raced wide throughout, behind midfield early, improving to midfield into far side and further closer up down the Rock, soon weakened from a prominent position into straight.
Led easily on the rails. Made every post a winner, straightened a couple in front and finished off well to repel late challenge.
Parked in 4th position, 1 off no cover. Chased gamely all the way down the running.
Settled ahead of midfield, 3 wide with cover. Rounded the home bend widest, closed off of determinedly.
Went back from a wide gate and settled, in 2nd last position on the rails with cover. Closed off well.
Showed plenty of speed early, eventually taking up the box seat approaching the 600m. Closed off one paced in the straight.
Never looked comfortable throughout the run, settling midfield, 2 wide with cover. Raced greenly for most of the trip, finished off steadily.
Raced 3rd from the rear, 1 off with cover. Finished off reasonably out wide.
Settled just behind midfield on the paint with cover. Made the first turn a little awkwardly, stayed on only evenly in the run home.
Parked 4th last on the fence with cover. Stayed to the inside in the home straight, failed to close off.
Hard ridden to hold a forward position, racing 3 deep without cover on the circle. Travelled just off the speed, faded in the straight.
Raced midfield, 2 deep with cover. Was flat when asked for an effort early in the straight and weakened after the furlong.
Settled in last position, close to the rail, had cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, gradually improved rounding the Home Turn, dashed on strongly to score by a short head.
Raced midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched to 3 wide with cover rounding the Home Turn, finished off nicely for 2nd.
Slow to muster early, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, dashed well to get 3rd.
Prominent, settled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on well until inside 50M weakened.
Hard ridden forward to occupy the box seat, ran on nicely until final 50M weakened.
Taken back to rear from a wide barrier, settled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off impressively.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, closed to the line well.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Sent forward to share the lead, stayed on until final 150M weakened.
Always at rear, made some late ground in straight but without any threats.
Raced midfield, niggled along throughout the race, never a threat.
Hard ridden forward to take the lead by 3/4L, flattened badly soon after straightening.
Bumped rival at start, slotted 1 off with cover behind midfield, switched 3 deep 600m & advanced, driven to lead 220m, in command.
Smart start, sat 1 off with cover midfield, switched out & driven home turn, quickened to 2nd 200m, drifted to rail in pursuit, always held.
Awkward break, raced rail midfield, switched 1 off 600m & stumbled off heels, driven turning in, closed soundly to edge 3rd at wire.
Good break, prominent early, settled 3 back on rail, niggled 600m & lost position, switched out & driven 300m, stayed on dourly for sound late inroads.
Taken behind to rail near rear, drifted back to last trio 800m, switched out 500m & driven, crowded 200m, closed off to just miss frame.
Bumped at break, raced 1 off with cover near rear, progress 3 wide 600m, driven wide home turn, boxed on without threatening.
Steady start, raced 1 off in rear, bumped & 3 wide 1000m, ridden 500m, very wide home turn, stayed on evenly.
Bumped rival start, settled rail behind midfield, off heels 600m, switched out driven 300m, kept on same pace.
Broke well, raced wide until rolled to 3rd 1 off no cover 1000m, driven 400m, outpaced 300m & faded out.
Restrained at break, raced rear on rail, bumped rival & 1 off 1000m, last turning in, plugged on tamely centre track.
Speed to lead 1st turn, to rail 900m, shaken up 400m, all out & headed 220m, weakened markedly thereafter.
Rousted early to dispute lead, settled rail behind leader, ridden 500m, found nothing into stretch, weakened tamely.
Smart break, sat 3 wide near rear, scooted 4 wide 800m to lead 600m, 2L clear home turn, kicked 4L clear 200m, tapered late but in command.
Fair break, raced near rear, switched 3 wide with cover 600m, 5L back 400m & very wide home turn, stormed down centre track, closed to wire.
Sharp start & prominent 4 wide, led 1 off 1100m, set steady tempo, headed 600m, shaken up 300m, ran home evenly.
Broke OK, raced rail midfield, switched out in home stretch & driven 300m, ran home soundly without threatening.
Broke well, sat 1 off with cover midfield, switched 3 wide with cover back stretch, wide into home straight, kept on one pace.
Steady start & raced at tail, advanced a place 1100m, switched 1 off 600m, wide into stretch, stayed on moderately.
Rousted at break, to tail 1100m, 6L last 400m & ridden turning in, stayed on one pace.
Bustled early to race handy 1 off with cover, outpaced & ridden turning in, found little & plodded home.
Broke well, tracked on-pace most of way 3 wide no cover, ridden turning in, found nothing & faded.
Speed to lead, headed 1100m, sat close 2nd on rail until 600m, 3rd & driven 500m, emptied turning in & weakened markedly.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, made early move 500M to take advantages from the slow pace, well cleared 200M.
Bumped start, took rail in midfield, 5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Eased to rear, 7.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, bumped 500M, not suited by the slow pace, only little dash 300M.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, checked 500M, re-gather momentum 200M, little dash.
Settled in box seat, suited by the slow tempo, however soon flattened 200M.
Pushed early, 5.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok despite all negative racing situations.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1.5Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Eased to rear, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the slow pace, no dash, reduced 250M.
Slow away, hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, but soon emptied 300M.
Began fairly, shifted out 1150m and bumped, stayed in one-off position to turn, peeled out 400m, ran on strongly to win in last stride.
Began well, mustered along fence to grab box seat. Saved ground turn, crept forward along rail to take lead 200m, run down in final stride.
Slow into stride, ridden but failed to muster dropping to clear last. Ridden along turn, swung very wide into straight, finished off strongly.
Began fairly, not pressured, dropping to rear away from fence. Swung widest into straight, ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began fairly, ridden along to make ground settling 3-wide in midfield. Switched 4-wide entering straight and ran on steadily.
Jumped well, led on settling, set brisk pace. Caught 200m but kept on well until swamped final 50m.
Began awkwardly, raced keenly when close on heels 1000m. Cut to rail saving ground turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Jumped OK but checked 1000m, settling three-back the fence. Awkwardly placed turn, had clear run from 350m, one-paced.
Jumped well, rolled forward to sit outside leader. Took turn awkwardly, racing ungenerously from 600m, one-paced in straight.
Began well, steadied 1000m, dropping behind midfield but way from fence. Very wide into straight, kept on steadily until flattened 100m.
Pressed forward from wide draw and trapped three-wide without cover behind leader. Covered extra ground turn and spent force soon after entering straight.
Began OK, mustered along fence to sit three-back from leader. One-paced in straight and not pressured final stages.
Restrained and held up near the rear, 7Ls off the pace in the first half, made good progress when taken 3-wide home turn, swept to the front 100M for another comfortable win.
Began awkwardly, settled behind midfield, quickened well through a narrow gap entering the straight but was readily held by winner over final 150M.
Gently urged to a forward position just behind leader, went for inside run turning in, stayed on to claim 3rd but not matched finishing pace of first two final 100M.
Strode forward to clear the field, led steadily from 1300M, kept on same pace in straight, headed by first three inside 100M.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, switched out 450M for clear run, stayed on mildly for 5th.
Not far off from leaders, kept on same pace under pressure from 350M, never seriously threatened.
Reserved in a rearward position 5-6Ls off the pace, waited with until 300M, moderate headway final 200M.
Settled towards the rear, saved ground along the inside, briefly put to test entering straight, ran past beaten rivals (Jockey questioned re his riding.)
Positively ridden, raced outside leader, kept on same speed turning in, outpaced passing 150M.
Niggled along early to hold a position in mid-division along the fence, failed to pick up the pace when driven out 350M, never threatened.
Hampered shortly after the jump, dropped back to last 8Ls off the pace, shaken up 550M, bid wide, lacked further response inside 300M.
Caught 3-wide without cover in midfield, raced keenly and strode closer to leaders down the back-straight, came up empty turning home, weakened to last.

Ridden to soon join the leader from the widest gate, came under pressure in straight to assert authority 200 metres out, drew clear but flattered by the margin.
Jumped well from the middle draw, held slender lead on rails, challenged upon straightening and headed under pressure over 200 metres out, kept on to finish.
Ridden along in midfield early stages, in similar position turning in, made steady headway past beaten horses in the run home.
Niggled along in first few travelling wide without cover, kept on before finding no extra inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, settled 3 lengths back in 5th, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Jumped well from a poor gate, settled wide in midfield, lost position around home bend, made no impression in straight.
Niggled along early, settled one-back in 3rd on rails, dropped out tamely in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Never better than midfield, beaten when broke down near the post.
Jumped fairly, niggled along on rails in midfield, came under pressure approaching home straight, soon faded after straightening.
Slow out, trailed the field to halfway, saved ground turning in, made no progress in straight.
Began moderately, soon dropped to last few, made no impression in straight.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, never a factor.
Raced midfield, 3 wide with cover. Showed good turn of foot and finished off well, winning easily despite hanging in.
Raced in second position, 1 off no cover. Was narrowly in front at the furlong but couldn't sustain its finishing effort, stayed on gamely.
Missed the start, settling on the rails with cover. Ran on soundly.
Parked 3 deep without cover, ahead of midfield. Finished off well.
Parked behind the leader on the fence. Ranged up at the furlong but ended its run well before the line.
Was never likely after coursing 4 wide without cover on the circle, behind midfield. Managed to stay on despite wide run.
Slowly away travelling back in the field, 1 off with cover. Finished off reasonably.
Settled 3 wide midfield, had cover. Maintained a steady gallop down the running.
Camped worse than midfield, on the rails with cover. Kept plugging away in the home straight.
Raced in last position, settling 2-3 wide on the circle, had cover. Battled away fairly in the run home.
Showed good gate speed to lead from the early stages along the fence. Was under siege at the furlong, faded thereafter.
Tracked midfield, 1 off with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Broke slowly settling towards the rear, on the paint with cover. Failed to close off.
Had every chance, racing 1 out 1 back. Quickly gave ground after the 400m and tailed out.
Midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader 4 wide without cover throughout, benefited by the fast tempo, dashed on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, suited by the fast pace, finished off strongly until final 50M weakened.
Raced midfield, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, suite by the fast sectionals, ran on nicely to get 3rd.
At rear, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, swung wide rounding the Home Turn, dashed well.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, suited by the fast pace, ran on steadily without threatening.
Rolled forward, travelled 1L off outside the leader, despite hampered by the fast pace, stayed on until inside 100M weakened.
Bumped start, then travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, checked 700M, despite suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Settled in front of midfield about 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suite by the fast pace, never looked chance.
Eased start but failed to find a cover, then gradually improved to race 1L off 3 wide without cover, soon struggled after straightening.
Taken back, settled 7ls behind the leader on the fence, despite benefited by the fast pace, never ran on.
Bumped start, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, struggled rounding the Home Turn, flattened thereafter. (Lost left front plate soon after the start)
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the fast tempo, kept on the same pace until 200M flattened. (Questioned for performance, see incidents report)
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L at fast sectionals, flattened and headed 300M. (Questioned for performance, see incidents report)
Never in contention.
Led at break, headed 1st turn, tracked lead 1 off with cover, not clear run in stretch, switched out 200m & driven, quickened to lead 100m.
Good start, raced 1 back on rail, shaken up turning in, driven down fence 250m, closed off gradually to 2nd late, just held at wire.
Pace to lead 1st turn, headed briefly 1200m, set steady pace, pressed & driven 400m, all out in stretch duel, headed 220m, boxed on gamely.
Good break, rolled wide to brief lead 1200m, settled close 2nd, driven 400m, edged to lead 220m, soon emptied & swamped 100m.
Broke OK, tracked handy 3 wide with cover, 4 wide & driven home turn, kept on evenly.
Dropped in at break to 1 off behind midfield, shuffled to last trio 900m, 6L down & driven home turn, rattled home late for eye-catching gains.
Fast break, caught wide no cover midfield, rolled 4 wide to press lead 3 deep at 800m, driven 300m, boxed on one pace.
Broke OK, restrained to race rail last trio, 5L back & ridden 400m, switched out & stayed on for sound inroads.
Fair break, raced 1 off with cover midfield, drifted back in back stretch, hard-ridden final turn, battled on for minor gains.
Impeded after start, raced last trio, shifted 3 wide 1000m, ridden 600m, last & very wide turning in, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Rousted early, raced 3 wide with cover midfield, driven 600m, outpaced & plugged on tamely, eased late when beaten.
Missed break, behind to rail & recovered to sit midfield, ridden 400m, found little & weakened tamely.
Taken back at break, raced 4 wide behind midfield, driven without cover 600m & very wide home turn, struggled in run home.
Sharp start to lead on rail, extended 2L clear 400m, 3L clear 250m, tapered late & just held on under strong drive.
Broke well, keen & restrained 1 off with cover midfield, shaken up 400m & switched out, quickened in pursuit, to 2nd 200m, strong closer, just failed.
Smart start, trapped wide & soon taken back to 1 off with cover near rear, shifted out & driven 6L back final turn, flew home, just failed.
Taken behind from widest gate, slotted rail near rear, switched out 500m, progress & short of room 300m, closed well until tapered last strides.
Fast break to dispute lead, soon settled 1 back on rail, switched out & driven 430m, to 2nd 350m, all out & lost place 200m, tapered to wire.
Awkward start & bustled to sit 3 wide no cover midfield, shaken up 400m, plugged on one pace.
Taken behind to race last pair on outer, edged wider 600m for progress, 7L back & driven 400m, kept on for modest gains.
Sharp start, raced rail midfield, shaken up turning in, stayed on evenly.
Slow start, anchored last pair on inner, shifted out 500m, 8L last & widest turning in, driven 400m, boxed on for minor inroads.
Broke Ok, raced rail behind midfield, hard-ridden 350m, outpaced & plodded on steadily.
Tardy start, bustled forward to sit 2nd outside leader, hard-ridden & outpaced turning in, emptied 350m & weakened in run.
Broke OK, advanced to race 1 off 1 back, ridden under pressure 500m, soon outpaced & struggled in run home.
Held up behind midfield, not picked up the pace when asked, eased final 150M.
Sluggish start, bustled early to 3 wide no cover behind midfield, wide no cover final turn, found nothing & weakened tamely.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the good pace 2 wide, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear and scored easily.
Pushed forward to share the lead 2 wide at good pace, dominated 350m, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Slow away, 5.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the good pace 3-4 wide, closed off strongly 250M, however run ended 100M.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace on the fence, held up 4-2, made steady when clear.
Pushed forward, 3Ls off the good pace 3 wide, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, out of fuel 200M.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the good pace on the fence, raced ungenerously, ran on ok in straight.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the good pace 2 wide, raced keenly, weakened 250M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 4Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on fairly.
Briefly pushed early, 4Ls off the good pace 3 wide, flattened in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, emptied 250M, checked badly 200M.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the good pace 3 wide, reduced 350M.
Pushed forward to take rail and shared the lead at good pace, soon dropped off 350M.
Jumped with field, ridden along to hold rail behind leader, dropping 3-back at turn. Came off fence 500m, picked up momentum to hit front 200m, battled to line.
Began well, rolled forward but taken 3-wide with cover into turn, bumped entering straight, battled to line to just miss.
Began OK but kept wide with cover. Shifted in and bumped entering straight, loomed 200m but continued to lay in. Jockey reported reluctant to improve.
Began fairly, raced tightly 1000m, dropping to rear away from fence. Raced tightly turn, no clear run in straight, shifted in 200m when denied run. Boxed on.
Ridden along early, settling midfield between horses. Switched out turning for home but no run and forced to shift in 150m. Finished off nicely.
Pressed forward to sit on hindquarters of leader before dropping into box seat around turn. Rolled forward entering straight, hit front 200m, turning one-paced.
Began awkwardly, struck heels and blundered dropping to clear last. Edged closer to rail, saved ground turn, forced to shift in 100m when closing off nicely.
Began fairly, settling behind midfield. Three-wide around turn, taken wider into straight, kept on one-paced.
Not pressured at rear, edged closer to rail, switched out entering straight but no clear running. Kept on one-paced.
Jumped OK but no early pace, slipping back to rear but away from fence. Ran past tired horses in straight.
Pressed forward from inside draw to lead on settling. Set decent pace, kicked clear 400m, collared 200m, faded.
Began awkwardly, mustered along fence to sit behind midfield at turn. Gave ground gradually after entering straight.
Ridden forward but trapped three-wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, gave ground quickly in straight. Had irregular heart rhythm.
Slotted into a 3-wide spot in mid-division, travelled smoothly in middle stages, quickened to the front 250M, dueled with runner-up final 200M, gained upper hand close home.
Quickly into stride, relinquished the lead near 1200M, awkwardly placed behind weakening leader 500M-400M, joined eventual winner mid-straight, lost out near line.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, no room early straight, shifted out 350M, closed off soundly but always held by front pair.
Began well but soon reigned back to a rearward position, switched wide 500M, closed off well 1st half of straight, turned one pace final stages.
Had tendency to hang out from the outset, badly outpaced early and middle stages, still had plenty to do turning in, closed off the race strongly final 300M. (acing manners unacceptable.)
Positioned 2-wide in the group chasing leaders, briefly threatened 300M, turned one pace passing 200M.
Settled ahead of mid-division along the inside, lacked a turn of foot when placed under pressure, never a serious threat to leaders.
Ridden more prominently than usual, raced just off the pace, briefly led early straight, caught inside 300M, faded towards the finish.
Held up behind midfield, stayed on mildly when driven 400M, shifted out under pressure 200M, lacked further response thereafter.
Settled towards the rear, ran on only fairly turning home, never a threat to leaders.
In touch behind leaders but caught 3-wide no cover throughout, steadied 250M, weakened out of the race.
Settled behind midfield, saved ground along the fence but didn't respond to riding entering straight.
Began awkwardly, rushed along and obtained the lead before home turn, came up empty and dropped out rapidly 350M. (Unacceptable performance.)
Soon dropped to the rear, detached from the field passing 1000M, eased down by jockey. (Jockey reported his mount did not stretch out / Unacceptable performance.)
Jumped well, restrained, settling 3-back, one-off before turn. Taken out 400m to get run, hit front 200m, shifted out 150m, pulled clear final 100m.
Jumped OK, taken across behind runners from wide draw but kept away from fence. Rolled forward 700m, widest into straight, kept on well under hard riding.
Jumped well, pressed forward 3-wide to join leader around turn. Kicked clear entering straight, caught 200m, boxed on well.
Began OK, ridden along out wide without cover at 800m. Improved position around turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Ridden along to find cover, settling towards rear in one-off position. Improved around turn, taken out entering straight, checked 150m when making ground. Kept on.
Began OK, mustered along fence to sit 3-back before turn. Peeled out 500m but close on heels entering straight. Kept on steadily under hard riding.
Bumped shortly after start, dropping to near rear. Well back entering straight, but was finishing off nicely when forced to switch out from heels.
Began fairly, mustered along fence to within 3L of leader, came off bridle 600m, one-paced in straight. Jockey reported reluctant to stretch out.
Began fairly, settled at rear in one-off position. Improved around turn, taken wider by inside runner entering straight, one-paced in straight.
Led on jumping, cut to rail, taking box seat at 800m. Shuffled back to 4th entering straight, kept on one-paced final 400m.
Slow into stride and steadied shortly after, dropping to clear last. Well back entering straight, ran past beaten horses.
Pressed forward from wide draw to take clear lead from 1200m. Joined around turn, gave ground steadily final 400m.
Began OK, ridden along to hold midfield position to 800m, gave ground from turn, not ridden out final 400m. Run deemed unacceptable (See racing incidents).
Jumped well, settled 2 wide with cover in 5th, travelled nicely throughout, ridden after turning in, finished off strongly and scored by a length.
Bumped start, recovered to position prominently 1 out 1 back, travelled well throughout, took the lead near 250M but unable to hold off the winner late.
Average break, recovered to sit in midfield, 4 lengths back, 2-3 wide without cover, improved turning, finished off strongly to take 3rd.
Slow to begin, raced 5-6 lengths back on rail, saved ground and kept to inside after turn, finished off well final 300M to make frame.
Began well, took the lead easily and set an even tempo, 1 length clear, headed 300M and couldn't sustain effort final furlong.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back, came wider in the straight and made some progress without threatening.
Bumped start, raced at rear throughout, still well back turning in, came through between horses and made good progress final 300M. (See racing incidents.)
Jumped with them, restrained to sit 6-7 lengths back 2 wide with cover at rear, asked before turning in, but only made limited progress in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide with cover, 4 lengths back in midfield, ridden after turning in, finished off one-paced.
Average to begin, raced 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, soft run to turn, weakened gradually after turning in.
Began fairly from gate 13, unable to slot in and raced wide without cover throughout, made no progress in straight and faded after hard run took toll.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6-7 lengths away, bumped 900M, took widest after turning in, no response to riding in straight.
Jumped well from the widest gate, raced outside the leader and dropped out quickly for run to 400M, weakened soon after turning in.
Began well from gate 1, sat behind the leader on rail, travelled well throughout, weakened early in straight.

Jumped well and in front early, ceded advantage for cover coming out of home straight, settled one-back in 3rd on rails, saved ground turning in, fought on to gain upper hand final strides.
Jumped fairly, gradually took up running, set sedate pace middle stages holding narrow advantage on rails, fought on gamely when seriously challenged in the final stretch, overshadowed final strides.
Jumped well from a low draw, settled in rear of midfield on rails, shuffled backward to tail-end at the Rock, saved ground turning in, ran on well to do best work late.
Settled on rails in 5th within 3L of leader, similar turning for home, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, settled in last few, made swift progress out wide up Rock to dispute lead rounding home bend, faded under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped moderately, ridden for pace but forced to steady to last few, remained behind midfield throughout far side, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
Jumped moderately, settled in midfield, lost position passing 600 metres before making swift progress 3-wide around the bend, unable to sustain effort from 1.5L back in 4th into straight.
Jumped fairly from a poor gate, settled in midfield, carried backward to rear of field up Rock, recovered ground swiftly around the bend but ran home one-paced.
Not far off, shuffled back to midfield at the Rock, dropped further back around home bend, ran home one-paced.
Gradually came across to join leaders after beginning from the widest gate, settled half a length back outside leader, yielded ground 500 metres out. (Tactic questioned)

Gradually taken back for cover behind midfield after beginning from a wide gate, shuffled further back to last few around the Rock, came wide for a run rounding home bend, failed to quicken in straight.
Sluggish at start, travelled well behind early, made short-lived effort out wide up Rock to be as close as 3L back in midfield, run ended over 500 metres out.
Patiently ridden from 2nd last position, 1 off with cover. Made a sweeping run after the 500m, had plenty of momentum turning for home and finished off well.
Rated third from the rear, on the rails with cover. Kept grinding away early in the run home, got going strongly over the final 100m.
Camped 3 back the fence, had cover. Railed up in the home stretch, kept on at the same speed after having every possible chance.
Made its run from last position, on the rails with cover. Swung the home turn widest and let down well early in the straight, but came up one paced over the last 100m.
Settled behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Got a nice trail into the race on the home turn, but couldn't go on with it, tiring over the latter stages.
Worked forward and led on the paint. Hung out for most of the trip and proved a handful for its rider, was a spent force after the furlong.
Settled in 3rd position, 1 off. Was carried wider near the 800m, racing 3 deep no cover. Failed to close off.
Box seated in the early stages. Shifted out near the 800m when racing close to heels and travelled outside the leader. Was a beaten horse early in the home straight.
Began smartly, then crossed to the rail and led by 1.5Ls at slightly slow sectionals, made all and scored by a neck.
Hard ridden forward to settle 1.5Ls off outside the leader at slightly slow tempo, tried its best but missed by a neck.
Camped handy, 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slightly slow tempo, ran on well to get 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slightly slow sectionals, made ground gradually.
Midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover throughout, not suited by the slightly slow tempo, ran on steadily.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slightly slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Began slowly, then travelled midfield 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slightly slow pace, finished off fairly.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slow sectionals, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slightly slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, despite benefited by the slightly slow sectionals, flattened 200M.
Always at rear, never in contention.
Jumped slowly, then settled worse than midfield about 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, never a factor.
Broke well, settled rail midfield, progress 800m, ridden home turn, switched out & quickened to lead 150m, drew clear.
Quick break, sat close 2nd outside leader, driven to press lead into stretch, led 200m, all out & headed 150m, boxed on & just held 2nd.
Good start, sat 1 back on rail, driven into stretch, kept on well to snare 3rd.
Good break, raced 1 back 1 off, ridden & switched 3 wide home turn, every chance in run home & kept on soundly to just miss frame.
Fair start, raced mid rank, forced wider & driven home turn, switched out in home stretch & kept on evenly.
Slow start, crossed to rail near rear, shuffled back & hard ridden turning for home, stayed on for minor late gains.
Snagged back to race 1 off in rear, switched 3 wide 800m for progress to midfield, hard-ridden on turn, wide into stretch, kept on one pace.
Fair break, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven 500m, wide home turn, stayed on one pace.
Restrained at break, camped rail at tail, driven turning in, stayed on until tapered & bumped close home.
Fast break to lead, soon to rail & set steady pace, increased tempo 600m, driven under pressure final turn, headed 200m, faded tamely.
Smart start, sat 1 off with cover near rear, close to heels 850m, ridden 3 wide & progress 600m, wide on turn, outpaced in tepid run home.
Fast break to dispute early lead on fence, chased lead in 3rd 1L back, driven into stretch, darted to lead 200m, drew clear.
Sharp start, disputed lead 1 off, narrow 2nd 550m, led 300m when shaken up & unbalanced, headed 200m, battled to just hold 2nd.
Slow start, rolled to sit handy 3 wide with cover, driven 300m, kept on well to just miss 2nd.
Slow start, bustled to sit 1 off with cover midfield, ridden 400m, kept on evenly under hard drive.
Bustled at break to race 3 wide with cover midfield, driven 500m, ran on one pace to wire.
Good break, tracked pace 1 off with cover, ridden 500m, switched out 300m, out paced & tapered in run.
Dropped in at start, raced 1 off near rear, driven turning in, stayed on same speed.
Snagged back at break, soon at tail, off heels 800m, switched out & driven into stretch, ran on for minor gains.
Speed to dispute lead 3 wide, narrow lead 550m, hard-ridden into stretch, headed 300m, no extra but battled on until faded out final 150m.
Broke OK, raced rail midfield, ridden 400m, outpaced in stretch & plodded on tamely.
Taken back from widest gate, sat 3 wide near tail, scrubbed 400m, widest into stretch, one-paced & no impression.
Tardy start & bustled early, raced rail near tail, scrubbed 400m, widest into stretch, found nothing & plodded to wire.
Slow away, 5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, made ground around the field 3-4 wide from 800M, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to score.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Eased at start, 6.5Ls off the leaders, made ground around the field 3-4 wide from 800M, dashed strongly 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Rolled forward, 2Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 300M, little dash when clear.
Eased back and took rail, 5Ls off the leaders, lack room 300M, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, shared the lead 2 wide at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on until 150M flattened.
Eased back for cover, 5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, held up most straight, little dash.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 4Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, hung in badly 300M, just ran on ok.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leaders, harmed by the slow pace, blocked whole straight and checked 200M, not tested.
Hard ridden to share the lead along fence, benefited by the slow sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden forward, 1L off the leaders, suited by the slow tempo but trapped 3 wide no cover throughout, reduced 250M.
Hard ridden forward, however trapped very wide, then eased to midfield, 3Ls off the leaders, 3-4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, emptied in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, cut to rail 3-back first turn, dropping 4-back back stretch. Saved ground final turn, peeled wide entering straight, ran on strongly to win close home.
Pressed forward from start to settle one-out, one-back from 1000m. Waited around turn, rolled forward to lead 200m, battled to line.
Began fairly, settling at rear along fence. Saved ground turn, stayed inside entering straight, blocked for run 150m, finished strongly when clear.
Pressed forward from start holding rail inside leader before taking box seat from 800m. Had clear run in straight and kept on steadily.
No early pace, slipping back but 3-wide into back stretch. Remained at rear final turn, peeled widest into straight, ran on steadily down centre track.
Ridden along early, holding fence three-back from leader. Switched out 500m, entered straight behind wall of horses, finished off nicely when clear 200m.
Hard ridden from start to go forward settling 3-back, one-off back stretch. Swung wide into straight and kept on steadily under hard riding.
Jumped best but held three-wide first turn. Rolled forward to sit outside leader 800m. Took over lead entering straight, kept on well when collared until swamped final 100m.
Taken back from wide draw, settling last but away from fence. Saved ground final turn, ran past beaten horses in straight.
Jumped well, took over lead before 1000m, cut to fence 800m. Caught soon after entering straight, giving ground gradually.
Jumped fairly then awkwardly placed on heels 1000m. Bumped 600m, had clear run entering straight but found nothing. Bled from both nostrils.
Ridden along early but trapped 3-wide without cover, slipped to behind midfield back stretch. Covered extra ground final turn and soon beaten.
Quickly into stride, sat handily just off the pace, ran on well to taken lead 80M form home, held off a strong challenge from the 2nd who hung in late stages.

From draw 12 managed to slot into a 2-wide position in midfield, quickened strongly and looked a winner 100M out, shifted in final late stages forcing the jockey to stop riding, just held at the line.
Guided to a midfield position along the fence, kept to inside on straightening, ran on steadily to clinch 3rd in a close finish.
Never far off from leaders, had no room early straight, shifted back to inside near 200M, closed off well and could have got 3rd with a clear run.
Soon moved to the lead, set slow pace in 2nd quarter, kept on well passing 300M, not pace of first two inside 100M then beaten to 5th in a blanket finish.
Tracked leaders 2-wide, closed off steadily passing 300M, looked to have a strong claim for 3rd but was checked 50M and lost momentum, edged out in a blanket finish.
Pushed along to hold a position ahead of midfield, gave limited response on straightening, never reached contention.
Sat outside the lead, travelled comfortably enough at a slow tempo but lacked further response when driven 250M from home.
Very slowly away and soon detached, moved back to the rear of the field entering home turn, closed steadily from well off the pace, not reached leaders.
Began awkwardly, taken to the fence and sat towards the rear in a slowly run race, failed to quicken with leaders inside 300M, never threatened.
Fractious in stalls, sat well back off a slow pace, unable to quicken entering 300M, never involved.
Not hurried, settled towards the rear in a slowly run race, came under pressure 400M, had nothing to offer.
