Jumped well from a poor draw, soon ridden to lead, obtained rails run over 1000 metres out, kicked over 1L clear after straightening but soon flattered, just held on.

Sluggish at start, recovered to rear of midfield coming out of back straight, saved ground on inside turning in, baulked and switched out for a run 300 metres out, fought on steadily without threatening.
Settled in forward of midfield, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled in last few on rails, made significant progress in straight, did best work late.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, settled wide without cover in midfield, kept on steadily in straight without quickening.
Eased back to rear of field, commenced move and taken widest into straight, finished off well.
Niggled along, held rails run inside leader, steadied to obtain cover from leader coming out of far side, similar turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Jumped moderately, gradually settled behind midfield, towards rear turning in, unable to obtain a clear run the majority of the straight.
Travelled in last few, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
Jumped moderately, gradually improved to 2-wide in 2L 3rd, faded inside final 200 metres.
Settled in 4th on rails about 3L off the speed, shifted out for a run upon straightening, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.
Gradually settled behind midfield on rails, remained similar turning in, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Settled in midfield on rails, soon weakened under pressure after straightening.
Well behind early, made short-lived effort out wide around home bend, folded up quickly from midfield into straight.
Rolled forward to race in third position, no cover, near the stands side. Was set alight after the 400m, and lengthened strongly to post a convincing win.
Raced prominently, 1 off with cover, closer the stands rail. Drifted in near the 400m whilst endeavouring to improve, finished off soundly.
Settled about 2-3 off the stands rail with cover. Shifted in after the 400m, finished off fairly.
Began awkwardly, settling back in the field, on the outside rail with cover. Made good late headway.
Travelled ahead of midfield, the stands rail with cover. Kept on evenly over the final furlong.
Parked about 3rd from the rear on the grandstand side, had cover. Kept grinding away in the run home making some ground.
Camped 2nd last, the stands side had cover. Battled away in the run to the line and was one paced.
Settled 2nd last the grandstand side had cover. Didn't find any extra over the last 300m, and finished one paced.
Settled in 2nd position close to the stands rail no cover. Was asked for an effort near the 400m, never responded and faded soon after.
Tracked the speed, 3-4 off the stands rail, had some cover in the early stages. Drifted in midrace, to improve but was found wanting and gave in quickly soon thereafter.
Settled closer to the middle of the track, no cover, behind midfield. Struggled over the final 300m.
Reared on jumping and lost considerable ground settling a long last. Was never in the hunt.
Speared forward and led close to the stands rail. Was under heavy pressure after the 500m and failed to respond. Gave ground quickly passing the 400m, finished tailed out. (To trial)
Camped handy, settled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly to score by a neck.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, finished off strongly to get 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite not suited by the slow pace and reluctant to shift out near 300M, ran on nicely for 3rd.
Ridden forward to take the lead along the fence by 1/2L at slow sectional, stayed on well until inside 30M.
Settled worse than midfield about 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, dashed on nicely.
Sent forward to settle 1/2L off outside the leader, despite suited by the slow sectionals, kept on one pace only after straightening.
At rear, settled 7.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
At rear, travelled 7.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow tempo, ran on nicely.
Began slowly, then settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow sectionals, made some late ground.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, never ran on.
Always at rear, never a threat.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, made some late ground.
Sent forward, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened 150M and checked thereafter.
Raced midfield, 4Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, never ran on.
Good break, raced 5th 1 off with cover, switched 3 wide & progress on turn, bumped 400m, driven 300m, quickened to lead 200m, in command.
Speedy break, sat 4th 1 back on rail, shuffled 2 back on turn, switched out 430m, in pocket & bumped rival 400m, in clear 300m, closed but held.
Fast start wide, caught 3 deep no cover, rolled to lead 800m, edged to rail 500m, driven 350m, headed 200m, boxed on one pace.
Broke OK, settled rail midfield, forced way out 400m & driven, kept on soundly, just missed frame.
Fast start, sat 3rd 1 off with cover, easy progress to 2nd turning in, shaken up 350m, outpaced in run home.
Taken back to rail in rear, 6L back & hard-ridden into stretch, stayed on for solid inroads.
Bustled early 3 wide to settle midfield 1 off with cover, switched out & driven home turn, bumped 400m, out-paced in run & tapered out.
Smart start but bustled & outpaced, dropped back 3 deep no cover behind midfield, driven wide final turn, plugged on same speed.
Sharp start & led 1000m, soon to rail & headed 800m, 1 back on rail in 3rd turning in, hard-ridden but soon out-paced & weakened in run.
Slow start, raced 2 off in rear, shifted out & ridden 430m, plugged on in tepid run home.
Broke OK, settled 3 wide with cover near rear, driven wide final turn & plodded on tamely.
Started well, snagged back to race 3 wide at tail, taken wider & driven 430m, found nothing & plodded to wire.
Missed break, recovered to race rail behind midfield, switched centre track 400m, found nothing in run home.
Tardy start & bustled, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, pressure & shuffled back 500m, struggled & faded out.
Smart break out wide, sat close-up 3 wide no cover, shaken up 500m, hard-ridden to lead 200m, drew clear, workmanlike.
Taken behind from wide gate, raced at tail 1 off, switched out & driven 400m, closed off gradually to claim 2nd close home.
Decent break, slotted 1 off with cover midfield, switched 3 wide & driven 400m, crowded in run, battled to 2nd 150m, lost place last stride.
Veered right at start & barged rival, raced rail midfield, shifted out & driven 400m, kept on for late headway.
Reared & bumped start, lost ground & detached at tail, rolled to sit 3 wide just fore of rear, shifted wider & driven 400m, closed off soundly.
Fast break widest, sat close 2nd outside leader, edged to lead 350m, soon driven, emptied & headed 200m, faded in run home.
Tardy start, rail & niggled 1000m to behind midfield, off rail & driven 400m, switched out but stuck for run 150m, closed late for daylight.
Broke well & ridden early to track pace 1 off, ridden turning in, kept on same speed.
Good speed to lead, to rail 1300m, under pressure & headed 350m, battled on all out, tapered to wire.
Taken back at break, caught 3 wide with cover & rolled to midfield 800m, close enough when driven 400m, found little & tapered to wire.
Broke OK, settled back 1 off in rear rank, niggled 1200m, ridden for progress 600m, switched out & boxed on evenly in stretch.
Sluggish start, bustled early, niggled along on rail in rear, under the pump approaching home turn, plodded on one pace.
Fast start, raced rail 1 back, ridden 400m, drifted off rail under pressure, struggled & weakened out.
Broke OK, bustled early, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, switched out 600m, struggling when crowded & off heels 350m, no extra.
Pushed to sit 1L off the good pace 2 wide, closed off strongly and drifted away 250M to score.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, pace good, ran on well for 2nd but never got closer to the winner.
Very slow away, pushed to obtain a midfield spot along the fence, 4.5Ls off the good pace, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 6Ls off the good pace along the fence, blocked most straight, not properly tested.
Eased back, 7Ls off the good pace on the rails, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Pushed early but not muster, 7Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Pushed forward to take rail and led by 1L at good pace, reduced quickly 400M.
Eased back, 9Ls off the good pace along the fence, made minor ground 200M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 6Ls off the good pace 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, flattened 250M.
Eased back, 9Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made some ground 200M.
Pushed forward, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, emptied 250M.
Jumped OK, driven between horses to get good position, settling 3-back, one-off. Peeled out 500m, surged forward to hit front 300m, coasted home for easy win.
Restrained, settling 4-back along fence. Switched out 500m, picked up momentum from 300m, doing best work at finish.
No early pace, settling at rear away from fence. Taken wide entering straight, switched further out 300m to get clear running, finished well down centre track.
Jumped with field, ridden along to hold rail position, settling 3-back from leader. Came off fence 350m and kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Jumped well, ridden along early to hold one-off position 3-back from leader. Kept on steadily in straight.
Taken in from wide draw, settling behind midfield away from fence. Taken out 600m, was widest at 300m, kept on steadily.
Jumped fairly, hard ridden to hold position in midfield. Shuffled back turn, taken wide in straight, one-paced. Had substantial blood in trachea.
Jumped best but held wide by inside horses. Rolled forward to punch the breeze in 3rd place before finding cover turn. Got clear run top of straight but limited response.
Jumped well, led for a few strides before settling behind leader. Urged forward entering straight but soon beaten.
Began fairly, outpaced and clear last back stretch. Ran past beaten horses final stages.
Jumped in air at start, losing ground. In last pair throughout. Finished with substantial mucus in trachea. Jockey reported horse coughed on way to start. See racing incidents.
Pressed forward from wide draw, took lead 1400m and set fast pace to straight where soon beaten. Ride queried. Unacceptable performance. See racing incident.
Settled well in 5th never far off the pace, loomed behind leading pair mid-straight, responded to determined riding inside 100M, got up just in time.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, raced without cover for most of the trip, quickened well to join leader 150M, held narrow lead inside 100M, fought on, caught last stride.
Left with no cover from 1200M, strode forward to the lead passing 1100M, kept on well turning home, headed 150M, rallied towards the finish, narrowly beaten.
Held up at the rear 7-8Ls off the pace, driven nearing 500M, did best work final 200M, motored home to clinch 4th near line but not quite got to the leaders.
Up with early pace, sat close up in 4th making the turn, kept up the chase in straight, steadied 150M, every chance thereafter but always held by first few.
Reserved in a 2-wide position behind midfield, travelled well enough early and middle stages, shifted wide 550M, made some progress early straight but not reached leaders, one paced final 150M.
Dropped back to race on the outside of rear pair, driven along 500M but found less than expected, stayed on mildly over final 300M, never seriously threatened.
Held up towards the rear, saved ground along the fence, stayed on but never going the pace to challenge over this inadequate trip.
Set early pace, relinquished the lead passing 1100M, outdashed inside 350M, weakened gradually.
Settled in midfield, travelled well enough but failed to pick up the pace inside 400M when placed under pressure. (Jockey unable to offer explanation for the horse's below par performance.)
Slotted into a 2-wide position in midfield, kept on same speed passing 400M, weakened out of contention mid-straight.
Jumped OK, pressed forward to lead on settling, cut to rail 1000m, set steady sections, kicked clear 400m, kept on well.
Missed the start, caught up to field 1200m, improved position around turn, peeled out 600m, ran on well final 400m.
Fractious in gate but jumped OK, pressed forward to sit outside leader. Battled on gamely in straight.
Ridden along early to hold box seat behind leader. Came off fence to challenge 400m but unable close gap.
Began OK holding on to fence 4-back from leader. Saved ground turn, looked chance entering straight, one-paced.
Ridden along early but held wide without cover. Rolled forward 3-wide before turn, looked chance entering straight, one-paced.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield with cover to turn, switched out 600m to get clear run, kept on one-paced in straight.
Ridden forward from jump, settling three-back along fence. Switched out 3-wide entering straight, one-paced under hard riding.
Ridden forward from wide draw, settling between horses with cover 1200m. Switched out 600m, rolled forward to be 3rd entering straight, kept on until flattened 100m.
Began awkwardly, difficult to settle, drifting to rear. Got close to heels before turn, taken very wide into straight, found little.
Began OK, ridden along in midfield but difficult to settle from 1100m. Shifted out shortly after and continued to race fiercely. One-paced.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear. Clear last into turn, found little in straight.
Began fairly, ridden along but held wide without cover back stretch. Shuffled back turn, wide into straight, plodded.
Last on settling, taken across behind runners but kept away from fence. Last into straight becoming tailed off.
Taken back from wide gate, raced at rear, 6-7 lengths back on rail, saved ground and kept to inside after turning, finished off strongly to overhaul rivals and scored by 1/2 length.
Away with them, pushed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, ridden 300M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Average to begin, raced 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, soft run to turn, finished off well in straight, just missed 2nd.
Began fairly, difficult to settle early, raced 2 wide with cover in midfield, 4 lengths back, taken wider after turning in, ran home strongly to make frame.
Jumped fairly, raced 2 wide with cover, 3 lengths back, ridden vigorously before turning in, closed off well but posed no threat to the first few.
Began well, raced prominently 1 out 1 back, travelled well, improved from 400M, ran on only one-paced.
Jumped well from gate 13, raced outside the leader in 2nd to the home turn, made no progress in straight and weakened gradually.
Average break, unable to slot in from tricky gate, raced 3 wide without cover after 1200M, there to turn, ran on one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 8 lengths back, under pressure on turning, made minor progress in straight.
Restrained after start, raced 6 lengths back on rail behind midfield, ridden turning in, made little progress final 400M.
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, taken widest after turning in, made some minor ground in straight but set a big task.
Began fairly from the widest gate, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5-6 lengths back, made no progress in straight, eased late.
Slightly slowly out, raced 2 wide with cover behind midfield, difficult to settle 1000M, ridden after turning in, made no progress.
Moderately away, sat behind the leader on rail, travelled well, but showed no response to riding in straight and faded thereafter.

Jumped well from a poor draw, travelled with leaders 3-wide without cover, hit the front entering straight, soon drew clear.
Ridden along early, not far off in 5th or 4th within 3L of pace, fought on steadily without threatening.
Slowly away, settled well behind, finished off race well down the centre of straight, nearest at finish.
Began moderately, ridden along behind midfield, saved ground turning in, ran on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield, came closer off Rock before forced to steady coming out of far side, ran home one-paced from forward of midfield into straight.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon picked up on rails to join the leaders, steadied on rails and lost position 600 metres out, plugged on from 1L 3rd into straight.
Jumped fairly, made steady headway to take up running passing 1000 metres, soon headed under pressure after straightening.
Moderate start, travelled one from last, saved ground turning in, never nearer.
Jumped moderately, ridden along in rear of midfield, found nothing in straight.
Began from a poor gate, raced wide without cover throughout, with leaders briefly, gradually dropped back to forward of midfield, folded up in straight.
Jumped moderately from the widest gate, niggled along in rear of midfield, faded into straight.
Slotted in near the 1400m to race 1 off in 4th position, had cover. Kicked clear at the furlong and went to the post strongly.
Raced 2 wide, midfield with cover. Peeled out approaching the home turn and ran on steadily.
Had every possible chance after box seating. Was dour in the final stretch.
Parked worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Swung widest on the home turn and finished off steadily.
Pushed forward and camped outside the leader in 2nd position. Gradually faded over the last 150m.
Sent forward and led at a leisurely tempo on the fence. Was a beaten conveyance early in the home straight.
Slowly away, racing 4th from the rear, on the rails with cover. Made little headway while racing towards the inside in the home stretch.
Slow to begin travelling at the rear of the field on the paint with cover. Passed tiring horses in the run to the line.
Settled in last position, 1 of with cover. Just plodded down the running.
Traveled 3 back the fence, had cover. Faded over the final furlong.
Checked badly after the 1400m, settling behind midfield the fence with cover. Never recovered and was one paced in the home stretch.
Went back from a wide gate and settled 3rd from the rear, 1 off with cover. Failed to close off.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader with cover, under pressure turning in, ran on strongly to score by a short head.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on nicely to get 2nd.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 3/4L, challenged 800M, kept on well to the line for 3rd.
Slow to muster, then travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, dashed well for 4th.
Settled in front of midfield about 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace to the line without threatening.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung wide rounding the Home Turn, ran on fairly.
Eased back from a wide gate, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, one paced after straightening.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled 11Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Raced midfield, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Occupied the box seat early, then switched to park outside the leader near 800M, weakened 250M.
Settled worse than midfield, travelled wide without cover throughout, flattened rounding the Home Turn.
Broke well, settled back on rail, nudged to midfield 800m, ridden 500m, switched very wide into stretch, strong run to lead 100m, drew clear easily.
Smart start, settled 1 off with cover fore of midfield, bustled 500m, wide into stretch, quickened to lead 250m, all out & headed 100m, no extra.
Taken back at break, raced rail near rear, outpaced 900m, switched out & driven into stretch, closed off well to just miss 2nd.
Fast break to lead, headed 1000m & settled 3rd 1 back 1 off, shifted 3 wide home turn & pressed lead 300m, led until headed 250m & boxed on evenly.
Missed break & at tail, progress to race 2nd last, ridden along 600m, 8L back 400m, very wide into stretch, stayed on for sound inroads.
Snagged back initially, raced 1 off with cover near rear, ridden 3 wide 600m, very wide into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Smart start, bustled to race rail 4th, driven 600m, outpaced turning in & weakened.
Fast start out wide, caught midfield 3 wide no cover, driven 400m, wide into stretch & checked in run 300m, plodded home weakly.
Fast start, snagged back to midfield 1 off, niggled 600m, ridden 500m, found little in tepid run home.
Broke well, speed to edge lead 3 wide 1000m, soon slotted 1 off in disputed lead, driven into stretch, headed 280m & faded tamely thereafter.
Tardy start & outpaced, soon at tail, driven 600m, struggled in run home.
Broke OK, rousted to press lead on rail 1000m, disputed lead in very close 2nd until emptied 300m & faded out.
Broke well to sit 4th on rail, switched 1 off 1100m, shifted 3 wide 800m, increased tempo in duel for lead, forged to fore 300m, tapered late, held on.
Tardy break, sat rail midfield, popped 1 off 900m, shifted in to rail 600m, switched out 500m, wide out of turn, strong closer, just failed.
Speed early, snagged to 3rd on rail, edged 1 off for progress 800m, disputed lead 600m, driven home turn, headed 300m, battled but lost 2nd late.
Taken behind to tail on rail, 7L back when driven & switched out home turn, closed off for solid gains.
Broke OK, camped 1 off with cover in rear, driven 500m, 6L back & very wide into stretch, stayed on for sound inroads.
Broke well, covered in midfield 1 off, edged 3 wide no cover 1000m, driven 600m for progress to 4th, outpaced on turn, battled on dourly.
Rousted to settle 2nd 1 back on rail, switched 1 off briefly 700m & soon shuffled back, driven 500m, plugged on dourly.
Slow start, raced rail near rear, minor progress out of backstretch, squeezed on rail 600m, lost momentum, plugged on one pace thereafter.
Stumbled start & crowded, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, ridden 600m, emptied turning in & faded.
Driven to lead, to rail 1200m, opened long lead 1000m, restrained back to pack backstretch, headed 600m, under pressure 500m & faded out.
Broke OK, caught wide midfield no cover, outpaced & ridden 500m, wide into stretch, found nothing in run.
Strong restraint early to race 3 wide with cover near rear, ridden 600m, wide & under pressure turning in, found nothing.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250M to score by a short head.
Settled in box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on strongly and led 200M, only beaten by a narrow margin in last few strides.
At back, 4.5Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 200M, beaten in 3rd only by narrow margin.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 300M, little dash when clear, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide, 2Ls off the slow pace, ran on well to the line.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield along the fence, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 100M.
Hard ridden forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 150M flattened.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, not tested.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Eased at start, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M, checked badly 100M.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 0.5L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon emptied 200M.
Jumped best, ridden along inside leader, grabbing box seat back stretch. Saved ground final turn, picked up momentum along fence in straight, hit from 100m, kept on well.
Pressed forward, taking lead on settling. Set steady pace, kicked ahead entering straight, collared 100m, kept on well.
Began well, pressed forward 3-wide before settling outside leader back stretch. Boxed on gamely in straight under hard riding.
Ridden along inside leader early, before settling one-off, one-back from 1000m. Taken a little wide entering straight, kept on steadily.
Began OK but bumped shortly after start. Not pressured settling 4-back the fence. Came off rail 600m to make run and kept on fairly. Injured right front tendon.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling in one-off position initially before taken 3-wide with cover 800m. Very wide into straight, kept on gamely.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. Kept in one-off position back stretch. Taken out half way up the home straight and kept on fairly.
Taken out shortly after start, the cut in to one-off position 1400m. Kept on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Taken across behind runners to fence before first turn. Clear last from 800m, ran past beaten horses final 200m.
Pressed forward taking first turn 3-wide without cover. Rolled forward 800m when pace slacked and was second around final turn. Gave ground soon after entering straight.
Ridden along early and trapped 3-wide with cover. Rolled forward entering straight but soon beaten. One-paced.
Jumped well, mixed it with early leaders before cutting in to rail back stretch. Put under whip entering straight but found nothing, Not ridden out final stages.
Settled in midfield about 4Ls off the pace, went for inside run turning in, made stealthy progress passing 300M, got up last stride.
Took keen hold in mid-division, shifted out to 3-wide halfway, ran on well when switched to outside turning home, led 50M out, caught last stride.
Strode forward, always prominent behind the lead, responded well when driven 300M, led 200M to 50M, not pace of first two final stages.
Fractious in stalls and slowly away, settled near the rear early stages, strode closer to pace passing 1100M, kept on evenly inside 300M, well held by first three.
From draw 12 soon taken across behind runners, detached in last first 900M, moved closer over the turn, closed strongly from off the pace.
Held up near last, niggled along 600M out, stayed on mildly over final 300M, not reached leaders.
Caught wide no cover from 1300M, strode forward to take lead entering back straight, quickened up the pace in 3rd quarter, headed inside 200M, faded towards the line.
Not far off early stages, shuffled back to near the rear when the race tempo quickened up halfway, made some progress final 300M.
Caught 3-wide making the first turn, strode forward to track leader, struggled for pace passing 300M, no extra mid-straight.
Positively ridden, led 1300M-950M, still within striking distance turning home, kept on one paced in straight, steadied nearing 100M, eased down.
Slow to begin, raced behind field early stages, dropped back to the rear back straight, unbalanced 600M and soon under pressure, not quickened and eased towards the line.
Up with early pace, shuffled back to midfield middle stages, came under serious pressure 500M, dropped away rapidly. (Irregular Heart Rhythm.)

Made all the running after beginning from the one draw, held on well.
Jumped well, niggled along to hold place settling outside the leader far side, came under pressure to challenge inside final 200 metres but unable to quicken to threaten.
Began moderately, behind midfield before dropping further back far side, ran on well down the centre of home straight to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly, settled on rails in midfield, saved ground turning in, baulked for a run early in straight, finished off race nicely inside final 200 metres.
Settled in midfield from a middle draw, gained a little closer around the bend, kept on steadily without quickening.

Jumped moderately, settled in last few on rails, commenced move coming out of far side, baulked behind runners when just worse than midfield around home bend, fought on well under pressure in the run home. (Lame next day)
Jumped well, never far off and wide without cover most of way, kept on before fading closing stages.
Never far off to straight, faded gradually under pressure.
Taken back from the widest gate, trailed the field into straight, made significant progress down centre. (Tactic questioned)
Soon dropped to last few after beginning from a poor gate, ran past well-beaten runners in the run home.
Jumped well, settled not far off in 5th on rails, soon weakened in straight.
Jumped well from a poor gate, settled behind midfield, baulked briefly 300 metres out, no further impression.
Towards the rear, made short-lived effort when widest rounding home bend, kept on in midfield early in straight, weakened 200 metres out.
Jumped well from a poor gate, drifted backward early stages before making swift progress out wide down far side to soon reach midfield, remained same rounding home bend, soon weakened under pressure.
Ridden along from barrier rise and led early before handing up near the 900m, and taking up 2nd position, racing 1 off. Showed plenty of courage to keep going and won gamely.
Travelled midfield, on the rails with cover. Angled out and started to improve approaching the home turn, finished off well.
Made its run from 2nd last position, 2-3 wide on the circle, with cover. Straightened up nicely and made good ground through the field in the run home.
Travelled back in the field, close to the running rail, had cover. Made up steady ground to fill the frame.
Missed the start, after jumping awkwardly, travelling in last position, 2-3 deep with cover. Straightened widest and ran on soundly.
Coursed 3 wide without cover, whilst racing on the speed. Began to yield ground 150m out. (blood in trachea)
Parked ahead of midfield, 1 off with cover. Failed to go on with it after having every possible chance. Began to tire after the furlong.
Raced midfield, 1 off with cover. Was running one empty after the 400m, and weakened in the run to the line.
Camped 3 back the fence, had cover. Was a beaten horse early in the home straight.
Didn't show any early pace and settled midfield, 3 wide with cover. Gave ground rounding the home turn. (To trial)
Did plenty of work to go forward and cross to lead on the fence after the 800m. Was a spent force early in the straight.
Couldn't go the early speed of the race and drifted back to settle ahead of midfield, with cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Hard ridden forward to cross, then parked outside the leader at slightly slow sectionals, hung on strongly to score by a short head.
Ridden forward to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slightly slow tempo, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Camped handy, settled 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slightly slow pace, ran on steadily to get 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slightly slow sectionals, dashed on strongly.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader along the rail, despite hampered by the slightly slow tempo, dashed well.
Settled in front of midfield about 2Ls behind the leader on the fence at slightly slow pace, kept on one pace until 100M weakened.
At rear, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slightly slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slightly slow tempo, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slightly slow pace, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, stayed on until 250M flattened.
Never a factor.
Raced midfield, trapped 3 wide with cover, never looked likely.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and shared the lead at slightly slow sectionals, emptied soon after straightening.
Speed to lead widest, crossed to rail 950m, ridden & kicked on 400m, drew clear & maintained momentum for safe win.
Tardy start, settled rail near rear, 6L back & driven 400m, switched out & leaned on rival 250m, strong closer to 2nd close home.
Fast break on rail, switched out & settled 1 off with cover 4th, driven & switched out turning in, flat-footed in run until stayed on late for 3rd.
Slow start, ridden forward to race rail behind midfield, 5L back & driven turning in, stayed on for notable gains.
Broke Ok, rolled on rail to1 back 3rd at 800m, driven between horses 350m, battled all out to 2nd 200m, edged out of frame late.
Broke well, raced rail midfield, driven & switched out into stretch, staying on when checked close to heels 150m, ran on last strides.
Sharp start & bustled, raced wide no cover & progress to 2nd 1 off 800m, ridden 450m, battled on but emptied & faded final 100m.
Sharp start & driven, outpaced & soon niggled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven into stretch, boxed on same speed.
Fair break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, shuffled back 600m, driven 400m, one-paced & bumped 250m, found little.
Rousted to decent start, handy when bumped 1000m, shuffled back & 3 wide no cover 800m, 6th & driven wide 430m, faded in run.
Taken back at break, sat 1 off with cover near rear, switched wide home turn, driven 400m, plodded home tamely.
Missed break, raced at tail, shaken up 430m, found little in tepid stretch run.
Broke OK, rowed along 3 wide with cover, wide & driven into stretch, struggled in run & weakened out.
Broke OK, niggled initially & over-raced, bumped rival 1000m, snagged to midfield 1 off with cover 950m, driven 430m, found nil & faded.
Fast break to settle 1 back on rail, 2 back 1200m, shuffled back on turn, switched out 430m but stuck in pocket, clear 250m, led 100m, cosy.
Bustled to smart start, sat 1 off with cover handy, switched out turning in & driven to lead 300m, tapered & headed 100m, just held on to 2nd.
Taken behind to rail near rear, to tail 1000m, 3 wide & minor advance 800m, strong run centre track to just miss 2nd.
Snagged back at break to 1 off near rear, progress 800m, switched wide turning in, driven to 2nd 280m, boxed on same speed & lost place in run.
Good break, parked rail midfield, shuffled back 800m, driven 400m, stuck on heels 375m, switched out 300m & closed off for sound gains.
Eased to rear, pace good, lack room early straight, finished off quite well when clear.
Broke OK, camped 1 off with cover behind midfield, switched 3 wide with cover 1100m & progress, very wide home turn, boxed on one pace.
Tardy start & nudged to sit 1 off with cover midfield, ridden turning in, stayed on evenly until faded out closing stages.
Led 1st turn & to rail, headed 1200m & penned 1 back, ridden 500m, trapped in pocket 350m, switched out too late 250m, chance gone.
Taken back at break, raced at tail, slight advance 1off 1200m, driven 430m, one-paced in run.
Fair start, rolled to 3 wide no cover 3rd at 1500m, slotted 1 off 1300m, ridden to clear 2nd turning in, emptied & swamped 350m, plodded tamely.
Broke OK, caught 3 deep with cover fore of midfield, driven 3 deep no cover to 4th out of backstretch, hard-ridden home turn but no extra.
Fast start to sit 2nd 1st turn 1 off, led 1300m & soon to rail, shaken up 350m, all out & headed 300m, faded weakly.
Tardy start, sat 3 wide with cover near rear, to tail 1200m, ridden 1000m & minor advance 4 wide, very wide home turn, found nothing.
Pushed early, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, accelerated quickly around the field 500M, kicked away 300M.
Midfield, 5Ls off the leader on the fence, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
At rear, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to obtain the box seat, ran on until 150M flattened.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, ran on until 150M flattened.
At rear, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, made ground 300M.
3Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, moved forward 400M, flattened 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 3Ls off the leader, held up and checked 300M, just ran on.
At back, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, never improved.
Very slow away, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, on heels 400M, no progress.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L, ran on until 200M emptied.
Never a factor.
Trapped 3 wide no cover throughout, 2Ls off the leader, faded 350M.
Pushed to sit outside the lead, dropped off quickly 400M.
Jumped well, taken straight to front, set steady pace to course proper, kicked clear 350m, won comfortably, easing down final 50m.
Began fairly, ridden along towards rear, rolled forward from 600m, clear 2nd from 300m, kept on well without threatening winner.
Shifted in and bumped start, dropping to last on settling. Stayed along outer fence, picked up momentum gradually before switching in 300m to get run. Kept on steadily.
Began fairly, quickly taken to outer fence, made ground from 700m to 400m, turning one-paced final 200m. Had substantial blood in trachea.
Began OK, outpaced and dropped to last pair. Switched in to centre track approaching 400m and finished off nicely.
Began well, then got head up and lay in early stages behind pace. Settled better reaching course proper, turning one-paced.
Jumped well, taken forward to sit inside leading pair to 400m, under pressure from 300m, gave ground gradually.
Quickly into stride racing outide leader before shifting in from 700m. Under pressure to hold position from 600m, hard ridden from 500m but failed to respond, giving ground.
Bumped start, ridden along to race in midfield behind pace. Under pressure from 500m, shifted in off heels 200m, steadied 100m when disappointed for run. Faded.
Began only fairly, reluctant to stretch out initially, then picked up speed down centre track to get within range at 400m before running out of steam and slipping back.
Switched off to a rearward spot 5-6Ls off the pace, shifted out for run 350M, quickened up impressively to lead inside 150M, forged clear for a decisive victory.
Dropped back to last, switched away from fence passing 500M, stayed on strongly to go 2nd near 50M, but could not gain on the winner.
Settled in mid-division along the fence, badly held up for clear running turning in, unable to be tested until 100M, ran on well to snatch 3rd.
Tracked leader, loomed a threat at 250M, kept on steadily to the finish but could not match finishing pace of first 3 over final stages.
Raced outside leader, held narrow lead 250M, headed by winner 150M, swamped final 50M and beaten to 5th.
Held up towards the rear, switched widest on straightening, stayed on well from off the pace.
Slow to begin, recovered to race behind midfield, lacked a clear path entering straight, stayed on final 100M and looked to have more to offer.
Slightly slow out, sent forward and crossed to the lead 850M, headed nearing 200M, faded towards the line.
Held up behind midfield and settled within 4Ls of leaders, stayed on fairly when driven 400M out, never reached leaders.
Unable to slot in and caught wide without cover in midfield, kept on same pace in straight and no threat from 100M.
Held up in midfield along the 3-path, kept on same pace turning home, never threatened.
Travelled keenly in early stages, moved closer to leaders passing 900M and ranged up 3-wide turning home, run ended mid-straight and weakened.
Up with early pace, chased leaders 2-wide from 800M , outdashed passing 300M, weakened towards the line.
Not hurried early stages, reserved behind midfield and no closer than 3-wide throughout, found little under pressure, eased when well beaten.
Jumped OK, ridden along to lead on settling, kicked clear entering straight, battled on under hard riding to hold off late challenge.
Jumped with field, tried to find cover but held 3-wide at rear, swung very wide entering straight, loomed as likely winner 200m, just failed.
Slow, given reminders, picked up along rail, improved position around turn, behind horse entering straight, finished off well when clear 350m.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to last before turn. No clear run entering straight, switched out 200m, finished strongly.
Began OK, outpaced, settled at rear. Saved ground turn, forced to switch in 250m to get run, ran on steadily.
Ridden along early to hold position, unbalanced and lost ground approaching 900m, stayed on rail around turn, kept on steadily until flattened late.
Ridden to get forward position from awkward draw and held 3-wide into turn. Had clear run in straight but only one-paced.
Bumped soon after start, taken closer to fence and in last pair approaching turn. Swung widest into straight and ran on steadily.
Began awkwardly, ridden to hold midfield position along fence. Caught between tiring horses entering straight and taken back through field. Ran on fairly when clear 150m.
Began OK, pressed on behind leading bunch, steadied approaching 900m, got head up and raced ungenerously. Lost position top of straight, one-paced thereafter.
Pressed forward from outside draw and took first turn 6-wide. Taken out further 900m, continued to press forward, 3rd into straight, tired quickly from 350m.
Ridden along behind midfield to 800m, shuffled back slightly around turn, boxed on one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw, held 5-wide first turn, bumped 900m and taken out without cover from 600m. Steadied 250m when giving ground.
Jumped best, led for a few strides before sitting outside leader to and around turn. Gave ground shortly after entering straight. Had substantial blood in trachea.
Began well, unable to slot in from tricky gate, raced 3 wide and without cover throughout, hit the front after turning in and scored by 1-1/2 length.
Fairly to begin, rolled forward, raced 3 wide with cover, 2 lengths back, ridden turning in, finished off well but posed no threat to the winner.
Moderately away, raced 3 lengths back in midfield, there to turn, ridden 400M, finished off well to get 3rd.
Away with them, raced 2 lengths back on rail, travelled well throughout, did not have a clear run until 300M, but only ran on fairly.
Away in line, raced 3 lengths back on rail before the first turn, taken to 2 wide at turn, no clear running early in straight, made some progress after getting clear.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide with cover, 1-1/2 length back, travelled well throughout, ridden after turning in, made some progress early in straight, weakened in the closing stages.
Jumped fairly, raced 3-4 lengths back on rail, saved ground, ridden turning in, unable to obtain clear running early in straight, closed off well final 150M, checked near the finish.
Slightly slow out, raced at tail throughout, taken to widest in straight and made minor progress.
Taken back from widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4-5 lengths back, made little progress in straight, only passed a few tired horses.
Taken back from wide draw, raced at rear, 5-6 lengths back on rail, saved ground and kept to inside after turning in, found no daylight in straight and severely checked 100M.
Moderately away, pushed early but failed to muster speed, raced 2 wide with cover at rear, 4-5 lengths back, taken wide in straight, but failed to close off.
Began fairly from the wide draw, unable to slot in, raced wide with no cover, 4 lengths back behind midfield, weakened gradually after turning in.
Began well, pushed early to fight for the lead, raced 2 wide throughout, showed no response to riding in straight and faded thereafter.
Jumped well, sent forward for the lead, raced on rail throughout, ridden 400M, but showed no response, weakened thereafter.

Jumped moderately, settled behind midfield, commenced move out wide on top of home bend, quickened to hit the front over 200 metres out, fought on dourly against runner-up's serious challenge to prevail in the bobbing of heads.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw settling in last few, quickened well to draw level inside final 200 metres holding every chance, but only to be pipped at post.
Jumped well, amongst leaders early, gradually settled just better than midfield, did not find much room early in straight, finished off race nicely.
Sluggish at start, gradually picked up to midfield on rails, hampered and lost position coming out of back straight, remained behind midfield turning in, kept on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well, soon taken back to travel in midfield, took closer order around the bend, shared close-up 3rd into straight, faded gradually inside final 200 metres.

Began awkwardly, niggled along on rails to gain a prominent position early, taken 1-back coming out of far side before becoming 2-back on top of home bend, badly baulked early in straight, but produced good late impression close to home.
Jumped fairly, travelled at the back, took closer order along rails rounding home bend, baulked for a run early in straight, kept on same pace closing stages.
Settled well behind, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped fairly, gradually picked up to a prominent spot chasing leader into straight, still in touch early on but folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Driven to slender lead early stages, ceded advantage to settle behind eventual last-finisher coming out of far side, held up behind the weakening horse most of straight.
Missed the break badly, detached from main field before reaching the tail-end on top of home bend, ran home one-paced.
Jumped moderately from the widest gate, pressed on to take up running coming out of far side, led the field until overhauled inside final 300 metres.
Ridden patiently, third from the rear, 2-3 wide with cover. Rounded the home turn widest and closed off with plenty of purpose to have the race in its keeping 50m out.
Travelled on the rails with cover, behind midfield. Worked its way out into the clear in the run home and hit the line well.
Camped ahead of midfield, 2 wide with cover. Hit the front at the 150m, grudgingly gave way in the run to the post.
Made its run from 2nd last, after travelling close to the running rail with cover. Looked for runs through the field in the straight and closed off soundly.
Parked midfield, 2 deep with cover. Ran on steadily without threatening.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settling midfield the fence, had cover. Kept grinding away in the home straight.
Led early along the fence before being joined in the lead and travelling 2nd after the 900m. Kicked well clear early in the straight but was swamped near the 150m.
Jumped well then raced keenly in the early stages when looking for cover. Eventually coursed 1 out I back near the 800m. Couldn't find any extra under pressure & faded in the run to the line.
Box seated early prior to settling 3 back the fence. Kept battling away until the 250m, couldn't sustain effort and weakened soon after.
Left 3 wide without cover on the circle, racing midfield. Was never a factor thereafter and only plodded down the running.
Effectively box seated after the 800m. Had no real excuses and was well beaten approaching the 400m.
Went forward midrace after being wide & unable to secure cover back in the field. Led narrowly 1 off near the 900m. Failed to finish off.
Reared as the start was effected, missing the break considerably, settling a long last. Was never in the hunt and finished well back.
Raced worse than midfield, 2 wide with cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, dashed on strongly to score by 3.5Ls.
At rear, settled 8Ls 3 wide with cover early, made an early moved from 1100M to settle 3Ls off the leader, ran on steadily for 2nd.
Ridden forward to share the lead on the fence at slow sectionals, kept on well to the line for 3rd.
Taken back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slow tempo, dashed well in straight.
Settled worse than midfield 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide rounding the Home Turn, made some ground but without threatening.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, ran on only fairly. (Lame right front leg)
Settled in front of midfield 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, however was held up rounding the Home Turn, made some ground when clear.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the slow pace, kept on one pace to the line.
Sent forward to obtain the box seat, despite benefited by the slow sectionals, never ran on.
Settled in front of midfield 3Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, no turn of foot.
Sent forward to park outside the leader at slow tempo, weakened over the last furlong. (Blood in trachea)
Failed to muster early, then made an early moved from 1200M to settle 3Ls off the slow pace 3 wide without cover, soon emptied after straightening.
Always at rear, never a threat.
Smart start, raced 3rd 1 off no cover, forced 3 wide home turn, shaken up 400m & coaxed to lead 220m, in command to wire.
Fast break, settled 2nd 1 back on fence, switched 1 off turning in, driven 400m, battled on but always held in 2nd.
Speed to lead, to rail 800m, scooted clear, kicked 400m, overhauled 220m but remained in touch & battled gamely to wire.
Broke well, caught 3 wide no cover handy, 4 wide 4th turning in, hard-ridden 400m, kept on resolutely without threatening lead.
Slow break but mustered to sit rail 5th, ridden turning in, switched out 300m & kept on soundly.
Fair break, raced midfield 1 off with cover, driven 400m but crowded on heels, not clear running & kept on evenly.
Broke OK, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, wide into stretch, hard driven 350m, stayed on soundly.
Slow start, raced rail in rear, driven 400m, stayed on for minor inroads until tight for room late.
Tardy start, raced rail behind midfield, shifted out & driven 400m, boxing on evenly when off heels 150m, not clear run & eased thereafter.
Sluggish break, camped 1 off in rear, driven turning in, plugged on moderately.
Snagged back to last trio 3 wide, mustered 800m to sit fore of rear rank 1 off, shifted out & driven 400m, plodded on tepidly.
Broke will widest, over-raced early & slotted 3 wide with cover midfield, wide home turn & driven, found nothing & faded tamely.
Broke OK, raced rail midfield, shaken up & switched off fence 400m, gradual progress under hard drive to lead on inner last strides.
Smart start, settled 4th 1 back on rail, 3rd when switched out 420m, shaken up 400m & led 320m, all out when headed close home.
Fair break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, wide into stretch & driven 400m, wound up gradually, stayed on well to edge 3rd.
Fast break, settled back 5th 1 off with cover, driven 450m, kept on evenly to wire.
Broke well widest, raced 3 wide behind midfield, wide into stretch & driven, stayed on one pace.
Settled back at break, over-raced 3 wide near rear, ridden at tail turning in, widest in stretch run, plugged on for sound inroads.
Missed break & detached, recovered to race last pair 1 off, shifted out home turn, driven 400m, stayed on for dour headway centre track.
Fast break wide & nudged to lead, to rail 1100m, pressed 800m & shaken up 400m, found little & headed 320m, faded thereafter.
Fast start, crossed 1100m to sit 2nd 1 off, shuffled 1 back 1 off 4th 800m, switched out & driven home turn, outpaced & boxed on moderately.
Tardy start, raced rail near rear, switched out home turn, checked off heels 300m & lost momentum, stayed on for moderate late headway.
Good break, raced 3 wide midfield, mostly without cover, forced wider home turn, boxed on until emptied & faded from 150m.
Sharp break, raced 3 wide no cover 3rd until rolled to press lead 1 off 800m, driven 430m, emptied 300m & faded thereafter.
Slow start & outpaced, rousted to sit rail last pair, shifted out & driven home turn, never a factor in tame run home.
Settled in box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well to win.
Pushed to cross in front, 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 50M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Settled in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 350M, run ended 100M.
Very awkward away, 5.5Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked and checked 300M, dashed well when clear.
Eased at start, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, bumped 450M, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Very slow away, 4.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok in straight.
Very slow away, checked early whilst being shifted across behind runners, 4Ls off the leader on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, held ground in straight.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, under pressure 700M, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Pressed forward, 1L off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, however soon emptied 400M.
Pressed forward, 2Ls off the slow pace 3 wide, faded rapidly 500M.
Bumped start, mustered while edging closer to outer rail. Clear lead from 800m, shaken up and given reminders from 400m, held on well.
Began OK, racing behind midfield close to outer rail. Improved position from 600m, switched in 400m to get clear running, ran on well while laying in under pressure.
One of the first from the gate, ridden along to hold outer rail position 1L from leader, kept battling to the line.
Began well, shared early lead till passed 800m, held together outside leader to 200m, flattened final 100m.
Began well but soon outpaced, dropping to near rear while edging closer to outer fence. Forced to switch in 400m for clear run, kept on steadily.
Began well, settled outside leader from 800m, rolled forward 600m to look a chance at 400m before running out of gas. One-paced from 300m.
Began well, joined chasers behind leader from 800m, put under pressure from 600m, weakened gradually.
Slow into stride, hugged outer rail, making ground from 600m before turning one-paced final 400m.
Began awkwardly, dropping to rear. Raced greenly from 600m, hampered 500m, close to heels 100m, not ridden out. Jockey reported saddle shifted shortly after start.
Began awkwardly, mustered to settle in midfield in centre track. Found little when put under pressure from 500m.
Checked and lost ground start, picked up quickly to midfield while edging closer to outer fence. Found little when put under pressure 500m.
Began fairly, then raced tightly before settling towards rear. Lost position entering course proper and soon beaten.
Crowded out at start and soon last. Found nothing when shaken up from 600m.
Jumped OK but soon under pressure to hold position in midfield. Dropped back quickly from 500m. Rider reported abnormal breathing noises. Found to have substantial blood in trachea.
Restrained in midfield 4Ls off the pace, responded well when taken to clear 450M, hit lead near 200M, strongly challenged by the 2nd late but always had enough to hold on.
Not hurried early stages, settled near the rear and was given a waiting ride, chased Akeed Mofeed strongly from 250M, finished a very creditable 2nd.
Never far off, came through to challenge mid-straight but was readily held by the winner final 200M.
Settled within 3Ls of leader, moved to a striking position 500M out, had every chance in straight, kept on steadily to take 4th.
Tracked the speed along the inside, moved up to join leader 500M, briefly led passing 300M but was unable to sustain his effort into final 200M.
Held up towards the rear, offered no serious response when driven passing 400M, not reached leaders.
Assumed the lead from 1400M, led uncontested to 500M, fought on briefly turning home, weakened 200M out.
Switched off to last, well off the pace early stages, failed to make any progress on the principals over final 400M, never involved.
Close up but caught 3-wide without cover throughout, came under serious pressure 500M, soon no extra.
Began only fairly, moved up to race just off the pace, niggled along to maintain position entering home turn, weakened from 600M and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Began OK, picked up speed to lead on settling before being passed 1050m. Held behind leader at turn, caught flat-footed top of straight, picked up quickly from 100m, pulling clear last 50m.
Began well, pressed forward from wide draw to lead from 1050m. Restrained turn, kicked clear entering straight, still 2L clear 200m, swamped 50m.
Began well but restrained behind leaders in a one-off position. Taken 3-wide entering straight, battled on gamely under being weight.
Jumped with field, restrained in midfield along rail. Saved ground turn, finished off nicely along inside to just miss a place.
Slow into stride, held at rear while edging closoer to rail. Held up for run entering straight, shifted in 400m and ran home nicely.
Began best, not pushed and allowed to settle 3rd along rail to straight. Came off fence 400m but one-paced under hard riding.
Leaning on stall when gate opened and began awkwardly. Ridden along in midfield, shifted out abruptly 700mm, kept on one-paced in straight.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail but difficult to settle passing 1100m. Tightened 800m, one-paced in straight under hard riding.
Ridden along early but unable to cut in and held 3-wide before finding cover around turn. One-paced in straight.
Hampered shortly after start and taken across behind runners at rear. Taken very wide in straight but found little under hard riding.
Began OK, taken across behind runners but kept away from fence. Peeled out 600m to make run but found little when put under pressure.
Began OK, ridden along early settling along rail behind midfield. Came under pressure entering straight, giving ground gradually.
Slow into stride and soon last along rail. Ridden along around turn to improve but found nothing under pressure.
Away with them, pushed to sit outside the leader in 2nd, right there turning in, ridden 300M, just held off late challenger and scored by a nose.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, checked 500M, finished off very well to get 2nd, just missed.
Jumped well, unable to slot in from wide draw, raced 4 wide without cover for the majority of the race, ran home strongly to get 3rd, good effort given workload.
Taken back from wide draw, raced 4 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, improved position at turn, finished off well in straight, just missed 3rd.
Jumped fairly, initially raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, no cover after 900M, ridden before turning in, worked home well in straight, just missed frame.
Blundered start, regathered to take the lead, travelled well throughout, ridden along turning in, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
Fairly to begin, positioned at tail throughout, angled out after turning in, finished off well in straight, nice debut.
Moderate break, positioned prominently 1 out 1 back, ridden after turning in, finished off one-paced.
Began awkwardly, recovered to sit 2-3 lengths back on rail, difficult to settle throughout, made no progress in straight.
Jumped fairly, raced 2 wide with cover in 5th, 3 lengths back, bumped and checked on bend, made no progress in straight. (see racing incidents)
Began fairly, sat a length behind the leader on rail, travelled well to bend, no response to riding in straight.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced 2 wide at rear throughout, found no daylight in straight, never tested.
Jumped with them, raced 5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground and kept to inside after turning in, no clear running in straight, not tested.
Taken back from wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4-5 lengths back, ridden on turn, made no progress in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 6 lengths back, made run down middle after turning in, finished off strongly final 200M to score with some authority.
Jumped well, a shade keen early, raced prominently in 2nd, there to turn, took the lead near 300M, but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began awkwardly, positioned behind the leader on rail, 2-3 lengths back, travelled well to bend, saved ground and finished off well to get 3rd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide with cover in midfield, 7 lengths back, angled out after turning in, ran home well without threatening the first few, dead-heat for 4th.
Began fairly, positioned 8-9 lengths back at rear, 2 wide until 800M, before taken to fence on turn, angled out in straight and finished off well to make frame, dead-heat for 4th.
Slowly away, raced at rear on rail throughout, 9-10 lengths back, ridden after turning in, made decent progress in the middle of the track to be nearest on line.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in 5th, 3-4 lengths back, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 1 out 1 back, all favours to turn, ran home one-paced.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 2 wide at rear, 10 lengths back, under pressure turning, gave a big start but made some progress in straight.
Fairly away, mustered early to sit on rail, 4-5 lengths back in midfield, saved ground but under pressure after turning in, worked home without quickening.
Taken back from a tricky draw, raced at tail along the fence more than 12 lengths back, ridden after turning in, only made minor progress.
Bumped start, showed early speed to take the lead easily and set an even tempo, there to turn but weakened after turning in, eased 150M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, showed no response to riding in straight and eased thereafter.
Drifted back from wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide without cover in the back straight, dropped in on circle in turn, emptied in straight.

Jumped fairly, restrained and obtained cover when leader crossed to rails passing 800 metres, but still raced keenly at times, switched out to challenge from one-back position turning in, hit the front inside final 100 metres.

Jumped nicely from the 6 gate, soon took up running obtaining rails run passing the 800 metre mark and setting a sound pace, unable to sustain effort and headed inside 100 metres, jumped the shadows of the post near line.
Jumped fairly, settled mainly in one-out-two back position to straight, came under pressure on straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Began moderately, niggled along two-back on though one from last of the small field, unable to obtain a clear passage most of way in straight until too late.
Jumped moderately, taken time to muster rushing up to be 1L 2nd 2-wide at Rock, remained similar turning in, yielded ground inside final 200 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped quite well but soon dropped to the back, never a danger.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race 1 out 1 back. Hit the lead near the 150m and dug deep to repel late challenge.
Parked midfield, 2 deep with cover. Got going near the 400m and finished off well.

Lost its position early, and then travelled behind midfield with cover, 1 off. Peeled out and went forward 3 deep after the 500m. Ranged up and looked a winning chance, but peaked on its effort 50m out.
Camped 3rd from the rear, 2-3 wide with cover. Got a nice trail into the race approaching the home turn, made reasonable ground in the straight.
Settled midfield on the rails, had cover. Kept on steadily in the home straight without threatening.
Had every possible chance after box seating. Looked likely to make the frame but weakened on its effort approaching the 50m.
Went back from the outside gate, settling worse than midfield on the paint, had cover. Went to the line one paced.
Raced in 2nd position, 1 off with cover. Was under siege at the 200m, and faded soon after.
Worked forward to lead on the fence approaching the 1200m. Was swamped at the furlong and faded thereafter.
Settled in last position, 3 wide with cover. Was chased along after the 600m, failed to respond, and was a beaten horse turning for home.
Posted behind midfield, 3 deep without cover. Carried wider rounding the home turn, never a factor.
Travelled at the rear of the field racing 2-3 wide with cover. Went forward 4 wide no cover near the 700m, didn't go on with it a finished a long way back.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the slightly fast tempo, dashed well to take the victory by a neck.
Pushed to settle midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slightly fast sectionals, finished off strongly to get 2nd.
Taken back, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slightly fast pace, took off 650M and ran home strongly for 3rd.
At rear, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the slightly fast tempo, ran on nicely for 4th.
Pushed to settle 1L off outside the leader, despite harmed by the slightly fast pace, kept on well to the line.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slightly fast sectionals, hung on well until final 50M flattened.
Prominent with cover, not suited by the slightly fast tempo, kept on one pace to the line, checked final 50M.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite benefited by the slightly fast sectionals, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the slightly fast pace, never looked competitive. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Sent forward to occupy the box seat, harmed by the slightly fast sectionals, flattened soon after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Tardy start, rolled to race handy 4th on rail, advanced 500m to 2nd & switched out turning in, quickened to lead 200m, battled on to wire.
Sharp start & rousted early to race 2nd 1 off, 3rd & forced wider home turn, regained 2nd 150m, always held in run home.
Speedy break & ridden to lead, soon to rail & 2L clear, challenged & driven 300m, headed 200m, tapered in closing stages.
Fair start, raced 3 wide no cover 3rd until 4th at 500m, flat-footed when initially driven turning in, kept on evenly.
Moderate break, raced 1 off with cover midfield, driven into stretch & stayed on evenly.
Slow start & raced rail in rear rank, switched out home turn, stayed on for fair gains under firm drive.
Fast break, soon outpaced & bustled rail behind midfield, under pump 500m, plugged on one pace.
Taken back at break, raced in rear, bumped 600m, some headway on turn, switched out & driven 300m, boxed on one pace.
Snagged back from wide, raced wide in rear, bumped rival 600m, to tail & driven 500m, erratic in stretch but minor late headway.
Slow start, niggled early, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, plodded on tepidly in home stretch.
Smart break, unable to slot & caught wide no cover midfield, scrubbed along throughout, struggled in run home & faded.
Broke OK, caught wide & taken back to race towards rear on outer, wide into stretch, found nothing & eased when beaten.
Slow start, camped rail last pair, shifted out centre track & driven turning in, closed off strongly to lead 50m.
Snagged back to race tail 1 off, switched out for progress 450m, widest into stretch, rattled home mid track to snare 2nd late.
Quick break, settled back 1 off with cover midfield, driven wide home turn, ran home soundly to make frame.
Sharp break to race 1 back on rail, shifted 1 off & driven 300m, to narrow lead 200m, all out & swamped 50m.
Fast start, settled 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, driven & shifted wider home turn, quickened to press lead 200m, swamped 50m, no extra.
Broke OK, slotted rail midfield, driven into stretch & boxed on soundly without threatening.
Moderate start, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, ridden 450m & wide into stretch, stayed on one pace.
Sharp break, disputed lead, settled close 2nd on rail until edged lead 550m, kicked on 300m, headed 190m & tapered.
Speed to lead at break, restrained to track handy 1 off with cover, switched out & driven 300m, outpaced & plugged on tamely.
Taken behind at break to race 1 off near rear, shunted wider home turn, plodded home one pace.
Fast start to dispute lead 4 wide, settled 3 wide no cover 3rd, every chance turning in, emptied 250m & faded.
Ridden to dispute lead, led outright 800m 1 off, narrow 2nd 550m, driven 300m, soon emptied & weakened out.
Hard ridden early, took rail, led by 1.5Ls in main bunch, dominated 250M.
Eased to sit just off the leader in main bunch, ran on strongly 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader in main bunch, progressed steadily 200M for 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide in main bunch, made some ground 250M.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader in main bunch, trapped 3 wide throughout, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail and led by more than 3Ls at fast sectionals, ran on until 200M, out of fuel.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide in main bunch, ran on fairly.
Eased to rear and took rail, 6Ls off the leader in main bunch, ran on fairly.
Very awkward away, ended up at rear, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide in main bunch, no turn of foot.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide in main bunch, no progress.
Very slow away, pushed forward to cross to 2 wide, 1.5Ls off the leader in main bunch, emptied 200M.
Struggled in midfield, trapped 3 wide, dropped off 400M.
Began well, ridden along 3-wide to lead from 1000m. slowed pace, kicked entering straight and held on well for narrow win.
Began OK, ridden along between horses, raced in restricted room 800m and bumped, peeled out before home turn and finished strongly.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail, unbalanced when bumped 800m, not much room top of straight, shifted in 150m for run, restricted room final 50m and not fully tested.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader back stretch. Looked chance entering straight, kept on well till flattened 50m.
Fractious in gate, jumped OK and quickly taken across between runners to find rail entering back stretch. Peeled out 3-wide 400m, finished off nicely.
Jumped best, led for few strides before settling in box seat behind leader. Kept on one-paced in straight.
Hard ridden but failed to muster and taken across between runners from 1100m, settling in last pair. Last into straight and ran past beaten horses.
Pressed forward, racing wide into first turn before settling one-back, one-off. Taken 3-wide turning for home, one-paced final 300m.
Ridden along early to maintain midfield position but over raced from 900m when left without cover. Took final turn wide wide, one-paced in straight.
Restrained from the start, settling in one-off position towards rear. Put under pressure from 400m but found little.
Slow into stride, in last pair to turn, improved position entering straight, tired after passing 200m.
Travelled smoothly in mid-division, picked up strongly passing 250M, led near 50M, won going away.
Tracked leader, ran on well and briefly led inside 150M, caught by fast finishing winner near 50M.
Taken across behind runners, travelled strongly towards the rear, taken out inside 400M, ran on well to clinch 3rd.
Taken across behind runners, unhurried and camped at the rear, closed off soundly from off the pace.
Never far off from leaders, driven along 400M, stayed on steadily.
Travelled keenly in the lead, rolled along at good pace, caught inside 150M, weakened.
Chased the speed 2-wide, ran on same pace towards the finish, out of contention 150M.
Held up behind midfield, saved ground on the inside but offered no serious response turning home.
Raced along the rails, stayed within striking distance down the back-straight, held up for clear running turning home, not properly tested.
Towards the rear, unable to slot in and raced 3-wide no cover throughout, didn't respond to riding nearing 400M, never involved.
Restrained after the start, proved difficult to settle and over-raced badly at the rear, left behind passing 400M.
Began well, rolled forward from 1600m to sit outside leader first turn, held together final turn, flat-footed top of straight, picked up momentum 200m and finished nicely.
Squeezed out shortly after start, dropped to behind midfield away from fence, little room final turn, got clear top of straight, flashed home strongly to just miss.
Pressed forward from wide draw to settle one-back, one-off first turn. Edged forward final turn, led shortly after entering straight, unable hold off first two.
Jumped well, ridden along behind pace, checked 1600m and taken in. Peeled out entering final turn, kept on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish.
Began fairly, got head up 1700m when awkwardly placed on heels, dropping to rear. Held up for run final turn and early straight, finished off nicely when clear.
Began well, rolled forward from 1600m to lead into first turn, set steady pace to 200m, kept on one-paced when passed.
Began OK, over raced and difficult to settle approaching first turn. Settled midfield away from fence, improved position final turn but one-paced in straight.
Began OK but crowded for room soon after, settling in midfield along fence. Saved ground final turn, one-paced in straight under hard riding.
Hampered soon after start and dropped to rear along fence. Shuffled back to near last final turn, ran on steadily to 200m when tightened for space. Not ridden out.
Hampered shortly after start and thereafter raced mostly 3-wide without cover. Turned wide into straight and found little under pressure.
Jumped best and led to winning post first time before easing into box seat behind leader. Under pressure from 500m and gave ground gradually.
Hampered shortly after start, taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. Closed in 1100m but checked on heels. Never a threat after that.
