Restrained from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, ridden turning in and taken to widest in straight, finished off very strongly to score by a length.
Away with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths back, travelled well to bend, finished off well to take 2nd.
Raced 2 wide without cover at front, ridden after turning in, stayed on well for 3rd.
Slightly slow out, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths back, bumped 900M, ridden after turning in, made decent progress in the middle of the track to make frame.
Taken back from gate 11, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground and kept to inside after turning in, kept on steadily in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, taken to very wide in straight and made some progress.
Jumped well, positioned 2-3 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, ridden turning in, finished off fairly in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with cover before midfield, 2 lengths back, ridden 350M, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from a tricky draw, raced 4-5 lengths back on rail at rear, checked 900M, saved ground, made some progress in straight.
Began fairly, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, travelled well throughout, but no response to riding in straight.
Jumped well, took the lead and set a slow tempo, ridden after turning in, but failed to respond.
Jumped fairly, unable to slot in and raced 3-4 wide without cover in midfield, no response to riding in straight, eased 100M.
Began fairly from gate 10, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover at front, weakened after turning in when hard run took toll.
Fairly away, restrained early to find cover, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, over-raced and bumped near 900M, emptied in straight.
Camped 2nd on the stands rail without cover. Hummed along after the furlong, hit the line well.
Showed good gate speed to lead, two off the grandstand side. Held on gamely in the run to the post.
Began awkwardly racing in 5th position, settling 3 off the stands rail, had some cover. Made a mild bid without threatening.
Parked in 4th position tracking the speed with cover on the grandstand side. Maintained a sound gallop to the wire.
Slow to break settling midfield, 2 off the outside rail, had cover. Closed off steadily.
Raced midfield towards the middle of the track, no cover. Kept on reasonably over the final stages.
Settled last on the grandstand side with cover. Managed to make some ground passing tiring runners.
Raced approx 3-4 off the stands rail with cover. Faded over the latter stages.
Settled 2nd last with cover towards the far side. Made no appreciable ground in the run to the line.
Travelled behind midfield, towards the center of the track, no cover. Never fired.
Raced prominently 4-5 from the stands rail, no cover. Weakened prior to the 150m.
Settled worse than midfield, no cover, racing closer to the middle of the track. Failed to run on.
Travelled midfield, approx. 6 off the stands rail. Made no impression finishing well back.
Settled worse than midfield, the far side had some cover. Struggled throughout & finished tailed out.
Prominent, settled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered 250M, then finished strongly to score by 1L.
Camped handy, 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hung out slightly rounding the Home Turn, ran on nicely to get 2nd but not match with the winner.
Settled worse than midfield about 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed well for 3rd.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, dashed strongly to get 4th.
Raced midfield, settled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on steadily.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along throughout, travelled 3-4 wide without cover, one pace in straight.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, looked likely early straight however was checked badly 250M, ran on fairly thereafter.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader at good pace, kept on until 250M weakened.
Pushed to settle midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Sent forward to share the lead along the rail at good pace, checked 200M, flattened badly thereafter. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Missed break badly & adrift, joined tail on rail 1000m, 7L last turning in, switched very wide & powered stands' side to lead 50m.
Sharp start, tracked 1 back on rail, shifted out home turn, driven 400m, swept to lead above 200m, all out & headed 50m.
Taken back at break to near tail 3 wide with cover, 6 L back & wider home turn, strong run stands' side to claim 3rd.
Fair break, taken back to 1 off behind midfield, hard-ridden 430m, good headway for sound gains without threatening.
Good break & rolled to lead 1250m, soon to rail & narrowly headed 900m, driven to regain lead home turn, headed above 200m, boxed on evenly.
Broke well, drifted back to midfield, sat wide & advanced 1000m, progress to 4th home turn, kept on one pace.
Slow start & bustled to race rail behind midfield, lost place home turn, switched out 400m, stayed on for solid late inroads.
Dropped in behind at break, bustled last pair 1 off, shifted wide home turn, driven centre track 350m, stayed on moderately.
Broke OK, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, shifted 4 wide 650m, driven turning in, stayed on same speed.
Tardy start & rousted wide, mustered to narrow lead 900m 1 off, headed & driven turning in, weakened in run home.
Tardy start, mustered to midfield on rail, checked off heels 1100m, over-raced 700m, driven into stretch, found nil & weakened.
Fast start wide, sat handy 3rd 1 off, shifted 3 wide no cover 700m, driven turning in, outpaced & faded in run.
Smart start to midfield 1 off, snatched off heels 1100m, ridden 500m, struggled in weakening run to wire.
Sharp break, sat handy off with cover 1 off, bumped & over-raced 900m, switched out & driven home turn, found nil & faded tamely.
Taken back & anchored at tail, progress on rail 600m, remained far side, driven 400m, scooted to lead 100m, drifted left close home.
Fast start wide, led 1100m, to rail 800m, crossed to stands' side in stretch run, battled on but headed 100m, just held on for 2nd.
Broke well, raced 3rd 1 off, lost cover 800m, progress to press lead home turn, shifted to stands' side, fought on but always held.
Fast break to dispute lead, taken back to midfield 3 wide no cover, found cover 600m & pushed 4 wide, driven to stands' side, closed off OK.
Sharp break but outpaced & soon near tail on outer, shifted 4 wide 600m, closed off centre track for sound gains.
Sharp start to dispute lead, checked to 2nd 1 back on rail 800m, driven 400m, remained far side, plugged on evenly.
Moderate break & rousted to settle rail midfield, over-raced & switched 3 wide 600m, boxed on evenly centre track.
Taken back at break, over-raced 1000m 3 wide near tail, last & wide home turn, edged to stands' rail & stayed on for minor inroads.
Fair start, tracked handy on rail, driven 400m centre track, one-paced in run home.
Broke OK, snagged to behind midfield 1 off with cover, shifted wider 500m, driven 400m, one-paced in tepid run towards stands' side.
Slow start & bustled early, raced 1 off in rear rank, shifted wide turning in, plodded tamely centre track.
Broke OK to race handy 1 off with cover, switched 3 wide no cover 600m, driven home turn & faded tamely in stands' side stretch run.
Behind midfield, 7.5Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made early move 500M, progressed steadily to win.
Eased to sit in midfield, 6Ls off the good pace 2 wide, blocked 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Eased back, 9Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 300M on the stand side for 3rd.
Settled in front, box seat, pace good, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to hold the rail and led by 1L at good pace, raced on the inside part of straight, hung on until 200M flattened.
At rear, 10Ls off the good pace on the rails, made late ground 200M.
Midfield, 6Ls off the good pace along the fence, made some ground on the inside part of straight.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace on the fence, just held ground in straight.
At rear, 10Ls off the good pace 3-4 wide, ran on ok.
Hard ridden early, 3.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, no dash, weakened 250M.
Eased back, 8Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made ground 400M, reduced 200M.
Trapped wide in midfield early, pressed forward to sit just behind the lead 2 wide, emptied 350M.
At back, 3-4 wide, never competitive.
Midfield, 4Ls off the good pace 3-4 wide, out of fuel 300M.
Jumped OK, held together behind pace in one-off position, rolled forward turn, hit the front 150m, kept on well to win easing down.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing very wide until taking lead 780m and crossing in to one-off position. Collared 150m but battled gamely to the line.
Jumped best and led till crossed 780m, holding position inside leader. Kept on gamely along rail in straight.
Pressed forward from good draw, taking box seat 800m before shuffled 2-back along fence around turn. Taken 3-wide entering straight and kept on steadily.
Jumped fairly, no early speed dropping to near rear along fence. Stayed on rail, improved around turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Outpaced, dropping to last of main bunch but away from fence. Stayed in one-off position into straight and ran on steadily in straight.
Ridden along early to hold midfield position but trapped 4-5 wide and left without cover from 780m. One-paced in straight under hard riding. Lame left fore.
Rolled forward, sitting outside early leader to 800m then dropping to 3rd between horses around turn. Gave ground steadily after entering straight.
Ridden along early to stay with pacemakers and held wide without cover. Got shuffled back turn and found little in straight.
Began awkwardly, bumped soon after, hard ridden but failed to muster dropping behind midfield. Limited response when asked for effort 350m.
Began OK, ridden along behind rely pace to 800m, shuffled back around turn dropping to near last, one-paced.
Began awkwardly, then darted to outer fence losing plenty of ground. Soon lost touch with field.
Moved up to join leader passing 900M, dueled with that rival passing 400M, gained upper hand from 200M, drew away to score final stages.
Set a well handled pace, sprinted home well with eventual winner from 400M, dueled for 200M, weakened late stages but finished well ahead of the 3rd.
Held up towards the rear, travelled well, was prompted to challenge between rivals 350M, ran on reasonably well to go 3rd 50M from home but not getting to first two.
Urged forward on jumping from wide barrier, 3-wide no cover with leaders entering home turn, outdashed by first 2 inside 400M, kept on steadily to hold 3rd until 50M.
Began only fairly, dropped back to a rearward position, didn't travel well and found less than expected when asked, never reached leaders (Lame left front.).
Chased the pace along the 2-path, came under pressure 500M out and outpaced by leaders, kept on same pace to the line.
Began well from draw 1 to gain a forward placing behind leaders, saved ground along the inside but lacked the needed response when they sprinted home from 350M.
Slightly slow out, urged along to take up a 3-wide position not far behind leaders, failed to pick up when the race got serious, out of contention 200M out.
Held up midfield, kept on same pace turning home, never a threat.
Held up in mid-division along the 3-path, driven 350M but failed to make any progress , never factored.
Failed to muster on this AWT debut and raced in detached last early stages, got back to the tail of the field entering home turn, not quickened inside 400M.
Dropped back, held up near the rear, fanned wide home turn, outpaced and left behind passing 400M.
Slow into stride, held rail at rear, shifted to outside fence entering straight and ran home strongly to win on the line.
Jumped well, raced inside leader before leading at 1200m. Well clear turn, stayed on rail entering straight, looked winner until caught last stride.
Jumped OK settling 3-back, one-off. Peeled out 600m to centre track in straight, looked chance 200m before peaking on run.
Ridden along from wide draw before finding cover 3-wide before turn. Took closer order 600m, kept on steadily in straight.
Restrained and held towards rear away from fence. Taken very wide into straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit one-off, one-back on settling. Rolled forward turning for home, looked chance entering straight, one-paced final 200m.
Slow into stride, cut to rail and improved to midfield but awkwardly placed on heels. Ran on steadily down centre track in straight.
Began fairly, ridden along inside horses, settling behind midfield. Came down centre-track in straight without looking a threat.
Jumped best from wide draw and led field before easing into box seat from 1200m, Rolled forward to challenge entering straight and kept on until swamped 50m.
Began well, pressed forward to sit two back from leader along fence. Took closer order entering straight before run ended 100m.
Ridden along from wide draw to sit three-wide with cover behind pace. Taken wide in straight but found little under pressure.
Began fairly, taken across behind runners to sit in last pair. Taken to outside fence entering straight but no response. Found to have substantial blood in trachea.
Began fairly, outpaced and dropped to last. Made up some ground around turn before tiring.
Slow into stride, raced tight 1300m and then steadied before turn. Never competitive.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground and travelled well turning, taken to the stands rail in stretch, won very comfortably.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back, taken to the stands side in straight and finished off well without posing any threat to the winner.
Fairly away, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover in midfield for the majority of the race, taken to the stands side after turning in and finished off well to get 3rd.
Slowly away, raced 6-7 lengths back at rear throughout, angled out turning in, finished off well down the center of the track to make frame.
Positioned 2 wide in front of midfield, 3 lengths back, ideal run to turn, taken wider in straight, ran on fairly.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 6-7 lengths back at rear, saved ground on rails, made decent progress along the far side.
Began well from gate 12, took the lead easily and set a moderate tempo, travelled well throughout, stayed on without quickening in straight.
Moderately away, positioned 5 lengths back on rail in midfield, pushed 800M, kept to inside after turning in but shifted out when under pressure, finished off one-paced.
Began fairly, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in front of midfield, saved ground and travelled well, closed off one-paced down the centre of the track.
Jumped fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, taken back to race at tail, 9 lengths back, under pressure turning and taken to the stands rail, only made minor progress in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 2-3 wide with cover, 7-8 lengths back, under pressure turning and taken to the stands side in straight, failed to close off. (See racing incidents)
Fairly away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, angled out after turning in, emptied in straight.
Away with them, raced outside the leader in 2nd, there to turn, weakened early after turning in, never looked competitive.

Jumped nicely, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground and travelled well to turn, closed off strongly and scored with a little to spare.
Moderate break, raced 4-5 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground turning and finished off well without threatening the winner.
Began well from gate 1, positioned 2-3 lengths back on rail, ideal run to turn, ran home well to get 3rd.
Fairly to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4-5 lengths back, same margin back to turn, finished off well to make frame. (See racing incidents)
Jumped well from the widest draw, pushed early to take the lead, travelled nicely throughout, hung on well until final100M flattened.
Taken back from wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6-7 lengths back, angled out in straight, clear final 150M but finished off fairly thereafter.
Slow to begin, raced at rear throughout, 10 lengths back, made some progress after turning in although never looked likely.
Slightly slowly out, positioned on rail, 6-7 lengths back at rear, there to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, angled out after turning in, made no progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, still well back turning in, only made limited progress in straight.
Moderate break, unable to slot in, raced in midfield, 3 wide without cover throughout, emptied in straight after hard run took toll.
Began well, raced outside the leader in 2nd, weakened shortly after turning in, never a threat.
Travelled midfield, 1 off the fence with cover. Peeled out and got going before the turn, dug deep to score close to the line.
Rolled forward and led on the fence. Responded well to riders efforts in the straight, but was gunned down late.
Settled in 2nd position outside the leader. Maintained a sound gallop in the home straight.
Effectively raced 1 out 1 back. Finished off steadily to make the frame.
Parked 3 back the fence. Kept plugging away, was only one paced in the run to the wire.
Had every possible chance after box seating. Faded after the 100m.
Went back from a wide gate, settling 2nd last, 1 of with cover. Made reasonable ground in the run home.
Slow to begin, settling last on the rails had cover. Kept to the inside in the final stretch, finished off steadily.
Raced just off midfield, 2 deep with cover. Shifted out wide in the straight, making no impression.
Never likely after being posted 3 deep without cover for most of the trop. Settled ahead of midfield, never got into the race.
Camped behind midfield on the paint, had cover. Failed to close off and was never in the hunt.
Travelled worse than midfield, 2 off with cover. Struggled in the home straight and finished well back. (Irregular heart rhythm and substantial amount of mucopus in its trachea).
Prominent, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly to score by a head.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 2Ls at slow sectionals, hung on well for 2nd, just missed by a head.
Taken back, settled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, despite not suited by the slow pace, dashed strongly for 3rd. (Questioned for riding)
Pushed to obtain the box seat, benefited by the tempo, kept on well to the line.
Hard ridden forward to settle 2Ls behind outside the leader, suited by the slow sectionals, kept on one pace to the line.
Pushed to settle midfield from wide barrier, however tapped 3 wide without cover throughout, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow sectionals, ran on fairly.
At rear, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, settled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, hampered by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, settled 5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked likely.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield early, however switched to 4 wide without cover when proving very difficult to settle, struggled soon after straightening, tailed out.
Broke OK, crossed to rail behind midfield, switched out home turn & driven, darted inside 200m, quickened to snatch lead close home.
Taken behind to rail in rear, niggled to close & off heels 700m, 7L back & driven at tail turning in, strong run to vie for lead close home, just held.
Broke well, raced fore of midfield 1 off & shifted 3 wide with cover backstretch, quickened 300m & finished well but outpaced by first two.
Slow start & initially detached at tail, progress from 800m & skirted field to lead 550m, kicked on 300m, all out & headed close home.
Broke OK, dropped in to 1 off with cover midfield, shifted out 700m, flat-footed & driven 500m, stayed on for sound late headway.
Fast start, tracked 1 back on rail, over-raced 1100m & shifted 1 off 900m, driven in 3rd 450m, all out & swamped 150m, faded thereafter.
Awkward start, raced 1 off behind midfield, shifted out & ridden wide into stretch, plugged on for minor gains.
Tardy break, raced rail midfield, over-raced 1100m, shifted out & driven turning in, boxed on one pace.
Sharp break, snagged to race midfield but caught wide no cover, driven very wide 400m, plugged on in tepid stretch run.
Fast start, soon led, crossed to rail 1st turn, headed 550m & ridden in 2nd, emptied 300m & faded out.
Good break, raced handy 2 back on rail, took closer order 1 back 800m, driven 500m, found nothing & weakened tamely.
Awkward break, pace to track leader 1 off no cover, pushed 3 wide 900m, driven 500m, struggled in weakening stretch run.
Taken back at break to 1 off with cover behind midfield, shaken up 400m & wide into stretch, strong run to lead close home.
Decent break, sat rail midfield, shifted out & driven 300m, strong run to vie for lead 80m, could not match pace of winner, just failed.
Slow start, settled 1 off with cover near rear, driven & shifted out home turn, not clear run in stretch, quickened through gap 100m to make frame.
Broke well, settled 1 off with cover midfield, ridden 450m & wide into stretch, solid run to 2nd 150m, tapered late & edged out of frame.
Taken behind & raced at rear, progress & ridden turning for home, strong run late to just miss frame.
Broke OK, bustled early to rail behind midfield, shuffled back 1000m, progress on turn & driven 300m, ran on soundly without threatening.
Rousted at break to lead, to rail 1st turn, pressed 900m, controlled tempo & kicked on 300m, all out & swamped 80m.
Broke well & prominent early, trapped wide & gradually taken back to slot 1 off with cover in rear 600m, niggled 500m, plugged on evenly.
Broke well, initially raced 2nd 1 off, got cover in 3rd 1 off 1 back 900m, shifted 3 wide 600m, driven into stretch to 2nd, soon emptied & faded.
Broke well, sat 1 back on rail in 4th, ridden 500m, found little & weakened in run to wire.
Tardy start & 3 wide no cover midfield, rolled to press lead 900m & slotted 1 off, under pressure 400m, emptied & weakened tamely.
Settled just off and outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, led 250M, got the prize only by a nose on the line.
Trapped 3 wide no cover throughout, 2.5Ls off the slow pace, closed off strongly 300M, just beaten by a nose on the line.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Pushed to obtain box seat, on heels 800M, favoured by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, little dash 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 4.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
At rear, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 300M, little dash 200M.
Failed to muster, eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, on heels 600M, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Very awkward away, 7Ls off the leader at rear, trapped 4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Hard ridden forward, checked badly 800, unbalanced 600M, reduced 400M.
Began fairly and raced fiercely, tightened 900m settling between horses behind midfield. Peeled very wide into straight and ran on strongly to win close home.
Ridden forward from wide draw and raced 3-wide mostly before getting cover around turn. Widest into straight, ran on strongly.
Began well, pressed forward inside leading pair to turn before easing into box seat. Challenged on entering straight, hit front 150m, swamped final 50m.
Slow to muster, cut to fence and held together near rear. Shifted out turn, improved steadily in straight, shifting out 150m to continue improving.
Outpaced, hampered and lost ground 1000m dropping to last. Saved ground turn, ran on steadily in straight.
Began OK, crowded for room 1000m. awkwardly placed inside heels 900m and again 600m, kept on steadily.
Jumped with field, shifted in 1000m settling 2-back from leader. Shifted out entering straight and boxed on gamely.
Began fairly, shifted in off heels 1000m, settling behind pacemakers but wide. Took turn 3-wide, battled on gamely in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw but unable find cover. Pushed on from 800m to lead 600m, kicked clear 400m, collared 150m, flattened final stages.
Began well, travelled between horses at front, relaxed when pace slacked before turn, did not quicken when put under pressure 500m, weakened final 100m.
Began fairly, settled at rear away from fence. In last pair entering straight and found nothing under pressure.
Began well, ridden along close to fence in midfield, shuffled back around turn, found nothing in straight.
Moved forward as expected, crossed to the lead near 1200M and dictated the pace, headed early straight but rallied strongly to regain the lead 100M from home.
Soon taken across behind runners, settled near the rear 7Ls off the pace, bid wide 350M, closed strongly to be nearest on the line.
Stayed within striking distance in 4th, not helped by the slackening pace middle stages and proved difficult to settle, moved up to the lead inside 300M, headed 100M, lost 2nd near line.
Switched off to last, 8Ls off leaders down the back straight, under patient handling then made solid progress passing 300M, nearest finish.
Settled behind midfield, went for outside turning home, finished willingly.
Reserved in midfield along the 2-path, hampered passing 300M, kept on evenly towards the finish.
Caught 3-wide no cover in midfield, shifted in early straight, kept on steadily final 300M, outdashed by a few rivals final stages.
Led early stages, had cover behind leader from 1200M, kept to inside on straightening, one paced and hung on to 3rd until swamped 50M.
Given a waiting ride near the rear, 6Ls off the pace halfway, taken out to challenge entering straight, gained some ground without threatening.
Settled along the fence in mid-division, faded away from 250M. (Bled.)
Broke only fairly, rushed forward to a one out one back position, came under pressure 500M, gave ground rapidly.
Slow to begin, held up behind midfield, checked at the top of straight, never recovered and eased.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, taken wider turning in, finished off strongly to score.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, angled out early in straight, closed off strongly when clear final 150M.
Fairly away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, there to turn, closed off well to get 3rd.
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground and travelled well throughout, kept to inside after turning in, finished off fairly to make frame.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced outside the leader in 2nd, there to turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Slowly away, recovered to sit 4-5 lengths back on rail, couldn't obtain clear running early in straight, finished off fairly when clear final 200M.
Drifted back from a tricky gate, raced at tail throughout, taken wider in straight and made some progress.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, ridden after turning in, ran home one-paced.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, took widest after turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Began well, pushed early to take the lead, travelled comfortably throughout, ridden after turning in, weakened rapidly near 150M.
Bumped start, ridden early to recover, raced 6 lengths back on rail, ridden early in straight and angled out, made little progress in straight.
Began well, positioned 1-2 lengths behind the leader on rail, ideal run to turn, under pressure after turning in but showed no response.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in front of midfield, 2-3 lengths back, there to run, made no progress in straight.
Jumped well from wide gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover in 3rd, weakened early in straight, never competitive.
Went forward leading on the fence and made every post a winner. Kicked clear approaching the furlong and won impressively on debut.
Had every chance after box seating. Switched out into clear running near the 350m, chased gamely.
Travelled ahead of midfield, 2 wide with cover. Took some time to wind up but found the line soundly.
Raced midfield, on the paint with cover. Railed up in the straight and kept grinding away to the post.
Raced with the backmakers on the rails with cover. Kept to the inside in home stretch and made good ground, didn't have a lot of room over the last 100m.
From an outside barrier went back, settling worse than midfield the fence, had cover. Made steady ground down the running.
Raced midfield, 2 wide with cover. Made a short dash to the furlong but was one paced in the run to the post.
Raced behind midfield, 2-3 deep with cover on the circle. Battled away in the home straight.
Parked in 2nd position, outside the leader. Was swamped near the 100m and weakened quickly thereafter.
Raced back in the field, 2-3 wide with cover. Made no impression in the final stretch. (See incident report).
Posted 3 deep without cover, travelling behind the speed. Never likely and struggled in the run home.
Camped 3 wide, midfield with cover. Was a beaten horse after the 300m and gave ground thereafter.
Taken across behind runners from a wide gate settling 3-4 deep with cover towards the rear. Failed to close off and was disappointing.
Settled last 3-4 off the rail with cover. Failed to pass another runner and finished well back.
Raced midfield, settled 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, finished off well to score by a neck.
Raced midfield, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, dashed strongly to get 2nd, missed by a neck.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, peeled wide turning in, dashed well for 3rd.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, ran on nicely until 100M weakened for 4th.
Taken back from wide gate, travelled 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, closed to the line well.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, swung wide turning in, ran on nicely.
Pushed to settle midfield 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on only fairly.
Pushed forward to take the fence and share the lead at good pace, kept on until final furlong weakened.
Began slowly, then travelled 10Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some late ground in straight.
Failed to muster, settled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader at good pace, flattened 300M.
Settled in front of midfield 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, soon weakened after straightening.
Pushed forward to settle 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, soon flattened badly after straightening.
Pushed to settle midfield, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, emptied shortly after straightening.
Broke well, raced rail midfield, squeezed through to lead 200m, kicked away for comfortable win.
Taken back to race 1 off near rear, shifted out & driven 300m, switched out 150m, strong run to snare 2nd at wire.
Fast start, drifted back to behind midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out & driven 430m, stayed on to 2nd 50m, all out & lost place at wire.
Broke with others, raced midfield 3 wide no cover, driven wide turning in, boxed on to dispute 2nd 200m, edged out of frame late.
Taken back from wide gate to tail, tight for room & shifted out 400m, squeezed through & bumped rival 350m, solid closer.
Broke OK, sat handy 1 off no cover until cover 1 off 1 back 950m, 3 wide 600m, driven 430m, outpaced & bumped 350m, boxed on evenly.
Smart start wide, trapped 4 deep & rolled on to slot 1 off leader 950m, driven home turn to lead 350m, headed 200m & tapered.
Missed break & ridden early, soon sat rail near rear, progress on turn, shifted out & driven 400m, plugged on evenly.
Broke OK, caught 3 wide with cover behind midfield, ridden wide 450m, plugged on one pace.
Bustled & soon led, restrained & headed 1450m, sat 1 back on rail, trapped in pocket into stretch, driven 200m, found nil.
Ridden early to lead outright 1450m, soon to rail, pressed & ridden 420m, all out & headed 350m, faded thereafter.
Smart start wide, taken back to race near rear 3 wide with cover, wider & driven into stretch, bumped 350m, weakened in run.
Fair break, bustled initially, over-raced & prominent, restrained to 1 off with cover midfield, niggled 500m, struggled & faded tamely.
Decent break, trapped 4 wide no cover, gradually taken back to rear, very wide & driven home turn, bumped 350m, found nothing thereafter.
Fast start to dispute initial lead, settled 1 back on rail 1000m, driven & switched 1 off 430m, quickened to lead 300m, forged on.
Fast start & led 1100m, crossed to rail 1000m & set tempo, driven 350m, headed 300m, kept on soundly but no match for winner.
Taken behind at start to race in rear on inner, shifted out & shaken up 400m, good headway to 3rd 100m, closed to wire.
Bustled at break to race handy 1 off with cover, driven 430m, battled on evenly without threatening.
Fast start wide, caught 3 deep no cover & raced handy, ridden turning in, stayed on evenly.
Dropped in at break to race 3 wide no cover in rear, 6L back & driven very wide into stretch, closed off for sound inroads.
Broke OK, taken back to race 1 off with cover behind midfield, switched out & driven 430m, stayed on for modest headway until tapered late.
Broke well, raced 1 off no cover 2nd, hard-driven into stretch, all out 300m & faded thereafter.
Slow start, scrubbed to race rail behind midfield, shifted out & driven home turn, outpaced & struggled in run home.
Broke OK, caught 4 wide no cover & taken back to rear, outpaced 10L back & detached at tail turning in, stayed on for very late minor inroads.
Tardy start & rousted to rail midfield, driven turning in but outpaced & faded in run.
Broke OK, caught 3 wide with cover & raced behind midfield, niggled 900m, wide into stretch, found little in weak run home.
Fair start, snagged to settle 1 off with cover midfield, driven 500m, found nothing & faded tamely in stretch.
Pushed to cross in front, settle in box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well to win.
Slow away but soon took a midfield spot, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, lack room 400M, dashed well despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pressed forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, ran on for 3rd.
Pushed to take a midfield spot, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on well.
Eased back and took rail, 8Ls off the leader, held up 400-200M, dashed well when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide and raced keenly, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 300M.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Slow away, 6Ls off the leader along the rails, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, ran on ok.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the slow pace on the fence, soon emptied 300M.
Hampered early, dropped to rear, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1.5Ls, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, soon reduced 350M.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Slow, given reminders, mustered between horses settling behind pace. Peeled 4-wide turning for home, levelled up with 200m to go, battled gamely for narrow win.
Began well, raced inside leaders along rail to back stretch, held box seat around final turn, drew level 200m, battled gamely to just fail.
Jumped with field but difficult to settle before taking position one-back, one-off. Pocketed final turn, blocked for run in straight, finished strongly when clear 150m.
Began fairly, restrained and taken across behind horses at rear. Swung widest turning for home and ran on strongly to just miss a place.
Began best, pressed forward to lead on settling, set steady pace to straight. Caught 200m out but battled on till swamped final stages.
Began well but outpaced slipping to behind midfield close to rail. No run early in straight and awkwardly placed 200m, stayed on nicely.
Jumped fairly, outpaced, dropping to rear but close to fence. Peeled out turning for home and kept on steadily.
Began OK, restrained and taken closer to fence at rear. Layout both terms, shaken up entering straight but limited response.
Pressed forward from wide draw and trapped 4-wide first firm, thereafter racing without cover. Stayed with leaders early in straight but soon beaten and tired.
Jumped well, hard ridden, rolled forward to sit on hind-quarters of leader from 800m. Battled on early in straight before giving ground from 200m.
Travelled well behind mid-division, picked up the pace from 600M, swung wide making rapid progress, loomed behind leader and wrestled the lead at 100M, lengthened away towards the line.
Settled 2-wide in mid-division, quickened well approaching the straight, led near 300M, stuck on gamely but outstayed by winner final 100M.
Settled in mid-division, within striking distance turning for home, ran on well entering straight but clearly no match with first two going into final 200M.
Broke well, led from 1400M and slowed things down, outdashed by first 3 early straight, kept on same pace for non-threatening 4th.
Rolled forward along the fence, set early pace until 1400M when overtaken, lacked a change of pace when the principals sprinted home inside 400M, kept on same pace to line.
Tracked leader in a slowly run race, driven and outpaced from 400M, soon out of contention.
Blundered at the start and lost ground, was slow to pick up when the pace quickened inside 450M,
Slow to begin, guided to a rail spot in midfield, made on real progress on leaders when driven 400M out.
Stayed within striking distance, not able to quicken when the race got serious nearing 400M, soon beaten.
Switched off to last, 8-9Ls behind leaders in a slowly run race, taken widest to challenge in straight, found nothing in reserve.
Held up towards the rear, nudged along 550M but never going the pace to challenge.
Restrained after start, in rear pair 8-9Ls off a slow pace, failed to quicken passing 400M, never involved.
Slow, mustered between horses, cut to rail 900m and pinched ground around turn. No run top of straight, switched in 250m for clear run, finishing strongly for narrow win.
Outpaced, dropping to rear away from fence, Started forward move wide turning for home, taken to centre track in straight and finished strongly to just miss.
Began awkwardly, hard ridden to go forward, held narrow lead when bumped and unbalanced 1100m. Led around turn, kicked clear entering straight, kept on strongly till run down final strides.
Outpaced early and taken closer to fence at rear settling in one-off position. Switched out very wide entering straight and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began OK, taken in, settling in midfield close to rail. Stayed on fence entering straight and kept on steadily. Not fully tested final strides.
Began fairly, restrained and taken across behind runners at rear. Switched wide entering straight and ran on fairly to be closest at finish.
Outpaced, dropped to rear close to fence. Last entering straight, held up for run before picking up momentum final 200m to be closest at finish.
Hampered start but recovered quickly, picking up ground close to rail to grab box seat back stretch. Looked a chance turning for home before becoming one-paced final 200m.
Began OK, ridden along early settling away from fence behind midfield, Taken very wide turning for home and kept on one-paced in straight.
Began well, ridden along behind early pace, improved position from 900m but checked 800m. Held for run early in straight but only one-paced when clear.
Began well, ridden along to hold position one-back, one-off back stretch. Hard ridden from 400m but found little and weakened. Jockey reported not comfortable in action.
Pressed forward from inside draw settling two-back, one off. Began racing fiercely from 900m, checked and shifted out to be without cover final turn. Tired.
Began well and held lead to 1200m before easing back to race on hind-quarters of leader. Started to give ground soon after entering straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, took the lead easily, challenged by outside horse near 800M but still travelled comfortably throughout, ridden 300M, kept on well to score by a head.
Average to begin, raced 2-3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4-5 lengths back, travelled well to turn, finished off very strongly, just missed.
Began well, initially positioned on rail, improved outside leader, challenged from 800m, ridden after turning in, kept on well to take 3rd.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, finished off well to make frame, a good debut.
Jumped well, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail in 4th, saved ground and travelled well to turn, finished off fairly in straight, couldn't raise enough to place last.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced at tail throughout, 9 lengths back, taken to widest after turning in, closed off strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back, came wider on turn and made some progress in straight to be nearest at finish.
Fairly to begin, positioned on rail in midfield, 5 lengths back, there to turn, kept running inside after turning in, finished off one-paced.
Began fairly, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover in 6th, 3-4 lengths back, under pressure turning and ridden early in straight, but made no progress.
Moderately away, raced 3-4 wide with cover behind midfield, 5-6 lengths back, under pressure turning, made no progress in straight and eased thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 7-8 lengths back, angled out after turning in, showed no progress in straight, never competitive.
Checked at start, positioned 6 lengths back on rail at rear, ridden after turning in, made no progress in straight and eased final stages.
Bumped start, showed early speed to race 2 wide in 3rd, made contact near 1000M, ridden after turning in, but failed to respond and eased final 150M.

Jumped well, raced 1-1/2 length behind the leader on rail, ideal run to turn, kicked clear in straight and won very comfortably.
Began well, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail, saved ground and travelled well to turn, kept running inside after turning in, made decent progress to get 2nd.
Fairly away, pressed forward to race prominently in 2nd, travelled well to turn, closed off fairly to get 3rd.
Began fairly, positioned 3-4 lengths back on rail behind midfield, difficult to settle near 800M, angled out after turning in, made some ground in straight to make frame.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 5 lengths back on rail throughout, ridden after turning in, made some progress in straight, just missed frame.
Jumped well from gate 8, positioned 1 out 1 back, under pressure turning, made no progress in straight and bumped final 75M.
Jumped with them, pushed to take the lead, travelled well to turn but failed to muster in straight, weakened rapidly final 100M.
Taken from back from a wide draw, raced at tail throughout, ridden after turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide at rear for the majority of the race, angled out in straight and made minor progress only.
Fairly away, checked when making the first turn, raced 2 wide in midfield, difficult to settle throughout, made no progress in straight.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover, 2-3 lengths back, under pressure turning, but failed to respond, never a threat.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back, under pressure turning, emptied early in straight.

Raced midfield, 1 off the fence with cover. Got a nice cart into the race, peeling out and rolling forward near the 700m, 3 deep. Had good momentum rounding the turn and ran on well, finishing out wide.
Raced behind midfield on the rails with cover. Closed off well towards the inside.
Had every conceivable hope after stalking the leader along the fence. Grudgingly gave ground late.
Settled 3rd from the rear, 1 off with cover. Made the home turn with one wider, closed off soundly.
Went forward and led on the fence. Strolled along at a leisurely pace, didn't quicken at the business end and was overhauled near the 150m.
Settled behind midfield, 2 wide with cover. Got going at about the 700m, 3 deep with cover, maintained a steady gallop down the running.
Effectively raced 1 out 1 back. Had every conceivable hope, was one paced in the run to the line.
Parked in 2nd position outside the leader. Faded over the final 100m.
Camped back in the field, on the fence with cover. Failed to close off.
Travelled in last position on the rails with cover. Made no impression in the home stretch.
Raced in 2nd last position. 1 off with cover. Made a forward move near the 900m, joined the leaders 3 deep without cover. Was gassed passing the 500m.
Settled midfield on the rails with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at good pace, hung on well to score by 1/2L.
Began smartly, then eased to settle 2.5Ls 2 wide with cover, finished off strongly for 2nd, missed by 1/2L.
Hard ridden forward to occupy the box seat, stayed on well for 3rd.
Sent forward to park outside the leader at good sectionals, kept on steadily to the line.
Taken back to rear, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, dashed well in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Eased back from wide gate, settled 5.5Ls 2 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
Jumped awkwardly, then travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Never in a competitive position.
Sent forward, however travelled 4 wide without cover throughout, soon weakened after straightening.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, soon flattened after straightening.
Camped in rear on rail, 12L off lead until switched 1 off & closed at rear 700m, widest into stretch, flew home centre track to easy lead 50m.
Speedy at break, sat 1 back on rail 3rd, switched 1 off to challenge turning in & disputed lead until drew clear 200m, all out & headed 50m.
Broke OK, raced rail midfield, off heels 600m & over-raced 500m, shifted out into stretch, ran on well to take 3rd close home.
Broke OK, bustled early & raced midfield 1 off with cover, switched 3 wide & driven forwards 450m, closed off well to just miss frame.
Taken back at start, raced last pair 1 off, soon 13L back at tail, to rail 700m & closed up, closed off in stretch for sound late gains.
Good start & rousted to 2nd 1 off no cover, driven turning in, disputed lead 300m, edged lead 250m, soon headed, one-paced & swamped in run.
Taken back to 1 off with cover near rear, forced wide into home turn & driven, kept on evenly.
Sharp start & soon led, to rail 900m, shaken up 300m, hard pressed & headed 250m, faded thereafter.
Fast break but soon niggled, settled 1 off with cover handy, driven under pressure 400m, shifted out in stretch but outpaced, kept on same speed.
Fair start, taken back to midfield & caught 3 wide no cover, driven to advance 500m, pressed lead 300m, soon emptied & weakened out.
Outpaced early & raced rail near rear, driven 1 off for progress 500m, wide into stretch, outpaced & struggled in tepid run home.
Moderate start, bustled to race rail midfield, shuffled back 500m, driven into stretch, found nothing & soon beaten.
Smart start, camped 3rd 1 back on rail, nudged to 2nd 500m, shifted out & driven turning in, quickened to lead 200m, just held on at wire.
Broke OK & bustled early to track winner on rail midfield, switched out turning in & driven, closed right to wire, just failed.
Sharp start & bustled to lead 1st turn, shaken up in front 320m, headed 200m & tapered.
Decent start, caught 3 wide no cover & sat back of midfield, hard driven 450m, widest into stretch, closed late without threatening.
Awkward start, raced rail back of midfield, gradual progress out of backstretch, driven 320m, one-paced to wire.
Taken behind at start to race rear rank 1 off with cover, to rail 900m & some progress, ridden 450m, outpaced & boxed on evenly in stretch.
Fast break wide, slotted handy 1 off with cover 1100m, forced wide & driven home turn, outpaced & plugged on moderately.
Slow start, soon slightly detached at tail, ridden 600m, still last at 200m, plugged on for late headway past beaten rivals.
Good break, camped 1 off with cover midfield, over-raced 950m, niggled 600m, ridden 400m, found little in tepid run home.
Tardy start & bustled early, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, scrubbed to hold place backstretch, wide in home run, struggled to wire.
Fast break to lead, soon settled 2nd 1 off no cover, under pressure & to 3rd 500m, all out 300m & weakened tamely.
Broke OK, restrained to race 3 wide with cover near tail, to rail & scrubbed 600m, found nothing in weak stretch run.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well to win.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, enjoyed the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M, just missed by neck in 2nd.
Trapped 3 wide in midfield throughout, 3.5Ls off the leader, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, 1L off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 100M flattened.
Awkward away, midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 300M, little dash 150M.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leader along the rails, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 300M, checked 50M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 3Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, flattened 200M.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 6.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the slow pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, emptied 200M.
Ridden along early, settling two-back, one-off into first turn. Edged forward passing 500m, entered straight very wide, finished strongly.
Began well but retrained, holding position close to rail behind midfield. Took closer order final turn, found inside run in straight and finished strongly.
Shifted across behind runners early and held patiently at rear before edging forward approaching final turn. Swung wide into straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, not pushed, settling in midfield away from fence. Took turn a little wide and ran on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Still well back turning for home, very wide in straight, kept on steadily.

Jumped well and ridden along early to hold one-back, one-off position though well behind fast pace. Closed in steadily turning for home, joined leaders top of straight, kept on steadily till flattened 100m.
No early pace but managed to get close to rail from wide draw on settling. Taken wide entering straight and kept on steadily without looking dangerous.

Hard ridden from wide draw to taken lead around first turn but unable to cross to fence despite setting fast pace. Held 1-wide back stretch and final turn, joined at front entering straight, kept on till flattened late.
Ridden along early to stay with pace before settling in box seat behind leading pair. Edged closer turning for home but soon tired and hung in when giving ground.

Hard ridden to stay on pace, holding position inside leader and refusing to give ground. Joined leading pack top of home straight, still a chance 200m before tiring. Jockey told ride lacked judgement (See racing incidents).
Outpaced early, dropping to rear and under pressure from 600m but with limited response.
Began well and ridden along to hold rail 2-back from leaders. Came off fence turning for home to make challenge but found little and tired final 200m.
Slow to begin, settled at the rear first half, moved out to the 4-path and strode forward, finished strongly to lead inside 50M.
Soon led, took them along at a well-handled pace, fought on willingly entering straight, caught by fast finishing winner near 50M.
Held up in midfield, saved ground on the inside, made steady gains from 250M, got up for 3rd passing 100M, continued on well to the line.
Not hurried, guided to the fence and settled near rear 5Ls off the pace, stayed on well between horses.
In mid-division early stages, shuffled back to near the rear passing halfway, shifted out to 3-wide home turn, closed off well to clinch 5th near line.
Held up behind midfield along the 3-path, moved forward into contention 500M, ran on well early straight, run peaked 100M from home.
Settled just off the lead, loomed a threat 300M, turned one pace inside 200M, swamped late stages.
Settled at the near 5-6Ls off the pace, taken widest in straight, ran on well.
Prominent early, restrained to a midfield spot middle stages, moved out for clear run passing 300M, stayed on fairly.
Tracked leader early stages, stayed within striking distance when the race got serious 500M, run ended 200M from home, eased.
Along the 3-path never far off leaders, left with no cover entering back straight, joined leader 500M, weakened rapidly mid-straight.
Caught wide no cover early stages, strode forward to race outside leader near 1000M, gave ground from 500M, soon left behind.

Jumped moderately, raced keenly in 4th within striking distance, quickened to hit front inside 200 metres, soon drew clear under pressure.
Ridden to just better than midfield far side, in 5th when within 3L of pace around home bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace near rails, switched out for a run approaching home straight, kept on same pace without quickening under pressure.
Niggled along in first few racing quite wide down far side, quickened to hit front momentarily over 200 metres out, died on its run inside final 100 metres.
Began moderately, gradually dropped to last few, switched very wide into straight, made modest progress down the centre of the track.
Crowded shortly after start, made swift progress on rails from 1000 metres to reach 3L 6th on home bend, similar turning in, one-paced before fading close to home.
Broke well from the widest gate, remained wide in midfield early far side dropping to tail-end around home bend, made up late ground close to home despite steadied 200 metres out.
Jumped well, soon taken back to rear of field, switched onto rails rounding home bend, kept on same pace without quickening.
Never better than midfield.
Niggled along in prominent position early, lost position approaching home bend, failed to make any impression in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped fairly settling in midfield, remained similar turning in, found nothing under pressure in the run home.
Made good use of low draw driven to lead, held 1L advantage most of way to straight, folded up quickly under pressure.
Travelled in second position outside the leader. Was under plenty of pressure after the 500m, to stay in touch. Responded to vigorous riding and came up trumps in the shadows of the post.
Parked 4th on the fence had cover. Hit the lead at the furlong and looked the likely winner but was out dulled in the run to the wire.
Effectively raced 3 back the fence with cover. Peeled out before the home turn and closed off soundly under strong riding.
Raced ahead of midfield, 1 off with cover. Battled away fairly in the home stretch.
Led along the fence. Quickened the tempo near the 600m, straightened a length in front, faded approaching the furlong.
Camped behind midfield, posted 4 deep without cover for the majority of the race. Swung the home turn widest, made some progress in the run to the wire.
Raced midfield, 3 deep with cover. Only plodded to the line. (Returned lame right fore leg).
Posted 3 deep without cover for most of the trip, behind midfield. Was one paced up the running.
Pulled hard in the middle stages racing towards the rear, 3 deep, mostly with cover during the run. Never looked likely.
Crowded at the start, settling behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Failed to make any appreciable ground in the run to the line. (Blood in trachea post-race)
Raced keenly in the early stages on the fence with cover, in last position. Never quickened in the home stretch and finished down the track.
Travelled with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Never let down and was a beaten horse a long way from home.
Raced back in the field, on the paint with cover. Struggled in the straight, finishing well back.
Did plenty of work early to go forward and raced wide until about the 1200m, settling 1 out 1 back. Was a spent force prior to straightening.
Taken back from wide gate, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, stayed inside, dashed well to score by 1-1/4Ls.
Rolled to share the lead at good sectionals, kept on well until final 100M weakened.
Taken back, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, dashed well for 3rd.
Prominent, settled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on nicely for 4th.
Began slowly, then pushed forward to take the lead on the fence at good pace, hung on well until inside 100M emptied.
Began nicely, then taken back to rear and settled 5Ls behind the leader 3-4 wide with cover, ran on nicely.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls off the leader 4 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Eased start, settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace to the line.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, never ran on.
Camped handy, settled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, soon weakened after straightening.
Never looked likely.
Settled in front of midfield, however trapped 4 wide without cover throughout, weakened rapidly 250M.
Rolled forward to share the lead, however travelled 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened badly 300M, tailed out.
Sent forward, then trapped wide throughout, flattened badly rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Fast start to lead, crossed to sit half width off fence, edged tighter to rail 850m, in control turning in, shaken up 350m, stretched clear easily.
Fast break, sat 1 back on rail 2nd, edged back to 3rd 620m, ridden turning in, boxed on evenly to regain 2nd 100m, kept on without threatening.
Slow break, raced rail behind midfield, shifted out home turn & shaken up, progress when steadied off heels 250m, strong closer to 3rd last stride.
Broke sharply, bustled early to 3rd 1 off no cover, 2nd 620m, shaken up in pursuit 400m, soon all out & faded final 150m, lost 3rd late.
Fair break on outer, caught wide no cover & drifted back to slot behind midfield, wide home turn, stayed on for sound inroads.
Taken back at break, raced 3 wide with cover near rear, ridden wide home turn, stayed on for decent headway centre track.
Taken back to camp 2nd last, 9L back when wide into final stretch & driven, stayed on centre track for minor gains.
Tardy start, rolled forward to race handy 1 off with cover, driven in 4th turning for home, outpaced & weakened in run.
Broke OK, bustled early to race handy on rail, driven turning in & shifted out, failed to pick up & faded tamely.
Taken behind at start, raced 1 off with cover near rear, over-raced 650m, driven & one-paced into stretch, shifted centre track in tepid run.
Slow start, recovered to midfield 1 of with cover, shaken up & switched out 450m, faded in tame run home.
Went back from widest gate to race detached at tail, 11L back & driven turning in, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Moderate start, raced rail midfield, niggled 500m, hard ridden into stretch, found nothing & struggled to wire.
Snagged from wide to slot rail near rear, driven turning for home, found nothing & soon weakened out.
Rousted to lead & crossed to rail 900m, led comfortably into stretch, shaken up 250m & quickened, all out under pressure but held on at wire.
Broke OK, lacked pace initially, raced midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide 800m, driven into stretch for progress, solid closer, just failed.
Sound start & raced rail 1 back, switched out & driven 300m, quickened to 2nd but no extra & lost place 100m, kept on evenly.
Tardy start & ridden to rail midfield, niggled 600m, driven 400m, stayed on gradually for sound late headway.
Outpaced early, rousted to rail behind midfield, shifted out & driven 400m, stayed on for eye-catching gains final 150m.
Sharp break and driven to race 2nd outside lead, driven turning in, outpaced & lost position 200m, boxed on one pace.
Broke OK, drifted back to behind midfield 3 wide with cover, niggled 800m, hard-ridden wide into stretch, stayed on for minor headway.
Smart start, sat handy 1 off with cover, dropped back a touch 600m & niggled, lost position into stretch, bumped rival 100m as plugged on late.
Sharp break wide, taken back to sit 3 deep with cover behind midfield, wider into stretch, moderate progress, emptied 100m & faded.
Broke OK, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven 400m, plugging on evenly when crowded & bumped 100m, never a threat.
Awkward start & lost ground, ridden forward 3 wide, no cover from 900m, to 3rd 700m, driven 400m, emptied 220m & weakened quickly.
Broke OK widest, snagged to race rear rank 3 wide, niggled 800m, driven wide into stretch, plodded on same speed.
Slow start & bustled along in rear rank, hard ridden 650m, plugged home one pace & never a factor.
Slow start & niggled at tail, soon detached, hard-ridden into stretch but no impression.
Settled in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader along the rails, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace, just scored by a short head.
3.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, made early move 700M to take advantages from the slow pace, led 400M, hung on well until 50M overhauled, just beaten by a narrow margin.
Settled in front, 2Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the slow sectionals, checked 450M, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased back to take rail, 7Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, checked badly 450M, regained balance 200M, dashed well.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 500M, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1.5Ls, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, but soon out of fuel 400M.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by slow pace, badly hampered 450M, ran on ok.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, moved forward 600M, flattened 200M.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, taken wide round the home bends, hampered 450M, no progress.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, held up 500M, checked badly 450M, tailed out.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, suited by the slow tempo, however soon reduced 500M.
Pressed forward, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, 3.5Ls off the slow pace, dropped off 600M, hampered 450M.
Began well, settling behind leader going into first turn. Travelled comfortably back stretch and final turn, angled out for run 500m, accelerated to the front 200m and pulled clear for easy win.
Pressed forward to lead from the jump, slowed pace first turn, picked up momentum 1000m, kicked ahead 400m, caught 200m, battled on gamely.
Began well but restrained and ridden stone cold at the rear. Taken 3-wide passing the 500m to start long run while hanging in up the straight.
Jumped well, settling on hind quarters of leader at first turn. Moved alongside leader passing 1200m. joint leader into straight, kept on one-paced.
Jumped with field, bumped and unbalanced 1800m after which over-raced till passing 1400m. Put under pressure 900m to hold position but little response. One-paced in straight.
Taken across behind runners shortly after the start, settling at rear. Put under pressure turning for home but found little. Never competitive.
Slow into stride, checked at first turn and bumped another. Remained at rear throughout. Never competitive.
Lightly urged after the start, moved up to share the lead on the inside, travelled strongly to straight, not asked until 250M and always had enough to hold off the persistent 2nd.
Sat close up just off the pace, moved out to a striking position 500M, tackled the eventual winner from 250M, always held but finished clear from rest.
Dropped back to the rear, kept on inside throughout, awkwardly placed mid-straight, stayed on well to go 3rd near 50M but no impression on first two.
Tracked leaders along the fence, briefly held up near 200M but ran on only fairly when clear.
Rushed forward to join leaders, niggled along to keep up 500M, outpaced from 250M, weakened to 5th.
Settled near the rear but never far off from leaders in a compact field, stayed on mildly, never a serious threat.
Raced greenly, dropped back to a rearward spot but never too far off the leaders, kept on one pace final 400M.
Restrained after the start, caught wide no cover near the tail throughout, failed to pick up turning in, no impression.
Strode forward from wide barrier, shared lead along the 3-path, weakened badly passing 400M.
Held up 3-wide, stayed within striking distance turning home, taken wider passing 500M, soon weakened and dropped away. (Bled)
Began well but soon outpaced dropping to midfield. Shuffled further back when leaving rail 600m. Rattled home very wide in straight to hit front 90m before pulling clear.
Ridden along early to sit one-back, one-off along back stretch. Rolled forward final turn, hit front 250m, kept on well till flattened final 100m.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw to sit at rear. Checked at 600m when making forward move, ran on strongly between horses in straight to snatch third placing.
Bumped at start but pressed forward to lead before first turn. Set good pace to 300m when collared. Kept on well till swamped final stages.
Began fairly, bumped and unbalanced 1400m and taken wide first turn. Settled in 5th back stretch, wide final turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail behind leader at first turn. Remained in box seat to straight where kept on one-paced.
Began awkwardly, racing in pack behind midfield. Improved position around final turn, taken wide in straight, one-paced.
Vigorously ridden from wide draw soon after start but failed to muster and trapped wide at rear. Remained at rear till home stretch when ran past tired horses.
Taken across behind runners soon after the jump, settling last. Remained at rear till entering home stretch before running on steadily past beaten horses.
Caught on wrong foot when gates opened and slow into stride. Cut in to rail, improved to midfield before bumping rail 700m. Kept on one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, ridden along but wide into first turn, racing without cover, Still wide turning for home, found little in straight under hard riding.

Began OK, ridden forward but bumped and unbalanced 1400m, causing saddle to shift. Shifted to outer rail as rider tried to correct saddle, looped field to sit outside leader 700m, gave ground shortly after straightening for home.
Bumped start, recovered, rolled forward to sit behind leaders. Shuffled back along back stretch, lost more ground final turn, weakened steadily in straight.
Began fairly and soon at rear close to fence. Dropped to last turning for home and finished tailed off. Performance deemed unacceptable.
Slowly out, soon recovered to race in midfield 4-5 lengths away, travelled well throughout, angled out at turn, finished off strongly to score a narrow win.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 6 lengths back, same margin back to turn, taken to widest in straight and closed off very strongly final 200M, just missed.
Jumped well, pushed to take the lead and set a moderate tempo, travelled well throughout, ridden after turning in, headed 100M but still kept on well to get 3rd.
Fairly away, sent forward to position 3 lengths back on rail, easy run and saved ground to turn, angled out early in straight, kept on fairly to make frame.
Jumped fairly from a wide draw, pressed on to race prominently in 2nd, outside leader throughout, ridden after turning in, finished off at same pace but wasn't too far away on line.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 7 lengths back, under pressure turning and ridden early in straight, made some progress in straight to be closest at finish.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced on rail, 8-9 lengths back at rear throughout, improved along rails after turning in, made some progress before running out of room in the concluding stages.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently, a length behind the leader on rail, travelled well to turn, in mix early in straight but dropped off after passing 200M.
Jumped with them, raced 6 lengths back on rail in midfield, under pressure turning, made limited progress in straight.
Began fairly, sent forward to race 2 wide in 5th, right there to turn, failed to respond in straight.
Moderately away from the widest draw, taken back to race 10 lengths back at the back of the field, 3 wide without cover, struggling turning and made little progress in straight.
Slightly slowly away, raced 7 lengths back behind midfield on rails, niggled along turning, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide at rear, 8 lengths back, made no progress in straight.
Fairly to begin, raced at tail throughout, well-back turning, never competitive.
