Soon switched across for inside run from a middle draw settling in midfield, saved ground on rails turning for home, ran on under pressure to prevail narrowly.
Settled in last few after beginning from a poor gate, switched wide for a run on straightening, ran on well.
Jumped well, soon taken back for rails run on heels on leader, remained in one-back position to straight, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Slowly away, settled well behind, baulked behind runners approaching straight, finished off race well down the inside of the track.
Tightened at start, settled well behind, ran on under pressure to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well from a low draw, soon took up running and held narrow lead until headed into straight, faded under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well, soon taken back to midfield, commenced move inside 500 metres circling the field around home bend, hit the front briefly inside 200 metres but unable to sustain effort close to home.
Jumped well, settled in 5th just over 2L off the speed, came under pressure to hold place rounding home bend, kept on well to finish.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped towards the rear, found nothing under pressure.
Jumped well, travelled outside the leader most of way to straight, gradually faded under pressure.
Ridden along from a poor gate settling just worse than midfield, went wide into straight, one-paced when badly squeezed inside final 200 metres.
Travelled prominently and wide without cover after beginning from the widest gate, remained similar turning in, weakened steadily after straightening.
Raced behind midfield, 2 wide with cover. Peeled out and started a sweeping run before the home turn and closed off well.
Settled 4th from the rear, 1 off with cover. Chased soundly in the straight but couldn't find that bit extra.
Raced in last position close to the rail with cover. Crept forward after the 600m, swung wide turning for home and closed off well late.
Began awkwardly then was crowded for room settling towards the rear on the rails with cover. Closed off soundly to fill the frame.
Camped midfield, 2 deep with cover. Stayed on fairly, never threatened.
Raced 3 back on the paint with cover. Did nothing in the home straight, failed to quicken.
Settled in 2nd position, 1 off with no cover. Vied for the lead after the 800m, was a spent force over the final 100m.
Parked behind midfield the fence. one paced whilst racing along the inside in the home stretch.
Had no excuses after box seating. Weakened noticeably over the final 100m.
Did plenty of work eventually crossing and leading along the fence after the 1200m. Was pressured in the lead after the 800m and was swamped at the furlong, tiring quickly.
Went forward eventually box seating. Was a beaten horse prior to the home turn.
Never looked likely after being posted 3 deep without cover until about the 800m, racing at the rear of the field. Raced 1 off with cover on the circle but was gone a long way from home.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1/2L, hung on strongly to score by a neck.
Sent forward to park outside the leader, kept on nicely for 2nd.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, stayed on well for 3rd but without any serious threat.
At last, settled 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, dashed on strongly. (Questioned for riding, see incident report)
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, settled 4Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on steadily.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover until 450M, kept on one pace in straight.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader at rear, never looked likely.
Settled worse than midfield about 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, soon weakened after straightening.
Stumbled start, tracked 1 back on rail, keen 800m but soon settled, switched out & driven into stretch, led 200m, ran home strongly.
Slow start, camped rail near tail, driven 300m & shifted out, closed off gradually to 2nd 90m, held to wire.
Tardy start & bustled early, raced rail midfield, ridden 400m, tracked winner into stretch, switched out 300m, kept on to claim 3rd.
Speed to lead, driven 300m & soon under pressure, all out & headed 200m, no extra & tapered to wire.
Fair break, trapped wide & snagged to tail, very wide & driven into stretch, ran on for good headway centre track.
Fair start, sat midfield 1 off with cover, switched 3 wide for progress 500m, hard-driven & wide into stretch, some headway until tapered late.
Tardy start, raced 1 off with cover near rear, shifted into rival home turn, driven 300m, plugged on one pace.
Fast start, caught 3 wide no cover handy, ridden turning in, boxed on until weakened out final 200m.
Broke well, back to behind midfield, progress 3 wide to midfield 700m, forced 4 wide no cover 500m & scrubbed, wide & one-paced in run.
Sharp start to sit 2nd 1 off no cover, ridden 500m, emptied 300m & faded out.
Slow break, sat 3 wide with cover near rear, impeded & wide on final turn, found little in weak run home.
Smart break, stalked lead 1 off with cover, off heels 650m & soon niggled, driven 500m & began to fade, struggled thereafter.
Slow start & bustled to sit behind midfield on rail, switched out 400m, driven 300m, strong run down centre to lead close home.
Taken back early to behind midfield 1 off with cover, shuffled back 700m, shifted out & progress turning in, led 125m, emptied & headed 50m.
Slow break & near tail 2 wide, switched 3 deep & ridden forward 700m to press lead on outer, led 200m, headed 125m & no extra.
Broke well, slotted midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 450m, gradual progress & switched inside 150m, stayed on soundly.
Snagged to tail on rail, switched 3 wide for minor headway 650m, 5L last & widest into stretch, boxed on for sound inroads.
Taken back to 3 wide near rear, advanced wide with cover 1000m, outpaced & driven 500m, stayed on evenly in wide stretch run.
Disputed early lead, headed 1800m & sat rail 1 back, shifted 1 off to edge lead 600m, all out & headed 250m, tapered thereafter.
Broke OK, raced midfield on rail, shifted out home turn & driven, plugged on one pace.
Vied for early lead, snagged to handy 1 off, no cover from 1600m, driven 3 deep 500m, boxed on to 3rd 350m, soon emptied out.
Tardy start & bustled wide no cover to midfield, rapid advance 700m, briefly pressed lead 4 wide, struggling when impeded home turn, faded.
Fast start to dispute lead initially, soon restrained & handy on rail, niggled 600m, driven 500m, weakened tamely from home turn.
Started well, rolled to lead 1800m, to rail 1600m & set tempo, headed 600m, hard-ridden 2nd into home turn but swamped into stretch & faded.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the slow pace 2-3 wide, made early move 500M around the field, dominated 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 300M.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader on the fence, taken wide 800M, made early move around the field 500M to take advantages of the slow pace, ran on for 3rd.
Very slow away, 7Ls off the leader along the rails, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Slow away, pushed early but not muster, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 8Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 200M, little dash.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1.5Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 250M weakened.
Hard ridden forward, box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, checked 400M, emptied 300M.
Pushed early, settled 3Ls off the slow pace on the fence, soon dropped off 400M.
Never a factor, tailed out.
Snagged back soon after jump and cut to rail before first turn. Improved position around turn while hugging rail and got clear passage when others fanned out. Finished strongly to win close home.
Jumped best and led past winning post first time before settling in box seat first turn. Came off fence turning for home, took over lead 200m, run down close to line.
Began fairly, ridden along in midfield, settling in one-off position. Shuffled back around final turn but accelerated strongly final 300m to just miss quinellla spot.

Began well, hugging rail inside leaders till first turn when bit got slipped. Remained 2-back the fence back stretch, rolled forward to challenge entering straight, kept on steadily under hard riding. (See racing incidents)
Hard ridden from wide draw but unable lead and eased to midfield to find cover without success. Travelled wide back stretch and turn but kept on steadily in straight.
Began fairly, not pressured, racing between horses towards rear. Taken 3-wide back stretch, wide around final turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Pressed forward 3-wide to lead passing 1300m before cutting in to fence. Clear leader back stretch and final, caught 200m, one-paced.
Jumped well, ridden along to hold forward position before settling 2-back, one-off back stretch. Gave ground entering straight and one-paced thereafter.
Slow into stride and then steadied, dropping to last. Raced fiercely 1400m, shifted out and bumped another. Left rail turning for home but found little under hard riding.
Began fairly, ridden along to hold rail behind midfield, rolled forward turning for home, made ground to 200m, flattened.
Snagged back from jump, taken across behind runners to sit in last pair. Taken wide passing 900m, wide into straight, found nothing when asked.
Quickly into stride, settling one-back, one-off first turn and back stretch. Started to give ground final turn and finished tailed off. Performance unacceptable.
Not hurried after the start, held up in midfield along the 2-path, switched wide nearing home straight, responded to vigorous riding, ran home strongly and got up final few strides.
Restrained in a 2-wide position in midfield, picked up the pace well from 250M, couldn't match the winner final 100M, got up for 2nd last stride.
Strode forward to race outside leader, took over 300M, continued on well to line, caught by first 2 concluding stages.
Broke well from wide draw but soon dropped back to last, responded well 300M, closed off strongly between horses, nearest finish.
Well placed along the fence tracking the leaders, kept to inside turning home, had every chance but only held his ground in the run to the finish.
Taken back from wide draw, settled well near the rear, closed off steadily on the inside over final 300M.
Positioned 2-wide in the group chasing the pace, moved out to a striking position 500M, ran on one paced.
Settled towards the rear, not used until reaching home straight, made no real progress.
Began awkwardly, guided to the fence 4Ls off the pace, kept on same pace in straight and never a threat to leaders.
Obtained a midfield position 3Ls off the pace, came under pressure halfway round the home turn, weakened 250M.
Driven forward, raced keenly in the lead, soon headed entering home straight, no extra and weakened rapidly over final 200M.
Began awkwardly, caught 3-wide in mid-division and left with no cover 1000M, pushed wider home turn, had little left in reserves, weakened to last.

Jumped well, made good use of rails draw to virtually make all the running, soon drew clear in straight.
Jumped well, close up early stages, gradually dropped to rear of midfield coming onto home bend, made modest progress in straight.
Began moderately, settled 3-wide behind midfield to straight, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well from a poor draw, raced very wide and prominently without cover early, 3-wide in 2L 5th around home bend, kept on one pace under pressure.
Soon taken back and across from the widest gate, saved ground on inside turning in, ran home well to do best work late.
Began moderately settling in forward of midfield, made steady headway around home bend and early in straight, reached distant 2nd over 200 metres out but soon faded.
Jumped fairly, settled in rear of midfield on rails, gained slightly closer coming out of far side, similar turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.

Slow out, travelled towards the rear on rails far side before taking slightly closer order on home bend, remained behind midfield turning in, kept on steadily without quickening. (Sore hindquarters and back)

Jumped quite well from a middle draw, well there without cover early on, obtained cover in one-out-one-back spot 1100 metres out, remained similar turning in, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.

Travelled in rear of midfield, hampered and lost position coming out of back straight, hampered again and dropped to tail-end on top of home bend, ran on past well-beaten runners in the centre of the straight.
Jumped fairly, soon taken across to last few, shifted out for a run on straightening, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly, close up and sharing pace briefly far side, similar turning for home, weakened inside final 250 metres.
Eased to sit behind midfield, not suited by the slow tempo, never improved.
Pushed to obtain box seat, faded soon after straightening.
Crowded at the start, settling behind midfield 1 off with cover. Shifted out deep on straightening and hit the line strongly over the final 100m.
Led early on the fence before handing up passing the 800m, soon after shifted off the fence to travel 1 off in 2nd position. Looked the likely winner at the 200m, but was nailed near the 50m.
Parked close to midfield, 2 deep with cover. Kept on evenly, just couldn't find that bit extra late.
Parked worse than midfield, on the rails with cover. Finished off satisfactorily.
Made its run from back in the field, 2 deep with cover. Closed off well.
Worked to the line soundly after travelling on the fence with cover, midfield. Didn't have a lot of room over the latter stages.
Settled second 1 off before rolling forward and assumed the lead near the 800m. Crossed to the fence soon after, was still in the mix at the 100m but faded over the final 50m.
Raced with the backmakers, 3 deep with cover. Came widest in the stretch and made steady headway in the run to the line.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and lost considerable ground. Managed to tack onto the field in last position, on the rails. Made reasonable progress towards the inside in the home stretch.
Raced keenly in the early stages whilst stalking the leader on the fence. Commenced to give ground after the furlong.
Drifted back to settle towards the rear, 3 deep with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Settled handy to the leaders, 1 off with cover. Carried 4 deep on the home turn, soon faded.
Settled close to midfield, had cover on the circle, 3 deep. Gave in quickly after the 150m.
No luck whilst racing on the speed, after being posted 3 deep without cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Settled in front of midfield about 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the slightly slow tempo, ram on strongly to score by 1.5Ls when clear 250M.
Eased to settle 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slightly slow sectionals, dashed well to get 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slightly slow pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slightly slow sectionals, hung on nicely for 4th.
Pushed forward to park 1L outside the leader, benefited by the slightly slow tempo, kept on well to the line.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 200M, ran on only fairly.
Settled in front of midfield about 4Ls off the leader, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, lack room 200M, kept on one pace to the line.
Settled worse than midfield, niggled along throughout, never a threat.
Knocked over on jumping, then taken back from wide barrier, settled 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slightly slow pace, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 7.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slightly slow sectionals, never ran on.
Began slowly, at rear throughout, never looked likely.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, despite benefited by the slightly slow tempo, flattened 300M.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Started OK & soon led, to rail 1000m, pressed 950m but soon asserted, shaken up 400m, kicked clear, held off closers at wire.
Smart start, drifted back to rail midfield, switched out 250m & shaken up, closed to 2nd late, held in run to wire.
Moderate start, sat rail behind midfield, tight on fence into stretch, driven 400m & closed off strongly to just miss 2nd.
Slow start, raced 1 off behind midfield, shifted wide 800m, driven 430m & strong closer centre track to just miss frame.
Slow start, sat rail near rear, shifted 1 off 650m, driven 350m, checked 300m, switched out for run 200m, stayed on late without threatening.
Broke OK, raced 1 back on rail, head on side on turn until ridden into stretch, switched out to 2nd 300m, emptied 250m & tapered.
Rousted wide, raced 3 wide with cover midfield, ridden home turn, staying on evenly when hung in 175m & bumped rival, one-paced.
Decent start, snagged to midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 550m, crowded centre track in stretch, to rail 150m, plugged on tepidly.
Smart break to dispute lead initially, snagged back to track pace 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, outpaced & plodded on evenly.
Tardy start & bustled wide to press lead 950m, settled 2nd on outer, ridden 450m, bottomed out 300m & weakened tamely.
Taken back at break to slot 1 off with cover near rear, 3 wide 650m, driven turning in, found nothing & struggled in run home.
Decent start, sat 3 wide no cover handy, ridden turning in, one-paced when impeded & snatched up 175m, eased thereafter.
Reared & missed start, closed to race last pair 1 off, wider 700m & very wide into stretch, minor headway until emptied & faded late.
Taken back to sit last pair on rail, ridden at tail turning in, plodded on & never a factor.
Smart start & ridden to sit 1 back on rail 3rd, switched out & driven 350m, edged 3-way battle for lead 100m, boxed on to hold narrow advantage.
Good break to rail fore of midfield, shaken up 400m, switched 1 off 300m to press lead, always held in tight battle to wire.
Broke with others, raced midfield 1 off with cover, switched wide & ridden home turn, quickened to slim lead 200m, headed 100m & tapered to wire.
Taken back for cover on inner behind midfield, ridden 500m, stayed on gamely for gradual gains, to 4th 50m, closed to wire.
Smart break, snagged to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, overraced 800m, switched wider final turn, closed to 4th 150m, tapered late.
Taken back early & soon niggled rail near rear, driven 430m & shifted out, to rail 200m & closing, shifted out again late for solid gains.
Slow start & niggled rail in rear, shifted wide & driven turning in, plugged on evenly for minor inroads.
Fast break to lead widest, crossed to rail 1000m, extended into stretch, driven all out 250m, headed 200m & faded thereafter.
Broke with others, railed midfield, ridden 550m, crowded in stretch, impeded 250m & unbalanced, plugged on.
Fair break but outpaced midfield & rousted, soon rolled to handy 4th 3 wide no cover, outpaced turning in, crowded & bumped 400m & 300m, no extra.
Broke well, raced 1L 2nd 1 off no cover, driven under pressure 430m, found nothing & emptied 300m, weakened tamely.
Good break to sit fore of midfield 1 off with cover, driven turning in, hung out & repeatedly bumped rival in weakening stretch run.
Snagged back at break to near rear on outer, niggled for minor advance 800m, widest home turn, plugged on one-pace until weakened & eased late.
Pressed lead initially, soon taken back to midfield 3 wide with cover, niggled 700m, forced wider home turn, found nothing & soon at tail, well beaten.
Settled in midfield along the fence, 4Ls off the good pace, lack room 400M, closed off strongly 250M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M, just beaten by a short head in 2nd.
Bumped start, 5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, held up 400M, progressed steadily 200M for 3rd.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made steady ground 400M, run ended 150M.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the good pace along the fence, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 6.5Ls off the good pace, held up 400M, made ground 200M.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, led 400M, ran on well until 200M flattened.
Bumped start, 6Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made some ground 200M.
Eased back, 5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, lack room 400M, weakened 200M.
Eased to rear, 6.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to share the lead 2 wide at good pace, soon emptied 350M.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at good pace, reduced quickly 400M.
Never a factor.
Began best, kicked clear before joined up front 700m, Hung out turn, flat-footed top of straight and passed by two others, fought back strongly to win.
Jumped well, challenged for lead before settling one-back, one-off. Turned 4-wide, picked up momentum from 200m, finished strongly.
Jumped with field, pressed forward along rail settling in box seat. Got inside run entering straight, led 300m, run down final stages.
Began awkwardly, shifted in and bumped another, ridden along behind leading bunch. Taken wide in straight and ran on strongly.
Began fairly, outpaced, settling 7L from leader entering turn. Taken wide entering straight and ran on steadily.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing 4-wide into turn. Drew level with leader 700m, kept on well in straight until flattened 50m.
Jumped OK, not pressured, settling 7L from leader along rail. Made up some ground final turn, taken wide in straight, ran on steadily.
Began fairy, ridden along early settling midfield 5L from leader. Peeled out turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, outpaced, settling in last pair away from fence. Dropped to last entering straight, ran past beaten horses final 200m.
Began fairly, taken across behind horses, settling last. Improved slightly around turn, then one-paced.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped. Taken to fence, made good ground around final turn, but tired quickly passing 200m.
Always prominent, loomed behind leader 450M, driven to lead 250M out, kept on strongly to line.
Travelled well ahead of midfield, stayed within striking distance passing 500M, chased winner from 200M but always held.
Taken back to the rear, kept to inside turning home, made stealthy progress between runners, got up for 3rd 50M but unable to get closer to first two.
Positioned ahead of midfield, moved out to a contending position passing 500M, kept on steadily to line but well held by first two.
Settled behind midfield, taken wide 500M, stayed on moderately.
Held up towards the rear, made good initial progress on straightening, one paced final 200M.
Dropped back to the rear, 7-8Ls off the pace middle stages, moved out to clear 350M, stayed on without threatening.
Soon led, headed inside 250M, no extra final 100M.
Slow to begin, settled towards the rear along inside, ran on fairly final 400M, never a serious threat.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, kept on same pace final 400M, never threatened.
Slow to begin, improved to a midfield position, moved out passing 600M, never going the pace to challenge.
Rushed forward to track leader, had nothing left turning home, weakened badly 350M.
Raced behind midfield, came under pressure early home turn, badly outpaced approaching straight, soon beaten.
Strode forward to race outside leader, gave ground rapidly passing 500M.
First out, eased and taken in, settling outside leader before turn. Moved up around turn, kicked clear 300m, held off late challenge.
Began OK, settling 3-back, the fence. Improved position around turn, taken out 400m, ran home strongly to just miss.
Hampered shortly after start, dropping to rear. Awkwardly placed 900m, taken very wide entering straight, finished strongly.
Jumped well, pressed forward to lead from 1200m. Joined top of straight, battled on gamely until flattened final 50m.
Began fairly, ridden along close to rail to take box seat before turn. Three-wide entering straight, kept on steadily to be closest at finish.
Reared and lost ground start, ridden to make up ground settling midfield. Put under pressure turning for home, boxed on one-paced.
Ridden along early but wide, steadied passing 1200m, covered extra ground turn, very wide in straight, one-paced.
Ridden to take forward position but held wide without cover. Rolled forward turning for home, 4th into straight, then one-paced.
Began fairly, restrained and cut in to rail, dropping to last entering turn. One-paced straight running past beaten horses.
Bumped shortly after start, shifted out and dipped 1200m. Ridden along at rear but wide, one paced straight.
Began awkwardly, bumped, striding forward while difficult to settle. Three-wide into turn, shuffled back entering straight, weakened gradually.
Began fairly, ridden along but held wide at rear, racing without cover for most of the way. Found little in straight under pressure.
Began awkwardly, shifted out, bumped, hard ridden to make up ground, sitting behind leading pack 800m. Gave ground turning for home and weakened further in straight.
Began fairly, taken to rail and improved position around turn. Faded quickly from 200m. Found to have had irregular heart rhythm.
Began well, positioned 1-2 lengths away behind the leader on rail, ideal run to turn, set out after leader at 400M, finished off too well and scored by a head.
Jumped well, took the lead easily, no pressure throughout, 1 length clear entering straight but just unable to hold off the winner late.
Away well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, same margin back to turn, ridden after entering straight, finished off well without posing any threat to the first two.
Began moderately from a poor draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, well back to turn, couldn't obtain clear running early in straight, closed off very strongly when clear to make frame.
Tardy into stride, positioned 3-4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground and travelled well to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off fairly, just missed frame.
Jumped nicely from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently in 4th, travelled well throughout, 2 lengths back under pressure after turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, same margin back to turn, no daylight until 250M, made some progress thereafter.

Away with them, raced 6 lengths back on rail at rear for the majority of the race, kept running inside after turning in, made some progress early in straight, not fully tested in the concluding stages. (See racing incidents)
Slowly away, positioned 4-5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, same position to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, 7-8 lengths back, improved on turn and same to middle, only made minor progress in straight.
Tardy getaway, recovered to race outside leader, struggling turning, showed no response to riding and weakened gradually after turning in, never competitive.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover throughout, did share of work to bend, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, showed no early speed early, positioned 3 wide with cover in midfield, 5 lengths back, under pressure turning, showed no response in straight.
Slowly away, positioned 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, angled out after turning in, shifted out sharply early in straight, made no progress and never competitive.

Quickly ridden to hold prominent spot on rails, crossed by eventual runner-up coming out of far side, fought on under pressure to just get up on line.
Jumped well from the middle draw, holding narrow advantage one off, crossed for rails coming onto home bend kicking 1.5L clear turning in, kept on steadily under pressure only to be pipped at post.
Jumped fairly, settled not far off the pace in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, ran on under pressure without threatening.
Slowly away, ridden along on rails to join the rear of field, remained similar but saved ground turning in, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Broke well, soon taken back to travel just worse than midfield, shifted out for a run entering straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Slowly away, soon picked up to forward of midfield, ran home one-paced.
Jumped well from a poor draw, travelled prominently and wide without cover most of way to 400 metres, faded gradually.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, travelled wide without cover in midfield, made no impression in straight.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.
Jumped moderately, soon dropped towards the rear racing 3-wide, made no impression in the run home.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, soon taken well back to race wide without cover, made no impression in straight.
Raced in 5th position, 1 off with cover. Peeled out on straightening and wound up nicely to take control of the race 50m out.
Travelled midfield, 1 off with cover. Swung deep on the home turn & finished off soundly.
Parked 3 back the fence with cover. Darted through into clear running along the inside near the 250m, hit the lead after the 150m, but was overhauled in the run to the line.
Camped behind midfield, 2 wide with cover. Came widest in the straight and finished off well despite having to shift away from heels near the 70m whilst laying in.
Flew out of the gates and led before handing up near the 900m and box seating thereafter. Was still in the mix at the 100m but was swamped late.

When being taken back from a wide gate, was crowded for room, settling worse than midfield the fence, had cover. Had no luck in the straight after being badly held up until the 100m. Had plenty of excuses.
Ridden negatively from barrier rise & raced with the backmakers, on the paint with cover. Worked home steadily.
Led along the fence. Hung out on the home turn and in the straight, faded after the 200m and proved somewhat difficult to ride out.
Settled in last position from the outside gate, close to the rail, with cover. Was severely checked near the 200m after being held up, never recovered thereafter.
Ridden aggressively early, travelling in second position outside the leader, no cover. Was a beaten horse at the furlong.
Posted 3 deep without cover for most of the trip whilst racing on the speed. Never looked likely and finished well back. (See incident report)
Settled 3rd from the rear, 1 off with cover. Drifted back after the 700m and tailed out in the straight. (to trial)
Pushed forward to cross from a wide gate, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast pace, ran on well to score by a neck.
Raced midfield, settled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, dashed well for 2nd, missed by a neck.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast tempo, dashed on strongly to get 3rd despite lacked of room over the concluding stages.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 1.5Ls at fast sectionals, hung on well until over the last few strides to get 3rd.
Taken back, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, enjoyed the fast tempo, switched wide turning in, ran on nicely.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, despite harmed by the fast pace, kept on well until 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the fast tempo, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 7Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast pace, never ran on.
Sent forward to settle 1.5Ls outside the leader without cover, hampered by the fast sectionals, flattened badly over the last furlong.
Began smartly, then travelled 7Ls behind the leader 4 wide without cover throughout, never looked likely.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Raced midfield, settled 6.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover throughout, soon flattened after straightening.
Smart break, sat 1 off no cover 2nd, to 3rd with cover 750m & niggled, switched 3 deep & driven 400m, quickened to lead 150m & drew clear.
Awkward start, raced rail near tail, bustled 750m, hard-driven into stretch & headway, closed off late to snag 2nd.
Speed to lead, to rail 1st turn, headed 650m, niggled & regained lead 450m, shaken up 300m, all out & headed 150m, tapered to wire.
Fair start, raced 1 off with cover mid pack, driven 600m, shifted out home turn, hard-ridden for solid headway to wire.
Broke OK, raced rail midfield, nudged along 600m, hard-ridden final turn & shifted out, kept on soundly for decent inroads.
Good break, posted 1 off with cover 4th, overraced 1200m, switched 3 wide 800m to lead 650m, headed 450m, driven 300m & battled one pace.
Sharp start, tracked 1 back on rail, every chance when driven 300m, outpaced & boxed on evenly.
Camped at tail at break, bustled & shifted out 700m, hard-driven 450m & widest into stretch, made negligible inroads.
Slow start, raced 1 off near tail, niggled 700m, driven wide home turn, outpaced & plugged on one pace.
Snagged back at break, raced near tail on rail, progress 400m, switched 1 off & shaken up 300m, quickened & led 100m, in command.
Slow break & impeded start, bustled to rail & settled midfield, progress & shifted out home turn, gathered 300m & strong closer to 2nd last strides.
Smart start, tracked one back on rail, niggled 600m, shifted out 500m & driven, progress to lead 290m, emptied & headed 100m in tapering run.
Good start, sat fore of midfield 1 off with cover, flat-footed & driven 400m, shifted out final turn, stayed on for late headway.
Tardy start & bustled to race near rear 1 off with cover, under pump 500m, ran on soundly for gradual inroads.
Sharp start, settled 3rd 1 off with cover, pushed 3 wide 500m & ridden into stretch, weakened in run home.
Broke OK, raced midfield 1 off with cover, driven turning in, outpaced & plugged on in tepid stretch run.
Shifted left start, rolled 3 wide to slot 2nd 1 off with cover 900m, led 650m & extended 400m, emptied & headed 290m, faded out.
Reared state & lost many lengths, closed gradually to tail 1000m, 2L detached turning in, kept on past beaten rivals.
Sharp break, snagged to sit midfield 3 wide no cover, minor advance 750m but soon hard-ridden, wide into stretch, found nothing & eased.
Dropped-in to race near tail 3 wide with cover, switched 4 wide 600m, hard-ridden 450m & wide on turn, struggled in run home.
Speed to lead, headed 650m, ridden under pressure to hold position turning in, soon swamped, faded tamely from 300m & eased.
Settled nicely in box seat, kicked away 300M to take advantages from the slow tempo, hung on well to win.
Hard ridden early, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide throughout, made early move 900M, dashed strongly for 3r despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide no cover throughout, not suited by the slow pace, moved forward 900M, run ended 200M.
Midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, blocked most straight, just ran on.
Settled at back, 5Ls off the leader on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight and checked 200M, not tested.
Eased back, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 300M, run ended 150M.
Very slow away, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, blocked all straight, not tested.
Pushed forward, just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
Pushed to take rail and led by 0.5L at advantageous slow sectionals, however gave ground quickly 300M.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, set steady pace, momentarily passed 100m, kicked back to win narrowly.
Ridden forward with early leader before settling in box seat first turn. Took closer order final turn, joined leader 100m couldn't go on.
Outpaced, dropping to behind midfield along rail. Improved position around final turn, bumped and unbalanced 150m when making ground, finished strongly final stages.
Ridden along early, cut in to rail back stretch, made ground final turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Taken across behind runners shortly after start but kept away from fence. Checked 700m, shifted out and raced keenly into turn. Blocked for run 150m, shifted out, kept on steadily.
Began fairly, not pushed, settling between horses behind midfield. Badly held for run entering straight, shifted out 300m and ran on steadily.
Pressed forward, settling one-off, one-back into first turn. Took final turn a little wide, one paced in straight, tiring final 50m.
Began awkwardly, no pace and soon last. Vigorously ridden from 500m to stay in touch and ran past tired horses in straight.
Slow into stride, ridden along to obtain forward position but kept wide. Steadied behind the pace back stretch, taken wide final turn, one-paced final 200m.
Ridden along early to obtain forward position but trapped three-wide and mostly without cover. Started to give ground entering straight. Rider severely reprimanded (See racing incidents).
Snagged back from wide draw and taken across behind runners in last place. Found nothing in straight under hard riding.
Began OK, ridden along early but wide, rolled forward passing 1200m to sit outside leader. Gave ground steadily from 400m.
Not hurried after the start, travelled smoothly in midfield, quickened up impressively to take lead inside 200M, kept on strongly to line.
Held up near the rear, kept to inside turning in, made good progress over final 200M to get within 0.5L of the winner.
Settled 2-wide about 3Ls back in mid-pack, into clear 350M, stayed on to chase winner final 100M, always held.
Settled just off the leaders, had every chance, stayed on for moderate 4th.
Tracked leaders along the fence, badly held up early straight, clear run from 150M, closed off steadily.
Hard pushed early to keep up with leader, kept on steadily turning home, outpaced by first few final 150M.
Broke well, steadied 1100M and fell back to a midfield position, stayed on mildly turning home.
Towards the rear, made some progress final 300M but never threatened.
Held up in mid-division, ridden and no impression turning in, kept on same pace.
Slow to begin, vigorously driven but failed to muster, detached in last 8-9Ls off the pace, stayed on fairly final 300M, never a threat.
Rushed forward to lead, caught inside 200M, no extra.
Settled in mid-division, 3-wide no cover throughout, gave ground from 300M.
Began well, crossed quickly to sit at hindquarters of leader. Shaken up entering straight, hit front 300m, kicked clear 200m, running on empty 50m but held.
Steadied soon after start, dropped to clear last first turn. Not pressured till 400m when taken 5-wide, ran home strongly to just miss.
Began OK, outpaced, dropping to near rear in one-off position. Not pressured, taken out turn and widest in straight, finished strongly.
Began well, ridden along between horses to stay in touch with leaders. Had clear run entering straight and kept on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began fairly, threw head up passing 1000m and raced ungenerously to 900m when unbalanced. Did not settle until final turn, finished off nicely final 150m.
Slow, steadied from heels 1100m settling towards rear. Improved along rail before turn, came off fence 300m, not fully ridden out in straight.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, cutting to fence 1000m. Set steady pace, hung out home turn, joined 300m, kept plugging until swamped 50m.
Began well, ridden along to hold box seat turning into back stretch. Saved ground final turn, kept on steadily to 200m before stopping quickly. Lame right front.
Jumped OK but raced too keenly and trapped wide without cover. Rolled forward from 800m, wide into straight, found nothing under pressure.
Ridden forward from wide draw, found cover but wide passing 1000m, awkwardly placed 500m, taken out entering straight but one-paced.

Hard ridden to get forward position, hung out first turn and left racing wide without cover. Faded quickly in straight. Jockey reported did not travel comfortably. Performance ruled unacceptable (See racing incidents).

Jumped moderately, settled in 6th on inside about 3L off the pace, saved ground on rails turning in, did not find much room early in straight, finished off race nicely to assert over 80 metres out.
Began from a poor gate, travelled wide without cover in midfield most of way, ran on steadily in straight doing best work late.
Jumped well, travelled one-out-one-back, shifted out for a run entering straight, did not find much room early on before producing a good late finish.
Broke well, gradually taken back to midfield, shifted wider for a run entering straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly settling in rear of midfield on rails, briefly baulked for a run 300 metres out, finished off well.
Jumped moderately, soon moved up to join the lead, gained slender advantage on straightening, unable to sustain effort and swamped over 100 metres out.
Raced freely and wide towards the rear far side, one of the widest around home bend, produced good late impression down the centre of home straight.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped just worse than midfield despite niggled along, made some late impression close stages.
Began well from a poor draw, gradually settled 3-wide without cover in 5th some 3L back, kept on steadily without quickening in straight.
Blundered at start, settled one back on rails, shifted off rails for a run entering straight, one-paced before fading inside final 200 metres.
Soon taken back from a poor draw, always in last few.
Always well behind. (Bled)
Jumped moderately, soon took up running setting a steady pace, narrowly headed upon straightening and dropped away quickly inside final 250 metres.
Always well back and never seen with a chance. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Travelled 3-4 back on the stands rail 1 off, with cover. Switched into clear running near the 200m, and had the race in its keeping 50m out.
Parked fourth from gate 1, 3-4 from the outside fence, no cover. Shot clear near the 150m, but was nailed approaching the 50m.
Raced ahead of midfield, 3 from the grandstand side with cover. Maintained a good gallop right to the finish.
Raced back in the field, close to the stands rail with cover. Was held up for clear running approaching the 400m, switched in to continue improving after the furlong, finished off soundly.
Settled behind midfield, 3-4 off the outside rail, had cover. . Worked home steadily.
Worked forward to lead about 3 off the stands rail. Was still in the mix near the 150m, but faded over the final 100m.
Settled midfield, grandstand side with cover. Briefly held up approaching the 200m, made some late headway.
Positioned in the back half of the field, drifting towards the middle of the track, had some cover. Was one paced in the run to the wire.
Parked on the speed, the stands rail, no cover. Was under pressure after the 600m, suffered a check near the 200m, but was a beaten conveyance prior to that point.
Raced close to midfield, about 5 off the stands rail had cover. Was giving ground after the furlong.
Raced with the backmakers drifting to the far side, had cover at stages. Only plodded home and made no discernable ground.
Settled towards the rear on the stands side with cover. Failed to make any impression at the business end of the race.
Showed no gate speed settling a long last closer to the middle of the course. Was never in the hunt and finished well down the track.
Raced prominently towards the grand stand side, no cover. Was a beaten conveyance prior to the 400m, finishing tailed out. (To trail)
Rolled to occupy the box seat, dashed on well and won comfortably by 2Ls.
Ridden to take the fence and led by 3/4L at good tempo, kept on strongly to claim 2nd but never match with the winner.
Began awkwardly, then settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on gradually but without any threats to the first two.
Pushed to settle 5Ls behind the leader from a wide gate, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, ran on nicely for 4th.
Taken back from a wide barrier, settled 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, made minor ground in straight.
Raced midfield, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some progress along the inside run until 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced until final 100M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield about 6.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, swung wide but found nothing.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, ridden rounding the home turn but only kept on one pace until 200M flattened.
Taken back from a wide gate, travelled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, never a factor.
Taken back from a wide gate, settled 8Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never looked likely. (Heart Irregularity)
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, then travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader at good sectionals, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, eased down shortly after straightening. (Questioned for performance, see incident report)
Fair break, nudged along rail to track lead, shifted out a touch 700m, driven 350m, grinding run to wear down leader & snare win on nod.
Speed to lead wide, crossed to rail 750m, 1L clear & hard-ridden 350m, battled on determinedly, mugged at line.
Rousted at break to race rail fore of midfield, under pump 500m, stayed on gradually to go 3rd 100m, kept on to wire without threatening.
Broke well & prominent, soon settled 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, shifted wider turning in, gradual inroads to snare 4th late.
Broke OK, initially 3 wide behind midfield, drifted back & bustled 800m, hard-ridden centre track for solid inroads to wire.
Broke well, driven to race handy wide no cover, very wide on turn to 2nd 400m, outpaced by first two, boxed on until no extra at 200m & tapered.
Missed break, raced rail last pair, shifted out 600m, stayed on dourly in stretch for minor headway.
Sluggish start wide, raced 3 wide no cover midfield, edged very wide & hard-ridden home turn, plugged on evenly until tapered late.
Slow start, raced last pair on outer, shifted wider & ridden 450m, plodded on one pace in stretch.
Tardy start, niggled to roll on & race midfield 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, outpaced in tepid run home.
Broke OK, speed to roll on & sit handy 2nd 1 off no cover, forced wider & shuffled to 4th 700m, driven but found nothing turning in & faded tamely.
Moderate start to race rail midfield, bustled 800m, driven 600m & outpaced to tail turning in, quickly tailed off.
Dropped in to rail behind midfield, steadied off heels 800m, smooth progress stalled on heels 300m, shifted out & driven 250m, flew to lead close home.
Fast break, led rail, headed 1300m & settled 1 back 1050m, scrubbed into home turn, battled to 2nd 300m, kept on but held at wire.
Prominent 3 wide early, unable to slot in so to lead & across to rail 1050m, 1L clear & shaken up 430m, all out 150m, headed 50m, no extra.
Slow break, overraced early & covered at tail, settled rear rank 1 off, fanned wide into stretch, shaken up 400m, closed off well centre track.
Sluggish start, rolled to rail midfield, shifted 1 off 800m, driven into stretch, stayed on evenly to wire.
Slow start, raced rear rank on rail, driven into stretch & shifted off fence, stayed on for fair headway.
Tardy start, niggled 1 off with cover behind midfield, hard-ridden turning in, plugged on one pace.
Broke OK, unable to slot, rolled on to dispute lead 1300m, steadied to 3rd 1 off no cover, 2nd & driven home turn, emptied 300m & swamped.
Broke OK, taken back to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, shifted wide home turn & driven into stretch, outpaced & eased when beaten.
Slow start, ridden & soon prominent, snagged back 1400m to sit handy 1 off with cover, 3 wide on turn, outpaced & found nothing in weak run to wire.
Taken back at break, caught 3 wide with cover midfield, bustled on 800m, 4 wide progress home turn, fading when off heels 250m, no extra.
Broke well, sat midfield 1 off with cover, overraced 800m & shifted 3 wide, wider into stretch, plugged on tamely & eased when beaten.
Tardy start, raced rear rank 3 wide with cover, to tail 950m, niggled 800m & hard-ridden very wide home turn, found nothing & struggled.
Ridden to dispute lead 1300m, settled 2nd 3 wide no cover, niggled 600m & lost place on turn, wilted into stretch.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, made early kick 500M to take advantages of the slow pace, ran on to win.
Pushed to hold the rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 250M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Pushed to keep up in front of midfield, 2Ls off the leader along the fence, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 3-4 wide, dashed well 250M despite all negative racing situations.
Eased back, took rail, 7.5Ls off the leader, little dash in straight despite not suited by the slow pace.
Settled in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Very slow away, pushed to obtain a midfield spot along the fence, 4.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, however soon emptied 400M.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no progress.
Never competitive at rear.
Eased to sit midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, raced very keen, not suited by the slow pace, emptied 300M.
Slow to muster, hard ridden forward, trapped 3-4 wide outside the lead, hung out and reduced rapidly 500M.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, faded quickly 500M.
Jumped OK, ridden forward but forced 3-wide without cover passing 800m. Covered extra ground turn, took lead 250m and kicked clear, held off late challenge.
Knuckled over start losing left from plate. Clear last on settling, last and widest entering straight, ran home strongly.
Jumped fairly, ridden to hold rail but not pressed and dropped to near rear. Got head up when awkwardly placed 500m, found clear run 250m and finished off nicely.
Pressed forward to take lead on settling, set steady pace to straight, caught passing 250m but boxed on well until swamped final 50m.
Began fairly, ridden along but wide to home turn. Taken further out entering straight and kept on steadily to be closest at finish.
Pressed forward but prevented from crossing by inside horses and held 3-4 wide turn. Rolled forward to sit outside leader 700m, kept on well in straight until flattened 50m.
Steadied soon after start and then steadied, racing 3-wide in midfield but with cover. Covered extra ground turn, closed in steadily to 200m turning one-paced.
Began well, ridden to get box seat, checked 700m when crowded, saved ground around turn, still in contention 200m before fading. Lame left front.
Jumped OK, ridden along in midfield before hampered 700m losing position. Found inside run turning for home but limited response.
Aggressively ridden from inside draw but failed to muster, settling fifth close to rail. Hampered 700m, hard ridden to hold position turn, faded straight.
Began awkwardly, no pace, dropping to rear. Never competitive.
Always prominent, driven to lead 250M and powered away towards the line (fastest final 400M of the day).
Along stands' rail just behind leader, ran on steadily for 2nd but couldn't match winner's turn of foot final 200M.
Tracked leaders, kept on evenly over final 300M, no impression on winner.
Never far off, within 2Ls of leaders throughout, stayed on reasonably well over final 300M. Encouraging effort having been off the track for 8 months.
Sped to lead, headed 250M, weakened towards the line.
Reserved in the rear, gave limited response when driven 400M, ran past well beaten runners only.
Held up at the back, failed to pick up passing halfway, never troubled leaders.
Settled towards the rear along the stands' rail, urged along inside 400M but never going the pace to challenge.
Settled on the outside of field, near rear, hung out 600M, didn't respond to riding.
Chased the pace, struggled to keep up halfway, soon out of contention.
Prominently placed just off the pace, found nothing when driven near 400M, eased over final 300M.
Began well, ridden along behind pace but boxed in passing 800m. Badly held up for run 300m, shifted in, forged through narrow gap 100m for close win.

Began OK, not pressed, settling midfield along outer fence. Took closer order entering straight proper, shifted in for clear run, hit front 150m, run down final stages. Found to have substantial blood in trachea.
Began well, settling along outer rail behind leader. Got dream run 400m when leader drifted in, joined leaders 200m, boxed on well when passed.
Began fairly, outpaced, crossed towards outside fence. Improved position passing 300m, finished off nicely between horses final 100m.
Began OK, not much speed slipping to behind midfield along outer rail. Rolled forward passing 400m but held for clear running from 200m. Finished off well when clear 50m.
Began awkwardly, bumped and unbalanced. Mustered quickly to sit third behind leading pair from 800m. Pressed forward to lead 300m but tired quickly when passed.
Began well, ridden to take lead while crossing to outer fence. Dropped to second passing 500m, retook lead passing 300m, kept on till flattened 50m.
Began fairly, gradually crossing closer to outer fence. Rolled forward passing 400m but only one-paced final 200m.
Began well, ridden along to stay with pacemakers to 400m before giving ground gradually.
Began well, crossed to outer fence, momentarily headed 800m before retaking lead. Drifted in passing 500m, passed 400m, tired quickly.
Bumped soon after start, dropping to near rear. Raced greenly and shifted ground when put under pressure from 600m. Never competitive.
Bumped shortly after start, dropped to rear along outer fence. Never likely thereafter.
Began fairly, ridden along to sit in midfield between horses on settling. Taken to outer fence 500m to make challenge but found nothing, faded.
Began awkwardly, steadied and taken to centre track. Hard ridden to make ground 400m but found nothing and tired quickly.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, travelled well and enjoyed the slow sectionals, led near 200M, kept on well to hold off the challenge and scored.

Began fairly from gate 7, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with cover, 6 lengths back throughout, still there to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off well, pressed winner from 100M but always held.

Fairly to begin, positioned nicely 1-2 lengths behind the leader in 3rd, ideal run to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly in straight without posing any threat to the first two.
Jumped well, took the lead easily and set slow tempo, enjoyed the unchallenged lead to turn, but didn't show much turn of foot in straight, just kept on fairly to make frame.
Average to begin, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover, 1-2 lengths back, ridden after turning in but didn't show any turn of foot, only kept on evenly after hard run took toll.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2-3 lengths back, 3 wide with cover at turn, angled out after turning in, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 5, raced on rail behind midfield, 4 lengths back, gradually improved on turn, but made no more progress in straight, just finished off one-paced.
Jumped well from wide draw, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at the back of the field, under pressure turning, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 lengths back on rail at rear, niggled along the rail to turn, no daylight early in straight, made little progress thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail, in front of midfield, saved ground to turn, no daylight early in straight, but made no progress when clear afterwards.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back, angled out after turning in, made no progress in straight, never competitive.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 4-5 lengths back, similar position to turn, made no progress in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, taken back to race at tail, 6 lengths back, kept to inside after straightening and got traffic early in straight, failed to close off thereafter.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover in midfield for the majority of the race, weakened gradually after turning in. (See racing incidents)

Settled just worse than midfield one off the rails, made swift progress passing the Rock to hit the front 500 metres out, narrowly headed entering straight but re-gained advantage under pressure over 150 metres out.

Settled towards the rear to obtain cover behind eventual winner and chased him when he quickened from the Rock, fought on doggedly from 1.5L 3rd into straight, unable to peg him back the length of the straight.

Broke well from the widest gate, settled outside leader, commenced run over 450 metres out in response to eventual winner's early move around the bend, hit the front into straight and led until no extra 150 metres out.
Jumped well, given reminders to maintain one-out-one-back position in 4th, commenced move when passed by eventual winner 500 metres out, ran on from 3L 5th into straight, did best work late.
Given reminders shortly after jump settling just better than midfield in 5th on rails, shuffled backward around the bend but saved ground turning in, produced good late impression closing stages.
Settled in last few on rails to the inside of eventual 2nd, commenced move after him at Rock to be rear of midfield in 4L 7th into straight, sustained progress without threatening.
Broke well from a low draw, settled one back in 3rd on rails, left flat-footed on the bend when pace quickened but saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Jumped very awkwardly, settled in midfield on rails, left flat-footed when pace quickened after the Rock but saved ground turning in, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening.

Broke well to lead, crossed to rails passing winning post the first time and set slow early sectionals, lost slender lead to eventual winner's early move at 500 metres when left flat-footed, dropped out from 3rd into straight.
Taken back from a poor gate to tail-end of field, remained well behind on rails to straight, ran past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Niggled along to gain better than midfield position early settling 2 wide in 6th about 3L off the slow pace, came under pressure around home bend, made no impression in straight.
Gradually settled at the back from a middle draw, went wide home turn, did nothing in straight.
Travelled midfield, 1 off with cover. Swung deep on the home turn wide and closed off strongly.
Began full of running, eventually settling 4th, 1 off with cover. . Had every chance, was nailed late.
Camped 3 back the fence with cover. Didn't have the clearest of passages passing the 200m, worked home soundly.
Settled in 2nd position, 1 off with cover. Was still there at the 100m, faded late.
Parked worse than midfield on the rails with cover. Struck interference near the 600m, recovered to finish off fairly.
Went back from an outside gate, travelling towards the rear on the fence with cover. Received a steady near the 600m, never on went on with it.
Led early from an inside gate before handing up early and box seating. Faded over the final 150m.
Posted 3 deep without cover for most of the trip behind midfield. Was one paced in the final stretch.
Raced worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Failed to make any appreciable ground in the straight.
Settled a long last on the fence, with cover. Plodded to the line along the inside.
Showed no early speed settling well back, coursed wide in the middle stages, eventually racing 2-3 wide with cover. Was one paced in the straight.
Was wide early before rolling forward and leading on the rails after the 800m. was a beaten horse near the furlong.
Pushed forward to settle 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slow sectionals, finished off well to score by 1/2L.
Began awkwardly, then travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, made an early move rounding the Home Turn, ran on nicely for 2nd despite harmed by the slow tempo.
Began awkwardly, then pushed to settle 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, closed to the line well to claim 3rd despite not suited by the slow pace.
Sent forward to park outside the leader at slow sectionals, took the rail and led on its own 850M, kept on strongly until 100M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, ran on gradually but without real threats.
Taken back to last from wide barrier, travelled 7.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slow tempo, made some ground in straight. (Questioned for riding, see incident report)
Eased back early, then allowed to stride forward gradually to park outside the leader 1200M, weakened over the last furlong.
Taken back from wide barrier, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Pushed forward to take the fence and share the lead at slow pace, dropped off when the pace quicken 800M, one paced home.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the slow tempo, never ran on. (Rider reported for disappointing performance, see incident report)
Always at rear, never a factor.
Broke OK, caught 3 wide no cover, rolled to 2nd 1000m & soon slotted 1 off, pressed lead 400m, led 300m & in command, kept on to hold late threat.
Broke OK, raced 1 back on rail, scrubbed 600m, responded & gradually stayed on to 2nd 50m, closed to wire.
Smart start, soon led on rail, driven under pressure 400m, headed 300m & boxed on in pursuit, tapered & lost 2nd 50m out.
Taken back to race last pair 1 off with cover, switched 3 wide 700m, driven & very wide home turn, stayed on centre track for good headway.
Broke with others, sat midfield 3 wide with cover, lost cover 800m, ridden for progress 550m, edged to 3rd 300m, lost place 200m & faded.
Broke OK, taken back & settled rail midfield, switched out & driven 400m, all out for progress to 5th turning in, plugged on evenly centre track.
Taken behind at break to rail near rear, driven 450m, shifted out in stretch, battled on for minor inroads.
Bustled at start, off heels & shuffled back 1st turn to behind midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 500m, plugged on under drive.
Sharp start, snagged back & overraced, settled midfield, switched wide & hard-ridden 400m, boxed on one pace until emptied & tapered final 150m.
Broke OK, drifted back to last pair on rail, to tail 700m, driven 450m, plodded past beaten rivals in tepid run home.
Taken back near tail initially, soon rolled on 3 wide with cover to behind midfield, driven on 550m, widest into stretch, found nothing.
Fast break to lead, snagged & soon handy 1 off no cover, shuffled to 4th 1 back 1 off 800m, driven & weakened 500m, tailed off in stretch.
Fast start, snagged to track 1 off with cover 5th, driven 500m, closed-off centre track under vigorous drive to lead 100m, fought on.
Broke well & bustled early to sit 4th 1 back on rail, driven 330m & shifted out, to narrow lead 150m, headed 100m, battled to wire.
Broke OK & bustled initially to settle midfield rail, keen backstretch, driven 300m, closed off to take 3rd 100m without threatening.
Smart start & bustled initially to sit handy 3 wide no cover, vied for 2nd 700m, ridden to press lead 400m, every chance, boxed on one pace.
Taken to rail behind midfield, overraced 1000m & shuffled back, advanced on turn, driven 300m, progress when crowded 150m, kept on.
Missed break, rolled to sit 1 off with cover behind midfield, ridden 450m & wide into stretch, kept on for minor gains.
Sharp start wide, taken back to 3 wide near rear, hard-ridden 400m, outpaced on outer into stretch, stayed on for moderate late gains.
Dropped in at break to 1 off with cover near tail, off heels 500m & driven, kept on gradually under strong drive.
Fast start to lead, soon to rail, pressed 400m & shaken up turning in, headed 150m & weakened out.
Fair break, settled 3 wide with cover midfield, overraced 820m, driven 400m, very wide home turn, plugged on one pace until tapered late.
Taken to tail from widest gate, raced 3 wide with cover, 8L back & driven turning in, stayed on for some minor late headway.
Fast break, sat close 2nd 1 off no cover, 3rd & driven into stretch, soon under pressure, folded 250m & faded tamely.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, kicked away 200M to score again impressively.
Eased back, raced keenly, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, dashed well 250M for 2nd.
Settled in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 250M for 3rd.
Awkward away, 4.5Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, made some ground in straight.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Pushed early, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead, under pressure throughout, not suited by the fast sectionals, hung on until 200M flattened.
Hard ridden forward, 1L off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, reduced quickly 300M.
At back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no turn of foot.
Pushed early to keep up in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 6Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, no progress.
Eased early to search for cover in midfield, however raced keenly, allowed to stride forward, shared the lead 2 wide at fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Began fairly, pressed forward, took lead 800m and crossed in sharply. Joined 600m, retook lead entering straight, kept on strongly to line.
Began fairly, ridden to hold rail and box seat into turn. Came off fence 300m and kept on well to be closest at finish.
Jumped OK, steadied to find cover but shuffled back. Improved position around turn, switched in 300m, ran home steadily. Injured right tendon.
Began well, aggressively ridden but failed to muster and trapped wide behind midfield. Improved around turn, switched out straight and ran home steadily.
Jumped best, led to 800m, crossed in an settled outside leader. Rolled forward to join leader 600m, 2nd into straight, kept on till flattened 50m.
Jumped fairly, pressed forward but checked 750m. Held one-off, one-back position entering final turn, but only one-paced in straight.
Jumped fairly, ridden along close to rail in midfield before checked 750m. Taken wide entering straight but found little under hard riding.
Ridden along early but trapped wide, then shuffled back entering turn. Found little under hard riding in straight.
Pressed forward from outside gate and trapped three-wide without cover behind leading pair. Covered extra ground turn, kept on steadily in straight before tiring final 150m.
Began well, ridden along between horses till checked 750m, dropping to midfield. Covered extra ground turn, faded gradually in straight.
A little slow into stride, outpaced and dropped to rear. Hard ridden in straight but failed to muster. Bled from both nostrils.
Began fairly, taken across behind horses but soon lost touch with field. Never competitive.
Settled nicely ahead of midfield, in 5th place turning for home, quickened up well under confident riding, swept past the leaders inside 100M for a back to back victory.
Caught wide first 400M, crossed to the lead 1100M, quickened up again passing 300M, unable to fend off winner final 100M but held on for 2nd well.
Unable to slot in, caught wide no cover until 600M, pressed leader home turn, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Held up at the rear along the 2-path,7Ls off the pace as they settled, nudged along 450M, made stealthy headway in straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled behind midfield, 3-wide with cover throughout, stayed on mildly over final 300M for moderate 5th.
Towards the rear, taken to a 3-wide spot entering back straight, ran on fairly turning home and never a serious threat to leaders.
Tracked leader in a 2-wide position, had no cover until reaching home turn, driven and no impression on leaders early straight, faded passing 200M.
Switched off to last, not hurried, detached from the field 500M, made some progress turning home but never got into contention.
Set early pace, tracked leader from 1100M, lacked further response when driven 350M, weakened mid-straight.
Fractious in stalls, slowly away, travelled in mid-division first half, shuffled back a bit passing 800M, not picked up when pressed along leaving the bend. (Lame next day.)
Began well, restrained to race behind mid-division, kept on same pace final 400M, never factored.
Tracked leaders early stages, dropped back to midfield back straight, under pressure 500M, soon no extra and dropped away rapidly.
