Jumped well, settled in midfield, obtained clear run passing 400 metres, ran on and asserted authority close to home.
Jumped awkwardly, gradually settled in 4th or 5th just over 2L back, gained closer turning in, ran on steadily to hit the front briefly inside 200 metres only to be headed about 100 metres out.
Broke well from a poor draw, niggled along to hold prominent position early and remained there and thereabouts, fought on to hold every chance 200 metres out, unable to sustain effort close to home.
Settled behind midfield on rails, shifted off rails for a run upon straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Ridden from the widest gate to join leader taking over approaching home bend, led until headed over 200 metres out, soon faded.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, settled 3-wide with cover in midfield, similar turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Jumped moderately, settled at the back, made up good ground closing stages down the centre of the straight.
Ridden early settling in midfield or just worse, towards the rear turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Slow to muster, improved along rails to join last few of field after first 200 metres, saved ground turning in, produced some late impression closing stages.
Jumped moderately, settled wide with cover behind midfield, similar turning in, kept on same pace in straight.
Jumped well from the middle draw, settled not far off pace 3-wide without cover, remained similar turning in, faded in straight.
Jumped awkwardly, soon taken back for cover on rails shuffling further back 1200 metres out, in forward of midfield turning on rails turning in, found nothing in straight.
Jumped moderately, always in last few and difficult to settled far side, made no impression in straight.
Jumped moderately, soon ridden to close-up spot pulling to the front 1300 metres out, taken back for cover approaching home bend, folded up quickly after straightening.
Went straight to the front and led on the fence. Made every post a winner thereafter and won with some authority.
Settled midfield, 2 wide with cover. Switched back to the inside near the 200m to continue into clear running, kept on nicely.
Raced ahead of midfield, 3 deep with cover. Maintained a good even gallop right to the wire.
Posted 3 deep without cover whilst in the leading trio. Kept on gamely despite the tough trip.
Parked behind midfield, 3 wide with cover. Shifted deep on straightening and finished off soundly.
Missed the start, settling midfield on the paint with cover. Recovered after being checked early in the straight, closing off satisfactorily.
Made its run back in the field after settling 3rd last, 1 off with cover. Shifted widest in the straight and made pleasing ground to the post.
Settled a distant last close to the rail with cover. Made steady progress in the straight, passed tiring runners. (see incident report)
Crowded for room at the start, settling 2nd last on the paint with cover. Worked home one paced.
Had no excuse after settling 1 out 1 back. Failed to find any extra in the home straight and was running on empty at the furlong.
Travelled just behind the speed but was caught 4 deep without cover on the circle. Never likely and finished well back.
Camped 2nd outside the leader. Was under pressure turning for home and was gone after the 300m.
Had every chance after box seating. Struggled in the home stretch and finished tailed out. (To trial).
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, dashed strongly 150M to score by 1/2L.
Raced midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow pace, finished off well for 2nd.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow sectionals, ran on steadily to lead 150m, headed 50M.
Camped handy, settled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slow pace, kept on well to the line.
Settled worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow tempo, ran home nicely.
Taken back from wide draw, settled 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, closed to the line well.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite benefited by the slow pace, only kept on the same pace to the line.
Pushed to settle midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite hampered by the slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Began badly, then travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, made minor ground in straight.
Sent forward to share the lead on the fence at slow tempo, kept on until last furlong weakened.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead at slow sectionals, kept on until last furlong weakened.
Raced midfield, settled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Eased back, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, never ran on. (Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
Travelled keenly and trapped 3-4 wide without cover throughout, never a factor.
Speed to lead on rail, shaken up & pressed 400m, driven in head-bobbing duel, edged advantage 200m, all out & just held on at wire.
Moderate start, rolled to 2nd 1 off 1350m, vied for lead 400m, matching strides when slightly unbalanced 200m, rallied final 100m, just failed.
Sharp break, raced 1 back on rail, driven 400m, grinding rail run to close, just failed.
Fast start, caught 3 wide no cover & snagged to 5th, to close 3rd 800m, pressed lead into stretch, battled determinedly but edged out of frame late.
Broke well, settled back rail midfield, switched 3 wide for progress 850m, 4 wide & pressed leaders 400m, peaked on run 300m, kept on evenly.
Broke OK wide, taken back to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, wide & driven into stretch, closed off for sound late gains.
Allowed to drift back at start, sat midfield 1 off, switched 3 deep with cover home turn, crowded in stretch, checked in run 250m, kept on evenly.
Broke well, snagged to race midfield 3 wide with cover, advanced on turn & driven wide into stretch, stayed on evenly to wire.
Tardy start, raced rail behind midfield, shifted 1 off 600m, driven 400m but stuck in behind, checked & switched out 300m, solid late headway.
Snagged back to race near tail 1 off with cover, taken wide on turn & 6L back into stretch, ran home well for minor inroads.
Fast start, prominent & overraced wide, soon slotted handy 1 off with cover, hard-driven & outpaced 400m, boxed on same speed.
Taken behind to rail in rear, hard-ridden turning for home, stayed on one pace for modest headway.
Outpaced & scrubbed early, progress to settle rail midfield, switched out turning in, ridden 400m, found little in tepid run home.
Restrained widest, taken to tail & raced 1 off, under pump 450m, found nothing, lost touch in weak run to wire.
Smart start, stalked lead in 3rd 1 off 1 back, smooth progress to 2nd tuning in, led & shaken up 350m, pressed to wire, battled & just held on.
Bumped start, camped midfield 1 off with cover, to rail 800m, switched out home turn & driven, quickened to 2nd 250m, pressed lead, held to wire.
Taken back to 1 off in rear, 3 wide on turn, stuck behind runners until switched widest 4L back at 200m, flew to snag 3rd last stride.
Taken to rail at tail, shifted 1 off 600m, driven into stretch, sound headway to 3rd 150m, mugged for place last stride.
Missed break, raced rail near tail, shifted 1 off 800m, in pocket 400m, switched inside & driven 200m, strong late headway, just missed frame.
Broke OK, caught wide & ridden early to race midfield 3 wide with cover, driven wide final turn, boxed on evenly.
Broke well widest, dropped in 1000m to midfield 1 off with cover, driven under pressure 450m, crowded 400m, stayed on one pace.
Broke OK & bustled to race rail fore of midfield, under pump 400m & outpaced, plugging on when checked off heels 150m, kept on.
Bumped start, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, shifted 3 wide 800m, driven wider home turn, kept on moderately.
Moderate break, overraced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, forced 4 wide no cover 800m, shaken up 400m, headway until tapered final 150m.
Broke OK, pace to race handy 4th but caught 3 deep no cover, shifted 4 wide into stretch, outpaced & plugged on tamely.
Speed to lead & raced keenly, crossed to inner 1200m, pressed for lead until strode 1L clear 900m, headed & driven 350m, weakened thereafter.
Tardy start, raced rail midfield, niggled & drifted back 800m, hard-ridden near tail 430m, plodded on tepidly.
Fast break, pushed on to vie for lead on outer, settled 1L 2nd 900m, shifted wide on turn, driven all out 400m, faded in run.
Pressed forward, 2Ls off the fast pace 3 wide, closed off strongly 250M to score comfortably.
Pushed forward to take rail and led by 2Ls, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well until 200M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Slow away, 5.5Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 4-2, ran on strongly when clear.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace, made ground 250M.
Very slow away, took rail at rear, 8Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
At back, 8Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 300M.
Slow away, hard ridden forward, 4Ls off the fast pace 3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pushed forward to obtain the box seat, not suited by the fast pace, ran on until 200M flattened.
Midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Eased back, 9Ls off the leader 2 wide, advantaged by the fast tempo, made minor ground.
Eased back, 9Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Pushed forward to sit outside the lead, not suited by the fast sectionals, out of fuel 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, however emptied 350M.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, soon reduced 500M.
Ridden along early to maintain forward position and held 3-wide with cover. Ridden patiently hands and heels, turned 4-wide into straight, finished off strongly.
Ridden along to stay with leading pack and kept 3-wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, 3-wide into straight, joined leaders 300m, kept on gamely when passed 150m.
Jumped OK, restrained and held at rear in a one-off position. Switched out turning for home, picked up momentum from 200m, finished off nicely.
Steadied shortly after start, restrained and held at rear close to rail. Saved ground turn, stayed on rail and ran home steadily despite restricted room from 300m to 200m.
Began well and soon in one-off, one-back position. Steadied 1100m, recovered and travelled comfortably to turn. Shaken up 350m but found little. Kept on one-paced.
Hard ridden from outside draw to sit outside leader on settling. Travelled well around turn, moved forward to challenge 300m, kept on till flattened 50m.
Crowded at start, ridden forward before over-racing and getting close to heels 1100 losing position. Three-wide into straight and one-paced under hard riding.
Began fairly, outpaced and distant last back stretch. Closed in approaching turn, switched wide entering straight, ran past tired horses.
Began fairly, ridden along to hold rail 3-back from leader. Saved ground turn, came off fence 400m but one-paced under hard riding.
Jumped well, ridden along early to hold box seat before turn. Gave ground steadily soon after entering straight.
Began best and soon had uncontested lead. Set steady pace around turn, joined up front 300m, gave ground steadily.

Taken back to the rear, bid wide 700M and advanced to a contending position leaving the bend, quickened impressively once asked, was strongly challenged form both sides from 200M, asserted towards finish.
Restrained to race behind midfield, settled nicely along the 2-path, kept to inside passing 450M, quickened to join DESIGNS ON ROME 200M, briefly in front 100M but winner found extra final stages.
Dropped in from widest draw, settled last, switched widest passing 700M and headway on turn into straight, chased eventual winner final 350M, always held.

Rolled forward, caught 3-wide first 600M, shared lead briefly from 1400M then eased back for cover, moved out to 4-wide top of the bend, left flat-footed by top 3 from 300M, kept on evenly for distant 4th.
Never far off from leaders, 3-wide and no cover from 1200M, soon moved forward to join leader, outpaced by top 3 inside 300M, kept on same pace for remote 5th.
Held up midfield on inner, in touch turning for home, short of room early straight, stayed on for non-threatening 6th.
Unable to get closer than 3-wide for most of the trip, travelled in mid-division, ran on one paced, no impression on leaders.
Soon moved to the lead, pressed by rivals back straight and went quick middle stages, headed 250M, weakened and no extra final 100M.
Caught wide no cover early stages, joined leader passing 1200M, eased back to sit behind the pace nearing home turn, unable to quicken with leaders final 300M.
Settled in midfield along the 2-path, within striking distance turning for home, failed to quicken.
Tracked leaders along the rails, left flat-footed when pace quickened 450M, weakened final 200M.
Slow to begin, held up towards the rear along the rails, not picked up passing 400M, eased when no chance final 100M.
Eased after the start, proved difficult to settle early stages and no closer than 3-wide throughout, came under pressure 500M, soon out of contention.
Went forward, tracked leaders early stages, eased back to mid-division back straight, had little left when driven out 400M, eased final 150M.
Blundered start, pushed along 3-4 wide to sit on hind-quarters of leader 1300m. Took over running 400m, kept kicking when challenged, just held.
Began OK, ridden along to hold rail 2-back from leader. Saved ground turn, behind horses top of straight, got split 200m, finished strongly.
Began fairly, restrained, dropping back to near last. Came off fence 800m, improved position turn, switched wide 400m, finished off strongly.
Got off OK, ridden along between horses to stay ahead of midfield. Rolled forward entering straight, looked chance 200m, no extra close home.
Taken across behind horses from wide draw and clear last back stretch and turn. Got split between horses 350m, picked up momentum and doing best work final 200m.
Began awkwardly, lost ground and cut to fence. Made up some ground before 800m, bumped twice around turn, kept on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Jumped OK, ridden along to hold fence 3-back from leader. Came off fence 600m, kept on steadily in straight.
Began well, ridden along 3-wide and left without cover from 1300m. Allowed more rein 800m, covered extra ground turn, 3rd into straight, gave ground steadily final 200m.
Began OK, ridden along behind midfield but trapped wide. Inconvenienced around turn, wide in straight, one-paced.
Restrained early and taken closer to fence at rear, Closed in steadily around turn and made some headway in straight while hanging out under pressure.
Began well, pushed along outside early leader before easing into one-off position before turn. Left flat-footed when pace quickened 600m, kept on one-paced in straight.
Jumped well, hard ridden to stay with leaders before cutting to fence 1300m and holding box seat. Came off fence 500m, but soon under pressure, giving ground gradually.

Began well, soon in front. Caught on entering straight and faded. Jockey reported hotses did not relax and noticeable breathing noise. Performance unacceptable. Found to have substantial mucus in trachea (see raicing incidents).
Take across behind horses from wide draw, settling at rear in a one-off positions. Last entering straight and finished tailed off.
Jumped well from a wider gate, raced 3 wide with cover in front of midfield, 2 lengths back, improved on turn, kicked clear passing 300M, kept on well to hold off challenger late.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, same position to turn, finished off very strongly in straight, just missed.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, improved on turn, made good progress to take 3rd.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead and set a moderate tempo, travelled well to turn, headed near 300M, stayed on evenly to make frame.
Stumbled start, recovered to race 2 wide in front of midfield, 2 lengths back, similar position to turn, taken to inside after straightening and ran on evenly.
Fairly away, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, under pressure turning, made reasonable progress in straight but never a threat to the first few.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, same position to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced on rail at rear, 6 lengths back sharing rear, same position to turn, angled out in straight and made some progress.
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to position outside the leader throughout, showed no response after turning in and weakened gradually.
Fairly away, raced 2 wide at the back of the field, 6-7 lengths back, taken widest after turning in but only made minor progress.
Moderately away, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail in midfield, similar position to turn, one paced and failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, 6 lengths back, under pressure turning, made no progress in straight. (See racing incident and additional veterinary report)
Bumped start, positioned 4 lengths back on rail behind midfield throughout, easy run to turn, made no progress after turning in, never a factor.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race prominently on rail, saved ground to turn but weakened sharply after turning in. Never competitive.

Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4-5 lengths back, found rail near 600M, angled out after turning in and closed off very well to score.
Began well from gate 1, raced a length behind the leader in 3rd, saved ground and travelled well to turn, finished off well to get 2nd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at rear throughout, 6-7 lengths back, taken very wide in straight and finished strongly to get 3rd.
Jumped with them, raced on rail at rear, 5-6 lengths back, there to turn, made good progress to make frame.
Fairly away, raced in midfield, 3-1/2 lengths back, same margin to turn, angled out in straight and finished off evenly.
Jumped well, pushed to take the lead and set a faster tempo, ran on well until headed near 100M, emptied thereafter.
Began well, raced 2 wide in front of midfield, 1-2 lengths back, made no progress after turning in, kept on one-paced.
Slowly away, raced at tail for the majority of the race, still well back to turn, made some progress in straight.
Fairly away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide throughout, no cover at turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, recovered to race in midfield, 2 lengths back, kept to inside after straightening, failed to close off.
Began well from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 4-5 lengths back, taken to widest after turning in, showed no response in straight, never competitive.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, travelled wide and without cover throughout, weakened gradually after turning in, never competitive. (See racing incident)
Settled 5th early, 2 wide with cover. Peeled out and got going 3 deep prior to the home turn. Made a sweeping run and kept on well.
Settled 5th-6th in the run on the fence, had cover. Switched in early in the straight when disappointed for running, chased gamely over the latter stages.
Raced behind midfield, on the fence with cover. Peeled out rounding the home turn and had a nice cart into the race. Finished off soundly.
Made its run fourth from the rear, 1 off with cover. Finished off fairly without ever threatening.
Parked worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Was dour in the home stretch.
Set a genuine tempo in front, leading on the rails. Was nabbed at the furlong and was well beaten at the 100m.
Traveled back in the field from a wide gate, settling at the rear on the paint with cover. Plugged away in the straight.
Camped 4th, 1 off with cover. Hampered at the entrance to the straight, but was under pressure prior to that point, did nothing thereafter.
Travelled last on the paint with cover. Passed tiring runners in the home stretch.
Settled 2nd last, 1 off with cover. Shifted widest in the straight, failed to close off.
Had every chance after box seating. Was running on empty at the 150m.
Settled 2nd, 1 off with cover. Was under pressure approaching the home turn and was a beaten horse early in the straight.
Sent forward to share the lead on the fence, benefited by the slightly slow sectionals, kept on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slightly slow pace, ran on nicely for 2nd but not match with the winner.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slightly slow tempo, stayed on well for 3rd but without any serious threat.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the slightly slow sectionals, closed to the line well for 4th.
Settled worse than midfield, 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slightly slow tempo, dashed well.
Settled worse than midfield, 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slightly slow tempo, ran on only fairly.
Pushed to settle midfield, 5Ls off the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Eased to rear from wide gate, 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite not suited by the slightly slow pace, made some ground in straight.
At rear, 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Blundered on jumping, then ridden to park outside the leader, despite suited by the slightly slow sectionals, weakened badly after straightening.
Speed to lead on rail, rolled 3L clear 500m, quickened into stretch, tapered close home but untroubled at wire, made all.
Fast start, settled 2nd 1 off no cover, niggled 450m, driven in pursuit turning in, gradually closed on leader but always held.
Smart start to slot rail 1 back in 3rd , driven 300m, not pace of first two, kept on soundly without posing threat.
Snagged from wide gate, sat 3 wide no cover midfield, shaken up 450m, fanned wide into stretch, ran on for some late headway.
Sluggish start, raced rail behind midfield, under pump turning in, stayed on gradually for minor inroads.
Good break, settled midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 400m, stayed on for moderate headway.
Smart start, camped rail midfield, hard-ridden 500m, boxed home steadily.
Sharp break but caught wide in front rank, soon snagged back to 4th 1 off with cover, hard-ridden 450m, plugged on one pace.
Taken back at break, overraced 1000m, settled rear rank 1 off with cover, driven wide into stretch, stayed on for minor late gains.
Taken to tail from widest gate, sat 1 off, ridden 400m, running on centre track when stalled in pocket 150m, not fully tested.
Tardy break, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, ridden 500m, widest into stretch, found nothing.
Slow start, raced near tail on rail, hard-ridden final turn, struggled in stretch run.
Tardy break & niggled to settle rail midfield, niggled 500m to close & switched 1 off, strong closer in stretch to lead 100m, held on.
Bustled to sit 4th 1 off with cover, 6L off lead 900m, closed up & driven 3 deep 500m, wide into stretch, strong run to 2nd 60m, just failed.
Smart start, led rail until 1200m, sat 2L 2nd, pressed lead on outer from 500m, all out for narrow lead 300m, dug in but headed 100m, no extra.
Slow break, crossed to rail & settled midfield, ridden for progress 450m, sound headway to wire without threatening.
Good break, 2nd 1 off until led 1200m, to rail & drew clear 1000m, reeled in 500m, driven on turn & headed 300m, battled on but tapered.
Good break, settled rail 3rd, 5L off lead at 900m, closed to 1L at 500m, switched out & driven into final turn, kept on one pace.
Crowded start, soon at tail, settled rail last pair, ridden 400m, ran on for minor late headway.
Broke OK & handy early, settled back 3 deep no cover midfield, bustled forward 600m, driven wide home turn, boxed on evenly.
Restrained to race 1 off with cover near rear, driven 500m, stayed on evenly to wire.
Taken back to race 3 wide last pair, hard-ridden 400m, wide into stretch, stayed on for moderate inroads.
Taken behind to midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 500m & forced 3 wide, hard-ridden but plugged home tepidly.
Broke OK, caught 3 wide with cover towards rear, ridden 600m, widest into stretch, found nothing in tame run home.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 2Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, dashed well 250M to score.
Pushed forward, parked outside and 1L off the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, led 250M, overhauled 100M, ran on for 2nd.
Eased back, took rail, 5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, held up 400-200M, demonstrated strong finishing efforts when clear.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M, lack room 150M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1L, clocked slow sectionals, ran on until 150M flattened.
Pushed early, 2.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, held ground in straight.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
Bumped start, 3Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, held up 400-200M, no dash when clear.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the slow tempo, trapped 3 wide throughout, weakened 300M.
Hard ridden early but not muster and trapped wide, then eased back to sit 2 wide, 6.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Took rail at rear, not suited by the slow pace, never nearer.

Began OK, restrained and taken in closer to fence but lost position as outside runners moved forward. Started forward move 700m, swung very wide into straight, ran on strongly, holding off late challenge.
Jumped fairly, raced 3-wide to first turn before dropping back to last. Not hurried at tail, swung widest into straight, finished off strongly to just miss.
Pushed along early to hold midfield position, switching to rail 1300m. Steadied 750m. came off rail 400m to make challenge, ran on well between horses.

Bumped start, recovered and pushed along wide to go forward but held without cover from 900m. Allowed to improve to sit outside leader passing 600m, joint leader into straight, boxed on gamely under pressure.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail position but shuffled back passing Winning Post first time. Stuck to rail, saved ground final turn, ran home steadily.

Began fairly, taken in to rail but steadied 1400m when outside horses moved forward, dropping to near last. Shuffled back further final turn, behind horses entering straight, clear run from 300m but one paced.
Jumped OK, ridden along, settling midfield but 3-wide. Under pressure from 700m, rolled forward but wide turn, one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, got fired up and raced keenly with leaders to first turn before easing into box seat 1000m. Lost position final turn, found little under pressure 400m, one-paced.
A little slow into stride, ridden along in a one-off position between horses, taking closer order before final turn. Switched out entering straight but found nothing.

Hard ridden from widest draw to share lead to first turn before easing to third but wide entering back stretch. Wide into straight, kept on gamely to 150m when gave ground quickly. Lame left front leg.
Pressed forward but wide from good start, taking lead 1250m. Increased tempo 500m, passed 350m out, faded.
Began OK, niggled to maintain one-off position 1400m, travelled well to 600m when came off bridle. Under pressure final turn, gave ground steadily from 200m. Performance unacceptable.
Travelled comfortably in mid-division, switched out to clear 200M, dashed home strongly to score with something in hand.
Held up behind midfield along the 2-path, quickened well to challenge inside 300M but always held by winner over final 150M.
Quickly into stride, crossed to the fence chasing leaders, ran on well down inside, held narrow lead near 100M, caught by first two final stages. Promising debut.
Driven forward from wide barrier, settled one-out-one-back, briefly in front 250M, couldn't match finishing pace of first 3 final stages.
Settled towards rear, moved to outside passing 400M, closed off well.
Crossed to a 2-wide position with cover 900M, moved closer 400M out, kept on steadily, no impression on leaders final 100M.
Eased back, sat behind midfield, gave limited response final 300M.
Rushed to the front, led steadily to straight, caught 250M, weakened badly.
Bumped after the start, travelled at the back 7Ls off the pace, shifted in abruptly 600M, made no real progress in straight.
Settled towards the rear, travelled only fairly, failed to pick up when driven 400M, never involved.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward chasing leaders in a 2-wide position, under serious pressure 450M, dropped out of contention 300M.

Well there, held up in 2nd inside the early leader one off the stands rails, took up running 600 metres out, ridden cozily to easily fend off runner-up. (Lame next day)
Never far off, disputing lead coming onto course proper, fought on well but found winner too good.
Jumped well settling not far off the pace, came under pressure inside final 300 metres, kept on steadily without quickening.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon picked up to not far off the pace, reaching 2L 3rd briefly inside 400 metres, one-paced and lost placing late.
Not far off in early stages, yielded ground steadily from halfway out.
Jumped fairly, soon gained narrow advantage on stands rails, led until headed by eventual winner about 600 metres out, folded up quickly.
Travelled not too far back down the centre of the track, came under pressure coming onto course proper and soon weakened.
Jumped awkwardly, always struggling at the back of the small field.
Ridden with purpose in the early stages to cross and lead on the rails after the 1100m. Got a mid-race breather and in the straight kept finding all the way to the line.
Settled 4th, 2 wide with cover. Chased evenly right to the wire, despite having a tendency to lay in briefly after the furlong.
Raced behind midfield, 2 deep with cover. Rolled out on straightening, and finished off well.
Travelled back in the field, 1 off with cover. Shifted deep on straightening, made good progress down the running.
Enjoyed the box seat after the 1100m. Peeled out 3 deep turning for home, was a beaten horse near the 150m.
Parked midfield the fence, had cover. Kept battling away in the home straight.
Settled 4th last, on the fence with cover. Under pressure early in the straight, kept on steadily, passed tiring runners.
Parked ahead of midfield, on the paint with cover. Faded over the final 150m.
Camped midfield, 1 off with cover. Made no impression in the run to the line.
Settled last from a wide gate, 3 deep with cover. Came widest in the home straight, was dour in the stretch.
Went back from a wide alley, settling 3 deep at the rear, had some cover on the circle. Shifted with 1 wider in the straight, only plodded to the post.
Raced worse than midfield, close to the rails, with cover. Failed to close off.
Settled 2nd, 1 off no cover. Had every chance, but was well beaten at the furlong.
Showed no early dash and settled with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed on strongly to score impressively when clear 300M.
At rear, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, swung widest, finished off nicely to get 2nd.
Taken back from a wide gate, then travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed forward, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on well to the line.
Camped handy, settled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced home.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1/2L at good pace, hung on well until final 150M weakened.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, stayed on one paced until final 100M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Prominent, 2Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, flattened soon after straightening.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
Ridden forward to settle 1/2L outside the leader, run ended 300M.
At last throughout, never a factor. (Questioned for riding and also found substantial amount of mucopus in the trachea)
Smart start, settled back rail midfield, switched out on turn, driven 400m, solid run to lead 75m, edged verdict.
Bumped start, soon handy, snagged to cover 1 off 5th, shifted out & driven 500m, to lead 300m, hung across track, headed 75m, just beaten.
Smart start, tracked 1 off 1 back, switched out 500m, shaken up turning in to dispute lead, boxed on until tapered late.
Taken behind from wide, raced rear rank, minor progress 850m but last pair & shifted wide final turn, stayed on for sound late headway.
Missed break & bustled at tail, rail progress to behind midfield 800m, shifted out home turn, driven & stayed on one pace.
Fast break, sat rail 1 back, stuck in pocket home turn, daylight 300m, stayed on evenly.
Broke well, raced behind midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide on turn & driven, bumped 400m, plodded on tamely.
Broke OK, sat near rear 1 off with cover, off heels 850m & shifted wider, driven 500m, kept on evenly.
Sharp start wide to lead, to rail 1200m, headed 430m & driven, outpaced & weakened to wire.
Good break wide, crossed to sit 2nd 1 off no cover, ridden 430m, found little in tepid run home.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide no cover in rear rank, to tail 850m, under pump home turn, struggled in weak stretch run.
Good start wide, crossed to sit 3rd 1 off no cover, advanced to 2nd 750m, driven 420m to lead 350m, pulled clear.
Fast start & bustled to lead, crossed to rail 1150m, driven 400m, headed under pressure 350m, battled on to wire but always held.
Broke OK, sat rail midfield, switched out & driven into stretch, shifted wider 150m & ran on to 3rd 50m.
Tardy break, raced rail midfield, driven 430m, rallied for late gains to 4th close home.
Good start, sat fore of midfield 1 off with cover, progress on turn & driven to 3rd 400m, emptied & swamped close home.
Sharp break, bustled to sit rail 2 spots back in 4th, driven into stretch, outpaced & lost position, stayed on again for minor inroads to wire.
Disputed early lead, settled 1 back on rail 2nd, to 3rd 750m, shifted out in stretch & outpaced, boxed on in 4th until swamped late.
Fair break, bustled early, raced 1 off with cover midfield, advanced on turn, driven & outpaced into stretch, kept on one pace.
Restrained to race 1 off near tail, shifted widest into stretch & driven, plugged on for moderate headway.
Taken back to tail on rail, hard-ridden last turning in, plugged on one pace.
Broke OK, dropped back to behind midfield 1 off with cover, wide & driven 400m, found nothing in run home.
Slow start, raced rail near tail, shifted out 500m, wide into stretch, struggled & wandered under pressure.
Dwelt start, advanced rail initially & switched 1400m to 1 off with cover, advanced 850m to midfield, driven 400m, found little & faded weakly.
Taken behind & bustled to rail behind midfield, scrubbed & shifted out 500m, struggled & faded in weak stretch run.
Always prominent, 1.5Ls off the fast pace, closed off strongly 250M to score.
Pressed forward, just off the leader, not suited by the fast sectionals, hung on strongly until last few strides, just beaten by a neck.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Very slow away, 3.5Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 5.5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M.
2Ls off the fast pace, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased at start, 7Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, made steady ground when clear.
Pushed early, 5.5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, just held ground.
Hard ridden to lead by 1L, clocked fast sectionals, soon emptied 400M.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast pace, flattened 300M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 7Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, held up 4-2, ran on ok.
Failed to muster, 5.5Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace but never improved.
Pushed early, 4Ls off the leader, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Pressed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the fast pace, dropped off 400M.
Began fairly, restrained and taken closer to fence. Urged forward passing 800m, saved ground turn, got clear run 250m, ran home strongly.
Began fairly, taken across behind runners and settled at rear. Not pressured, no clear run top of straight, got split 150m, strong burst before run ended close to line.
Slow into stride, taken to fence and mustered quickly to sit two-back from leader 1000m. Saved ground turn, ran home steadily along fence to grab third.
Jumped fairly, outpaced and taken to fence. Clear last back stretch and final turn, switched widest in straight, finished strongly.
Began OK, ridden forward between horses, sitting two-back, one-off. Taken out turning for home, kept on steadily in straight.
Jumped well, restrained, taken closer to fence 3-back from leader. Taken out 800m, improved position turn, kept on steadily in straight. Rider queried (See racing incidents).
Began awkwardly, taken across behind horses settling near last along fence. Saved ground turn, stayed on rail in straight, ran home steadily to be closest at finish.
Began well, ridden along but unable hold position and shuffled back before turn. Turned wide and kept on steadily in straight.

Fractious in gate, jumped well, ridden but failed to muster and trapped wide without cover from 1300m. Rolled forward around turn to look chance 400m before fading gradually. Ride queried. (See racing incidents).
Jumped well, restrained to behind midfield but away from fence. Peeled out turning for home, rolled forward early in straight before run ended 200m.
Jumped OK, pressed forward to lead on settling, kicked clear entering turn but collared soon after straightening. Shifted out under pressure in straight while giving ground.
Pressed to go forward and trapped 3-4 wide outside leader to turn. Very wide into straight, kept on steadily to 200m, flattened.
Began well but proved difficult to settle early stages. Lost position around final turn and weakened gradually in straight.

Ridden along early to find cover but kept outside leader longer than intended. Hard ridden from turn, closed in top of straight before tiring quickly passing 200m. Jockey admitted ill-judged ride. (See racing incidents).
Settled just off the pace, driven along 350M and loomed a threat behind leaders, dug in 200M from home and was up final stages.
From draw 2 driven forward, crossed towards the stands' side contesting the pace, led 200M out, fought on through final 100M, caught late stages.
Within striking distance always, closed off well and moved strongly into contention 200M, held final stages.
Gently urged, emerged to lead along fence 600M, strongly pressed by another rival 400M out, fought on until giving in final 150M.
Dropped back towards the rear, not used until 400M, stayed on well.
Settled in midfield 3Ls off the pace, ran on one paced and never a threat to leaders.
In mid-division travelling along the stands' rail, switched out from fence 350M, checked 200M, ran on towards finish but no impression on leaders.
Slotted into a position behind midfield early stages, moved out to challenge passing halfway, not pace to challenge leaders.
Urged along, never far off from leaders, gave limited response over final 300M.
Worked his way to the front, gave up the lead 600M, was roused along halfway, lacked further response, faded towards the finish.
In mid-division but travelled only fairly, weakened 200M out, never involved.
Hung out early stages, ended up at the rear, didn't respond to riding final 400M and raced greenly.
Failed to muster, outpaced in the rear 6Ls off the pace, failed to respond inside 400M, never a threat.
Near the rear, under pressure halfway but had no closing bid.
Bumped start, restrained, taken in, settling at rear. Stayed on rail turn, switched out 400m to get clear running, ran on strongly to just get there.
Bumped start, ridden along early but wide, settling 2-back, one-off before turn. Threw out challenge entering straight, hit front 200m, caught on line.
Began best, led for 300m before settling behind leader entering turn. Moved up entering straight, joint leader 250m, kept on well when passed.
Bumped start, restrained, settling 3-back, one-off back stretch. Switched out turning for home, kept on well in straight despite being taken wide 100m.
Began OK, mustered along rail to hit front 1250m. Kicked clear 800m, joined up front 250m, kept on well till swamped final 50m.
A little slow into stride but picked up quickly settling in midfield along rail. Saved ground turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Began awkwardly, mustered and pressed forward to sit two back from leader before turn. Rolled forward entering straight, looked chance before one-paced final 200m.
Bumped start, held, taken across behind runners, settling last but away from fence. Put under pressure turning for home, taken to outside fence 400m, kept on steadily.
Began fairly, taken in from wide draw, settling 4-back the fence. Saved ground final turn and kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Jumped best but restrained, settling ahead of midfield in a one-off position. Put under pressure turn, made ground early in straight before turning one-paced.
Bumped start, taken across behind runners, settling toward rear. Hard ridden from 800m, awkward on heels, no clear running early in straight, one-paced.
Began fairly, not pushed, settling towards rear in one-off position. Taken very wide entering straight but limited response under pressure. Lame right front.
Began OK, ridden to obtain forward position and trapped wide without over in fifth place. Taken wider turning for home, found little in straight, tired final 200m.
Began awkwardly, shifted in, bumped. Hung in approaching 1400m, hard ridden from 700m, found nothing in straight, faded.
Moderately away, raced 3 lengths back in midfield, 2 wide same margin back at turn, challenged at 300M, finished off well to score with some in hand.
Jumped with them, showed early speed to race 2 wide in 4th, travelled well to turn, took over passing 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began well, raced 3 lengths back on rail in 5th, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening, closed off well without matching the first two.
Began awkwardly, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 6-7 lengths back, same position to turn, angled out in straight and finished off strongly to make frame.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently on rail in 3rd, same margin to turn, kept on evenly in straight, never a threat to the first few.
Slowly away, raced at rear throughout, 8-9 lengths back on rail, similar position to turn, made good progress along inside to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced 5-6 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, finished off evenly in straight without looking lively.
Fairly away, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 7-8 lengths back, similar position to turn, angled out after turning in and made reasonable progress final 300M.
Began well, sent forward to race at the front, took the lead near 1000M and set a moderate tempo for the mid-section, travelled well to turn, headed near 250M and weakened gradually thereafter.
Taken back from wide gate and raced at tail to 700M, improved on turn, still well back but made only moderate progress in straight.
Slightly slowly out, raced on rail behind midfield, 8 lengths back, similar position to turn, in traffic early in straight but failed to closed off thereafter.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, same margin back to turn, found nothing in straight and dropped out tamely.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, was last turning in, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Jumped well from the widest gate, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd outside leader throughout, under pressure turning, showed no response and weakened early in straight, never competitive.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, similar position to turn, finished off well to score a narrow win.
Fairly away from a tricky gate, taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths back, still last turning, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly, just missed.
Average to begin, raced 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, same position to turn, no daylight until 150M, closed off very well thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide in front of midfield, improved position on turn, hit lead briefly but soon headed, finished off evenly in straight to make frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6-7 lengths back on rail sharing rear, saved ground to turn, made good progress in straight, just missed frame.
Fairly away, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover for the majority of the race, wider at turn, peaked on run when work load took toll.
Average to begin, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail in midfield, similar position to turn, finished off fairly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6-7 lengths away, still well back to turn, there to turn, angled out early in straight and made minor progress late.
Began well, showed early speed to take the lead, enjoyed the uncontested lead throughout, headed near 200M and weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderate break, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, similar position to turn, finished off evenly in straight, never a threat.
Began awkwardly, positioned 6 lengths back on rail at rear, under pressure turning, made no progress in straight.
Jumped well from the widest gate, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, travelled well to turn, faded quickly in straight.

Moderately away, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 5Ls back, hampered near 900M, similar position to turn, angled out early in straight, checked near 200M, gave ground thereafter. (See racing incidents)

Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.

Jumped fairly, ridden along racing wide in midfield early stages, gradually improved to join 2nd approaching home bend, hit the front over 200 metres out, won readily.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, travelled 3-wide just better than midfield in 6th, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped well, soon taken back for cover travelling just worse than midfield 3-wide, ran on steadily down the centre of the straight.
Settled just off the pace on rails, gradually shuffled backward approaching home bend, saved ground turning for home, kept on well to finish.
Jumped fairly, travelled just better than midfield, baulked for a run approaching home turn and into straight, produced good late impression.
Soon took up running, let until headed on rails over 800 metres out, chased leader into straight, kept on one pace.
Jumped fairly, settled just behind midfield, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Niggled along, took up running 800 metres out, led until overhauled inside final 200 metres.
Broke well from a poor draw, raced prominently without cover far side, drifted back to 2L 4th around the bend, one-paced in the run home.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, ridden to soon join rear of field, remained towards the rear into straight, kept on without quickening.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, soon drifted back to last few, made no impression.
Soon in rear dropping to tail-end from halfway out.
Punched the breeze, 3 deep without cover, whilst racing in 3rd position. Powered forward approaching the 200m, and held on gamely.
Made its run from ahead of midfield, 3 wide with cover. Made gradual progress at the business end of the race, chased all the way down the running.
Parked worse than midfield, 3 deep with cover. Finished off well.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, settling well back in the field, 4 wide with cover. Came wide in the straight, finished off fairly.
Camped 2nd from the rear, travelling close to the rails, had cover. Battled away in the run home.

Didn't have the best of starts but recovered to spear through & take up the lead in the early stages on the fence. Under pressure turning for home, did not quicken in the straight and over the final 100m weakened noticeably.
Settled 2nd, 1 off without cover. Was well beaten after the 150m and faded quickly thereafter.
Settled towards the rear, 3 wide with cover. Made no impression in the run home.
Tracked the on pace runners, 2 wide with cover. Showed some dash approaching the furlong, but was gone at the 100m.
Settled 3 back the fence after beginning awkwardly, had cover. Railed up in the straight, found nothing when under pressure, yielding ground after the furlong.
Settled in last position, 3wide with cover. Struggled in the straight, finishing well back.
Raced deep, 4 wide without cover on the circle, travelling behind the speed in a handy position. Gave ground easily in the straight, never likely.
Hard ridden to settle 2.5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, finished off strongly to score by 1L.
Send forward as usual to settle 1.5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, ran on nicely to take the lead until final 50M for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3-4 wide with cover, dashed well to get 3rd but without any threats to the first two.
Prominent, trapped 3-4 wide without cover throughout, one paced home without threatening.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, 6Ls behind the leader 1-2 wide with cover, made some ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield 5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 5 wide without cover, never ran on.
Sent forward to take the lead on the fence at good sectionals, run ended 200M.
Hard ridden to park outside the leader at good pace, flattened badly 250M.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, never looked competitive.
Hard ridden along throughout, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
Jumped badly, never a factor.
Began well, ridden along in midfield to hold rail into back stretch. Came off fence 800m and got souffled back to near last, taken very wide 400m, ran home strongly to win on line.
Bumped start, recovered but held 3-wide into back stretch without cover. Rolled forward 800m, took lead 700m, kicked clear 300m, run down on line.

Began well and led for few strides but difficult to settle first turn. Raced in midfield to home straight, kept on steadily. Rider reported saddle slipped at start and again top of straight putting him at a disadvantage.
Jumped well, ridden to go forward despite racing 3-4 wide first turn. Cut in to rail back stretch, took box seat turn, looked chance 200m, kept on one-paced.
Began fairly, hard ridden from wide draw to take up running 1200m then slowed pace. Overtaken 700m, kept battling till 150m when one-paced.
Began OK, outpaced, settling at rear along fence. Improved position turn, came off fence 400m but cut back in 300m, kept on steadily.
Jumped well, pushed to take up rail position forcing other front runners to race wide. Stayed on fence 3-back from leader, taken out top of straight, one paced.
Ridden forward from wide draw and held wide first turn, settling two-back, one-off back stretch. Taken wider entering straight but only one-paced.
Bumped start, no speed, dropped to rear along fence. Shuffled back to last 800m, came off fence turn, one-paced in straight.
Bumped shortly after start, raced ungenerously to first turn, checked back stretch when a runner broke down. turned wide, found little in straight.
Bumped start, no speed, dropping to last in one-off position. Made forward move 800m but effort short-lived. One paced straight.
Began fairly, ridden along between horses first turn, hampered and taken wider 800m, lost touch with field around turn. Performance unacceptable.
Hard ridden from widest draw, racing wide first turn to sit behind leader. Shuffled back final turn, checked top of straight, faded. Unacceptable performance.

Placing: PU
Comment: Hard ridden to go forward from wide draw, settling midfield but wide back stretch when broke down 800m and pulled up.
Jumped well, ridden along in slipstream of leader in one-off position. Cut in top of the straight, drew level 150m, shifted out 100m bumped runner-up, edged ahead for solid win.
Began well, pressed forward to lead on settling but kept away from fence, kept good tempo, joined up front 150m, battled to line.
Jumped well, ridden along to hold one-back, one-off position on settling, turned a little wide, kept on well till faltered last few strides. Lame left front leg.
Pushed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader. Kept on well in straight without closing gap.
Jumped fairly, restrained and taken in to rail. saved ground turn, kept plugging away in straight without closing gap.
Jumped fairly, ridden to hold forward position but kept laying out. Kept on one-paced in straight while laying out.
Began fairly but ridden along to hold midfield position. Taken very wide in straight and only one-paced. Rider reported never travelled comfortably.
Began fairly, outpaced and soon at rear in one-off position. Stayed inside on turning for home but found little in straight.
Lost glue-on shoe before start and replaced with normal plate. Began OK, held behind midfield to turn, improved position early in straight, turning one-paced final 200m.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to near rear. Found little under hard riding in straight.
Began fairly, ridden to go forward but held wide in midfield. Taken wider in home straight but tired final 200m.
Jumped OK but no pace and last on settling. Lost contact with other runners before home turn. Unacceptable performance.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made early move 500M, dominated 300M.
Took rail easily and led by 0.5L at good pace, soon overhauled 350M, but hung on well for 2nd.
Pushed to obtain box seat, pace good, held ground for 3rd.
Eased back, 5Ls off the good pace 3 wide, checked 400M, progressed steadily 300M.
Midfield along the fence, 4Ls off the good pace, held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the good pace, ran on ok.
Hard ridden forward to sit outside the leader, pace good, out of fuel 400M.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 5.5Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, checked 400M, dashed fairly when clear.
Eased at start, 7Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on fairly.
Struggled to keep up at rear, 9Ls off the good pace on the rails, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the good pace 2 wide, emptied 400M.
Midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 3 wide, checked 400M, reduced 200M.
Slow away, 4Ls off the good pace 2 wide, dropped off quickly 400M.
Eased at start, never competitive at rear, eased out of race.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling. Kept up steady pace, kicked further ahead entering straight, won comfortably. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Began OK, ridden along behind the pace 3-wide to turn, tightened 500m, kept on well in straight.
Began OK, ridden along in midfield close to fence, taken out 500m to get clear running, kept on steadily in straight.
Began fairly, restrained and taken across behind runners to rail. Improved position steadily, saved ground turn, kept on steadily in straight while hanging out under pressure.
Jumped well, hard ridden but failed to muster and kept wide without cover. Swung widest into straight, finished off nicely.
Pressed forward from good draw to sit behind leader along back stretch and turn. Kept on till flattened 200m.
Began well, grabbing one-back, one-off position early before losing place around turn, Kept on one-paced in straight. Lame right fore.
Began awkwardly, ridden along early but wide, awkwardly placed entering turn, found little in straight under hard riding.
Began fairly, hard ridden but failed to muster, dropping back and taken across behind runners. Hung turn turn, found little in straight.
Began awkwardly, outpaced and clear last on settling. Stayed on rail turn, made up some ground before straight, one-paced.
Began fairly and steadied shortly after, dropping back. Shuffled back to last around turn, one-paced in straight.
Began well, pressed forward sitting 3-wide behind leader at turn. Gave ground steadily soon after straightening.
Taken across behind runners, settled last and unhurried over first half, bid wide 600M, closed off strongly entering straight, got up near line.
Moved forward under light coaxing, tracked leader from 1200M, advanced to the lead 400M, fought on gamely to the wire, headed close home.
Settled 3-wide towards the rear, came wider 600M and gradually improving, closed off steadily final 300M, well held by first two final 50M.
Along the fence in close aim of the leader, responded well entering straight, loomed a threat mid-straight chasing leader, one paced final stages.
Dropped back, held up towards the rear, switched wider 600M, stayed on mildly over final 300M, no impression on leaders.
Unhurried early stages, settled behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, moved closer nearing home turn, briefly went 3rd 250M, lacked further response final stages.
In 5th place not far off from the pace early stages, fell back to a position behind midfield halfway, made limited progress final 300M.
Sent forward, tracked leaders early stages, fell back a bit nearing home turn, failed to quicken final 350M.
Slow to begin, guided to the rails and settled 3-4Ls off the leader, kept on one pace in straight, never threatened.
Fractious in stalls, slowly away, no closer than 3-wide throughout, strode to a contending position passing 800M, faded 250M.
Settled 2-wide in mid-division, found rail near 700M, had to shift out for clear run turning home, lacked further response passing 200M.
Began awkwardly, taken back to near last, raced as the back-marker from 700M, badly outpaced by leaders passing 400M.
Driven from wide draw 12, got to the front 1300M and led uncontested, pressed by rivals 400M, had nothing in reserves and dropped away to last.

Pressed on to take up running on rails, led or disputed lead before going over 1L clear 200 metres, hung on well under pressure.
Jumped well from the one draw, taken back for cover on rails before checked and lost position 1400 metres out, remained on rails in midfield to straight, ran on without threatening.
Began from the widest draw, soon taken back across for inside run, shifted out for a run turning in, bumped heavily 300 metres out, sustained progress to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well, settled in handy position on rails, shifted off rails for a run on straightening, kept on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Settled towards the rear, baulked for a run 300 metres out and did not see much daylight the length of straight.
Began well from the middle draw, travelled wide in a prominent position before hitting the front narrowly 1000 metres out, shared pace around the bend, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Prominent to straight, shifted out for a run turning in, kept on steadily without threatening.
Broke well from a poor draw, soon shifted across to rear of midfield, badly baulked for a run and tightened 300 metres out, kept on well to the line.
Jumped poorly, soon shifted across for rails run at the rear, trailed the field into straight, made some late headway under pressure down the centre of the track.
Began moderately, settled on rails in rear of midfield, kept on before fading closing stages.
Always in last few and never seen with a chance.

Jumped quite well from a poor draw, soon taken to rear of field for cover, took closer order coming out of back straight, midfield and one of the widest turning in, badly jostled 300 metres out, no further impression.
Jumped in the air losing ground, towards the rear and 3-wide without cover far side before making swift progress to join leaders on top of home bend, soon dropped out in straight.
Jumped fairly, travelled not far off in 5th or 6th, soon dropped out under pressure in straight.

Shot out of the gates, obtaining cover in the early stages 3 back on the fence with cover. Raced a bit keenly on the circle, rolled out, travelling 1 off after the 700m. Hit the lead at the 50m, held on gamely.

Travelled midfield, 2 deep with cover. Peeled out after the 600m, and shifted with 2 wider on the home turn. Closed off strongly but did want to hang in and not want to go straight in the home stretch.
Cruised to the lead in the early stages, travelling on the fence. was overhauled inside the final 50m.
Camped 3rd from the rear, 1 of with cover. Swung deep on the home turn and finished off with plenty of purpose.
Enjoyed the box seat. Was flat out approaching the 200m, commenced to weaken soon after.
Settled on the circle 3 back, 1 off with cover. Taken wider after the 800m, 3 deep still with cover. Kept on one paced in the run home.
Sent forward and raced outside the leader. Was gassed 150m from the line.
Parked worse than midfield, 2 wide with cover. Was running on empty 250m from home.
Settled 4 back the fence, had cover. Commenced to tire and give ground after the furlong.
Settled midfield, on the paint with cover. Was dour in the home straight, making no real impression.
Camped behind midfield, on the fence with cover. Was never likely and only plodded home.
Punched the breeze, 3 deep, on the speed. Was a beaten horse at the 300m. (blood in trachea)
Missed the kick badly, settling last 1 off the fence with cover. Was never in the hunt and finished a long way back. (Mucopus post-race) (To Trial)
Began awkwardly, settling 2nd last, but never appeared to travel comfortably along the fence, did have cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Sent forward to settle 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the very slow sectionals, ran on strongly to take the trophy by 3/4L.
Pushed to settle 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide rounding the Home Turn, despite not suited by the very slow tempo, dashed well for 2nd.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 2Ls at very slow sectionals, kept on well until 150M weakened for 3rd.
At rear, settled 7.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the very slow tempo, ran on steadily.
Taken back as usual, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the very slow sectionals, swung widest turning in, ran on only fairly.
Midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the very slow pace, switched wide turning in, never ran on. (Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
Smart start, raced rail handy in midfield, overraced 900m, driven turning in & shifted out, quickened to narrow lead 150m, held on.
Tardy start, caught 3 deep with cover behind midfield, progress on turn, wide into stretch & driven, closing run to 2nd last strides, just held.
Rousted wide at break, worked hard to lead 1200m, to rail & soon 1L clear, headed 500m, battled to press lead all out150m, lost 2nd close home.
Taken behind to race rail in rear rank, overraced 900m, driven 430m & stayed on soundly for minor gains.
Broke well, restrained to sit 3rd 1 off no cover, pushed 3 wide 800m, edged lead 500m, shaken up 400m, faltered & headed 150m, faded.
Rousted at break to 1 off with cover handy in midfield, under pump 700m, kept on dourly.
Broke OK, shifted to race 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven 600m, stayed on for moderate headway.
Speed to lead, steadied & headed 1200m, sat 1 back on rail 2nd, shifted 1 off 800m, driven 400m, outpaced & plugged on same tempo.
Taken back & overraced at tail 1 off with cover, off heels 1300m, 7L back & ridden 430m, stayed on for modest inroads.
Tardy break, overraced early & taken to sit rear rank 3 wide with cover, hard-ridden turning in, struggled in tame run home.
Broke OK, overraced rail behind midfield, shifted off fence & driven 430m, found nothing in stretch.
Snagged at break, trapped 3 wide no cover midfield, some progress 4 wide from 800m, driven turning in, soon emptied & faded tamely.
Fair break, slotted midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 600m, progress into stretch, charged to narrow lead 200m, just held on.
Missed break, raced rail near tail, shifted out 550m, 7L back & driven 430m, rattled home late, just failed.
Fast start, 2nd on outer at 1st turn, slotted handy 1 off with cover, shifted out & driven 400m, led 210m, soon headed & lost 2nd close home.
Tardy break, niggled 1 off near rear, progress 700m, switched widest & driven into stretch, stayed on for minor headway.
Broke well, snagged to slot behind midfield 1 off with cover, driven wide home turn, outpaced but stayed on for minor gains.
Broke OK, sat rail fore of midfield, driven 430m, kept on evenly.
Tardy start & bustled to sit rail midfield, steadied off heels 900m, overraced on turn, shifted out 430m, one-paced in run home.
Broke well, rousted to narrow lead on rail, headed 1300m & tracked 1 back, in pocket early in stretch but plugged on 1 pace when clear.
Smart start, settled 2nd 1 off no cover, pressed lead 400m but soon driven & outpaced, tapered to wire.
Speed to lead, snagged 1st turn & 3 wide no cover handy, rolled to lead 1300m & to rail, driven 400m, headed 210m, weakened.
Slow start, detached & niggled at tail, driven 600m, found nothing for pressure & well beaten.
Broke well, soon dropped to rail behind midfield, driven 450m, struggled in stretch & eased when beaten.
Hard ridden forward, took box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, closed off strongly to win but only by narrow margin.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, held up 400M, dashed well when clear, just beaten by a short head in 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M for 3rd.
Eased early but trapped wide, allowed to stride forward, took rail easily, led by 0.5L at advantageous slow sectionals, overhauled 200M, ran on until 50M, just missed 3rd.
Very slow away, 4Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, started to pick up well 300M, however raced in restricted room final 200M.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the slow pace, closed off strongly until 100M, run ended.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated good finishing efforts 250M.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Very slow away, pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
At rear, 8Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, raced keenly, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden to take midfield spot, 3.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden early to hold rail, eased off 900m settling 3-back the fence. Moved up around turn, shifted out 400m to get run, pressed forward to lead 150m, kept finding when challenged for close win.
Began best, led to 900m before settling 3rd in one-off position. Taken 3-wide entering straight, challenged strongly from 150m, just failed.
Began fairly, revved up out wide to lead from 900m. Kicked clear entering straight but caught 150m, kept on one-paced.
Hard ridden early to race with leading pack before shuffled back to fourth passing 900m. Lost momentum when taken out top of the straight, kept on steadily to line.
Jumped OK but outpaced and clear last from 950m. Last into straight, ran past beaten horses.
Began fairly, hard ridden wide to go forward, sitting outside leader from 800m. Second into straight but soon tired, dropping back gradually.
Jumped with field, ridden along between horses to stay with leading pack before shuffled back entering turn. Lay out 700m, turned wide, gave ground gradually.

Placing: UR
Comment: Began well but got head up when steadied 1000m, shifted out 800, shifted out abruptly 700m dislodging jockey. (See racing incidents).

Sent forward, tracked leader from 1100M, cruised to the lead passing 300M, shifted in and out when placed under pressure 150M but had enough to hold off late challenge of 2nd. (Objection from 2nd overruled.)

Guided to the rails, settled behind midfield and not helped by the slow pace middle stages, took a while to get going in straight, strongly pursued the winner final 100M, nearest finish. (Objection on winner overruled.)
Close up and travelled along the inside, proved difficult to settle when crossed by a rival 1300M, responded well under urging turning home, stayed on for 3rd not beaten far.
Settled just off leaders but was 3-wide without cover for much of the way, had every chance turning home, did best work final stages, clinched 4th near line.
Up with early pace, moved to a solo lead near 1100M, all out passing 350M, soon headed by winner, battled on but faded inside 100M.
Raced in the 2-path never far off from leaders, kept on one paced under pressure, always held by leaders.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, dropped back to a spot closer to the rear nearing home turn, moved out 450M, stayed on mildly but not quite getting to main rivals.
Taken back to last 6Ls off the pace, briefly held up for clear run early straight, stayed on fairly final 300M and only slowly getting to main rivals.
Settled near the rear, came widest 500M, kept on same pace and no threat to leaders, weakened final stages.
Held up 3-wide in midfield, nudged along nearing 400M but failed to respond, dropped to last 200M out.
On the bridle and straight to the front when gates opened. Set steady sections, kicked clear entering straight and pulled further ahead under hands and heels riding for effortless win.
Began OK, settled in midfield about 4L from leader and close to rail. Inched closer turning for home but badly held for clear run until after 200m when got split and finished strongly.
Jumped well, ridden along wide but with cover 3L from leader. Covered extra ground turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Ridden along from wide draw but unable cut in and held 3-wide behind midfield. Pushed forward from 700m, widest into straight, kept on steadily.
Jumped OK, restrained and taken across behind runners, settling last. Picked up momentum entering straight but had to weave way between horses, doing best work at the finish.
Jumped with field, eased and taken in behind horses, settling at rear. Held up behind horses in straight until bumped and directed out 100m when saw daylight and finished strongly.
Ridden along early, settling behind pace away from fence. Rolled forward 500m out but inconvenienced 300m. Steadied 150m when unable to improve. Not fully tested.
Began well, ridden forward to find cover but kept out passing 900m and again 800m. Raced 3-wide thereafter to 200m when running on empty.
Jumped with field, ridden along to hold rail behind leader. Stayed on fence, saved ground turn, kept on early in straight before fading gradually from 200m.
Hard ridden early to sit between horses behind leader. Forced way through turning into straight, looked chance 300 but flattened soon after.
Taken in behind runners from wide draw to sit at rear away from fence. Taken 3-wide entering straight but found little and checked 250m.
Hard ridden early, racing four-wide without cover back stretch and turn. Tired quickly after entering straight.
Began fairly, restrained and taken across behind runners to fence at rear. Shuffled back to last turning for home. Never competitive.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, similar position to turn, finished off well in straight and held off late challenger to score by a neck.
Jumped well from the widest gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same position to turn, taken to middle in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, under pressure turning, made good progress in straight to get 3rd.
Jumped well, took the lead and set an even tempo, set terms to suit run to turn, headed 200M, kept on well to make frame.
Began fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in, 3 wide no cover on circle throughout, 3 lengths back, same position to turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide at rear at the back straight, 8 lengths back, 2 wide at turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line. (See racing incidents)
Jumped with them, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, no daylight early in straight and checked 200M, ran on fairly thereafter .
Began awkwardly, raced at tail throughout, 10 lengths back, still last turning, taken widest in straight and made good ground in straight to be nearest on line.
Fairly away, positioned 6 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off evenly thereafter.
Jumped well, showed early speed to take an ideal position, a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, kept to inside after straightening, showed no turn of foot, only kept on one-paced.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, taken wider at turn, showed only minor progress in straight.
Began fairly from a tricky gate, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, peaked at turn, ran on empty in straight and dropped out tamely.
Jumped well, positioned 1 out 1 back in 4th, under pressure turning, showed no response and weakened early in straight, never competitive.
Slowly away, raced 9 lengths back on rail at rear, still well back at turn, never a factor.
