Jumped moderately, settled one back in 4th on rails, obtained split over 200 metres out, quickened well to snatch race on line.
Jumped well to soon take up running, nearly made all but only to be pipped at post.
Jumped fairly settling in midfield on rails, gained closer turning in, sustained progress down straight without threatening.
Began well from a poor draw, travelled prominently without cover throughout, kept on without quickening under pressure in straight.
Never far off in 5th, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Travelled outside the leader, faded under pressure inside final 200 metres. (Lame next day)
Settled just worse than midfield, kept on well in straight.
Soon taken back, trailed the field to straight, ran on past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Jumped moderately, settled towards the rear on rails, gained closer around home bend, saved ground turning in, failed to quicken under pressure in straight.
Taken back from the widest gate, remained well behind throughout, ran home one-paced.
Awkward at start, raced wide without cover around midfield, made no impression in straight.
Ridden early, soon dropped to wide in last few, never a danger.
Punched the breeze 3 deep without cover in the early stages before slotting in to race 1 off in 4th position after the 1000m. hit the front near the 150m, held off late challenge.
Made its run third from the rear, 1 off with cover. Peeled out on the home turn and finished off with plenty of purpose.
Travelled worse than midfield, on the rails with cover. Finished off soundly.
Settled in the box seat. Enjoyed a nice run in the race, copped a check near the furlong, battled away thereafter.
Worked to eventually cross and lead on the fence near the first bend. Was still there at the 150m but was overhauled inside the 150m.
Parked worse than midfield 3 wide with cover. Was one paced in the home straight.
Camped midfield, 2 deep with cover. Didn't find any extra in the home straight.
Settled at the rear, 1 off with cover. Shifted deep on the home turn, plodded to the line.
Settled with the backmakers, on the rails with cover. Kept to the inside in the straight, passed tiring runners.
Had no excuses after racing 2nd, outside the leader. Was ridden along after the 500m, failed to respond and did nothing in the stretch.
Left 3 wide without cover, midfield after the 1000m. Struggled in the home straight.
Settled midfield, 1 off with cover. Was under pressure after the 700m, and was a beaten horse at the 500m.
Began fairly, then pushed to occupy the box seat, suited by the fast tempo, ran on well to score by 1/2L.
At rear, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, closed off strongly for 2nd.
At rear, 9Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, favored by the fast pace, finished off impressively to get 3rd.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast tempo, ran on steadily.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader at fast sectionals, kept on well until final 50M weakened.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite benefited by the fast pace, ran on only fairly.
Ridden forward to take the fence and share the lead at fast tempo, hung on until 150M weakened. (Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
At rear, settled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide, suited by the fast sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the fast tempo, never ran on.
Hard ridden forward, however trapped wide without cover throughout, flattened soon after straightening.
Sharp start, settled 1 off with cover 5th, shifted out & driven into stretch, quickened to lead 190m, immediately pressed but held on in duel to wire.
Taken back to race rail near rear, shifted 1 off for progress 500m, wide into stretch, driven to press lead 175m, held in tight duel.
Broke well, stalked 1 back on rail, shifted 1 off & driven 300m, quickened to challenge 175m, held in run.
Tardy break, posted 3 wide with cover near rear, hard-driven 400m, widest into stretch, 5L last 300m, rallied for solid late inroads.
Bustled at start, raced wide with cover behind midfield, hard-driven final turn & outpaced, stayed on well for minor later headway.
Tardy start, sat rail midfield, hard-ridden 300m, shifted out 200 & bumped rival 150m, stayed on one pace.
Taken back at start to last pair 1 off, driven into stretch, crowded & bumped 150m, boxed on evenly.
Sharp start, sat 2nd 1 off no cover, shaken up to lead 250m, emptied & swamped 190m, no extra.
Bustled to lead 1100m, soon to rail, driven 300m, all out & headed 250m, tapered thereafter.
Missed break, overraced last pair on rail, ridden 300m, plugging on in defeat when eased off heels close home.
Speed to lead but snagged back, sat handy but 3 wide no cover, ridden 400m, struggled in home stretch & weakened tamely.
Broke OK, slotted 1 off with cover midfield, driven 400m, forced wide home turn, found nothing.
Bumped start, sat 1 off with cover fore of midfield, off heels 900m, shifted out 600m, progress & driven 500m, chased until led 100m, held on.
Awkward start, sat 1 off with cover midfield, forced 3 wide 900m, driven 700m, gritty progress to 3rd 300m, 2nd at 75m, held in run.
Bustled at break, led 1200m & to rail, extended on turn, shaken up into stretch, all out & headed 100m, no extra.
Taken behind, detached at tail, closed up & switched 3 wide 850m, advanced to midfield & driven 450m, wide on turn, closed off for late gains.
Started well, raced rail midfield until shifted 1 off 900m & shuffled back, ridden 600m & progress on turn, kept on evenly in stretch.
Taken behind, sat 1 off with cover near tail, last pair & driven home turn, closed off for minor headway.
Sluggish start, sat rail near tail, bustled at tail 600m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Smart break, handy on rail until shuffled to midfield 1000m, 3rd last & driven 400m, stayed on evenly.
Snagged at start to sit 3 wide near tail, progress back stretch & driven forward on turn, all out turning in, struggled & tapered in stretch.
Broke OK, rolled 3 wide to sit handy no cover 900m, 2nd 1 off 600m, driven to chase lead 550m, emptied 300m & weakened.
Fair start & niggled 3 wide no cover, rolled to sit to 2nd 1 off 900m, driven but outpaced 600m & weakened, soon beaten & eased.
Rolled to initial lead, headed 1200m & settled 1 back on rail, niggled 4th 800m, off heels 750m, struggled & faded, well-beaten before home turn.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, closed off strongly 200M to score by a neck.
Hard ridden forward, used up too much energy to cross, led by 1L at fast sectionals, hung on strongly until last few strides overhauled, stayed on for 2nd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail just off the leader, on heels 600M, wasted too much fuel during the fast early sectionals, ran on for 3rd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to keep up with the fast pace, 2Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, flattened 200M.
Bumped start, took rail at back, 4.5Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Bumped start, pushed to keep up in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 1L off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, reduced 250M.

Placing: PU
Comment: At rear, broken down 400M.
Began OK, ridden along between horses but shuffled to behind midfield in one-off position 900m, Began run from 400m, swooped on leaders 150m, kept on strongly to line.
Began well, ridden along to settle ahead of midfield in one-off position. Got clear run entering straight, looked chance 200m, kept on well.
Slow, cut to rail, improved to 10th then shut off. Taken out top of straight but disappointed and shifted in, only to be checked 250m. Taken out widest and finished strongly.
Jumped well, ridden along but wide 900m. Rolled forward around turn, looked chance 150m when inconvenienced, kept on one pace after that.

Began well from wide draw, pressed forward to sit outside leader 900m, taking over from 700m. Led field to 150m when caught but kept on well till swamped 50m. Found to have substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Hard ridden from widest draw to stay with pace before slotting in to one-off position around turn. Rolled forward entering straight, with leaders 200m, kept on to line.
Bumped start, recovered quickly, pushing forward close to rail to sit behind leader at turn. Stayed on rail entering straight, kept on steadily without looking a threat.
Pressed forward to lead on settling then tried to slow pace and was passed 700m. Stayed on rail, rolled forward on straightening, kept on steadily till flattened 50m.
Began OK, held rail in midfield, but tightened 1000m. Kept in box around turn, found no clear running in straight and not tested. Lame left front leg and declared a "roarer."
Began fairly, outpaced and soon in last pair away from fence. Taken out entering straight but only one-paced.
Began fairly, cut to rail but soon in last pair. Never competitive and one-paced in straight.
Began well, ridden forward but unable find cover and left wide 1000m. Allowed to stride forward to sit outside leader into straight before tiring.
Held up in mid-division along the 2-path, nudged along 500M, stuck on determinedly final 200M, swept past leader inside 100M, won readily.
Rolled forward, crossed to a 2-wide spot just behind leader, driven to lead near 200M, headed by winner inside 100M, held on for 2nd just.
Dropped back to the rear, 8Ls off behind leader as they settled, closed off strongly final 300M, almost clinched 2nd.
Chased leader early stages, 3Ls back in 5th passing 1200M, travelled well to straight, kept on steadily final 300M.
Tracked leaders early stages, shuffled back a bit entering back-straight, held up 300M-200M then raced in restricted room final 150M. Could have been closer with a clear run.
Reserved along the 2-path behind midfield, was roused along passing 500M, stayed on mildly, no impression on leaders.
Began only fairly, settled in midfield along the fence, held up for clear running until 250M, made limited progress when clear.
Soon in front, led until 1200M, raced just off the pace, outdashed by leaders final 200M.
Settled towards the rear, saved ground on the rails, driven but unable to quicken entering straight, no impression on leaders.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settled towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, hard pressed from 450M, stayed on only fairly, never reached leaders.
Went forward, caught wide no cover nearing first turn, moved to a solo lead passing 1200M, set steady pace to straight, headed near 200M, no extra.
Slow to begin, sat in rear 8Ls behind leader, came under serious pressure 500M, lost touch with main rivals inside 300M. (Lame next day.)

Waited with, commenced move on straightening, obtained clear run inside final 300 metres, quickened well to snatch victory close to home.
Ridden along in rear of midfield on rails, no clear passage until after 150 metres, fought on doggedly to the line.
Never far off, racing wide without cover around the bend, fought on steadily without threatening.
Never far off, in 4th and about 2L off the lead into straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Niggled along and wide behind midfield, fought on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, did not find much room in straight until inside final 200 metres.
Broke well to lead early, headed coming out of back straight, kept on from 2nd into home straight but swamped closing stages.
Settled in last few, shifted wide into straight, fought on steadily down the centre of the track.
Not far off on rails, one-paced in the run home.
Jumped moderately, ridden to join lead taking over coming onto home bend, went over 1L clear turning in but unable to sustain effort, overhauled inside final 200 metres.
Began well, travelled 3-wide prominently, lost cover rounding home bend, faded inside final 300 metres.
Sluggish at start, raced in rear on rails, baulked for a run early in straight, made no impression closing stages.
Jumped poorly, trailed the field to straight, kept on one pace.
Jumped awkwardly, raced wide in forward of midfield, lost position around the bend, weakened into straight.
Made its run from last position, 4 off the stands rail had cover. Let down strongly towards the middle of the course, to have the race in its keeping 70m from home.
Not the best to begin, settling, midfield on the near side rail with cover. Ran on nicely.
Traveled worse than midfield, along the stands rail with cover. Closed off well.
Settled 4th, 3-4 from the stands rail without cover, at stage. Was in front 200m out but was swamped over the final 50m.
Travelled in 2nd position, closer to the grandstand side. Assumed the lead approaching the 400m, was gassed 100m from the line.
Raced handy to the leaders with cover, 3 from the stands rail. Maintained an even gallop to the wire.
Travelled ahead of midfield, 2 from the near side with cover. Didn't find any extra at the business end of the race, and finished off fairly.
Raced worse than midfield, had cover, and closer to the center of the track. Was one paced in the run to the line.
Took up leading duties on the stands side. Faded over the final 150m.
Camped ahead of midfield, 4 from the near side had some cover. Gave ground quickly after the furlong.
Settled 2nd last, had cover, and racing 3-4 off the grandstand rail. Didn't run on.
Settled worse than midfield, had cover. Drifted out to closer to the middle of the course but failed to close off. (Bled & was found to be lame the following day, RF)
Settled in third position, the stands side, and no cover. Commenced to give ground after the 400m.
Crowded at the start, settling towards the rear, with cover. Was steadied near the 300m, but was well beaten at the time.
Taken back, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed well to score a comfortable victory.
Midfield, travelled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily for 2nd.
Sent forward to lead on the fence at very slow sectionals, kept on strongly to get 3rd.
Jumped slowly, then rolled forward to settle in 2nd position without cover, ran home one-paced without any threats.
Began only fairly, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Sharp start, raced handy 3 wide with cover, ridden turning in, advanced to 2nd 350m, grinding pursuit, wore down lead to score on the nod.
Tardy start, rousted to lead & to rail 1000m, dictated tempo, driven clear 400m, battled on, emptied close home & mugged at wire.
Broke OK & bustled to hold midfield slot 3 wide with cover, hard-ridden into final turn, boxed on to 3rd 150m, closed steadily to line.
Good start, niggled to sit handy 1 off with cover, shifted out for clear run 380m, kept on dourly.
Broke well, tracked 1 back on rail, niggled 650m, driven 400m, shifted out to 3rd 300m, out-paced & tapered late in moderate run home.
Broke OK, ridden & outpaced initially, settled 1 off with cover midfield, not clear run 300m & shifted out, shaken up & ran on late.
Driven at break from widest gate, caught 4 deep no cover midfield, ridden 420m, boxed on same speed in centre track run.
Snagged back at start, ridden 1 off near rear, shifted wide home turn & driven, stayed on for minor headway but eased late when beaten.
Slow start, raced rail midfield, ridden 600m, under pump turning in, outpaced in tepid run home.
Missed break, crossed to rail & settled near rear, driven & shifted out 400m, found little.
Taken behind to race at tail, hard-ridden turning in, plugged on tamely.
Fair break, outpaced initially & niggled 3 wide with cover near rear, driven widest home turn, struggled in stretch run.
Rousted to dispute lead, sat narrow 2nd outside leader, under pressure & driven turning in, found nil & faded tamely.
Driven early to settle 3 wide on pace, ridden in 3rd 430m, soon emptied & weakened markedly, tailed off.
Tardy start & bustled early, raced midfield 3 wide with cover, driven into stretch & closed gradually to snag lead late.
Taken back from outside gate, sat wide with cover near rear, widest into stretch & shaken up, driving run to lead all out 100m, headed close home.
Soon led on rail, headed 1200m, narrow lead 800m, skipped clear & shaken up 350m, all out & headed 100m, no extra.
Sharp break & bustled to sit 1 back 1 off 4th, shifted out & hard-ridden to 2nd 350m, one-paced & lost place 200m, battled on.
Sharp break but wide no cover, snagged to slot midfield 3 deep with cover 900m, driven wide 430m, kept on evenly.
Broke well, sat fore of midfield on rail, niggled 700m, under pump turning in, outpaced in moderate stretch run.
Awkward start, raced near rear 1 off with cover, 3 wide 800m, driven 430m, stayed on for minor headway.
Moderate break, bustled on rail near rear, brief progress 800m, driven & shifted out 400m, found little in tepid run home.
Taken back & raced at tail, switched 4 deep 600m, last & driven wide turning in, plugged on same speed past beaten rivals.
Good start but soon niggled fore of midfield, driven 400m, plodded home tamely.
Slow start, bustled to race behind midfield 1 off with cover, outpaced & shuffled back 800m, plodded on, never a factor.
Slow break, raced rail in rear rank, niggled 600m, driven into stretch & some minor headway, soon struggled & faded right out.
Broke OK wide, bustled 3 deep no cover to sit 3rd, driven wide final turn, found nothing & weakened out quickly, finished adrift.
Tardy start, rolled 1 off to narrow lead 1200m, headed 800m, under pressure turning in, folded tamely & tailed off.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, closed off strongly 400M, dominated 200M.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300M for 2nd.
Box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased and tried to sit midfield early, however trapped very wide, allowed to stride forward 1200M, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 100M flattened.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pressed forward, settled in front of midfield 2 wide, made early move 500M to take advantages of the slow pace, however soon flattened 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon out of fuel 400M.
Began very awkwardly, 6Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, emptied 200M.
Eased to rear, raced 3-4 wide, raced keenly, harmed by the slow pace, never a factor.
Bumped start, trapped 3-4 wide at back, raced keenly, harmed by the slow pace, never competitive.
Jumped well, not rushed near the grandstand rail, shared the lead from 600m, edged clear from 400m to win well.
Began well, settled in centre part of the track, stalked the leaders, ridden from 400m. No match for winner.
Began well, fired up inside horses, followed the leader on grandstand rail, under drive from 300m. Just fair.
Quickest out of the gates, led briefly facing breeze, challenged by winner 600m, hard ridden and faded gradually.
Slow out. Travelled on his own, showed good finishing speed when shaken up in final 300m.
Bit slow out. Ridden to take up a position in midfield, bit keen and dropped out.
Jumped well, always in worst part of the track to join the leaders and faded badly.
Jumped well, in touch with the leaders and gradually gave ground.
Held up behind mid-division, travelled well along the inside, switched out 400M, quickened to a narrow lead nearing 100M, prevailed.
Waited with towards the rear of the field, saved ground on the fence throughout, picked up well when asked but was held up a bit near 300M, soon renewed his challenge, held by winner final stages.
Sent forward, tracked leader, briefly led inside 250M, kept on steadily towards line but couldn't match finishing pace of first two over final 150M.
Began only fairly, given a waiting ride in the rear 8Ls off the pace, made progress when pulled out wide passing 450M, got up for 4th just in time but well beaten by first three.
Began well from draw 11, eased back to find cover in mid-division, raced wide again making the turn, kept on well in straight, in contention until weakening final 150M.
Settled towards the rear, took time to gather entering straight, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 6th over this shorter trip.
Dropped back to the rear about 7Ls off leader, crowded for room entering straight, made some progress final 300M without troubling leaders, shifted in abruptly near 100M.
Niggled along to hold a spot ahead of midfield, not quickened under pressure in straight, faded final 150M.
Sped forward to the lead, tacked over to the rails passing 1200M, set quick pace to straight, headed 250M and weakened rapidly.
Held up in midfield and no closer than 3-wide throughout, weakened rapidly entering straight, eased passing 400M. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Chased leader 2-wide, gave ground from 500M, heavily eased. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Jumped, well, sat 3 wide, fairly handy in the run, challenged the leaders turning for home, took the lead 350m and battled on well to win.
Jumped well, sat wide, bit keen 800m, turned the final bend 7 wide and ran on nicely under drive out wide.
Jumped well, pushed hard, checked 900m, settled one out one back at the 800m mark, followed the winner after turning in and kept on well.
Jumped well, ridden out to sit behind the leader on the rails, fired up before the turn, had every chance. Blood in the trachea.
Jumped on terms, settled rare, travelled one off the rails and closed off despite being held up in the straight.
Jumped fairly, sat rare, hugged the paint throughout before closing off in an improved effort with blinkers on.
Jumped with the field, sat wide throughout, followed the leader turning for home, difficult ride in the final 300m.
Tight when jumping, sat further back, bit keen in the run before making minor ground.
Jumped fairly, didn't show much speed, settled 3 wide at the rear, turned the final bend 8 wide, closed off OK.
Good gate speed, led, challenged by the winner at the 350m and faded.
Jumped well, travelled mid pack, sat back of the winner turning in and gave ground. Bled from both nostrils.
Jumped fairly, settled mid pack on rail, travelled well, no room in final 300m. Not ridden out.
Jumped well, sat 2 wide outside the leader and made no impression after turning for home. Faded badly.
Slowly out, recovered to race 3 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, no cover on turn, angled out after turning in, finished off well to hold off the late challenge and scored.
Average to begin, difficult to settle early, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, angled out after turning in and closed off very well in straight, just missed.
Fairly away, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, no daylight until 150M, closed off well thereafter to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover in midfield, 5 lengths back, taken widest after turning in, finished off strongly to make frame.
Began well, sent forward to race in 3rd, 1-2 lengths back, same position to turn, kept on fairly in straight, just missed frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, 8 lengths back, still well back at turn, made good progress in straight.
Broke well, raced 2 wide in front of midfield, 4 lengths back, checked near 900M, angled out turning, ran home evenly in straight, never a threat to the first few.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead to turn, headed near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, nearly same margin to turn, showed no response and weakened gradually final 300M.
Began awkwardly, raced at tail throughout, 8 lengths back, last turning in, made minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 4 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, made no progress down the centre of the track. (See racing incidents.)
Taken back from a widest draw, positioned 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, wider with cover at turn, made no progress in straight, never competitive.
Slowly away, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail, checked near 1100M, saved ground to turn, showed no response after turning in and eased final stages.

Jumped fairly, gradually improved to take up running after 1000 metre turn, kicked 2L clear shortly after straightening, held on to the line.
Jumped fairly, niggled along before settling for forward of midfield position in 5th within 3L of pace on rails, did not find much room early in home straight but finished off race well.
Jumped moderately, quickly improved to 2L back in 4th, fought on steadily under pressure without quickening in straight.
Broke well from the one draw to lead early, taken back to settle just off the speed in 1.5L 3rd, remained same into straight, kept on one pace under pressure.
Ridden along after starting from a poor draw, obtained prominent 2-wide position 800 metres out, kept on at the one pace in straight.
Sluggish at start, settled mainly 2-wide in midfield, commenced move turning in, minor inconvenience early in straight, kept on steadily under pressure while laying in.
Soon dropped to tail-end, remained well behind, saved ground turning in, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, gradually shifted back to the rear, trailed the field to 400 metres, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish. (Tactic questioned)
Sluggish at start, towards the rear, came under pressure around home bend, kept on same pace without quickening.
Jumped moderately, settled wide in worse than midfield, came under pressure approaching home turn, made no impression in the run home.
Crowded at start losing ground, soon recovered to worse than midfield on rails while racing keenly, remained in similar position to straight, soon faded.
Jumped moderately, settled 3-wide in midfield, faded from approaching home turn.
Sent forward, crossed and led early along the fence, at genuine clip. Was never headed and finished off gamely.
Travelled midfield, 2 deep with cover. Lost some ground after the 700m despite riders efforts. Rallied in the straight, finished off soundly.
Camped in 4th position, 1 off with cover. Chased with plenty of purpose in the run home.
Parked 1 off in 2nd position. Was still there at the 100m but was overhauled late.
Traveled 3 back the fence, had cover. Kept on finding the line.
Settled 2nd from the rear close to the rail with cover. Closed off reasonably without threatening.
Posted 3 wide without cover until the 600m, travelling midfield. Was one paced in the home stretch.
Settled last, close to the rail. Made a midrace move around the field, travelling 3 deep no cover, close to the speed. Held on fairly in the run to the line.
Had every possible hope after stalking the leader on the rails. Was a spent force at the furlong.
Settled worse than midfield, 3 deep with cover. Shifted very wide on the home turn, only plodded to the line.
Raced back in the field, 2-3 wide with cover. Was under heavy pressure before the home turn, didn't have a lot of luck down the running.
Settled worse than midfield the fence. failed to close off.
Settled worse than midfield 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, dashed on strongly to win by a neck.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at fast pace, kicked 3Ls clear, however headed by the winner over the last few strides.
Prominent, settled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, enjoyed the fast tempo, ran on nicely for 3rd.
Ridden forward to settle 1L outside the leader at fast pace, kept on well until final 100M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast pace, ran on steadily.
Hard ridden to settle in midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the fast sectionals, one paced home.
At rear, 8.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover throughout, benefited by the fast tempo, made minor ground in straight.
Sent forward to obtain the box seat, hampered by the fast pace, kept on one pace until 150M weakened.
Midfield, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast sectionals, unable to show any dash in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
Taken back from wide gate, settled 9.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast tempo, never ran on.
Lacked early pace, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, never a factor.
Fast start, sat handy 1 off with cover, to 2nd 1100m, shaken up & swung wide turning in, quickened to lead 250m, driven clear.
Good break, raced rail fore of midfield, shifted out & driven turning in, closed off to claim 2nd late.
Missed break & at tail, switched out & slid forward back stretch to midfield 3 deep, advanced 4wide on turn, to 2nd 200m, no extra close home.
Speed to lead wide, crossed to rail 1300m, driven 400m, all out & headed 250m, boxed on.
Fair break, sat rail midfield, checked & shuffled back 1100m, 2nd last & driven 400m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Tardy break, bustled to eventually sit 1 off with cover 4th, shifted out & driven 400m, off heels 220m & lost momentum, kept on evenly.
Broke OK, raced 1 off with cover midfield, shifted 3 deep & ridden 450m, stayed on for minor headway.
Moderate break, soon in rear 1 off, 3 wide backstretch, driven 450m & widest home turn, stayed on moderately.
Sharp break, settled 1 back on rail, snagged off heels 1100m, hard-ridden turning in, outpaced & faded in run.
Awkward start & bustled early to race 1 off behind midfield, ridden 450m,wide into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Smart break & bustled early to rail midfield, overraced 1000m, shifted 1 off 400m, driven wider home turn, struggled thereafter.
Awkward start, soon in rear on rail, off heels & to tail 1000m, hard-ridden & shifted wide home turn, found nothing.
Broke OK, soon led & to rail 1st turn, headed 700m, switched 1 off in pursuit & driven home turn, grinding effort to snag verdict on line.
Crowded start, sat 1 back on rail, shuffled back 700m, progress on turn & switched out, driven 400m, battled to lead 100m, mugged on line.
Impeded start, sat 1 off with cover midfield, shuffled back 700m, 3rd last & shifted wide 400m, strong closer centre track, just failed.
Badly squeezed at break, sat 1 off with cover near rear, to 3 wide 900m, gradual progress, wide turning in, strong run flattened close home.
Snagged back, overraced initially, sat 3 deep near rear, rapid wide advance 900m to 700m, to rail & kicked clear on turn, emptied & headed 100m.
Bumped rival at start, sat at tail, checked badly 900m & detached, soon back in touch, driven 6L back 400m, stayed on for sound headway.
Shifted right & bumped start, ridden to sit outside leader no cover, ridden 400m, outpaced & plugged on evenly.
Awkward start, sat rail midfield, severely checked & lost ground 900m, bustled 650m, plugged home evenly.
Prominent at break, restrained to 1 off with cover fore of midfield, heavily impeded 900m, ridden 600m, crowded & checked 300m, boxed on evenly.
Broke well, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, pushed 4 wide & ridden forward 700m, all out 4th home turn, emptied 300m & faded.
Led initially, soon tracked pace 1 off with cover, keen & shifted heavily into rival 900m, then shifted 3 deep, driven 500m, one-paced.
Bumped start, bustled to rail behind midfield, badly impeded 900m, lost ground & detached at tail, found nothing thereafter.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace, scored easily.
Pushed forward, box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, closed off strongly just to hold 2nd.
Pushed forward but not intended to lead, sat 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leader along the rails, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, 3Ls off the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield early, trapped 3 wide throughout and no cover, moved forward 1000M to sit 1L off the slow pace, emptied 300M.
Eased back and took rail, 6Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon reduced 250M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Very slow away, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Never a factor.
Jumped fairly, taken in to rail and shut off at rear. Allowed more rein 700m, ridden for luck entering straight, found split 200m, powered home strongly.
Ridden along 3-wide from outside draw to sit 3rd into first turn. Kept wide back stretch, rolled forward from 450m, grabbed lead 200m, run down near line.
Began OK, ridden along but failed to muster dropping 4-back along rail on settling. Under pressure from 400m, cut to rail entering straight, ran on steadily.
Began well, settling 2-back, the rail. Improved position passing 700m, got clear run turning for home, ran on steadily to just miss a place.
Began best, led to 1500m when passed, taken out and rolled forward to retake lead 1000m, Kept up good pace, collared 200m but kept on well till swamped final stages.
Restrained, taken across behind horses but kept 3-wide back stretch with cover. Widest into straight, ran on steadily without threatening. Lame right from leg with quarter crack.
Began well, pressed forward, settling one-back, one-off before awkward on heels 1150m, dropping to 4th. Hard ridden 450m, kept on steadily in straight.
Began OK, ridden along to maintain forward position but held wide and without cover, from 1000m. Turned wide, kept on fairly in straight.
Began OK, ridden along between horses in midfield, slipping back slightly before final turn. Found little in straight under hard riding.
Began well, pressed forward to lead 1500m, tried to slow pace but was immediately passed and tightened, becoming unbalanced. Remained 2nd to straight before giving ground gradually.
Began fairly, not much pace and shuffled back before home turn. Became detached from field after entering straight.
Began fairly, taken across behind horses, settling last in one-off position. Started to drop off passing 500m and finished tailed off.
Not hurried, held up towards the rear in a strongly run race, headway 500M, squeezed through to challenge leaders from 200M, finished strongest of all to grab the lead 50M. Won in class record time.
Driven forward, vied for the lead on the inside setting strong pace, kept on well and held a narrow advantage in straight, caught by fast finishing winner 50M out.
Sent forward, vied for the lead on outside setting strong pace, ran on steadily final 300M, not pace of winner final 100M.
Not far off from the pace, steadied 600M and shifted out to 3-wide, ran on well down outside to clinch 4th.
Slotted into a 2-wide position behind leaders, soon into clear entering straight, ran on steadily but not quite getting to leaders.
Not pace of leaders early stages, travelled 3-wide in midfield, taken widest on straightening, stayed on moderately.
Began only fairly, guided to a midfield position 4Ls off the pace, took time to gather entering straight, did best work final stages.
Hard pressed early stages, chased leaders rounding the bend, kept on same pace when driven, faded late.
Held up towards the rear, 6-7Ls behind leader turning home, ran on without troubling main rivals.
Not pace of leaders early stages, settled in 6th/7th 3Ls off the pace, kept on one pace in straight.
Obtained a good position behind leading pair, travelled well but gave little response when asked.
Dropped back to last, raced as back-marker throughout, 8Ls off the strong pace 400M, not picked up and never involved.

Jumped awkwardly, well there, sustained fast mid-section to take up running 400 metres out, soon drew clear to win easily.
Never far off, about 2L back in 4th coming onto course proper, fought on steadily to snatch 2nd late.
Held slender lead most of way to 400 metres when headed by eventual winner, kept on steadily but lost 2nd late.
In touch, found nothing closing stages.
Jumped awkwardly, soon shifted to stands rails, under pressure most of way, ran home one-paced.
Never seen with a chance.
Close up in a compact field early racing near the centre of the track, faded gradually after coming onto course proper.
Well there to 400 metres, folded up quickly.
Rated midfield, 2 deep with cover. Ran on well and held of late challenge.
Settled 2nd last, 1 off with cover. Ran into traffic in the home stretch, made a good late bid.
Led early, before settling 3rd, 1 off with cover. Led approaching the furlong but weakened on its effort well short of the line.
Made its run from a rearward position after settling on the fence with cover. Finished off soundly despite some inconvenience near the 200m.
Parked behind midfield, 3 deep with cover. Swung wide on the home turn and finished off steadily.
Couldn't go the early speed of the race settling with the back makers, 3-4 deep with cover. Worked home fairly. (Rider dropped whip at 300m)
Camped just forward of midfield, on the rails with cover. Whacked away at the same pace in the run to the line.
Raced worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Was dour in the final stretch.
Travelled last on the fence, had cover. Did nothing in the straight, passed tiring runners.
Raced just in advance of midfield, 2 deep with cover. Was under pressure at the 500m, struggled in the home stretch.
Led easily on the paint. Was overhauled approaching the furlong and yielded ground thereafter.
Worked forward to eventually cross and race outside the leader on the circle. Was a spent force at the 200m.
Had no excuses after box seating. Was well beaten after the 300m.
Had no joy after punching the breeze 3 wide without cover, ahead of midfield. Was a beaten horse early in the straight. Tailed out.
Rolled forward to settle 3Ls off the leader 4 wide without cover, improved gradually rounding the Home Turn, ran on strongly to the line.
Midfield, travelled 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide with cover, ran on gradually to get 2nd.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, closed to the line well for 3rd.
Raced midfield, settled 4.5Ls behind the leader 3-4 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow pace, ran on steadily.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls off the leader 3 wide without cover, suited by the slow sectionals, kept on until final 100M weakened.
Sent forward to settle in 2nd position without cover, one paced until final 150M weakened.
At rear, niggled along throughout, made some ground in straight.
Taken back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 4-5 wide, made some ground in straight.(Questioned for riding, see incident report)
Jumped awkwardly, then ridden hardly to catch up the field along the fence in midfield, ran on fairly until 200M weakened. (Lame left front leg)
Hard ridden along to take the fence and led by 1L at slow sectionals, kept on until 250M flattened.
Always at rear, never a factor.

Prominent, however failed to respond when placed under pressure rounding the Home Turn, tailed out. (Heart Irregularity, substantial amount of mucopus in its trachea. Next day also lame in its right front leg)
Broke well, sat 1 out 1 back, keen 1200m, shifted out shifted out 430m & ridden, swept to lead 250m, drew clear.
Broke OK, raced midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide with cover 1000m, very wide & driven home turn, strong run to 2nd 100m, no match for winner.
Steady start, darted to rail & settled behind midfield, shifted out & driven into stretch, solid run to claim 3rd close home.
Bustled to lead on rail 1st turn, set tempo, pressed & driven 300m, headed 250m, tapered to wire.
Speedy break & led briefly, sat 2nd outside leader, ridden 650m, all out 250m, faded to wire.
Broke OK, snagged to tail, niggled 750m, driven 400m, hung out & repeatedly leaned on rival in stretch, moderate headway.
Prominent at break, taken back & caught wide no cover near rear, hard-ridden wide final turn, one-paced in tame run to wire.
Rousted at break & outpaced, raced 3 wide with cover near rear, under pump 500m, one-paced & repeatedly leaned on in home stretch.
Slow start & driven at tail, gradual progress 3 wide no cover to 3rd 900m, driven 600m & forced wide home turn, weakened tamely.
Tardy start & bustled to settle 1 back on rail, driven turning in, found nothing in weakening run.
Broke OK, settled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, shifted wide 7L back & shaken up turning in, storming run to lead last strides.
Broke OK, sat 3 wide with cover midfield, progress 600m, driven to 2nd turning in, led 250m & boxed ahead, all out & headed close home.
Good break, slotted 1 off with cover midfield, niggled 800m, driven & shifted out 500m, one-paced initially, grinding late headway to 3rd .
Settled 3 wide with cover in rear, shifted very wide & driven 450m, 8L back turning in, stayed on centre track for solid inroads.
Slotted 1 off with cover behind midfield, slipped to rear rank 800m, progress & shaken up 400m, ran on for minor headway.
Missed break, raced rear on rail, driven 8L back 430m, edged off rail into stretch, steadied 350m, soon driven, shifted out 200m, ran on soundly.
Smart start, keen 1 back 1 off, progress to 2L 2nd 600m, soon driven & one-paced in stretch, tapered closing stages.
Tardy start, sat rail midfield, hard-ridden & outpaced 400m, plugged on evenly.
Bustled wide to sit 2nd outside leader, shuffled back 800m, ridden 4L back 550m, outpaced & faded in run home.
Broke well, sat rail behind lead, shuffled to midfield 800m, under pump turning in, weakened in run.
Speed to lead 1400m, headed 800m, driven 3L back 550m, lost ground on turn, plugging tamely when shifted off heels 200m & eased.
Fair break, snagged & 4 wide no cover midfield, progress 900m to lead 800m, 2L clear & kicked on 400m, emptied & headed 250m, weakened.
Bustled & caught 3 wide no cover handy, pushed 4 wide 900m, found nothing into home stretch & faded right out.
Taken to tail, soon shifted 4 wide with cover behind midfield, niggled & flat-footed 650m, pushed widest on turn & soon tailed off.
Pushed to take rail and led by 0.5L, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, made all.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to sit just off the leader 2 wide, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased at start, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
In front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader, suited by the slow pace but trapped 3 wide no cover, out of fuel 350M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, emptied 250M.
At back, 6.5Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, never improved.
At back, 5.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow tempo, raced keenly and hung out badly at bends, no progress.
Raced wide at back, harmed by the slow pace, never competitive.
In front of midfield, 2Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, reduced quickly 500M.
Midfield, not suited by the slow pace, checked badly 400M, dropped off afterwards.
Began fairly but hard pressed along rail to go forward and lead passing 700m. Joined up front 300m but kicked again, holding off late challenge while hanging in.
Jumped OK, allowed to find feet settling 5th, 3L from leader. Taken out 500m for clear run but took time to get into top gear doing best work final 200m.
Began well, led field along back stretch before settling 2nd passing 700m. Pushed forward entering straight to join leader but unable get past. Kept on well.
Bumped start, mustered to join leaders before taking hold and slipping back to box seat passing 700m. Turned in behind leaders and kept on steadily to the line.

Bumped start, recovered, settling behind midfield close to rail. Rolled forward approaching turn, taken out entering straight, ran on steadily while racing greenly, shifting out several times under hard riding.
Began OK, restrained and taken across behind runners, settling distance last passing 1000m. Revved up before turn, taken wide into straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Began fairly, but trapped three-wide in midfield for most of the journey. Covered extra ground turn, one-paced in straight.
Jumped fairly, ridden along away from fence before checked and difficult to settle passing 800m. Over-raced approaching 600m and blundered when close to heels. Kept on steadily in straight.
Began OK but raced keenly and difficult to settle after 1000m. Taken out turning for home and ran on fairly in straight.
No early speed and soon at rear but away from fence. Steadied passing 600m, became detached entering straight, found little.
Began fairly, not pressured, holding rail towards rear. Hampered around final turn and found little in straight under hard riding.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader before easing into one-back, one-off position. Kept on gamely early in straight before giving ground from 300m.
Slow to begin, patiently ridden in the rear, 8Ls off the pace middle stages, moved out to clear 400M, closed off strongly to get up just in time, won in course record time.
Began well, restrained to sit behind leaders, travelled strongly throughout, quickened to lead 300M and opened up 2Ls advantage mid-straight, continued on gamely, caught final stages.
Restless in stalls, reared and lost ground at start, held up near the rear, switched into clear 300M, stayed on to go 3rd near line without troubling the first two.
Reserved behind midfield, saved ground on the inside, pushed along 500M, stayed on without ever troubling the first two.
Settled near the rear, moved closer 600M, ran on well early straight and briefly went 2nd 200M, one paced final stages and weakened to 5th near line.
Settled just off the pace, pressed along nearing 500M but failed to quicken, out of contention passing 200M.
Strode forward, vied for lead early stages, set good pace to straight, all out turning in, headed near 300M, weakened towards finish.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, moved out to challenge 500M but gave limited response, no impression on leaders over final 250M.
Sent forward, vied for lead early stages, prominent outside leader entering back-straight, came under pressure 600M, faded turning home.
Not far off early stages, caught wide no cover until 1300M, gave ground 700M out, soon no extra and finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Began well, ridden to hold rail 3L from leader. Saved ground around turn, got dream run after straightening, took lead passing 300m and kept on strongly.
Dislodged jockey on way to start. Began OK but not pushed, settling behind midfield away from fence. Revved up around turn, wide into straight, kept on strongly to line.
Began awkwardly, throwing head around several times, dropping to last back stretch. Still well back entering straight, switched wide and picked up momentum from 200m to be closest at finish.
Jumped with field, kept to rail settling 3-back from leader. Stayed on rail around turn but held for clear run early in straight before checked 200m. Ran on well when clear late.
Began OK, ridden to stay with pace in a one-off position. Took closer order around turn, rolled forward to look chance at 300m, kept on well till flattened late.
Began awkwardly, steadied from heels, dropping back to near last. Saved ground turn but unable to get run until passing 200m. Not fully tested.
Began well but trapped 3-wide and restrained to find cover, dropping to last passing 1000m. Revved up round turn, wide into straight, kept on steadily.
Began OK, ridden along in a one-off, one-back position back stretch. Kept battling early in straight before tiring after passing 200m.
Quickly in front and not pressured, setting steady pace. Collared passing 300m but kept battling to 200m before giving ground gradually.
Taken forward from wide draw to settle outside hind quarters of leader back stretch and turn, Gave ground soon after straightening.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide without cover in front of midfield, 4 lengths back, similar position to turn, finished off strongly in straight to score.
Jumped with them, showed early speed to position behind the leader in 2nd, travelled well to turn, ridden near 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, difficult to settle at turn, angled out after turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to get 3rd.
Slow to begin, raced on rail at rear, 6 lengths back, gradually improved on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Began well, positioned 2 wide in 3rd, 3 lengths back, same position to turn, finished off fairly in straight, just missed frame.
Fairly away, raced 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, closed off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead to turn, headed near 350M, ran on one-paced thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 5 lengths back, same position to turn, angled out after turning in, made no progress, finished off one-paced.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at tail, similar position to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced on rail at rear, 7 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, made no progress in straight, never a threat.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, weakened early after turning in, never competitive.
Fairly away from a wide draw, taken back to race 3 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, wider at turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, travelled well to turn, took the lead 300M, kept on well to score by a neck.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in front of midfield, 3 lengths back, similar to position to turn, finished off well in straight to be nearest on line.
Moderately away, raced 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, closed off well in straight to get 3rd.
Fairly away, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, angled out after turning in, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, same margin to turn, made good progress in straight, hampered by a broken-down horse 250M, stayed on well final 200M.
Taken back from a tricky gate, positioned on rail behind midfield, 5 lengths back, kept to inside after straightening, made some progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced at rear throughout, same position to turn, taken very wide in straight and made some progress.
Began fairly, raced 1-2 lengths back on rail in 4th, saved ground to turn, made no progress in straight, weakened gradually.
Hampered start, recovered to race 3 wide without cover in front of midfield, 2 lengths back, same position to turn, made no progress in straight and was hampered by a broken-down horse near 250M.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position to turn, made no progress in straight before hampered by a broken horse near 250M.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, 7-8 lengths back, still well back to turn, taken very wide in straight and made little progress.
Average to begin from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 4 lengths back, showed no acceleration in straight, never competitive.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently in 3rd, travelled well to turn, lost all chance when badly affected by a broken horse near 250M, eased thereafter.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Jumped well from a wide gate, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well to turn, broken down 300M.

Ridden along from the one draw to keep from being crossed, remained a joint leader on rails down the back straight, gained 1L advantage around the bend and drew clear into straight, won readily.
Amongst leaders early, taken to one back position 800 metres out, remained similar turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Began moderately, settled not far off the pace on rails most of way, fought on steadily under pressure without threatening in straight.
Jumped moderately, travelled towards the rear on rails, made up good ground down the rails in straight, nearest at finish.
Slowly away, remained well behind to straight, switched out to obtain clear run over 200 metres out, finished off race well.
Soon taken back from the widest gate settling towards the rear, widest runner turning in, ran on quite well down the centre of the track in the run home.
Jumped moderately, travelled mainly in rear of midfield to straight, fought on steadily down the inner of straight but without threatening.
Slowly away, travelled at the back to straight, finished off race well.
Contested lead from a poor draw, gradually taken back to rear of midfield far side, wide into home straight, made no impression in the run home.
Jumped awkwardly but close up early, travelled mainly 2-wide in 2L 4th to straight, soon weakened.
With leaders for the first 200 metres, gradually shifted back to 2.5L 5th but remained wide without cover throughout far side, weakened into straight.
Ridden to contest early lead, managed to lead or dispute lead to 600 metres, dropped out from approaching home straight.
Made its run from behind midfield, was 3 deep without cover on the circle. Got going after the 500m, and had the race in its keeping 100m from home.
Showed plenty of gate speed, then was restrained early, eventually shifted in after the 700m to take up the box seat. Closed off soundly.
Did plenty of work early to cross and race in 2nd position outside the leader. Kept on well.
Went forward and led on the paint. Faded over the last 100m.
Eventually travelled 3 back the paint. Kept up an even gallop right to the wire.
Travelled 3rd from the rear, 3 deep with cover. Shifted deep on the home turn, finished off dourly.
3 wide early before slotting in to race 1 out 1 back before the circle. Weakened over the latter stages.
Parked worse than midfield, on the fence with cover. Kept whacking away down the running.
Went back and settled midfield, 1 off with cover. Failed to find an extra gear in the run home.
Camped worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Was dour in the home stretch.
Raced with the backmakers , 2 deep with cover. Failed to close off.
Not the best away then was crowded approaching the first turn, whilst travelling at the rear on the paint. Struggled in the run home.
Prominent, travelled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the slow pace, ran on strongly to score by a short head.
Pushed forward to take the lead at slow sectionals, kept on strongly to get 2nd, just beaten by a short head.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow pace, dashed well for 3rd.
Midfield, settled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow sectionals, swung wide rounding the Home Turn, closed off nicely for 4th.
Rolled forward to settle in 2nd position along the fence, benefited by the slow tempo, kept on nicely until final 50M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Taken back from a wide gate, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, made no impression in straight.
Pushed to settle midfield, 3Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, never looked likely.
Taken back from a wide barrier, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, made minor ground in straight.
Rousted early to settle fore of midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 400m & closed strongly centre track to lead last stride.
Bustled to slipstream leader on rail, steadied off heels 600m, shifted out 300m & driven in pursuit, led 50m, pipped at post.
Rousted to snare lead on rail 1000m, steadied pace & overraced a touch, 1L clear & kicked on 300m, all out & headed 50m.
Broke well, settled back 1 off with cover midfield, niggled 800m, hard-ridden 400m, wide on turn, strong late closer.
Good break, raced rail fore of midfield, ridden 400m, switched out & stayed on evenly.
Sharp break, sat handy 1 off no cover, 2nd & driven turning in, plugged on one pace until tapered late.
Taken back to settle rail fore of midfield, switched out 500m & ridden home turn, wide into stretch, closed off evenly.
Moderate break, sat rail near rear, switched out on turn & driven into stretch, kept on one pace centre track.
Taken back to race 1 off with cover near tail, driven 400m & shifted out in stretch, plodded on tamely.
Slow start & bustled, raced at tail, ridden 400m, found little in tepid run home.
Tardy start, caught wide & snagged back, trapped near rear on outer no cover, bustled 500m, last turning in, soon tailed off.
Smart start, sat rail midfield, switched 1 off & nudged for progress 400m, driven 300m & back to rail, grinding run to lead last strides.
Speed to soon lead, to rail 1300m, shaken up turning in & kicked on, all out 50m & headed close home.
Speed at break, slotted 1 off no cover 2nd, niggled 500m, hard driven home turn, boxed on soundly.
Snagged at start, raced rail behind midfield, under pump 500m, stayed on for sound inroads.
Sharp start, tracked 1 back on rail, niggled 500m, hard-ridden turning in, progress to 2nd mid-stretch, no extra & tapered to wire.
Broke OK, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, switched wide into stretch & driven, stayed on for minor headway.
Fair speed early, sat 1 off with cover midfield, switched 3 wide & driven home turn, plugged on one pace.
Broke well, raced handy 1 off with cover, driven into stretch, kept on one pace.
Broke OK but lacked pace & soon raced near rear, to rail backstretch, ridden 400m, found little in tame run home.
Snagged back from wide to race near tail 1 off with cover, minor advance 700m, ridden 400m but limited response & never a factor.
Tardy start, rousted & outpaced, soon at tail, 3L detached 700m, ridden 400m, plodded on past fading rival.
Broke OK, rolled wide no cover to race close-up on outer, under pressure to hold position 450m, beaten turning in & faded tamely.
Eased to sit in midfield early but trapped wide, allowed to stride forward 900M, took advantages from the slow pace, closed off strongly 300M to win.
Bumped start, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed strongly 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to take rail in midfield, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 300M for 3rd.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, on heels early, 6Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Bumped start, pushed early, under pressure throughout,, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 150M.
Hard ridden to take a midfield spot, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Pushed forward to take rail and led by 1.5Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, soon emptied 250M.
Slow away, at rear, not suited by the slow pace, never improved.
Began well, rolled forward, settling in box seat behind leaders back stretch. Saved ground turn, came off rail 300m, picked up momentum to hit front 100m, battled on gamely.
Jumped with field, ridden along to settle one-back, one off first turn. Shuffled back to 5th passing 500m, wide in straight, battled strongly to line.
Bumped heavily and taken out start, recovered and pressed forward to lead 1500m cutting in to fence back stretch. Steadied pace 800m, put under pressure 500m, collared 100m, boxed on solidly.

Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling in last pair. Got close to heels 1300m and over raced. Shifted out 900m and allowed to circle field to sit outside leader 500m. Kept on gamely in straight before flattened 50m.
Jumped well, ridden along settling 3-back, one-off along back stretch. Taken very wide into straight and ran home steadily.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped another. Difficult to settle early, settling at rear. Taken wide entering straight, ran home steadily under hard riding.
Began well, pressed forward to settle outside leader first turn. Shuffled back to 3rd passing 500m, kept on well in straight until crowded for room 150m. One paced.
Began OK, not hurried settling in midfield away from fence. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Slow into stride and soon in last pair along rail. Stayed on rail final turn, found little in straight under hard riding.
Crowded out start, taken in, grabbing rail before first turn. Shaken up entering final turn but little response.
Began OK, quickly on rail, travelling well in midfield to 800m when came off bridle, Hard ridden from 700m but found little, giving ground gradually.
Settled handily in the 2nd flight, travelled strongly behind leaders turning home, switched and challenged on the inside, got up inside 100M, held on well under pressure.
In touch in midfield, 3-wide bid passing 600M to join leaders, ran on well and was given every chance, held by winner towards finish.
Driven forward, always prominent behind leader, enjoyed the slow sectionals, challenged the lead passing 400M, kept on well but not pace of first 2 final stages.
Positively ridden, crossed to the lead 1200M, set very slow pace in front, battled on well when joined by rivals inside 300M, headed 100M out, faded to 4th late stages.
Began well, eased to a midfield position on the rails, travelled well to straight, ran on steadily under top weight, nearest finish.
Restrained in midfield along the 2-path, made his move 600M out, had every chance in straight, stayed on and slowly closing the gap with leaders. (Lame next day.)
Settled towards the rear 7-8Ls off the pace, saved ground on the inside throughout, stayed on moderately under pressure but never reached contention.
Mildly urged after the start, soon sat on the rails settled just off the pace, ridden and unable to quicken turning home, gradually outpaced and beaten entering 200M.
Restrained to race behind midfield, moved out from fence 500M, stayed on fairly down outside, never dangerous.
Slotted into a 2-wide position towards the rear, bustled along 600M out, kept on one paced turning home and never a serious threat to leaders.
Began only fairly, settled near the rear 8Ls behind leader in a slowly run race, waited with till 300M but hung when placed under pressure, made limited progress only.
From wide barrier soon taken across behind runners, held up in last almost 10Ls off the slow pace, crept closer home turn but made no real progress final 300M.
