Sluggish start, settled in last few, obtained clear passage 300 metres, ran on well down the centre of the track to take charge close to home.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, quickened to hit the front over 150 metres out only to be headed close to home.
Jumped well from a poor draw, soon taken back to just worse than midfield, commenced move over 500 metres out, ran on to hold some chance until finding no extra final stages.
Jumped moderately, ridden along to hold prominent spot in 4th or 5th, similar turning into straight, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.
Missed the break as usual, settled at the back on rails, saved ground turning for home, finished off race nicely without threatening.
Well back, ran on past well beaten runners down the stands side of home straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Jumped well but blundered shortly afterwards, chased leader most of way to 200 metres, soon swamped.
Began well from a poor gate, settled mainly 2-wide in forward of midfield, came to challenge turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Jumped fairly, soon took up running setting a smart pace, unable to sustain and headed 200 metres out.
Jumped fairly, settled behind midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.
Began well from the one gate, settled mainly in 2L 3rd on rails, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres. (Blood in trachea.)
Broke well, gradually taken back to just worse than midfield 3-wide, made no impression down the centre of the straight.
Well behind, trailed the field into straight, made no show.
Jumped fairly from the widest gate, raced wide without cover, gradually improved to dispute 3rd coming out of far side, folded up quickly from a similar position into home straight.
Made its run from 2nd last, three off the near side rail. shifted to the middle of the track after the 400m, and finished off with plenty of purpose.
Settled midfield, along the stands side, had cover. Hit the front at the 100m, but was collard at the 50m, finished off well. (Blood in trachea post race)
Raced midfield, along the center of the course no cover. Kept up a good gallop to the wire.
Travelled behind midfield, 1 off the grandstand rail, was second at the furlong, but was swamped late.
Raced with the leaders, closer to the middle of the track. Faded late.
Took up 3rd last position, towards the center of the course. Finished off steadily without threatening.
Not the best away then settled midfield with cover. Went for a narrow run near the 300m, but was checked soon after and never recovered.
Settled towards the middle of the course, no cover. Stayed on reasonably.
Speared across to lead along the outside fence in the early stages. Faded over the final 100m.
Parked midfield, 3 from the stands rail, had cover. Failed to find any extra in the run home and plodded to the line.
Travelled on the speed, about 6 off the near side rail, no cover. Commenced to yield ground after the 350m.
Raced prominently, 3-4 off the stand side, no cover. Was under pressure to stay in touch a log way out and after the 500m, was a beaten horse. Gave in quickly passing the 200m.
Camped 2nd towards the stands rail, no cover. Was under pressure at the 400m, and was a spent force at the furlong. (Bled)
Settled a long last. Was never in the hunt, hung in over about the last 400m and drifted in to race along the far side, finishing well back.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on strongly to score by a head.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, had every possible chance to win, however missed by a head.
Hard ridden to settle midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on well for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, ran on steadily.
Taken back from a wide barrier, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on well until 200M was checked, not fully tested.
Raced midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily.
Prominent, 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on only fairly when placed under pressure rounding the Home Turn.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, travelled wide and without cover throughout, never looked likely.
Settled worse than midfield about 6.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, unable to make any impression in straight.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Sent forward to settle 1L behind the leader, flattened badly soon after straightening.
Sharp break, snagged to race rail midfield, tracked runner-up into stretch, switched out & shaken up 250m, quickened to lead close home.
Broke with others, sat 1 back on rail, switched 1 off & driven 400m, led 250m, all out & headed close home.
Taken back from widest gate, raced wide at tail, slightly detached & driven 600m, relentless wide run to 3rd but always held.
Taken back to 1 off with cover behind midfield, shifted out 350m & driven, closed off smartly for minor gains.
Snagged at start to tail, advanced to sit rail fore of tail, switched out 400m, driven 300m, ran on soundly.
Taken back from wide gate, sat 1 off with cover near tail, wide into stretch, shaken up & off heels 250m, closed off for minor late inroads.
Decent start, caught handy 5 wide no cover, rolled wide to edge lead 750m, headed 400m & outpaced, plugged on one pace.
Broke well, trapped handy 4 wide no cover, 3 wide no cover 750m, driven 375m, boxed on same speed until tapered late.
Bustled at start to race fore of midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out & crowded into stretch, foiled in search for clear run, not fully tested.
Bustled at break, barged & sandwiched 1200m & knocked back to near rear, driven on outer 600m, sound headway until emptied 150m & faded.
Tardy start, recovered to lead on rail 1100m despite bump, just headed 750m, regained lead & kicked on 400m, emptied & headed 250m, faded.
Broke with others, sat 3 wide with cover midfield, shuffled back 600m, shifted wider & driven 450m, outpaced & weakened out.
Broke well, impeded rival 1200m, overraced on leader's flank, to 3rd 750m & niggled, under pump home turn, clipped heels 350m & eased.
Led initially, soon headed, snagged to race handy 3 wide with cover, shuffled back & niggled 550m, toiled into stretch & tailed off.
Broke OK, raced rail midfield, switched 1 off & driven 450m, quickened to edge lead outright 250m, tapered late, just held on.
Sharp start wide, settled 1 back on rail, edged 1 off 900m, pressed lead turning in & driven to share lead 300m, soon headed, battled on & just failed.
Smart start, settled midfield 1 off with cover, switched out & ridden 500m, battled on for 3rd.
Missed break, bustled rail to settle behind midfield, shifted out 500m, driven 400m, closed off for solid gains.
Taken behind to rail near rear, progress & switched out 500m, driven 400m, stayed on centre track without threatening.
Good break, sat midfield 1 off, shifted 3 wide 800m, driven widest 430m, kept on dourly centre track.
Fast break widest, soon led & to rail, shaken up 325m, headed 300m, no extra & tapered.
Missed break, raced last pair on inner, driven home turn, shifted centre track 300m, plugged on for minor inroads.
Broke well, raced handy 2 back on rail, shifted out & driven into stretch, tapered to wire.
Tardy start, rolled to sit handy 1 off no cover, got cover 900m, all out turning in, tame effort & faded.
Moderate break, caught 3 deep no cover midfield, forced wider 500m, ridden 350m, found nothing in tepid run home.
Slow start & rousted, raced 1 off behind midfield, niggled throughout, tame run to wire.
Sluggish start, raced 1 off near tail, niggled 1000m & some wide progress, ridden into stretch, found nothing.
Slow start, raced wide last pair, stoked 800m, found nothing in run home & never a factor.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead, clocked fast sectionals, hung on well to win.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield along the fence, 3.5Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 500M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Very slow away, 7Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, on heels 500M, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the fast pace, checked 600M, ran on well until 200M flattened.
Pushed early, settled in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3-4 wide, checked badly 600M, ran on ok in straight.
At rear, never a factor.
At back, trapped very wide, never competitive.
Pushed to keep up in midfield, 3Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace but trapped 3-4 wide, checked 600M, weakened afterwards.
Pushed early but failed to muster, 3.5Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, dropped off 400M.

Placing: DNF
Comment: Pressed forward, broke down 600M.
Jumped OK, ridden along to maintain forward position while edging closer to outside fence. Held behind horses from 800m, got clear 350m, powered home under hands and heels riding.
Began best, joined up front 800m but back in lead 600m. Looked winner 200m before run down close to line.
Was leaning on stall when gates opened and lost ground. Ridden along to keep tabs on leaders, shifted in 400m to get clear run and finished off strongly.
Began well, made to work to keep with pace while trying to get closer to outer fence. Raced fiercely when close to heels 500m, kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Jumped well but did not have enough speed to stay with leaders, settling behind horses 2.5L from leader. Held for run for some distance passing 500m, got clear 200m out and finished off strongly.
Jumped with field, ridden to maintain forward position while drifting to outer fence. Closed in on leaders and looked chance 400m but only one-paced final 200m.
Began OK, ridden along behind leading pack about 3L from leader. Ran about final 400m when put under pressure. Kept on OK.
Began fairly, allowed to settle behind midfield but away from outer fence. Kept on steadily down the middle of the track final 400m without looking dangerous.
Began fairly, taken closer to outer fence, settling in last pair. Clear last entering course proper but checked 70m when closing off nicely.

Jumped well, hard ridden early to stay with leaders while crossing to outside fence. Travelled well to 600m, shifted in for clear run, kept on well to 300m when hung and proved difficult to ride. One-paced.
Lost ground start, dropping to clear last. Remained at rear entering course proper and never competitive.
Began OK, hard ridden to take clear lead approaching 800m but headed 600m, Gave ground steadily after entering course proper.
Soon taken across from draw 9, settled in mid-division, moved out 500M, ran on strongly when driven passing 300M, led near 50M won going away.
In touch behind leaders, driven along nearing 500M, led 250M, continued on well but not pace of winner final stages.
Never far off, 3Ls off the pace along the 2-path, strong run turning home, challenged for the lead passing 200M, one paced final stages.
Not hurried, eased to the rear 8Ls off the pace, stayed on well under pressure, went 4th just before the line.
Settled in midfield, pushed to a 3-wide position halfway, progress on outer passing 500M, kept on evenly in straight, not troubled leaders.
Held up 3-wide and never far off from the pace, moved into contention 500M, briefly led early straight but soon joined by rivals, faded final 150M.
Taken across after the start, held up behind midfield first half, saved ground on the inside, crept closer to pace over the final turn, driven for some initial progress, one paced final 200M.
Pushed wide entering 1st turn, dropped back to a rearward spot, switched out 500M, stayed on only fairly.
Shaken up early to take the lead, set good pace first 800M, headed 300M, no extra and weakened towards line.
Dropped back from wide barrier and taken across, 7Ls off the pace middle stages, driven but never going the pace to challenge.
Pushed wide entering 1st turn, slotted into a 3-wide position at the rear, not picked up under pressure, eased 150M.
Held up towards the rear along the 3-path, ridden but no response passing 500M, soon behind.
Rushed forward from wide barrier, caught 3-wide until 900M, driven along to keep up with leader home turn, swamped entering straight, soon no extra.
Always prominent, came under serious pressure 500M and gave ground, weakened to last.
Began well, sat on tail of leader and carted in from wide draw across field with little effort. Kicked clear passing 250m and finished off strongly.
Began OK, pushed along fence to grab box seat entering back stretch. Boxed in top of straight, finished off nicely when clear 150m.
Began awkwardly, ridden along to hold position before settling 3-back, the fence. Came off rail 350m and ran home steadily.
Began well, ridden along early before settling 3-back, one-off. Taken 3-wide entering straight and ran home steadily without looking dangerous.
Jumped OK, not much early speed, dropping 4-back from leader along fence. Stayed on fence around turn, shifted out 300m for run, kept on steadily.
Stumbled start, hard ridden to lead then quickly cut to fence from wide draw to set good pace to straight. Caught 300m out but kept on well until swamped final stages.
Steadied shortly after start, dropping to rear. Took closer order entering final turn, raced tightly 300m, one-paced thereafter.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to rear but wide. Hampered around final turn, dropped to last entering straight, ran past tired horses final stages.
Began well, hard ridden to hold forward position one-off, one-back. Kept on early in straight before tiring final stages.
Fractious in gate, bounded in air and lost ground start. Trailed field to final turn, taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
Began OK, not much speed. dropping to one-off position towards rear. Crowded for room around final turn, found little in straight.
Began fairly, hard ridden to go forward from wide draw but failed to muster and caught wide without cover at rear. Covered extra ground around final turn and faded badly in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide in 5th, 4 lengths back, gradually improved 3 wide on turn, finished off strongly in straight and scored by a head.
Jumped well from widest draw, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, travelled well to turn, took the lead after turning in, headed near 200M (rider dropped whip), stayed on well to finish 2nd.
Began awkwardly, raced 8 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line, just failed to get 2nd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 5 lengths back, same position to turn, finished off well to make frame.
Away with them, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, similar position to turn, closed off well to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, raced 3 lengths back on rail in 4th, easy run and saved ground to turn, ridden 300M, lacked an extra gear and just finished off evenly, never a threat to the first few.
Began well, raced handy in 3rd, 2 lengths back, similar position to turn, made no progress after straightening, finished off one-pace.
Average to begin, positioned on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening, made no progress.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 8 lengths back 2 wide at rear, under pressure turning, taken widest in straight and passed some tired runners.
Slowly away, raced 7 lengths back on rail at rear, well back at turn, showed no turn of foot in straight, only passed a few tired runners.
Fairly away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield before turn, 5 lengths back, 4 wide no cover turning, made some progress until 200M, eased thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead and set an even tempo, headed shortly after turning in and dropped off gradually. (Lame next day)
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, emptied early in straight, never competitive.

Niggled along in a prominent position, in 5th and about 2L off the pace around the bend, soon came to challenge in straight and hit the front passing 200 metres, held up under pressure.
Jumped fairly, settled towards the rear, finished off race well but unable to peg back the winner.
Jumped well, settled one back on rails, kept on steadily without quickening.
Jumped moderately from the widest gate, travelled in forward of midfield and wide without cover most of way, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Began moderately, settled in rear of midfield, remained similar to straight, baulked behind runners early in straight, kept on steadily to finish.
Broke well from a poor gate, soon taken back for cover travelling in 6th in forward of midfield, kept on same pace without quickening in straight.
Jumped moderately, settled behind midfield on rails, angled off rails on straightening, kept on steadily while not having much room most of straight.
Travelled well back, kept on steadily past well-beaten runners in the straight.
Jumped moderately, settled wide in last few, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly, settled in last few, went widest into straight, one-paced under pressure running down the centre of the track.
Jumped moderately, ridden to dispute lead around the bend gaining narrow advantage early in straight, unable to sustain effort and folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Began from a poor gate, raced wide prominently far side before moving up to 3-wide in 3rd around the bend, weakened passing 300 metres.

Jumped fairly from a middle draw, gradually took up running and obtained rails run 1000 metres out, held slender advantage to 400 metres when narrowly headed, folded up quickly inside final 200 metres.
Never seen with a chance.
Ridden patiently in second last position, 1 off the rail. Peeled out after the 700m, came widest in the straight and let down well to take control near the 50m.
Had every chance after box seating. Held up slightly early in the straight and looked the likely winner at the 100m, but ended its run approaching the 50m.
Travelled 4th from the rear, 1 off with cover. Held up until near the 200m, motored home once in the clear.
Raced behind midfield, 3 wide with cover. Stayed on evenly.
Parked midfield, 1 off with cover. Maintained and even gallop down the running.
Settled midfield, 3 deep with cover. Was dour in the home stretch.
Camped in second position outside the leader. Was overhauled at the 200m and weakened thereafter.
Effectively settled in the box seat. Shifted out into clear running turning for home only plodded to the line.
Went forward and led on the rails. Faded over the final 200m.
Punched the breeze, three deep without cover, whilst travelling prominently. Never likely.
Wasn't the best away, travelling midfield the paint, had cover. Gave in quickly near the furlong.
Was never in the hunt after becoming detached in last position. Was ridden along from the 700m, didn't respond and finished well back. (To trial)
Settled towards the rear 3 deep with cover. Failed to close off.
Went back from a wide gate, settled behind midfield, the fence with cover. Struggled in the home straight. (Collapsed after race, see incident report)
Hard ridden forward to settle outside the leader at slightly slow tempo, battled on strongly to score by a short head.
Pushed forward to obtain the box seat, benefited by the slightly slow pace, however could not find a day night until final 150M, ran on strongly thereafter to get 2nd.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slightly slow tempo, ran on well until last 50M weakened for 3rd.
Sent forward to take the fence and led at slightly slow sectionals, kept on well to get 4th.
Eased back, settled 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slightly slow pace, dashed well.
Settled worse than midfield, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slightly slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Taken back from wide barrier, travelled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slightly slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on until final 150M weakened.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the slightly slow tempo, never ran on.
Always at rear, never looked chance.
At rear, never a factor.
Prominent, despite benefited by the slightly slow tempo, flattened soon after straightening.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls on the fence, not suited by the slightly slow sectionals, unable to show any dash in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, no progressed.

Began well, led initially before handing up and settling one-back, one-off. Shuffled back to fourth entering turn, 4-wide into straight, picked up momentum to hit front 200m, pulled clear. Lame left front.
Bumped soon after start, mustered along fence to take lead 1100m, momentarily headed 900m, retook lead, caught 200m but boxed on well.
Ridden along early but trapped wide without cover. Rolled forward from 1000m to sit outside leader before turn, kept on steadily in straight under hard riding.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail and box seat. Saved ground turn, switched out 400m to get clear running, kept on steadily.
Jumped with field but caught wide and allowed to drift back to 2nd last along fence. Made forward move from 800m, four-wide around turn, taken to centre track straight and ran on steadily.
Began well, ridden along but rapped wide from 900m. Bumped and unbalance turn, wide into straight, kept on steadily.. Had substantial amount of blood in trachea.

Began only fairly and then crowded out 1100m dropping back. Checked on heels around turn, wide into straight, ran on well final 200m. Found to be lame right front and had substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Began OK, crowded out 1100m, cut to rail, saved ground home turn, got rails run in straight, making ground steadily until flattened 100m.
A little slow into stride, hard ridden but didn't muster, settling at rear along rail. Turned in behind horses and kept shifting in straight to get clear running. One-paced.
Began awkwardly, losing considerable ground. Trailed field to straight and ran past beaten horses.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to rear away from fence. Taken very wide entering straight but only one-paced.
Began well, ridden along early settling three-back the fence. Put under pressure turning for home but found little and slipped back gradually.
Bumped shortly after start, recovered and travelled nicely four-back, one-off. Put under pressure top of straight but failed to respond. Faded.
Pressed forward from wide draw to race alongside early leaders before settling three-back, one-off. Shifted out 600m, checked rounding turn, faded gradually.
Began well, mustered along fence to grab box seat back stretch. Came off fence entering straight, lengthened gradually under hard riding, hit from 150m, tiring at finish but just held.
Jumped with field, ridden along 3-back from leader in a one-off position. Taken wide in straight and ran on strongly to just miss.
Began well, ridden along early to stay ahead of midfield away from fence. Wide around turn, taken to centre field in straight and finished off strongly.
Got off well but snagged back from wide draw to sit at rear. Switched out 3-wide final turn, ran on steadily in straight while hanging in. Rider reported difficult to ride.
Bumped and unbalanced start, pressed forward to share lead 800m. Joint leader into straight, kept battling until 50m when swamped.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to rear. Taken wide entering straight, picked up momentum from 300m to be closest at finish.
Quickly into stride, setting steady pace. Joined 800m, still in front entering straight, kept battling until flattened final 50m.
Ridden forward to find cover but trapped 3-wide back stretch and turn. Kept on steadily in straight without threatening.
Ridden along but trapped 4-wide without cover. Covered extra ground home turn but kept plugging away in straight.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, dropping to last. Put under pressure from home turn, switch out 400m for clear running, little response and ridden hands and heels final 200m.
Began awkwardly, recovered and taken to fence behind midfield. Stayed on fence turning for home but found little in straight. Lame right front.
Began fairly, taken to fence towards rear. Hard ridden from turn to hold position, but gave ground gradually in straight.
Pressed forward 3-wide to stay with leading pack before settling one-back, one-off back stretch. Under pressure soon after straightening for home and gave ground gradually.
Began OK and ridden along to hold fence 4-back from leader. Got shuffled back turning for home and found nothing under hard riding in straight.
Slow away, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace, just won by a narrow margin.
In front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader on the fence, lack room 400M, dashed well when clear, just missed by a head in 2nd.
Box seat behind the slow pace, momentarily held up 400M, closed off strongly when clear.
Pressed forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, led 400M, ran on until 100M flattened.
Eased at start and took rail, 6.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, dashed strongly when clear.
Midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, moved forward 600M to take advantages from the slow pace, hit the front 400M, out of fuel 150M.
Pushed forward, shared the lead 2 wide at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on until 250M flattened.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, checked 150M, never tested.
In front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened 200M.
Eased at start, 7Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, made early move 600M, no dash in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, weakened 400M.
Pressed forward, took rail and shared the lead, clocked slow sectionals, reduced quickly 400M.
Began OK, restrained and taken back but away from fence. Moved forward 3-wide from 500m widest into straight, picked up momentum from 200m and finished strongly for easy win.
Began well, ridden forward to sit outside leader. Took over lead 350m, well clear 200m, flattened final 50m.
Began awkwardly, ridden forward but unable find cover and held 3-wide. Covered extra ground turn, took time to wind up in straight, doing best work final 200m.
Missed the start, taken to fence, improved to 3-back from leader. Saved ground final turn, came off fence 250m, kept on steadily.
Began fairly, didn't really settle throwing head about. Got close to heels 900m, shuffled back entering straight, ran on steadily final 300m.
Began OK, no early speed settling midfield but wide. Covered extra ground around turn, wide into straight, kept on steady without threatening.
Jumped well, no early space, settling between horse in midfield. Ran on steadily early straight turning one-paced from 200m.
Jumped straight to the front, set slow pace, put under pressure entering straight but caught 350m and weakened steadily. Substantial amount of blood in trachea.
Began best, not pushed, settling in box seat in slipstream of leader. Put under pressure on straightening but found little, tiring quickly after passing 200m.

Placing: PU
Comment: Began well, snagged back to last and taken to fence. Broke down around home turn and pulled up in straight.
Held up towards rear, shaken up nearing 600M and moved closer to pace, quickened up strongly to press leader mid-straight, dueled final 200M and gained upper hand near line.
Restrained in mid-division, switched back to inner entering straight, quickened well to lead 250M but soon joined by a rival, dueled final 200M, hung out late on, headed near line.
Held up in mid-division, shuffled back to near the rear passing 500M, responded well when gap opened up inside 300M, went 3rd 200M out but well held by first two.
Not far off from leader, raced 3-wide without cover for majority of race and did not settle, moved into a contending position 400M, stayed on moderately and not pace of first 3 final 200M.
Dropped back to the rear 7Ls off leader, mildly urged 600M out, progress on outer, stayed on over final 300M without threatening.
Soon taken across behind runners, settled near last, closed off fairly final 400M, never troubled leaders.
Led uncontested, set quicker pace middle stages, headed near 300M, no extra final stages.
Sat 4Ls off the pace in first half, crept closer home turn, not quickened under pressure entering final 400M, never threatened.
Positioned one out one back, couldn't sprint with them passing 400M, checked near 200M and eased towards the line.
Slow to muster despite ridden along, raced keenly behind leader, came under pressure 600M, dropped away to last.
Began well, restrained, settling between horses 3L from leader. Taken 3-wide around turn, pressed forward entering straight, drew clear passing 200m, won eased down.
Began well, ridden along one-back, one-off to turn. Switched 3-wide entering straight and ran on solidly to snatch quinella on line.
Jumped best and led to 1000m before sitting outside leader into turn. Back in front 300m and kept battling when passed. Just missed quinella.
Jumped with field before settling 3-back the fence. Saved ground turn, found little room entering straight, finished off nicely when clear 200m.
Began fairly, pressed forward from wide draw to lead 1000m, cutting to fence 800m. Collared 300m out but kept battling till swamped final stages.
Bumped start, recovered and rolled forward along fence to grab box seat. Stayed on fence turning for home, got inside run top of straight, looked chance 200m before tuning one-paced.
Began fairly, taken across behind runners but kept away from fence towards the rear. Held for run entering straight, kept on steadily when clear.
Jumped with field, restrained and taken across behind runners from wide draw. Improved along fence turning for home. kept on steadily early in straight turning one-paced final stages.
Began well, ridden along early but held 3-wide without cover. Taken further out turning for home, rallied early in straight before tiring.
Began awkwardly, ridden along between horses, got close to heels entering turn, one-paced in straight.
Began OK, not pushed and settled behind midfield 3-wide with cover. Lost position home turn, ran on well early in straight becoming one-paced final 200m.
Began fairly, didn't settle throwing head around several times while trying to hang out. Found little in straight under hard riding.
Began OK, snagged back and taken across behind horses settling at rear. Raced tight final turn, taken out in straight, found little.
Began fairly, no pace, settling at rear away from fence. Shuffled back to last entering straight, never competitive.
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in front of midfield, saved ground to turn, no daylight early in straight, closed off well when clear to score narrowly.
Slightly slowly away, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, similar position to turn, finished off very strongly in straight, just missed by a short-head.
Away with them, raced a length back on rail in 4th, easy run to turn, took the lead near 250M, unable to hold off the first two late.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide in 5th, 2 lengths back, same position to turn, angled out early in straight and kept on evenly to make frame.
Slowly away, raced 8 lengths back at rear, taken wider and improved on turn, made reasonable headway in straight to be not far away at finish.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced at tail throughout, 9 lengths back, still well back on turn, taken widest after turning in and made good progress to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from a wide draw, positioned 2 wide in 3rd, a length back, same margin to turn, made no progress after straightening, finished off one-paced.
Began awkwardly, raced 4-5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, made some progress in straight, reasonable debut.
Slowly away from a wide draw, recovered to race outside leader in 2nd, shared lead to turn, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began fairly, raced 6 lengths back on rails at rear, similar position to turn, made some ground in straight but never a threat.
Jumped well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover in midfield throughout, weakened early in straight after hard run took toll.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 4-5 lengths back, made little progress after turning in, wasn't threatening when checked at 200M.
Began well from a wide gate, sent forward to take the lead and set a moderate tempo, travelled well to turn, headed near 300M, emptied and dropped out thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, there to turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.

Jumped moderately, settled in midfield, commenced move and switched widest into straight, quickened up well down the centre of the track to swoop on horses, won with authority.

Jumped well from a low draw, soon held back from the front to settle in forward of midfield mainly in 3L 5th on rails, commenced moved turning in, fought on steadily to hold good chance but outsprinted by winner close to line.
Jumped well, raced 3-wide prominently before shifting in to one off the rails in 1L 2nd, soon came to challenge turning in hitting the front briefly over 100 metres out but swamped close to home.
Slightly slow out, settled in last few and waited with, commenced move entering straight, ran on well between runners to be nearest at finish.
Broke well from a poor draw to contest lead, took up running coming out of home straight the first time setting a steady pace, headed under pressure over 100 metres out, swamped for a placing late.

Jumped fairly from a poor gate but ridden positively to take up rails run in 2L 3rd rounding stables bend, commenced move approaching home turn but baulked and held up on heels of runners most of way in straight.

Broke well, settled in 4th within 3L of pace, commenced move over 400 metres out to come within 2L of lead in 3rd when 3-wide turning for home, looked a place chance closing stages but unable to sustain inside final 100 metres.

Soon taken across from the widest draw to trail the field, remained similar entering straight but saved a lot of ground turning in, made modest progress under pressure in straight without threatening.
Slow out, settled one from last, made swift headway around field from the 900 metres to reach 4th briefly when 4-wide around the bend, unable to sustain run after straightening.
Began well from a poor draw, gradually taken back for cover to behind midfield in 9th, became 10th around home bend, made no impression in the run home.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield on rails, lost position around the Rock, towards the rear home bend but saved ground turning in, tired badly.
Jumped fairly, settled 3-wide without cover most of way in midfield in 6th, weakened out of contention under pressure from over 400 metres out.
Box seated. Hit the front at the 150m, managed to repel late challenge to win by the narrowest of margins.
Ridden nicely from a wide gate to settle 3 back the fence with cover. Finished off with plenty of purpose, laid in over the final 100m, which didn't help its cause.
Camped behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Shifted deep on straightening, closed off well.
Showed plenty of gate speed, then drifted back to settle 1 off with cover, midfield. Finished off soundly.
Speared forward and led on the fence. Commenced to give ground near the 100m.
Travelled in 2nd position, outside the leader. Had every chance, faded over the final 150m.
Didn't enjoy the best of trips after being crowded at the start then being checked at the 800m. Raced towards the rear one off with cover. Did nothing in the run home.
Travelled worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Kept on at the same pace down the running.
Missed the start settling second last on the paint with cover. Was one paced in the home stretch.
Was detached for most of the race in last position. Made no impression finishing with backmakers.
Effectively raced one out one back. Raced keenly in the early stages, struggled in the home straight, finishing at the rear.
Hard ridden forward to settle 1L behind the leader without cover, benefited by the slightly slow tempo, dashed strongly to score by 1-3/4L.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slightly slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow tempo, kept on well until final 100M weakened to get 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slightly slow pace, closed to the line well.
Sent forward to occupy the box seat, despite benefited by the slightly slow sectionals, kept on one pace without any threats.
Settled worse than midfield about 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slightly slow tempo, made some ground in straight.

At rear, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, despite not suited by the slightly slow sectionals, made some ground in straight. (substantial amount of blood in trachea)
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slightly slow pace, unable to show any dash in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 5.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suite by the slightly slow tempo, never ran on.
Pushed forward, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened over the last furlong.
Never a factor.

Began awkwardly, then pushed to settle 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slightly slow tempo, never ran on and finished tailed out. (questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)

Jumped well, restrained and take across behind horses to rail, dropping to last back stretch. Improved around turn, switched out 400m but had to shift across heels for clear run approaching 200m. Ran on strongly to just get there.
Jumped to the front, ridden along to hold position before dropping to 3rd 1200m. Shuffled back to 5th passing 900m, 4-wide entering straight, rolled forward to lead 200m, run down last two strides.
Ridden along early to get forward position before settling in midfield away from fence. Taken wide turning for home and battled on gamely to get 3rd close to line.
Began OK, ridden along to get forward position but held 3-wide into first turn. Edged closer turning for home, looked chance 200m, one-paced final stages.
Bumped start, mustered along rail to sit inside leaders from 1200m before taking over lead passing 900m. Kept on well early in straight before caught 100m and swamped final stages.
Began fairly, allowed to settle grabbing rail 3-back from leader. Stayed on rail turning for home, switched out 200m to make run, kept on steadily.
Bumped and unbalanced start, recovered and rolled into box seat around first turn as leaders fanned out. Saved ground final turn, got inside run but only one-paced final 200m.
Jumped OK but snagged back and taken across behind runners but still held 3-wide first turn. Continued to race wide back stretch, gave ground steadily in straight.
Slow into stride, ridden to catch up but kept away from fence. Shifted in abruptly passing 1000m, widest on straightened, one-paced.
Hard ridden to go forward, taking lead passing the 1200m before settling outside leader from 900m. Kept on early in straight before running on empty from 200m.
Ridden forward from wide gate but unable to find cover and raced 3-wide mostly. Bumped and taken wider from 450m, tired passing 200m.
Began OK, allowed to settle, dropping towards the rear away from the fence. Put under pressure turning for home but found little.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, cutting to rail. Set steady pace to straight and kept finding when challenged final 200m.
Began well, unable to match speed of leader and settled in box seat. Came off rail 450m, threw out challenge from 300m, unable to close gap.
Bumped after start, mustered, settling one-back, one-off. Denied run top of straight, shifted out 200m, finished off nicely.
Ridden out early to hold fence 2-back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn to look chance top of straight. Kept on steadily to 100m when flattened.
Began well, pressed forward to sit outside leader, lay out around final turn and early straight, one paced from 200m.
Began awkwardly, dropping to last and cutting in to fence, Switched out 400m to get clear run, kept on steadily doing best work at finish.
Began OK but not pushed, easing back through field to sit in last pair away from fence. Clear last entering straight, taken very wide and ran on fairly.
Bumped start, rolled forward to sit behind midfield away from fence. Taken wide entering straight but only one-paced final 300m.
Began well, pressed forward but held wide in midfield. Put under pressure entering straight but only one-pace.
Began fairly, hard ridden but didn't muster, slipping back to rear. Took closer order around turn but found little in straight. Not ridden out final stages when beaten.
At back, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M to score.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M for 2nd.
Box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
In front of midfield, 3Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, hung in 300M, hampered 250M, just held ground in straight.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader on the rails, favoured by the fast tempo, made minor ground 250M.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, flattened 200M.
Eased at start and took rail behind the field, 6.5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Pushed to share the lead 2 wide at fast sectionals, out of fuel 250M.
Slow away, 3.5Ls off the leader along the fence, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, flattened 200.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead, under pressure throughout and harmed by the fast pace, soon emptied 300M.
Crowded out start, picked up quickly to sit behind 4-way fight for lead, easing 2-back entering turn. Switched out 250m to get clear running and finished off strongly.
Raced in restricted room after start, shuffled back to last pair along fence. Stayed inside turning for home, found split 200m out and ran on strongly.
Began fairly, ridden along behind midfield but away from fence. Taken very wide entering straight and ran on steadily.
Dislodged jockey before start. Began well and then pressed forward to join 4-way fight for lead. Got ahead 550m, joint leader to 80m when swamped.
Began well, ridden along early, cut in to fence and improved position. Turned in behind leaders and kept on well to the line.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Over-raced 1000m when got close to heels, taken out from 400m and ran home strongly down the centre of the track.
Began well and joined cut-throat battle for early lead before settling one-back, one-off entering turn. Kept on steadily to 250m when bumped and unbalanced. Faded.
Began well, ridden to hold forward position and caught in 4-way battle for early lead. Kept on steadily in straight under hard riding but flattened final stages.
Slow into stride, last on settling, cut to fence and took closer order. Stayed on fence in straight but only one-paced final 300m.
Began well, hard ridden out wide to join battle for lead, raced without cover thereafter. Gave ground soon after straightening for home.
Jumped OK, ridden along early but kept 3-wide mostly. Lost left hind plate 900m. Found little in straight.
Jumped fairly, ridden along early but held wide. Stayed towards rear mostly and never competitive.
Utilised his inside draw well to take the lead, set steady tempo, kept finding extra in straight to fend off pursuers, shifted out abruptly late stages but had enough to hold on.
Held up in midfield about 3Ls off leader, taken wide passing 400M, strong late challenge to clinch 2nd near line.
Began well, sat handily behind leaders but no closer than 3-wide throughout, stayed on final 250M and slowly getting to winner.
In touch just behind the pace, ridden 450M and loomed outside leader, pushed winner all the way to the line but always held, lost 3rd near line.
Began very awkwardly, settled in mid-division along the rails, headway on inner passing 400M, still pressing winner when not much room entering straight, faded closing stages.
Restrained in midfield, shuffled backwards nearing the turn, 5Ls to make up on leader 400M, ran on well despite not clearest of runs entering 200M.
Dropped back to last from wide draw, proved difficult to settle, blundered near 750M, waited with till 400M, closed off well when driven, not much room late stages. (Tactics questioned.)
Engaged in early speed battle, eased back 1000M to sit behind leaders, shuffled back a bit home turn, held every chance in straight but not making headway on leaders, weakened final stages.
Began only fairly, held up towards the rear along the fence, stayed on mildly over this shorter trip, not much room late stages.
Raced keenly in a 3-wide position behind midfield, kept on same pace in straight, no impression on leaders.
Crossed to a 3-wide spot in midfield from draw 11, placed under pressure 450M, swung widest for home, kept on same pace to line.
Vied for early lead, chased leader 2-wide, came under pressure inside 400M, weakened 300M and soon lost touch.

Jumped well, tracked leader, cantered to lead over 300 metres over, soon drew clear.
Jumped well from the one draw, held lead to 300 metres when outclassed, held on for 2nd.
Prominent early, gradually shuffled back to 4L 5th home bend, saved ground on rails turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Jumped fairly from a poor gate, soon taken back to 4th within 3L of pace but wide without cover, came under pressure entering straight, one-paced.
Moderate start, settled one from last in 6th on rails, made no impression in the run home.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, soon picked up to one-back on rails, came to challenge entering straight, found nothing.
Slow out, lacked pace, always well behind.
Enjoyed all the favours in the box seat. Obtained a nice run turning for home had the race in its keeping at the 200m.
Went back from a wide gate to travel at the rear, 1 off with cover. Swung widest on the home turn and finished off well.
Travelled midfield the fence, had cover. Kept battling away right to the line.
Camped 2nd from the rear, 2 deep with cover. Shifted out on straightening and closed off well.
Parked in 5th position, 2 wide with cover. Peeled out prior to the home turn, was dour in the run home.
Shared leading duties along the fence. Was overhauled near the 250m, and gave in quickly soon after.
Was left racing 3 wide without cover midfield, after the 1000m. Only plodded to the line. (Lame in the R/F the next day)
Settled worse than midfield, on the fence with cover. Made some ground along the inside until the 200m, but ended its run shortly after.
Settled just off midfield, 3 deep with cover. Commenced to weaken over about the last 250m.
Settled back in the field, on the paint with cover. Failed to close off.
Raced 1 off without cover before effectively setting 1 out 1 back midrace. Was yielding ground approaching the 300m.

Raced three wide without cover in the leading division before eventually crossing to race 1 off whilst continuing to vie for the lead. Was a spent force before the home turn & was gone at the 300m & tailed out. (To trial)
Raced 4th last, 2 deep with cover. Struggled in the home straight and tailed out. (To trial)
Travelled midfield, 2 deep with cover. Was a beaten horse prior to the home turn and finished tailed out. (To trial)
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1-1/4L, made all and scored comfortably.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, ran on steadily to get 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 4 wide without cover, kept on one pace for 3rd without threatening.
Pushed to settle midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, ran on well for 4th.
Taken back, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide turning in, ran on nicely.
Raced midfield, settled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight.
Settled in front of midfield, 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on only fairly when clear 300M.
Ridden forward to settle 1L behind the leader 2 wide without cover, kept on one pace to the line.
Eased back from wide barrier, settled 7.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, closed to the line well.
Hard ridden forward, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, unable to show any dash after straightening.
Lacked early pace, settled worse than midfield 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 6.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never looked competitive.
Never a factor.

Began well, held and allowed to drift back to the tail between horses. Switched off until home turn when edged out but unable find run. Bumped when taking split 250m but ran on strongly to win close home.
Snagged back from wide draw but held 3-wide at the rear. Taken wide turning for home, rolled forward from 400m, bumped and unbalanced 200m, kept on strongly.
Ridden along early to lead but held wide, easing to second passing 1000m. Stalked leader to straight, kicked ahead 350m, kept on well till swamped last few strides.
Hard ridden from wide draw to get forward position and thereafter raced without cover. Covered extra ground turn, kicked ahead to share lead 350m, kept on well till flattened final strides.

Jumped well, ridden along to hold rails inside leading pack before easing back to box seat turning for home. Caught behind horses entering straight, raced awkwardly when close to heels 300m, ran on steadily when clear 200m.
Ridden along early despite being held 4-wide, settling in midfield. Turned wide, kept on steadily in straight under hard riding.
Began well, pushed along early inside leader before easing to fifth entering turn. Wide into straight and kept on steadily under hard riding.

Jumped fairly, eased and taken across behind horses in last place to rail, then improved position from 1000m to 900m. Stayed on rail turning for home, kept on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Jumped fairly, ridden at own pace but 3-wide behind midfield. Turned in behind wall of horses and no run till passing 200m. Ran on steadily.
Steadied after start. recovered and held rail 3-back from leader. Saved ground turn, ran on steadily before badly held up 100m and not fully tested.
Ridden along early to keep tabs on leaders but held 3-wide mostly. Rolled forward entering straight, had clear run but only one-paced.
Jumped fairly, outpaced and soon in last trio along fence. Dropped to last entering turn. Taken out gradually in straight to get run, finishing widest without making ground.
Jumped OK but not pushed, settling towards rear in a one-off position. Entered straight behind horses and had difficulty in finding run. Not properly tested.
Began well, pushed along inside leaders to take lead 1000m. Collared soon after entering straight and faded gradually.
Jumped well, eased to sit 3-back from leader but away from fence. Turned 5-wide into straight, rolled forward, hit front 200m and pulled clear under hands and heels riding.
Jumped OK but snagged back from wide draw and clear last before home turn. Crept closer from 500m, wide into straight, finished off strongly.
Jumped with field but no early pace, drifting back to rear but away from fence. Straightened behind horses, had clear running passing 400m and ran on steadily.
Began awkwardly, shifted out and bumped, but quickly on the bit and travelled nicely to 700m when got head on side and lay out. Kept on in straight under hard riding.
Quickly into stride to lead on settling, crossing to rail passing 900m but headed 700m, taking box seat. Urged forward top of straight, led passing 300m but running on empty final 100m.
Began fairly, outpaced and soon at rear close to rail. Switched out passing 500m and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began well, hugging rail inside leading pair before settling in box seat before turn. Not much room top of straight but only one-paced when clear, fading final stages.
Bumped after start, pressed forward and ran mostly wide thereafter. Looked a chance when rolled forward top of straight but run ended passing 200m.
Jumped fairly, no early pace, settling behind midfield close to fence. Stayed on fence turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Began well, ridden to maintain forward position passing 700m. Caught 300m out and faded gradually.
Jumped with field, ridden positively but didn't settle and allowed to stride forward to lead passing 700m, caught 300m out and faded gradually.
Pushed forward early, shuffled back 800M, 3Ls off the leader 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to score.
In front of midfield, 2Ls off the leader 3 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Eased at start and crossed behind the field but soon obtained a midfield along the fence, 3.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, held up 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 3 wide, demonstrated its usual strong finishing efforts 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, checked badly 800M when the pace slackened, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Extremely slow away, 6.5Ls off the leader on the fence, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pressed forward but trapped very wide, attempted to eased back for cover but failed, moved forward again 1100M, sat outside the leader at slow sectionals, flattened 200M.
Hard ridden to take rail, led by 0.5L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 150M flattened.
At rear, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 250M.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
Pressed forward, 2Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, never picked up, out of fuel 300M.
Box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, however soon emptied 400M.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, trapped 4 wide and raced keenly throughout, soon reduced 300M.
Crowded out start, taken across behind runners to be last in one-off position. Moved up around turn, switched out 350m for clear run, finished strongly to win on line.
Bumped start, recovered and driven forward between horses settling 3L from leader. Edged closer around turn, ran on strongly in straight to just miss.
Jumped best, led for few strides before easing off to settle in a one-back, one-off position. Shaken up top of straight, took lead 250m, kept on well till swamped last few strides.
Began OK, ridden to maintain forward position 2-back from leader. Came off fence 600m, ran on well but hampered 250m when caught between horses. Kept on. Lost both front plates in the running.
Jumped well, pressed forward to lead from 1000m before headed 800m. Retook lead entering straight, collared 300m, kept on one-paced.

Began fairly, hard ridden along rail to make up ground, settling in box seat 800m. Saved ground turn, not much room top of straight, checked 250m and shifted in abruptly, kept on one-paced. Had substantial blood in trachea.
Began fairly, outpaced, settling towards rear but away from fence. Improved around turn but one-paced home stretch.
Jumped OK, outpaced. settling towards rear. Switch out turning for home, wide in straight, one-paced.
Bumped start, outpaced, settling in last pair close to fence. Taken out at home turn but found little in straight under hard riding.
Began OK and ridden along early to hold position behind midfield. Taken very wide on straightening but only one-paced.
Began fairly, outpaced, settling at rear. Shuffled back to last turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Crowded out start, pressed forward but wide to lead passing 800m in a one-off position. Started to give ground soon after entering straight.
Began fairly, ridden along but outpaced, settling toward rear and wide. Taken wider turning for home but never competitive.

Pressed forward from wide draw to sit behind early pace but wide. Started to give ground shortly after entering straight. Found to be suffering from irregular heart rhythm and had substantial blood in trachea.
Allowed an easy lead, set very slow pace first half of the race, joined by rivals passing 600M, stayed on best of all final 300M under top weight, always holding off the persistent 2nd and 3rd.
Had a nice trail behind leader in a slowly run race, moved out to challenge inside 500M, kept giving under pressure but always held by winner.
Began very awkwardly and lost ground, caught 3-wde early then strode to race outside the lead, pressed leader inside 600M, fought on well to the finish but always held.
Began very awkwardly, settled in midfield 3-4Ls off the pace, kept on evenly entering straight, never troubled leaders.
Held up behind midfield, stayed on well initially after straightening, briefly went 4th 200M but faded over 150M.
Reserved in midfield in a slowly run race, driven passing 600M, stayed on evenly final 400M without reaching leaders.
Given a waiting ride, held up in rear 6-7Ls off the slow pace, kept to inside entering straight, ran on only fairly and never reached contention.
Settled in 4th place, always in touch, brought wide passing 600M, outpaced inside 400M, weakened towards the finish.
Held up near rear, not helped by the slow pace, overraced for the majority of the event, unable to pick up under pressure, never threatened.
Held up at the rear, switched wide nearing 500M, not quickened.

Began well, hard ridden to go forward, leading to 1150m before easing off to sit outside leader. Shaken up again 600m, rolled forward but wide to lead entering straight, pulled clear for effortless win.

Jumped well but caught wide and eased back through field to find cover, landing at the rear. Got caught in bumping match 1000m to 900m, switched out 600m,ran on strongly down centre field but unable match winner.
Pressed forward after jumping well but trapped four-wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, looked chance top of straight, kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began fairly, no early speed and allowed to settle between horses towards the rear. Got strung up in traffic around turn, but finished off nicely from 300m when clear.
Got off OK, rolled forward between horses to get within 3L of leader and switched off. Entered straight behind horses, switched in for clear running, kept on steadily.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail, grabbing box seat back stretch. Came off fence 600m to challenge, looked chance entering straight but run ended 200m, one-paced.

Began well but snagged back and taken across behind runners to sit at rear. Got into bumping match with eventual runner-up 1000m to 900m, turned in behind horses but ran on steadily when clear from 350m.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold forward position but forced to race 3-wide mostly. Rolled forward turning for home but effort was short-lived. One-paced.
Began fairly, ridden along but wide back stretch. Bumped and unbalanced turn, kept on one-paced in straight.
Crowded out at start but recovered and mustered to settle one-back, one-off before turn. Got shuffled back entering straight and found little under hard riding.
Jumped with field but restrained, drifting back to clear last. Switched out from 600m, widest into straight, ran past beaten horses.
Checked on jumping and made heavy contract with another. Rallied along rail to sit at midfield before turn. Stayed on fence and made ground to straight before turning one-paced.
Bumped and unbalanced start, recovered and mustered close to fence to take lead passing 1150m. Collard entering straight and faded gradually.
Began fairly, taken closer to rail before settling toward rear. Improved position around turn but tired soon after straightening and finished tailed off. Unacceptable performance.
Average to begin, raced 5 lengths back at rear on rail, saved ground to turn gradually improved along the rail turning, closed off well final 250M to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, angled out near 600M and slightly improved, finished off strongly in straight to get 2nd.
Began well from the widest gate, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd outside leader, shared lead at turn, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Fairly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, 3 wide at turn, no clear running until near 200M, finished off strongly when clear thereafter to make frame.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4 lengths back, similar position to turn, angled out in straight and made reasonable headway, just missed frame.
Began well, raced 2 wide in front of midfield, 2 lengths back, similar position to turn, kept battling away in straight, holding ground.
Jumped with them, positioned 4 lengths back on rail, slightly improved along the rail at turn, no clear running in straight, not tested. (See racing incidents.)
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead and set a moderate tempo, shared lead at turn, headed near 300M, kept on evenly thereafter.
Average to begin, taken back to race at tail, 5-6 lengths back, angled out at turn, made minor headway in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover, 1-2 lengths back, improved to challenge on turn, didn't finished off final 300M.
Began fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in and difficult to settle early, travelled 4 wide without cover in midfield to turn, made no progress in straight after hard run took toll.
Fairly away from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position to turn, made no headway in straight, kept on one-paced.
Jumped well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, showed no response after turning in and dropped out gradually.
Began fairly, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail, 2 wide with cover at turn, last turning in, emptied early in straight, gave in cheaply.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead and set a slow tempo, shared lead to turn, kept on very well in straight, kicked scored easily.

Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race at tail, 7 lengths back, niggled along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, no daylight until 100M, finished off well when clear to get 2nd.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced 4-5 lengths back at rear on rail, checked near 700M, took inside runs and finished off strongly in straight, just missed 2nd.
Jumped well, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, 5-6 lengths back, still well back turning, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly late to make frame.
Average to begin, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, slightly improved on turn, looked a place chance at 200M, just missed frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in front of midfield, 2 lengths back, 3 wide with no cover at turn, made some headway after straightening, never a threat to the first few.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position to turn, no clear running early in straight, finished off evenly when clear final 250M.
Jumped with them from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover in midfield, sent forward to race outside leader at turn, emptied in straight after hard run took toll.
Slowly away, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4-5 lengths back, similar margin to turn, angled out in straight and finished off one-paced.
Fairly away, positioned a length behind the leader on rail in 4th, easy run to turn, showed no extra gear in straight and weakened gradually over the concluding stages.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, similar position to turn, made no progress in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 5 lengths back at rear, 2 wide at turn, angled out after turning in, no clear running early in straight and checked near 200M, made no progress thereafter.
Bumped start, recovered to race 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths back, 4 wide without cover at turn, emptied in straight after hard run took effect.
Average to begin, difficult to settle early, sent forward to race prominently outside leader, got cover in 3rd at circle, emptied early in straight and dropped out.

Slow out as usual, settled one from last on rails, commenced move entering straight angling off the fence to challenge, ran on well to just get up on line.

Moderate start, just worse than midfield early stages, made swift headway passing 900 metres to reach one-out-one-back position at Rock, hit the front inside 200 metres only to be caught nearing finish.
Jumped fairly, prominent early settling in midfield on rails, similar turning in, ran on steadily without threatening.
Jumped moderately, soon driven to a prominent spot settling just off the pace on rails, similar turning in, fought on steadily without quickening.

Jumped well, travelled wide just better than midfield, made swift progress passing 800 metres to join the leader up the Rock, still sharing pace into straight but gradually faded under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Travelled in better than midfield within 3L of pace, similar turning in, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Raced wide without cover in rear of midfield, commenced move around the bend to reach 2L 5th entering straight, kept on same pace without threatening.
Led or disputed lead to straight, swamped under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, remained well behind, gained closer on rails turning in, no further impression under pressure.
Niggled along in rear of midfield, raced keenly down far side, towards the rear when hampered and lost position 500 metres out, made no impression in straight.
Sluggish at start, behind midfield when badly hampered over 900 metres out, in similar position and wide around home bend, found nothing in straight.
Jumped well, with leaders early, gradually shuffled back to midfield down far side, cropped a bad check 500 metres out, made no impression thereafter.
Settled 5th, 1 off with cover. Accelerated well early in the straight, swept to the front near the 200m, and the race in its keeping a long way from home.
Travelled midfield the fence, had cover. Finished off gamely.
Parked midfield, 2 wide with cover. Made good steady progress down the running.
Crowded at the start, settling worse than midfield, the fence. Was disappointed for running at the furlong, finished off soundly to make the frame.
Box seated. Looked a place hope at the furlong but was swamped late.
Eventually raced 1 out 1 back. Had every hope, but was one paced in the run to the line.
Camped worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Came widest in the straight but only plugged away.
Vied for leading duties, 2 deep, no cover. Was a beaten horse at the furlong.
Went back from the outside gate and settled last 1 off with cover. Made no real impression in the home stretch.
Held the fence whilst sharing leading duties. Was gassed at the furlong.
Travelled second last on the paint with cover. Was yielding ground before the home turn and finished well back.
Ridden forward to lead on the fence at fast sectionals, kept on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, despite harmed by the strong pace, ran on nicely to 2nd.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, dashed well for 3rd.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the strong pace, hung on nicely.
Taken back from a wide gate, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast pace, showed some dash in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, benefited by the strong tempo, ran on fairly.
Midfield, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, despite benefited by the fast sectionals, ran on only fairly.
Sent forward to park outside the leader at strong tempo, emptied 150M.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the fast tempo, flattened badly over the last furlong.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the strong pace, well beaten soon after straightening.

Began OK, ridden along at steady pace to sit 3L from leader going into first turn. Remained switch off in one-off position back stretch, taken 3-wide 500m to begin run, collared leader 100m out and pulled clear.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead into first turn, cutting to fence 1200m. Slowed tempo back stretch, kicked ahead on straightening, caught 100m, kept on.
Missed the start, taken to fence and ridden to make up ground, settling in midfield. Switched out 350m and ran home strongly.
Began well, ridden along to maintain forward position, settling one-back, one-off at first turn. Got some cover from 700m, put under pressure 500m, boxed on gamely.
Jumped OK, ridden along to hold rail, settling 2-back from leader. Saved ground final turn, shaken up from 400m, kept on steadily without threatening.
Began fairly, taken to rail 1200m, switched off back stretch, took closer order home turn, ran on nicely in straight while laying out. Lame right front.

Pressed forward to race inside early leader to first turn before settling in box seat. Came off fence 900m to sit outside leader. Put under pressure turning for home, kept on steadily till running on empty from 100m.
Began fairly, taken across behind runners before settling in a one-off position towards rear. Switch out 500m to make run but didn't respond. One-paced straight.
Jumped outwards start, taken across behind horses from wide draw settling in last pair along fence. Taken very wide turning for home but failed to respond to hard riding.
Ridden along early in a one-off position but not much speed, settling midfield. Dropped back slight back stretch, one-paced in straight.
Taken across behind horses from wide draw to sit with last pair in a one-off position. Stayed at rear mostly and never competitive.
Ridden along early, bumped and shifted in 1200m, then held wide without cover back stretch. Hard ridden entering turn but soon beaten, giving ground from 400m. Tailed off.
Began fairly, mustered to sit behind leader but shuffled back to 5th passing 1000m. Ridden quietly back stretch, came off fence 400m but switched back to rail and ran on strongly to win on the line.
Began well, ridden along early before allowing outside runners to cross 1000m, dropping to 3rd. Switched out turning for home, picked up momentum 300m, looked winner 100m, caught on line.
Began awkwardly and bumped, cut quickly to rail, settling 3-back from leader. Switched out 300m for clear run and finished off strongly to just miss.

Bumped and unbalanced start, ridden along behind midfield in a one-off position before cutting to rail back stretch. Stayed on rail turning for home, forced to switch out 200m when run closed, finished strongly.
Began only fairly, mustered out wide to take lead 1000m before cutting in to rail. Kicked clear top of straight, kept on strongly till swamped final 50m.
Jumped with field, riding along inside early leader before settling one-off, one-back passing 800m. Chased leader to straight turning one-paced from 200m.
Began fairly, caught wide without cover and drifted back gradually till clear last passing 800m. Stayed on rail around turn, ran on fairly in straight to be closest at finish.
A little slow into stride, cut to rail and remained at rear till entering straight. Ran on fairly under hard riding.
Jumped OK, caught wide and ridden along early before finding cover four-back, one-off. Taken very wide entering straight but only one-paced. Bled from both nostrils.
Jumped OK, restrained and taken across behind horses from wide draw to sit at rear in one-off position. Taken out at turn, widest in straight, one paced.
Ridden along early to hold forward position, settling 3-back, one-off. Found little when put under pressure turning for home and gave ground gradually.
Began well, pressed forward but over raced when crossed 1000m, settling one-back, one-off. Found little when put under pressure 300m and faded gradually.
Eased to rear, 5.5Ls off the leader 2-4 wide, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 300M, dashed strongly when clear for 2nd.
At back, 4Ls off the leader on the fence, dashed strongly 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Box seat, enjoyed the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on until 150M flattened.
Eased at start, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, checked 300M, held up until 150M, little dash when clear.
Midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground.
Eased to rear, trapped 3 wide throughout, made early move 800M to gain advantages from the slow pace, flattened 200M.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no dash, bumped 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, trapped 3 wide, moved forward steadily from 1000M to take advantages from the slow tempo, out of fuel 250M.
Eased to sit 1.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, lack room 300M, flattened in straight.
Bumped start, 3Ls off the leader 2-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, checked badly 200M, emptied.
Began well, raced alongside leading pack to first turn then eased back to 5th, 3L from leader. Began forward move 500m, took lead 350m and kept on strongly to the line.
Bumped and unbalanced shortly after start, taken to rail behind midfield and switched off. Came off fence turning for home, found inside run and ran on strongly to just miss.
Ridden along early to hold rail but not pressed, settling initially in box seat and then 2-back along back stretch. Switched out 300m for run and kept on steadily.
Began well, ridden along early but caught 3-wide first turn and eased. Got shuffled back along back stretch, began forward move 500m out, turned wide and ran on steadily down centre of the track.
Began best, led to first turn before easing up to settle in box seat from 1000m. Taken off fence turning for home, looked chance when threw out challenge 350m, but one-paced from 200m.
Began OK, ridden along behind pacemakers in a one-off position and steadied 1300m.Took closer order but wide around home turn, kept on steadily to 200m before one-paced.

Bumped and unbalanced start and then bumped again shortly after. Recovered, pressed forward to sit one-off, one-back back stretch, Pressed forward 400m out, took lead entering straight, boxed on until running on empty from 200m.
Crowded out start, dropped to clear last before first turn. Caught up with field around final turn, taken out entering straight, ran past beaten horses.
Jumped OK, snagged back and taken across behind horses to sit at rear in a one-off position. Switched out turning for home but found little in straight under hard riding.
Crowded out start, dropping to rear along fence. Shaken up around final turn but no response.
Began OK, pressed forward from wide draw and swooped around field first turn to lead from 1000m. Caught just before entering straight and gave ground abruptly.
Settled in mid-division, remained in range 3-4Ls off the pace, responded well to urge inside 300M, led inside 200M, continued willingly to the line.
Switched off to last, over 10Ls off the pace early stages, took closer order passing 800M, bid wide home turn, ran on well but couldn't match finishing pace of winner.
Settled towards the rear, waited with on the fence, had to shift across the track for clear run, closed strongly over final 150M.
In touch behind leaders, had a ground saving trip on the fence, ran on well initially entering straight, run peaked 100M, lost 2 placing late stages.
Held up behind midfield along the 2-path, shifted out to challenge past 400M, stayed on mildly.
Tracked leaders 2-wide just off a contested pace, behind heels of leaders and unwilling to shift out inside 300M, ran on fairly when clear.
Held up near the rear, shuffled back to last home turn, made some progress when switched back to inside passing 250M but never troubled leaders.
Restrained in midfield along the inside, waited with until 400M, lost all chance when badly held up 200M, failed to recover and eased towards finish.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled near the rear 8-9Ls off the pace middle stages, taken to 3-wide 700M and crept closer home turn, not quickened when urged inside 300M however.
Sent forward, pressed by a rival and set good pace middle stages, had little left turning in, weakened towards finish.
Attended the pace along the 2-path, briefly led when driven out inside 350M, weakened rapidly over final 200M.
Unable to slot in from 12, caught 3-wide no cover throughout the race, gave ground nearing 400M, weakened to last.
