Jumped fairly from the one draw, never far off, soon came to challenge upon straightening hitting the front over 200 metres out, just held on to finish.
Raced in rear of midfield of bunched field, took closer order rounding home bend gaining 2.75L 3rd into straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately, ridden to take up running after first 200 metres, held narrow advantage until headed over 200 metres out, ran home one-paced.
Slow out, well behind early, made swift headway approaching home bend, switched out when 5L back in 8th entering straight, sustained progress in the run home, nearest at finish.
Jumped well from a wide draw, travelled close up in 3rd out wide far side, similar rounding home bend and into straight, found no extra inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped back to last few, saved ground on rails turning in, ran home one-paced.
Close up early, gradually drifted back to worse than midfield, wide in rear entering straight, went past well-beaten runners closing stages.
Ridden along in prominent position early, not far off in 5th around home bend, found nothing under pressure in straight. (Blood in trachea)
Jumped fairly, soon dropped well behind, saved ground on rails turning in, no further impression.

Jumped well, amongst leaders early, gradually dropped back to 3L 6th coming out of back straight, lost further ground around home bend, no further impression. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Ridden early, with leaders to 500 metres, folded up quickly in straight.
Jumped fairly, travelled in better than midfield far side, virtually pulled up on home bend. (Bled)
Parked just behind midfield 3 deep with cover. Lengthened nicely and took control of the race 150m from the line.
Went forward and led on the paint. Kept grinding away in the run to the line.
Made its run from last position, 3 wide with cover. Made the home turn deep and finished off soundly to make the frame.
Went forward and raced in 2nd spot outside the leader. Was still there at the 100m, but commenced to give ground soon after.
Camped 5th, 2 deep with cover. Was one paced over the final 200m.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race, tracking the leader on the fence. Didn't respond to hard riding in the run home and was swamped over the final 100m.
Taken back from a wide gate, settling behind midfield, on the rails with cover. Weakened on its run 100m from home.
Crowded at the start travelling worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Failed to close off.
Began only fairly, racing midfield the fence had cover. Was gone at the furlong and weakened soon after.
Travelled with the backmakers, 1 off with cover. Failed to close off.
Did plenty of work to eventually cross and travel with the leaders on the circle 3 deep, no cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Camped behind the speed 3 wide, had cover. Was a beaten horse prior to the home turn and finished tailed out. To trial
Jumped well then drifted back to travel ahead of midfield but was 4 deep without cover on the circle. Never likely, finishing tailed out. To trial.

Placing: DISQ
Comment: Ridden patiently back in the field, 1 off the fence with cover. Ran on well.
Showed good early speed to take the lead, quickened up smartly and scored by a neck.
Prominent, 1L off the leader, ran on strongly to get 2nd.
Showed good early pace to take the lead, fought on gamely to get 3rd.
Rolled forward to share the lead, stayed on well until final 100M weakened.
Travelled 1L behind the leader along the fence, kept on steadily to the line.
Lacked early pace, 4Ls behind the leader, closed to the line well.
Prominent, 1L off the leader, kept on one pace until final 200M flattened.
Niggled along throughout, 4.5Ls off the leader, passed some tired runners.
At rear despite hard ridden along throughout, never looked competitive.
Pushed to settle in midfield, 3Ls behind the leader, found nothing when placed under pressure near the course proper.
Showed some early paced in the early stages, 3Ls off the leader, weakened 350M.
Never a factor.
Pushed along to settle in midfield, faded away near the course proper.
Never looked likely and finished tailed out.
Speed to dispute early lead, headed & raced rail 2nd, advanced to lead 650m, shaken up 400m, kicked clear for easy win.
Good break, led 1100m 1 off, headed 650m, ridden 450m, chased to wire but no inroads on winner.
Sluggish break, initially bustled at tail on inner, smooth progress & in contention turning in, 3rd & shifted out 200m, boxed on evenly to wire.
Broke OK, taken back to near rear 1 off with cover, driven 400m, plugged on to 4th 200m, kept on one pace.
Sharp start to dispute early lead, soon raced 1 back 1 off, to rail 1 back 700m, soon niggled, shifted out 400m, outpaced & tapered.
Snagged and taken behind to rail, rolled on to settle midfield, progress to 450m, switched out & driven into stretch, plugged on tepidly.
Broke well, soon bustled to race midfield 1 off with cover, shifted wider & ridden 600m, very wide into stretch & plodded on one pace.
Slow start, bustled in rear wide on track, to tail 800m, last pair & shifted very wide turning in, plodded on tamely.
Smart start, rousted to race handy 1 off with cover, under pressure when hard-ridden 600m, weakened right out in run.
Broke with others, rousted early, outpaced & drifted back to rear 500m, no extra & last turning in, eased & hacked home past fading horses.
Smart start, raced handy but very wide no cover, driven to dispute 3rd 600m, emptied turning in, faded rapidly & tailed off.
Fast start to sit prominently but trapped very wide no cover faded tamely from 600m & tailed off.
Sharp start & bustled wide to lead 1300m, crossed to rail 1050m, joined 820m, shaken up to edge ahead 400m, drew clear but hung across to outside rail.
Taken behind midfield from widest gate to 3 wide with cover, ridden turning in & closed off stands' side to snag 2nd at wire.
Good break, sat 1 off with cover midfield, overraced 950m & continued for some way, stayed on dourly to make frame.
Sluggish start, raced rail behind midfield, niggled 850m, hard-ridden 600m, stayed on dourly.
Broke well, raced rail midfield, shifted out & driven into stretch to 3rd, plugged on one pace & swamped late.
Slow start & raced 1 off with cover near tail, shifted towards stands' side in stretch, progress & switched inside 200m, for fair inroads.
Tardy break, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, off heels 900m & soon niggled, driven 450m, plugged on for minor inroads.
Speed to lead, soon headed & sat handy 3 wide no cover, shuffled back 800m, driven into stretch, stayed on moderately.
Smart break, raced handy 1 off no cover, niggled 350m, driven into stretch, plodded on one pace.
Dropped to race at tail, detached & rousted to close 900m, hard-ridden 800m & kept on moderately to wire.
Broke with others, sat 3 wide with cover midfield, drifted back on turn & ridden 500m, plugged on one pace.
Broke well & disputed lead 1350m, sat wide no cover handy until crossed to 1 off & vied for lead 820m, shaken up 430m, one-paced & tapered late.
Broke OK, raced very wide midfield, lost cover 950m, ridden forward on turn to race handier, flattened out into stretch & weakened.
Broke well but trapped wide, soon taken to 3 wide with cover near tail, very wide home turn & found nothing.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, dashed well 300M to score.
Slow away, hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot on the fence, 3Ls off the leader, dashed well 300M for 2nd despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward to sit just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, ran on well for 3rd.
At rear, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, saved good ground round the bends, little dash 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to take rail and led by 0.5L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon weakened 300M.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the slow pace 2-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, maneuvered along the stand side, however ran on only fairly.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash, checked 250M.
Hard ridden forward to sit just behind the leaders, suited by the slow tempo, however trapped 3 wide throughout, bumped and unbalanced 300M, out of fuel.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide, 2Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, reduced rapidly 500M.
Eased back, faded badly in straight.
Began well, niggled to stay behind pacemaker, sweated on a run from 400m before bursting through split 200m and pulling clear.
Broke well, held outer rail behind leader, forged ahead 400m, outsprinted by winner final 200m.
Began awkwardly and then steadied, settling worse than midfield. Improved steadily, close to heels 200m before getting split. Finished off nicely.
Began OK but outpaced, settling 6L from leader. Still well back entering course proper but picked up momentum from 150m to just miss a place.
Broke well and ridden along early to stay behind pacemakers. Under pressure from 500m but unable make ground and not ridden out last few strides.
Jumped with field, ridden positively to say inside leader, taking over from 500m. Caught 400m, kept on one-paced.
Allowed to roll forward at own pace down centre track, to share lead 500m out before giving ground gradually.
Bumped start, outpaced, settling at rear. Put under pressure from 500m, but hung out and proved difficult to settle. One-paced.
Bumped start, dropped to rear and over raced. Still well back entering course proper but made some late ground.
Jumped best, set good pace till joined up front 500m, kept on till 200m before giving ground.
Ridden positively from inside draw but unable cross to outer fence and held behind midfield. Found little when put under pressure from 400m.
Began fairly, outpaced and soon at rear. Taken to outside fence but never competitive.
Jumped OK but no early speed and soon in last pair. Clear last entering course proper and never competitive.
Broke well, ridden along to stay with pacemakers, sharing lead 500m before giving ground gradually.
Travelled well just off the pace, moved up to join leader 400M, pulled clear inside 200M, kept on strongly to score.
Never far off, driven 400M to challenge front pair, stayed on evenly on rain affected track, got up for 2nd near line but not making headway on the runaway winner.
Driven forward, led uncontested, joined by eventual winner at top of the straight, no match, faded towards line and lost 2nd close home.
Niggled along early stages to hold a midfield spot along the 2-path, kept on same pace final 400M for remote 4th.
Settled in midfield along the fence, not pace to challenge leaders inside 400M, flattened out in the drive home.
Taken back, not hurried and settled behind midfield 7Ls off the pace, driven along passing 400M, made limited progress.
Dropped back from wide barrier, 8-9Ls off the pace, waited with until 500M, ran past only beaten runners in straight, never a threat to leaders.
Slow to begin, settled near last 8Ls off the pace, not quickened entering straight, never factored.
Began only fairly, rushed forward to sit in 3rd 2Ls off leader, came under pressure 500M, found no extra and weakened towards finish.
Well back in last almost 10Ls behind the pace, plenty to do turning home, failed to make any progress.
Positively ridden early stages, tucked in to a 2-wide spot ahead of midfield, keen near 800M, asked along at top of the bend, had little left over final 300M.
Held up towards the rear, 9Ls off the pace middle stages, lost touch and dropped out rapidly 400M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Broke well, pressed forward to settle one-off, one-back. Waited till straight to throw out challenge, hit front 250m, won eased down.
A little tardy at start, then awkward on heels drifting back to rear. Switched wide entering straight, dashed strong down centre track while shifting in abruptly.
Began moderately, ridden to hold rail 4-back from leader. Tightened passing 1200, came off rail 500m, finished off nicely.
Pressed forward from good draw to lead on settling. Set steady tempo, kicked clear 400m, caught 250m but kept on gamely.
Ridden along from inside draw to hold box seat on settling. Saved ground turn, kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Used from wide draw to sit outside leader on passing 1000m. Revved up turning for home, drew alongside leader for a few strides, then one-paced.
Ridden along early but kept 3-wide mostly back stretch. Shaken up entering straight, taken to outside fence, ran on fairly.
Jumped OK but restrained, settling 3-back along fence. Hampered and lost ground when crowded 1200m. Stayed on rail in straight and kept on fairly to line.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear away from fence. Remained at rear mostly, running past beaten horses in straight.
Snagged back from widest draw and last on settling. Last into straight, making some late ground.
Broke well, held forward position but over-raced. Turned wide, had clear run from 300m but only one-paced.
Ridden along early in a one-off position to sit in midfield Lost some ground turning for home and one-paced in straight.
Fractious in box and slow into stride, racing at rear mostly in one-off position. Never competitive.
Ridden forward to sit 3-wide and raced mostly without cover. Gave ground soon after entering straight.
Average to begin, positioned 1-2 lengths back on rail behind leader, easy run to turn, no clear running until passing 300M, closed off well thereafter to score narrowly.
Crowded out start, raced 6 lengths back on rails at rear, similar position to turn, kept to inside after straightening, into clear final 200M and finished off strongly to finish 2nd, just missed.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead and set a moderate tempo, easy lead to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the challengers final 100M.
Fairly away, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd outside leader, similar margin away to turn, unbalanced near 350M, finished off steadily thereafter to make frame.
Jumped with them, positioned 2-3 lengths back on rail, saved ground to turn, kept on evenly in straight without threatening the first few.
Average to begin, positioned in midfield on rail, 4-5 lengths back, similar margin away to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5-6 lengths back, switched out and under pressure turning, finished off only fairly in straight.
Began evenly from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back, similar position to turn, ran home one-paced.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, 4 lengths back, no cover throughout, emptied in straight after hard run took toll.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, similar position to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 7 lengths back at rear, under pressure turning, made no progress in straight. (See racing incidents.)
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 7-8 lengths back at tail, still well back turning, made no headway in straight, kept on one-paced. (See racing incidents.)
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back, improved 4 wide with no cover at turn, made no progress final 300M when hard run took effect.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in 4th, 2-3 lengths back, weakened gradually from turn and finished tailed off.

Ridden along to contest lead settling outside the leader, quickened to hit the front entering straight and soon drew clear.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield, came closer turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Began moderately, soon picked up along rails to settle just off the pace, kept on steadily under pressure without threatening.
Jumped fairly, settled in forward of midfield in 6th on rails, saved ground turning in, baulked for a run inside 200 metres, finished off race well late.
Soon taken behind midfield from a wide draw, switched out for a run turning for home, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Always thereabouts, kept on before finding no extra closing stages.
Jumped well, with leaders 3-wide without cover, lost a stride and dropped to 2L back 500 metres out, ran home one-paced.
Soon taken back from a wide draw, remained well behind to straight, switched out for a run turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Settled towards the rear on rails, fought on well, nearest at finish.
Jumped well, niggled along and with leaders early, led on rails going up the Rock, narrowly headed on straightening, soon faded.
Ridden along wide in midfield, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.
Never on terms.
Assumed the lead near the 1000m, on the rails. Made every post a winner and maintained a strong gallop to the wire.
Settled 4th, 1 off with cover. Ran home soundly.
Stalked the leader on the fence. kept grinding away in the run to the line.
Settled 3rd last 1 off with cover. Swung wide on the home turn, finished off soundly.
Parked behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Finished off steadily.
Did plenty of work to cross and race on the speed, 2 deep no cover. Started to give ground over the final 150m.
Camped midfield, 3 deep with cover. Failed to quicken in the home stretch.
Travelled with the backmakers, 2 deep with cover. Came widest in the straight, plugged away to the line.
Jumped well but after looking to settle behind runners in the early stages was posted 3 deep without cover, ahead of midfield. Was a spent force at the furlong. (see incident report)
Rated 3 back the fence, had cover. Commenced to tire after the 200m.
Settled back in the field, on the paint with cover. Failed to close off.
Began only fairly, settling at the rear along the fence with cover. Never ran on.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 3/4L at slow sectionals, kept on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Sent forward to park outside the leader, benefited by the slow tempo, fought on well for 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, ran on well to get 3rd.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, despite suited by the slow sectionals, one paced home.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Camped handy, however trapped 3 wide without cover, weakened soon after straightening.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never a threat.
At rear, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow sectionals, no dash.
Taken back, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow tempo, unable to run on.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, then settled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never ran on.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Midfield, trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, never looked likely.
Broke well, settled midfield 1 off with cover, shaken up home turn & shifted wide, led 190m, quickened clear.
Prominent early, slotted rail fore of midfield, shuffled back a touch 800m, ridden 300m, boxed on to nick 2nd.
Tardy start, raced behind midfield on fence, shifted 1 off & to tail 840m, good progress on turn, ran on soundly under stretch drive to make frame.
Early speed, settled fore of midfield 1 off with cover, 3rd & driven 450m, challenged lead 250m, no extra 200m, one-paced thereafter.
Tardy start, soon at tail, niggled & advanced 1000m to sit handy 3 wide no cover 700m, driven turning in, stayed on evenly centre track.
Broke OK, settled 1 off no cover 2nd, pressed lead 600m, ridden to lead turning in, all out & headed 190m, tapered to wire.
Fair break, dropped in near rear 1 off, overraced 1000m & shifted 3 wide with cover, rear & driven widest home turn, plugged on for modest inroads.
Broke OK, bustled early to race midfield on rail, shuffled to rear backstretch, ridden & outpaced 460m, plugged on one pace.
Slow break & bustled, initially at rear on rail, advanced 3 wide with cover backstretch to sit midfield, ridden 450m, found little in tepid stretch run.
Speed to lead to 1500m, slotted 1 back on rail, shifted out & driven 300m, soon emptied & weakened out.
Broke well, ridden wide to lead 1st turn, joined for lead 600m, ridden under pressure 400m, faded tamely in stretch.
Taken to tail, 2L detached & ridden 600m, switched widest for progress & driven home turn, rattling run centre track to lead at wire.
Smart break, raced rail fore of midfield, ridden & shifted out turning in, grinding progress to nick 2nd at wire.
Sharp start & led, to rail 1200m, pressed 800m but extended a touch, kicked clear into stretch, tapered final 100m & headed close home.
Snagged to rail 2nd last, shifted 1 off & advanced a touch 1000m, switched wide & driven home turn, closed off soundly for minor gains.
Broke OK, cover 1 off behind midfield, niggled & 3 wide 850m, off heels 750m, driven for progress on turn, stayed on without threatening.
Speedy break, settled 1 back on rail, driven turning in, every chance but outpaced in tepid run home.
Broke OK, sat rail midfield, switched 1 off 850m, niggled 650m & shuffled back, hard-ridden rear rank 300m, stayed on moderately.
Speedy break, raced fore of midfield 1 off with cover, switched 3 wide no cover750m, driven turning in, flattered briefly but plodded on one pace.
Broke well, wide early & soon rolled to 2nd 1 off, shuffled back 800m, off heels 600m & under pump midfield, plugged on same speed.
Crowded start, settled 3 wide with cover midfield, ridden 550m, hard-driven into stretch, found nothing & weakened.
Tardy start & bumped, raced rail near rear, off heels then niggled & bumped fence 500m, in rear turning in, plugged home one pace.
Broke OK, midfield 3 wide until rolled to 2nd 1 off & pressed lead 800m, driven 400m but outpaced, emptied 250m & faded right out.
Settled in prominent spot, 2Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to win.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 100M overhauled.
Settled in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, made steady ground 200M for 3rd.
Eased at start and took cover at rear, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, progressed steadily 250M.
Eased for box seat, just off the fast pace, ran on only fairly in straight.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Eased at start, took rail, 6.5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast tempo, made some ground 200M.
Pressed forward, trapped 3-4 wide no cover throughout, harmed by the fast pace, weakened 200M.
Pushed early, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, no turn of foot.
Midfield, 3Ls off the fast tempo, trapped 3 wide throughout, flattened 200M.
Prominent on the fence early, shuffled back 1200M, 4Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, however no progress.
Pushed forward to share lead 2 wide at fast sectionals, soon out of fuel 300M.
Began fairly, mustered, cut to rail to grab box seat. Stayed on rail turning for home, shot through to hit front 300m, cleared away to effortless win.
Bumped start, no early pace, dropping to rear but away from fence. Taken widest entering straight and finished off nicely.
Began OK, ridden along to hold rail, settling 2-back along back stretch. Stayed on rail turning for home and kept on steadily in straight.
Jumped with field, ridden along but bumped and unbalanced 600m. Taken wide entering straight, ran on steadily.
Began only fairly, taken back from wide draw and cut to fence back stretch. Stayed on rail around turn and boxed on fairly in straight.
Bumped start, recovered and ridden along, settling 3-back one-off back stretch. Switched wide entering straight, loomed as chance 200m, then one-paced.
Began fairly, shifted in behind horses from wide draw and last on settling. Became further detached home turn, still last 200m, ran past beaten horses final stages.
Reared when gates opened and slow into stride. Bumped, unbalanced 600m then checked 400m when denied run. Kept on one-paced.
Pressed forward to take clear lead passing 1000m, set good pace till collared 300m, battled on till 200m before giving ground gradually.
Began well, ridden to maintain forward position behind leader. Rolled forward turning for home, looked chance 300m, flattened. (Distressed with irregular heart rhythm).
Broke well, ridden alongside leaders but unable cut in and held three wide. Came off bridal 700m, shortened stride 600m, eased final 300m. (Substantial blood in trachea. Unacceptable performance).

Placing: PU
Comment: Began well, pressed forward 3-wide into back stretch before breaking down 800m and pulled up.
Broke alertly, restrained to sit just off the pace, strongly pressed leader inside 200M, surged to lead 50M out for back to back win.
Guided to a 2-wide position from widest draw, never far off from leaders, stayed on well under pressure from 350M, got up for 2nd just before line.
Began only fairly, urged to take the lead, set steady pace up front, kept on well to finish, headed by winner near 50M, beaten to 3rd just before line.
Tracked leader along the fence, kept on steadily turning home and pressed leaders all the way to the line.
Eased back to sit behind midfield, travelled well, switched out to challenge 400M, stayed on well but always held by leaders.
Began well, restrained to race in midfield but never lost touch with leaders, kept on same pace final 300M, unable to get closer to main rivals.
Settled just off the pace but caught 3-wide without cover, outpaced turning home, plugged on.
Held up near the rear, 6Ls behind leader passing 400M, never going the pace to challenge.
Began awkwardly, slow to muster in early stages, settled in midfield eventually, struggle to keep up 500M, soon beaten.
Began awkwardly and lost ground, settled last 7-8Ls off the pace, made no progress over final 300M.
Eased back, held up near last, again found nothing when asked, never involved.

Jumped awkwardly losing ground, quickly recovered to take up running passing 1000 metres, briefly headed around the bend, resumed lead early in straight and soon drew clear.
Jumped moderately, gradually recovered to forward of midfield on rails, shifted out for a run entering straight, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Close up early, restrained for cover behind leaders on rails, still raced keenly upon straightening, baulked and switched out for a run over 300 metres out, ran on without threatening.
Soon taken back from the widest draw, saved ground on rails turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly, settled mainly in rear of midfield on rails, fought on steadily.
Settled well behind, made up a lot of ground down the centre of the straight. (Jockey warned.)
Jumped awkwardly, soon joined leaders racing on rails, gained narrow lead around home bend, headed just inside 300 metres, weakened.
Soon taken back from a poor draw, remained towards the rear to straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Ridden to forward position from a poor draw, remained wide without cover throughout, faded under pressure inside final 300 metres. (Tactic questioned)

Close up early, hampered by eventual winner and lost a few lengths over 1000 metres out, recovered swiftly to just behind leaders around the bend, soon faded in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Mainly in midfield to halfway, faded gradually.
Jumped well, then was allowed to drift back to race midfield, 3 wide with cover. Ran on well.
Went forward and led at an even tempo. Strolled along in front on the rails, fought on gamely to the wire.
Ridden patiently from the outside alley, settling 2nd last, on the paint with cover. Closed off with plenty of purpose.
Enjoyed the box seat. Kept to the rails in the stretch and finished off evenly.
Raced behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Briefly held up early in the straight, finished off gamely.
Began awkwardly then was slow to muster, settling just off the speed. Was left 3 wide without cover after the 1200m and was never likely from that point. Overhauled late.
Settled 3rd last, 3 deep with cover. Swung wide on the home turn and finished off fairly.
Travelled midfield, 2 deep with cover. Kept on at the same speed down the running.
Settled 3 back the fence with cover. Stayed towards the inside in the home stretch, whacked away at the same speed.
Settled in 5th position, 2 deep with cover. Stayed on only one paced.
Raced in last position, 2 off the fence with cover. Came wide in the straight and battled away to the line.
Camped worse than midfield the fence, had cover. Failed to close off.
Showed speed, settling 2nd outside the leader. Capitulated 150m from the post.
Parked midfield, 3 deep with cover. Was paddling 200m from home.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead 2 wide without cover, despite harmed by the quick sectionals, ran on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1.5Ls at fast pace, kept on well for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the strong tempo, dashed well to get 3rd.
Prominent, settled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite hampered by the fast pace, kept on steadily.
Pushed to settle midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, benefited by the strong sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Taken back, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, suited by the quick tempo, ran on only fairly.
Failed to muster, settled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Sent forward, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened over the last furlong.
Always at rear, travelled 9Ls behind the leader 3-4 wide with cover, despite benefited by the fast tempo, never ran on.
Raced midfield, settled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast sectionals, never looked likely.
Never a factor, finished tailed out.
Hard ridden forward to occupy the box seat, flattened badly soon after straightening, tailed out.
Fast break, settled 1 back 1 off, shifted 4 deep on turn, driven to join leader 130m, bumped 120m, battled to lead at wire.
Led on rail, headed 1200m & niggled 1100m, soon 3rd 1 back, driven to 2nd & switched out 550m, led 330m, hung & bumped rival 120m, mugged at wire.
Broke well but outpaced & rousted, soon rail behind midfield, shifted 1 off & driven for progress 500m, switched wider 250m, soon 3rd, held in run.
Smart start, settled rail midfield, progress on turn, shifted out 450m & driven into stretch, bumped rival 250m, boxed on evenly.
Tardy start & soon rail at tail, minor advance backstretch, driven very wide for progress home turn, stayed on for minor inroads.
Broke well, rolled to close 2nd 1 off, led 1200m, clear & to rail 1000m, shaken up turning in, headed 300m, beaten when bumped & unbalanced 250m.
Sharp start, caught 3 wide no cover handy, rolled 2nd 1 off 850m, pushed wider under pressure 550m, weakened tamely in stretch.
Sharp start, prominent & wide 1st turn, slotted 1 off with cover midfield, shifted 3 wide & driven home turn, found little & weakened out.
Outpaced & rousted early, bustled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven 600m, soon beaten & plodded home tamely.
Snagged back to race 1 off with cover near tail, shifted wider on turn & driven, struggled in run home.
Broke OK, outpaced & soon in rear, to tail 1000m, niggled along, driven on turn, no response, never a factor.
Broke OK, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, ridden 700m, crowded & bumped 500m, found nothing in run home & faded.
Sharp start, hung left & very wide 1st turn, taken back to 3 wide with cover in rear, niggled under pressure 500m, soon at tail & no extra.
Rousted from wide to race front rank 1st turn, taken back to 3 wide with cover midfield, lost cover 850m, driven & outpaced 600m, faded tamely.
Tardy break, camped last pair 1off, 6L back & driven 400m, shifted centre track, grinding run to lead close home.
Fast start, settled rail fore of midfield, shifted out 600m, driven turning in & battled to narrow lead 80m, all out & headed final strides.
Tardy break, sat rail midfield, shuffled to near tail 850m, driven on fence 400m, closed off to close 3rd at wire.
Steady start, rolled to sit midfield 1 off with cover, forced 3 wide 600m, wider & driven 400m, edged to lead 150m, headed 80m, no extra.
Decent start, raced fore of midfield 1 off with cover, progress 3 wide to lead 400m, all out & headed 150m, tapered to wire.
Speedy break but caught wide no cover front rank, settled 3rd until niggled to share lead home turn, driven & headed 400m, boxed on moderately.
Outpaced & bustled early, soon to rail & raced rear rank, driven into stretch, stayed on for moderate late headway.
Broke OK, raced 1 off near rear, shifted 3 deep 850m, driven into stretch, plugged on dourly centre track.
Smart start, slotted 1 back on rail, shuffled to 4th 480m & shifted out, every chance turning in, boxed on until emptied 150m & faded.
Good break & bustled early, worked to lead outright, joined final turn & headed under pressure 400m, faded quickly.
Broke OK, raced mid rank & forced to sit 3 wide no cover, 4 wide & driven on turn, found nothing & faded.
Snagged start & in rear initially, 4-wide progress backstretch to midfield no cover, 5 wide & shuffled back 500m, beaten turning in.
Eased at start, took rail at back, 6Ls off the leader on the rails, benefited by the fast temp, blocked 400M, progressed steadily when clear and scored.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1.5Ls, clocked fast sectionals, drifted away 400M, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 3rd.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, just held ground when clear.
Struggled to keep up at rear, 8Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Eased to rear for cover, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, made some ground 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward, harmed by the fast tempo, out of fuel 250M.
Pressed forward, 2.5Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3 wide, flattened 200M.
Midfield, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, suited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, ran on only fairly when clear.
At back, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader, trapped 2-4 wide, favoured by the fast pace, no progress.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 300M.
Hard ridden to obtain box seat, not suited by the fast pace, soon reduced 300M.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling, slowed pace back stretch, outsprinted from 300m but stuck on gamely.
Began fairly, picked up along rail to grab box seat. Pocketed top of straight, lost momentum for a few strides before picking up again from 100m.
Broke well, ridden along to hold forward position but wide. Poked up between horses to look a chance turning into straight, one-paced final 200m.
Slow, failed to muster despite vigorous riding, becoming detached from field. Last into straight, switched out 300m and finished off nicely.
Began fairly, ridden to hold fence 3-back from leader. Switched out 500m to make run but only one-paced under hard riding.
Began well, steadied, settling one-back, one-off. Over-raced when pace slowed, rolled forward without cover to look a chance 400m, one-paced final 200m.
Began OK, outpaced, dropping to rear in one-off position. Made forward move approaching 500m but found little under hard riding.
Began fairly, no pace, dropping to rear but kept away from fence. Taken widest entering straight but little response.

Placing: DISQ
Comment: Jumped best, eased, settling outside leader. Travelled strongly to turn, edged head passing 300m, pulled away for smart win.
Taken back from widest gate, settled in the rear 8Ls off the pace, brought wide 450M, ran on strongly final 300M, got up near 50M for 5th victory of the season.

Slotted into a 2-wide spot, never far off 3Ls off the pace, moved to a striking position 450M, quickened to lead inside 300M, kept on well to line but unable to hold off fast finishing winner final stages.
Switched off to the rear, 8Ls behind leaders middle stages, kept to the fence throughout, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Had uncontested lead through slow fractions, headed inside 300M, stayed on same pace final 200M to hold 4th.
Gained a forward position, crossed to the rail 1100M tracking leader, driven 350M but not quickened as well as his main rivals, raced in restricted room final 100M.
Began only fairly, restrained in a position near the rear, stayed on under hands and heels riding final 300M but never going the pace to challenge. (Tactics questioned.)
Held up in mid-division 3-4Ls behind leader, ran on one paced entering straight never a serious threat.
Lost ground when reared in the air at the start, settled towards the rear along the rail, had to be taken wide for a clear run in straight but failed to trouble leaders.
Close up early stages, travelled keenly 1100M, eased back to a position ahead of midfield, failed to go on when placed under pressure in straight, weakened 200M.
Reserved in midfield along the 2-path, gave brief response early straight, weakened badly final 200M. (Bled 2nd time.)
Caught wide early stages, advanced to a 2-wide spot behind leader just before the turn, found disappointing little turning home, gave way passing 300M.
Began well, joined leader 800m, raced keenly but under tight hold, shaken up 300m and pulled clear under hands and heels riding.
Broke well, ridden along to maintain forward position but well away from outer fence. Outsprinted from 300m but battled on under vigorous riding.
Jumped with field, pressed forward between horses while trying to lay in. Vigorously ridden from 250m and kept on steadily.
Broke nicely, taken closer to outer rail, settling 2L from leader. Given reminder 300m, kept on steadily under hard riding.
Jumped OK, ridden along down centre of track to keep tabs on leaders. Put under pressure 300m out and kept on fairly.
First out and led for a few strides until joined 800m. Put under pressure 500m out, kept on fairly before bumped 150m and fading gradually.
Began fairly, quickly taken to outer fence settling 3-back from leader. Battled on fairly final 400m without making ground.
Began OK, failed to settle and drifted towards rear. Limited response when put under pressure 300m. (Bled from both nostrils).
Broke well, taken closer to outer rail, settling at rear. Found nothing when asked 400m out. One-paced.
Slow into stride, switched out and made ground between horses to sit in midfield 3.5L from leader. Under whip 200m out and faded steadily.
Slow into stride and struggled to keep up with field thereafter. Never competitive.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead and travelled comfortably throughout, shared lead turning, kicked clear after straightening, won easily.
Slowly away, raced 3-4 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off well to get 2nd, never a threat to the winner.
Average to begin, unable to slot in, positioned 3 wide without cover in midfield, 3 lengths back, crept closer in 3rd at turn, kept on evenly in straight to get a place.
Jumped with them, taken back to race at rear, 5-6 lengths back, saved ground to turn, made decent progress in straight to make frame.
Fairly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 4 lengths back, angled wider on turn, made reasonable progress after straightening, never a threat to the first few.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race outside leader, same position to turn, lacked an extra gear in straight, stayed on at same pace.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back, hampered near 900M, 4 wide with cover turning, closed off fairly in straight.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, saved ground turning, showed no response in straight and weakened gradually.
Slow to begin, raced at tail throughout, 7-8 lengths back, still last turning, made minor headway in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths back, hampered near 900M, 3 wide no cover turning, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail in midfield, checked near 900M, 2 wide at turn, showed no response in straight and eased final 150M.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide, 2-3 lengths back, hampered near 900M, carried to 4 wide without cover at turn, emptied early in straight after hard run took effect, beaten a long way.

Jumped fairly from the one draw, settled just better than midfield in 5th on rails mainly within 4L of pace, switched off rails for a clear run 200 metres out, made modest headway closing stages.
Jumped well niggling along early, settled one back in 3rd on rails, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly from a wide-ish gate, improved steadily to race 2-wide just off the pace, came under pressure around the bend, one-paced under pressure.
Jumped fairly, gradually settled in rear of midfield on rails, similar turning for home, made steady progress without threatening.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, took closer order to be just worse than midfield in 8th entering far side, fought on under pressure.
Jumped fairly, settled 2-wide in 4th within 3L of pace, faded gradually under pressure in the run home.
Held up in midfield in 6th, found nothing in the run home.
Jumped fairly, settled towards the rear, ran home steadily from 9th into straight.
Began from a poor gate, soon taken back in last few, made no impression.
Soon taken back from a poor gate, remained well behind throughout.
Settled in 4th position, close to the rail with cover. Peeled out rounding the home turn and finished off full of running under hands and heels riding.
Showed plenty of early speed to eventually settle behind the leader on the paint with cover. Was in front at the furlong, kept on gamely.
Raced prominently, 1 off without cover. Maintained a sound gallop down the running.
Landed midfield, 1 off with cover. Was shifted deep on straightening, kept grinding away to the line.
Didn't show a great deal of gate speed and settled 3rd last, 1 off the rails with cover kept on evenly down the running.
Parked 2-3 off the fence with cover. Shifted widest in the straight and worked home steadily.
Couldn't go the early speed of the race and settled worse than midfield, on the rails with cover. Battled away in the home stretch.
Camped midfield the fence had cover. Never quickened in the straight and was yielding ground 150 from home.
Led on the fence. Was under pressure early in the straight, gave ground quickly near the 100m.
Settled last, close to the rail with cover. Failed to close off.
Travelled with the backmakers, on the paint with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, despite harmed by the quick tempo, ran on strongly to score comfortably.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at fast sectionals, kept on strongly to get 2nd.
Taken back, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast pace, dashed well for 3rd.
Sent forward to park outside the leader at strong tempo, kept on one steadily to the line.
Lacked early pace despite ridden along, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite benefited by the fast run, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the strong tempo, unable to show any dash in straight.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the fast sectionals, one paced until 150M weakened.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Pushed to settle midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, made an early move 700M however flattened badly rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Sharp start & disputed lead, soon settled 1 back on rail, shifted out & shaken up 300m, swept to lead 150m, drew clear.
Quick break, bustled to lead 1120m, to rail 900m, 1L clear & driven 300m, all out when headed 150m, no extra.
Broke well out wide, shuffled to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, widest turning in, closed off well to claim 3rd without threatening.
Moderate start, raced rail midfield, nudged along on turn, shifted off fence & driven 300m, kept on one pace.
Quick to stride wide, driven on outer to slot 1 off no cover 850m & niggled along, shifted out turning in & hard-ridden 3rd, tapering when hung in 150m.
Fast break, settled 4th 1 off with cover, ridden along 480m, fanned wide into stretch, driven out & stayed on evenly.
Moderate break, raced rail behind midfield, driven into stretch, stayed on moderately.
Fastest to stride, soon headed & settled midfield, caught 3 wide no cover, under pump 400m, impeded 300m, plodded home tamely.
Tardy start, sat 1 off with cover last pair, minor progress on turn, driven 300m but badly impeded by faller 290m, no extra.
Sluggish break, raced rail last pair, to tail 600m, detached when badly hampered by faller 290m, eased thereafter.

Placing: FE
Comment: Bustled at break to race midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out home turn but not clear run, attempted to edge out 300m, clipped rival & fell.
Sharp start, bustled initially to sit 1 back on rail, shifted out & quickened between horses 250m to lead 150m, won readily.
Moderate break & niggled early to race rail behind midfield, rousted along 400m, shifted out & not clear run until 200m, quickened to take 2nd.
Awkward start, sat rail midfield, switched out 400m, driven wide into stretch, slight check 250m, stayed on to 3rd late.
Slow start, ridden at tail early, settled rail near rear, ridden 400m, hung out into stretch & shunted rival 275m, closed for minor inroads.
Slow break & bumped, bustled last pair, sat rail at tail, switched out & driven 450m, stayed on & switched to inner 150m, sound gains.
Fast break widest & driven to lead, crossed to rail 1st turn, narrow advantage under pressure turning in, battled but headed 150m, swamped late.
Shifted left at start, driven wide to slot 2nd 1 off no cover 1100m, pressed lead turning in, emptied 200m & faded.
Broke well, tracked handy 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide & driven into home turn to challenge, weakened under pressure.
Broke moderately, niggled along 1 off behind midfield, shifted wide & driven home turn, struggled in one-paced run home.
Broke well, niggled early to sit midfield 1 off with cover, driven under pressure 450m, wide into stretch, nudged wider 275m, outpaced, eased when beaten.
Slow start, sat 1 off with cover near rear, driven 600m & switched very wide on turn, found nothing.
Broke OK, bustled early, advanced on outer to sit 3wide no cover 3rd at 800m, faded from 500m, tame last turning in, eased & tailed off.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide, progressed steadily 250M to win just by a narrow margin.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at good pace, hung out round the home bend, ran on strongly until last few strides, just missed by a short head.
Eased to sit 2Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Prominent, 2Ls off the good pace 2 wide, bumped 300M, lack room 200M, ran on ok when clear.
Very slow away, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, lack turn of foot, just ran on ok.
Hard ridden to hold the rails in midfield, 3Ls off the good pace, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, pace good, ran on until 150M flattened, checked 50M.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead 2 wide at good pace, soon out of fuel 250M.
Pushed early but not mustering enough to cross in front, dropped back for cover rather than raced 4-5 wide, 4.5Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made some ground 200M.
At rear, 5.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made some ground 250M, lack room 100M.
Pushed early to keep up with the field, 5Ls off the good pace along the fence, blocked most straight, not fully tested.
Began OK, not pressured, settling midfield in one-off position. Shifted to 3-wide position 1000m without cover, taken wider in straight, finished off strongly to win close home.
Broke fairly, ridden along in midfield but left without cover near 1200m. Pressed forward to lead passing 1000m, outsprinted final 100m but kept on well.
Began best and led to 1200m before easing into box seat. Came off rail passing 500m, under whip from 300m, battled on gamely.
Jumped outwards, worked forward but wide to hold one-off, one-back position back stretch. Flat-footed top of straight before picking up speed to finish close.
Broke fairly, outpaced, settling at rear in one-off position. Over-raced passing 1000m when switched out, covered extra ground final turn, finished off nicely.
Got off with field, cutting quickly to rail 3-back from leader. Came off fence turning for home, under whip 300m out, kept on fairly.
Jumped fairly, taken in from outside position to sit towards rear in one-off position. Still well back entering straight, switched out and made late ground.
Broke OK, switched in towards rail passing 1500m, stayed on rail back stretch and turn, boxed on fairly in straight.
Began well, worked forward to sit behind leader, checked and lost ground 1200m. Under pressure final turn, giving ground in straight. Rider reported refused to stretch out.
Began fairly, worked forward to lead passing 1200m, crossed by another 1000m, dropping back to 3rd final turn. Found little in straight and faded.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to last. Crowded for room passing 1200m but never competitive.
Began OK, pushed forward between horses to sit behind pace first turn. Shuffled back to midfield back stretch, tired after turning for home.
Soon crossed to the lead under positive riding, allowed an uncontested lead, kept on well in straight under hands and heels riding and was never seriously challenged.
Tracked leader along the fence, rallied to strong handling entering straight but was well held by winner.
Held up in midfield along the inside, moved out to challenge 300M, ran on steadily to clinch 3rd but never looked like getting to the winner.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled behind midfield about 3Ls behind leader, swung wide 400M, closed off willingly for 4th.
Overcame a wide draw to race in a one out one back position, driven inside 300M but not making headway, faded passing 100M, checked late stages and not ridden out to finish.
Settled behind midfield 4-5Ls behind leader, found less than expected when asked, never going the pace to challenge.
Taken back to last, 8-9Ls off the pace and became detached making the home turn, made some late progress over final 200M. (Jockey questioned.)
Dropped back to a rearward position, roused along passing 500M but never going the pace to challenge.
Close up behind leaders in 4th, first to come under pressure, hard driven 400M but gave limited response, weakened towards finish.
Assumed a midfield position along the 2-path, waited with until 350M but had little to offer when asked, never reached contention.
Eased back, held up near last 7Ls off the pace, not quickened when asked entering straight, never involved.

Jumped moderately from a low draw, settled one back in 4th on rails, hit the front over 200 metres out, won comfortably.
Jumped fairly, settled in 5th within 3L of pace, slightly inconvenienced turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, remained well back on home bend, saved ground turning in, ran on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly attempting to make all, soon led far side but narrowly headed briefly around home bend, re-gained lead on straightening only to be headed over 250 metres out.
Jumped fairly from the middle draw, raced wide early and well there, hit the front momentarily over 200 metres out before tiring noticeably.
Travelled just worse than midfield, commenced move entering straight when slightly inconvenienced, kept on same pace without quickening.
Broke well from a poor draw but soon taken back to last few, remained on inside turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Slightly slow out, gradually recovered on rails to be reach forward of midfield on home bend, saved ground turning in, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Slightly slow out, soon recovered to midfield, remained similar or just worse but went wide into straight, kept on before fading closing stages. (Lame next day)
Jumped well, travelled wide without cover in prominent position far side, pulling when gained slender advantage 2-wide around home bend, folded up quickly inside final 300 metres.
Jumped moderately, soon dropped to last few.
Jumped fairly, settled wide in forward of midfield, carried wider entering straight, soon dropped out.
Parked 4th, 1 off the rails with cover. Peeled out deep turning for home a showed a good turn of foot to hit the lead at the furlong, cruised home for effortless win.
Settled midfield, coursing 3-4 wide had some cover on the circle. Finished off well despite the wide trip.
Did plenty of work to eventually cross and lead on the fence near the 800m. Turned for home with a 2length margin and maintained a sound effort to the post.
Raced ahead of midfield, 2-3 deep with cover. Battled away in the run home to stay in the frame.
Settled 5th on the fence with cover. Kept grinding away to the wire.
Raced behind midfield, on the rails with cover. Made some ground over about the last furlong.
Began awkwardly, settling 2nd last on the paint with cover. Didn't find any extra when asked for an effort in the run home.
Taken back from the outside alley to race in last position 2-3 wide with cover. Shifted wide on straightening and finished off one paced.
Went back from a wide gate to settle 4th last 3 deep with cover. Kept on evenly in the final stretch.
Crowded at the start, and then raced with the backmakers, 1 off the fence with cover. Whacked away at the same speed down the running.
Parked worse than midfield, 3-4 deep on the circle. Only plodded to the line after tough trip.
Not the best to begin, settling behind midfield, 2 deep with cover. Failed to close off.
Raced on the speed but coursed 3-4 wide without cover. Was a spent force early in the home straight. (See incident report)
Settled 2nd position, close to the running rail, shifted out to race 1 off after the 700m. Struggled in the straight and finished tailed out. (See incident report)
Camped handy, travelled 1L off the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, dashed strongly to score with plenty in hand.
Sent forward to park outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, kept on strongly for 2nd.
Pushed forward to settle in a prominent position, despite trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, stayed on nicely to get 3rd.
Rolled to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, kept on well to the line for 4th.
Showed good early pace, then eased to settle midfield 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow pace, kept on ok.
At rear, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led at slow tempo, soon flattened when placed under pressure 350M.
Pushed to settle midfield, 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, one paced until 250M weakened.
Eased back, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow sectionals, unable to run on.
At rear, settled 5Ls behind the leader with cover, never ran on.
Began awkwardly, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never a threat.
Always at back, never looked competitive.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader, never ran on.
Smart start, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, smooth progress final turn, shaken up to lead 360m, quickened away for easy win.
Fair break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven on outer turning in, responded with progress to 2nd 220m, kept on but always held.
Snagged back from wide gate, soon bustled 1 off behind midfield, shifted wide home turn & driven 400m, stayed on well to 3rd close home.
Disputed lead at break, settled rail fore of midfield, shifted out on turn, crowded into stretch, shaken up 260m, ran on without threatening.
Prominent at break, settled handy 1 off with cover, overraced 700m, shifted 3 wide to challenge home turn, shaken up 400m, kept on evenly.
Smart start & bustled to sit 1 off no cover 2nd, driven to lead 375m, immediately headed, boxed on one pace.
Snagged to rail at tail from widest gate, 8L back & shifted widest into stretch, driven centre track for minor headway.
Fast start, settled 1 off with cover midfield, shifted out turning in, driven 320m, one-paced in run home.
Broke OK, niggled rail behind midfield, driven & shifted out entering stretch, plugged on same speed.
Broke with others, raced rail midfield, driven 400m, shifted out 350m, outpaced in tepid run to wire.
Broke well, soon rousted & outpaced, raced rail near tail, driven turning in, plugged on but never a factor.
Broke with others, taken back to 1 off near tail, under pump turning in, struggled in run home.
Broke well, worked wide to lead 850m, soon to rail, driven 400m, folded & headed 375m, weakened out.
Speed to lead, crossed to rail & headed 850m, sat 1 back, found nothing in stretch & faded tamely.
Speed early, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, gained cover 1400m, smooth advance final turn, driven 430m, quickened to lead 220m, battled to wire.
Good start, slotted handy 1 off with cover, driven 550m, battling run to 2nd 50m, held in run to wire.
Broke OK to sit midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 700m, driven 400m, crowded in run, closed off soundly to claim 3rd.
Broke OK, settled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, ridden 680m, outpaced initially but stayed on for sound headway in stretch.
Slow start, settled rail behind midfield, shifted out 400m, to rail 150m, kept on soundly.
Prominent at break, sat 2nd 1 off no cover, pressed lead 650m, led 430m, all out & headed 220m, tapered & swamped.
Broke OK, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, ridden 550m & shifted out into stretch, boxed on evenly.
Missed break, raced rail 2nd last, shifted very wide into stretch & driven, ran on for minor inroads centre track.
Tardy start, keen early, covered up 3 wide near rear, very wide final turn & driven into stretch, plugged on tepidly.
Niggled from gate to race rail midfield, ridden 600m, found nothing for pressure & plodded on weakly.
Taken back to settle at tail on outer, driven very wide 680m, still last turning in, found little in run home.
Steady start, sat wide with cover near rear, rolled on to sit handy 3 wide no cover 1500m, pressed lead 650m, emptied turning in & faded.
Rolled to lead, set tempo until pressed 650m, driven turning in & headed 430m, faded thereafter.
Broke well, settled 1 back on rail, hard-ridden into home turn, found nothing & weakened tamely.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 4Ls off the slow tempo 3 wide, made early move 600M, dominated 400M and dashed well to the line and scored.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M for 2nd.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader 3 wide, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Very slow away, struggled to keep up at back, 8Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 400M, dashed strongly when clear.
Settled in front, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 200M flattened.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, little dash 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to rear, 10Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back, however failed to obtain cover and consequently over raced badly, improved 1100M to sit 2.5Ls off the slow pace 3 wide, still no cover, emptied 250M.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, out of fuel 300M.
Pressed forward, 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, lack room 400M, weakened 300M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, emptied 200M.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon reduced 400M.
Crowded out start, dropping to rear in one-off position. Ridden quietly, peeled out 600m, got clear passage 350m, finished strongly to win close to line.
Pressed forward from awkward draw to settle one-off, one-back before turn. Came off heels top of straight, hit front 300m, run down final strides.
Broke well, ridden along outside leader initially before taking over 1000m but kept in one-off position to straight. Outsprinted from 300m but kept on well.
Began fairly, ridden to hold midfield position but kept 3-wide back stretch and turn. Taken wider 350m but boxed on gamely.
Began well, pressed forward from wide draw but held 3-wide in second line behind leading pack. Kept on well early in straight turning one-paced from 200m.
Began awkwardly, then bumped and unbalanced dropping to last in a 3-wide position. Taken wider turning for home, widest in straight, kept on fairly.
Broke fairly, restrained and taken across behind runners but kept in 3-wide position. Got shuffled back turn, ran on fairly in straight.
Bumped heavily start, taken to rail and made ground to sit in box seat before turn. Looked a chance early in straight before flattened 200m.
Crowded out start, dropping to rear but close to fence. Saved ground turn, but only one-paced in straight despite hard riding.
Broke well, disputed early lead but tended to over-race. Joint leader into straight, kept battling to 200m before tiring quickly. (Declared a roarer).
Began awkwardly, no early pace, drifting toward rear between horses. Put under pressure turning for home, taken wide but limited response.
Bumped heavily start, recovered and taken to rail to sit 3-back from leader. Stayed on rail turning for home but one-paced in straight.
Began well, pressed forward from wide gate but unable to get past first two and held 3-wide back stretch and turn. Gave ground abruptly passing 500m. (Rider dropped left rein 400m).
Ridden along early to hold midfield position between horses 3-back from leaders. Raced tight for some distance early in straight before tiring.
Travelled smoothly in 4th, quickened to take over passing 300M, pulled clear mid-straight and maintained the advantage to the line.
Held up near the rear, waited with until 400M, stayed on well to go 2nd 70M from home but no impression on the runaway winner.
Held up in midfield, driven along 450M, finished off moderately but could never trouble the runaway winner, not pace of 2nd over final 100M.
Allowed an outright lead at slow pace, joined by rivals 350M, rallied briefly, faded final 150M.
Switched off to last, about 10Ls off the pace first 800M, urged along 600M out, found less than expected in the sprint for home.
Tracked leader in a slowly run race, outdashed passing 350M, soon out of contention.
Given a waiting ride about 8Ls off the pace, found disappointingly little entering straight, faded final 100M.
Attended the pace 2-wide, unable to quicken when the race got serious passing 400M, weakened out of contention mid-straight.
Broke nicely, ridden along close to rail 3-back from leader. Awkwardly placed entering turn, switched out and ran on strongly to win close home.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader before taking over and crossing to fence. Kicked clear top of straight, kept on strongly until running on empty final strides.
Bumped start, ridden forward between horses 3-back from leader. Peeled out turning for home and kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began OK, snagged back from wide draw and taken across behind horses to sit in last pair but away from fence. Switched 3-wide turning for home, hampered 200m, kept on well.
Ridden along to hold midfield position but kept 3-4 wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, kept on steadily in straight while laying in 200m.
Jumped with field, ridden to maintain forward position but held 3-wide mostly. Steadied 1200m, wide into straight, kept on despite being checked 200m.
Outpaced early, drifting to rear but held 3-wide mostly. Taken further out 500m but only one-paced in straight.
Began fairly, crossed to rail and improved position to 4-back from leader. Stayed on rail around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Broke well, pressed forward 3-wide to stay with leading pack. Rolled forward to sit 2nd around turn, kept on early in straight before tiring from 200m. (Rider dropped whip 300m)
Ridden forward from wide draw before crossing to fence in box seat before turn. Dropped back to 3rd entering straight and gave ground steadily in straight.
Began OK, snagged back from wide draw and taken across behind runners in last place to turn. Wide around turn but found little in straight despite hard riding.
Bumped start, mustered and led initially before being crossed, dropping to 3rd before turn. Checked 200m and dropped out.
Began fairly, ridden along between horses toward rear, put under pressure from 500m but found nothing.
A shade tardy, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with cover in front of midfield, 2-3 lengths back, similar position to turn, finished off strongly to score a narrow win despite hanging in. .
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide in 4th, 2 lengths back, easy run to turn, kept on well after straightening, bumped inside 100M, just missed.
Jumped well from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 4-5 lengths back, similar margin to turn, closed off well to press winner close to home.
Began fairly, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, same margin to turn, kept on very well until inconvenienced final 100M, just held on for 4th.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 7-8 lengths back, same position turning, taken widest in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Began fairly, raced at tail throughout, 8 lengths back, still well back turning, made decent progress in straight to be closest on line.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead and set a moderate tempo, shared lead turning, headed at 200M but still kept on evenly in straight.
Began well, positioned 2-3 lengths back on rail, bumped near 1000M, saved ground turning, finished off fairly in straight without showing extra gear.
Moderately away, raced 6 lengths back on rail at rear, saved ground to turn, made some headway in straight without threatening the first few.
Began well, raced prominently outside leader in 2nd, travelled well to turn, stayed on evenly until near 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths or so back, same position to turn, kept on at same pace in straight.
Average to begin, raced 4-5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, made no progress in straight, never a threat.
Taken back from a wide gate, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5-6 lengths back, same position turning, made no headway in straight, kept on one-paced.
Jumped with them, sent forward to race in 3rd, 2 lengths back, raced 3 wide with no cover until turning in, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide in 5th, 2 lengths back, no cover turning, finished off well in straight to score narrowly.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield to turn, 4 lengths back, closed off well in straight to get 2nd.
Began well, raced 2 wide in 3rd, travelled well to turn, took the lead near 250M, kept on well but unable to hold off the challengers late.
A touch slow away, raced 4-5 lengths back 3 wide at rear, similar position turning, angled out in straight and finished off well to make frame.
Crowded at start, raced 5 lengths back on rail at rear, slightly improved along the rails turning, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position turning, no daylight early in straight, passed a few tired runners when clear.
Began fairly, raced a length back behind leader in 4th, easy run to turn, lacked an extra gear and just stayed on at same pace in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground turning, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead and set a moderate tempo, travelled well turning, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, weakened gradually after turning in, eased final 100M. (see racing incidents)
Moderately away from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover throughout, 3-4 lengths back, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Began fairly from a wide draw, taken back to race at rear, 4 wide with cover, 4-5 lengths back, similar position turning, failed to close off in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide at tail, 5-6 lengths back, still well back turning, emptied early in straight, never competitive.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position turning, showed no response in straight, dropped off gradually.
