Horse Name: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Jockey: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Comment: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Began well from a low draw, settled about 2L off the pace in 4th or 5th on rails, commenced move entering straight and hit the front over 200 metres out, won readily.
Slightly slow out, tight between runners early and shuffled backward early stages, waited with in last few until over 400 metres out, went widest into straight, ran on well to do best work late.

Jumped fairly from a poor gate, obtained rails run in front at the 1200 metres but soon restrained to cede lead for 2nd position off the rails on top of stables bend, fought on to hold every chance but outsprinted closing stages.
Soon taken well back from a wide gate and waited with, made significant progress down the straight to be nearest at finish.
Vied for lead from the widest gate, eventually took up running on top of stables bend and led until finding no extra over 100 metres out.
Soon taken back towards the rear on rails, saved a lot of ground entering straight, ran home full of running but did not find much room the length of straight.

Jumped fairly, travelled 2-wide mainly within 2L of pace in 3rd or 4th, became 5th rounding home bend, kept on steadily without quickening in straight. (Lame next day and questioned for disappointing performance)
Broke well from the one draw, tightened passing winning post the first time, settled mainly in midfield on rails, came out to challenge entering straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Settled mainly 2-wide in midfield, came to challenge entering straight, kept on before finding no extra closing stages.

Niggled along early after beginning from a middle draw, travelled 3-wide without cover better than midfield stables bend, took closer order to join 2nd passing 800 metres, faded gradually from close up position into straight.
Soon taken back from a poor gate to just worse than midfield, lost position coming out of far side, towards the rear into straight, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, gradually taken back to last few but raced without cover most of way, made short-lived impression around home bend and went very wide into straight, folded up quickly.
Enjoyed all the favors box seating. Hit the front after the 150m, and closed off gamely to land the prize.
Ridden along from barrier rise but soon drifted back to settle 3rd from the rear, on the rails with cover. Finished off with plenty of purpose.
Camped behind midfield, on the paint with cover. Swung deep on the home turn and ran on soundly.
Missed the start, settling last 2-3 wide with cover. Closed off willingly.
Settled 1 off the fence had cover. Looked for an inside passage after the 600m, railed up in the straight and finished off steadily.
For the majority of the race, travelled 3 deep without cover. Maintained an even gallop down the running.
Had to work to eventually cross and lead on the fence after the 700m. Was overhauled near the 150m, gave in sharply 50m from home.
Raced worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Was one paced in the home straight.
Travelled in 2nd position, 1 off no cover. Was yielding ground 150m from the line.
Raced back in the field, one off the paint with cover. Failed to close off.
Maintained the 1 off line, 3 back with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Settled at the rear, 3 deep had cover at stages. Gave ground noticeably in the straight and tailed out. (To trial)
Ridden forward to take the fence and led at slow sectionals, kept on nicely to score in a dead heat victory.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite not suited by the slow tempo, dashed strongly to gain a dead heat victory.
Prominent, despite trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, ran on well to get 3rd.
Rolled to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, kept on steadily.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow pace, closed to the line well.
Settled worse than midfield 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite hampered by the slow tempo, ran on well.
Pushed to midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line.
Jumped slowly, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead from outside barrier, kept on until final 100M weakened.
At rear, settled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, unable to run on.
Eased to settle worse to midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never looked likely.
Taken back, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never a factor.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, slowed tempo to 500m then accelerated. Joined by runner-up passing 250m but kept battling to win on line.
Began well, ridden along to sit outside hind quarters of leader to final turn. Took closer order from 450m, joined leader 250m, battled to line but just failed.
Broke well, ridden to hold box seat 2L from leader. Switched out 350m for clear run but unable match finishing sprint of first two.
Got away OK, settling 3-back from leader along fence. Saved ground turn, came off fence 350m, boxed on without looking dangerous.
Began awkwardly, lost ground and failed to muster, dropping to last 1400m. Improved position first turn, 4-back from leader. One-paced in straight under hard riding.
Broke well, raced with leading pack before settling one-off, one-back. Kept on steadily early in straight before giving ground final 200m.
Got off fairly but outpaced and soon last but kept away from fence. Switched 3-wide entering final turn, widest in straight, one paced.
Shifted out start, bumped, hard ridden to hold position settling 2-back, one-off 3L from leader. Kept on early in straight before tiring final 100m.
Began well, restrained and taken in gradually from wide draw to sit 4-back, one-off back stretch. Turned a little wide but found little in straight.
Outpaced early, dropping to rear along fence. Made little headway thereafter. Never competitive.
Jumped well, ridden vigorously but failed to muster and trapped wide without cover in midfield. Gave ground soon after entering straight.
Began fairly, outpaced and held in one-off position toward rear. Dropped to clear last final turn. Never competitive. (Unacceptable performance).
Broke well, ridden to keep tabs on leader in one-off position. Switched 4-wide entering straight, hit front 150m and bolted clear for easy win.
Began OK, outpaced settling towards rear but wide. Rolled forward passing 700m to join leaders 450m, hit front 300m but outsprinted final 150m.
Began well, ridden along but held 3-wide without cover. Urged forward from 700m to join leaders 450m, kept on well in straight but not ridden out final stages when racing tight.
Slow, ridden to make up ground, settling midfield before being shuffled back passing 600m. Switched widest into straight and finished off strongly.
Began OK, failed to muster. shifted across behind runners, racing tight to first turn. Steadied 1100m, dropping to rear. Switched out 350m, one-paced initially before picking up momentum final 200m.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling in last pair away from fence. Pressed forward passing 700m, 5th but wide into straight, kept on one-paced. (rider dropped left rein 250m).
Began well, holding box seat into first turn before getting close to heels 1100m and losing position. Shuffled back to near last final turn before finishing off strongly between horse final 200m.
Began well, over-raced approaching first turn, strolled forward to lead passing 900m, joined up front entering straight, battled on well until flatted final 100m.
Began best, led to first turn before easing off to grab box seat back stretch. Got shuffled back home turn when outside runners moved forward, kept on one-paced in straight.
Outpaced, shifted across behind horses, jumped shadow and became unbalanced 1400m, dropping to last. Failed to respond to hard riding in straight.
Pressed forward to lead passing 1200m, dropping to 2nd when crossed 900m, Held box seat final turn before giving ground gradually in straight.
Pushed early but not muster, soon eased back to rear, 6.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 200M to score.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, checked 600M, dashed strongly 250M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed early but not muster, soon eased back for cover, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M despite all negative racing situations and ran 3rd.
Pushed early, box seat, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on well until 100M flattened.
Trapped 4 wide throughout without cover in midfield, moved forward 700M, ran on well to the line.
Prominent, 1.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, flattened 100M.
Pushed to hold the rail in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow pace, checked severely 300M, not fully tested.
In front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the slow pace, trapped 3 wide, no turn of foot.
Hard ridden to lead by 0.5L, took rail after 600M, suited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 150M.
Slow away, 6.5Ls off the leader along the rails, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Slow away, 5Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, held up 4-2, ran on ok when clear.
Eased at start, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed fairly.
Bumped and unbalanced start, ridden to hold position 3-back, one-off first turn, travelled easily to turn, revved up passing 450m, hit front 150m, pulled clear.
Bumped start, pressed forward to settle one-back, one-off. Took closer order turning for home, looked chance 200m, outsprinted final 150m when racing tight.
Shifted in and bumped start, allowed to find feet settling towards rear away from fence. Urged forward passing 500m, taken wide into straight, finished off strongly.
Pressed forward from wide gate and caught 3-wide without cover first turn. Kept rolling forward but wide back stretch, loomed as chance 300m, battled gamely till flattened 50m.
Began awkwardly, then threw head up when taken across behind runners. Came off rail back stretch, turned wide and finished off strongly.
Pressed forward from good draw to hold box seat into first turn. Dropped 3-back along fence passing 800m, kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
A little slow into stride, taken to rail behind midfield, switched out passing 600m to move forward, kept on steadily in straight.
Began fairly, ridden along but wide first turn, gradually drifting back to be last at 600m. Revved up final turn, widest into straight, ran on steadily.
Began well, ridden to hold rail and joint leader from 1400m to 1150m. Under pressure passing 500m, kept on steadily before running out of gas 150m.
Began best, joined up from 1400m before taking clear lead 1150m. Led into straight, still a chance 200m before tiring quickly final 50m.
Began OK, restrained and taken across behind runners in last place. Improved position back stretch but found nothing straight. (Lame left front, stiff action behind).
Jumped fairly, outpaced, settling at rear. Taken 3-wide passing 600m to make run but failed to muster. (Rider reported horse not willing to stretch out).
Began well from inside barrier, led steadily to straight, established 2L lead entering straight, kept on strongly to line, never being challenged.
Held up in touch within 3Ls of leader, closed off well final 300M to go 2nd 50M from home but could never get near to the runaway winner.
Broke alertly, settled just outside leader, driven entering straight but could not get near to winner, ran on evenly to line, lost 2nd 50M out.
Slowly away, soon taken across behind runners, took closer order in midfield before home turn, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 4th.
Never far off from the pace, stayed on fairly final 300M, no impression on leaders.
Soon hugged the rail, took closer order passing 850M, on heels of leader turning for home, outsprinted over final 200M.
Lost ground at start, ended up near the rear, overraced 800M, made limited progress on straightening, never threatened.
Dropped back from wide barrier, settled last 7Ls off the pace, ran on fairly final 300M and never reached contention.
Not hurried early stages, settled behind midfield along the 2-path, driven 300M but not making any progress.
In midfield, caught wide no cover for the majority of race, failed to pick up the pace entering straight, never involved.
Restrained in a rearward position, no closer than 3-wide for majority of the race, brought wider 400M, found disappointingly little.
From barrier 12 caught wide in early stages, slotted in behind mid-division, roused along 400M but had little left in reserves, eased 150M.

Settled just better than midfield on rails within 3L of pace, soon came under pressure to challenge upon straightening, fought on dourly to assert authority inside final 100 metres.
Jumped fairly, ridden to hold prominent rails position early settling just off the pace, took the lead from tiring pace-setter over 200 metres out only to be swamped close to home.
Soon taken back from the widest gate to obtain rails run just worse than midfield, snuck up on inside entering straight, fought on well in the run home to be nearest at finish.
Settled towards the rear on rails after beginning from a wide gate, commenced move upon straightening, unable to sustain run inside final 100 metres.

Prominent early, shuffled back to better than midfield position in 7th or 8th within 4L of pace, similar turning in but baulked early in straight, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
Settled just worse than midfield, raced wide rounding home bend, made modest headway down the centre of straight.
Sluggish at start, remained well behind to straight, kept on steadily under pressure.
Very slowly away, trailed the field to straight, kept on past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Began moderately, pressed on to soon take up running, led until overhauled inside final 250 metres.
Never far off to straight, soon faded.
Jumped moderately, raced wide in forward of midfield, kept on at the one pace in straight.
Prominent 3-wide to straight, faded gradually under pressure.
Amongst leaders early, gradually shifted back to rear of midfield by home bend, lost further ground in straight.

Raced very wide without cover throughout, after jumped well from a poor draw, travelled wide with leaders early stages, then taken back to just worse than midfield coming out of back straight, dropped to tail-end into straight.
Slow to begin settling 4th from the rear after being hampered near the 1400M, racing on the paint. Rolled off the rail on the circle .Closed off soundly, edged clear after the 50m.
Parked 2nd, outside the leader, no cover. Hit the front approaching the 300m, and fought gamely right to the wire.
Settled last close to the rail with cover. Peeled out early in the straight and maintained a solid gallop down the running.
Camped 3 back the paint. Was still there at the 100m, but was collard late to miss third placing.
Settled just off midfield, 2 deep with cover. Maintained a steady gallop down the running.
Enjoyed the box seat. Had every possible hope. Faded inside the 100m.
Had absolutely every possible hope after settling 1 out 1 back. Was a beaten horse soon after straightening.
Raced back in the field, on the rails with cover. Failed to close off.
Raced towards the rear of the field, 2 deep with cover. Never quicken, plodded to the line.
Led on the paint at a slow tempo. Weakened quickly after the 150m.
Sent forward to share the lead along the outer fence, kept on strongly to take the victory by a neck.
Prominent, travelled 1L behind the leader along the outer fence, dashed well for 2nd.
Camped handy, settled 2Ls behind the leader in the middle of the track, ran on well for 3rd.
Ridden forward to share the lead near the stand side, kept on nicely to get 4th.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader in the middle of the track, ran on ok.
Settled worse than midfield 5Ls behind the leader in the middle part of the track, ran on well.
Raced midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader in the middle part of the track, made some ground over the concluding stages.
Raced midfield along the outer fence, made ground steadily when placed under pressure near the course proper.
At rear, travelled 9ls behind the leader in the middle part of the track, made plenty of ground when placed under pressure near 150M. (Questioned for riding, see incident report)
Taken back, travelled 3Ls behind the leader in the middle part of the track, never ran on.
Sent forward to share the lead near the stand side, kept on one pace when placed under pressure near the course proper, flattened 200M.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Ridden forward to share the lead in the middle part of the track, however found nothing when placed under pressure 400M.
Lacked early pace, under pressure 700M, never a factor.
Slow, taken to rail, improved position, then switch off 5-back from leader. Close to heels 500m, taken to centre track in straight, finished off strongly. (Rider dropped whip 300m).
Pressed forward racing 3-wide until 1000m when left without cover. Edged closer around turn, joined leader 200m, outsprinted final 50m.
Jumped well, quickly in front, pressured early before taking clear lead and slowing pace. Kicked ahead 400m, joined 200m, battled to line.
Bumped and unbalanced start, ridden along settling 3-back, one-off. Switched out turn, wide into straight, ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Pressed forward racing outside early leader to 1000m before switching in to box seat. Stayed on fence around turn and kept on steadily in straight.
Pushed forward from wide draw, racing 3-wide before settling outside hind quarters of leader. Rolled forward entering straight before turning one-paced from 250m.

Ridden along very wide initially, steadied 1400m and taken in. Off bridle 1200m, hard ridden to hold position, taken to fence in straight, held for run 200m, finished off well from 100m. (See racing incidents).
Broke well, ridden to hold position one-back, one-off to turn. Under pressure from 400m and gave ground gradually in straight.
Began well, ridden along to hold rail settling 3-back from leader. Stayed on rail around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Jumped OK, taken closer to fence settling 4-back from leader. Switched out turning for home but found little in straight under hard riding.
Began fairly, outpaced and soon at rear but away from fence. Taken wide turning for home but little headway. Never competitive.
Jumped with field, not pressed, settling between horses at rear. Taken wide entering straight but found nothing under pressure. Not ridden out final strides.
No early pace, dropping to rear in 3-wide position. Switched widest in straight but never competitive.
Began OK, became unbalanced before settled 3-back, one-off. Travelled smoothly to turn, rolled forward from 400m, hit front 100m, held off late challenge.
Taken in soon after start settling 4-back, the fence. Switched out turning for home but no run until 250m when accelerated strongly to just fail.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit on hind-quarters of leader. Draw alongside leader entering straight, hit front 300m, run down final 100m.
Began OK, not pressed and settled behind midfield away from fence. Tended to lay in turning for home, ran on steadily in straight while laying in.
Ridden along early, unable find cover, drifting back 3-wide at rear. Taken very wide in straight, finishing strongly down centre track.
Began fairly, unable hold rail position, dropping 3-back. Unable find clear passage in straight until 150m when crowded and unbalanced. Kept on well.
Broke best, soon in lead and slowed pace. Joined up front soon after turning for home, kept on steadily till running on empty passing 100m.
Ridden to obtain forward position from wide draw, settling one-back, one-off passing 1200m. Looked chance turning for home but only one-paced. (Had substantial blood in trachea).
Broke fairly, taken across behind runners, settling at rear. Switched out to centre track entering straight and ran on fairly under hard riding.
Began OK, steadied shortly after then proved difficult to settle, racing behind midfield away from fence. Under pressure from 500m but only one-paced in straight.
Fractious in gate, crowded out at start then taken across behind runners in last place. Edged forward approaching turn but found little in straight when asked.
No early pace and soon at rear away from dropping to clear last before turn. Taken wide in straight but little headway. (Rider reported did not stretch out at any stage).
Broke well, hard ridden to hold position behind leader and under further pressure 500m before weakening. Unacceptable performance. (See racing incidents).
Began OK, ridden along early 4L from leader. Got shuffled back around turn and faded in straight.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide no cover, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 250M to score.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 300M to run a remarkable 2nd.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts and got 3rd.
Hard ridden forward to share the lead 2 wide, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 100M flattened.
Jumped very well, eased back to rear, 8Ls off the leader 3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, little dash when clear.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
In front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Very slow away, 6Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, little dash when clear.
Settled in front, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 300M.
Eased back, 7Ls off the leader, trapped 4 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, never improved.
Box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, however soon reduced 300M.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 400M, no progress when clear.
Slow away, never a factor.
Began OK, allowed to settle at rear in one-off position. Dropped to last entering turn, switched wide for clear run in straight and finished off strongly.
Jumped best, led to 1200m when put under pressure by another runner. Kicked clear 1000m, led to 200m, outsprinted final stages but kept on well.
Began fairly, ridden to hold rail 3-back from leader. Edged closer at turn, lay in 400m, then lay out under pressure in straight, doing best work final 200m.
Ridden along between horses early to obtain forward position before switched off back stretch 5L from leader. Turned wide, had clear run and finished off nicely.
Jumped OK, outpaced and soon last. Inched forward turning for home, widest into straight, ran on steadily.
Pressed forward to put pressure on leader from 1200m to 1000m before easing a length back. Kept on gamely to 200m before giving ground gradually.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold rail grabbing box seat on settling. Shuffled back slightly final turn, boxed on fairly in straight.
Jumped well, racing alongside leading pack before easing to 5th. Put under pressure 600m but only one paced. (Rider said horse sweated up badly and firm ground did not suit).
No early pace, settling at rear before edging forward but wide from 800m. Taken wider entering straight but little response to hard riding.
Ridden aggressively to obtain forward position but unable to cross to rail and left wide without cover from 1500m. Gave ground steadily from 800m.
Began well, restrained to sit about 2Ls off the pace in 5th, travelled strongly, quickened up smartly to lead 200M, pulled clear under hands and heels riding. Impressively.
Soon led, took them along at steady pace, lost lead 200M and no match with winner, kept on evenly to hold 2nd.
Tracked leader along the fence, not finishing pace of winner, shifted out under pressure passing 300M, ran on for moderate 3rd.
Driven forward, tracked leader from 900M, kept on same pace turning in, held 4th just.
Taken back to back of the field, 6-7Ls off the pace turning home, closed off well from off the pace but hung in and difficult to ride, no impression on runaway winner.
Held up in mid-division, saved ground on the fence but had difficulty obtaining clear running early straight, stayed on mildly final 300M.

Held up behind midfield, bumped 1000M and became unbalanced, lost ground 900M, made limited progress turning home, never a threat to leaders. (Jockey reported his horse didn't stretch out in straight.)
Rushed forward from 14 but caught wide no cover throughout, kept on same pace turning home, faded towards finish.
Held up towards the rear, saved ground along the fence, not pace to challenge, same pace over final 300M.
Proved difficult to settle, caught very wide throughout behind midfield, gave limited response turning home, never threatened. (found to be distressed post race.)
Restrained in midfield, 3-wide for majority of race, faded nearing 200M, no extra.
Dropped back to the rear, had nothing to offer turning home, never involved.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, made no progress when placed under pressure early straight, weakened rapidly passing 200M. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Crowded out start, ridden to make ground between horses, settling 3-back, one-off. Presented dream run top of straight and finished off well under whip.
Bumped after start, taken closer to fence towards rear. Difficult to settle passing 850m, checked and unbalanced. Edged closer turn and finished off nicely.
Crowded out start, taken across behind runners, settling in last pair away from fence. Had clear run in straight and ran on well.
Began OK, taken closer to fence at rear in one-off position. Switched out 500m to make run but forced to shift in abruptly 250m when closing off well.
Stumbled out of gates, recovered and pressed forward to lead on settling. Not challenged until entering straight, caught 250m but kept on well till swamped 50m.
Ridden along from awkward gate and held 3-wide behind midfield back stretch. Taken very wide in straight but ran on steadily.
Began OK but began to race fiercely passing 1200m and then bumped. Covered extra ground turn, kept on steadily in straight before turning one-paced 200m.
Began OK but restrained, dropping 4-back the rail along back stretch. Made forward move turning for home, kept on steadily before turning one-paced passing 200m.
Pressed forward from wide draw and raced 3-4 wide mostly without cover. Edged forward around turn, looked chance 400m before running on empty final stages.
Ridden forward to sit on hind-quarters of leader back stretch before moving alongside turning for home. Gave ground from 200m. (Substantial blood in trachea and declared a roarer).
Broke well, pushed forward from inside draw to sit in box seat back stretch and turn. Kept on well to 250m before tiring.
Jumped fairly, outpaced and soon last along the rail. Trailed field to straight and ran past beaten horses.
Began awkwardly, ridden to make ground settling in midfield. Edged forward around turn but found little in straight under hard riding.
Bumped after start, recovered and pressed forward to sit 3-wide behind pacemakers. Under pressure from 600m and became tailed off in straight. (Unacceptable performance).
Began well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in early, sent forward to race in 2nd near 1100M, kept same position on turn, loomed at 400M, hit lead and finished off well to score narrowly.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, set a moderate tempo in mid- section, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner.
Slowly away, raced 4-5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, difficult to settle early, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off very well to get 3rd.
Jumped well, positioned 1-2 lengths back on rail in front of midfield, easy run to turn, lacked a threat at 400M, kept on evenly in straight to make frame.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 4-5 lengths back, improved on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Began fairly from the widest draw, taken back to race 2 wide 7 lengths back at tail, slightly improved on bend, taken widest after turning in, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide throughout, 4 lengths back, no cover turning, closed off evenly in straight without threatening the first few.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths or so back, similar margin to turn, finished off evenly final 300M without showing extra gear to trouble them.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently in 3rd, traveled well to turn, soon under pressure and just kept on evenly in straight without threatening.
Began fairly, positioned 3-4 lengths back on rail in midfield, similar position to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6-7 lengths back on rail at rear, still well back turning, made only minor progress in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4-5 lengths back, similar position turning, made no headway in straight, kept on one-paced.
Began well, positioned 1 out 1 back, same position to turn, under pressure after 600M, weakened gradually in straight.
Slowly away, raced at tail throughout, still last turning in, made no progress in straight, never competitive. (See racing incidents.)

Jumped well, taken back to rear of midfield for cover, commenced move out wide over 400 metres out, fought on well under pressure to assert authority over 100 metres out. (Lame next day)
Taken back from the widest draw, taken 3-wide around home bend to poise for a run, ran on steadily in straight to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, soon a joint-leader before settling just off the lead, gained slender advantage rounding home bend, found no extra when swamped over 200 metres out.
Settled 2-wide in 4th just over 2L off the pace, came under pressure from around home bend holding some chance early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Settled in midfield on rails, came under pressure home bend, snuck up on rails early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Settled towards the rear on rails, improved steadily under pressure in straight but did not find much close to home.
Jumped well from the one draw, amongst leaders of three before slipping back to settle in 2L 3rd on rails, failed to quicken under pressure early in straight, faded inside final 200 metres.
Taken well back and waited with, came under pressure inside final 500 metres, made modest headway in straight without threatening. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped awkwardly, remained well behind to straight, ran past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Ridden along from a poor draw travelling 3-wide without cover in forward of midfield, met minor interferences early in straight, kept on under pressure before faded inside final 200 metres.

Jumped moderately, soon amongst leaders, took up running on rails passing the winning post the first time, held narrow lead to 600 metres, dropped away quickly from 2nd into straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped fairly, settled mainly 2-wide in midfield, soon weakened in straight.
Wasn't the best away but soon mustered to travel midfield, 1 off the fence with cover. Closed off with plenty of purpose to clinch victory close to the wire.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race stalking the leader on the fence. was nailed close to the line.
Went forward and led on the rails. Maintained a solid gallop down the running, grudgingly gave ground late.
Parked 1 out 1 back. Kept grinding away right to the wire.
Parked worse than midfield, on the paint with cover. Peeled out prior to the home turn and swung deep on straightening. Kept finding the line.
Had to be used in the early stages from a wide gate to eventually settle, 2nd 1 off no cover. Weakened over the latter stages.
Raced with the backmakers, 2-3 wide had cover. Checked at the 400m, kept on steadily to the wire.
Settled close to midfield, on the rails with cover. Whacked away at the same peed in the run to the line.

Jumped on terms, then drifted back in the early & middle stages, travelling close to the rail, 3rd last with cover. One paced in the straight. (Reported lame the following day). (See Incident report.)
Traveled last, on the rails with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Eventually got in to travel 1 off after the 700m, settling worse than midfield, with cover. Did nothing in the straight.
Posted 3-4 deep without cover on the circle, settling at the rear. Failed to close off.
Raced midfield, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on well to score by 1/2L.
Taken back from wide draw, settled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast pace, dashed strongly when clear 250M for 2nd.
At rear, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, ran on well when clear 200M to get 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the quick tempo, dashed well.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led at fast sectionals, kept on until final 100M weakened.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Settled worse than midfield about 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast pace, never ran on.
Sent forward to share the lead at fast tempo, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, flattened 200M.
Raced midfield, however trapped 4-5 wide without cover throughout, never looked likely.
Sent forward to share the lead at fast sectionals, however travelled 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened soon after straightening, tailed out.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite suited by the quick tempo, weakened badly rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Settled worse than midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, checked 1000M, never in a competitive position thereafter, tailed out.
Speed to dispute early lead 3 wide, settled 2nd 1 off no cover, pressed leader 600m, quickened to lead turning in, driven clear.
Broke well, tracked handy 1 off with cover, hard-ridden 450m, stayed on in stretch to snag 2nd last stride.
Bustled early to dispute lead, led outright on rail 1200m, driven & headed turning in, boxed on, tapered late & pipped for 2nd.
Broke well, handy early & settled rail fore of midfield, driven into stretch, closed off to share 3rd at wire.
Awkward start & driven initially to settle 1 off with cover midfield, driven 420m, stayed on for minor headway.
Dropped in at tail from widest gate, shifted 3 wide 600m & rolled on, 5L back & driven 400m, wide into stretch, closed off well centre-track.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide no cover midfield, driven wide home turn, plugged on one pace.
Moderate break & bustled to settle rail midfield, shuffled back 850m, driven final turn, kept on one pace.
Good start to dispute early lead on rail, settled 1 back, driven home turn, outpaced & plugged on evenly.
Missed break, raced rail near rear, to tail 600m, ridden 300m but found little in tepid run home.
Bumped start, settled near rear 1 off, driven turning in but found nothing.
Bustled to lead, soon to rail & set tempo, driven when pressed for lead turning in, fought off rival to assert & draw clear final 150m.
Sharp start, tracked 1 back on rail, driven & shifted out turning in, kept on doggedly to claim 2nd late.
Niggled at break to sit 1L 2nd 1 off no cover, joined leader turning in, dueled neck and neck until emptied 150m & weakened.
Broke well, raced 1 off with cover fore of midfield, ridden turning in & shifted centre track, ran on for minor inroads under strong drive.
Sharp break, settled back midfield on rail, niggled 450m, ridden turning in, plugged on same speed.
Smart start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 500m, driven turning in but not clear run 300m & 150m, kept on in crowded run to wire.
Taken back from wide gate, niggled near tail 1 off, shifted 3 wide no cover 600m, driven 400m & widest into stretch, closed for minor headway.
Tardy start, sat rail near rear, shaken up 300m, plugged on one pace.
Smart start, slotted 3 wide with cover midfield, ridden 400m, found little in tame stretch run.
Sluggish start, raced 1 off with cover near rear, switched wide & driven home turn, found nothing in stretch.
Broke well, caught 3 wide no cover & settled handy, shaken up in 4th final turn, found little & weakened, eased late when beaten.
Slow break, soon adrift at tail, driven 470m to close at rear, outpaced & plodded on same speed.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace, not fully tested.
Settled 1L off the leader 2 wide, enjoyed by the slow sectionals, led 300M, hung on well until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Midfield on the fence, 3.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Eased to sit in midfield early, however trapped very wide, then was allowed to stride forward 1200M, led by 1L at slow sectionals, ran on until 200M flattened.
At rear, 6.5Ls off the leader along the fence, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased at start to take cover at rear, 6.5Ls of the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the slow pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, reduced 250M.
At back, 5Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Pushed to take box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 250M.
At rear, harmed by the slow pace, never progressed.
Jumped well, soon in front and quickly crossed to rail. Awkward around turn, kicked ahead 300m, kept finding when challenged final 200m.
Pressed forward to sit in slipstream of leader. Took inside run entering straight and battled strongly to line.
Jumped OK, lost left front plate start, ridden to hold position one-back, one-off. Took turn a little wide, picked up speed passing 250m, kept on.
Ridden early to hold forward position, settling 3-back the rail. Took inside run entering straight and kept on steadily to line.
Ridden for luck from wide draw before finding cover 4-back and one-off. Taken very wide in straight and ran on steadily down centre track.
Began fairly, no early pace drifting back in one-off position. Well back entering straight before finishing off nicely between horses.
Hard ridden early to hold rail position behind midfield. Put under pressure 400m, turned a little wide, kept on fairly in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped. Hard ridden to get forward 3-back from leader. Tightened around turn, kept on fairly in straight racing tight between horses final 100m.
Began awkwardly, losing ground, then ridden to improve position. Made forward move passing 450m but only one-paced straight.
Used up early to go forward from wide draw, sitting outside leader from 750m to straight. Under pressure passing 200 and gave ground noticeably.
Began OK but no early speed dropping to near rear along turn. Hard ridden entering straight but found nothing. Never competitive.
Jumped OK but soon outpaced and taken across behind runners in last place. Never likely. (Jockey reported horse not comfortable in action).
Forwardly placed, tracked leader in a steadily run race, went through narrow passage to lead near 200M, ridden clear.
Held up in midfield along the fence, 3Ls off leaders making the turn for home, stayed on evenly for 2nd but well held by winner.
Bustled along early, positioned one out one back, led briefly turning home but not finishing pace of winner, kept on mildly for 3rd.
Not hurried, reserved behind midfield 5Ls off the pace, made moderate progress getting up for 4th near line.
Crossed to lead passing 1300M, set even pace, headed nearing 200M, stayed on same pace, faded to 5th near line.
Settled in 4th and stayed within striking distance throughout, kept on mildly entering straight, never a serious threat to leaders.
Checked shortly after the jump, held up near the rear 7Ls off the pace, stayed on fairly down outside of field, not reached main rivals.
Held up in mid-division along the 2-path, kept on same pace over final 250M and lacked the needed response.
Dropped back, at the rear of the field 8Ls off the pace, made limited progress turning in, never involved.
Taken across behind runners, settled near the rear, had little to offer under pressure 300M and failed to make any impression.
Held up behind midfield, proved difficult to settle passing 1100M, inclined to hang out in middle stages, under pressure 500M out, soon beaten turning in.
Taken back from wide draw, settled near the rear and raced without cover in middle stages, struggled to keep up 500M out, soon left behind.

Settled in last few, 3-wide into straight, ran on to assert authority inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well, gradually settled in midfield in 6th, commenced move entering straight but did not find much room early on, ran on inside final 300 metres to be nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately settling well behind, last into straight, briefly baulked on straightening, finished off race nicely.
Slowly away as usual, remained well back on rails to straight, shifted out for a run on straightening, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Ridden along in rear of midfield, similar turning for home, hung in early in straight, made steady progress without threatening.
Settled towards the rear, badly baulked for a run most of way in straight.
Ridden to the front early, ceded lead to assume one-back position on rails coming out of far side, remained same into straight, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.
Close up early after beginning from a poor draw, niggled along 2-wide in 4th within 2L off pace, quickened to hit front briefly over 200 metres out only to be swamped shortly after.
Jumped well, travelled just better than midfield in 5th about 3L off the pace, similar turning for home, kept on before tiring inside final 200 metres.
Jumped moderately, gradually worked his way up to gain slender lead coming out of back straight, led until headed over 200 meres out, soon weakened.
Pressed on from a poor draw joining leader around the bend, drew level briefly upon straightening, folded up quickly.
Jumped well, with leaders briefly, dropped to midfield coming out of back straight, worse around home bend but saved ground turning for home, soon weakened.
Camped midfield the fence. Had to overcome some traffic early in the straight after being checked. Hit the line with plenty of purpose.
Settled 3rd 1 off without cover. Worked forward to race outside the leader after the 700m. Hit the front near the 100m but was overhauled late.
Worked forward and led along the paint after the 1000m and set a fast tempo. Grudgingly gave ground late.
Made its run 2nd from rear after settling 1 off with cover. Finished off well.
Settled with the backmakers, 2-3 wide with cover. Swung deep on the home turn, maintained a sound gallop down the running.
Parked behind midfield, on the rails with cover. Made fair ground in the home stretch.
Jumped on terms then went back from a wide gate to settle last, at least 3 wide with some cover. Came widest in straight and closed off with plenty of purpose.
Settled 4th, on the rails with cover. Peaked on its effort 100m from home.
Posted 3 deep without cover behind midfield. Battled away in the run home.
Raced 4th last, 2 deep with cover. Just plugged away to the line.
Raced ahead of midfield, 2 deep with cover. Gave ground quickly over the final 50m.
Settled 3rd last, 2 wide with cover. Ran deep on the home turn, was only one paced in the run home.
Aggressively ridden in the early stages to cross and travel in 2nd in position, following the leader with cover. Was a beaten horse early in the home straight.
Parked midfield, 1 off with cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Raced midfield, 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, demonstrated a strong finishing effort to score by 1-3/4L.
Sent forward, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on strongly until 100M weakened to get 2nd.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, switched wide turning in, dashed well for 3rd.
Eased to settle midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily.
Jumped slowly, then ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, stayed on steadily.
Sent forward to settle 1L behind the leader 2 wide without cover, unable to close off the race. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Taken back from wide gate, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung wide turning in, ran on only fairly.
Hard ridden to settle in midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace to the line.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, kept on until 200M weakened.
Camped handy, trapped 4 wide without cover throughout, emptied 100M.
Prominent early, however hung out rounding the first turn, never a threat thereafter.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Began awkwardly, then failed to muster pace and settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
At rear, travelled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked likely.
Driven from wide gate to lead, to rail 1000m & extended 3L clear, 1.5L clear & driven 400m, kicked on under drive & in command at wire.
Good break but soon bustled to sit 4th on rail, shuffled back home turn, driven in pursuit 350m, to 2nd 250m, chased to wire but always held.
Started OK, raced 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, ridden 550m, gradual inroads to 3rd final 50m.
Sluggish start, niggled to settle rail midfield, shifted out into stretch but stuck in pocket, in clear final 100m & quickened for late headway.
Broke well, caught 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, ridden for progress 550m, outpaced top of stretch, stayed on dourly.
Broke OK, speed to press early lead, keen & restrained to 3rd 1 off no cover, ridden 550m to 2nd 400m, lost place 250m & faded in run.
Fair start, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, ridden into stretch, in pocket to 300m then plugged on one pace.
Fast start, sat 2nd on rail, pressed to close on lead into final turn, driven 430m, outpaced 400m & weakened thereafter.
Tardy break, bustled to sit 1 off with cover fore of midfield, driven 570m but one-paced & faded closing stages.
Taken behind at start to rail & rolled to sit behind midfield, under pump turning in, plodded home tamely.
Slow start from widest gate, raced tail on rail, driven into home turn, kept on same speed past beaten rivals.
Decent break, taken back to 1 off with cover near tail, switched wide & ridden final turn, plodded one pace in tepid run home.
Slow break, sat 3 wide with cover in rear, forced wide & hard-ridden turning in, found nothing & never a factor.
Broke OK, eventually slotted 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven home turn, emptied 300m & faded.
Broke OK, raced rail midfield, ridden for progress 500m, shifted out on turn, grinding run under strong drive to lead 150m, held on.
Fast break to share lead, soon settled rail fore of midfield, progress on turn, trapped in pocket, bumped 170m, shifted out 90m, closed rapidly, just failed.
Driven to vie for early lead, sat handy 1 off until slotted 1 back on rail 880m, to 2nd & driven 350m, shared brief lead 150m but tapered to wire.
Broke well, caught 4 wide no cover until slotted 1 off with cover 4th 850m, switched out & ridden into stretch, boxed on dourly.
Sluggish break, rolled 3 wide to sit midfield no cover, under pump 550m, wide into stretch, closed off for sound inroads without threatening.
Taken back to sit 3 wide with cover near rear, under pump 7L back 500m, rattled home late centre track for sound inroads.
Smart start, bustled to lead & soon to rail, 1L clear & driven 400m, headed 150m & swamped.
Moderate start, niggled forward 3 wide to sit 1 off no cover 950m, driven under pressure turning in, outpaced & boxed on evenly.
Slow start, pushed on to sit 1 off with cover midfield, driven 550m, one-paced in run home.
Missed break, recovered to rail behind midfield, driven & progress final turn, closing to challenge when checked & unbalanced 170m, chance gone.
Struggled to muster & soon at tail, hard-ridden into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Snagged to tail at break, rolled to race 1 off with cover near rear, driven 400m, moderate effort centre track & weakened late.
Broke OK, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven 500m, plugged home tamely.
Taken back & 4 wide no cover near tail until slotted last pair 1 off at 1000m, wide in to stretch & found nothing.
Pushed to take rail and led by 0.5L at good pace, drifted away 300M to score.
Settled in box seat, pace good, lack room 400M, just held ground when clear, hold on for 2nd.
Bumped start and checked, 5.5Ls off the good pace along the fence, made steady ground 250M.
Hard ridden forward but failed to cross in the lead, trapped 3 wide no cover throughout, ran on fairly.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made some ground 200M.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 7Ls off the good pace, blocked most straight and checked 300M, not tested.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, pace good, weakened 300M.
Eased to rear, 8Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on ok.
Hard ridden but failed to tackle the lead, 1.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, reduced 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4LS off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, emptied 400M.
Never competitive.
Eased back, trapped 3 wide, never a factor.
Slow, settled at rear, suited by pace and switched off. Taken out 600m, wide into straight, ran on strongly, bumped and unbalanced when taking lead 100m, held.
Broke well, not rushed, settling 4-back, one-off. Turned a little wide, finished strongly between horses, tightened, bumped and unbalanced 100m, just failed.
Began well, ridden forward settling 3-back, one-off. Got clear run entering straight, shifted away from inside horse nearing 100m, kept on well.
Broke well, taken to fence, settling 3-back from leader. Switched out 350m to get run, looked chance 200m, shifted out abruptly 100m, swamped.
Began fairly, not rushed and allowed to settle in second half of field in one-off position. Caught behind horses turning for home, finished off nicely when clear final 200m.
Allowed to stride forward from inside draw settling 4-back the fence. Came off rail turning for home and kept on steadily to be closest at finish
Speared out of gate before being eased into box seat behind leader. Made forward move around home turn, looked chance 200m before flattened.
Began well, taken to front and crossed to rail 1800m. Given more rein 1200m to prevent being crossed, kicked further ahead 600m before coming under pressure 200m and fading.
No early pace, settling towards rear along fence. No change in position back stretch and final turn, made up some ground in straight.
Pressed forward early to sit behind leader before being crossed and dropping to 3rd passing 1200m. Still in contention 200m before giving ground quickly.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw, settling in last pair away from fence. Taken wide into straight but found little under pressure.
Taken across behind horses from wide draw and last on settling. Under pressure turning for home, responded initially before tiring final 200m. (Rider reported did not travel comfortably).
Slow into stride, got head up and soon at rear along fence. Shaken up turning for home, wide in straight but found nothing when asked.
Jumped OK, ridden along but left wide 1500m. Circled field to sit outside leader 1200m, but tired quickly soon after straightening for home.

Sped forward, allowed an uncontested lead at even pace, opened up 2Ls advantage turning in, was tackled and headed by rival at 200M, showed battling qualities and fought back to re-gain the lead inside 100M.
Broke well, tracked leaders in 3rd, made rapid headway entering straight to join eventual winner 200M out, briefly in front but run peaked 150M, gave away the lead inside 100M.
Settled well in mid-division, stayed on well for 3rd but not pace to challenge first two.
Restrained to a rearward position 6Ls off the pace, ran on moderately to go 4th 100M from home, no threat to first two.
Dropped back from wide barrier, settled near last 7-8Ls off the pace, made steady progress turning in, raced tight 200M.
Never far off from leaders, switched to 3-wide 600M, had every chance entering straight, kept up the pursuit to 150M then backed away.
Held up behind midfield along the 2-path, failed to pick up sufficiently entering straight, no impression on leaders.
Held up towards the rear, driven along passing 500M but lacked the necessary response.
Rushed early to take up a 2-wide position just behind leader, went into final 400M with little left, weakened towards the finish.
Waited with in the rear, swung wide near 400M for his run, made only limited progress and never reached a contending position. (Lame.)
Jumped OK, restrained, settling 3-wide at rear with cover. Switched out nearing 500m, taken to centre track and finished strongly under hands and heels riding for easy win.
Broke well, raced up front before being eased back to sit between horses 3L from leader. Steadied approaching 1000m, switched out 300m and finished off nicely.
Ridden along outside early leader before taking over and crossing to rail 900m. Kicked clear around turn, caught 200m out, kept on steadily.
Began well and raced with early leaders before easing one-back, one-off. Raced tight passing 500m, kept on gamely in straight.
Out quickly, led initially before being crossed and taking sit on leader. Edged closer turning for home, looked chance 400m before running on empty from 200m.
Aggressively ridden early to maintain forward position, settling 4L from leader in 3-wide position and left without cover from 1000m. One-paced final 400m.
Pressed forward from inside draw to hold rail behind leader. Checked and unbalanced 700m, picked up again turning for home, but one-paced final 200m.
Began OK, shifted in behind horses from wide draw settling in last pair in one-off position, Checked and shifted out abruptly near 700m bumping another. One-paced in straight.
Began OK, taken quickly to rail 3-back from leader. Steadied approaching 1200m, stayed on rail turning for home but found little in straight.
Began fairly, taken in quickly settling four-back along rail. Steadied 1000m, got close to heels 800m, raced in restricted room to straight, lay-in under pressure final stages.
Taken in from wide draw settling in last pair but away from fence. Crowded for room 1000m, bumped and taken out 700m, widest in straight, found nothing.
Slow into stride, made ground along rail before turn, gave ground in straight and not ridden out final stages.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide 3 lengths back in 6th, travelled well throughout, dashed clear early in straight, held off the late challenger to score narrowly.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, same position to turn, made good progress in straight to take 2nd, just missed.
Average to begin, raced 2 lengths back in 5th, ideal run to turn, no daylight until near 200M, finished off well to get 3rd.
Jumped well, raced 3-4 lengths or so back in midfield on rails, improved turning in, angled out in straight and made reasonable headway to make frame.
Began well, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, in traffic early in straight, finished off evenly when clear final 250M, just missed frame.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race in 2nd, same margin back turning, looked a place chance but lacked an extra gear final 200M, stayed on at same pace.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, similar position turning, made some ground in straight but never a threat.
Fairly away, raced 3 wide with cover, 5-6 lengths back in 9th, similar position on turn, closed off evenly in straight.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, sent forward to race prominently, 3 wide no cover throughout, weakened gradually in straight after hard run took effect.
Slowly away, raced 7-8 lengths back on rail at rear, checked near 1000M, still well back turning, made only minor progress in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, unchallenged to turn, headed near 250M, emptied thereafter and eased.
Average to begin, raced 6 lengths back on rails at rear, checked near 1000M, 2 wide on turn, emptied early in straight, never competitive.
Crowded out start, raced 8 lengths back at tail, difficult to settle after 1000M, slightly improved on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Slowly away, raced 8 lengths away at rear, difficult to settle near 700M, still well back turning, taken widest in straight but made no progress, never competitive.
Jumped well, raced 3 lengths back on rail in 5th, easy run to turn, finished off very well in straight to score with some in hand.
Began well, raced a length back on rail in 3rd, saved ground to turn, took the lead near 200M, kept on well but unable to hold off the winner late.
Began fairly from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide without cover in midfield, 5 lengths back, did work to turn, closed off very strongly in straight to get 3rd.
Slow into stride, recovered to race 5 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, no daylight until 150M, finished off very strongly thereafter to make frame, a very impressive debut.
Jumped well, raced 2 wide in 6th, 4 lengths back, same position turning, angled out in straight and closed off well without threatening the first few.
Began well, positioned 2 wide in 4th, 2-3 lengths back, travelled well to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead to turn, headed near 200M, dropped off gradually thereafter. (lame left front)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8 lengths back at tail, improved along the rail turning, made reasonable headway in straight to be closest at finish. (Saddle shifted)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide, 8 lengths back at rear, well back at turn, made some progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, difficult to settle near 900M, same position on turn, kept on one-paced in straight.
Fairly away, sent forward to race outside leader in 2nd, same position turning, weakened gradually in straight, never a factor.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 7-8 lengths back at rear, well back on turn, taken widest in straight but made no progress, never competitive.
Slowly away, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, steadied near 800M, under pressure turning, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover at rear, 6-7 lengths back, carried wider turning in, emptied early in straight after hard run took effect.

Jumped fairly from the one draw, settled on rails in 5th within 3L of pace far side improving to 4th coming out and 1L 3rd into home straight, hit the front under pressure over 200 metres out, won readily.
Taken back from a poor draw, waited with on rails, ran on steadily down inside of home straight, nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly from the middle draw, travelled 1L back in 3rd far side, obtained cover around home bend, kept on steadily inside final 200 metres, lost 2nd late.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield, fought on steadily without threatening.
Driven along close up on rails, came to dispute lead rounding home bend, soon faded upon straightening.
Gradually taken towards the rear from the widest gate, similar turning in, made moderate progress under pressure in the run home.
Hard ridden in midfield early, travelled quite wide without cover 2.5L back in 5th, lost position turning in, one-paced.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, settled wide in just worse than midfield, further behind turning for home, fought on past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Ridden to lead one off the rails, joined around home bend, weakened quickly shortly after straightening.
Hard ridden at the back early stages, remained well behind throughout and never seen with a chance.
Towards the rear, snuck up on rails for short-lived impression turning in, soon weakened. (Bled)
Enjoyed a soft trip on the back of the leader along the rails. Finished off well and edged clear after the furlong.
Sent forward and led on the paint. Maintained a sound gallop down the running.
Parked behind midfield, 1 off with cover. Made a forward move near the 600m, and was prominent on the home turn, straightening up 5 deep. Peaked on its effort after the 200m, one paced thereafter.
Slow to begin, settling with backmakers, 2 wide with cover. Got going after the 600m, following the frontrunners. Couldn't sustain effort, tiring late.
Settled midfield the fence, had cover. Kept battling away down the running.
Settled in 2nd position, 1 off no cover. Whacked away at the same speed in the run home.
Settled close to midfield, 2 deep with cover. Started to improve after the 600m, was one paced in the run home.
Travelled worse than midfield, on the rails with cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Went back and settled at the rear on the paint with cover. Swung deep on the home turn but never let down.
Had every hope after settling 1 out 1 back. Disappointed for running near the 500m, was a beaten horse soon after.
Ridden along early but couldn't go the early speed, settling in last position, 1 off with cover. Was under pressure for most of the trip, didn't respond and was never in the hunt.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 2Ls, kept on strongly and scored by a short head.
Pushed forward to settle 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, blocked most straight, dashed strongly for 2nd when clear final 50M, unlucky trip.
Sent forward to settle 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Eased to midfield, 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on well for 4th.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on strongly.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
At rear, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made ground gradually in straight.
Raced worse than midfield, settled 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not able to fish off after disappointing for running 300M.
At rear, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Prominent, settled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide without cover, found nothing when placed under pressure 400M.
Camped handy, however travelled 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened 300M.
Raced midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Pushed to settle midfield, checked badly 1000M, travelled ungenerously thereafter and never looked likely.
At last throughout, never a factor.
Rousted form gate, niggled 1 off with cover 5th, under pump 700m, shifted out & advanced turning in, grinding run to lead 80m, cosily.
Disputed early lead 1 off, led narrowly 740m, headed 600m, shared 2nd & driven 400m, edged lead 200m, headed 80m & boxed on.
Broke well, tracked lead & settled 4th on rail, niggled 570m, driven turning in & shifted out, stayed on to snare 3rd close home.
Broke OK, niggled on rail midfield, driven 6L back 500m & outpaced, 4L back 200m, ran on strongly late to just miss frame.
Outpaced at start & bustled last pair 1 off with cover, switched out 600m, driven 8L back 450m, strong closer centre track.
Tardy start, rolled on rail to press lead 740m, edged lead 600m, 1L clear turning in, all out & headed 200m, plugged on.
Slow start & niggled 1 off near rear, some progress into stretch, ran on under strong drive, shifted off heels 50m, minor inroads.
Fast break & rousted to lead 3 wide no cover, headed 740m & close-up 3rd, vied for 2nd on outer 400m, held but boxed on until faded final 100m.
Driven at break, bustled 1 off with cover midfield, under pump throughout, kept on one pace.
Missed break & rousted initially, raced at tail, switched out & driven 9L back turning in, plugged on for modest headway.
Slow start, rousted to sit rail behind midfield, ridden & outpaced 450m, found nothing & faded tamely.
Tardy break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, struggled on turn & wide, eased at top of stretch when beaten, bled.
Rousted initially, settled handy 1 off with cover, driven 500m & to rail on turn, shifted out 300m, closed off gamely to lead final strides.
Speed to vie for early lead 1 off, shifted to rail 700m & settled close 2nd, led turning in & 2L clear 400m, all out final 200m, faded & mugged late.
Broke well, caught 4 wide no cover handy, smooth progress to loom on turn, shaken up 350m to brief 2nd, soon flattened on run & tapered to wire.
Fair break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, shifted wider & driven 500m, under pump into stretch, stayed on solidly without threatening.
Moderate break, advanced 3 wide with cover to sit 3rd 1 off with cover 650m, driven into stretch, outpaced & plugged on evenly.
Broke OK, bustled but outpaced & drifted back to last pair 600m, 3 wide & driven 500m, stayed on centre track for moderate headway.
Moderate start, soon bustled near rear, mustered to fore of midfield 3 wide with cover, driven wide to 5th 350m, no extra in tepid stretch run.
Broke OK but soon at tail on rail & niggled, shifted 1 off 500m, found little & plugged home one pace.
Mustered to dispute lead on rail 950m, tightened up 700m & shuffled to midfield, driven thereafter, plodded on tamely.
Rousted at break, bustled along on rail midfield, shuffled back & shifted out 600m, hard-ridden until off heels 250m, no extra.
Tardy start, rolled to sit rail behind midfield, snatched off heels 600m & lost ground, hard-ridden but found nothing in stretch run.
Speed early to dispute lead 3 wide, rolled to lead outright 750m, emptied & headed turning in, quickly faded out.
Pushed forward, took rail and led by 0.5L, hung out whilst attempting to slacken the tempo, kicked away 200M to score.
Pushed forward, 2.5Ls behind the slow pace along the fence, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader along the fence, blocked 400M, dashed well despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to take box seat, favoured by the slow sectionals, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 2-3 wide outside the leader, suited by the slow tempo, flattened 250M.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, held ground in straight.
Slow away, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, checked 250M, not properly tested.
Slow away, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, little dash 250M.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased at start, 4.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 400M, ran on ok.
Behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pressed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 300M.
Slow away, never a factor.
Never competitive, tailed out.
Ridden to obtain forward position from wide draw, settling one-back, one-off into back stretch. Started forward move 500m, hit the front 280m, kept on strongly.
Began well but not pushed, settling 3-back in a one-off position. Edged closer turning for home, challenged strongly but unable catch winner.
First out, taken quickly to rail, settling behind leader back stretch. Not much room early in straight, got split 150m and finished off nicely.
Taken across behind runners from awkward draw to sit on fence towards rear. Edged closer final turn, switched out 300m and ran on steadily.
Ridden to hold rail in midfield and allowed to settle back stretch. Switched out for run 450m and ran home steadily between horses.
Ridden along early in 3-wide position around first turn and left without cover entering back stretch. Kept on one-paced in straight.
Began well, racing in midfield close to fence first turn and back stretch. Got shuffled back turning for home but finished off nicely between horses.
Raced wide early before shifting in to find cover before first turn, dropping to rear. Three-wide back stretch, wider into straight, made ground to 200m then one-paced.
Began OK, pressed forward from wide draw racing without cover. Allowed to roll forward to take lead passing 1100m, caught shortly after straightening, kept on till flattened final stages.
Pressed forward initially before being restrained and taken across behind horses at first turn in last position. Became detached from field turning for home before making late ground.
Raced tight to first turn, got close to heels and blundered, dropping to rear in one-off position. Switched out in straight but only one-paced.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw settling at rear. Asked to improve along fence turning for home but found nothing under hard riding.

Began well, pressed forward but wide to lead around first turn, taken to fence 1200m and dropped anchor. Overtaken 1100m, switched out, but under pressure from 600m, giving ground quickly from 400m. (Lame right front leg).
Stayed within striking distance in a strongly run race, advanced to 2nd nearing 400M, led 200M out kept on well to hold off the persistent runner-up.
Held up behind midfield, urged along passing 500M, made steady headway, got up for 2nd 150M and pushed winner all the way to the line.
Dropped back to the rear, 9Ls off the pace in a strongly run race, driven near 600M, stayed on moderately to take 3rd inside 50M, not reached leaders.
Settled behind midfield, roused along 600M out, stayed on for moderate 4th without threatening first two.
Vied for lead on the outside, set lightning pace first 800M, led to 200M out, weakened towards finish.
Switched off to last 9Ls off the pace early stages, taken widest near 500M, stayed on only fairly, no threat to leaders.
Held up towards the rear, moved to a 3-wide position making the home turn, gave limited response turning in, no significant progress.
Slow to begin, held up midfield, failed to pick up entering straight, never threatened.
Driven forward, tracked leaders in a 3-wide position without cover, steadily faded from contention passing 450M.

Close up behind leaders along the fence, came under pressure 700M out and soon hard driven, faltered inside 300M. (Jockey reported that his mount felt short in its action in the latter part of the race.)
Rushed forward, vied for lead, set lightning pace first half, faded nearing 400M, dropped away. (Unacceptable Performance.)
From draw 12 caught very wide in midfield for the first half of the race, weakened making the turn for home, soon left behind. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Stayed close to the pace early stages, came under pressure 1000M and weakened to last, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance.)
