Broke well and quickly into lead, dictated pace until challenged by eventual 2nd entering straight, headed over 300 metres out but fought back steadily to just get up on line.
Jumped moderately, travelled 2-wide in 3rd just over 1L back, moved closer rounding home bend to eventually hit the front passing the 400 metres, unable to sustain effort and pipped at post.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the speed on rails in 2nd and then 3rd from the 1000 metres, switched out to challenge 300 metres, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.

Jumped moderately, settled in 2.5L 4th early before tightened and dropped to 3L 5th approaching home bend, remained same on rails into straight, produced good late impression. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Soon found itself in rear of small field, remained in last most of way, fought his way past one well-beaten runner close to home.
Began moderately, settled in 5th of six-horse field far side becoming 4th rounding home bend, one-paced in straight.
Handed up and box seated after the 900m. Fended of challenge for most of the straight to record grinding win.
Settled 2nd, 1 off no cover. Maintained a good gallop down the running, but couldn't find an extra gear.
Parked midfield, 2 deep with cover. Finished off gamely.
Ridden along early, only managed to settle 3rd from the rear on the paint with cover. Closed off soundly.
Raced behind midfield the fence, had cover. Caught up in traffic approaching the home turn, made good ground late.
Camped 4th 1 off with cover. Was one paced in the straight, weakening over the final 150m.
Posted 3 wide without cover on the circle, behind midfield. Made no impression in the home stretch.
Worked forward to cross and lead on the fence after the 900m. Was gassed in the straight.
Settled 2nd last from a wide gate, 1 off with cover. Peeled out after the 600m, didn't go on with it and only plodded home.
Raced worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Was dour in the home stretch.
Travelled 3 back the fence early, before drifting back to race midfield on the bend. Was a beaten horse before the home turn.
Settled in last position, close to the rail with cover. Failed to pass another runner despite rider's efforts after the 800m.
Camped handy, settled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the slow pace, ran on strongly to score by a head.
Pushed to settle midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite hampered by the slow sectionals, dashed well for 2nd.
Bumped start, then settle midfield 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Began awkwardly, then settled 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow pace, finished off nicely to get 4th.
Settled worse than midfield about 6.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, ran on steadily.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slow sectionals, kept on until final 200M weakened. (Lame left fore)
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader, despite benefited by the slow pace, finished off only fairly. (Questioned for riding, see incident report)
Ridden forward to settle 1L off the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the slow pace, kept on one pace to the line.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow sectionals, unable to finish off.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, found nothing in straight.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the slow pace, flattened soon after straightening.
Broke OK, camped rail midfield, shaken up 500m, stretch progress sunder hard drive, angled out 300m, led 170m, clear & jinked close home.
Tardy start, raced 1 off with cover midfield, shifted 4 wide turning in, shaken up 400m, stayed on dourly to edge 2nd.
Tardy start, rolled to dispute lead 1000m, soon settled 1 off no cover 2nd, ridden 530m, boxed on evenly, no match for winner, just lost 2nd.
Speedy break to dispute lead, nudged to outright lead 900m, 1L clear & shaken up 400m, all out & headed 170m, tapered closing stages.
Smart start, settled 3 wide with cover midfield, ridden turning in, kept on & switched wider 320m, plugged home evenly.
Broke OK, slotted rail behind midfield & niggled along, shifted 1 off 650m, driven 530m, kept on soundly without threatening.
Slow start, raced 1 off with cover near tail, 6L back & driven 500m, shifted wide final turn, stayed on widest for solid late headway.
Fast start, disputed lead early, soon settled 1 back on fence, under pump 450m, all out 300m, outpaced & plugged on moderately.
Broke OK, taken back to race 1 off with cover near rear, bustled along, driven 430m, kept on but never a factor.
Smart start, caught 3 wide no cover 4th, shaken up turning in, emptied 250m & weakened out.
Dropped back at break, to tail 850m & soon 2L detached, hard-ridden turning in, kept on same speed in tame run to wire.
Taken to rail at tail, soon rolled forward a spot, under pump into stretch, found nothing & folded tamely.
Broke OK, settled midfield 1 off with cover, checked off heels 800m, shifted out & shaken up 400m, closed strongly & led 125m, drew clear.
Sharp start to lead, headed 1250m & raced close 2nd, shaken up on inner & quickened to lead 300m, extended but all out & headed 125m.
Bustled at break and handy, settled back 3 wide no cover midfield, shifted wider & ridden 500m, plugged on evenly to make frame.
Dropped in at tail on rail, advanced a spot 800m, shifted out & ridden 430m, stayed on soundly to just miss frame.
Good break, sat handy 4th 1 back on rail, driven turning in, outpaced but plugged on dourly.
Moderate break, overraced early 1 off behind midfield, off heels & shuffled back 800m, shaken up 300m, stayed on dourly.
Broke well wide & led 1 off 1250m, driven 400m but limited response, headed 300m & weakened in run home.
Missed break, settled rail near rear, driven 430m & shifted out, crowded 250m, boxed on evenly.
Moderate start, sat 3 wide with cover behind midfield, forced wide & driven turning in, checked off heels 400m & hampered rival, plugged tamely.
Slow break, overraced early & dropped in near rear 3 wide with cover, widest & driven turning in, hampered slightly 300m, tepid run thereafter.
Tardy start & niggled along in rear 1 off, driven 500m, shifted out into stretch, found little in tame run to wire.
Smart start & handy early, settled midfield 1 off with cover, 3 wide for progress 500m, driven but found nil in tepid stretch run.
Moderate start, raced rail midfield, shifted 1 off 650m & soon ridden along, struggled & faded in run home.
Broke OK, rolled wide to slot 3rd 1 off with cover 950m, niggled 800m & soon driven along, emptied 300m & faded weakly.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L, clocked fast sectionals, kicked away 300M to score.
Hard ridden but failed to muster in order to cross in front, trapped 3 wide, 2Ls off the fast pace, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace but trapped 3-4 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 3rd.
Midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, suited by the fast pace, lack room 400M, made ground 200M without threat.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast pace, just held ground.
Eased back and took rail, 8Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast tempo, made some ground 250M.
Slow away, 6Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Bumped start, 8Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, raced keenly, suited by the fast pace, made good ground 150M.
Eased at start, 9Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the fast tempo 2 wide, ran on until 250M flattened.
Hard ridden forward, 1L off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, reduced 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, flattened 200M.
2Ls off the fast pace along the fence, soon weakened 400M.
At back, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Began OK, pressed forward between horses settling one-back, one-off before getting close to heels 900m and eased. Clear run in straight, picked up speed 250m, ran on strongly to win close home.
Began well, ridden along inside leader to 1300m when crossed. Raced outside leader when paced slackened, then taken to rail around turn. Rolled forward 400m, looked winner 200m, run down.
Hard ridden from widest draw to lead on settling, crossing to rail 1300m and slowed tempo. Kicked clear nearing 1000m, still in front 200m, run down final stages.
Broke well, scrubbed up inside leaders to grab rail but hampered 1300m when pace slowed. Crowded for room turning for home, kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began awkwardly, dropping to rear before making ground 3-wide back stretch. Swung wide into straight and finished off nicely.
Hampered start, mustered between horses to sit just behind midfield at turn. Kept on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Began well, ridden along ahead of midfield close to fence before hampered 1300m. Hampered again 900m. Made ground along fence early in straight before turning one-paced.
Began OK, not rushed, settling towards rear in one-off position. Switched wide entering straight and ran on fairly under hard riding.
Steadied shortly after start dropping to near last but away from fence. Inconvenienced 1300m when pace slackened. Very wide in straight, kept on one-paced.
Ridden along early to find cover, cutting in to one-off position behind midfield. Rolled forward 3-wide approaching turn, taken wider in straight, steadied 300m when run closed. No extra.
Outpaced and soon at rear, then hampered 1300m when pace slackened. Hampered again when making ground at turn, but one-paced in straight. (Lame right front)
Began fairly, not pressured, slipping back along rail towards rear. Hampered approaching turn, stayed on fence in straight, one-paced.
Began awkwardly, ridden to obtain forward position but wide, checked and lost ground 1300m. Raced without cover thereafter, giving ground quickly.
Hampered start, mustered along rail to sit at midfield. Hampered again turning for home losing position, before tiring in straight. Not ridden out final stages.
Set even pace, waited with until 250M, shook off pursuers to win with something in hand.
Taken back, held up near the rear 4Ls off the pace, stayed on moderately between horses, got up for 2nd just before line but never a serious threat to winner.
Reserved in midfield, responded well to go 2nd 200M out, unable to get closer to winner, run peaked 100M and lost 2nd near line.
Settled 3Ls behind the pace, guided to center of track for his challenge, kept on moderately for non-threatening 4th.
Outpaced early stages, fell back to rear 4-5Ls off the pace in middle stages, closed off well final 300M over this shorter trip.
Settled in midfield, nudged along midway, kept on same pace past weakening rivals.
Hampered at the start, ended up further back than usual, driven halfway but stayed on only fairly.
Close up, unable to keep up with leaders halfway, soon weakened out of contention.
Checked at the start, settled towards the rear 4-5Ls off the pace, inclined to hang in for the majority of the race, ran on one paced final 300M.
Up with pace along the stand's rail, lacked further response passing 300M, weakened towards finish. (Bled.)
Always prominent, found disappointingly little when urged inside 400M, soon weakened.
Strode forward, up there with leaders, driven along near 400M, outpaced and no extra passing 200M.
Badly hampered at the start, ended up behind midfield along the stands' rail, shaken up 400M but failed to make significant progress, awkward placed final stages and not ridden out.
Proved difficult to settle, raced right up with leaders, outpaced and weakened rapidly over final 350M.
Began well, allowed to stride forward settling one-back, one-off into turn. Began run on straightening, hit front 200m, pulled clear while laying in under pressure.
Jumped OK, not pressed, settling 3-back along fence. Switched out to make run 500m, looked chance 200m, kept on well.
Broke well, no early speed but quickly taken to rail. Got inside run on straightening, ran home strongly switching out final stages for clear running.
Began best, led on settling, before allowing another to go forward but holding rail. Kicked strongly entering straight, co-leader 200m, kept on well till swamped last few strides.
Ridden along to hold rail behind leader to turn. Saved ground turn, kept on well behind horses in straight shifting in 150m and then shifting out 50m.
Broke well, pressed forward to lead from 900m but in one-off position. Joined up front 200m before giving ground gradually. Bumped and unbalanced 50m.
Taken across behind horses soon after start to sit at rear in 3-wide position. Taken out and bumped 400m, widest in straight, ran on steadily under whip.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit 3–wide in second tier behind leader. Taken wider in straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
No early seed and held between horses towards the rear. Taken out turning for home and kept on fairly in straight.
Caught flat-footed at start, taken to fence but soon detached from field in last place. Tagged on turning for home, shifted out abruptly 400m, kept on one-paced.
Began fairly, ridden along to sit behind midfield but away from fence. Lost position turning for home and found little in straight under hard riding.
Slow into stride, ridden to make ground but failed to muster and held wide behind midfield. Failed to settle entering turn and no response when popped the question.
Pressed forward racing 3-wide to turn without cover. Under pressure from 600m, giving ground gradually from 500m. Not ridden out final stages.
Hard ridden from widest draw to go forward, sitting 4-wide without cover outside leading bunch. Spent force on entering straight.
Jumped well, raced prominently on rail in 2nd, easy run to turn, showed good turn of foot to kick clear 300M, safely held rivals to score comfortably.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, unchallenged to turn, headed near 300M, kept on well to get 2nd.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, travelled well to turn, closed off well in straight but never a threat to the first two.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, similar position to turn, finished off strongly down outside to make frame.
Slowly away as usual, raced 6 lengths back on rail at rear, niggled along the rail to turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide in 4th, 1-2 lengths back, same position to turn, failed to quicken up in straight, just stayed on evenly.

Jumped well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with cover, 2-3 lengths back in front of midfield, steadied near 1000M, similar position turning, made ground to 200M but no extra thereafter.
Jumped with them, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, still well back turning, made reasonable headway in straight but never looked lively.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 4-5 lengths back, similar position turning, angled out in straight but unable to make progress to be competitive.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race on rail in 5th, 2-3 lengths back, saved ground turning, weakened gradually in straight, never a factor.
Jumped well from the widest draw but unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover in 3rd, a length or so back, still 3 wide turning, bumped near 500M, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, under pressure turning, showed no response and was a beaten horse early in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 4-5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, same position turning, failed to close off in straight. (Mucopus in trachea)
Jockey retired the horse out of the race shortly after the start. (See racing incidents) (Lame left front next day)

Moderately away from a tricky gate, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, outside leader, travelled well to turn, took the lead near 250M, stuck on bravely to hold off the late challenger and scored narrowly.
Jumped well, raced 3 wide with cover in front of midfield, 3-4 lengths back, improved on turn, closed off very well in straight to take 2nd.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently on rail in 3rd, easy run to turn, kept on well in straight to take 3rd without threatening the first two.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed an easy lead to turn, headed 250M and weakened gradually, but still able to hold off the late challengers to make frame.
A shade tardy, recovered to race 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, made run turning, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Began well, positioned 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, kept to inside in straight and finished off fairly without showing extra gear.
Bumped start, positioned 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4-5 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths back, difficult to settle after 1000M and blundered badly near 900M, well back on turn, made some headway in straight but never a threat.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 4 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground turning, angled out in straight but finished off only fairly.
Crowded out start, raced 6-7 lengths back at tail, shifted out sharply near 900M, 3 wide with cover turning, made no progress after straightening, finished off one-paced.
Began fairly from a wide draw, severely hampered 1100M, raced 3 wide without cover thereafter, a length back, weakened gradually after turning in.
Taken back from the widest draw, severely checked and carried out 1100M, lost a considerable amount of ground, was set an impossible task thereafter. (See racing incidents.)
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in 5th, 2 lengths back, under pressure turning, emptied early in straight and dropped out. (Irregular heart rhythm & lame right front next day)

Placing: PU
Comment: Crowded out start, broke down near 1100M.

Given reminders when just off the pace, commenced to make ground coming onto course proper, switched out for a run passing the 300 metres, hit the front inside the 100 metres.
Well there, gained narrow advantage over 350 metres out, unable to sustain effort and headed inside the 100 metres.
Settled just off the pace near the centre of the track with cover, came to challenge inside final 200 metres, finished off race well.
Always well there, kept on until finding no extra closing stages.
Close up racing down the centre of the track, unable to sustain effort inside final 80 metres.
Always well there on stands rails, failed to quicken under pressure in the run home.
Jumped slowly, remained in last few to halfway, fought on steadily under pressure, did best work late.
Jostled with runners and unbalanced jumping out, settled just off midfield most of way, made moderate progress closing stages.
Bumped and unbalanced at start, shared the pace most of way to 400 metres, faded gradually.
Slow out, lacked early pace, kept on under pressure past well-beaten runners in the run home.
Jumped fairly, lacked pace, soon dropped well behind.
Jostled at start, settled just off the pace, faded under pressure inside final 300 metres.
Tightened and lost ground at start, settled just off the pace, faded gradually from over 300 metres out. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Jumped awkwardly, travelled just worse than midfield early stages, gradually faded under pressure after coming onto course proper.
Shared the lead 2 off the outside rail. Shot clear near the 300m, but was tiring late, managed to fend off late challenge.
Vied for leading duties on the grandstand side rail. Was easily headed after the 400m, but rallied late to finish off well.
Raced prominently, 3 off the stands rail with cover. kept up an even gallop in the run to the line, only maintaining its ground.
Parked behind midfield, 1 off the outside rail. Finished off well drifting in to the middle of the track after the 500m.
Camped midfield, 3 off the outside rail, had cover. Only plodded to the post.
Raced closer to the center of the course, near the rear of the field. Made fair ground, in the run to the line.
Settled midfield, 4-5 from the stands rail. Drifted towards the middle of the track after the 400m, didn't find a lot when asked for an effort.
Tracked the speed, 1 off the stands rail. Was giving ground after the furlong.
Travelled well back in the field, closer to the grandstand side, had cover. Was one paced towards the finish.
Travelled midfield, closer to the far side, no cover. Failed to make any appreciable ground in the run to the line.
Raced worse than midfield the near side, had cover. Was a beaten horse before the 400m.
Settled a long last closer the near side. Passed a few tiring runners.
Raced prominently towards the stands side no cover. began to yield ground near the 450m.
Settled behind midfield with cover. Commenced to give ground a long way from home and finished well back.
Prominent, settled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow pace, dashed strongly to score with plenty in hand.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, kept on nicely for 2nd, winner too good.
Raced midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Camped handy, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, benefited by the slow pace, kept on steadily for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, hampered by the slow sectionals, kept on one pace to the line.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Take back to rear, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, never ran on.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by a short head at slow sectionals, hung on until 300M weakened.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Prominent, despite benefited by the slow pace, flattened badly 300M.
Bustled at break, camped rail midfield, shifted 1 off 850m for progress, crowded on turn, 4 wide into stretch & quickened to lead 380m, drew clear.
Slow start, niggled early, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, shifted 3 wide for progress 850m, 5 wide & outpaced turning in, stayed on to snag 2nd.
Moderate start, raced rail behind midfield, shifted out 600m, very wide into stretch & driven, closed off to snare 3rd at wire.
Smart start, ridden to settle 1 off 1 back, left without cover 1000m & rolled 2nd 850m, pressed lead on turn, boxed on, edged out of frame late.
Broke OK, bustled initially to settle 1 off with cover fore of midfield, shifted wide & driven turning in, kept on evenly.
Fast break, soon led & to rail, headed 1180m & stalked 1 back on inner, driven turning in, plugged on one pace.
Led from gate, soon restrained to rail 1 back, shuffled back a spot 1000m, shifted 1 off 600m, driven 500m, boxed on until flattened out final 150m.
No early pace, raced last pair initially, rolled 3 wide no cover to behind midfield, ridden 640m, never a factor in tame run home.
Slow start, raced last pair 1 off, last & driven turning in, plodded home weakly.
Missed break, sat rail & soon to tail, under pump 600m, struggled in weak run to the wire.
Smart break wide to race close 2nd 1 off, rolled to lead 1180m & to rail, pressed 480m, headed turning in & weakened tamely.
Good break, rousted initially & niggled on rail to dispute 3rd 6L back, driven & shifted out into stretch, grinding advance to lead close home.
Fast start, niggled along in 2nd 5L back, ridden to close 400m, led 170m, all out & headed inside final 50m.
Bustled at start, eventually disputed 3rd 1 off no cover, under pump 500m, closed dourly to claim 3rd late.
Taken back from wide gate to 1 off near rear, 11L back into final turn, shifted wide on turn & driven, solid closer to 4th late.
Moderate start, raced near tail, wide into stretch & hard-ridden, stayed on for minor gains centre track.
Pace to soon scoot 5L clear, nursed into stretch, 2L clear & shaken up 250m, bottomed out & headed 170m, faded thereafter.
Broke well, soon outpaced & niggled along 1 off behind midfield, under pump into stretch, plodded on one pace.
Taken behind from wide gate, ridden along at tail, plugged on for moderate headway centre track.
Bustled to race rail midfield, driven 420m, plugged home same speed.
Broke well & rousted, caught 4 wide no cover, back to 1 off fore of midfield 650m, driven home turn, soon emptied out.
Slow start, recovered to rail behind midfield, under pump turning in, found nothing, eased when beaten.
Tardy start, rolled to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, hard-ridden into stretch, found nothing & faded to tail.
Pushed to keep close to the front runners, 3Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M, drifted away 200M to score.
Behind midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, checked 1200M, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to share the lead at fast sectionals, led 400M, soon overhauled 300M, ran on well for 3rd.
Pushed forward but failed to cross, trapped 3 wide no cover outside and just off the leaders, harmed by the fast sectionals, ran on ok.
Eased to rear, 6.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, just ran on ok.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders, favoured by the fast tempo, but trapped 3-4 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 6.5Ls off the leaders, suited by the fast pace but trapped 4 wide throughout, no progress.
Pushed forward and shared the lead, clocked fast sectionals, soon reduced 350M.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders along the rails, suited by the fast tempo, emptied 300M.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the leaders on the fence, harmed by the fast pace, dropped off quickly 400M.
Never competitive, tailed out.
Broke well but quickly left rail to race in one-off position behind leader. Began forward move 500m, hit front 300m and pulled clear, one-paced final stages, just held.
Badly crowded out start, dropping to near rear but well away from fence. Switched widest turning for home and finished off strongly to just miss.
Jumped well, ridden to maintain forward position between leaders moving to fence entering turn. Got inside run in straight, looked chance 200m, boxed on but no extra.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear of field. Took inside run entering straight, finished off nicely while shifting out closing stages.
Began fairly, taken gradually to fence, saved ground turn, ran on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Jumped with field, ridden along early, settling one-back, one-off before turn. Looked chance top of straight but gave ground from 200m.
Ridden along to obtain forward position and trapped wide without cover. Raced tightly around turn, swung wide into straight, kept on one-paced.
No early pace, settling along fence towards the rear. Improved position around turn, stayed on fence in straight, one-paced.
Jumped awkwardly, slow into stride, hard ridden but failed to muster and became detached from field. Last into straight, ran past beaten horses.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling, cutting in to rail before turn. Collared shortly after entering straight and weakened. (Lame left front. Unacceptable performance)
Bumped and unbalanced start, recovered and ridden forward between horses to sit behind pace makers. Raced tightly around turn gave ground gradually in straight.
Began fairly, not pressed and taken in at rear of field in one-off position. Got further back turning for home and never likely.
Travelled strongly in midfield, advanced to challenge passing 450M, picked up well and gained the lead 200M, drove clear.
Near the rear early stages, moved closer to midfield entering back-straight but raced keenly, stayed on to go 2nd 50M out but no impression on winner.
Slotted into a 3-wide position ahead of midfield, within striking distance turning home, had every chance in straight but failed to seriously kick on, stayed on for non-threatening 3rd.
Chased leaders in 2nd flight, ranged into contention with a 3-wide move home turn, briefly led nearing 200M, unable to sustain run final stages.
From draw 1 took up a prominent position just behind leaders, had no clear run mid-straight, checked 200M, rebalanced and stayed on towards the finish.
Began only fairly, settled near last not hurried, swung out to challenge 450M, closed off mildly.
Prompted the pace in a 2-wide position throughout, briefly led turning home, headed inside 250M, weakened towards finish.
Settled behind midfield 4-5Ls off the pace, had to be pushed along 500M out, kept on past beaten rivals.
Eased back to the rear, was always well off the rail, swung wider home turn, failed to pick up.
Went forward, shared lead on the inside, faded out of contention passing 400M.
Raced along the 3-path in midfield, kept on same pace in straight, never troubled leaders.
Held up midfield along the inside, failed to pick up the pace when driven 400M, never involved.
Caught wide early stages before slotting into a 3-wide position towards the rear, came up empty entering straight.
Driven forward, caught 3-wide no cover in the front rank, became badly unbalanced in action 700M out, eased out of the race.

Broke well to soon join the leaders, quickened well to hit front passing 400 metres winning readily.
Jumped fairly, soon taken to stands side to settle just off the heels of the leading trio, came to challenge under pressure inside final 400 metres, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield gradually crossing to stands rails at halfway, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Given reminders early stages, settled just off the pace in 5th, switched in off stands rails for a run nearer the centre of the track, kept on steadily under pressure without quickening.
Jumped moderately, settled behind midfield, finished off race well under pressure inside final 200 metres, did best work late.
Broke well from the best draw, held narrow advantage on stands rails until hanging in 400 metres out, soon headed and swamped inside final 200 metres. (Bled)
Jumped fairly from the innermost draw, settled at about midfield, found nothing in the run home.
Jumped fairly, gradually settled behind midfield, made no impression in the run home.
Began awkwardly losing ground, raced wide without cover behind midfield near the centre of the track, found nothing.
Disputed lead racing keenly at times, faded gradually inside final 350 metres.
Began awkwardly losing ground, soon dropped well behind and never seen with a chance.
Jumped moderately, soon tailed-off, never seen with a chance.
Rolled forward from a wide gate to settle outside the leader. Edged forward after the furlong to record a sound win.
Settled 4th on the fence, a couple of lengths back from the leader. Held on narrowly in the run to the post.
Raced worse than midfield the paint. Ran on smartly over the final 100m.
Settled 3rd last, 1 off with cover. Was carted wide on the circle racing 4 deep. Swung deepest on the home turn, closed off reasonably, was inclined to hang in over the final 200m.
Led narrowly on the fence. Commenced to yield ground approaching the 200m.
Travelled 4th from the rear, 1 off with cover. Made some ground in the run home without threatening.
Settled 3rd 1 off with cover. Straightened four deep, was one paced in the run to the line.
Camped close to midfield, 1 off with cover. Got tired over the final 200m.
Didn't enjoy the easiest of passages during running settling at the rear on the rails. Only plodded to the line.
Parked midfield, 3 deep with cover. Was well beaten at the furlong.
Went back from a wide gate and settled 1 off with cover, towards the rear. Raced keenly on the circle travelling 3 wide with cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Raced in 5th position early posted 3 deep without cover on the circle. Commenced to drift back near the 500m, and tailed out.
Rolled forward to settle 2Ls behind the leader, benefited by the track that favors front runners, ran on strongly to score by 1.5Ls.
Raced midfield, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the track that favors front runners, dashed well for 2nd.
Ridden forward to take the lead along the fence by 2Ls, benefited by the track which favors front runners, hung on nicely to get 3rd.
Camped handy, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the track which favors front runners, ran on steadily.
Prominent, settled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the track that favors front runners, kept on steadily.
At rear, travelled 10Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the track that favors front runners, ran on only fairly.
Eased back to rear, settled 10.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the track that favors front runners, ran on fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the track that favors front runners, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield, 9Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the track that favors front runners, never a factor.
Raced midfield, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the track that favors front runners, unable to run on.
Taken back from wide gate, settled 9.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, hampered by the track that favors front runners, never ran on.
Broke well, settled back midfield on rail, shifted out 540m, shaken up 400m to vie for lead 200m, led outright 150m & edged clear.
Smart start, dropped in 1 off fore of midfield, shifted 3 wide 900m, wider into stretch & driven to dispute lead 220m, headed 150m, held in run.
Dropped back to race 1 off near rear, shifted out on turn, driven 420m, closed off soundly to snare 3rd on nod.
Fast break, rolled wide to 2nd 1 off no cover, ridden to lead 400m, all out & challenged for lead 220m, headed 200m, tapered & lost 3rd at wire.
Good break, bustled early to sit 3 wide no cover handy, under pump 520m, outpaced into stretch but & plugged on evenly.
Fair break, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, shifted out 550m, driven turning in, stayed on for minor inroads.
Sluggish start, bustled early 3 wide, checked off heels & to tail 1050m, soon slotted rail & rolled forward a spot, stayed on moderately in stretch.
Speed to lead, set tempo on fence, driven turning in, under pressure & headed 400m, tapered in run home.
Broke well, chased pace 1 off with cover, driven turning in, found little & weakened in run.
Broke well, posted 3 wide with cover midfield, shunted 4 wide 900m & lost place, wider into stretch, plodded on one pace.
Smart start & overraced initially 1 back on rail, every chance & driven 375m but found little & faded in tepid run home.
Missed break, bustled to sit rail behind midfield, bustled 500m, crowded 370m, driven but plugged on tamely.
Broke OK, initially 3 wide midfield but soon dropped to rear, driven into stretch, unable to quicken, never a factor.
Missed break, raced wide with cover near rear, driven 500m, found little & last turning in, tailed off.
Fast start to lead & crossed to rail, extended into stretch, shaken up 340m scooted clear for easy win.
Smart start, tracked 1 back on rail, switched out 370m & shaken up, outpaced by winner, boxed on well but unable to close.
Snagged from wide to sit 3 deep midfield, ridden wide home turn, closed to 3rd 200m, flattened out late but just held on to make frame.
Fast start, dropped to 1 off with cover fore of midfield, caught behind horses into stretch, shaken up 330m, stayed on but just held for 3rd.
Steady start, camped 1 off behind midfield, hard-driven & switched wide into stretch, ran on centre track for minor headway.
Tardy break, niggled along on fence fore of midfield, under pump 430m, plugged on one pace.
Broke OK, caught wide & bustled forward, impeded rival when crossed to race at leader's flank 880m, found little & faded in stretch.
Tardy break, niggled to sit midfield on inner, ridden 450m, stayed on evenly until checked off heels 150m, plugged on to wire.
Slow start, raced 2nd last, shifted wide into stretch, found nothing, plodded on past fading rivals.
Broke OK, soon niggled near rear, hard-driven into stretch, found nothing, plodded home past beaten runners.
Missed break & detached, rousted to settle at tail, hard-ridden home turn, plugged on in tepid run.
Decent start wide, slotted 3 wide with cover midfield, driven 500m, found little & weakened tamely.
Ridden at break, niggled 3 wide no cover behind lead, clipped heels 880m, lost a spot, handy when shaken up 430m, soon weakened.
Started OK & soon 1 back 1 off, checked off heels 1200m, raced handy, driven turning in, soon outpaced, struggled & eased.
In front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader 3 wide, made early move 600M, dashed well 400M to score.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the track that favours front runners, ran on well for 2nd.
Settled in a more prominent spot, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the track that favours front runners, closed off strongly for 3rd.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the track that favours front runners, dashed well 300M.
Box seat, benefited by the track that favours front runners, lack room 300M, just held ground when clear.
Hold rail in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the track that favours front runners, little dash 250M.
Slow away and bumped, 5.5Ls off the leader on the rails, not suited by the track that favours front runners, little dash 200M.
In front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the track that favours front runners, lack turn of foot.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1.5Ls, benefited by the track that favours front runners, flattened 250M.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, lost ground 700M, checked 650M, not suited by the track that favours front runners, just held ground.
At rear, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the track that favours front runners, ran on ok.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, hampered 650M, not suited by the track that favours front runners, no progress.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the track that favours front runners, emptied 300M.

Placing: UR
Comment: Eased back, trapped wide, rider dislodged 650M.
Broke well, pressed forward crossing to outer rail passing 800m, put under intense pressure 200m but kept kicking to score narrow victory.
Crowded for room start, pressed forward, switching out to obtain cover behind leaders. Revved up 400m, issued strong challenge from 200m, just failed.
Jumped OK, not pressured settling midfield in one-off position from grandstand fence, Shaken up 400m, switched in off heels 300m, kept on steadily.
Away well, crossed to outer fence 2L from leader. Put under pressure 400m out and kept on steadily to the line.
Jumped well, racing alongside leader until 300m when began to give ground gradually.
Began OK, restrained and taken to outside fence behind runners. Began forward move passing 400m, doing best work final 200m.
Lost ground start, switched in from outer fence when crossed 800m. Switched in further passing 400m and ran on fairly between horses.
Began OK, taken to outer fence but got shuffled back to near rear. Under hard riding from 400m and under whip 250m but only one-paced.
Crowded for room at start, ridden to maintain forward position, settling behind leaders. Put under pressure but started to give ground passing 300m.
Began OK, ridden along down centre track behind midfield. Under whip entering course proper but found nothing and faded. Not ridden out final stages.
Jumped with field, restrained and taken to outer fence behind runners in last place. Never in contention.
Settled behind midfield, looked one paced early straight but picked up strongly when shifted out into clear 250M, led nearing 100M, well in control.
Dropped back to a rearward position, taken out to challenge 450M, stayed on well to go 2nd near line, not reached winner.
Driven to the front from wide barrier, was given a breather turning for home, kept on evenly to line, not pace of first two final 100M.
Caught wide from wide barrier, taken back for cover, in last place 6Ls off the pace turning in, stayed on steadily for non-threatening 4th.
Stayed within striking distance from leaders, saved ground on inside throughout, kept on same pace over final 300M.
Began well, restrained to sit 2-3Ls behind leaders, responded well early straight and briefly went 2nd 250M, unable to sustain run final 150M.
Patiently ridden, near the rear 5Ls off the pace turning in, hampered when making his challenge near 300M, kept on past weakening rivals.
Towards the rear and no closer than 3-wide, swung widest for home, made limited progress only.
Forwardly placed, tracked leader to straight, failed to pick up, weakened over final 200M.
Began awkwardly, caught 3-wide no cover behind leaders, moved up to a striking spot 400M, brief effort before fading 250M out.
Held up in mid-division, niggled along halfway round the home bend, found little when placed under maximum pressure entering straight. (Blood in trachea.)
Unable to slot in from wide barrier, caught 4-wide no cover throughout, weakened passing 400M.
Began well, pushed forward from wide draw to sit on behind leader passing 800m. Taken out entering straight, shaken up 300m, started to kick from 150m, hit front 100m and held off late challenge.
Replated before start. Bumped, unbalanced shortly after start, ridden forward settling 5th but away from fence. Revved up entering straight, switched in passing 200m, ran on strongly.
Broke well, quickly in front and set good pace. Swung wide into straight, kept on well till collared 100m, boxed on.
Began well, ridden along to stay with pace, switching in to rail. Saved ground turn, had clear run in straight, kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began awkwardly, got close to heels and shuffled back, racing between horses 5L from leader. Took closer order turning for home, 5-wide into straight, kept on fairly.
Pressed forward from wide draw and trapped 3-wide without cover behind front-runners. Kept on steadily early in straight turning one-paced final stages.
Began OK, ridden along to hold rail grabbing box seat behind leader. Shuffled 3-back before turn, stayed on fence and kept on steadily in straight.
Jumped with field, restrained and taken closer to fence, settling towards rear between horses. Ran on steadily in straight, switching out 250m to get clear running.
Crowded out and lost ground start, taken quickly to fence four back from leader. Switched out entering straight and boxed on one-paced.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling along fence in last position. Taken out turning for home, had to switched out 300m to get run, kept on one-paced.
Ridden along early though unable to cross and held 3-wide. Steadied 900m when crossed, raced greenly several times, faded.
Began fairly, restrained and taken in to fence though refused to settle for some distance. Turned very wide into straight and found little under hard riding.
Began OK, taken in behind horses to rail, settling in last pair. Stayed on fence around turn but found nothing when asked in straight.
Began fairly, ridden but didn't muster and trapped 3-wide. Rolled forward passing 1000m to within 3L of leader, then tired and finished tailed off. (Unacceptable performance).
Jumped well from the widest draw, sent forward to take the lead until 800M, travelled well and positioned in 2nd on turn, regained the lead 400M, kicked clear to score by 3/4 length.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position turning, angled out early in straight and finished off well to get 2nd without threatening the winner.
Slowly away, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back, taken widest after turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to be nearest on line.
Moderately away from an awkward gate, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4-5 lengths back, same position turning, made reasonable ground in straight to make frame.
Crowded out start, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 5-6 lengths back, same position turning, in traffic early in straight, finished off well when clear final 200M.
Began well, showed early speed to race prominently in 4th, 2 lengths back, angled out turning, closed off evenly final 300M but lacked extra gear to figure.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide in 5th, 2-3 lengths back, difficult to settle near 1400M, similar position turning, finished off evenly in straight but lacked usual close.
Began well from a wide draw, taken back to race at tail, 7-8 lengths back, still well back turning, taken wider in straight and made some headway from an impossible set.
Began well, raced 3 lengths or so back on rail in midfield, gradually improved along the rail on turn, peaked near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slowly away, showed no early speed, raced 6-7 lengths back on rail at rear, well back turning, just passed some tired runners in straight.
Jumped with them, unable to slot in, positioned 3 wide without cover in 3rd pressed on to take the lead 800M, shared front turning, emptied early in straight and dropped out gradually.
Moderately away, sent forward to race prominently on rail in 2nd, under pressure turning, showed no response and dropped out tamely in straight.
Average to begin, failed to muster early speed, raced 5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, similar position turning, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out.

Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover, 3-4 lengths back, 3 wide with no cover on turn, failed to close off in straight after hard run took effect, finished tailed out.

Began moderately, made good use of low gate to settle on rails in midfield or just worse, saved ground on rails turning in, finished off race nicely to assert authority closings stages.
Attempted to make all setting a steady pace, driven down the centre of track upon straightening, unable to sustain effort and caught by fast-finishing winner on rails close home.
Moderate start, settled in forward of midfield, saved ground on inside turning in, kept on steadily without quickening.
Always thereabouts, unable to sustain run on rails inside final 200 metres.
In touch to straight, faded gradually.

Began from a poor draw, soon dropped to last few while wide despite ridden along, came under pressure approaching home turn when widest dropping to last, ran on past well-beaten horses inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, gradually settled wide in rear of midfield, dropped further back around home bend, made moderate progress early in straight. (Tactic questioned.)
Never better than midfield, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Niggled along from the widest gate, raced wide throughout far side and around the bend in midfield, soon faded in home straight.
Soon taken back and across from a poor draw for rails run, ridden to join rear of field before racing keenly towards midfield, found nothing under pressure in straight.
Never far off to straight, faded gradually.
Soon dropped well behind despite niggled at early stages, never on terms.
Stalked the leader on the fence. Peeled out turning for home and made a late bid to win narrowly.
Dictated terms on the rails. Held a 2 length advantage at the furlong, fought on gamely but was nailed on the post.
Raced forward of midfield, on the paint with cover. Maintained a sound gallop in the home stretch.
Went back from the outside gate, racing worse than midfield on the rails with cover. Made good ground in the run to the wire.
Effectively raced 1 out 1 back. Was one paced in the final stretch.
Went forward from a wide alley, parked outside the leader. Faded over the final furlong.
Settled towards the rear, 1 off with cover. Made steady progress in the home straight.
Crowded at the start travelling midfield the fence. Made only fair ground in the run to the line.
Travelled worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Kept on at the same speed down the running.
Raced on the fence with cover in last position. Kept to the inside in the run home, made some ground on tiring horses.
Settled 5th, 3 deep without cover. Was under pressure well before the home turn but failed to respond, tiring early in the stretch.
Parked just ahead of midfield, 1 off with cover. Was a beaten horse early in the straight, giving ground quickly after the 250m.
Couldn't go the early speed of the race, eventually settled well back in the run, 3 deep with cover. Was never in the hunt finishing well back.
Settled midfield 3 deep with cover. Struggled in the straight and finished tailed out. (To trial). Vet reported mildly lame Left fore leg.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on strongly to score by 1/2L.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader, ran on nicely until final 50M weakened for 2nd.
Pushed along to settle in midfield, 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, dashed well for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed strongly in straight.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide without cover, kept on one in straight.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on fairly.
Settled worse than midfield, however trapped very wide without cover throughout, never looked likely.
At rear, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on until final 200M flattened.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Raced midfield, settled 7Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never looked competitive.
Camped handy, travelled 1Ls behind the leader 2 wide without cover, flattened badly soon after straightening. (Found substantial amount of blood in its trachea and also lame left front the next day)
Awkward start, raced near tail on rail, 3rd last when switched out & shaken up 400m, strong progress, burst through to lead 150m, in command.
Broke well & bustled to race handy 1 off with cover, niggled 650m ridden along 500m, 5th when shifted out in stretch, stayed on to snag 2nd.
Rousted at start near tail, rolled on a touch to 1 off near rear, to rail on turn & driven 450m, closed off soundly, to 2nd 100m, edged out to 3rd at wire.
Moderate break, soon at tail on rail, niggled 800m for progress, 2nd last when switched out & rousted 680m, ran on for sound headway.
Good break, rolled to sit 2nd 1off, driven to lead 350m, all out & headed 150m, weakened thereafter.
Moderate start, covered 3 wide behind midfield, shifted wide & driven 500m, widest in stretch, plugged on one pace.
Sharp start, sat 1 back on fence, shifted out 450m & driven into stretch, boxed on in one-paced pursuit until tapered final 150m.
Missed break, rolled on rail from tail to soon sit handy midfield, ridden 500m, plugging evenly when checked off heels 200m, no extra.
Slow start, settled on inner behind midfield, switched out turning in, shaken up 350m, struggled in run home.
Broke OK, rolled 3 wide no cover to race handy, under pump 650m, outpaced turning in, no extra & struggled in run home.
Rousted at break to race 3 wide with cover midfield, outpaced when driven wide home turn, found nothing & faded tamely.
Smart break, caught wide & slid back to 3 wide near rear, to tail 700m, struggled & never a factor, eased.
Sharp start, soon led & to rail 1400m, driven under pressure 450m, headed 350m, emptied & faded quickly.
Broke OK, raced 1 off with cover midfield, niggled 800m, outpaced when crowded & off heels 300m, not a factor thereafter.
Led at break, soon headed & camped handy 5th on rail, shaken up 400m, driven on inner to lead 200m, drew clear.
Good break, disputed lead on rail, shuffled to 1 back 1000m, caught in pocket & switched out 300m, ran on late to claim 2nd.
Taken behind at break to rail behind midfield, driven into stretch & shifted out, stayed on to 3rd 50m, held in run to wire.
Tardy start, raced rail fore of midfield, shifted out 400m & hard-ridden, switched centre 300m, every chance, kept on dourly.
Broke well, sat handy 3 wide with cover until slotted 1 off, switched 3 wide & progress 520m, quickened to lead 380m, headed 200m & faded.
Tardy break, settled rail midfield, shifted 1 off 950m, 3 wide final turn & driven 400m, plugged on one pace.
Snagged to race 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled back stretch, on bridle but in pocket turning in, switched wide & shaken up 200m, moderate inroads.
Restrained start, raced rail near tail, last into stretch & driven, kept on evenly, never a threat.
Broke OK & rousted, soon 1 off near tail, driven 3 wide 800m, all out turning in, unbalanced 400m, stayed on dourly.
Missed break, raced at tail, switched wide for progress 600m, widest into stretch, stayed on moderately until tapered late.
Rousted at break, raced 1 off with cover midfield, forced 3 wide no cover 950m, ridden 650m, wide & under pressure home turn, struggled to wire.
Broke well to dispute early lead, raced 2nd 1 off no cover, led 1000m & to rail, under pressure when driven & headed 380m, weakened out.
Broke OK, bustled to sit 1 off with cover fore of midfield, shifted wide & driven turning in, faded in stretch.
Smart start, rolled to lead 3 wide, unable to gain clear advantage, headed 1000m, shuffled back to 4th on turn, faded tamely thereafter.
Bumped start, 4Ls off the leader on fence, made good ground 400M, dashed well to win.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead, benefited by the pace biased track, hung on strongly until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Hard ridden to share lead 2 wide, favoured by the pace biased track, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader, benefited by the pace biased track, lack room 4-2, ran on ok when clear.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, hung out badly at bends, not suited by the pace biased track, ran on ok in straight.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the pace biased track, just held ground.
5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the pace biased track, just held ground.
Hard ridden early, 3Ls off the leader, hampered badly 800M and was taken out to 3-4 wide, no turn of foot.
At rear, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the pace biased track, no progress.
At rear, 8Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the pace biased track, no progress.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, hampered badly 800M and was taken to 4 wide, not suited by the pace biased track, nothing left in straight.
Trapped 4 wide throughout at back, not suited by the pace biased track, never competitive.
Jumped well from widest gate, restrained and taken back to find cover, sitting at rear in one-off position. Revved up 500m, entered straight behind horses, got split 250m and motored home strongly.
Began fairly, vigorously ridden to make up ground, grabbing box seat before turn. Came off fence 500m, hit front 250m, run down final 50m.
Broke well, ridden along but unable find cover and held 4-wide towards rear. Widest into straight but kept on well under hard riding, drifting in final stages.
Jumped OK, hard ridden to lead on settling. Set steady pace, kicked ahead entering straight, caught 250m but kept on steadily.
Taken in gradually from wide draw to sit at midfield in one-off position before the turn. Had clear running entering straight and kept on fairly.
Pressed forward from awkward draw but trapped 3-wide without cover behind leaders. Travelled three or four wide around turn and one-paced in straight.
Taken in soon after the start, settling along fence at rear. Stayed on fence around turn, no clear run entering straight, kept on fairly but checked close to line when held for running.

Began awkwardly, bumped and badly unbalanced. Ridden to make ground but started over-racing. Hampered 500m when trying to improve, raced tight in straight. (Horse struck on nose 50m by whip of another rider).
Crowded out start, taken in but away from fence at rear. Made ground quickly before steadied 900m. One-paced in straight, taken very wide 200m, ran past beaten horses.
Broke well, pressed forward sitting outside hind quarters of leader to straight. One-paced soon after entering straight, before running out of gas 100m.
Ridden along to maintain midfield position away from fence. Turned in behind horses and found little under hard riding.
Began OK, taken quickly to fence settling 3-back from leader. Got shuffled back around turn. Spent force entering straight, becoming tailed off.
Sat behind leading pair, checked 700M when attempting to improve position, soon recovered, quickened clear inside 250M, won with plenty in hand.
Restrained in midfield, saved ground along the fence, stayed on well to go 2nd 100M but never looked like bridging the gap on winner.
Held up behind mid-division, shaken up 500M from home, did best work final 200M for a non-threatening 3rd.
Stayed within striking distance throughout, kept on evenly entering straight but never a serious threat to first two.
Soon in front under positive riding, was challenged for the lead entering back-straight, headed near 250M, no extra final 100M and weakened to 5th.
Restrained to a 3-wide position behind midfield, taken out 450M to challenge, stayed on fairly and never reached leaders.
Taken back from wide barrier, settled near the rear about 7Ls off the pace, stayed on mildly past weakening rivals.
Soon guided to the rail, settled 5Ls behind leaders, placed under serious pressure 500M out, failed to pick up the pace.
Rushed forward from draw 10, chased leaders along the 3-path, made his bid 700M out, briefly led nearing home straight but run ended 250M and weakened towards finish.
Towards the rear but never really travelled, detached from main group 600M out, niggled along and only began to pick up final 200M, made some progress without threatening.
Settled into middle of pack, raced along the 2-path 3Ls off the pace, failed to pick up under pressure, weakened 250M.
In mid-division, 3-wide throughout, found little when driven 500M from home, never reached a contending position. (Lame left front.)
Eased back to the rear, soon detached from the field over 10Ls off the pace entering final 400M, eased 300M when well beaten.
Caught wide early stages, strode forward to race outside leader, under pressure 700M and gave ground, weakened rapidly entering straight.

Began from a poor draw, travelled prominently until taking over the lead 1400 metres out setting a steady pace, kicked over 2L clear shortly after straightening, won unchallenged.
Close up on rails, settled just over 2L off the steady pace to straight, switched out for a run turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped well from a wide draw, niggled at early settling just off the pace, kept on at the same speed without quickening under pressure in straight.
Moderate start, settled in midfield, ran on under pressure inside final 300 metres, nearest at finish.
Began from a poor draw, gradually moved across to rails settling just off the steady pace, came under pressure entering straight, kept on same pace without quickening.
Jumped with others, gradually settled in last few, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly, travelled worse than midfield, produced moderate late headway inside final 200 metres.
Began from the widest gate, travelled 3-wide mainly in midfield, slightly worse into straight, made moderate late impression closing stages.
Slightly slow out, soon driven to midfield on rails, remained similar to turn, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Towards the rear on rails, saved ground turning in, kept on without quickening due to no clear run.
Jumped fairly, settled just over 2L off the pace 2-wide in 5th and then 4th, came to challenge turning in but soon found nothing.
Settled wide in forward of midfield, came under pressure into straight, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres. (Lame next day) (Mucus)
Jumped fairly, soon dropped well back, trailed the field to 800 metres, made short-lived effort when wide around home bend, no further impression in straight.
Jumped fairly, behind midfield when checked 1600 metres out, remained in last few before dropping to tail-end 800 metres out.
Travelled back in the field, on the fence with cover. Closed off strongly towards the inside.
Settled in 6th position, 1 off with cover. Worked home nicely.
Raced worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Finished off soundly.
Made its run from back in the field, 1 off with cover. Ran on well, peaking on its effort 50m, from home.
Travelled midfield, 3 deep with cover. Ranged up approaching the 200m, but ended its run soon after.
Settled at the rear of the field, 2-3 deep with cover. Came wide in the straight and battled away down the running.
Raced on the fence in 5th position with cover. Peeled out near the 500m, didn't go on with it and only plodded to the line.
Travelled midfield on the fence with cover. Didn't have the clearest of runs early in the straight, was one paced thereafter.
Parked worse than midfield, on the rails with cover. Failed to find any extra in the home stretch. (Blood in trachea)
Sent forward and crossed to lead approaching the first turn staying1 off on the circle. Began to tire quickly at the furlong. (Blood in trachea)
Posted 3 deep without cover on the speed. Was never likely, and was well beaten at the furlong.
Camped 3rd 1 off with some cover on the circle. Faded early in the home straight.
Settled with the backmakers 3 deep with cover. Came under pressure from the 600m and failed to respond, finishing tailed out. (To Trial).
Settled 2nd on the fence, no cover. Gave ground quickly from early in the straight and finished tailed out. ( To Trial)
Sent forward to obtain the box seat, ran on strongly to take the victory by a nose.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed well to get 2nd in a very tight finish.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 0.5L, hung on nicely for third in a very close finish.
Parked midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, closed to the line well for 4th.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on steadily.
Camped handy, settled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line.
Settled in front of midfield, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, unable to make any ground in straight.
Sent forward to park outside the leader, kept on until final furlongs flattened.
Raced midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
At rear, settled 10Ls behind the leader 2 wide, made some ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, never likely.
Settled worse than midfield, 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never seen with a chance.
Always at rear, never in a competitive position.
At last throughout, never a factor.
Broke well, outpaced to sit midfield 1 off, off heels 800m & to rail, not clear run in stretch, daylight 200m, sprinted to lead 70m, drew clear.
Moderate break, soon behind midfield 1 off, off heels 800m, switched out for progress & driven 300m, swept centre track to 2nd close home.
Smart start, led 1000m, scooted clear to rail 750m, headed & ridden 360m, fought on gamely to snatch third at wire.
Speed to lead, bustled & headed 1000m, raced 2L 2nd 1 off no cover, driven to edge lead 360m, all out & headed 70m, lost duel for 3rd at wire.
Tardy start, raced rail near rear, off heels 800m, checked & lost ground 700m, switched wide into stretch & driven, stayed on for sound inroads.
Broke well, sat 1 back on rail, shifted 1 off & driven into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Taken behind from widest, raced wide with cover behind midfield, widest & driven 430m, ran on well for minor headway.
Outpaced & rousted to race rail last pair, ridden at tail 500m, plugged on in stretch for minor inroads.
Slow break, raced behind midfield 3 wide with cover, shake up 400m, good headway until peaked & tapered final 50m.
Heavy bump at start, settled midfield 1 off with cover, shifted out & driven turning in, outpaced & plugged on same speed.
Good start, raced handy 3 wide no cover, ridden under pressure 500m, kept on one pace until tapered out final 150m.
Snagged back to sit last pair 1 off, driven 400m, ran on one pace.
Shifted & bumped rival start, rousted to race handy out wide, under pump four wide no cover 500m, hard-ridden but faded tamely.
Good break, raced fore of midfield 1 off with cover, checked 850m,tracked lead turning in but crowded, unbalanced 250m, driven but faded weakly.
Speed to lead & soon to rail, extended 2L clear on turn, shaken up in front 430m, scooted clear for commanding win.
Broke well, raced midfield & found rail 1000m, under pump turning in, weaving run down inner, rattled to 2nd 100m, held in run.
Tardy start, niggled early 1 off near rear, under pump 550m, shifted out turning in & closed off strongly centre track to just miss 2nd.
Moderate break, mustered to race 1 back on rail, niggled 550m, soon driven to 2nd, no extra final 100m & swamped.
Slow start, taken back to sit 3 wide with cover near rear, progress 800m, driven widest home turn, closed centre track for sound headway.
Bustled at break to race outside leader, settled 1 back 1 off, 4th & driven 500m, dour progress to vie for 2nd until emptied 200m & tapered out.
Taken back from wide gate to rail at tail, driven 400m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Broke well, slid back to midfield & found cover on outer, driven wide on turn, plugged home evenly.
Broke OK, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven turning in & to rail, not clear run & switched out 250m, plugged on one pace.
Disputed early lead 3 wide, slotted 2nd 1 off 950m, hard-ridden turning in, emptied 300m & weakened out.
Missed break & sat 1 off last pair, brief 3 wide progress 700m, hard-ridden turning in, kept on one pace.
Broke OK, bustled to sit 1 off with cover fore of midfield, to rail 850m, shifted 1 off 650m, driven 500m, one-paced until faded mid-stretch.
Broke well, bustled midfield until checked 1200m, lost ground & soon bustled near rear, struggled turning in & soon weakened out.
Sharp start, 3 wide no cover fore of midfield until slotted 1 off 850m, forced wide again 650m, ridden 550m, faded tamely in stretch.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, kicked away 250M to score.
Box seat, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide throughout, 2.5Ls off the fast pace, ran on well to the line for 3rd.
Eased at start, took rail behind the field, 6Ls off the leaders, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leaders, suited by the fast pace but trapped 3 wide, just held ground in final stages.
Pushed early but not muster, 4Ls off the leaders 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, held up 4-2, ran on ok when clear.
Settled in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, blocked 400M, just held ground when clear.
Hard ridden forward, shared lead 2 wide at fast sectionals, flattened 250M.
Eased to rear and took rail, 8.5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, made some ground 150M.
Eased to rear, 7.5Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast pace but raced 3-4 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden to taka rail and shared the lead, clocked fast sectionals under pressure throughout, hung on until 200M emptied.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, out of fuel 200M.
At back, 6Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, suited by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 4-5 wide at back, soon emptied 400M.
Came out running to lead clearly to halfway mark, given reminders when pressured 400m and kicked clear for easy win.
Began OK, ridden along but outpaced, dropping to rear on settling. Picked up momentum along outer fence from 300m and finished off strongly.
Broke well, ridden along between horses to obtain forward position. Made forward move passing 400m and kept on steadily without looking dangerous.
Leaning on stall when gates opened and began only fairly. Lost left front plate passing 600m, hard ridden down centre track to just make the frame. (Rider dislodged on pulling up).
Ridden along to hold midfield position between horses. Put under pressure passing 400m and kept on fairly to line. Bumped final stages.
Jumped well, pushed forward while crossing to outer fence to sit inside leader. Put under pressure from 400m, kept on well to 100m before flattened. Bumped close to line.
Away quickly, ridden forward but unable to get closer than 4-away from outer fence. Kept on well under pressure from 400m before tightened 50m and dropping back.
Pressed forward from awkward gate but unable to get cover and raced on his own down centre track close to leading pack. Kept on well under pressure until 100m when gave ground rapidly.
Slow into stride, taken straight to outer fence but outpaced and shuffled back before reaching course proper. Never a factor.
Slow to move, ridden along but failed to muster and taken across towards outer fence. Switched in again pasting 250m but never a factor.
Pressed forward while edging towards outer fence, settling inside leaders 800m. Put under pressure passing 400m but soon out of gas and gave ground quickly.
Lost ground at start, trailed field thereafter, racing down centre track. Never competitive.
Began OK, ridden along in midfield along outer fence until crowded and lost ground 400m. Faded steadily and tailed off. (Unacceptable performance).
Settled into mid-division, shifted out to clear 400M, picked up steadily to wrestle the lead close home.
Began well from draw 1, tracked leader, responded well to lead near 150m, kept on steadily along fence, headed by winner late.
Settled towards the rear 4-5Ls behind leader, hard driven passing 450M, finished final 400M fastest, got up for 3rd just before line.
Outside leader, kept on well when driven entering straight, unbalanced when bumped 200M, recovered to chase leaders but always held, lost 3rd near line.
Held up towards the rear, saved ground on inside, ran on steadily over final 400M but never a serious threat to first few.
Held up in mid-division along the fence, ran on one paced in straight, well held by leaders.
Went for the lead, took them along at good pace, joined by rivals nearing 200M, shifted out under pressure, run ended inside 100M.
In touch behind leaders, niggled along 550M, chased leaders turning in but lacked further response mid-straight.
Taken back to the rear, 5Ls off the pace in a strongly run race, stayed on mildly over final 300M.
From wide draw taken across behind runners, raced at the back 6Ls off the pace, made limited progress over final 350M.
Unable to slot in, caught 3-wide without cover throughout, stayed within striking distance turning in, weakened and no extra 200M.
Settled 3-wide in midfield but not picked up entering straight, soon weakened.
Caught 4-wide without cover in midfield, weakened rapidly turning home, soon behind. (Unacceptable Performance)
Began well, pressed forward to hold rail inside leading pair. Got inside run entering straight, hit front passing 300m, temporarily headed but fought back to win on line.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing 3-4 wide. Covered extra ground turn, rolled forward to hit front 300m, shifted in under pressure 100m and rider stopped riding to straighten 50m. Just failed.
Began well, taken in passing 1000m to sit in one-off position four-back from leader. Ran on strongly final 400m shifting in twice to get clear running.
Bumped after start, hard ridden to go forward, taking over lead 800m between horses but headed 700m. Urged forward entering straight, joint leader 300m, outsprinted final 200m but kept on well.
Ridden along early to maintain forward position, racing one-off behind leading trio. No run top of straight, shifted in 350m to get clear running, kept on well.
Bumped soon after start, got close to heels passing 1100m then proved difficult to settle. Shifted out from heels passing 700m and left without cover. Kept on steadily in straight.
Jumped best, led to 850m when jumped shadow, became unbalanced and lost ground. Retook lead 700m but held wide without cover. Caught 300m and raced erratically final 200m.
Began fairly, shifted in behind runners but kept away from fence towards the rear, Improved position around turn, kept on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Jumped OK but lost right hind plate after start. Shifted in behind runners passing 900m but still held 3-wide. Very wide in straight and kept on one-paced.
Ridden along early shifting in behind horses passing 1000m but got close heels 800m. Three-wide into turn and one-paced in straight.
Slow into stride, taken in behind runners to fence at rear. Shifted out entering straight but found little under hard riding.
Jumped with field, ridden to hold rail two-back from leading trio. Got clear running entering straight but only one-paced. (Lost left hind plate 1000m).
Broke OK, hard ridden but failed to muster, then taken across behind runners to sit at rear but wide. Lost position around turn and never a factor in straight.

Placing: UR
Comment: Began well, ridden along to sit 3-wide behind leading trio. Checked and struck heels of horse falling back, dislodging jockey. (Swollen left hind fetlock).
Jumped well, slotted in nicely from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in 4th, 1-2 lengths back, made run turning, dashed well in straight and won comfortably.
Moderately away, raced 5-6 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, in traffic early in straight, finished off strongly when clear final 250M.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, bumped near 900M, 3 wide with cover turning, angled out in straight and closed off well to take 3rd.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 5-6 lengths back, 3 wide with cover turning, taken widest in straight and made decent progress to make frame.
Began fairly, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover in midfield, 4 lengths back, bumped near 900M, 4 wide no cover turning, kept on evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear , 6-7 lengths back, similar position turning, no daylight until 200M and made some headway thereafter.
Slowly away, raced 6-7 lengths back on rail at rear, 2 wide turning and gradually improved, no clear running until near 300M and closed off steadily when clear.
Jumped with them, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead to turn, lacked an extra gear in straight and headed near 300M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slow to begin, raced 9 lengths back on rail at tail, still well back turning, kept to inside after straightening and got traffic until 150M, closed off evenly thereafter.
Taken back from the widest gate, raced 7-8 lengths back at tail, well back turning, only passed a few tired runners in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run to turn, emptied early in straight and dropped off gradually.
Began well from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, no cover throughout, same position turning, emptied early in straight after hard run took effect.
Moderately away from an awkward gate, sent forward to race in 3rd on rail, difficult to settle near 1300M, same position turning, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in front of midfield in 5th, 2-3 lengths back, similar position turning, emptied early in straight and eased thereafter, never competitive. (lame right front leg.)
