Moderate start, settled mainly two back in 5th on rails, obtained a clear run over 300 metres, quickened well to take command 150 metres out, won at ease.
Prominent early, shuffled back to 3L 7th approaching home turn, tight between runners upon straightening, ran on well to be nearest at finish.
Began fairly, settled in rear of midfield, slightly worse entering straight, finished off race strongly.
Jumped fairly from a poor gate, soon dropped well behind, switched out for a run down the centre of the track after straightening, finished off race strongly.
Jumped moderately, settled behind midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, kept on steadily without quickening under pressure.
Jumped fairly, settled in rear of midfield, remained similar turning in, kept on well in straight.
Jumped fairly from the poor draw settling in forward of midfield early, gradually dropped back behind midfield approaching home bend, hampered about 350 metres out, fought on steadily.
Broke well from a poor draw, ridden along to take up running passing 900 metres crossing to rails shortly afterwards, headed when no extra inside final 300 metres.
Raced prominently and wide without cover to straight, soon faded under pressure.

Jumped well, holding narrow lead on rails early on, ceded advantage to take box-seat run coming out of back straight, remained same turning in, hit the front under pressure briefly 300 metres out, swamped passing the 200-metre mark.
Soon outpaced and intractable, only ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Soon dropped well behind, never seen with a chance.
Prominent to 500 metres, dropped away quickly after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Camped 1 out 1 back. Peeled out prior to the home turn and had the race in its keeping 150m from home.
Led on the fence at even fractions. Was overhauled near the 150m, maintained a sound effort to the wire.
Went forward from the widest alley and parked outside the leader. Was running on empty over the last 100m managed to hold on for 3rd.
Missed the start, settling 3rd from the rear, 1 off with cover. Hit the line well.
Stalked the leader on the fence. had every possible chance. Yielded ground over about the last 100m.
Camped 3 back, 1 off with cover. kept on at the same speed in the run to the line.
Settled behind midfield, on the paint with cover. Didn't find any extra wen asked for an effort in the straight. (Blood in trachea)
Travelled with the backmakers, 3deep with cover. Shifted widest on straightening, was one paced down the running.
Raced worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Was dour in the home straight.
Posted 3 deep without cover, midfield. Never likely and failed to respond to riders efforts early in the straight.
Settled last, close to the rail with cover. Made some ground on tiring runners.
Parked 3 back the paint. Was a beaten horse at the furlong.
Raced at the tail of the field, was 4 deep no cover approaching the 900m, managed to slot in and travel 3 wide with cover after the 800m. failed to close off.
Raced towards the rear on the paint with cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slow tempo, dashed strongly to score by 2.5Ls with plenty in hand.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow pace, dashed well for 2nd.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slow sectionals, dashed well for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led at slow sectionals, kept on steadily in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on fairly.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite suited by the slow sectionals, one paced until 200M flattened.
Raced midfield, settled 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, never likely.
Taken back to rear from a wide barrier, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow pace, never ran on.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the slow sectionals, flattened badly 300M.
Ridden forward to occupy the box seat, despite suited by the slow tempo, eased down 300M. (Lame left fore)
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, checked 350M, weakened badly thereafter, tailed out.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, despite benefited by the slow pace, flattened badly soon after straightening, tailed out.
Fast break & soon led on stands rail, shaken up 400m & quickened, bolted clear for easy win.
Fast start, crossed to sit handy toward stands' side, niggled 450m & soon hard driven to 2nd 250m, kept on evenly.
Mustered to track leader on rail, caught flat-footed & hard driven 400m, kept on to close on runner-up at wire.
Moderate start, niggled along behind midfield centre track, ridden for progress 520m, kept on for minor late headway.
Smart start, raced close 2nd until under pressure & ridden 400m, no match for winner's kick, all out &lost 2nd 250m, faded thereafter.
Sluggish start, raced near rear, driven 500m & kept on for moderate inroads centre track.
Broke OK, raced midfield, niggled 500m, hard-ridden 450m, outpaced & boxed on evenly.
Decent start, raced midfield close to stands rail, bustled 550m, driven 450m, outpaced & plugged on.
Fast start from low gate, soon niggled in midfield toward stands' side of centre, driven 400m, faded in tepid run home.
Tardy break, soon at rear of main group, under pump 600m & shifted centre track, found little in tepid run home.
Missed break & detached many lengths, never a factor but ran on late to pass fading rivals close home.
Tardy start & bustled centre track near rear, hard ridden 400m, plugged on modestly until faded close home.
Moderate start, raced rail near rear, driven 400m, outpaced & plugged home tamely.
Slow break, rousted initially centre track near rear, driven 450m, outpaced & weakened in run home.
Rousted widest to lead, crossed to rail 950m, shaken up 400m, all out & joined at head 300m, fought off rival & exerted 150m, boxed on to wire.
Broke OK, raced 3 wide until shifted in to 1 off fore of midfield 950m, switched out turn & driven to 3rd 300m, nicked 2nd close home.
Smart start, raced handy & settled 1 off with cover, 3 wide 520m, driven to 2nd 420m, joined lead 300m, run flattened 150m, tapered to wire.
Prominent at break, snagged to sit 3 wide no cover midfield, driven wide into stretch & outpaced but stayed on late for minor inroads.
Snagged from wide to race rear rank 3 wide, progress very wide into stretch & hard ridden, closed soundly mid-track without threatening.
Fast start & disputed lead, son, skipped to fore of midfield on rail, checked off heels 950m, shifted out & driven 450m, kept on evenly.
Fast break to dispute lead, soon settled 1 off no cover & rolled to 2nd 890m, driven 430m, outpaced but plugged on in defeat.
Slow start, raced rail midfield, checked 950m & lost spot, soon recovered, shaken up 400m, kept on for minor inroads.
Sluggish break, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, ridden 420m, stayed on for minor headway.
Broke well & bustled initially, sat 1 off with cover midfield, under pressure & driven turning in, plugged on tepidly.
Slow start, soon at tail 1 off, last & driven turning in, unbalanced 300m, plodded on past weakening rivals.
Tardy start, bustled to sit 3 wide with cover behind midfield, niggled 600m, driven 500m, found little & plodded home tamely.
Tardy break, raced rail near tail, forward a spot 800m, driven into stretch, found nothing in weak run home.
Fast start & driven to slot rail 1100m, settled 1 back, under pump turning in, outpaced when checked 380m, faded thereafter.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L, clocked fast sectionals, just managed to hold on and win by a neck.
Settled in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Pressed forward, 1L off the leader, trapped 3 wide and not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward but checked early, 2Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, checked again 200M, ran on ok.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, not suited by the fast pace, held ground in straight, on heels 50M.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, trapped 3 wide, 2.5Ls off the fast pace, flattened 200M.
Behind midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
At back, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace, but trapped 3-4 wide, ran on fairly.
Eased to rear, 8Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 3.5Ls off the fast pace on the fence, soon dropped off 400M.
Broke well, taken to fence, grabbing box seat. Raced tight when shifted out top of straight to get run, hit front 250m and pulled clear.
Began OK, switched in gradually to get into a one-off position towards the rear. Peeled out passing 600m, very wide in straight, finished strongly under vigorous riding.
Ridden along early, then eased and taken in to find cover, settling three-back, one-off. Made forward move 4-wide around turn, chance on straightening, kept on steadily.
Pressed forward from widest draw, racing outside leading pack. Lost position when steadied to find cover. Rolled forward turning into the straight, hit from 350m, outsprinted final 250m.
Slow into stride, taken to fence, settling four-back. Edged out around turn to get run, got close to heels 300m then steadied 200m when denied run. Not tested concluding stages.
Began well, ridden along before settling one-back, one-off. Shuffled back before turn, checked from heels 500m, shifted out 300m but steadied 250m when run closed.
Jumped fairly, outpaced, dropping back to last but away from fence. Stayed at rear till passing 600m, widest into straight, ran on fairly under whip.
Began fairly, no early speed settling at rear. Made forward move approaching turn, very wide into straight but within striking distance, before tiring final stages.
Pushed to lead on settling but passed on the inside 1250m then dropped to 3rd 1100m when passed on the outside. Lost ground turn, switched to fence 350m, kept on one-paced.
Began well, ridden to stay with leading pack before rolling forward to sit outside leader passing 1200m. Raced tight around turn, 3rd into straight, gave ground gradually from 300m.
Ridden along early, crossed to fence then rolled forward to take lead passing 1200m. Caught 350m and gave ground gradually.
Began fairly, outpaced, settling in last pair along fence. Steadied from heels 1400m and never likely thereafter.
Ridden along from inside draw to sit at midfield three-back from leader. Looked for inside run entering straight but checked when crowded 200m, losing position. (Lame left front leg).
Pressed forward from wide draw to race alongside leading pack but left without cover entering turn. Lost position on straightening and weakened gradually.
Not hurried, settled near the rear 5Ls off the pace, moved out 450M to challenge, closed off strongly and got up late stages.
Held up near the rear outside eventual winner, driven 550M, picked up well to lead nearing 100M, collared by winner late going down narrowly.
Taken back to rear from wide barrier, 6-7Ls behind leaders in middle stages, brought widest passing 450M, got going final 250M, got up for 3rd late stages.
Settled into midfield, lost ground when checked inside 600M, no clear run 300M, closed off nicely final 300M but not pace of first two final stages.
Tucked in behind midfield, waited with until 350M, stayed on moderately for 5th.
Up with early pace, travelled 3-wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace over final 300M.
Unable to slot in from 11, caught wide without cover on the home turn, responded well early straight, led 250M, weakened and was swamped over final 100M.
Began well from draw 1, shared lead, headed 250M, weakened towards the finish.
Not far off behind leaders, 3rd turning in but soon outpaced by rivals.
Stood flat-footed and lost a considerable amount of ground, 9-10Ls to make up passing 400M, made some progress but never reached contention.
Held up in touch, had a 3-wide trip, not quickened when driven 500M, weakened passing 200M.
Slow to begin then rushed forward to join leaders, came under serious pressure 600M, gave ground rapidly entering straight.
Jumped with field, ridden along but held three-wide without cover 3L from leader. Covered extra ground turn, pressed forward entering straight, hit front 150m and held on well.
Began OK, taken in to find cover settling three-back, one-off. Switched out to centre of track on straightening and finished off strongly.
Broke well, pressed forward to lead on settling. Set decent pace under a good hold, kicked ahead entering straight, caught 150m, kept battling to line.
Ridden along to maintain forward position settling one-back, one-off. Rolled forward entering straight, looked chance 300m, kept on steadily under hard riding.
Jumped fairly, restrained and taken in, settling 4-back, one-off. Taken to centre of track on straining and ran on steadily under vigorous riding.
Began well, ridden to hold rail 2-back from leader. Switched out turning for home, rolled forward to look chance 200m, then one-paced.
Pressed forward to sit outside hind-quarters of leader. Shaken up top of straight, given reminders 300m but only one-paced.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling in last pair along fence. Steadied passing 1000m, still last entering straight but shaken up and finished off nicely.
Taken across soon after start to sit on rail, five-back from leader. Got close to heels 1000m and over-raced. Peeled out turning for home but one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling in last pair away from fence. Taken very wide entering straight but only one-paced.
Slow from the gates, taken to rail and improved position, four-back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn, kept on fairly before tiring passing 300m.
Pressed forward from good draw to sit in slipstream of leader to straight. Kept on fairly till 200m before fading.
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, same position to turn, finished off very strongly in straight and scored narrowly.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same margin turning, dashed well in straight and took the lead near 250M, just couldn't hold off the winner late.

Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 5-6 lengths back, difficult to settle near 900M, shared last turning, taken widest in straight and finished off very well, just missed 2nd. (See racing incidents.)

Began fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide at rear, 5-6 lengths back, unbalanced near 900m, carried to 4 wide without cover on turn, finished off well to make frame despite hard run.
Slowly away, recovered to race 3 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening and made reasonable headway.
Began well from the widest draw, sent forward to race 1-out 1-back, same position turning, lacked an extra gear in straight, finished off evenly without threatening.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 lengths back on rail in 4th, easy run to turn, no daylight early in straight, finished off fairly when clear final 300M.
Taken back from a wide gate, raced at tail throughout, 8-9 lengths back, still last turning in, in traffic until near 250M, made some headway thereafter.
Average to begin, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide, 2-3 lengths back, no cover from 1100M, similar position turning, peaked on run when work load took toll.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5-6 lengths back, similar position turning, no daylight early in straight and checked near 200M, closed off fairly when race was over.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide in front of midfield, 2-3 lengths back, travelled well to turn, made no progress after straightening. (See racing incidents.)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 lengths back on rail at rear, saved ground turning, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from an awkward draw and pressed on to take the lead, easy run to turn, headed near 300M, dropped out gradually thereafter, never competitive.
Began well, positioned prominently in 2nd on rail, under pressure turning in, showed no response and finished tailed out. (See racing incidents.)
Jumped well, positioned 3 wide with cover just off pace in 6th, same position turning, angled out in straight and finished off very strongly to score an overdue victory.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, travelled well to turn, took the lead near 150M but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well, positioned 2 wide in 4th, 2 lengths back, similar position turning, finished off well in straight to take 3rd. (checked final 50M.)
Slow to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths or so back, still well back turning, taken to widest in straight and made good headway to be nearest on line and make frame.
Crowded out start, showed no early speed to recover, settled 4 wide with cover behind midfield, 3 wide with cover turning, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Jumped with them, raced 3-4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, made steady headway in straight without threatening.

Crowded out start, difficult to settle near 1000M, raced 2 wide at rear, 5-6 lengths back, same position turning, angled out in straight and made some headway to be nearest on line. (Rider dropped his whip near 200M.)
Slowly away, sent forward to race prominently in 3rd, 1-2 lengths back, 3 wide without cover on turn, found no extra gear in straight and only stayed on evenly. (See racing incidents.)
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead to turn, headed final 150M, emptied thereafter.
Crowded out start, raced 8-9 lengths back at tail, still well back turning, made up many lengths in straight, inconvenienced close home.
Jumped well, positioned 2-3 lengths back on rail in 5th, easy run to turn, lacked a turn of foot, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back shuffled back near turn, just kept on at same rate in straight, never a factor.
Average to begin, raced 7 lengths back on rail at rear, similar position turning, failed to close off in straight. (See racing incidents.)

Broke well, settled in midfield, commenced move inside final 300 metres, asserted authority inside final 100 metres.
Pressed on from a poor gate to contest lead, took up running over 1200 metres out before crossing to the rails shortly after, led until finding no extra inside final 100 metres.

Jumped fairly, settled in rear of midfield on rails, carried backward towards the rear coming out of far side, switched off rails for a run upon straightening, ran on well between runners closing stages.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, settled in last few, slightly closer in 10th round home bend, made steady progress in straight, nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately, settled in last few, ran on under pressure past beaten horses inside final 200 metres.
Slowly away, quickly recovered to midfield along rails, saved ground turning in, badly baulked for a run most of straight, not properly tested.
Broke well, settled not far off in 3rd or 4th, about 2L off the pace rounding home bend, came under strong pressure upon straightening, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Jumped moderately, soon dropped well behind, made steady progress down the centre of the straight.
Jumped fairly, soon picked up to a prominent position on rails, checked and lost ground 1000 metres out dropping to 3L 5th around home bend, kept on same pace and swamped closing stages.
Soon taken back for rails run after beginning from the widest gate, remained well back most of way, ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Well there to 300 metres, faded under pressure.
Jumped fairly, gradually dropped back towards the rear, failed to make any impression thereafter.
Jumped fairly from a poor gate, settled in rear of midfield, tight between and behind runners early in straight, kept on without quickening.

Jumped well from a poor draw, soon shifted back to 5th and wide just better than midfield, made swift headway passing 1200 metres to join the leader around home bend, folded up quickly inside final 250 metres.
Made its run from the rear after settling 3rd last, 3 deep with cover. finished off strongly, drifting towards the middle of the track over the final furlong.
Travelled in 2nd position, close to the rail, had cover. Fought on gamely down the running.
Travelled worse than midfield, 3 wide with some cover. Was inclined to lay out on the circle, finished off well.
Settled handy in the run, 2 wide with cover. Kept grinding away in the run to the line.
Went forward and led on the paint. Held a length margin turning for home, unwillingly gave ground over the concluding stages.
Ridden back in the field, settling last, 2-3 deep with cover. Made good ground in the home stretch.
Travelled 4th 3 deep no cover. Hung out, particularly on the circle, kept plugging away to the line.
Effectively raced 3 back the paint. Stayed on only fairly, tiring late.
Parked worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Kept on one paced in the home stretch.
Taken back at the start, traveling at the rear, on the fence with cover. Peeled off the rail near the 600m, was dour in the straight.
Camped 3rd, 1 off no cover. Faded over about the final furlong.
Went back from a wide gate, racing worse than midfield, on the rails with cover. Failed to close off.
Raced keenly at times, settling midfield on the paint with cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Raced towards the tail of the field, 3 deep with cover. Shifted widest on the turn, failed to respond to heavy pressure, and was gone a long way from home.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, settled 5L behind the leader on the fence, stayed inside and dashed well to score comfortably.
Camped handy, settled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on steadily to get 2nd.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on nicely until final 100M weakened for 3rd.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on gradually to get 4th.
Parked midfield, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on ok.
Pushed to settle midfield 3Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on only fairly.
At rear, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, made minor ground in straight.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, made no impression after straightening.
Prominent, however travelled 3 wide without cover throughout, weakened 200M.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 3/4L, kept on until 250M emptied.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked competitive.
Never a factor.
Fast start widest, led 1000m & scooted clear to rail, travelled smoothly in front, shaken up 350m, stretched away for comfortable win.
Fast start, sat 1 off no cover 3rd forced 3 wide 530m, shaken up 420m, battled to 2nd 250m, kept on but no match for winner.
Broke well, sat handy 4th rail, shifted 4 wide into stretch & driven, closed to 3rd 70m & chased right to wire.
Tardy start, sat rail back of midfield, shifted out into stretch & driven, boxed on & closed off for minor late inroads.
Moderate start, raced 1 off with cover midfield, ridden & switched wide home turn, driven centre track & stayed on dourly.
Sharp break to dispute early lead, soon settled 1 back on fence, shifted 1 off 530m, pressed lead 400m, soon all out & lost 2nd 250m, tapered.
Moderate start, slotted rail near rear, shaken up 400m, kept on for minor headway.
Rousted from wide gate, slotted 1 off with cover fore of midfield, switched wide & ridden turning in, outpaced & tapering when impeded late.
Slow start & taken back, rolled to sit 1 off with cover behind midfield, niggled 800m & off heels 720m, driven 500m, plugged on to wire.
Tardy start, raced 3 wide no cove behind midfield, ridden turning in, one-paced in run & tapered late.
Reared start & lost ground, raced last pair on rail, hard-ridden into stretch, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Veered & hit rail soon after start, lost ground, niggled & soon tagged on to tail, 3 wide for progress 620m, driven into stretch but found nothing.
Broke OK, sat rail midfield, ridden 510m, found little & struggled in run home.
Taken back from wide gate, sat 1 off near rear, ridden turning in, found little, never a factor.
Moderate start, mustered to stalk lead 3 wide with cover, shifted out & shaken up 400m, swept to lead 220m, kept on.
Taken back at start to 3 wide with cover near rear, progressed a spot 800m, wide & driven into stretch, strong closer to snag 2nd late.
Fair break, camped rail 1 back, daylight & shaken up 400m, not pace of winner but closed off soundly to make frame.
Slow break & initially rousted rail last pair, shifted 1 off 650m, driven wide home turn, rattled home centre track, just missed frame.
Tardy start, mustered to press lead 1 off, snagged 1 back 1 off 1000m, in pocket turning in, daylight & shaken up 300m, kept on without threat.
Broke OK, mustered on rail to dispute lead 1000m, continued to press lead & driven 400m, battled on but tapered & swamped 150m.
Fast break, worked hard to dispute lead 1 off lead, pressed either side & narrow advantage from 900m until headed 220m, battled on but tapered.
Crowded start & raced last pair 1 off, shifted 3 wide 700m, widest into stretch, ran on for minor inroads.
Lacked pace & rousted initially near tail on rail, outpaced turning in, staying on & not clear run 250m, ran on late until checked last strides.
Smart start, snagged to rail midfield, driven & shifted out 430m, plugged on one pace.
Snagged at start, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, shifted out & driven turning in, kept on one pace.
Fast start to dispute lead until slid back from 1200m, sat midfield 1 off, ridden 500m, plugged on.
Broke well & bustled in behind pace, settled 3 wide with cover midfield, ridden 4 wide home turn, struggled & faded out.
Sharp start, trapped very wide no cover until mustered to 3 wide no cover outside lead 1000m, under pump turning in & fading when checked 250m.
Settled in a more prominent spot, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, closed off strongly to score.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked 400-200M, demonstrated strong finishing efforts when clear.
Settled in front of midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader on the rails, made early move 600M to take advantages of the slow pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, just held ground.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon flattened 300M.
Eased at start, took rail behind the field, 7Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 400M, only little dash when clear.
Eased to rear, 10Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 300M without threats.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the leader 2-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 250M.
Midfield, 6Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, no dash when clear.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 7.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Pushed forward, 1L off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, faded quickly and checked 400M.
Slow away, hard ridden forward to sit 2 wide, however shuffled back in middle stages, 5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, soon reduced 350M.
Broke well, ridden along early to hold rail, settling in slipstream of leader. Came off fence 350m and gradually overhauled leader under vigorous riding.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, harassed by another from 900m to 700m, kicked clear entering straight, kept on well while hanging in, run down final strides.
Jumped with field, outpaced, dropping back to settle between horses at the rear. Ran on strongly between horses on entering straight to be closest at the finish.
Shaken up at start, rolled forward but held three-wide, three-back from leader. Steadied 900m, swung wide entering straight, kept on fairly under hard riding.
Ridden along early but caught three-wide without cover in second row behind leader entering turn. Looked chance 400m before turning one-paced final 200m.
Niggled to maintain forward position settling three-back one off. Checked 800m when attempting inside run, shifted out 650m, wide into straight and kept on steadily.
Began awkwardly, switched in quickly to grab fence three-back from leader. Came off fence on straightening and kept on fairly under hard riding.
Began well, pressed forward to harass leader 900m, got head in front momentarily, raced outside leader to straight, giving ground steadily from 300m.
Broke well, restrained and taken across behind runners but held three-wide at rear. Swung wide entering straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Began awkwardly, ridden along to find cover but held four-wide entering turn. Bumped and unbalanced 650m, one-paced in straight.
Raced tight after start, dropping to rear while edging closer to fence. Swung 4-wide entering straight had clear passage but found little under hard riding.
Pressed forward to sit 3rd passing the 800m but shuffled back to 6th around turn. Steadied shortly after entering straight, losing ground gradually from 300m.
Ridden along early but unable find cover, settling one-off towards rear. Crowded for room passing 650m, wide into straight, one-paced under vigorous riding.
Began well, ridden to hold forward position before being outpaced, settling three-back one off. Shuffled back around turn, gave ground in straight. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Settled into midfield, travelled 3-wide with cover, shoved along 500M, picked up strongly from 250M and made rapid headway, hit lead 100M drew away impressively.
Unable to find cover from wide draw, moved forward to attack the lead, pulled over 2Ls clear along with joint leader inside 350M, kept on well but not pace of winner final 150M.
Shaken up after the start, settled 3-wide in the group chasing the pace, stayed on evenly for 3rd over this shorter trip, no impression on runway winner.
Held up in midfield, saved ground along the inside, 3Ls to make up on leader 400M, kept on steadily but no match with winner's acceleration final 200M.
Crossed to the lead near 1000M, pressed by rival entering home turn, dueled 400M-200M, weakened final stages.
Slow to begin, vigorously ridden, settled near the rear 6Ls off leaders, stayed on mildly, not reached leaders.
Held up in midfield along the 2-path, fell back a bit nearing home turn, switched out 500M but lacked the needed response, never got into contention.
Blundered after the start and lost ground, ended up in the rear 7Ls off leaders, not clear run early straight, ran on only fairly past weakening rivals final 300M.
Soon guided to the fence, raced towards the rear 5Ls behind leader, kept on same pace turning in , ran past well beaten rivals only.
Taken back from wide barrier, reserved at the rear 7Ls off the pace, brought wide 550M, failed to quicken. (Jockey reported his horse felt short in its action in the straight)
Held up towards the rear, travelled 3-wide home turn, failed to pick up, never involved.
Hard driven early stages to take up a forward position, sat just off the pace making the turn, soon outpaced passing 350M, soon weakened out of contention. (Lame next day)
Up with early pace, tracked leaders from 900M, unable to keep up entering straight, weakened rapidly.
Never far off from leaders, raced a shade keenly middle stages, failed to pick up the pace inside 400M, faded to last.
Crowded at star, eased, dropping to rear in one-off position. Suited by fast pace, rolled forward 3-wide passing 600m, hit front 200m, edging clear final stages.
Began OK, ridden along while edging closer to rail 3-back from leader. No clear run entering straight, awkwardly placed approaching 200m, finished off nicely when clear.
Ridden along early but unable find cover and held four-wide. Pressed forward around turn, looked chance 350m, outsprinted by first two final stages.
Crowded out start dropping to clear last. Edged closer around turn, widest in straight, finished off nicely down centre track. (Rider dropped right rein after start)
Pressed forward from wide draw and trapped 3-wide without cover around turn. Hit front on straightening, caught passing 200m. (Not ridden out to satisfaction of stewards)
Began OK, ridden to hold rail behind leader. Saved ground turn, blocked for clear run in straight until passing 200m, kept on fairly.
Broke well, ridden along inside leader before taking over lead passing 1000m. Headed 400m but kept battling until flattened final 50m.
Pressed forward but not enough speed to match leaders, settling 4-wide in second tier. Wide around turn, put under pressure 400m but weakened gradually.
Hard ridden from wide draw to lead initially before settling 3rd but wide into turn. Rolled forward entering straight but soon beaten, dropping back.
Allowed to stride forward from inside draw, settling one-off in second row. Bumped before turn, kept on early in straight before denied run passing 200m.
Slow into stride, taken to fence, settling toward rear, Shuffled back to last around turn, one paced in straight.
Began OK but got close to heels passing 1000m, raced tight 900m, lost ground 700m after which travelled only fairly. (Jockey reported did not respond when pressured)
Hard ridden from wide draw to go forward, sitting three-wide without cover outside leaders. Fourth into straight before tiring. (Unacceptable performance)
Ridden along between horses, shifted in 1100m and bumped, after which difficult to settle. Raced tight turn, gave ground quickly in straight. (Unacceptable performance)
Moderately away, raced 2 wide in 4th, 2 lengths back, travelled well to turn, dashed nicely at 300M, kept on well to score with some in hand.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, same position to turn, found no daylight early in straight, closed off well when clear final 300M.
Average to begin, showed early speed to race prominently on rail in 2nd, easy run to turn, in mix to 300M and kept on well to the finish.
Crowded out start, raced at tail throughout, 8-9 lengths back, still well back turning, angled out in straight and finished off very strongly to make frame.
Jumped well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover in 3rd pressed on to take the lead at 1000M, found no extra gear after turning in, headed near 200M but kept on evenly.
Began awkwardly from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths or so back, same position turning, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 5 lengths or so back, same position turning, in traffic and steadied near 300M, made some headway when clear final furlong.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide 6-7 lengths back at rear throughout, taken widest after turning in and made reasonable headway without threatening.
Moderately away, positioned 4-5 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, failed to quicken in straight, just stayed on one-paced.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently in 3rd, easy run to turn, found no extra gear in straight and weakened gradually final 300M.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 6 lengths or so back on rail at rear, same position turning, made only minor progress in straight before running into in later stages.
Crowded out start, raced 3-4 lengths back on rail in midfield, difficult to settle in the early stages, saved ground to turn, kept on evenly until 200M, emptied thereafter.
Crowded out start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 4 lengths back, similar position turning, failed to close off in straight.
Began well from an awkward gate, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover, 3 lengths back in 5th, still no cover turning, emptied early in straight after hard run took effect.
Jumped well, positioned a length back on rail, easy run to turn, took the lead near 200M, kept on well to finish and hold off the late challengers to score narrowly.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover, 4-5 lengths back behind midfield, angled wider on turn, finished off very well in straight, just missed by narrow margin.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 5-6 lengths back, same position to turn, taken widest in straight and finished off very strongly, just missed.
Moderately away, unable to slot in, sent forward to challenge for the lead near 900M, 3 wide without cover turning, headed near 250M, stayed on evenly to make frame.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race 4-5 lengths back on rail, slightly improved on turn, made reasonable headway in straight, just missed frame.
Jumped well, showed early speed to race prominently, 2 wide, 1-2 lengths back, travelled well to turn, kept on evenly in straight but couldn't trouble the first few.
Average to begin, checked near 1500M, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, similar position to turn, angled out in straight and made steady progress.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at tail, well back turning, made some headway in straight without threatening.
Jumped well. sent forward to race prominently on rail in 2nd, similar position turning, lacked an extra gear in straight, weakened gradually final 250M.
Slowly away, recovered to race 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, even run in mid-section, saved ground to turn, closed off only fairly in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position turning, failed to quicken in straight, stayed on one-paced.
Slow to begin, raced 6-7 lengths back on fence at rear, shared rear turning, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in 4th, carried wider 600M, failed to close off in straight, dropped out gradually final 200M.
Began well from a tricky gate, sent forward to race next to the leader, similar position to turn, showed no response in straight and finished tailed out.

Jumped well from the one draw, led before ceded advantage to take up one-back position on rails, shifted out to challenge entering straight hitting the front 200 metres out, won readily.
Gradually settled 3-wide in midfield after beginning from a tricky gate, remained similar turning for home, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Soon joined the leader, took up running over 1100 metres out, led until finding no extra on rails 200 metres out.
Reared in the gates, jumped moderately, settled on rails just better than midfield, saved round turning in, ran on steadily despite hanging in under pressure and not able to be properly tested.
Jumped fairly from a wide-ish gate, soon settled towards the rear, made up good ground inside final 200 metres, did best work late.
Jumped fairly but soon dropped to one from last, trailed the field from around home bend and into the straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Jumped fairly from a tricky gate, gradually picked up from wide in midfield to be 2-wide and 2L back in 3rd, faded under pressure soon after straightening.
Jumped moderately, settled wide without cover in forward of midfield, similar rounding home bend, kept on one pace in the run home.
Jumped moderately, settled 2-wide in rear of midfield, kept on at the one pace under pressure in straight.
Began moderately, travelled in last few most of way to straight, kept on past well-beaten horses in the run home.
Began fairly, travelled prominently early and better than midfield around the bend, similar in 4th or 5th within 3L of lead turning in, soon faded.
Began moderately, soon picked up on rails to rear of midfield, dropped out tamely soon after straightening.
Settled well behind after beginning from the widest gate, saved ground on rails turning in but never a danger.
Parked midfield, 1 off the rails with cover. peeled out turning for home, cut loose early in the straight and had the win 50m from home.
Ridden with purpose early, settling in 2nd spot, 1 off with cover. was overhauled near the 50m.
Travelled behind midfield, 1 off the fence with cover. Shifted deep on straightening and ran on nicely.
Coursed wide on the circle eventually taking up a 1 off position after the 800m, in 3rd position. Was running on empty over the final stages.
Went back from a wide gate settling back in the field, 3 wide with cover. Closed off with purpose over the latter stages.
Eventually settled third, from the rear, on the rails with cover. ran on soundly in the home stretch.
Raced worse than midfield on the fence with cover. kept plugging away down the running.
Slowly away settling 2nd last with cover. Made usual honest ground in the run home.
Travelled back in the field, 2 deep with cover. Labored to the line.
Went forward and led along the paint at a good clip. Was gone at the furlong.
Settled ahead of midfield but posted 3 deep without cover on the circle. Never likely.
Handy early, 1 off before getting shuffled back when crowded for room near the 1000m. Was in a handy settled slightly ahead of midfield, but never fired a shot.
Slow to begin, settling last on the rails with cover. Failed to close off.
Had no excuses after tracking the leader on the fence. Was a beaten horse early in the straight.
Began nicely, then eased to midfield about 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed strongly to take the trophies by a neck.
Camped handy, settled 2Ls behind the leader, ran on nicely for 2nd despite traveling 3 wide without cover throughout.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 3/4L, kept on strongly until 100M weakened.
Eased back, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, dashed well when clear 300M.
Raced midfield, settled 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground without any threats.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one after straightening.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, unable to show any dash in straight.
Taken back to rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on. (Questioned for riding, see incidents report)
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, failed to respond when asked 350M.
Ridden forward to settle outside the leader, found nothing when placed under pressure soon after straightening. (displaying an irregular heart rhythm)
At rear, travelled 3-4 wide without cover throughout, never ran on.
Bustled initially to sit handy 2nd 3 wide no cover, closed upsides leader turning in & driven, led 300m, drew clear easily.
Broke well, restrained & settled to track leader 1 off in 3rd, driven 400m, outpaced but battled on to snag 2nd late.
Rousted to lead, soon to rail, driven under pressure 400m, headed 300m, outpointed but kept on until tapered & lost 2nd close home.
Sharp break, raced midfield 1 off with cover, ridden 400m, boxed on evenly to wire.
Broke with others, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, shifted out & driven 400m, ran on for minor late headway.
Started well, settled rail midfield, shifted 1 off turning in & ridden, stayed on without threatening.
Missed break, soon closed on tail to race 3 wide last trio, last turning in, shaken up 400m, sound headway under strong drive.
Smart start, raced 4th 1 back on rail, driven into stretch, outpaced & weakened in run.
Crowded start, raced rear 1 off with cover, ridden 430m, ran on for minor inroads.
Sharp break, soon outpaced & sat 1 off near rear, shifted 3 wide 600m, very wide into stretch & driven 400m, plugged on tepidly.
Driven to race handy wide no cover, slotted in 3 wide 600m, driven under pressure 400m, found little & weakened in run.
Fast start, snagged to race 3 wide with cover near rear, forced 4 wide no cover 600m, widest into stretch, never a factor.
Slow start, raced rail in rear trio, niggled 800m, ridden 600m, struggled in weakening run home.
Broke with others, bustled wide to race 3 deep no cover midfield, driven on outer into stretch, found nil & faded tamely.
Slow start, raced stands' side last pair, ridden 400m, fair progress until picked up final 150m, surging late run & switched out close home to nail it last stride.
Moderate break, raced behind midfield 1 off stands' rail, shaken up for progress 500m, switched toward centre 200m, flashed home for 2nd last stride.
Sharp start, sat handy 3rd, shaken up 450m, kept on under strong drive to snag third final strides.
Reared start, rolled centre track to 2nd 700m, niggled 500m & soon driven, crossed to join leader 360m, won that duel but swamped close home.
Fast start, soon led & set sharp tempo, crossed to stands' rail 550m, driven 400m, emptied close home & swamped last strides.
Smart start, raced handy stands' side, ridden 430m, outpaced but boxed on.
Broke OK, raced mid rank, soon outpaced & drifted to last trio 700m, stayed on centre track for minor inroads.
Broke OK, raced centre track fore of midfield, ridden 550m, found little, tapered final 100m.
Tardy early stages, soon niggled midfield, off heels 450m, bumped rival 250m, plugged on one pace.
Sharp break to vie for lead, headed 800m & raced handy, ridden & outpaced 400m, found nil & faded thereafter.
Broke well & raced handy until unable to maintain sharp tempo from 500m, soon ridden, weakened tamely thereafter.
Tardy start, rolled to sit handy on stands' rail, soon back in midfield, hard-ridden 550m & wilted thereafter.
Tardy start, niggled along at rear toward centre, driven 400m, never a factor.
Moderate start, raced midfield, ridden under pressure 400m, fading tamely when bumped 250m, no extra.
Eased at start to take rail behind the field, immediately ridden aggressively to regain a midfield spot, 3Ls off the good pace, lack room 400M, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 0.5L at good pace, soon overhauled 400M but kept running on strongly for 2nd.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the good pace on the fence, blocked most straight, dashed well when clear.
Not mustered any speed, dropped to rear, 9Ls off the good pace along the fence, blocked whole straight but kept finding the line well.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on strongly until 100M flattened.
Eased to sit just off the leader 2 wide, pace good, ran on strongly until 100M, flattened.
Settled in box seat, pace good, blocked most straight, just ran on, not properly tested.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, progressed steadily 250M.
Midfield, 5.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, forced to race 5 wide from 700M, made steady ground in straight but without threats.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, just held ground in straight.
At back, 7Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, on heels 800M, blocked most straight, ran on well despite not being able to be properly tested.
Trapped 4-5 wide, never a factor, tailed out.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit just behind leader to turn. Hit front passing 400m and pulled clear for easy win.
Began well but not pushed, settling wide behind midfield with cover. Taken out turn, hung in badly but kept on steadily in straight to grab 2nd.
Ridden along early sitting one-off behind leading pack. No clear run early in straight and bumped, but finished off nicely when clear.
Began OK, raced between horses back stretch, tight around turn, taken out entering straight for clear run, ran on steadily.
Ridden along early to maintain forward position and left without cover 1000m. Covered extra ground turn, looked chance 400m, no extra final 200m.
Began well to lead initially before being eased into box seat. Looked chance entering straight but found little under pressure. One-paced.
Ridden along early behind leading bunch in one-off position. Took closer order turn, got inside run on straightening and kept on fairly without threatening.
Began awkwardly, dropping to rear away from fence. Made forward move turn, wide in straight, kept on fairly to be closest at finish.
Began awkwardly, ridden along but failed to muster and trapped wide without cover mostly. Pressed forward turn, looked chance 400m, one-paced.
Not pressured from wide draw, settling at rear but three-wide. Got close to heels around turn, one-paced in straight.
Pushed along early, settling along fence two-back from leader. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to near rear along fence. Lost position around turn and found nothing in straight under hard riding.
Hard ridden from wide draw to lead clearly before turn. Caught soon after entering straight and faded quickly.
Began awkwardly, dropping to last passing 1200m. Never competitive.
Broke sharply, always prominent behind leader, strode to lead nearing 300M, kept on well and always had enough to hold off the late challenge of 2nd.
Eased back to a midfield position, 3-4Ls back along the fence, got going inside 300M, raced greenly when placed under pressure but still made good progress to get within 0.5L of winner.
Held up towards the rear, stayed on moderately to go 3rd near line but posed no danger to first two.
Broke well, soon led, set even pace, headed by eventual winner 300M, one paced final 200M and lost 3rd near line.
Settled in mid-division, brought wide 500M, made good initial progress entering straight, one paced final 200M.
Pushed along early but failed to muster, dropped back to a rearward spot approaching home turn, made limited progress over final 300M.
Began only fairly, caught very wide without cover making the turn, not pace of leaders entering straight, weakened late stages.
Never far off from leaders but failed to respond entering straight, kept on same pace. (Blood in trachea)
In touch, gave little response turning home, faded mid-straight.
Restrained on jumping from a wide barrier, settled near last, was urged along nearing 500M but failed to respond, never a factor.
Settled in the group chasing leaders, 3-wide no cover turning for home, found disappointingly little when asked, never a threat to leaders.
Dropped back to last 7Ls off the pace, not picked up and never involved.
Quickly into stride, racing three-wide inside leader. Took over running passing 400m and kept on well under hard riding.
Began OK, sat close to fence behind leading trio. Got clear run passing 200m and finished off well.
Began awkwardly, checked and blundered. Made up ground between horses to sit behind leaders 400m. Kept on steadily without threatening.
Began awkwardly, checked and blundered. Taken to outside fence behind runners, made ground between horses, finished nicely when clear 200m.
Pressed forward to lead on settling. Lay-in mostly, collared 400m, tired gradually.
Ridden along early sitting in centre track behind leaders. Under pressure entering course proper but only one-paced.
Began OK, outpaced but held outer fence behind midfield. Pressed forward from 400m to be closest at finish.
Began awkwardly, ridden along between horses behind leading pack. Put under pressure from 400m but only one-paced.
Bumped start, taken towards outside fence behind midfield. Kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Outpaced, crowded for room 900m dropping to clear last. Shifted in to find clear running and finished off nicely.
Began OK, ridden along between horses moving to outside fence passing 400m. Tired gradually.
Jumped OK, no pace and taken closer to outside fence behind horses. Found little final 400m.
Bumped start, ridden along on own down centre track. Found little when asked passing 400m.
Began well, pressed forward to sit inside leader to halfway. Under pressure from 400m and gave ground quickly.
Began well from gate 13, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover throughout, 1-1/2 length back, slightly improved on turn, took the lead near 250M, kept on well to score a strong win.
Jumped well, showed early speed to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, headed near 250M, stayed on well to get 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide with cover in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position to turn, made good progress in straight to take 3rd.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide with cover in 5th, similar position turning, kept on evenly in straight to make frame, never a threat to the first few.
Crowded out start, raced 3 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run to turn, no daylight early in straight, made some headway when clear final 200M.
Slowly away, positioned 5 lengths back behind midfield, similar position turning, made some progress in straight without threatening.
Began well, taken back to race at rear, 7 lengths back, same position turning, made reasonable headway in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover until near 900M, 2 wide with cover turning, closed off fairly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, same position turning, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 3 wide with cover in 6th, same position turning, closed off one-paced in straight. (Had superficial abrasions to the right hock.)
Taken back from the widest gate, raced 8 lengths back at tail, still well back turning, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, no cover throughout, weakened early in straight and dropped off gradually.
Fairly away, positioned behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, made no progress in straight, eased final 100M.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 7 lengths back on rail, still well back turning, showed no response in straight, never competitive.

Tracked leader on rails, soon shaken up upon straightening, fought on dourly to just get up on line.
Soon took up running setting a steady pace, held pace under pressure in straight and nearly made all but only to be pipped at post.
Soon dropped to tail-end of field, waited with, saved good ground on rails turning for home, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Drifted back from a wide gate, travelled in last few to straight, shifted wide turning in, ran on inside final 250 metres to be nearest at finish.

Pressed on from a wide gate racing wide round stables bend eventually joining leader turning into back straight, remained similar to 250 metres when unable to sustain run under reminders, swamped for a placing close to home.
Jumped fairly settling in 6th off the rails in rear of midfield, similar turning in, ran home one-paced.
Soon taken back from the one gate, moved slightly closer up mid-way, failed to obtain a clear passage turning in and early in straight, made no further impression. (Blood in trachea)
Began well with leaders early, taken back to settle just off the pace but remained wide without cover throughout back straight and around home bend, soon faded after straightening.
Held rails run up with the pace early, ceded advantage to travel 2 wide in 5th about 2L off the pace coming out of stables bend, dropped away quickly after straightening.
With leaders early before shifting backward to race 3-wide in 7th just worse than midfield, remained similar far side, faded out into the last rounding home bend.
Ridden with purpose from a wide gate and parked 1 out 1 back on the circle. Had the race in its keeping 150m out.
Ridden along to race outside the leader. Maintained a sound gallop to the wire.
Raced keenly back in the field, 1 off with cover. Struck heels near the 800m, ad lost considerable ground when badly checked. Kept finding the line.
Got some cover on the circle behind the speed, 2-3 deep. Kept grinding away down the home stretch.
Ridden handy, got some cover on the circle, 3 deep. Kept on only evenly in the home stretch.
Raced wide and at the back of the field with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Worked forward and crossed to lead on the fence in the early stages. Was overhauled at the 400m and gave in quickly down the running.
Began awkwardly then received some inference approaching the first turn while racing on the fence with cover, midfield. Never looked likely thereafter.
Slow to begin settling with the backmakers on the paint with cover. Copped a check near the 800m, never recovered.
Had every possible chance after tracking the leader on the fence. Was a spent force well before the furlong.
Was going to take up 1 out 1 back position, but became badly unbalanced after being galloped on near the 800m. Lost significant ground and was never in the hunt finishing distant.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, finished off strongly to score by a narrow margin.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on strongly however weakened final 50M, just beaten by a neck.
Showed good early speed as usual to take the fence and led, stayed on nicely for 3rd.
Rolled to occupy the box seat, ran on steadily for 4th.
Taken back from the wide gate, then settled 6Ls off the leader 3 wide, closed to the line strongly.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on one pace until final 100M weakened.
Hard ridden to settle midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced home.
Travelled midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace in straight.
Began slowly, then failed to muster pace despite hard ridden along throughout, never ran on.
At rear throughout, never looked likely.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward to settle 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, soon flattened after straightening.
Broke OK, lacked early pace, raced 1 off behind midfield, ridden & shifted wide into stretch, swept home to lead close home.
Speed to lead on rail, shaken up & kicked on 350m, ran home well but overhauled last strides.
Moderate break, raced 1 back on rail, driven 400m & shifted out, battled on to edge 3rd.
Tardy break, soon rolled to sit rail midfield, switched 1 off & driven 430m, shifted wider in stretch, boxed on for inroads, just missed frame.
Missed break & bustled, settled rail near tail, shifted out on turn & ridden, progress checked & switched back inside 200m, ran on for sound gains.
Smart start, raced 1 back 1 off, shaken up 400m, outpaced and plugged on evenly to wire.
Sharp break, bustled wide to slot outside leader 900m, hard-ridden 2nd turning in, boxed on until emptied & swamped 150m, faded out.
Tardy break & outpaced early, niggled on rail behind midfield, shifted out 430m, not clear run, shifted wider 300m, plugged on.
Taken back from widest gate, rolled to 3 deep behind midfield, hard-ridden turning in, kept on one pace.
Good break, steadied & settled 1 off with cover midfield, ridden along 550m, switched out in stretch, tepid run home.
Broke OK, rolled to sit handy 3 wide no cover, ridden under pressure 500m, soon emptied & faded tamely.
Taken back at break, raced 3 wide near tail, hard-ridden 650m, found nothing in stretch.
Rousted early from wide to race 3 deep with cover midfield, ridden into home turn, found little & weakened out closing stages.
Taken back to last from wide gate, niggled & losing touch at tail 500m, never a factor.
Broke well, settled midfield 1 off, smooth traveler & switched very wide for clear run 500m, shaken up 250m, swept to lead close home.
Smart start, stalked leading trio, switched 3 wide on home turn, driven to lead 340m, grinding run, all out & headed close home.
Slow start, soon at tail, 13L back & driven backstretch, progress to 6L back 400m, shifted out & driven, strong closer to take 3rd.
Good start, raced rail midfield, ridden 750m, switched out into stretch & driven, progress to 2nd 200m, flattened out closing stages.
Slow start, bustled along near tail, closed to 6L back 400m & widest into stretch, closed off well for solid gains.
Broke well, driven early to settle 3 wide fore of midfield, niggled back stretch, very wide & hard-ridden home turn, boxed on evenly.
Driven at break to press lead 1 off, niggled along 800m, 2nd & under pressure into home turn, tapered in run home.
Tardy start & rousted to race behind midfield, under pressure when bumped home turn & unbalanced, plugged on one pace.
Snagged back at break & soon bustled to rail behind midfield, driven back stretch, all out home turn & struggled in run home.
Broke well, ridden 3 wide 1st turn & pressed lead, began to fade 590m, weakened tamely.
Speed to lead on rail, soon joined at head, edged outright lead 1200m, pressed throughout, driven 400m, soon headed & folded tamely.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed strongly 250M to win with some in hands.
Trapped 3 wide early, but soon settled just off the leader 2 wide, enjoyed the slow tempo, closed off strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, lack room 400M, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased to sit 2.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, held up 400M, just ran on when clear.
Bumped start, hard ridden forward to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 150M flattened.
Slow away, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, not tested.
At back, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased to sit in midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
Very slow away, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Bumped start, never traveled, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leader, suited by the slow pace but trapped 3 wide throughout, soon emptied 300M.
Began OK, taken closer to outside fence, picked up momentum from 500m, charged through split 150m, won handily.
No early pace, dropping to last passing 700m. Came off outer fence passing 400m, and finished off strong final 150m.
Slow into stride, last on settling, made ground down centre track, under pressure from 400m, finished off well.
First into stride, set steady pace, joined and under pressure from 200m, kept on well till flattened final 50m.
Lost ground start, picked up quickly to sit in midfield 500m, switched in 200m, hampered 150m when baulked for run. Kept on.
Began well, rolled forward to stay with leading pack, looked chance passing 200, flattened 150m.
Quickly into stride, taken closer to outer fence to share lead 400m, bumped and hampered 150m, faded. (Substantial blood in trachea).
Pressed forward from gate 5 to race alongside leaders. Poked head in front momentarily before unbalanced 150m. Faded. (Bled from both nostrils).
Began OK but soon hampered. Stayed on centre track, rolled forward to sit behind leaders by 400m, before turning one-paced.
Began well but not enough speed and shuffled back to behind midfield 500m. Gave ground gradually.
Began OK, inconvenienced passing 900m, stayed on centre track to halfway mark before giving ground gradually.
Not hurried after the start, held up 3Ls behind leader along the inside, switched out near 250M, closed well to lead 100M out, strode clear.
Always prominent outside leader, ran on under pressure in straight but not finishing pace of winner final 200M, held on for 2nd.
Failed to muster speed despite ridden along, last turning in, shifted out under pressure in straight, stayed on well to claim 3rd but could never get near to the winner.
Strode forward from wide barrier, pressed leaders in a 3-wide position without cover, looked beaten at 200M but renewed effort to go 4th near the line.
Crowded for room at the start, raced at the rear along the fence, ran on steadily over final 200M. (Jockey questioned re riding in the straight.)
Broke sharply, raced keenly in the lead, joined by rivals passing 200M and unable to find extra, weakened to 6th.
Dropped back to the rear, taken wide 500M, stayed on mildly and never a serious threat.
Began only fairly, recovered to race just off leading trio, lacked the needed response when driven entering straight, weakened final stages.
Niggled along to hold his position, never travelled, dropped to near the rear approaching home straight, made no progress.
Shaken up early stages, tracked leaders, came up empty in straight, weakened to last 100M from home.

Jumped well from the widest gate, gradually came across with the leader to settle one off the rails, hit the front entering straight, hung on well.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace on rails, ran on steadily to reach 2nd closing stages.
Never far off, shifted out for a run entering straight, fought on steadily without threatening.
Niggled at early travelling in rear of midfield, raced keenly when steadied coming out of far side, fought on steadily from midfield into straight but without threatening.
Settled in rear of midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, ran on steadily.
Jumped well, niggled along to gain a prominent but wide without cover position, produced some late impression inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well from a high gate, soon took up running and held slender lead to 500 metres, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.
Slightly slow out, settled well behind, hampered on rails passing 900 metres, saved ground on rails turning in, baulked for a run early in straight, kept on well inside final 200 metres.
Settled towards the rear, crowded passing 900 metres, raced keenly around home bend, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Soon dropped to the last and trailed the field most of way.
Settled in forward of midfield, made no impression under pressure in straight.
Jumped moderately from a poor gate, travelled behind midfield out wide far side and around home bend, made no impression in straight (Tactic questioned)
Travelled 4 deep without cover on the circle, midfield. Raced keenly during the midsection, kept going in the straight, recording a tough win.
Raced ahead of midfield 3 deep had some cover on the circle. Angled out after the 600m, showed good determination in the home stretch.
Box seated in the early stages, was 3 back the fence approaching the 500m. Held up briefly early in the straight, finished off gamely.
Travelled 3rd from the rear 1 off with cover. Was under pressure after the 600m, closed off soundly.
Parked 4th 1 off the rails with cover. Was still in contention at the furlong but ended its run near the 150m.
Raced worse than midfield, 3 deep with cover. Finished off evenly.
Settled last, 1 off the rails with cover. Made steady ground in the home straight out wide.
Vied for the lead in the early and middle stages, eventually racing behind the leader on the rails with cover after the 500m. Was one paced down the running.
Coursed 3 wide without cover on the circle, eventually crossing to lead on the fence after the 500m. Held on reasonably in the final stretch.
Camped at the rear on the fence with cover. Failed to close off.
Travelled 3 back, 1 off the fence with cover after the 600m. Gave ground quickly after the furlong. (Heart Irregularity).
Settled worse than midfield on the fence with cover. Was a beaten horse at the 400m.
Ridden forward to take the lead and led by 1L at very slow sectionals, kept on strongly to score by 3/4L.
Pushed forward to sit 1L off outside the leader at very slow tempo, had every possible chance to pass the winner after straightening, however missed by 3/4L.
Taken back to rear, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the very slow pace, dashed well for 3rd.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, suited by the very slow sectionals, kept on one pace to the line.
Began fairly, then settled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the very slow tempo, progressed steadily.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the very slow pace, kept on until 150M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield, 3Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, hampered by the very slow sectionals, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader, harmed by the very slow tempo, never ran on.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, soon flattened after straightening.
Taken back at start, sat 1 off with cover near rear, shifted 3 wide 650m, wide in stretch & shaken up 400m, swept to lead 70m, pulled clear.
Steadied start, overraced back stretch, midfield 1 off with cover, driven turning in, battling run to snag 2nd at wire.
Tardy break, mustered to stalk 1 back on rail, switched 1 off for progress 400m, checked slightly 325m, driven to lead 160m, tapered & headed 70m.
Moderate break, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven 400m, outpaced a touch until stayed on for sound inroads final 150m.
Snagged to rear from widest gate, shifted out home turn, 7L back & wide into stretch, driven 350m, stayed on for notable gains.
Smart start, raced 3 deep with cover midfield, wide & driven into stretch, grinding run until tapered close home.
Taken back at break, rolled to sit behind midfield 1 off with cover, driven turning in & shifted out, boxed on evenly to wire.
Broke well, settled 1 off 1 back, switched 3 deep 500m, driven 300m to share lead, every chance but soon out-paced & tapered in run to wire.
Smart start, soon led, headed 1050m & posted outside leader, shaken up 400m, led 280m but all out & soon headed, faded in run.
Tardy start, bustled & worked to lead on rail 1050m, shaken up 300m, soon headed & faded.
Good start, unable to slot in, drifted back to last trio, driven wide home stretch, found little in tepid run.
Broke OK, bustled early to race midfield, driven into stretch, soon all out & weakened in run home.
Bustled at start, trapped wide, taken back to tail & ridden 900m, hard-ridden wide in home straight, plodded on same speed.
Slow start, raced rail near rear, niggled 650m, driven 500m, found little & struggled in run home.
Fair start, bustled to settle rail midfield, switched off fence & ridden 400m, dour progress initially until surged late to lead close home.
Moderate start, trapped 3 wide no cover midfield, rolled 4 wide on turn to vie for lead 500m, battling duel to nick 2nd, no match for winner's surge.
Broke well, sat 1 off no cover 3rd, shifted 3 wide final turn, smooth progress to lead 400m, battled in front but headed close home, pipped for 2nd at wire.
Broke OK, sat 1 off with cover fore of midfield, shuffled back & bumped on turn, driven 430m, shifted out & boxed on soundly.
Speed to lead, headed 1400m & led main group, closed on lead 600m & shifted 1 off, led 490m, shaken up & headed 400m, boxed on.
Missed break, mustered to race midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide on turn, hard-ridden 400m, ran home evenly.
Taken back from wide gate, sat last pair 1 off, to tail 800m, driven 430m, stayed on for minor late headway.
Broke OK, taken back to 3 wide near rear, shifted 4 wide for progress 700m, hard-ridden turning in, plugged on evenly.
Snagged back to tail from wide gate, wide progress 800m, hard-ridden turning in, boxed on centre track without threatening.
Tardy start, raced 1 off near rear, switched out 550m, hard-ridden for one-paced stretch run.
Smart start, raced 4th on rail, bustled 500m & driven into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Snagged back to rail, raced near rear, checked off heels 550m, shifted out turning in & driven, tepid run home.
Moderate start, mustered & led 1400m, soon surged 7L clear, reeled in 600m, headed 490m, soon beaten & weakened out.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Very slow away, 7Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, made early move 600M, dashed strongly 400M despite not suited by the slow pace.
In front of midfield, 4Ls off the leader along the rails, not suited by the slow pace, dashed well 300M for 3rd.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the slow tempo, held up 4-2, little dash when clear.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1.5Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on until 150M flattened.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed by the slow sectionals, out of fuel 200M.
Awkward away, checked early, 7Ls off the leader on the fence, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to obtain a more prominent spot in front of midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no progress.
At rear, 8Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Midfield, not suited by the slow pace, emptied 300M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Pressed forward to sit in slipstream of leader to straight. Unable to get run till passing 200m, bulldozed through narrow gap 150m, kicked clear inside final 100m.
Began well, rolled forward to sit outside leader to straight. Bumped several times 150m but unable match winner's finishing burst.
Jumped with field before being eased to find cover. Taken 3-wide 600m, widest into straight, ran on steadily.
Pressed forward between horses 2L from leader. Slightly inconvenienced half-way up the straight, kept on steadily.
Ridden along early to hold forward position but trapped 3-wide without cover mostly. Inconvenienced early in straight, boxed on.
Got off nicely but unable stay with early pace, dropping three-back along rail. Put under pressure entering straight but only one-paced.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, setting quick sections to 150m when bumped and unbalanced. Faded quickly.
Lost considerable ground at start and trailed field until passing tired horse final stages.
Began awkwardly, steadied, dropping to rear in a one-off position. Take out 400m, under whip 300m, found nothing.
Dropped back to a rearward spot 6Ls off the pace, patiently ridden, switched out 400M and quickened impressively, led near 100M, well in control.
Quickly seized the lead, led uncontested, responded well when driven along 300M, not finishing pace of winner and lost lead near 100M, held on for 2nd just.
Reserved along the fence about 3Ls off the pace, travelled well into straight, into clear 300M, closed off willingly just failed to catch 2nd.
Shifted across from wide barrier, settled in a 3-wide position 5Ls behind leader, ran on steadily for a promising 4th.
Shaken up early stages, tracked leader one out one back, had every chance in straight but lacked the needed response, one paced final 200M.
Began only fairly, ridden along to obtain a forward position just behind leader, failed to offer a serious challenge passing 400M, kept on same pace to the finish.
Held up 3-wide in midfield, had no cover for much of the way, kept on well first half of the straight, briefly went 2nd but couldn't sustain run late stages.
Restrained in a 2-wide position behind midfield. held up for clear running turning in, steadied 200M and lost momentum, unable to challenge leaders.
Taken across from wide barrier, settled in last 7Ls off the pace, stayed on over this shorter trip, did best work final stages.
Held up 2-wide, never far off from leader, failed to quicken when driven inside 400M, kept on same pace to line.
Towards the rear 5Ls off the pace, not picked up over this shorter trip, never involved.
Pressed forward to sit outside hind quarters of leader to straight, Shaken up 300m, took lead 200m, kicked clear.
Began fairly, settled behind midfield in one-off position. Shifted out from heels 400m, taken to centre track and ran on steadily while laying in under pressure.
Ridden along early to find one-off spot, 3-back from leader. Entered straight behind horses, bumped 300m, finished off nicely when clear.
Began OK, no early speed, dropping 4-back along fence. Taken out turning for home, switched in 300m, ran on steadily.
No early speed, settling towards rear in one-off position. Taken out entering straight and ran on steadily.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, setting good pace till 300m when gave ground steadily.
Began fairly, racing at rear away from fence before dropping to last around turn. Ran on fairly down centre track to be closest at finish.
Hard ridden from wide draw but took time to muster, settling 3-back in a one-off position by turn. Looked chance entering straight but unable close gap.
Began awkwardly and last on settling. Made up some ground around turn, kept on fairly in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit midfield in one-off position. Rolled forward entering straight, closest 200m, flattened.
Began OK, settling in box seat before turn, dropping three-back entering straight. Gave ground final 200m.
Pressed forward to sit behind early leaders but raced fiercely and didn't settle. Looked chance entering straight, still there 200m, flattened.
Slow into stride, settling at rear along fence. Improved position turn but tired soon after straightening for home.
Moderately away from gate 12, raced 2 wide with cover, 2-3 lengths back, similar position turning, finished off strongly and scored narrowly.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race in 3rd, 2 wide with cover turning, took the lead near 250M, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Began well, taken back to race 2 wide with cover behind midfield, 6 lengths back, angled out on turn, finished off strongly in straight to get 3rd, never a threat to the first two.
Average to begin, sat 2-3 lengths behind the leader on rail, saved ground to turn, made reasonable headway in straight to make frame.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced prominently in 2nd outside leader throughout, travelled well to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Slowly away, raced 5 lengths back on rail in midfield, similar position turning, no clear running early in straight, closed off evenly when clear final 150M.
Fairly away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5-6 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, taken widest in straight and made some progress.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover throughout, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide with cover behind midfield, 4-5 lengths back, similar position turning, finished off one-paced in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 4 wide without cover at rear until near 800M, 3 wide with cover turning, only passed a few tired runners in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 6-7 lengths back on rail, same position to turn, kept to inside after straightening, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, showed no response after turning in, eased final 150M.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide with cover at rear, 7-8 lengths back, well back turning, emptied early in straight, never competitive.
Average to begin, showed no early speed and raced at tail throughout, still well back turning, emptied early in straight, tailed-out, unacceptable performance.
