Began well to lead or dispute lead, responded well to assert authority inside final 300 metres.
Soon took up running and crossed for stands rails, held slender lead until headed over 200 metres out.
Began from a low draw, soon picked up prominent 3rd and crossed to stands side, unable to quicken with first two but hung on for a place.
Given reminders behind midfield early stages, shifted in for a clear coming onto course proper, ran on but unable to sustain run closing stages.
Travelled in midfield near the centre of the track, kept on well without threatening.
Settled in last few, finished off race well inside final 300 metres.
Broke well, settled just off the pace, kept on steadily without quickening.
Jumped fairly, settled just better than midfield on stands rails, ran home one-paced under pressure.
Jumped moderately, soon recovered to a prominent spot, hung in badly and not able to make any impression.
Jumped fairly, soon taken back to settle off the pace, inconvenienced by a badly hanging runner throughout critical stages. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Jumped fairly, soon taken across to stands side behind, tailed-off coming onto course proper, produced significant late progress inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly, always in last few.
Jumped moderately, always well behind.
Slowly away, raced in last few near the centre of the track, dropped away quickly from over 200 metres out.
Settled in 3rd position 2-3 off the fence, had cover at stages. Peeled out rounding the home turn had the race a furlong from home.
Went forward and led on the fence at leisurely pace. Stayed on well.
Coursed deep without cover in the early and middle stages, eventually rolling forward to race outside the leader after the 900m. Kept up a sound gallop down the running.
Tracked the leader on the fence, mostly had cover. Kept plugging away down the final stretch.
Went back from the outside alley, settling on the fence towards the rear with cover. Closed off satisfactorily.
Settled back in the field 3 deep with cover. Made a midrace move to improve 3 deep without cover after the 750m, racing on the speed. Was flat over the final 200m.
Crowded shortly after the start setting with the backmakers, 2-3 wide with cover. Battled away in the home straight.
Parked midfield on the paint with cover. Was a beaten horse before the home turn.
Settled 3 deep with cover. Was never a factor finishing well back.
Travelled well, midfield, 2 wide with cover. Came under pressure near the 500m, never responded and struggled in the straight. (To Trial).
Settled close to midfield, 3 wide with cover. Commenced to give ground approaching the home turn, finishing tailed out. (To trial).
Camped handy, despite travelled 3 wide without cover throughout, ran on strongly to score impressively.
Lacked early pace, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, swung widest turning in, finished off nicely for 2nd.
Raced midfield, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2-3 wide with cover, ran on well to get 3rd.
Pushed forward to settle 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on well for 4th.
Ridden forward to occupy the box seat, kept on one pace to the line without threatening.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, out of fuel 250M.
Began slowly, then travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace until final 150M weakened.
At rear throughout, never ran on.
At rear, despite ridden along throughout, never looked likely.
Ridden forward to lead on the fence, flattened badly soon after straightening. (Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
Sharp start, stalked lead 1 off, drew upsides 440m, led & shaken up 300m, scooted well clear for easy win.
Broke OK, bustled early to race handy midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 650m, shifted out 350m & driven, stayed on to 2nd 150m, well held.
Broke well & rousted to race 2nd 3 wide no cover, 3rd & driven 400m, outpaced & lost place in stretch, plugged on to nick 3rd at wire.
Speed to soon lead, crossed to rail 980m, pressed & driven 400m, headed 300m, no extra & faded to wire.
Broke OK, slid back near tail 850m, progress from 650m, shifted wide on turn & driven 400m, stayed on for minor headway.
Missed break, rolled to race 3 wide with cover midfield, bustled 600m, driven very wide into stretch, stayed on one pace.
Fast break, raced handy 4th 3 wide no cover, ridden 440m, found nothing in tame stretch run.
Tardy start & bustled to race handy midfield on rail, hard-ridden home turn, found nothing & tapered.
Lacked early pace & raced last trio 1 off, driven 700m, struggled in weak stretch run.
Broke well, caught wide no cover & taken back to last trio 3 wide, out of touch & ridden 480m, found nil.
Missed break & detached, rousted to join tail 700m, hard-ridden 500m, never a factor.
Sharp start, urged to lead 1100m & soon to rail, pressed & shaken up turning in, hard-ridden to maintain narrow advantage in stretch, held on.
Broke OK, bustled 1 off with cover midfield, wide & driven 450m, motored centre track to press leader, emptied close home & just held.
Moderate start, settled handy 1 off with cover, shifted out turning in & crowded, stayed on for late headway to make frame.
Smart start to dispute early lead, settled close 2nd 1 off no cover, driven to challenge leader 400m, emptied 200m & tapered.
Slow start & bustled on rail at tail, 6L back & under pump home turn, shifted out 250m & closed off for late inroads.
Smart start, slotted rail midfield, hard driven 450m, outpaced in stretch but shifted out & stayed on moderately.
Moderate start, rolled to sit 1 back on rail, overraced 900m, driven 400m, one-paced in run.
Broke OK, rousted wide to press lead 3 deep, close 3rd on home turn but emptied turning in & faded tamely.
Tardy start, settled last pair 1 off, driven 400m, struggled in run home.
Lacked early pace & raced 3 wide near tail, niggled 650m, ridden turning in, found nothing & never a factor.
Pushed to take rail, led by 1.5Ls and clocked advantageous slow sectionals, just hung on to win.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, demonstrated strong finishing efforts when clear.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow sectionals, closed off well for 3rd.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, made early move 500M, dashed strongly 300M.
Hard ridden early, 5.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden early, 3.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Pushed forward to cross, box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on until 200M flattened.
Box seat early, eased back further, 3.5Ls off the leader, checked 400M, harmed by the slow pace, ran on ok when clear.
Very slow away, 6Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, just ran on.
Pushed to keep up in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, emptied 250M.
Behind midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Began well, settling three-back the fence. Taken 3-wide to find clear running entering straight and battled strongly to just get up final strides.
Bumped, unbalanced start, pressed forward to lead on settling. Set steady sections to straight. Kept on well final 400m only to be run down on post.
Ridden along from inside draw to hold box seat on settling. Stayed on rail around turn, raced tight 350m, kept on well to be closest at finish.
Pressed forward to sit outside hind quarters of leader to straight. Raced tight passing 350m, kept on steadily.
Ridden along from wide draw to obtain forward position and trapped three or four wide without cover. One-paced in straight without threatening.
Began well but unable keep up, slipping back and moving closer to rail. Not much room top of straight, shifted out and kept on steadily.
Shifted out abruptly and bumped start, then unbalanced. Travelled nicely when settled, sitting in midfield with cover. Switched out top of straight but only one-paced.
Jumped OK, eased back and switched in to sit at rear along fence. Taken out entering straight and boxed on one-paced.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw to sit at rear in one-off position. Put under pressure 400m and ran past tired horses.
Ridden along three-wide with cover early before easing back to rear in one-off position. Widest into straight but only one-paced.
Ridden along to hold one-off, one-back position on settling. Carried out four-wide entering straight, gave ground gradually final 200m.
Caught 3-wide early but managed to find cover in midfield before the turn, responded to strong riding, took it up inside 150M, shifted in under pressure but maintained momentum to the finish.
Broke well, soon crossed to the lead and took them along at a steady pace, kept on well when pressed by pursuers in straight, not pace of winner inside 150M but safely secured the 2nd place.

Restrained in a midfield position, unable to shift out for clear run early straight, switched back to inner and loomed a threat behind leader, failed to find extra inside 200M, steadied near 50M and lost momentum.
Close up in 4th, stayed on moderately final 300M but not going the pace to challenge first three.
Away in good order, raced keenly behind leader, not quickened when driven 400M, checked mid-straight, one pace final 200M.
Held up behind midfield, outpaced by leaders passing 400M, never a threat.
Bustled along after the start, crossed to race one out one back, kept up with the pace until no extra mid-straight, faded to 7th.
Restrained to a rearward position 5Ls off the pace, failed to quicken turning home, never involved.
Dropped back to the rear from wide draw, lost ground when steadied near 800M, found little off the bridle entering straight, never a factor.
Settled at the back 7Ls off the pace, struggled to keep up 500M, made no progress in straight, well beaten.

Began fairly, gradually improved to a close up position, hit the front under pressure over 150 metres out.
Jumped well from the unfavourable low draw, soon came to hold slender lead or dispute lead, outsprinted close to home.
Jumped awkwardly, travelled behind midfield, switched in before switching back out for a clear run over 200 metres out, finished off race nicely. (Blood in trachea)
Jumped awkwardly, settled just off the pace early, lost position coming onto course proper, produced good late impression under pressure inside final 100 metres.
Soon taken back and travelled close to stands rails, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
Jumped awkwardly, raced keenly amongst leaders to the 200 metres, faded under pressure.
Not far off, soon came to join leaders disputing lead 400 metres out, unable to sustain effort inside final 100 metres.
Slow to begin, soon recovered to settle behind leaders, faded under pressure inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well from the one draw, settled in last few racing down the centre of the track without cover, made no impression closing stages.
Jumped well, settled amongst leaders, faded gradually from halfway out.
Slow to begin, soon taken to stands rails and dropped to the rear, ran past well-beaten horses closing stages.
Jumped well, ridden to share early pace along rails, unable to sustain effort halfway out.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace, faded away from halfway out.
Went forward and led on the fence after the 1100m, setting a slow tempo. Maintained a strong gallop down the running.
Posted 3 deep without cover, midfield. Finished off nicely despite the wide run in transit.
Hummed along from a wide gate and raced in 2nd position outside the leader. Stayed on gamely.
Raced midfield, on the paint with cover. Was still in contention 150m from home but peaked on its run soon after.
Camped midfield, 2 deep with cover. Ran on steadily in the straight.
Enjoyed a nice run box seating. Had every conceivable hope but was flat after the furlong and made no impression in the run to the line.
Parked fourth from the rear, 2 deep with cover. Made a mild bid without threatening.
Raced 3rd last, on the rails with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Parked 2nd last, 1 off with cover. kept on a the same speed in the home straight.
Raced in last position on the fence with cover. Was one paced in the final stretch.
Travelled worse than midfield on the fence with cover. Failed to close off.
Settled 4th 1 off with cover. Had every possible chance but was well beaten after the 300m.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo, finished off nicely to score by a short head.
Prominent, settled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast pace, ran on well for 2nd. (Rider dropped the whip 200M)
Ridden forward to take the lead 2 wide at fast sectionals, kept on strongly to get 3rd, just beaten by a neck.
At rear, settled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, dashed well for 4th.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast sectionals, however could not find a day night most straight, never tested.
Began very awkwardly, then settled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, ran on steadily.
Taken back, settled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast tempo, ran on fairly.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast sectionals, never ran on.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover, weakened badly 300M, tailed out.
Hard ridden forward to take the lead along the fence at fast pace, flattened badly soon after straightening, tailed out.
Broke well, camped rail midfield, driven 500m, shifted out 430m & dour progress to lead 50m.
Smart start to race 1 off with cover midfield, shifted out 600m, awkward on turn & soon ridden, wide stretch progress to press lead 100m, held in run.
Sharp start wide to lead, crossed to rail, hard ridden under pressure 330m, battled under strong drive to hold lead, all out & headed 50m.
Broke OK, niggled early stages, caught 3 wide midfield, very wide in stretch & stayed on for inroads under strong drive.
Good break, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven 500m, shifted very wide in stretch, rattled home for solid headway.
Snagged back to 1 off near rear, shuffled back to rail last pair 800m, switched out on turn, driven 400m, closed off for solid gains.
Broke OK, rousted early to settle 2nd outside leader, upsides turning in, vied for lead in stretch, emptied & tapered final 100m.
Missed break and bustled early to race rail near rear, driven & shifted out final turn, stayed on well for minor gains.
Rousted at break, settled 1 back 1 off 1000m, shaken up 430m & switched out, plugged on one pace.
Smart start, sat 1 back on rail, niggled 560m, driven 400m, switched out 300m, one-paced in run home.
Good start, sat 1 off with cover fore of midfield, hard driven turning in, soon emptied & eased.
Tardy break, sat rail behind midfield, ridden 500m, soon under pressure & struggled in run home.
Moderate start, 1 off behind midfield when overraced 1200m & 1000m, restrained to last trio, shifted out 650m, soon beaten in tame run to wire.
Missed break & rousted at tail, beaten turning in & never a factor.
Slow start, mustered to rail midfield, shuffled back 830m, soon regained spot, shifted out & driven 400m, bumped 300m, quickened to lead 150m.
Smart start wide, snagged to 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven widest into stretch, strong run centre to press lead 150m, held in final strides.
Good break, prominent on fence until settled handy 1 back 950m, shifted out turning in, vied for lead 350m, emptied 150m & tapered.
Tardy start, rousted to sit fore of midfield 3L back, switched out & driven 400m, quickened to narrow lead 220m but veered into rival & unbalanced, plugged on.
Smart start, settled rail fore of midfield, checked 850m, shaken up 300m, not clear run, daylight final 100m & closed of soundly.
Tardy break, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, under pump 400m, boxed on without threatening.
Sharp break to dispute early lead, headed & switched to sit outside leader in 2nd, driven to challenge 350m, outpaced & weakened in run.
Slow start, raced rail at tail, 7L back when switched out & driven 400m, stayed on centre track for minor inroads.
Rousted start, slotted 3 wide with cover midfield, shifted 4 wide & driven into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Rousted 3 deep to outright lead 1300m, worked clear to rail 950m, shaken up under pressure 330m, all out & headed 220m, faded.
Sharp break, taken back to camp rail near rear, steadied off heels 840m, ridden a touch 550m, driven turning in, shifted out & green in stretch, kept on moderately.
Broke OK, off heels 1150m to sit 1 off with cover midfield, shifted out & driven 400m, in contention when badly hampered 200m, faded thereafter.
Bustled at break, outpaced & soon raced 1 off near tail, wide into stretch & driven 400m, plugged on one pace.
Broke well, raced 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, driven 470m, outpaced when crowded & hampered 300m, eased when beaten.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, dashed well 300M to score with some in hands.
Hard ridden forward, 3.5Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in a more prominent spot, 3Ls off the fast pace, made some ground 300M.
Very slow away, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, lack room 400M, made steady ground 250M.
Behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, made some ground 200M.
Pushed forward, trapped 3 wide in the lead, harmed by the fast pace, out of fuel 250M.
At rear, 10Ls off the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 200M.
At back as usual, 7Ls off the leader 3-4 wide, suited by the fast pace, made early move 500M, progressed well until run ended 150M.
Pushed to take rail, shared the lead at fast sectionals, emptied 200M.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, however no progress.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader, suited by the fast tempo, ran on until 150M flattened.
Pushed forward to share the lead 2 wide, harmed by the fast sectionals, soon dropped off 400M.
Very slow away, never competitive.
Hard ridden early, eased back 1500m and caught 3-wide without cover from 1200m. Shaken up passing 500m, took over lead 200m, nothing in tank 50m but held.
Began awkwardly, got head up when close heels 1300m, dropping four-back, one-off. Close to heels again 500m, switched out and finished off straggly.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing 4-wide before taking lead passing 1200m. Caught 200m but kept on well until lost second place close to post.
Hard ridden from wide draw racing 5-6 wide into first turn before settling behind leader passing 1200m. Looked chance entering straight but one paced to line.
Began well, racing outside early leader before being shuffled back to fourth when outside horses crossed over. Under hard riding from 500m but one-paced.
Outpaced and trailed field back stretch. Switched out and shaken up passing 500m, widest into straight, kept on steadily.
Eased back from wide draw settling at rear in one-off position. Well back turning for home but ran on steadily between horses in straight.
Began OK, ridden along between horses to straight. Got inside run and looked chance passing 200m, one-paced.
Began well but caught wide passing 1500m, eased and taken in behind runners to find cover. Switched out 400m, loomed up 200m, flattened 100m.
Began fairly, staying close to rail at rear. Got inside run turning for home, made some ground initially, turning one-paced.
Jumped with field, ridden along to hold position before brushing running rail 1100m. Checked from heels 450m and lost ground. No extra.
Hard ridden to lead into first bend before settling third passing 1200m. Under pressure around turn, gave ground steadily from 450m.
Towards the outer of the field, always close up, quickened to lead 250M, kept on strongly and repelled challenges from both sides.
Settled 2Ls off the pace, responded strongly passing 200M, pressed winner all the way to the line.
Never far off from leaders, came through to challenge 300M out, briefly went 2nd inside 150M, well held by winner final stages.
Quickly into stride, crossed to lead along the Stands' rail, pressed by rivals 300M, gradually outpaced by first three final 150M but fought on well for 4th, not beaten far.
Settled in 5th just off the pace, not quickened with leaders inside 350M, stayed on for non-threatening 5th.
Held up 3Ls off the pace, ran on same speed final 400M, never a serious threat to leaders.
Not the quickest away, moved up to share the lead passing 600M, found less than expected when pressed by rivals near 200M, weakened final stages.
Held up towards the Stands' rail, kept on same pace final 400M, no threat to leaders.
Slow to begin, settled 3Ls off the pace midway, not quickened when pressed, weakened final 150M. (Blood in trachea.)
Crossed to race along the Stands' rail, 3-4Ls off the pace, picked up well passing 200M but soon ran into heels of horses in front, held up for clear running final 150M, not properly tested.
Settled on the outside of the field 3Ls off the pace, failed to quicken passing 400M over this shorter trip, faded away 200M.
In touch for the first half of the race, dropped away passing 400M, never threatened.
Never far off form leader, unbalanced 600M, found nothing when asked, beaten 300M out. (Bled.)
Outpaced in last, never travelled and detached from field halfway.
Began well from wide draw, eased to sit 3-wide at rear. Began forward move 800m, five-wide into straight, hit front 250m, challenged 150m but kicked clear.
Began fairly, racing between horses behind midfield. Switched widest into straight, rolled forward to join leader 200m, no extra.
Jumped well, cut in to hold rail behind leader. Shuffled back to fourth making turn, no clear run until 250m, finished off nicely.
Began fairly, sitting at rear in one-off position. Edged forward entering turn, wide into straight, ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Ridden along to hold forward position between horses but badly crowded 1400m. Bumped 900m. Switched out in straight and kept on steadily.
Hard ridden from wide draw to lead on settling. Passed by another entering turn, retook lead entering straight, kept on until swamped final stages.
Ridden along early to hold 3rd, became awkward when passed by outside horse. Closed in top of straight, looked chance 200m, kept on without threatening.
Taken forward from wide draw and held without cover passing 800m. Raced tight around turn, pressed forward entering straight, no extra close home.
Began well but badly crowded 1400m, dropping back but holding rail. Shifted out 900m, bumped, no run in straight. Not tested.
Began OK, racing along rail behind midfield. No run in straight until passing 200m, kept on when clear.
Outpaced, dropping to clear last on settling. Trailed field thereafter, passing tired horse final stages.
Began fairly, crowded 1400m then pulled hard. Steadied but caught without cover 1100m, rolled forward to lead 800m. 2nd into straight before tiring.
Moderately away, raced prominently in 2nd, travelled well to turn, closed off well in straight and scored by a neck. (Lost right front plate)
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide with cover in 5th, 2 lengths back, same position turning, taken to middle in straight and finished off strongly to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, recovered and took the lead, travelled well to turn, headed near 250M, but still kept on well to finish.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 2 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, angled out in straight and finished off very strongly to make frame.
Average to begin, positioned nicely behind the leader on rail in 4th, easy run to turn, kept on evenly in straight without threatening the first few.
Taken back from gate 7, raced 7 lengths back on rail, same position to turn, made reasonable headway in straight.
Bumped start, positioned 5 lengths back on rail in 8th, 2 wide with cover turning, finished off evenly in straight.
Moderately away, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide with cover in 7th, 3 lengths back, 3 wide with cover turning, made no progress in straight, just stayed on one-paced.
Began well from gate 11, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover in 3rd, same position turning, failed to close off in straight when hard run took effect.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide with cover, 4 to 5 lengths back, taken wider at turn, found no extra gear in straight and only stayed on evenly.
Blundered after the start and lost ground, raced at tail throughout, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.

Slow to begin, soon settled just off the pace on rails, switched off rails for a run coming onto course proper, quickened well to take charge 150 metres out.
Jumped well, settled in forward of midfield near the centre of the track, ran on steadily inside final 200 metres, nearest at finish.
Settled on rails in last few, ran home quite well under pressure inside final 150 metres.
Jumped fairly, settled mainly 2L off the pace in 4th, unable to sustain effort and faded inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly from the number one poor draw, soon settled in rear of field, produced good late impression under hard driving inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, shot to lead and obtained stands rails run after first 400 metres, folded up quickly under pressure inside final 150 metres.
Jumped fairly from the unfavourable low draw, settled towards the rear, switched in for a clear run over 400 metres out, found nothing.
Jumped well, settled in forward of midfield, came under pressure coming onto course proper, one-paced.
Jumped well, settled not far off the pace, gave ground steadily inside final 400 metres.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped to tail-end.
Camped behind midfield, 2 deep with cover. Ran on well.
Settled 2nd, 1 off with cover. Stayed on gamely, gave late ground.
Missed the start by 3-4 lengths but recovered to race midfield the fence. Finished off soundly.
Stalked the leader on the fence. Kept battling away well in the home stretch.
Travelled 4th, 1 off with cover. Kept grinding away down the running.
Settled last on the paint with cover. Kept plodding to the line.
Went back from a wide gate, settled second from the rear. Dour in the home stretch.
Had all the favors enjoying an uncontested lead on the rails. Was tiring at the furlong.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the slow sectionals, dashed well to score by 1L.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow pace, ran on well for 2nd.
Rolled forward to settle 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the slow tempo, kept on well to get 3rd.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behinds the leader 2 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slow pace, gradually moved forward from 600M, kept on steadily in straight.
At rear, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow sectionals, swung widest, ran on fairly.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide without cover, despite suited by the slow tempo, kept on only one pace until 100M weakened.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 2Ls at slow sectionals, run ended 300M.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow pace, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 4.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, never looked likely.
Broke OK, camped rail midfield, switched 1 off 900m, forced rival wide on turn for daylight, driven 400m, grinding run to lead last stride.
Awkward start wide, pace to lead 1200m & over-raced 1 off, soon restrained & vied for lead, driven clear 400m, all out close home, mugged at wire.
Broke OK, soon mustered to lead on fence, headed 1200m, shared lead from 950m, shaken up 400m, outpaced but boxed on to wire.
Broke well from widest gate, slotted midfield 3 wide with cover 900m, shifted widest into stretch & driven, closed off soundly.
Broke front rank, snagged to race 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven very wide into stretch, ran on centre track for solid headway.
Broke well, raced fore of midfield 1 off with cover, progress to stalk 1 back 900m, raced keenly, driven 430m, one-paced in stretch.
Broke in front rank, snagged to camp 1 back on rail, over-raced 1000m, driven 400m, kept on one pace.
Taken back from wide gate, raced 3 wide in rear, 6L back & driven widest into stretch, kept on centre track for moderate gains.
Sluggish start, sat last pair on inner, driven 500m, plugged on for minor gains.
Taken behind to race rail near rear, over-raced 1000m, progress 600m, shifted out into stretch, plugged on evenly.
Missed break & rousted to race 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven 850m, hard-ridden 500m, plugged on same speed.
Tardy start, rousted wide no cover to sit 3rd, settled 3 deep outside lead, driven 500m, found nothing & faded tamely.
Smart start, prominent early, settled 3 wide with cover fore of midfield, pushed wide on turn & driven, tapered weakly in stretch.
Tardy start & raced 1 off near rear, progress on turn, 4L back when shifted out turning in & driven, closed gradually to lead 150m, edged clear.
Fast start, raced handy 1 off with cover, shifted out & ridden 430m to close on lead, kept on to clear 2nd 50m, no match for winner.
Speed at break, sat 1 back on rail, shifted out on turn & driven 430m, quickened to lead 350m, all out & headed 150m, tapered to wire.
Sharp break, settled 5th 1 off with cover, drifted to rail 750m, switched out 400m & driven, stayed on evenly.
Smart break, settled 1 off with cover midfield, shifted wide turning in & driven, sound progress until tapered late.
Tardy start & rousted, soon 2nd last on rail, niggled throughout & driven 550m, shifted out in run & stayed on for minor inroads.
Slow start, bustled 1 off behind midfield, hard-ridden 550m, ran home one pace.
Started well, taken back & soon at tail 1 off, 6L back when shaken up 400m, kept on for modest gains.
Tardy start, raced midfield on rail, checked off heels 750m & shuffled back a spot, under pump 470m, switched out in stretch, plodded on one pace.
Rousted wide to lead 1000m, crossed to fence, pressed 650m, headed 350m & driven, faded out & eased closing stages.
Moderate start & bustled, raced wide no cover near rear, driven wider into stretch, struggled in run home.
Smart start, pace to sit 2nd 1 off no cover, pressed leader on outer & matched strides from 650m, emptied 350m, & quickly folded.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, lack room 400M, dashed strongly when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden forward, settled just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Pushed to obtain box seat, favoured by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, closed off well for 3rd.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the slow pace, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Pressed forward, took rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon weakened 350M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, no dash.
Slow away, harmed by the slow pace, never a factor.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, bumped 400M, flattened 300M.
Quickly into stride, settling half a length inside leader about 3-away from outer fence. Edged closer entering course proper, hit front 250m, pulled clear.
Began OK, settling behind leading trio to course proper. Got run between horses passing 250m and finished off nicely.
Ridden along early to hold forward position 4-away from outer fence. Shaken up passing 400m, rolled forward to sit second 250m, lost quinella spot close to lune.
Began well, not pushed, sitting outside early leader to half way. Allowed to roll forward to lead momentarily 300m then one-paced. Raced tight closing stages.
Began fairly, unable match early speed, settling at rear. Switched in 370m and ran on steadily.
Began well, unable match early speed and shuffled back, one-away from outer fence. Unable to find run approaching 300m, kept on one-paced.
Reared start, slow into stride, then outpaced becoming detached. Switched in approaching course proper and ran past tired horses.
Began well, holding outer fence behind leading trio. Awkwardly placed 800m, raced tight 600m, crowded for room 300m and eased, hands and heels final stages.
Broke best and soon in lead racing keenly. Came off bridle 400m, got head up 300m, faded. (Elevated muscles enzymes with muscle pain).
Driven forward from a wide barrier, settled outside the leader, quickened to lead 300M out, dug in gamely final stages to keep rivals at bay.
Began well, settled behind leaders in 4th, chased eventual winner from 300M, always held.
Held up towards the rear, 6Ls behind leaders and taken out 500M, gained ground steadily and narrowly missed out on 2nd place.
Led early stages, stalked the pace passing 1000M, held up behind the weakening leader until 250M, ran on evenly when clear but was always held by winner.
Dropped back to the rear 7Ls off the pace, brought wide to challenge entering straight, closed off last 400M fastest, nearest line.
Rushed to the lead on jumping from a wide draw, ran on same pace when joined by rivals passing 300M, weakened final stages.
Niggled along to hold a position ahead of midfield, 3Ls to make up 400M, ran on same pace and unable to make headway on leaders.
Reserved in midfield 5-6Ls behind leaders, checked at 350M, failed to respond appreciably over this shorter trip, never a threat to leaders.
In mid-division, proved difficult to settle for a considerable distance near 900M, gave limited response when driven, never got near leaders.
Began awkwardly, ended up near the rear over 7Ls behind leaders, angled out advancing entering straight, hampered 350M, ran on only fairly.
Dropped back to last 8-9Ls off the pace, made only limited progress turning in, never reached contention.
Settled in midfield along the 2-path, came up empty turning home, weakened rapidly final 250M.

Ridden along early before easing off hot pace to settle in a one-off position in midfield. Checked 550m when close to heels, switched out for run 370m, hit front 170m, pulled clear. (Rider dropped whip 100m).
Jumped well from wide draw, ridden along while looking for cover, settling towards rear though 3-wide. Entered straight behind horses, switched out 350m, finished off well.
Jumped OK, no pace, taken in behind horses but held three-wide at rear. Widest into straight and battled on gamely.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward from wide draw, bumped 1350m before settling in one-off position behind leading trio. Rolled forward from 400m to share lead momentarily. Boxed on.
Began well, outpaced and last on settling. Moved up before turn, switched wide entering straight, still well back 200m, finished off strongly.
Hard-ridden to hold forward position, then raced keenly under hot tempo hilding leader three-wide. Rolled forward entering straight, looked chance 200m, one-paced final 100m. (Jockey reprimanded).
Began fairly, ridden along earlier but unable stay with pace, settling towards rear in one-off position. Found inside run on straightening and ran on nicely. Close to heels final stages.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling but three-wide without cover, setting fast second section. Still in front 250m before tiring gradually.
Began fairly, ridden to make up ground, settling in slipstream of leading trio along rail. No run early in straight but a spent force when one opened up close home.
Not pressed early, settling three-back the fence. Got head on side when awkwardly placed 700m, checked 550m when crowded for room. One-paced in straight.
Began OK, tried to find cover but hampered 1200m when crowded. Raced three-wide thereafter. Wide into straight, one-paced.
Hard ridden from inside draw, holding rail a half-length behind leader. Joint leader into straight but soon under pressure and faded.
Pressed forward to hold forward position behind fast pace to turn. Gave ground soon enter straightening.

Placing: PU
Comment: Began OK, ridden along wide before easing back to last. Became detached from field entering turn and pulled up. (Fractious and dislodged rider before start. Unacceptable performance).
Began well from the widest gate, showed early speed to take the lead and set a moderate tempo, travelled well to turn, kicked clear entering straight and won comfortably.
Moderately away, positioned 2 wide with cover in 5th, 2 lengths back, bumped near 1200M, same position to turn, made reasonable headway in straight to get 2nd.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back, improved on turn, finished off well in straight to get 3rd.
Began well from gate 7, race prominently in 2nd, same position to turn, kept on evenly in straight without threatening.
Average to begin, positioned a length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off evenly in straight, just missed frame.
Jumped with them, positioned 4 lengths or so back on rail behind midfield, similar position turning, taken wide in straight and made some progress without threatening the first few.
Crowded out start, raced 2 wide with cover in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position turning, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, similar position turning, made minor headway in straight.
Taken back from a tricky gate, raced 5 lengths or so back at rear, similar position turning, made some headway in straight.
Jumped fairly, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover in midfield until near 800M, 3 wide with cover turning, steadied early in straight, closed off one-paced thereafter.
Slowly away, positioned 7 lengths back at tail, improved on turn, 4 wide without cover, taken wide in straight and finished off one-paced.
Began awkwardly, recovered and positioned 2-3 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Average to begin, raced 5-6 lengths back at tail on rail, similar position to turn, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Moderately away from gate 11, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover throughout, emptied early in straight, dropped off gradually.

Driven to lead from the widest gate, obtained rails run 800 metres out and held clear running to finish.
Jumped moderately, raced keenly in rear of midfield, ran on well inside final 300 metres to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, gaining to 4th along rails about 3L off the pace coming out of back straight, switched off rails for a run turning in, made moderate late progress without threatening.
Sluggish at start, settled in rear on rails, made significant progress inside final 200 metres.
Niggled along mainly one back on rails, ran home one-paced.
Soon dropped to last few, hung in under pressure 200 metres out before making some late headway. (Tactic questioned).
Settled in rear of midfield on rails, ran home one-paced.
Settled at the back after beginning from a poor draw, trailed the field to 200 metres, never nearer.
Broke well from a moderate gate, settled just off the pace, inconvenienced when crossed by leader and eventual winner 800 metres out, folded up quickly after straightening.
Close up early, gradually settled in midfield, dropped away quickly after straightening.
Made its run third from the rear racing on the paint with cover. Commenced a forward move after the 550m and finished off well to have the race in its keeping 100m from the line.
Settled behind midfield, 2 wide with cover. Became badly unbalanced near the 550 but recovered and ran on soundly.
Camped 2nd, ¾L back, outside the leader. Was in front approaching the furlong, grudgingly gave ground late.
Travelled 2nd from the rear, 1 off with cover. Closed off fairly.
Slow to begin, settling midfield the paint had cover. Only plodded to the line.
Settled just off the speed, but posted 3 deep without cover for most of the trip. Labored in the home stretch. (see incident report)
Enjoyed an uncontested lead on the fence, setting slow fractions. Was gone at the 200m.
Parked 4th on the rails with cover. Angled out into clear running early in the straight but made no impression and weakened easily over the final 100m.
Settled at the rear of the field, on the paint with cover. Failed to close off.
Had every possible hope after settling ahead of midfield, 1 off with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Settled in front of midfield 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, switched with turning in, dashed on strongly to score impressively.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on nicely to get 2nd.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on ok.
Taken back, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, dashed on well.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls off the leader 3 wide without cover until 600M, ran home one paced.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 1/2L, kept on until final 100M weakened.
Began awkwardly, then settled worse than midfield 5Ls off the leader on the fence, made minor ground.
Raced midfield, settled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
Began slowly, then travelled 7ls behind the leader on the fence at rear, kept on one pace to the line.
Broke OK, caught wide early & slotted 1 off near rear, driven 430m, gradual progress & shifted out 200m, kept on centre track to snatch lead late.
Fast break, settled midfield 1 off with cover, edged out & bumped rival 430m, driving progress to vie for lead 200m, pipped final strides.
Sharp start, raced 1 off 1 back, 3rd & shifted 3 wide on turn, driven to challenge, battling run to maintain position.
Driven wide, slotted outside leader 830m, pressed lead turning in, edged ahead & driven 350m, all out & headed 50m, swamped close home.
Broke OK, lacked pace & bustled rail behind midfield, driven turning in, progress & switched 1 off 200m, closed well to just miss frame.
Taken back from wide gate, sat 3 wide at tail, progress on turn, forced very wide into stretch, 6L back 400m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Broke well, bustled early, settled 1 off behind midfield, shifted out & bumped rival home turn, boxed on centre track.
Broke OK, bustled to race rail midfield, shifted 1 off home turn, driven 400m, kept on one pace.
Slow start & driven early, raced rear on rail, hard-ridden 430m, stayed on for moderate gains.
Taken back to race in rear 1 off, shifted wide into stretch, off heels 400m, driven & sound progress until checked 100m & eased.
Rousted to lead 1100m, pressed on turn, headed 350m & ridden, tapered tamely thereafter.
Broke in front & rousted, soon outpaced & raced 3 wide with cover midfield, bumped & forced wide turning in, plugged on tepidly.
Broke well, stalked 1 back on fence, off heels 840m, attempted to shift out 400m, hemmed in, driven 300m, found nothing & faded.
Speed early to race prominently until checked 900m, caught 3 wide no cover handy, under pressure when bumped turning in, found nothing & faded.
Outpaced & rousted early, settled inner near tail, switched out & shaken up 450m, crowded in run until surged from 150m out to lead last strides.
Broke well, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, lost cover 1000m, ridden 600m for wide progress, driven to lead 250m, all out 50m, tapered & headed late.
Good start, settled 1 off behind midfield, shifted wide & driven into stretch, quickened to 2nd 200m, all out 100m & lost place in run to wire.
Taken back at break, camped 3 wide with cover, wider & driven turning in, stayed on centre track for sound headway.
Moderate break, bustled early to sit handy on rail, shifted to midfield 950m, shifted out & driven 430m, plugged on one pace.
Speed to lead on rail, pressed 1200m & settled 1 back on fence, shifted 1 off 700m, 3 wide to press lead 430m, emptied 200m & tapered.
Snagged back from wide to race at tail, driven into stretch, outpaced in rear but plugged on evenly for minor late gains.
Fast break, trapped 4 wide no cover, rolled to vie for lead 1200m, slotted 1 back 1 off 980m, ridden 650m, outpaced in stretch & plodded on.
Awkward start & rousted, sat 2nd until vied for lead 1200m, to rail 950m, narrow 2nd & driven 400m, swamped 250m & no extra.
Broke well, caught 3 wide no cover handy, rolled to vie for lead 1200m & raced 1 off, narrow lead & driven 400m, swamped 250m & weakened out.
Broke OK & rousted to sit 1 off with cover midfield, niggled 700m, shifted out & under pump 500m, plodded home tamely.
Awkward start & bustled, settled rail behind midfield, niggled 900m, under pump 600m, struggled in tepid stretch run.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed strongly 350M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Hard ridden to taka the rail and led by 0.5L, clocked advantageous slow sectionals, just hung on to share the win.
Pressed forward, sat outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on for 3rd.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated good finishing efforts 250M.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, little dash 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on until 100M flattened.
Very slow away, pushed to keep up in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 3Ls off the leader on the rails, not suited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 200M.
At back, 6Ls off the leader 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, emptied 300M.
At back, 6.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, checked 400M, no progress.
Very slow away, never competitive at rear.
Hard ridden forward, 3Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, soon dropped off 400M.
Eased back, never a factor.
Began well, led before easing back 1050m to sit 3rd. Pocketed top of the straight, forced through narrow gap 120m to win pulling clear.
Began well, with leading trio to 1000m before sitting on tail of leader around turn. Rolled forward top of straight, hit front 200m, run down near post.
Outpaced, dropping to near last away from fence. No clear run top of straight, switched in and then out, flashed home strongly when clear.
Began awkwardly and bumped, settling at rear between horses. Got clear running top of straight and ran home strongly.
Began well, ridding along to grab one-back, one-off position. Rolled forward top of straight, joint leader 250m, flattened final 50m.
Began OK, held together, settling 4-back from leader. Switched out top of straight, looked chance 250m, one paced.
Began OK, outpaced and soon clear last. Trailed field to straight, ran on steadily along the inside though passage closed 100m.
Jumped with field, revved up passing 1100m to lead 1050m. Showed clean pair of heels to straight before running out of stamina and dropping back.
Began well, taken closer to fence sitting midfield between horses. Got clear running 300m but unable to accelerate.
Jumped fairly, taken in from wide draw but held 3-wide without cover in midfield. Covered extra ground turn and one-paced in straight.
Ridden along to hold rail but outpaced, dropping toads rear. Looked for inside run top of straight but found nothing under hard riding.
Taken in soon after start but held 3-wide towards the rear. Swung widest into straight but only one-paced.
Guided to a midfield position, 3-wide turning for home, driven 400M, joined leaders 100M, rallied under urging to get up late.
Strode to the lead from 12, led evenly to straight, driven 350M, had 1L lead over pursuing rivals at 200M, kept on well up the fence, joined by rivals 100M out, edged close home.
Tracked leaders along the fence, into clear nearing 300M, closed off soundly to be right there at the finish, narrowly beaten.
Dropped back to near the rear, 5Ls off the pace in middle stages, switched out 350M and closed off well for creditable 4th.
Within striking distance 2Ls of leaders, held up badly until 200M, stayed on steadily when clear.
Held up behind midfield, lay in under pressure in straight and proved difficult to ride, stayed on moderately over final 200M.
Settled 3-wide in mid-division, brought wide 500M, ran on steadily but not getting to first three.
Close up behind leaders, pushed to a 3-wide spot with no cover from 750M, unable to sustain run inside 200M, weakened towards finish.
Reserved in a rearward position along the inside, had plenty to do turning in, stayed on well making stealthy progress final stages.
Held up in midfield 3Ls behind leaders, ran on same pace final 400M, never got into contention.
Never far off 2-3Ls off the pace but failed to quicken with leaders passing 400M, out of contention 200M.
Outpaced from the start, 7-8Ls behind leaders, not picked up turning in, never a factor.
From barrier 13 crossed to race outside leader, gave only brief response turning in, weakened rapidly passing 300M.
Jumped best, led before eased 1000m to sit behind leader. Had to angle out for run 300m, hit front but immediately challenged, just held.
Began well, ridden along two-back, one-off to straight. Swung wide, took a few strides to pick up momentum, flashed home.
Pressed forward to share lead before settling one-off, one-back around turn. Rolled forward entering straight and battled strongly to the line.
Began well, pushed hard to hold rail inside leader around turn. Rolled forward to lead into straight, battled strongly only to lose placing on line.
Began fairly, taken in behind runners but kept away from fence. Lost ground when checked off heels 600m, finished strongly down centre track when clear 350m.
Ridden forward from wide draw. Shifted in 1000m and bumped. Raced in restricted room 900m before settling three-back, one-off. Ran on in steadily in straight.
Ridden along early before shifting across behind runners. Last around turn, got inside run but taken out final stages when finishing nicely.
Hard ridden three-wide to lead into turn. Raced keenly when taken in to one-off position. Still in contention 200m before checked off heels final stages and eased.
Hard ridden from wide draw to hold forward position, sitting 3-wide without cover. Still wide entering straight, kept on fairly till flattened final 50m.
Began OK, taken in gradually to hold rail four-back from leader. Shifted about in straight but only one-paced.
Bumped start, no speed, drifted back but held 3-wide mostly. Taken very wide into straight but only one-paced.
Jumped OK, quickly on rail behind leader, but shuffled three-back entering turn. One-paced in straight.
Began well, raced keenly three-wide back stretch. Bumped and unbalance turn, swung wide, hands and heels riding in straight.
Ridden along 4-wide back stretch without cover. Covered extra ground turn, widest into straight, found nothing when asked.
Began awkwardly, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, same position to turn, taken wide in straight and finished off very strongly to score, comfortably.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide with cover in 6th, 3 lengths back, slightly improved on turn, finished off well without posing any threat to the winner.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced 3 wide with cover in 5th, similar position to turn, kept on steadily in straight, just missed 2nd.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 6 lengths back at rear, 3 wide with cover turning, taken widest in straight and finished off well in straight to make frame.
Moderately away from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, similar position to turn, closed off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back, same position to turn, no daylight early in straight, made some progress when clear thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 7 lengths back at tail, slightly improved on turn, taken wide in straight and made some progress.
Slowly away, raced 7 lengths back at tail, still well back turning, made minor headway in straight.
Average to begin, positioned 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, showed early speed to take the lead from near 1100M, enjoyed easy lead turning, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Slightly slow away, recovered and raced in 3rd on rail, easy run turning, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 2-3 wide in 4th, no cover turning, emptied in straight after hard run took toll.
Steadied start, raced 5 lengths back on rail at rear, same position turning, emptied early in straight, finished tailed out, unacceptable performance.

Jumped well from the one draw settling inside lead, crossed by the leader rounding home bend, commenced move over 200 metres out hitting front shortly afterwards, just held on.
Jumped fairly, gradually taken back to settle in middle of small field, shifted out for a run approaching home turn, ran on steadily to just fail to get up on line.
Jumped fairly, ridden along to hold prominent position early, 2-wide in 2L 3rd rounding home bend, kept on steadily without threatening.
Broke well holding narrow lead outside 2nd, obtained rails run in front about 500 metres out, led until overhauled 150 metres out. (Tactic questioned)
Jumped moderately, ridden to pick up on rails to 1.5L 4th over 800 metres out before easing off heels coming out of back straight, ran home at the one pace.
Travelled wide without cover behind midfield after beginning from a poor draw, ran home one-paced.
Slowly away, raced well behind of the small field most of way. (Tactic questioned)
Soon dropped to the tail-end of the small field, never seen with a chance.
Parked 2nd, 1 off no cover. hit the front near the 300m and repelled late challenge to register game win.
Enjoyed the box seat. Kept grinding away right to the post.
Made the running on the fence. Faded over the latter stages.
Travelled ahead of midfield, 1 off with cover. Made some late ground to finish in the frame.
Parked 4th, 1 off with cover. Kept plugging away in the home stretch.
Camped worse than midfield, 1 off the rail with cover. Kept whacking away in the run to the line.
Went back from a wide gate, racing 3rd last, 3 deep with cover. Made steady progress in the stretch.
Slowly away, settling midfield on the fence with cover. Stayed on at the same speed down the running.
Not the best to begin racing 2nd last on the rails with cover. Was one paced in the home stretch.
Raced back in the field, 2-3 deep with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Travelled near the rear, on the paint with cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Settled at the rear, 1 off with cover. Failed to close off.
Throughout the race, travelled 3wide and without cover, behind midfield. Never likely.
Camped handy, suited by the track that favoring front runners, fought on strongly to score in a tight finish.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls 3 wide with cover, gradually moved forward from 700M, suited by the track that favoring front runners, kept on well to get 2nd.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, benefited by the track that favoring front runners, hung on well for 3rd.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the track that favoring front runners, closed off nicely for 4th.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite not suited by the track that favoring front runners, ran on ok.
Camped handy, despite benefited by the track that favoring front runners, kept on one pace until 100M weakened.
Taken back, settled 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite hampered by the track that favoring front runners, made some ground in straight.
Prominent, despite suited by the track that favoring front runners, out of contention 250M.
Eased start, settled 4.5Ls behind the leader, made an early move from 700M, however trapped 5 wide without cover, no turn of foot after straightening.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the track that favoring front runners, never looked likely.
Broke well, sat 1 off with cover midfield, shifted out & driven turning in, quickened to lead 190m, ran home strongly.
Smart start, sat rail midfield, overraced 850m, shuffled back on turn, crowded 400m, shifted out & shaken up 350m, quickened & closed to 2nd late.
Good start, eventually settled 1 off with cover 4th, switched out & driven 400m, challenged lead 200m but outpaced in run.
Fast start to sit rail fore of midfield, held in pocket until shifted out & driven 250m, ran on without threatening.
Broke well, rolled to sit 2nd 1 off no cover 950m & overraced, pressed leader 400m & driven, edged lead 230m, soon headed & tapered.
Fast start & driven to rail 1140m, settled 1 back on fence, 3rd turning in but hemmed on inner, driven 250m, kept on evenly.
Missed break, rousted early, raced 1 off near tail, last pair & shifted out turning in, switched out for clear run 200m, ran on for minor headway.
Broke well, snagged to rail at tail on outer, widest & 6L back last into stretch, driven 420m, ran on centre track for minor gains.
Broke OK but trapped 4 wide no cover, checked 850m & niggled, under pump 660m, very wide into stretch, plugged on moderately.
Flew start & driven wide to lead, to rail 1000m, eager in front, shaken up 400m, all out & headed 230m, faded thereafter.
Taken behind from wide gate, settled rail behind midfield, dropped to rear rank home turn & driven, plugged on same speed.
Slow start, sat 1 off behind midfield, driven 460m & shifted out, plugging on evenly when hampered & lost ground 200m, stayed on again late.
Tardy break, caught 3 wide no cover midfield, wide progress on turn, hard-ridden 430m, found little in tepid run home.
Awkward start, 1 off behind midfield & overraced 1180m, checked off heels 850m, shifted out on turn, struggled in run home.
Tardy start, caught wide near rear, soon rolled 3 deep with cover to sit handy 4 wide no cover at 900m, joined lead 500m & driven, to lead 250m, drew clear.
Fastest to break, soon settled fore of midfield on rail, driven 350m,closing run to 2nd 50m but never troubled winner.
Broke well, very wide 1st turn & rolled to lead 1 off 1340m, headed 1050m, every chance & driven 350m, boxed on without threatening first two.
Broke OK, rolled on outer to sit handy 3 wide no cover, gained cover 850m, driven 400m, lacked toe, stayed on one pace to wire.
Speed to lead on rail, headed 1340m, led 1050m, pressed & driven 350m, all out & headed 250m, faded in run.
Broke well to sit handy 1 off 1 back, driven 400m but outpaced, stayed on evenly.
Rousted start, driven along near rear 1 off, wide progress to midfield backstretch, hard ridden 4 deep 600m, plodded on evenly in stretch.
Sluggish start, sat 1 off behind midfield, squeezed out 1200m, lost ground & shifted 3 deep, ridden 600m, stayed on for minor headway in stretch.
Moderate start, bustled early, sat 1 off with cover midfield, shuffled back & 3 wide 1000m, driven 500m, struggled in stretch.
Missed break, raced 1 off near tail, taken to rail 950m, niggled 640m, driven 480m, plodded on one pace past fading rivals.
Broke well, taken back to sit 1 off with cover midfield, driven 400m, plodded on same speed.
Tardy start & rousted early to race 3 wide midfield, rolled to join front rank 3 deep 850m, under pressure & ridden into stretch, found nil & faded.
Missed break, raced rail behind midfield, overraced 1100m, ridden 500m, weakened in run.
Missed break, raced at tail, under pump 600m, found nothing, never a factor.
Hard ridden to stay in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leaders on the fence, not suited by the track that strongly favouring front runners, dashed strongly to score.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the track that strongly favouring front runners, dashed strongly 300M for 2nd.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead, benefited by the track that strongly favouring front runners, just got beaten 50M, ran on for 3rd.
Pushed to share the lead 2 wide, suited by the track that strongly favouring front runners, ran on until 100M flattened.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, benefited by the track that strongly favouring front runners, just held ground in straight.
Very slow away, hard ridden to keep up at rear, 9Ls off the leaders on the rails, little dash 200M despite not suited by the track that strongly favouring front runners.
Hard ridden to keep up with the field, 7Ls off the leaders on the fence, not suited by the track that strongly favouring front runners, just held ground.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, out of fuel 250M.
Hard ridden to keep up at rear, 9Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the track that strongly favouring front runners, no progress.
Pressed forward, 2Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, weakened quickly 500M.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the track that strongly favouring front runners, faded 400M.
Pressed forward, 2.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, dropped off rapidly 400M.
Bumped at start, pressed forward to lead narrowly before crossing to fence 600m. Kicked clear 350m and kept finding to the line.
Began well, ridden along from wide draw to sit outside leader to straight. Shaken up 350m, battled but unable to close gap.
Bumped, unbalanced start, ridden forward 4-wide from outside draw before easing into one-back, one-off position around turn. Kept on steadily in straight but unable narrow gap.
Began well, kicked up along rail to keep leader one-wide until turn. In box seat to straight, one-paced. (Lame right hind).
Jumped with field, ridden to maintain forward position but 3-wide into turn. Kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Began fairly, ridden but failed to muster, dropping to last. Moved up turn, very wide into straight, finished off nicely near outer fence.
Ridden along early to go forward, steadied 900m to get cover, settling three-back from leader. One-paced in straight.
Began fairly, no early pace, dropping toward rear close to fence. Stayed on rail turning for home, one-paced in straight.
Ridden along early to go forward but badly crowded 750m and dropped back sharply. Hung in up straight and never a threat.
Bumped and unbalanced start, steadied, and settled behind midfield. Lay out 700m, wide into straight, boxed on one-paced.
Bumped start, shifted out and bumped another, settling near last but wide. Clear last into turn, one-paced in straight.
Began well, ridden along in midfield, took closer order turn before becoming distressed and eased 200m. Collapsed.
Soon led and dictated the pace, enjoyed an uncontested lead, had 2Ls in hand and plenty in reserves going into 200M, won comfortably.
Tracked leader along the inside, had 2Ls to make up on eventual winner at 200M, couldn't get closer but kept on well enough for 2nd, clear from rest.
Always prominent just off the pace, driven out near 400M, unable to make headway on the first two, faded late stages, held on for non-threatening 3rd.
Restrained after the start, settled behind midfield 4-5Ls off the pace, kept on evenly along the inside over final 350M.
Never far off from leader, ran on at same speed final 350M, never a danger to first two.
Forwardly placed, unable to slot in and raced 3-wide without cover for much of the way, battled on in straight without looking a threat to winner, faded final 100M.
Held up near the rear, shaken up 400M, switched out 250M, closed off well over this shorter trip.
Unable to go with the early pace, settled near the rear 6-7Ls behind leader, had plenty to do 400M, made limited progress in straight.
Settled midfield, gave little response to vigorous riding turning home, faded 150M out.
Shifted across behind runners in early stages, travelled 3-wide near the rear, not quickened when asked, never involved.
Fractious in stalls and blundered on jumping, caught wide without cover in midfield, emptied quickly from 400M, soon beaten.
Stood flat-footed at the start and lost considerable amount of ground, at rear 8Ls off the pace, came up empty 400M, tailed off.
