Jumped well from the one draw, gradually settled just off the pace on rails, shifted out for a run entering straight hitting the front 300 metres out, hung on under pressure.
Detached from the main body of the field early, gradually picked up to join the tail-end halfway out, switched very wide into home straight, made significant progress to be nearest at finish.
Jumped well from a poor gate, niggled along out wide in first few far side, remained same around home bend and into straight, unable to quicken under pressure.
Settled towards the rear on rails, slightly closer up rounding home bend, kept on steadily without threatening.
Broke well looking for cover, settled outside leader, hit the front briefly on straightening before headed inside 300 metres, no extra.
Began moderately, raced wide towards the rear, made headway around home bend to be 4-wide into straight, soon faded. (Questioned for disappointing performance) (Lame next day)
Jumped well looking for cover, gradually settled at the rear, shifted out for a run entering straight, found nothing. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Ridden for a prominent position early, dropped slightly backward to 3L 5th approaching home bend, faded under pressure in straight.
Niggled along to gain lead from a poor gate gradually crossing for the rails, led until headed 600 metres out, folded up quickly from approaching home straight.
Found the lead easily and enjoyed a nice run in transit. Kept finding all the up the running.
Slowly away travelling midfield, 1 off with cover. Finished off gamely.
Not the best away racing 3rd from the rear, 1 off with cover. Finished off soundly.
Made its run from back in the field, settling 3 deep with cover. Kept grinding to the line.
Missed the kick, travelling 2nd from the rear, on the paint with cover. Made steady ground in the straight.
Camped midfield the fence, had cover. Stayed on at the same speed down the running.
Crowded at the start settling 4th last, 3 deep with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race, settling 4th, and 3 wide with cover. Was a beaten horse at the furlong.
Posted 3 deep on the speed no cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Ridden along early, settling 3 wide with cover, midfield. Failed to run on.
Did plenty of work to maintain its position outside the leader. Punctured in the home stretch. (see incident report)
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader with cover, dashed strongly when clear 300M and scored comfortably.
Jumped fairly, then settled 3Ls off the leader with cover, ran on steadily however without any threats to the winner.
Rolled forward to take the lead along the outer fence, hung on until final 100M for 3rd.
Ridden forward to settle 1L behind the leader without cover, kept on steadily.
Taken back to midfield, 3Ls behind the leader along the outer fence, ran on ok.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader with cover, kept on one pace to the line.
Settled worse than midfield about 5Ls behind the leader along the outer fence, finished off ok despite could not find a clear run over the final stages.
Camped handy, settled 2.5Ls behind the leader without cover, kept on until 200M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader with cover, never ran on.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader without cover, kept on until 250M flattened badly.
At rear throughout, never looked competitive.
Niggled along throughout, never ran on.
Always at rear, never looked likely.
Never a factor.
Tardy start, advanced 1 off to midfield, to rail 700m & progress, bumped in pocket 400m, daylight & ridden 310m, quickened to lead 220m, held on.
Broke well, sat 1 off fore of midfield, crowded into stretch, shifted inside & driven 320m, switched out for run & closed to wire.
Missed break, raced 1 off behind midfield, progress & shifted out 600m, driven 430m, ran on well centre track to make frame.
Slow start widest, niggled along wide with cover 2nd last, 6L back & driven turning in, responded with closing run to just miss frame.
Quick break, lacked toe & slid to 3 wide behind midfield, driven 500m, outpaced into stretch, stayed on centre track for good headway.
Impeded start, ridden to settle 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, ridden turning in, stayed on evenly.
Good break, taken back to race 1 off with cover near rear, driven 430m, off heels 350m & shifted out, kept on one pace.
Fast start, raced 1 back on rail, driven & shifted out 430m, outpaced & plugged on tepidly.
Broke well, rolled wide to slot outside leader 850m, driven to lead 360m, all out & headed 220m, fading when rolled to rail & hampered rival 170m.
Squeezed out at start, lost ground & ridden at tail, plugged on past beaten rivals.
Fast break, soon led & to rail 1000m, pressed 400m & driven, headed 360m, weakening when off heels & bumped rail 170m.
Smart break, sat 1 back 1 off, ridden 530m, labored into stretch, weakened tamely.
Broke OK, rousted & outpaced to race rail midfield, off heels 740m & lost place, under pump 400m, struggled in run home.
Awkward break, rolled to sit 4 wide no cover fore of midfield, very wide into stretch & driven, soon emptied & tailed off.
Missed break, rolled to sit 1 off with cover fore of midfield, smooth progress to challenge turning in, shaken up 300m, quickened to lead 200m, drew clear.
Speed to lead, soon to rail, narrowly headed 1250m, led again turning in & driven, all out & headed 200m, boxed on.
Rousted start, caught wide & taken back to slot 1 off behind midfield, driven turning in & shifted out, sound headway to 3rd 120m.
Broke OK, raced rail midfield, switched out & driven into stretch, stayed on for minor late gains.
Decent break to race 1 back 1 off, switched 3 wide 550m & vied for lead turning in, all out 300m & faded thereafter.
Slow break, raced last pair 1 off, shifted 3 wide home turn, driven 420m, stayed on centre track for minor inroads.
Taken back to race 1 off with cover near rear, progress 3 wide on turn, hard-ridden 430m, kept on one pace.
Rousted start, raced rail near rear, driven 400m & switched centre track, plugged on same speed.
Rousted early to race 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, niggled 900m, driven 750m, faltering when bumped rival 320m, struggled in run.
Broke OK, rolled wide to lead 1250m, overraced a touch, settled 1 off for thin lead, awkward on turn, headed into stretch & weakened tamely.
Moderate start, niggled early to sit 3 wide with cover midfield, driven very wide home turn, bumped 320m, no extra.
Fair break, bustled to race rail behind midfield, driven into stretch, soon weakened out.
Squeezed out at start, lost ground, raced rail at tail, driven 400m, found little & eased when beaten.
Broke well, settled 1 back on rail, driven into home stretch, found nothing & soon tailed off.
Eased to sit in midfield, 6Ls off the leader 3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to win.
Took rail easily and led by 1.5Ls, clocked fast sectionals, hung on strongly until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Behind midfield, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Pressed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the fast pace, ran on well to the line.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly when clear.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, just held ground in final stages.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 200M.
Pressed forward, 3.5Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, no turn of foot in straight.
Eased back, 9Ls off the leader 2 wide, suited by the fast pace, blocked 4-2 and checked, made some ground when clear.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 6Ls off the leader, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress.
Failed to muster, trapped very wide, eased back to sit 3 wide 7.5Ls off the leader, suited by the fast pace, ran on ok.
Eased at start, 10Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast tempo but no progress.
Slow away, pushed forward, 3.5Ls off the fast pace on the fence, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden forward, 4Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, raced ungenerously, checked 1000M, emptied 400M.
Began well, crossed quickly to outside fence, clear leader from 800m. Shaken up passing 300m, kept finding under pressure to hold off challenger.
Jumped with field, quickly fell in behind leader along outer fence, shuffled back to 6th passing 800m, switched in 500m, got split 250m, finished strongly.
Began well but not pushed, switching out to find cover behind midfield. Got clear run from 500m and kept on well to be closest at finish.
Outpaced, settling behind midfield close to outer fence. Picked up momentum 500m, switched in 300m, ran on strongly to just miss a place.
First out, headed 800m but held outer rail behind leader till 300m when had to switch in for clear running. Boxed on gamely.
Began OK, outpaced, dropping to near rear one-away from outer fence. Last at 400m, given few reminders 300m, finished off well.
Ridden along between horses early to sit behind leading pack at the 800m. Shaken up entering course proper but only one paced.
Began fairly, outpaced, dropping to near last on settling. Switched in to centre track passing 500m but one paced when put under pressure.
Jumped with field, not pressured, dropping to behind midfield. Got close to heels 500m, revved up 400m, one-paced.
Slow into stride, last on settling, switched in passing 500m, kept on steadily down centre track.
Pressed forward from inside draw racing down centre-field behind leaders to 400m. One-paced when put under pressure.
Hard ridden to sit a length behind the two leaders to 400m when failed to respond to hard riding, slipping back gradually. Rider reported did not stretch out at any stage. (Unacceptable performance.)
Ridden early down centre track to maintain forward position until 400m when gave ground quickly.

Dropped back to near the rear but always within 4Ls of the pace, no closer than 3-wide over the bend, shifted in under pressure early straight and proved difficult to ride, responded well when driven 200M, kicked clear.
Settled in midfield along the inside, no clear run early straight, severely hampered 350M, ran on soundly when a gap opened up 250M, got up for 2nd near line.

Slow to muster speed despite ridden along early stages, raced in mid-pack and caught 4-wide making the turn, moved into contention 500M, ran on well to lead briefly 250M, soon caught by winner, weakened and lost 2nd late.
Reserved near the rear, 4Ls off leader going into 400M, switched wide and closed off the race steadily without getting to the winner.
Settled 3-wide about 2-3Ls behind leader, hampered 400M when brushed by winner, soon regained momentum to chase leaders, run ended 200M and flattened out in the final stages.
Began only fairly, strode forward and had to make some use to clear runners on the inside, led them at good pace to straight, unable to hold off rivals passing 250M, faded to 6th.
In touch just behind leaders, lost all chance when badly held up turning home, stayed on when clear 200M.
Held up in mid-division but never far off from leaders, checked 400M, ran on only mildly when regained balance, never reached leaders.
Towards the rear and under pressure to hold his position early stages, trapped on the inside and had a big task turning in, responded only fairly, never involved.
Taken back to last from 14, 6Ls behind leaders in a strongly run race, gave limited response when switched out to challenge 350M, never a threat to leaders.
Chased leading pair in a 3-wide position without cover, failed to muster a closing response passing 400M, ran on empty final 150M.
Began awkwardly, moved up to a handy position just off the pace, soon outpaced by rivals turning home, weakened away.
Attended the pace along the 2-path, had nothing left turning in, weakened rapidly from 300M.
Caught very wide throughout in mid-division, dropped out from 500M, tailed off. (Unacceptable Performance.)
Shifted in behind runners, dropping to rear in one-off position. Began forward move 700m, very wide into straight, hit front 100m, held off late challenge.
Shifted in behind runners, dropping to clear last before turn. Swung widest into straight, finished strongly to just miss.
Outpaced, settling behind midfield but away from fence. Improved around turn, looked chance passing 250m, swamped final stages.
Began fairly, pressed forward to grab box seat at turn, popped off fence 400m, hit front 300m, kept on till swamped final stages.
Pressed forward to lead on settling. Set good sections, first into straight, joined 300m, kept on till flattened 50m.
Began OK, ridden along inside leader settling in one-off position. Awkward inside heels 1000m losing position, rolled forward 600m, turned 4-wide, kept on steadily.
Ridden along early holding fence 3-back from leader. Took closer order around turn, found run between horses, kept on steadily.
Slow into stride, settling at rear in a 3-wide position. Taken out entering straight and ran on steadily while switching out for clear runs.
Ridden along in midfield 3-wide down backstretch and around turn. Shaken up 300m, awkwardly placed 200m, blocked for run final stages and not fully tested.
Taken in behind runners from wide draw, settling last initially before improving position before turn. Stayed on rail entering straight and kept on fairly to line.
Leaning on stall when gates opened and began awkwardly, racing mostly at rear. Took closer order around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw to settle outside leader before the turn. Spent force soon after straightening for home, dropping back gradually.
Pressed forward from wide draw and trapped 3-wide behind leading pack without cover. Rolled forward 700m but taken to outside fence by inside runner, losing significant ground.

Placing: PU
Comment: Began well, pushed forward in one-off position behind leader. Commenced to hang out from 700m, moving to outside fence and pulled up.
Began well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, angled out turning in, took the lead easily near 150M, won unextended.
Jumped well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed near 150M, kept on well for 2nd.
Slightly slowly away, positioned 2 wide with cover in 6th, 2-3 lengths back, similar position turning, closed off well to get 3rd.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 6 lengths back, hampered near 950M, same position turning, taken wide entering straight and finished off well to make frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths or so back at rear, 3 wide with cover turning, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Slightly slowly away, hampered near 1100M, positioned 4 lengths back in midfield, similar position to turn, made minor headway in straight.
Began well, difficult to settle in the early stages, raced 3 wide without cover in 5th, still no cover turning, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 9 lengths back at tail, still well back turning, made minor progress in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 4 lengths back, similar position turning, finished off one-paced in straight.
Moderately away, sent forward to race a length behind the leader, raced outside the leader on turn, showed no turn of foot entering straight, dropped off gradually.
Taken back from gate 11, raced 7 lengths back at rear, similar position turning, found no daylight early in straight, finished off one-paced thereafter.
Fairly away from a tricky gate, hampered near 1100M, position 2 wide with cover behind midfield, 6 lengths back, same margin turning, made no progress in straight.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently in 3rd, 3 wide without cover turning, emptied early in straight, never competitive.
Moderately away, raced 6 lengths back on rail at rear, lost ground near 600M, failed to close off in straight, finished tailed out.

Jumped fairly from the one draw, settled in midfield on rails, switched out for a run approaching home turn, ran on steadily alongside runner-up to just prevail.
Slow out, driven to steadily pick up third spot one off the rails, ran on steadily alongside winner in straight to just fail to get up on line.
Jumped fairly, pressed on to soon take up running attempting to make all, only to be swamped near finish.
Driven early, settled one back on rails, kept on without quickening in straight.
Soon dropped to last few, saved ground on rails turning in, kept on same pace without quickening.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, last into straight, ran past well-beaten horses.
Settled in midfield, faded into straight.
Jumped fairly from a poor gate, settled towards the rear, ran home one-paced.
Ridden along from a poor gate, travelled wide behind midfield far side and around the bend, never seen with a chance.
Camped handy, in 5th position on the paint, had cover. Peeled out prior to the home turn and ranged up to have the race in its keeping after the 200m.
Missed the start, settling worse than midfield. Improved to midfield approaching the home turn and chased gamely down the running.
Travelled just in advance of midfield, 1 off with cover. Was right in the mix at the furlong but peaked on its effort after the 150m.
Rolled forward to eventually settle 1 off in the lead. Grudgingly gave way over the final 150m.
Parked 2nd last, 3 deep with cover. Made some late headway in the home straight.
Raced 3rd from the rear, 1 off with cover. Failed to really quicken in the home straight.
Eventually settled 1 out 1 back after the 900m. Only plodded to the line.
Travelled midfield, but was left racing 3 wide without cover near the 900m. Struggled in the home stretch.
Not the best away settling last, 3 deep with cover. Failed to close off.
Went forward and settled 2nd on the fence, no cover. Was a spent force before the furlong.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, suited by the track that favoring front runners, dashed strongly to score by a neck.
Settled in front of midfield about 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the track that favoring front runners, dashed well for 2nd, just beaten over the last few strides.
At rear early, 6Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, made an early moved 900M, suited by the track that favoring runners, kept on nicely until 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the track that favoring front runners, ran on for 4th without any threats to placegetters.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls off the leader 3 wide without cover, gradually moved forward 500M, despite suited by the track that favoring front runners, emptied 150M.
Slow to begin, then settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the track that favoring front runners, one paced home.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the track that favoring front runners, no progress.
Rolled forward to settle 3/4L outside the leader, despite suited by the track that favoring front runners, soon weakened after straightening.
Taken back from the widest draw, settled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the track that favoring front runners, made minor ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by the track that favoring front runners, made minor ground in straight.
Pushed forward to take the fence and led by 3/4L, despite benefited by the track that favoring front runners, weakened 300M.
Taken back, travelled 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the track that favoring front runners, never ran on.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 5Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the track that favoring front runners, flattened badly in straight.
Fast start, raced handy 3 wide no cover, rolled to press lead 570m, led 450m & kicked clear into stretch, held on gamely.
Fair break, raced wide with cover midfield, advanced on turn, 2L back & driven into stretch, closed to 2nd 250m, held at line.
Smart start, bustled to track lead 1 off with cover, lacked toe & hard-ridden into stretch, rallied in stretch to gradually close, held at wire.
Sharp break, bustled to lead 1050m & soon to rail, headed 450m, plugged on in tapering stretch run.
Broke well, raced 3 wide with cover midfield, hung in & impeded rivals 800m, driven on turn, plugged on evenly.
Rousted break, outpaced & niggled to 3 wide with cover midfield, progress on turn, grinding stretch run for minor gains.
Slow break, raced near tail, ridden 700m & moderate progress wide, stayed on grittily for minor inroads.
Fast break, slipstreamed lead 2L back on rail, driven turning in, found nothing in weak run home.
Tardy start, niggled 1 off with cover behind midfield, driven 450m, plodded home tamely.
Broke OK, ridden to sit midfield 1 off with cover, hampered 800m & lost significant ground, struggled in run home.
Good break, soon outpaced & bustled, settled midfield on rail, badly impeded 800m, soon at tail & niggled, never a factor thereafter.
Missed break, raced at tail, driven last pair 650m, very wide final turn, found nothing.
Fast start, bustled to sit handy 1 off with cover, hampered & in turn edged into rival 700m, to 2nd 490m, grinding run to lead 100m, held on under pressure.
Broke well & bustled along 3 wide with cover midfield, driven 490m & shifted to rail, switched out 300m, closed to press lead at wire.
Speed to lead, soon to rail, extended 2L clear 600m, driven on 400m, all out & tapering when headed 100m, no extra.
Moderate start & scrubbed along behind midfield 3 wide with cover, driven 400m, stayed on centre track for sound inroads.
Taken back from wide gate, soon driven in rear on rail, shifted 1 off for progress 500m, driven into stretch, closed off well down inside rail.
Outpaced at break & driven, raced 1 off in rear, 3wide on turn, hard-ridden 400m, kept on evenly centre track.
Smart start, raced handy 3 wide no cover, hard-ridden turning in, plodded on one pace.
Tardy start, raced 1 off near rear, driven 500m, plodded on tepidly.
Broke well on outer, rousted to sit handy but caught four wide, ridden into stretch, ran home tamely.
Fast break & bustled to race 2nd 1 off, hung in 700m, weakening 3rd & niggled into stretch, struggling when shifted in 200m, eased thereafter.
Taken back from widest gate, settled wide in rear, forced 4 deep on turn, last & driven 400m, found little.
Broke OK, mustered on rail to sit handy 1 back, badly impeded 700m & lost many lengths, ridden in rear turning in, no extra in stretch.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead, benefited by the track that favouring front runners, made all.
Hard ridden forward, just off the leaders 3 wide, benefited by the track that favouring front runners, ran on well for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward, 1.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, suited by the track that favouring front runners, just held ground.
Very slow away, 5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, not suited by the track that favouring front runners, made early move 600M, little dash 300M.
Very slow away, 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the track that favouring front runners, just held ground.
Pushed early but not muster, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the track that favouring front runners, little dash 200M.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, checked 800M, not suited by the track that favouring front runners, little dash in straight.
Eased at start, 6Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, harmed by the track that favouring front runners, dashed well 100M.
Pressed forward, box seat, suited by the track that favouring front runners, soon reduced 300M.
Eased back, harmed by the track that favouring front runners, never a factor.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 4 wide first corner, 1000M shared lead 2 wide, suited by the track that favouring front runners, but soon faded 400M.
First out, ridden along in one-off position before crossing to rail 800m. Joined up front entering straight but kicked back final stages to win drawing clear.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit on hind-quarters of leader passing 800m. Rolled forward turn, joint leader 300m, battled but unable match winner final 100m.
Ridden along from wide draw, racing 3-wide back stretch and turn. Rolled forward entering straight to look chance but unable match first two.
Began awkwardly, ridden to make ground settling in box seat behind leader at turn. Raced keenly turn, stayed on rail entering straight and boxed on gamely.
Slow, pushed through along fence to get box seat by turn. Checked, lost ground 700m, rolled forward 300m to look chance, one-paced.
Outpaced, settling at rear in one-off position. Got close to heels around turn, kept on fairly in straight.
Difficult to load but began OK. No speed, dropping to behind midfield in one-off position. Shaken up entering straight but no extra.
Driven forward between horses to sit 1.5L behind leading trio. Turned a little wide but under pressure from 200m, dropping back.
Began OK, ridden along early but unable keep up, slipping back to near rear in one-off position. Under pressure from turn, one-paced.
Crowded out start dropping to clear last. Tagged on to field 900m, but never looked competitive.
Ridden to maintain forward position and held 3-wide back stretch and turn. Spent force entering straight and faded.
Knuckled over start, ridden along early but unable keep up, dropping to last from 800m. Never likely after that.
Dropped back to a rearward position 6Ls off the pace, patiently ridden, had plenty to make up passing 250M but quickened impressively, swept to the lead near line and won going away.

Began well from draw 1 to race handily, travelled smoothly behind leaders turning home, quickened well when guided to clear 250M, led 150M and look set to score only to be caught by fast finishing winner late.
Settled 2Ls behind leader in a compact field and well covered throughout, ideally placed to strike 400M, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Held up behind midfield but never far off, saved ground on the inside, made stealthy progress and just missed out on 3rd.
Settled 2-wide in mid-division, not helped by the slow pace middle stages, stayed on moderately when switched out 250M.
Restrained after the start, not helped by the slow pace and moved out to a 4-wide position entering back straight, stayed on well and made steady progress.
Made some early use to cross to the lead, pressed by rival 500M, led to near 200M, one pace final stages.
Dropped back to the rear 7Ls off the pace, patiently ridden, brought wide 450M, closed off well down the outside.
Sent forward to track the pace, drew alongside leader 500M, dueled to 200M, weakened.
Unable to slot in, settled 4-wide in midfield with cover, 3-4Ls off the pace at 400M, ran on one pace and lost touch with leaders 200M out.
Held up 3-wide behind mid-division, 4-5Ls to make up on leaders at 400M, no clear run turning in, checked 200M and lost all chances.
Gradually moved forward on jumping from a wide draw, caught wide no cover 2Ls off the pace, one paced entering straight, no extra 200M out.
Unable to cross from wide barrier, caught wide no cover throughout, outpaced by leaders early straight, weakened rapidly passing 200M.
Settled in midfield, came under pressure 500M, soon weakened turning home, eased.

Broke well from the one draw, settled two back on rails, commenced move rounding home bend, switching off heels of leader to challenge entering straight and soon took charge, won well.
Jumped well from a poor draw, took the lead briefly passing winning post the first time before settling on heels of pacesetter, hit the front on straightening but collared 100 metres out.
Jumped fairly then tightened shortly afterwards, settled in midfield on rails, shifted out for a run turning in, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Began from a poor draw, travelled at the tail-end of the field, snuck up on rails turning in, sustained steady progress down inside of straight under pressure.
Soon taken back towards the rear of field on rails, saved ground on inside turning for home, kept on at the one pace in the run to the line.
Broke well, settled in midfield, similar turning in, one-paced in straight.
Jumped fairly, settled in 3rd and then 4th mainly 2-wide without cover, found nothing under pressure in the run home.
Jumped moderately but ridden to take up running coming onto stables bend, led the field until finding no extra on straightening.
Jumped fairly, settled at rear of field, ran past well-beaten horses in straight.
Jumped fairly, soon taken back to travel towards the rear, made no impression in straight.
Began from the widest draw, raced wide without cover towards the rear, went wider entering straight, never a factor.
Began well, soon taken back to 3-wide without cover in midfield, dropped out from the 600 metres. (Bled)
Enjoyed a nice run in the race, 4th on the fence with cover. Peeled out after the 500m and let down nicely to hit the lead at the furlong, finishing off well.
Parked midfield, on the fence with cover. Chased gamely down the running.
Settled just off midfield, 2 wide with cover. Finished off soundly.
Settled back in the field, on the paint with cover. Worked to the line nicely.
Slow to begin then raced at the tail of the field, 2 deep with cover. Took inside runs turning for home, continually shifted out for clear running in the straight, worked home nicely.
Began awkwardly then recovered to share the lead until the 600m. Box seated thereafter but ran into traffic until the 100m.
Did enough work in the early & middle to eventually lead on the rails after the 600m. Was gassed by the furlong.
Settled 5th 1 off with cover. Was carried wider rounding the home turn and was a beaten horse soon after. (Blood in the trachea).
Camped behind midfield, 3 deep with cover. Just whacked away in the final straight.
Was in the middle of the leading trio early before settling 1 off, no cover, travelling 2nd. Gave in easily after the 150m.
Settled worse than midfield, 3 wide with cover. Failed to close off.
Posted 3 deep without cover for the major part of the race, midfield. Struggled in the home stretch.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, dashed away 250M and scored comfortably by 2.5Ls.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, ran on well for 2nd.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow pace, kept on well to get 3rd.
Eased back, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow sectionals, ran on strongly for 4th.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, progressed steadily.
Rolled forward to take the fence and led by 3/4L at slow sectionals, headed 300M, only one paced until final stages weakened.
Settled worse than midfield about 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slow pace, one paced home.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow sectionals, never ran on.
Taken back from the wide gate, settled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slow pace, made minor ground.
Eased start, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, made no impression in straight. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
At rear throughout, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, never a factor.
Eased to settle midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, not suited by the slow pace, weakened soon after straightening.
Fast start, camped 1 back on rail, shifted out on turn & shaken up 300m, quickened to lead 150m, drew clear under hands & heels.
Sharp start, disputed lead & to rail 1000m, led outright 950m, driven turning in, under pressure 300m, headed 150m, boxed on.
Fast break to dispute lead, soon settled 2nd 1 off no cover, ridden 450m to challenge, vied for lead until emptied 200m & tapered.
Slow start mustered to rail behind midfield, shifted out & ridden 300m, closed off for solid gains.
Smart start, raced 1 off with cover midfield, niggled 550m & soon ridden, shifted out on turn, stayed on one pace.
Broke OK, snagged to race 3 wide with cover near rear, niggled 450m, driven widest into stretch, closed centre track for sound inroads.
Tardy break, sat last pair 1 off, driven 300m, ran on for minor headway.
Broke well, lacked early pace & bustled to sit rail midfield, niggled 500m, hard-ridden 320m & plugged on one pace.
Speed to lead, headed 1st turn, caught wide & snagged to sit handy 3 wide no cover, driven 400m, no extra & weakened out from 200m.
Broke well, sat 3 wide with cover midfield, under pump 400m, very wide into stretch, found little in tepid run home.
Broke well, checked 1160m, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, switched out final turn, driven 300m, never a factor.
Taken back at start to race rail last pair, niggled 500m, driven 300m, found nil, struggled in run.
Moderate start, raced 1 off behind midfield, impeded & off heels 730m, ridden 400m, switched out in stretch & driven home to lead last stride.
Sharp start stalked 1 back 1 off, shifted out & driven into stretch, quickened to lead 100m, all out when mugged last stride.
Broke well, camped rail midfield, shuffled back home turn & switched out, driven 250m, rattled home, just failed.
Driven at break to lead 1350m, to rail 800m, driven under pressure 400m, extended clear 300m, all out & headed 100m, no extra.
Tardy start, raced awkwardly 1 off with cover midfield, off heels 730m & 660m, shifted out & driven into stretch, unbalanced 250m, kept on without threatening.
Slow break, sat rail behind midfield, impeded 730m & shuffled to 2nd last, under pump 400m, stayed on for sound inroads.
Taken back from wide gate to tail, 3 wide progress backstretch, ridden 480m, closed off centre track for solid headway.
Broke moderately, rousted wide no cover to settle handy, posted close 2nd 1 off 800m, driven to press lead 400m, soon outpaced & plugged on.
Bumped start, raced 1 off near rear until rolled 3 wide to sit midfield 660m, ridden 500m & wide home turn, found nothing.
Broke well & bustled to lead on rail, headed 1350m & settled 1 back on fence 800m, driven 450m but outpaced, plugged on.
Broke OK, taken back to rail near tail, off heels 730m & shuffled to tail, driven 400m, plodded on tepidly centre track.
Broke OK, raced midfield 3 wide, lost cover 800m & rolled to sit 3rd 500m, driven turning in, emptied 300m & faded.
Settled in front, 1.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Hard ridden to take rail, shared the lead at good pace, hung on strongly until 50M, just missed by a neck.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 200M for 3rd.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 3.5Ls off the good pace, lack room 4-2, progressed steadily when clear.
Pushed forward, shared the lead 2 wide at good pace, ran on until 100M flattened.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, ran on ok in straight.
Eased at start, 7Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Eased back, 5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, on heels 600M, just held ground in straight.
Slow away, pushed forward, box seat, pace good, soon emptied 300M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide throughout, no turn of foot.
Slow away, hard ridden to keep up with the field, 6Ls off the good pace along the fence, on heels 600M, no progress.
Eased at start and took rail, 7Ls off the good pace, no progress.
Began well, quickly in front and steadied pace. Lengthened stride passing 450m, pulled clear in straight for easy win.
Away only fairly but picked up quickly between horses to settle one-back, one-off by 950m. Three-wide into straight and kept on steadily to snatch second on line.
Began well, ridden to maintain forward position but shuffled two back from leader passing 1000m. Shifted in from heels passing 350m, got rails run 280m, kept on well to line.
Jumped with field but not pushed, cutting in three-back, one-off passing 1000m. Switched out passing 350m to get run and kept on fairly to line.
Began OK, restrained and shifted in behind runners but held 3-wide. Difficult to settle back stretch, found run between horses 300m and finished off fairly.
Began fairly, shifted across behind runners, settling last along rail at back stretch. Still well back entering straight but finished off nicely.
No early speed, settling four-back along rail. Eased out 350m for run, shifted in 200m to improve but tightened shortly after. One-paced.
Hard ridden to go forward from wide draw, settling outside leader passing 950m. Under pressure from 400m, giving ground gradually in straight despite hard riding.
Began well, held, shifted across behind runners, settling at rear but wide. Shifted in from heels 700m, very wide into straight, made minor headway closing stages.
Bumped heavily soon after start, ridden forward but held 3-wide without cover behind pacemakers. Got close to heels 400m, one-paced in straight. (Rider reported not comfortable in action).
Began well, ridden forward to hold box seat behind leader. Looked chance entering straight before giving ground from 250m. (Irregular heart rhythm, substantial blood in trachea).
Made heavy contact soon after start then refused to settle while racing at rear. Never competitive.
Caught wide early stages from 11, advanced to 2nd place 1200M, alongside leader 700M, strode 2Ls clear passing 300M, kept on well and maintained that margin to the finish.
Held up towards the rear 5-6Ls behind leader, 3-wide bid home turn, ran on steadily to go 2nd near line, not reached winner.
Jumped well from inside barrier, stayed within striking distance along the fence, driven 400M but not pace to challenge winner, held 2nd from 200M until near the finish.
Reserved in mid-division along the inside, shaken up 500M, checked 250M then held up until 150M, stayed on to take 4th, could have been closer.
Dropped back and guided to the fence, 7Ls off the pace in early and middle stages, moved closer home turn, quickened well in straight but no clear run over final 200M, not properly tested.
Held up 2-wide in mid-pack, 4-5Ls behind leader at 400M, stayed on moderately but never a serious threat.
Dropped back after the start, waited with in a rearward position 6Ls off the pace, brought wide to challenge 450M, stayed on only fairly, not reached contention.
Sent forward, led uncontested to 600M at steady tempo, unable to hold off eventual winner 300M, faded towards the line.
Switched off to the rear, 6Ls to make up 400M, never saw daylight in straight, blocked for a run final 100M.
Caught 3-wide no cover in midfield, strode closer to pace 600M, soon came under pressure, weakened away passing 300M.
Not far off in early and middle stages but struggled to keep up making the home turn, weakened to last 250M.
Began well, ridden along 3-wide to 1400m before edging forward to sit outside leader first turn. Took over lead soon after entering straight and kept finding to hold off challengers.
Began well but not enough speed and shuffled four-back along fence going into first turn. Entered straight behind horses, switched out 280m to make run, finished off strongly.
Slow into stride, last on settling but kept away from fence. Still last entering straight, shifted very wide 350m and finished off strongly.
Jumped with field, ridden along between horses settling three-back, one-off at first turn. Peeled out passing 350m for clear run and kept on steadily to line.
Ridden along to maintain forward position, settling along fence 3-back from leader. Got clear running from 250m and ran on steadily.
Taken in behind horses soon after start to sit at rear in one-off position. Made forward move 500m, very wide into straight, finished off nicely. (Lame right front leg.)
Taken in behind horses settling long rail at rear. Not hurried, found inside run turning for him and finished off well.
Pushed forward from inside draw to lead on settling. Slowed pace back stretch. Collared soon after straightening for home but kept on to 100m when swamped.
Began OK, settling between horses behind midfield. Got shuffled back making turn, found inside run in straight, one-paced.
Jumped with field, shifted in behind runners but held 3-wide without cover from 900m. One-paced in straight.
Ridden along early travelling 3-wide into first turn before finding cover back stretch. Switched out entering straight but soon tired, dropping back gradually.
Began well, holding box seat behind leader to home stretch when gave ground quickly. (Rider reported didn't stretch out after changing lead leg at turn).
Jumped well from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, travelled well to turn, finished off well to score.
Began well, showed early speed to take the lead, easy lead throughout, headed near 150M, hung on for 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned in midfield, 4 lengths or so back, saved ground turning, closed off well to get 3rd, just missed 2nd.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position turning, made minor headway in straight to make frame.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, taken back to race 6-7 lengths back at rear, same position turning, finished off very strongly in straight, just missed frame, nice debut.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 lengths back at rear on rail, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening, closed off well to be nearest on line.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, 7-8 lengths back, still well back turning, closed off well given workload to be nearest on line.
Crowded out start, positioned 3 lengths back in 4th, saved ground to turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in 3rd, same position to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Average to begin, difficult to settle near 1100M, continued to travel keenly, positioned 2-3 wide with cover in 8th, there to turn, made no progress in straight.
Slightly slowly away, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, same position to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover, 4 lengths back in midfield, similar position turning, failed to close off in straight and eased.

Vied for lead after beginning from a poor draw, obtained rails run in front at the Rock, steadied pace about 600 metres out causing interferences, just held on under pressure. (Jockey charged for slowed the tempo 600m out.)
Began fairly from the one draw settling just worse than midfield on rails, hampered by steadied runners 500 metres out, produced good late finish in the run home.
Taken back from the widest draw gradually crossing to inside, shifted out for a run entering straight, finished off race well.
Amongst leaders on rails early, gradually shifted back for cover but hampered by steadied runner 600 metres out, fought on steadily in straight but lost 3rd late.
Raced wide without cover in midfield for the majority of the race, fought on steadily down the centre of straight but without threatening.
Failed to muster early despite ridden along and soon dropped to the rear, saved ground on inside turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.
Ridden along amongst leaders, inconvenienced when headed coming out of far side, switched out for a clear run entering straight, swamped under pressure.
Amongst leaders early, gradually shifted back to forward of midfield before home bend, kept on same pace in straight.
Settled just worse than midfield, kept on steadily under pressure.
Niggled at early settling behind midfield, ran wide turning for home, made no impression in straight.
Ridden along amongst leaders after beginning from a poor gate, hit the front briefly inside 500 metres after pace slackened, soon headed after straightening, folded up quickly.
Tracked the leader on the fence. Fought gamely all the way to the post.
Parked midfield, 2 wide with cover. Chased gamely down the running.
Sent forward to race on the fence. Kept on soundly, claimed late.
Raced back in the field, on the fence with cover. Ran on steadily in the home stretch.
Rated behind midfield, on the rails with cover. Kept on at the same pace down the running.
Had cover early 1 off at the rear of the field, before electing to race 3 deep no cover and sliding forward after the 1400m. Posted wide most of the trip, one paced in the run home.
Settled 2nd early, camped midfield 1 out 1 back midrace. Was flat over the final furlong.
Settled last from a wide gate 1 off with cover. Made some ground without threatening.
Raced with the backmakers, 2 deep with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Travelled 3rd in the run, 1 off no cover. Joined the leader midrace but the tank was empty early in the straight.
Settled back in the field, on the paint with cover. Came wide on the home turn, struggled in the home stretch.
Ridden forward to park outside the leader, kept on strongly to score by a neck.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, dashed well however could not pass the winner over the final stages, missed by a neck.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 3/4L, stayed on well until 100M weakened for 3rd.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace to the line without threatening.
Midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace to the line.
Began awkwardly, then travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, one paced home.
Jumped slowly, settled 8.5Ls off the leader on the fence, made minor ground in straight.
Lacked early pace, travelled 6Ls behind the leader along the fence, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, found nothing when asked after 600M.
Crowded start, then settled 11Ls behind the leader on the fence, never a factor.
Prominent, however trapped 3 without cover throughout, weakened soon after straightening.
Began slowly, travelled 9Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked competitive.
Buffeted start, sat behind midfield 1 off, shifted 3 wide for progress 670m, shaken up 360m, wide into stretch, swooped on outer to lead 150m, drew clear.
Tardy start & buffeted, raced rail near rear, switched 1 off 670m, shifted wide & driven 350m, closed to 2nd 50m, held in run.
Sow start & rousted to 1 off near rear, forced 3 deep 670m, snatched off heels 550m & to tail, driven 300m, stayed on to snag 3rd last stride.
Good break, driven to sit 1 back 1 off, to rail 800m & stalked lead, ridden 450m & shifted out, all out to lead 200m, soon headed & tapered.
Broke well, settled rail behind midfield, shifted out & shaken up 300m, battled on for minor gains.
Tardy break, recovered & handy 1st turn, settled rail midfield, niggled 800m, under pump 580m, hard-ridden 400m & boxed on evenly.
Driven to lead at break, to rail 1st turn, 1L clear & ridden 400m, edged to centre track turning in, emptied & headed 200m, faded out.
Awkward start & bustled rail, soon at tail, niggled backstretch, progress on turn, ridden 300m & shifted out, stayed on moderately.
Broke OK, raced 3 wide with cover near tail, forced 4 wide 670m, last & driven into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Bumped start, bustled to midfield 1 off with cover, switched off heels turning in & driven, plodded tamely in run & eased late.
Broke OK, ridden 3 wide to sit handy, slotted 1 off 1 back 680m, shifted out & driven 3 wide 520m, wilted at top of stretch.
Sharp start to race 2nd, 4 wide 1st turn, slotted 1 off 970m, niggled 500m, gave ground & unbalanced final turn, eased in run.
Smart start, settled 1 back 1 off in 4th, shaken up 320m, quickened to lead 180m, drew clear.
Led at break, snagged & headed 1050m to settle 5th 1 back on rail, shaken up turning in, driven to 2nd 130m, held in run.
Broke OK, raced midfield 1 off with cover, niggled 500m, driven turning in, battled on to claim 3rd under pressure.
Rousted at break, race rail behind midfield, niggled 500m, driven 300m, stayed on to just miss frame.
Slow start, raced 1 off near rear, shifted out & driven into stretch, checked off heels 260m, stayed on for solid late gains.
Broke OK, raced 3 wide with cover near rear, to rail 550m, driven 320m & shifted out, kept on for minor inroads.
Broke OK, caught 3 wide no cover behind midfield, ridden 400m & wide in stretch, outpaced in tepid run home.
Driven to lead 1050m, raced 1 off, driven 320m, headed 180m & emptied, faded thereafter.
Taken back from widest gate, soon detached & bustled at tail, under pump 500m, minor progress on turn, plugged on one pace.
Tardy start, mustered to dispute lead 1050m, settled close 2nd rail, under pump 350m, wilted in run home.
Broke well, unable to slot & taken back to near rear, trapped 4 wide no cover, ridden along 430m, last pair turning in, found nothing.
Broke OK, rousted wide to dispute lead 1050m, snagged to sit handy 3 wide no cover, driven under pressure 400m, weakened tamely in stretch.
Pushed to obtain box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, made early and rapid move around the field 600M to take advantages from the slow pace, ran on strongly for 2nd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed well 250M for 3rd.
Settled in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, made its move 500M, dashed only fairly in straight.
Eased at start, 8.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, blocked 4-2, dashed strongly when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader, trapped 2-3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 300M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, 7.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Pressed forward, settled 1L off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, emptied 400M.
Pushed to take rail and led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, however weakened quickly 300M.
In front of midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, dropped off 400M.
Began well, allowed to stride forward but not pushed, settling 3-back, the rails. Had to switch out gradually before getting clear run 150n and finished strongly.
Rolled forward from wide draw racing 3-wide to first turn before settling one-back, one off. Under pressure from 450, wide into straight, battled on under hard riding. (Lame left front leg).
Began well, restrained, taken in gradually behind horses to settle one-off in last pair. Made forward move 400m out, widest into straight, ran on strongly.
First out, led to turn before giving way to inside horse passing 1200m. Edged forward turning for home, took lead 150m, swamped final stages.
Began fairly, not hurried, settling four-back, one -off. Entered straight behind horses, switch in for run and kept on steadily.
Ridden along to maintain forward position, racing one-back, one-off to turn before slipping into box seat behind leader. Got inside run on straightening but only one-paced.
Bumped start, recovered, pushed through along rail to lead passing 1200m. Set steady pace to turn when came off bridle and weakened. (Rider suggested track conditions did not suit.)
Began awkwardly, bumped and unbalanced. Ridden forward between horses settling three-back, one-off. Swung wide into turn but only one-paced under hard riding.
Hampered start, taken to rail 5-back from leader, Saved ground turn but found little under hard riding in straight.
Outpaced and soon at rear along rail. Never competitive.
Quickly into stride, led steadily, kicked 1.5Ls clear 200M, continued on well to keep the closers at bay over the final stages.
Settled 6Ls off the pace early stages, shaken up 600M and moved closer, into clear 250M, ran on well to go 2nd near line.
Tracked the pace, kept on steadily to chase eventual winner from 300M, always held.
Held up in midfield along the fence but never far off, kept to inside entering straight, chased winner but effort just flattened out late.
Held up in mid-division 4-5Ls behind leaders, taken wide 300M to challenge, stayed on mildly.
Taken back to the rear of the main group. Had over 7Ls to make up 400M, took time to get going, did best work late.
Forwardly placed just behind leaders, 3-wide no cover throughout, kept on steadily turning in, unable to sustain run final 100M, faded towards the line.
Settled 2-wide in the group chasing leaders, able only to find one pace under pressure rather than quicken, never seriously threatened.
Pressed leader on the outside, didn't find much entering straight, weakened from 200M.
Dropped back to a rearward spot about 6Ls off the pace, gave limited response turning home and could never get involved.
Settled 2-wide in midfield, 4Ls behind leader passing 400M, found no extra when driven, soon out of contention.
Stood flat-footed as the gates opened, lost a significant amount of ground, over 10Ls behind leaders throughout, eased entering home straight.

Jumped awkwardly from the best 14 draw, settled just off the speed along stands rails, came to challenge inside final 200 metres hitting the front 100 metres out, won readily.
Soon took up running holding 1L advantage most of the way until collared passing the 150 metres.
Slightly slow out, settled just over 2L off the pace on stands rails, shifted in for a run coming onto course proper, ran on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly, gradually settled in midfield, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly, settled in last few on stands rails, produced good late impression inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace, came under pressure passing the 300 metres but gave ground steadily.
Chased leaders to the 250 metres, faded under pressure.

Began moderately before crowded, pressed forward to soon come within 2L of pace and without cover, unable to sustain effort and faded inside final 150 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance.)
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, soon taken across to stands rails at the rear, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield, found nothing over 200 metres out.
Badly jostled at start, tailed-off most of the way before running past also-rans inside final 200 metres.
Lost balance jumping out, settled worse than midfield, gave ground from half way out.
Jumped fairly from a poor draw, settled worse than midfield, never seen with a chance.
Began fairly from the one draw, travelled towards the rear without cover near the centre of the track, soon faded under pressure after coming onto course proper.
Enjoyed nice run in the race, box seating. Peeled out early in the straight, closed off strongly to take control of the event 100m out.
Settled on the fence with leading trio. Fought gamely in the home stretch.
Posted 3 deep without cover on the speed. Kept on well until at the 150m, faded thereafter.
Made its run third from the rear, after travelling on the rails with cover. Finished off soundly.
Camped 1 out 1 back. Maintained an even gallop down the running.
Stalked the speed runners 3 deep with cover. Weakened over the final furlong.
Travelled midfield, 1 off with cover. Stayed on fairly.
Travelled 3 deep with cover midfield. Plodded to the line.
Posted 4 wide no cover on the circle, midfield. Was a beaten runner early in the straight.
Raced 2nd last, 2 deep with cover. Never ran on.
Camped midfield, 1 off with cover. Gave ground over the final.
Travelled last close to the rail with cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Settled worse than midfield, 1 off with cover. Failed to close off.
Sent forward and vied for the lead 1 off. Was gassed early in the straight.
Rolled forward to occupy the box seat, enjoyed the fast tempo, ran on strongly to score by 1-1/4L.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 2Ls at fast sectionals, hung on well until 100M weakened for 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast pace, closed to the line well to get 3rd.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the fast pace, ran on well until final 50M weakened.
At rear, settled 6.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo, dashed on strongly.
Pushed forward to settle 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the fast pace, kept on nicely to the line.
Settled worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, ran on steadily.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast tempo, ran on steadily however could not able to find a clear run over the last furlong.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast pace, made no impression in straight.
At rear, settled 8Ls behind the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Taken back from the wide barrier, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast tempo, never ran on.
Raced midfield, settled 3.5Ls behind the leader without cover, kept on until 250M weakened.
Failed to muster despite hard ridden along, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, eased 150M.

Placing: UR
Comment: Soon after the start, rider was dislodged.
Started OK, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, switched 3 wide 1200m for progress, 4 wide turning in, shaken up 400m & soon led, quickened away.
Slow break, recovered to rail midfield, bustled 700m, driven 400m, crowded & checked briefly 350m, ran on to 2nd inside last 50m.
Broke OK, rolled to sit 1 back, trapped in pocket turning in, clear run 320m & shaken up, ran on soundly without threatening.
Tardy break, mustered to race 1 off with cover midfield, shuffled back a spot 1000m, progress on turn, ridden 550m, wide into stretch, stayed on dourly.
Missed break, raced at tail behind midfield, shifted out & driven into stretch, plugged on for minor headway.
Broke well & bustled wide to sit 2nd 1 off, driven 430m to lead, headed all out 360m, emptied & faded.
Awkward start, snagged back to last trio on rail, 1off for progress 1000m, driven into stretch but tepid run to wire.
Smart start & bustled wide to lead 1900m, worked to snag rail 1640m, headed 430m & driven, no extra & tapered to wire.
Moderate start, raced last trio 1 off, forced 3 wide 1000m, driven for progress 650m, very wide final turn, plugged on dourly until tapered.
Sharp break & prominent early, settled 1 off with cover fore of midfield, ridden 650m, plodded on one pace.
Fast break, snagged to camp 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, niggled 800m & advanced to 3rd turning in, driven 430m & wilted tamely.
Broke well to dispute early lead, wide 1st turn & caught 3 wide with cover, back to last trio 4 deep 1000m, scrubbed at tail 800m, never a factor.
Fast break wide & driven to lead 1130m, soon to rail, headed 750m, narrow 2nd & ridden turning in, led again 250m, edged clear close home.
Broke well, caught 4 wide no cover midfield, advanced 800m to narrow lead 730m & posted 1 off, all out & headed 250m, tapered late.
Sharp start, settled 2nd 1 off no cover, shuffled back & shifted 3 wide on turn, driven 430m to press lead, always held & tapered late.
Broke with others, sat 1 off with cover midfield, ridden 450m, 3L 7th when crowded 400m, stayed on for minor late gains.
Tardy start & rousted initially, rolled to 3 wide no cover fore of midfield, over-raced 1000m, wide turning in & driven, kept on evenly.
Speed to lead, soon headed, sat rail 1 back, off heels 870m, shifted out & ridden into stretch, one-paced in run home.
Settled back at break to 1 off near rear, snatched off heels 770m, switched 3 deep, 6L last & driven turning in, closed off for minor inroads.
Broke well, taken back to 4 wide with cover near rear, rolled forward 800m to race 5 wide & handy turning in, plugged on evenly.
Taken back from wide gate & soon 3 wide at tail, shifted 4 wide & driven 550m, plodded on tepidly.
Broke well, settled rail midfield, snatched off heels 850m, shuffled back to 1 off near rear, niggled 650m, driven into stretch but found nil.
Broke OK, rousted early, snagged back to 3 wide near rear, rolled forward 800m, ridden turning in, found nothing in tame stretch run.
Slow start, sat rail near tail, niggled 650m, driven 430m, struggled in run to wire.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Slow away, pushed to take midfield spot, 4Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 250M for 2nd.
Eased to sit just behind the leaders 2 wide, pace good, ran on well for 3rd.
Eased at start, 8Ls off the good pace on the fence, lack room 400M, dashed well 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-5 wide throughout, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Hard ridden to occupy the box seat, pace good, flattened 200M.
Eased back, 6Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide throughout, made steady ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Eased to rear, 9Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made some ground 200M.
Very slow away, hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 5Ls off the good pace, just held ground in straight.
Midfield, 3Ls off the good pace along the fence, flattened 300M.
Hard ridden to taka rail and shared the lead at good pace, emptied 250M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide in the lead, pace good, soon out of fuel 300M.
Eased to rear, never a factor.
Pushed to share lead 2 wide at good pace, weakened quickly 400M.
Began well, held, settling midfield close to rail. Popped off fence 500m, got run between horses, powered through for easy win.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling. Travelled keenly after crossing in near 1100m, kept finding when joined upfront 300m, swamped final strides.
Hard ridden early to sit inside leader before taking box seat. Came off fence turning for home, joined leader 300m, battled to line.
Outpaced early, dropping to rear but away from fence. Raced 3-wide final turn, widest in straight, finished off nicely.
Began OK, settled towards rear in one-off position. Bumped when taken out for run top of straight, finished off nicely.
Outpaced, taken in behind horses settling in last pair along fence. Switched out entering straight but had to switch in again for run. Kept on steadily.
Pushed along early to get forward position settling two-back along rail. Had run of the race around turn but found little under hard riding in straight.
No speed, cut to rail at rear. Stayed along rail final turn and straight, kept on fairly.
Outpaced, dropping to rear but kept three-wide. Left without cover turn, switched in 400m but bumped and held for clear running. One-paced when clear.
Allowed to stride forward settling one-back, one-off. Lost position turn, taken very wide in straight but only one-paced.
Ridden along but unable find cover and caught three-wide in midfield. Rolled forward around turn, looked chance 400m before condition gave out.
Ridden forward from widest draw, cutting in 3-back, one-off into turn. Taken very wide in straight but found nothing under hard riding.
Outpaced, dropping to last in one-off position. Taken wide into straight but never competitive.
Began OK, hard ridden to sit 3rd before turn. Popped off fence 600m to look chance before running on empty from 400m.

Bounded in the air as the start was effected, 6Ls away at the rear and travelled much further back than usual, had a smooth run down the inside entering straight, made strong headway to get up near line.
Strode forward, crossed to the lead before home turn, given a breather home turn, quickened again 400M, kept on well but shifted out badly under pressure final 100M, headed close home.
From draw 10 shifted across to a 3-wide position behind runners, pushed very wide 600M, hit the line strongly for a close 3rd. Creditable run in defeat.
Reserved in a rearward position 4-5Ls off the pace, bid wide 600M, quickened up well to go 2nd inside 300M, loomed a serious threat but effort flattened final 100M.
Settled 3Ls back in midfield, held up behind a wall of horses entering straight, switched out to clear 250M, finished off well to claim 5th and should have been closer.
Went forward as expected, tracked the pace 2-wide, ran on same pace when driven 400M, caught up by pursuing rivals 250M, faded towards line.
Taken back behind runners from widest draw, settled at the rear 6Ls off the pace, ran on only fairly final 400M, never reached contention.
Held up behind midfield, kept on at the same pace when the race got serious inside 400M, no impression on leaders.
Began awkwardly, stayed within striking distance behind leaders, could not muster the pace to challenge inside 400M, soon weakened.
Travelled in midfield 3-wide, no cover from 800M, found disappointingly little when asked turning home, gave ground 200M.
Tracked leaders in 3rd, had little left turning home, soon beaten, eased towards the line.
Ridden along to hold forward position between horses about 3L from leader. No run top of straight, switched in and finished strongly to win on the line.
Allowed to stride forward, settling one-back, one-off before turn. Rolled forward entering straight, looked winner when hit front 100m, run down on line.
Taken in from wide draw but still 3-wide toward rear. Took closer order around turn, wide into straight, finished off strongly.
Ridden forward from wide draw and caught 3-wide when pace slackened. Rolled forward to sit outside leader, kicked clear 300m, caught with 50m remaining and crowded final stages.
Pressed forward, raced keenly, checked off heels 1000m, and left wide without cover. Covered extra ground turn, kept on well to just miss the frame.
Jumped well, taken straight to fence, holding box seat to straight. Had open run from 350m but only one-paced.
Jumped with field, held, slipping back towards rear. Came off fence 1000m. Kept on steadily in straight to be closest at finish.
Began OK, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Caught flat-footed turn, unable switch out 400m and switched in, finished off fairly.
Restrained early but raced keenly three-wide with cover. Took closer order turn, wide in straight, one-paced.
Taken in behind horses to sit in last pair, moving towards fence 1000m. Shaken up top of straight and kept on fairly.
Began OK, outpaced, dropping to last but away from fence. Took inside run top of straight but found little under hard riding.
Pressed forward to lead from wide draw, racing extremely wide before crossing in before turn. Collard soon after straightening for home and tired.
Ridden along early behind midfield, lost position turn, taken in top of straight but found nothing.
Pressed forward to sit 3-back from leader on settling. Under pressure soon after straightening and dropped out quickly. (Bled from both nostrils).
Fairly away, positioned 1 out 1 back, travelled well throughout, sent forward near 600M, kept on well in straight and scored by a neck.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back in 9th, same position turning, angled out in straight and made good progress to get 2nd.
Moderately away, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide without cover in 5th, 3 lengths back, took the lead near 500M, kept on well until headed final 100M.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, positioned 3 wide with cover in midfield, difficult to settle throughout, made reasonable headway in straight to make frame.
Average to begin, positioned 1-2 length behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, made minor headway early in straight, no clear run final 100M.
Jumped well, showed early speed to take the lead, easy lead until near 500M, headed turning in, kept on fairly in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned 3 lengths or so back on rail in midfield, saved ground to 500M, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover, 5 lengths back, still 4 wide turning, finished off one-paced in straight.
Average to begin, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, same position until near 500M, crowded turning in, difficult to ride in straight and weakened gradually.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back at tail, still well back turning, made minor progress before inconvenienced close home.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position turning, failed to close off in straight.
Slightly slowly away, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths or so back at rear, similar position turning, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Taken back from a wide draw, positioned 5-6 lengths back at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, emptied early in straight, never competitive.
Began awkwardly, raced 7 lengths back on rail at rear, same position turning, showed no response to riding in straight, finished tailed out.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced prominently in 2nd, travelled well throughout, closed off well in straight and scored narrowly.
Fairly away, sent forward to take the lead and set a moderate tempo, easy lead to turn, kept on very well in straight but just unable to hold off the winner late.
Began well, raced 2 wide, 3-4 lengths back in midfield, angled out turning in, finished off very strongly in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, raced 3-4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground to turn, made minor headway in straight to make frame without threatening the first few.
Began well from a tricky gate, positioned 2 wide, 3 lengths back in 4th, travelled well to turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Began awkwardly, raced 7 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn and hampered near 500M, kept to inside after straightening, no clear running after 200M, made some ground when clear thereafter.
Crowded out start, raced 5 lengths or so back on rail behind midfield, difficult to settle on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Average to begin, taken back to race 6 lengths back at rear, 2-3 wide with cover turning, taken widest in straight and made only minor progress.
Jumped well from gate 1, positioned 1-2 lengths behind the leader in 3rd, saved ground to turn, kept on evenly until near 200M, emptied thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide, 5 lengths back behind midfield, similar position turning, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from the widest gate, unable to slot in, travelled 4 wide and without cover throughout, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with no cover in midfield, similar position turning, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
