Led or disputed lead far side, obtained rails run going up the Rock, hung on well under pressure.
Soon taken back from a wide draw, waited with, finished off race strongly inside final 200 metres.
Vied for early lead after beginning from a poor draw, settled mainly one-out-two-back in 4th, fought on steadily in straight without quickening.
Broke well from the two draw holding narrow lead early stages, ceded advantage to eventual winner going up the Rock, one-paced under pressure from 2nd into straight.
Jumped well, settled towards the rear, made up good ground in straight to be nearest at finish.
Driven along after beginning from the widest gate, settled in 5th within 3L of pace far side, saved ground on inside turning in, improving well when forced to steady 100 metres out.
Broke well, settled one back on rails, found nothing under pressure after straightening.
Niggled along before settling in midfield on rails, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Began moderately, settled in last few, never nearer.
Soon in last few, made no impression in the run down the centre of the straight.
Given reminders to muster early pace, travelled in rear of midfield to straight, soon faded.
Wide in midfield early, towards the rear far side, dropped further backward from around home bend.
Made every post a winner. Led along the fence and kicked clear in the run to the line.
Made its run 4th from the rear, after settling 2 deep with cover. closed off nicely.
Parked midfield, 2 wide with cover. Made steady progress up the running.
Camped outside the leader. Was swamped over the final 50m.
Raced prominently on the paint with cover. Kept up a sound gallop in the straight.
Jumped awkwardly and lost ground soon after, travelling behind midfield on the fence. Made good ground in the run to the wire.
Not the best away, settling midfield the fence. Maintained an even gallop down the running.
Travelled on the speed but coursed 3 deep without cover. Faded over the final furlong.
Didn't begin cleanly travelling last on the paint with cover. Battled away in the home stretch.
Effectively settled 1 out 1 back after the 600m. Was well beaten after the 100m.
Raced worse than midfield, 3 deep, had some cover on the circle. Never looked likely.
Posted 4 deep without cover on the circle, whilst 2nd last. Struggled in the home straight.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1.5Ls at slow sectionals, kept on strongly to score by a neck.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on nicely for 2nd.
Ridden forward to settle in a prominent position, despite trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on strongly to get 3rd.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite hampered by the slow pace, ran on strongly for 4th in a bunched finish.
Jumped slowly, then settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow pace and blocked most straight, dashed strongly final 100M.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the slow sectionals, kept on steadily.
Eased start, settled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite hampered by the slow pace, ran on nicely in a bunched finish.
Camped handy, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide without cover, despite suited by the slow sectionals, kept on one pace until final 50M got crowded.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow tempo, finished off nicely in a bunched finish.
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, one paced home.
Pushed to settle midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, ran on fairly.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, harmed by the slow tempo, never a factor.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw settling clear last by 1500m. Saved ground turn, got clear run in straight, finished strongly for smart win.
Taken in soon after start to one-off position four-back from leader. Tightened 600m, bumped and unbalanced 500m, very wide into straight, rallied under hard riding.
Bumped start, ridden to obtain forward position settling 3-back from leader. Popped off fence 500m, flat-footed top of straight, finished strongly when run opened.
Shifted across behind horses from wide draw settling at rear along fence. Mode forward move passing 500m, widest into straight, finished off nicely.
Pushed forward early before easing off, settling 3-back, one-off. Moved forward 3-wide passing 500m, hit from 350m, kept on well till flattened 50m.
Bumped start, checked 1500m, tightened 600m and lost ground. Taken wide into straight and ran on steadily.
Ridden to obtain forward position, settling one-back, one-off. Lost position round turn, taken wide into straight, ran on steadily till tightened final stages.
Taken in soon after start, racing along rail. Switched out 600m, entered straight behind horses, held for clear run until passing 200m, one-paced.
Pressed forward from inside draw to grab box seat on settling. Came off fence 400m, looked chance 350m, kept on till hampered 150m losing ground.
Began well, led initially then raced inside leaders before taking command 1200m. Led into straight, joined soon after, gave ground quickly from 150m.
Pressed forward to sit outside leader before easing a length behind at the turn. Gave ground soon after straightening for home.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit three three-wide without cover to 450m when gave ground quickly. (Unacceptable performance).
Jumped well, pressed forward to lead on settling. Kicked clear top of straight and kept on well to line.
Ridden to maintain forward position grabbing box seat on settling. Stayed on rail around turn and kept on well in straight.
Bumped start, ridden along to sit 3-back along fence. Switched out turning for home and ran on steadily.
Bumped start, ridden forward to sit 3-back, one-off. Shifted in top of straight to get run and kept on steadily to just miss a place.
Began well, ridden along to hold position one-off, one-back. Swung wide into straight and kept on steadily.
Began fairly, taken closer to fence, took inside run turning for home and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Shifted across behind runners to settle at rear away from fence. Got run between horses top of straight and ran on fairly.
Ridden along to obtain forward position and held three-wide without cover. Turned wide, kept on steadily till tiring final stages.
Began OK, ridden along three-wide with cover to final turn. Turned wide, one-paced in straight.
Crowded out start and lost ground, settling in last pair along fence. Taken out turning for home but once paced. Hampered 150m.
Pressed forward to sit outside leader to straight. Under pressure from 400m and faded gradually.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear in one-off position. Put under pressure turning for home but never competitive.
Settled just off the leader, benefited by the slow sectionals, hung on strongly to score only by a narrow margin.
Eased to sit just off the leaders on the fence, enjoyed the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M, just beaten by a neck in 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, lack room 400M, dashed strongly when clear despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pressed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 200M.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, dashed only fairly along the inside.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M, run ended 100M.
Very slow away, pushed forward, on heels 1300M, 3Ls off the leader on the rails, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed fairly.
Eased back, took rail, obtained midfield spot, 4.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, blocked most straight, little dash.
Eased at start, on heels 1100M, 8.5Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 150M.
Crossed in front and took rail easily, led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon emptied 300M.
Eased at start, blundered badly 1100M, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no dash.
Began OK, allowed to settle three back from leader along rail. Came off fence 400m, had clear run top of straight, led 200m, kept finding to fend off challengers.
Pressed forward to lead on settling before taking sit from 850m. Switched out 450m, rolled forward to lead 350m, passed 250m but kept battling to line.
Shifted in behind runners and last on settling but away from fence. Started forward move 3-wide from 600m, widest into straight, finished off strongly.
Ridden along early but held three wide. Took off around field passing 500m, very wide into straight, battled to line.
Hampered start, raced behind midfield between horses. Checked from heels turning for home, ran on steadily in straight.
Bumped soon after start, pressed forward, settling in one-off position behind leading pack. Got close to heels 400m, one-paced in straight.
Ridden along early, settling three-back, one-off. Shaken up entering straight but only one-paced.
Pressed forward and held three-wide first turn. Continued to roll forward, taking clear lead from 850m. First into straight then one-paced.
Shifted in behind runners from wide draw, settling in last pair along fence. Clear last 500m, taken in turning into straight and kept on fairly.
Began well, ridden along to hold box seat first turn. Raced keenly from 1000m, stayed on rail entering straight, looked chance 250, one-paced.
Began fairly, outpaced, racing at rear in one-off position. Put under pressure turning for home but found little.
Pressed forward but unable lead, settling 3rd in one-off position. Put under pressure from 500m but failed to respond. (Unacceptable performance).
Away quickly, took up the lead 1000M, led steadily first half, quickened up making the turn, kicked clear 300M, continued on well and won unchallenged.
Dropped back from draw 10, settled behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, closed off well to go 2nd 100M but couldn't get to the runaway winner.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, taken out to challenge passing 400M, stayed on moderately for 3rd.
Bustled along after the start, improved to a one out one back position, unable to sprint with eventual winner passing 400M, kept on one paced, lost 2 placing over final 100M.
Never far off 3-4Ls behind leader, kept on same pace and never seriously threatened.
Not hurried early stages, sat in 8th position 5-6Ls off the pace, stayed on the inside turning home but not going the pace to challenge.
Caught wide from 11, moved forward gradually but remained without cover throughout, kept on same pace final 300M.
Began well, hugged the rails tracking leader, severely checked 400M and lost position, not recovered and failed to pick up when driven in straight.
Taken back to the rear 8Ls off the pace, taken wide on straightening, made limited progress only.
Towards the rear 7Ls off the pace, failed to pick up and not making any progress on leaders.
Taken across behind runners, settled in the rear pair, attempted to go through a narrow gap on the inside but was checked 200M, never threatened from the back of the field.
Began well, restrained to sit in midfield, severely checked 400M, lost momentum and gave way, eased mid-straight.

Broke well, soon took up running, led into straight before drifted losing advantage briefly over 200 metres out, fought on nicely to win the ding-dong battle.
Jumped fairly, well there, hugging the rails turning in, fought on doggedly throughout final stages only to be denied in the bobbing of heads.
Began fairly from a poor gate, travelled wide without cover in a prominent position far side, kept on steadily under pressure.
Settled in rear, steadied for a run and switched out 300 metres out, ran on down the centre of the track to be nearest at finish.
Settled in midfield, fought on steadily under pressure, nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately, settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, one-paced
Jumped fairly from a wide draw, ridden early but soon settled for midfield in 3-wide position, one-paced under pressure in straight.
Jumped fairly, gradually picked up under urge to come with a length of the leader, faded steadily after straightening.
Settled in rear of midfield, lost position rounding home bend, ran on past well-beaten runners closing stages.
Jumped well from the one draw, gradually settled behind midfield, remained similar into the straight, kept on.
Gradually taken backward after leaving the widest gate, travelled wide behind midfield to straight, one-paced under pressure.
Raced keenly and refused to settle in a prominent position far side, in 5th about 2L off the pace around home bend, weakened under pressure.
Slow out, remained well behind.
Tightened at start, remained well back and wide throughout. Found nothing in straight.
Handed up early, settling 2nd on the fence with cover. Got all the favours in the straight and won nicely.
Raced back in the field, 1 off with cover. Ran on strongly towards the outside, shifted ground inwards late.
Made its run 5th from the rear after settling on the fence with cover. Closed off well.
Travelled midfield, on the rails with cover. Held up early in the straight, finished off soundly.
Didn't have the best of runners suffering tightening early in the race and in the home stretch. Parked just ahead of midfield, 1 off with cover stayed on well.
Settled 3rd, 1 off without cover. Kept on at the same speed in the run to the wire.
Settled ahead of midfield, on the paint with cover. Was one paced in the run home.
Couldn't go the early speed of the race, travelling worse than midfield, 3 deep with cover. Shifted deep turning for home and was in the mix at the 200m before ending its run at the 100m.
Not the best to begin, settling last close to the rail with cover. Plodded away fairly to the line.
Led by a good margin on the rails. Faded after the furlong.
Raced midfield, 1 of with cover. Struggled in the home straight.
Parked 3rd last 1 off with cover. Failed to run on in the home stretch.
Camped 2nd last, 3 deep with cover. Failed to close off.
Used some gas in the early stages to go forward but drifted back to race ahead of midfield, was posted 3 deep without cover. Was gone at the 300m.
Pushed forward to park outside the leader at slow sectionals, ran on strongly to score by 1.5Ls.
Raced midfield, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow tempo, dashed nicely for 2nd.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the lead on the fence, despite hampered by the slow pace, ran on well for 3rd.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 0.5L at slow sectionals, key on nicely until final 150M weakened, held for 4th.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow sectionals, one paced home.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slow tempo, made some ground in straight.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow pace, kept on one pace to the line.
Eased start, then settled 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow temp, closed to the line well.
Settled worse than midfield about 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow sectionals, never ran on.
Jumped slowly, then travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow sectionals, ran on fairly.
Eased back to settle 4Ls off the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow pace, ran on fairly, blocked final 150M.
Prominent, despite suited by the slow pace, emptied 300M.
Ridden to hold forward position settling one-off, one-back passing 1300m. Took over running soon after straightening and pulled clear for easy win.
Began well, ridden forward to sit three-back from leader along fence. Popped off rail 500m, looked chance when got run 350m, kept on steadily to just hold second.
Taken across behind runners shortly after start but kept away from fence. Made forward move 800m, widest into straight, finished off strongly.
Checked and lost ground start, last on settling. Still last on straightening, switched wide and finished off strongly.
Ridden along early to hold box seat before turn. Blocked for run early in straight but finished off nicely when clear.
Outpaced early, settling towards rear in one-off position. Switched out turning for home, finished off nicely until restricted for room closing stages.
Taken in gradually from wide draw to find rail at rear before turn. No run in straight and kept switching out till finding late passage. Rallied.
Unbalanced soon after jump, dropping to rear away from fence. No clear run in straight until near 300m. Kept on fairly.
Ridden along to obtain forward position settling three-back, one-off. Taken four-wide into straight but only one-paced under pressure.
Hard ridden early to hold rail behind midfield. Got clear run entering straight but only one-paced under pressure.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward and tapped 3-wide without cover in midfield. Covered extra ground turn, one-paced straight.
Began awkwardly, ridden along then got close to heels settling between horses in midfield. Put under pressure 400m but one-paced.
Involved in bumping battle soon after start, mustered to lead passing 1150m, collared soon after straightening and faded.
Bumped several times start, pressed forward to lead on settling, raced keenly, dropping to 2nd 1150m. Hit front 400m but soon beaten and faded.
Hard ridden from wide draw to lead on settling. Put under pressure when challenged top of straight and kept finding to the lune.
Pressed forward to sit one-off behind leader on settling. Drew level on straightening but unable match winner final 300m.
Began well, slightly unbalanced when shifted in 1000m, settling three-back, one-off. Ran on steadily in straight without threatening first two.
Crowded for room soon after start, ridden along to hold rail at midfield. Lost ground when shifted out turn, kept on steadily in straight.
Bumped start, hard ridden but didn't muster, settling at rear. Shifted out turn and ran on steadily in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit two back, one-off. Took closer order around turn, but only one paced in straight.
Ridden along from inside draw to hold box seat before turn. Put under pressure top of straight but only one-paced.
Outpaced and practically detached from field by the turn. Plodded home.
Outpaced. Soon at rear and long away from leaders. Ran past beaten horses. Never competitive.
Bumped start, ridden to make up ground sitting three-back from leader along rail. Started to give ground soon after straightening.
Began fairly, ridden along wide without cover in midfield to turn. Race greenly in straight.
Bumped start, outpaced and soon last and struggling. Never competitive.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, progressed steadily 400M to score.
Pressed forward, shared the lead along the rails, hung on strongly until 100M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the leaders 2 wide, lack room 300M, just ran on for 3rd.
Pushed to share lead 2 wide, ran on until 250M flattened.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 9Ls off the leaders, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden forward, 3Ls off the leaders on the fence, blocked most straight, checked 150M, not tested.
Bumped start, hard ridden early but not muster, 7.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, made steady ground 200M.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, no dash.
Pressed forward, 1.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, soon emptied 300M.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, on heels 400M, ran on fairly.
Hard ridden but not muster, 5.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, out of fuel 200M.
Very slow away and checked, 6Ls off the leaser 2-3 wide, weakened 250M.
Eased to rear, never competitive.
Began well, not pushed and allowed to slide back towards rear in one-off position. Taken out turn, saw daylight 300m and finished strongly.
Began well, raced behind leading pair before being eased, slipping back to midfield in one-off position. Switched out 500m, looked chance 300m, unable match winner final stages.
Jumped well, taken in from wide draw to sit in one-off position behind midfield. Caught inside horses from 400m to 250m before getting run and finished off nicely.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead passing 1200m, crossing to fence 1000m. Still in front with 150m to go before weakening.
Ridden to hold forward position settling between horses two-back from leader. Caught flat-footed top of straight but picked up momentum final 150m.
Bound in air at start and slow into stride. Taken in to sit along fence four-back from leader. Taken out 400m but unable get run until 200m. Boxed on.
Pressed forward, three-wide behind leader and left without cover from 1100m. Rolled forward turn, looked chance 300m, one-paced.
Ridden along early to hold rail behind early leader, dropping two-back entering turn. Stayed on fence in straight and boxed on fairly under pressure.
Began well, settling one-off behind leader. Took closer order entering straight, looked chance 250m, one-paced.
Shifted in behind horses from wide draw and last on settling. Put under pressure turning for home but only one-paced.
Began fairly, ridden but did not respond, settling at rear. Never competitive. (Rider reported was never on the bridle).
Pressed forward from inside draw to take box seat. Still in contention top of straight but gave ground quickly final 100m.

Slow to begin, patiently ridden, 5Ls off the pace 400M and waited for a run along Stands' rail, quickened impressively when a gap opened up 150M, led close home and won going away. (Blood in trachea.)
Tracked leader along the Stands' rail, travelled strongly, held up for clear running 400M to 150M, quickened well when a gap opened up but was outsprinted by winner final stages.
Travelled behind midfield, had to be nudged along halfway, closed off well down center of track, got up for 3rd late stages.
Raced prominently throughout from draw 2, 4th at 400M, ran on well to lead narrowly 150M out, one paced final stages and caught up by rivals final 50M.
Settled on the outside of group, driven to chase leaders 350M, ran on steadily. (Lame next day.)
Up with the pace, all out 350M and looked one of the possible, run ended 100M, swamped close home.
Worked into the lead, led steadily along the Stands' rail, came under pressure halfway, rallied on, headed 150M, crowded for room late stages.
Held up in mid-division, proved difficult to settle in mid-stages, checked 200M and crowded for room, had no clear run until final stages.
Tracked leaders, crowded for room 300M, ran on steadily, awkwardly placed final stages and not able to be ridden out.
Outpaced in first half of the race, 6-7Ls behind leaders at 400M, made late progress without threatening.
Up with the pace, had a good position throughout and had every chance, weakened inside 300M.
Settled 2-3Ls behind leaders but lacked the necessary pace to challenge inside 400M, soon out of contention.
Close up within 2Ls of leaders, kept on same pace when driven 400M, checked 200M, eased.
Began awkwardly, settled towards the rear, hung in throughout the race, left behind passing 400M, eased.
Jumped with field, ridden along in midfield in one-off position. Took final turn wide and finished strongly down centre track to win on line.
Began well, racing with leaders before taking hold and settling 3rd. Brushed running rail 700m, no clear run until after 200m, burst through but caught on line.
Scrubbed up from wide draw to sit outside leader on settling. Took command soon after straightening but run down in final strides.
Blundered on jumping, recovered and pushed along close to rail to sit 3-back from leader. Held for run top of straight but finished off well when clear.
Ridden along wide behind midfield to turn when slipped into one-off position. Kept on steadily in straight until restricted for room closing stages.
Scrubbed up along rail to sit three-back from leader on settling. Took closer order around turn and boxed on steadily in straight.
Gradually taken in from wide draw to sit between horses at the rear. Got clear running soon after straightening and kept on steadily.
Outpaced, gradually taken in to sit along rail in last trio. Stayed on rail entering straight and kept on fairly.
Began well but unable find cover and held 3 and 4 wide into turn. Widest into straight and kept on fairly under hard riding.
Pressed forward from inside draw to lead on settling. Set steady pace to straight, caught 300m, kept on to 200m before fading.
Slow into stride, ridden but unable to make up ground settling last but three-wide. Last into straight, plodded.
Hard ridden to go forward early, settling two-back, one-off. Lay out home turn, gave ground from 250m.
Fast into stride, sat 1-2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, ran on well turning home, established narrow lead 250M, fought on strongly to line and held off challenges both side.

Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward near 1000M to take the lead, easy lead turning, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner final 200M, stayed on for 2nd.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 4 lengths back, bumped near 1250M, 4 wide turning, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line, just failed to get 2nd.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5 lengths back, sent forward and wider on turn, closed off well in straight to make frame.
Average break, positioned 2 wide,1-2 lengths back, similar margin back to turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Fairly away from gate 13, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, same position turning, made no progress in straight and weakened gradually.
Average to begin, raced 4 lengths back on rail behind midfield, saved ground to turn, made minor progress in straight.
Slowly away, raced 4-5 lengths back on rail at rear, difficult to settle throughout, finished off evenly in straight.
Jumped moderately, raced 3 wide in 5th, no cover on turn, steadied near 300M and weakened gradually thereafter.
Bumped start, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, difficult to settle near 800M, 3 wide on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Bumped start, raced 6-7 lengths back at tail, checked near 700M and severely affected by the fell of COMEBACK KID near 650M, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped fairly from the widest draw, taken back to race 3-4 wide at rear, hampered near 750M, improved on turn, 6 wide without cover, emptied in straight after hard run took effect.
Bumped start, raced 7 lengths back at tail, hampered near 700M and severely affected by the fell of COMEBACK KID near 650M, made no progress after turning in, finished last.

Placing: FE
Comment: Ran out abruptly at the start, raced 2 wide, 4-5 lengths back behind midfield, bumped near 900M, fell near 650M.

Bumped start, raced 3 wide, 2 lengths back before midfield, no cover on turn, closed off well in straight and scored narrowly.
Began well, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well to turn, kept on well in straight but unable to hold off the winner late.
Fast into stride, raced outside leader in 2nd, travelled well throughout, kept on well until 150M, still stayed on for 3rd.
Jumped well, positioned 1-2 lengths behind the leader in 4th, saved ground on turn, kept to inside after straightening, no clear running after 200M, stayed on for 4th.
Hampered start, recovered and raced 2-3 lengths back on rail in midfield, crowded near 600M, made minor progress after turning in without threatening the first few.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, still 4 lengths or so back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line.
Began awkwardly, recovered and raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths back, awkwardly placed turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Bumped start, recovered and raced 2 wide, a length or so back before midfield, difficult to settle on turn, made no progress in straight and weakened gradually. (See racing incidents)
Jumped with them, raced 3-4 lengths back in 10th, same position turning, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began awkwardly and bumped shortly after start, raced 4-5 lengths back at rear, no clear running early in straight, made no progress thereafter.
Average to begin, showed no early speed, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, similar position turning, emptied early in straight, never competitive.
Began fairly from a wide draw, unable to slot in, travelled 4 wide and without cover throughout, failed to close off in straight when hard run took toll, finished tailed off.
Travelled ahead of midfield, 2 deep with cover. Switched out into clear running and had the race in its keeping at the furlong.
Stalked the leading division on the rails with cover. Only secured clear running over the last 100m.
Travelled midfield on the fence, had cover. Ran on well.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race, travelling 3rd, tracking the leaders with cover. Maintained an even gallop in the home stretch.
Settled last, 1 off with cover. Made good ground down the running.
Faced the breeze 3 deep without cover, ahead of midfield. Kept on at the same pace down the running.
Shared leading duties travelling on the paint. Was yielding ground over the last 100m.
Settled 2nd last, on the rails with cover. Worked home fairly without threatening.
Camped 3 wide, midfield with cover. Only plodded to the line.
Crossed after the 900m, and vied for leading duties 1 off. Faded over about the final 150m.
Missed the kick, settling 3rd last, had some cover. Failed to close off.
Parked midfield, 2 deep with cover. Weakened quickly over the concluding stages.
Sent forward to share the lead along outer rail, kept on strongly to score by 1-1/4Ls.
Rolled forward to take the lead on the grand side, fought on gamely until 100M for 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader, kept on well for 3rd.
Ridden forward to travel about 1L behind leaders, stayed on one pace until final 50M weakened.
Midfield, settled 3Ls behind leaders, unable to find a clear run until 150M, made ground gradually thereafter.
Midfield, travelled 3Ls off leaders in the middle of the track, worked home steadily.
Failed to muster despite ridden along, travelled 6Ls behind leaders, ran home gradually.
Bumped start, travelled 4Ls behind leaders, made no impression when placed under pressure 600M. (Questioned for riding, see incident report)
Showed good early pace to share the lead, kept on one pace until final furlong weakened.
Midfield, settled 3Ls behind leaders, one paced until final furlong weakened.
Midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader along outer fence, kept on one paced until 300M flattened.
Prominent, however found nothing when placed under pressure near the course proper, flattened badly 300M.
Always at rear, never in contention.
Never a factor.
Broke well, bustled to race handy on rail, impeded 1100m, closed on turn to stalk 1 back, shaken up & switched out 300m, driven to lead 50m, in command at wire.
Speed to lead, snared rail & eased, headed 1240m & sat 1 back, shifted 1 off 1000m, rolled to lead 400m & kicked for home, all out & headed 50m.
Broke well, driven to lead 1240m & worked to rail 1100m, headed 400m & driven under pressure, kept on evenly.
Sharp start, raced handy 1 off, hung in & impeded rival 1100m, driven turning in, kept on evenly.
Broke OK, soon outpaced & bustled, settled rail midfield, driven 400m, stayed on for minor headway.
Good break & rousted early, sat handy 3 wide no cover, off heels & bumped 1070m, shuffled back, ridden 450m, kept on soundly.
Sharp start, raced handy 3rd but caught 3 wide no cover, ridden turning in, plugged on one pace.
Missed break & rousted to settle rail near tail, off heels 650m, driven turning in, stayed on for minor late headway.
Smart start, caught 4 wide no cover & over-raced 1240m, settled midfield until rolled to 3 wide with cover 600m, driven 400m, ran home moderately.
Broke OK, sat 3 wide with cover behind midfield, driven 430m & shifted out, boxed on centre track until tapered final 100m.
Slow start, raced 3 wide with cover near rear, shifted 4 wide 600m, widest into stretch & driven, plodded on tamely.
Tardy start, niggled along 1 off near rear, ridden 430m, struggled in run home.
Missed break, bustled along at tail, wide home turn & driven, found nothing.
Fair start, raced very wide no cover midfield, 4 wide & driven 500m, found nothing & weakened out in stretch.
Fair break, sat 3 wide no cover behind midfield, slotted 1 off 1000m, switched centre track 400m & shaken up, closing drive to lead 50m & in command.
Broke well, slotted handy 1 off with cover, switched 3 wide on turn to challenge, cruised to lead 350m, scooted clear, all out 100m, tapered & headed 50m.
Slow start, rolled to sit rail behind midfield, shifted out & ridden turning in, stayed on to snag 3rd close home.
Taken back to race 1 off near tail, travelled sweetly, 6L back & wide final turn, shaken up 430m & switched inside 260m, closed to 4th at wire.
Tardy start raced rail midfield, checked off heels 650m, crowded & unbalanced turning in, driven & stayed on dourly.
Broke OK, raced fore of midfield on rail, shuffled back & shifted out 600m, driven 430m, boxed on evenly to wire.
Missed break & niggled, settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, ridden 650m, wide turning in, kept on centre track for minor inroads.
Taken behind from widest gate, raced rail near rear, driven 500m, shifted out in run & plugged on one pace.
Missed break, mustered a touch but soon overraced & restrained to settle last pair, niggled 700m, plodded on for minor headway.
Fast start, ridden to lead, 1L clear & shaken up 430m, headed 350m, weakened in run.
Broke OK, rolled to track lead 1 off no cover, driven to challenge 430m, upsides leader 350m, soon emptied & faded weakly.
Moderate start, sat midfield 1 off with cover, over-raced 1230m, rolled up 4 wide into stretch, seen outpaced & faded in run.
Moderate start, raced at tail, under pump 750m, hard-driven turning in, struggled in run to wire.
Broke well, bustled to settle 1 back on rail, driven turning in, found nothing & wilted tamely.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leaders along the rails, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 300M to score.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow tempo, ran on well to the line for 2nd.
Eased to rear, 8Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, hung in badly 400M, dashed well 200M for 3rd.
Hard ridden to keep up in midfield, 4Ls off the leaders 2 wide, dashed only fairly in straight.
Pushed to take rail and shared the lead at slow sectionals, hung out quite badly throughout, out of fuel 200M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leaders along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, checked badly 200M, just ran on.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 300M.
Hard ridden forward, shared lead 2 wide at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on until 200M emptied.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, raced keenly, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 400M, ran on ok.
Eased to sit behind the leaders 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, out of fuel 250M.
Always at rear, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Hard ridden early but never muster, 7Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Began OK, ridden along quietly behind midfield along rail. Popped off fence 600m, got clear run from 350m, hit front 100m and held.
Began well, eased, dropping to rear in one-off position. Taken very wide entering straight and finished strongly to just fail.
Jumped with field, shifted in behind runners early but held in one-off position at rear. Taken to stands rail entering straight and finished strongly.
Began well, ridden along inside leader to 1200m when left outside leader. Rolled forward top of straight, hit front 200m, battled on gamely under pressure.
Hard ridden from wide draw to lead on settling, crossing to fence passing 1200m. Caught 200m out but kept on well until final strides.
One of the first into stride but did not persevere, easing three-back along rail. Got close to heels 1500m, steadied turn, improved along rail until one-paced final 200m.
Ridden along three-wide back stretch to stay in contact with leading bunch. Very wide into straight, kept on fairly until tiring final stages.
Began well, ridden along to hold box seat behind leader. Looked chance entering straight but found little under pressure and tired final stages.
Began fairly, taken in from wide draw settling last. Stayed on rail around turn and ran past tired horses in straight.
First out, eased, setting two-back, one-off. Looked chance entering straight, got close to heels 300m, tired final 200m.
Began fairly, ridden along in one-off position at rear. Bumped 600m, taken wider, found little room 300m, tired final 100m.
Ridden along early, settling close to rail in midfield back stretch. Taken out turning for home, edged forward initially before flattened.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing 3-wide without cover to turn before settling one-back, one-off. Looked chance 400m before tiring.
Began OK, outpaced, racing towards rear along fence. Switched out turning for home but found nothing under pressure.
Travelled well in midfield, gradually picked up momentum passing 400M, hit top gear inside 150M, soon led and was comfortably on top in the end.
Never far off from leaders, into clear passing 400M, loomed a strong threat mid-straight, ran on well but unable to fend off winner final 100M, kicked clear from rest.
Reserved in a position behind midfield, shifted out 450M to challenge, ran on steadily but unable to get closer to first two.
Chased leaders, ideally placed to strike turning home, ran on steadily but not finishing pace of first 3, got up for a non-threatening 4th late stages.
Quickly into stride, secured lead on the rails, joined by a rival passing 1000M, quickened again 400M, caught 200M, faded towards finish.
Checked shortly after the start, settled towards the rear, made limited progress passing 400M, not reached leaders.
In mid-division and no closer than 3-wide, kept on same pace final 400M and lacked the necessary response.
Dropped off to last about 8Ls back, gave only a mild response when driven 400M, never a threat to leaders.
Taken back to the rear 7Ls off leaders, taken wide 400M, stayed on only fairly, never reached contention.
Began awkwardly, caught wide no cover throughout the race, strode forward chasing leaders entering home turn, kept on same pace before weakening 200M.
Began only fairly, settled 3-4Ls behind leader in midfield, not quickened when driven along entering straight, eased 200M out.
Settled towards the rear, 3-wide home turn, failed to pick up and soon left behind by leaders, eased towards the finish.
Strode forward, pressed leader on the outside, gave way passing 450M, eased 200M when no chance.
Slow to begin, along the rails and travelled behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, weakened 350M and soon behind. (lost left hind plate 1100M / Unacceptable Performance).
Slow, pressed forward 3-wide with cover initially, lost cover around turn, picked up momentum from 400m, hit front 100m, held.
Allowed to stride forward to grab box seat back stretch. No run top of straight, close to heels 200m, finished strongly when clear, just failed.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, crossed to rail and steadied pace. Joined top of straight, kicked ahead, caught 100m, kept on.
Ridden to hold forward position, settling one-back, one-off. Rolled forward entering straight to lead for a few strides, caught 100m, swamped.
Ridden along early settling three-back the fence. No clear run top of straight, shifted out 200m looked chance before crowded and lost ground 100m.
Began OK, ridden along without being pushed, settling three-back, one-off. Taken out turn and left without cover from 800m. Wide into straight, one-paced under pressure.
Began well, racing behind leading pair till eased back to midfield between horses. Switched out entering straight and ran on steadily.
Began fairly, not pushed, settling along rail three-back from leader. Blocked for run top of straight, switched out and ran on fairly.
Slow, taken in, settling in one-off position towards rear. Stayed on rail around turn, switched out straight but only one-paced.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling at rear in one-off position. Taken wide entering straight but one-paced under pressure.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. No run top of straight, steadied 200m, one-paced.
Slow into stride, settling towards rear along rail. Improved position around final turn but one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward from wide draw but unable find cover 1400m and allowed to improve, sitting outside leader 900m. Gave ground soon after straightening for home.
Shifted in behind runners from wide draw but still held 3-wide towards rear. Covered extra ground turn and tired final stages.
Began awkwardly, positioned 4 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run to turn, angled out early in straight and finished off strongly to score by a short head.
Moderately away from gate 11, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, easy run to turn, took the lead 400M, kept on very well but just couldn't hold off the winner late. (lost right hind plate)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8-9 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off well to get 3rd.
Began well, taken back to race at rear, 8 lengths back, 3 wide with cover turning, taken wide in straight and finished off well to make frame.
Slowly away, raced 6-7 lengths back on rail at rear, saved ground to turn, made good progress in straight without threatening the first few.
Began well, sent forward to race 2-3 lengths back on rail before midfield, saved ground turning, kept to inside after straightening, finished off evenly.
Slow to begin, raced 2 wide at rear, 7 lengths back, similar position turning, no daylight early in straight, showed minor progress when in clear thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide and without cover, 4 lengths back in midfield, still no cover on turn, finished off evenly.
Fairly away, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, similar position turning, finished off one-paced.
Average to begin, raced 5 lengths or so back on rail in 10th, travelled well to turn, failed to close off in straight, never a threat.
Slightly slowly away, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back in midfield, similar position turning, found nothing in straight and eased final 100M.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, travelled 4 wide with no cover in midfield, same position turning, failed to close off in straight when hard run took effect.
Jumped well from a wide draw, took the lead easily, headed passing 400m and gradually dropped away. (See racing incidents)
Began fairly from the widest draw, raced 2 wide, 2-3 lengths back, similar position turning, steadied near 350M, emptied thereafter.

Jumped well, taken back to race 2 wide behind midfield, improved after 700M, finished off well in straight and scored.
Began awkwardly, recovered to race in 3rd, enjoyed the advantageous sectionals throughout, under pressure after 500M, closed off well to get 2nd.
Jumped with them, positioned 1-2 lengths behind the leader in 2nd, easy run throughout, took the lead near 500M, kicked clear entering straight but couldn't hold off the late challengers close home.
Fairly away, raced 8 lengths back in 6th, slightly improved along the rail after 700M, inconvenienced near 500M, angled out in straight and made some headway to be nearest on line.
Average to begin, race on rail in 4th for the majority of the race, shifted out near 700M and made contact with FLYING IN, finished off evenly in straight.
Taken back from gate 7, raced at rear throughout, inconvenienced near 600M, still well back turning, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, steadied near 2100M, difficult to settle for a short distance thereafter, raced at rear throughout, failed to close off in straight.

Jumped well, showed early speed to take the lead but difficult to settle in the early and middle stages, uncontested for the majority of the race, headed near 500M and gave ground thereafter, finished tailed off. (Bled)
Parked 1 off with cover, midfield. Cornered deep, took some time to wind up but motored home the last furlong.
When unable to find cover early when racing deep, pressed forward to take up leading duties on the rails after the 700m. Straightened a couple of lengths in front, nailed late.
Slow to begin to raced worse than midfield, on the rails with cover. Finished off well.
Missed the start settling last, 1 off with cover. Came widest in the straight and rattled home to the fill the frame.
Had no excuses, effectively racing 3 back the paint with cover. Didn't find a lot extra down the running.
Was handy early but as the race unfolded eventually settled midfield the fence, had cover. Didn't have the clearest of runs in the straight, finished off soundly.
Proved difficult to settle and the near 600M was left racing 3 wide without cover in front of midfield. One paced in the run home.
Made its run 3rd from the rear after settling, 3 wide with cover. Worked home fairly.
Camped 2nd on the rails, had cover on the circle. Faded over about the last 150m.
Raced at the rear, close to the running rail, had cover. Made no impression in the home stretch.
Settled worse than midfield, 2 deep with cover. Failed to run on.
Travelled 3rd, 2 wide with cover. Was a beaten horse early in the straight.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo, swung wide turning in, dashed strongly to score by a neck.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, dashed well for 2nd, just missed by a neck.
Ridden forward to settle 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, despite not suited by the fast pace, ran on strongly to get 3rd, missed by a neck.
Rolled to occupy the box seat, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader, hampered by the fast tempo, ran on well however final 50M weakened.
Prominent, despite harmed by the fast sectionals, kept on steadily to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, then ridden forward to settle 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast tempo, one paced home.
Travelled worse than midfield 8Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast tempo, ran on ok.
Sent forward to take the lead along the fence at fast pace, kept on until 150M weakened.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader at fast sectionals, kept on until final 150M emptied.
At rear throughout, 10Ls behind the leader, suited by the fast tempo, made minor ground over the concluding stages.
Pushed to midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite benefited by the fast pace, never ran on.
Jumped slowly, detached from the field throughout, never a factor.
Broke well, sat rail midfield, niggled 600m & shifted out, slight check 490m, wide into stretch, bumped rival 300m & driven, led 130m, drew clear.
Good start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, bustled 900m, forced wider 600m, driven 450m, widest into stretch, closed to 2nd 100m, held at wire.
Broke well & bustled early, raced rail fore of midfield, niggled backstretch, under pump 420m, stayed on under strong drive to take 3rd.
Taken back at break to race at tail on rail, slotted 3 wide for progress 670m, driven wide home turn, sound headway, just missed frame.
Led from gate, soon headed & 2nd 1 back, shuffled to 3rd 1 off in backstretch, shifted 3 wide 400m & driven, led 160m, soon headed & tapered.
Broke with others, caught 3 deep midfield, scooted to lead 1000m, to rail 880m, driven into stretch, headed 160m, tapered to wire.
Snagged to race last pair initially, soon rolled 3 wide to sit midfield, niggled 650m, driven 400m & slight bump 300m, weakened in run.
Broke OK, soon led, to rail 1200m, headed 1000m, shuffled to 1 back on rail, niggled 600m under pressure, all out turning in, plugged one pace.
Held up on rail near rear, shaken up 500m & checked slightly, driven 450m, plugged on moderately.
Broke OK, camped 1 off with cover near rear, shifted 3 deep 500m, last & driven 400m, plodded on same speed.
Fast start to race 3 wide no cover 3rd, rolled to 2nd 1 off & pressed lead 650m, driven 320m, under pressure when unbalanced 220m & faded.

Placing: PU
Comment: Fast start, slotted 1 off with cover fore of midfield, broke down 500m.
Broke with others, stalked 1 back on rail, shaken up final turn, driven on fence to lead 75m, edged ahead.
Broke well, sat 1 off 1 back, over-raced backstretch, shuffled back 650m, recovered spot 470m, driven 350m to narrow lead 150m, headed 75m, no extra.
Smart start, covered up 1 off midfield, shuffled back 700m, under pump 540m, shifted out 300m & driven to snag 3rd close home.
Smart start, rolled to 2nd 1 off no cover, moved upsides to press leader final turn, driven 320m, boxed on until tapered late.
Broke OK, soon to rail & raced midfield, driven 300m, shifted off heels 100m, closed off without threatening.
Started OK, raced 1 off behind midfield, shifted 3 wide 660m & brief advance, ridden on turn, shifted wide into stretch & closed to wire.
Sharp start to lead, dictated tempo, driven turning in & shifted off rail, soon all out & headed 150m, faded.
Missed break, raced last pair on rail, last & driven into stretch, plugged on one pace.
Awkward start, raced rail behind midfield, 1 off & driven turning in, plodded on tepidly.
Slow start, sat 1 off in last pair, niggled 500m, driven turning in, plodded on evenly.
Sharp break, caught 3 wide no cover & unable to slot, raced midfield, shuffled back 500m, switched widest turning in, soon emptied.
Tardy start, sat 3 wide with cover behind midfield, switched 4 wide 800m & advanced rapidly to 3 wide no cover 620m, weakened entering stretch.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M to score only by a narrow margin.
Settled just off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, ran on strongly 300M, just beaten by a nose in 2nd.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, lack room 300M, ran on strongly for 3rd.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 0.5Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, hung on well until 100M flattened.
Midfield along the fence, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, little dash in straight.
Pushed early, 5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 200M.
Midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Behind midfield, 5Ls off the leader on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, little dash in straight.
Eased to rear, 7Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
6Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on ok.
At back, 6Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Not suited by the slow pace, never a factor at rear.
Hard ridden to hold forward position two back from leader. Disappointed for run 300m, got clear 200m, powered home strongly. (Rider reported saddle slipped).
Pressed forward from wide draw to hold position about half a length inside leader. Joined leader from 300m, battled but caught final strides.
Hard ridden from widest draw to lead on settling but kept away from fence. Joined up front 300m, battled but caught final strides.
Bumped shortly after start, pressed forward 3-wide before finding cover at turn. Taken wide in straight and ran on well down centre track.
Began awkwardly, pressed forward but wide, hampered 800m before settling two-back, two-off. Had clear running straight but only one-paced.
Hard ridden early to hold forward position one-off, one-back to straight. Put under pressure 300m out but one-paced.
Unable go early pace, eased and taken to fence. Saved ground around turn, clear running in straight but one-paced.
Ridden along three-back, one-off to turn, taken wide into straight but only one-paced under hard riding.
Slow outpaced, drifting to rear but held three-wide. Taken widest in straight but unable make ground.
Began well, pressed forward, settling three-back from leader. Lay out from 600m, little response when pressured. Unacceptable performance. (Ride blamed lack of Happy Valley experience).
Slow into stride, settling at rear along fence. Never competitive. (Had minor injury left upper incisor tooth before start.)
Checked, crowded for room at start, and last on settling but away from fence. Never competitive.
Chased leaders in 3rd, travelled strongly throughout, allowed to stride on passing 300M, led 150M out and surged clear to win with ease.
From draw 10 worked his way to the front, slowed down tempo middle stages, kept on inside 350M, headed by fast finishing winner 150M, faded final stages but held on for 2nd.
4-5Ls off the pace in mid-division, stayed on creditably under pressure although no match for the winner.
Shifted across from wide barrier early stages, patiently ridden 8Ls off the pace, responded well 300M and made good late progress, just missed out on a minor placing.
Restrained in a rearward position, well off the pace early stages, nudged along 450M, steadily made progress over final 300M but never a serious threat to leaders.
Raced in midfield on settling down, 5Ls off leader 400M, kept to inside throughout but never going the pace to challenge.
Dropped back, outpaced and over 10Ls off the pace early stages, taken widest to challenge, stayed on mildly, shifted in final stages under pressure.
Up with early pace, sat back in 4th passing 700M, driven along 450M but didn't find a great deal for pressure, one pace over final 300M.
Quickly into stride, tracked leader, lacked further response 300M, no extra final 100M and was swamped.
Settled at the back of the field over 10Ls off the pace early stages, gave limited response when driven at top of the straight, never a factor.
Caught 3-wide in a position worse than midfield, had no cover from 700M, unbalanced 200M when bumped, not pace to challenge, eased towards the line.
Began awkwardly, travelled behind midfield, came under serious pressure 500M out, soon beaten.

Jumped well from a poor draw, niggled along amongst leaders throughout far side disputing lead around the bend, hit the front under pressure over 200 metres out, just held on.
Travelled mainly 5-wide just off the pace, improved around home bend to join leaders into straight, unable to peg back the winner throughout.
Jumped fairly, settled within 2L of pace off the rails, commenced move entering straight, kept on one pace without quickening.
Slightly slow out, soon recovered to chase behind leaders, similar turning into straight, one-paced.
Soon took up running and led along rails, unable to sustain effort when faded inside final 300 metres.
From a poor gate, settled just worse than midfield, kept on steadily in straight without quickening.
Not far off far side when mainly 4-wide, lost position around home bend, 3L 7th into straight, ran home one-paced.
Ridden early from the one draw, settled just off the pace on rails, gave ground steadily after straightening.
Soon dropped to last few, remained similar before saving ground on rails turning in, made no further impression.
Began fairly from a wide gate, travelled wide without cover about 3L off the pace, gave ground from home bend and dropped away quickly in straight.
Soon dropped to last few, never seen with a chance.
Very sluggish at start, always well behind and never seen with a chance.
Settled just ahead of midfield, 1 off with cover. Shifted out prior to the home turn and straightened 5 wide. Swept to the front near the 150m and the race in its keeping well before the line.
Raced afore of midfield, on the fence with cover. Finished off gamely.
Travelled 3 back the fence with cover. Peeled out before the home turn, hit the front near the 300m, and ended its run before the 100m.
Settled 3rd last, on the paint with cover. Kept grinding away down the running.
Settled fourth from the rear, 1 off with cover. Shifted deep turning for home, finished off soundly.
Travelled behind midfield, 2 deep with cover. Plugged away down the running.
Settled 2nd last, 1 off with cover. Shifted widest on the home turn, kept on at the same speed in the home stretch.
Travelled last on the rails with cover. Was one paced in the run home.
Camped 6th last, 1 off with cover. Kept plodding away in the home straight.
Settled 2nd, 1 off no cover. Yielded ground quickly over the final 150m.
Was handy in the run, travelling 1 off with cover. Carried wider after the 500m, failed to find any extra in the straight.
Travelled behind midfield, on the rails with cover. Made no impression in the home stretch.
Led along the fence. Was a beaten horse at the furlong. (Blood in trachea).
Had every hope after box seating. Struggled over about the last 300m.
Ridden forward to take the lead 2 wide at slow sectionals, kept on strongly to hold the challenger by a short head.
Raced midfield, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, worked home strongly, just missed.
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, kept on steadily for 3rd.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, 900M steadied, suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
Sent forward, despite trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, kept on steadily to the line.
Settled worse than midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite not suited by the slow pace, ran on nicely. (Bled)
Settled worse than midfield, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite not suited by the slow pace, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground.
At rear, settled 7Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slow sectionals, never ran on.
Jumped slowly, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, hampered by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 4 wide without cover, not suited by the slow pace, never looked likely.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and share the lead at slow sectionals, hung on until 250M weakened.
Always at rear, never a factor.
Pushed to midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, flattened 300M.
Speed to lead, set tempo unchallenged, asked to lengthen 350m, stretched clear, all out 100m, tapered but held on.
Tardy start, bustled along midfield, shifted wide & 4L down turning in, grinding closer to nick 2nd at wire.
Fast start & bustled to sit handy 3 wide no cover, driven turning in & to 2nd 240m, gradually closed on leader but mugged for 2nd at line.
Broke OK to race 1 off with cover fore of midfield, bustled 950m, shifted 3 wide final turn & driven 450m, boxed on evenly.
Broke OK, soon bustled 1 off, advanced to midfield & to rail 900m, shifted out & driven 430m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Fast break & bustled, caught wide no cover, edged across to settle upsides leader 850m, driven turning in, found little & emptied 250m, faded out.
Tardy start, raced 3 wide with cover midfield, under pump 800m, outpaced & lost ground, scrubbed along in stretch & plodded on evenly.
Broke well to race fore of midfield 3 wide with cover, outpaced on turn & forced 4 wide, hard ridden but found little in tepid stretch run.
Broke well, chased 1 back on rail, driven 430m & outpaced, plodded on same speed.
Taken back & raced 2nd last, sat 1 off, to tail 600m, ridden turning in, stayed on for modest gains.
Taken back, raced 1 off with cover behind midfield, to rail 600m & minor progress, switched out home turn, ridden 400m, plugged on until wilted final 100m.
Sharp start, raced outside leader until settled 1 off 1 back 850m, shaken up 400m & switched out, tapered thereafter.
Missed break & detached at rear, bustled to join tail 830m & minor advance 3 wide, all out turning in, struggled in run home.
Broke well but outpaced & bustled, soon near rear on rail, niggled throughout, plodded on same speed, eased 150m.
Sluggish start, camped last pair 1 off, 3 wide for progress 600m, widest into stretch, shaken up 410m, swept to lead 200m, drew clear.
Smart start, bustled to sit close 2nd 1off, pressed lead 500m, led 440m, narrowly headed 340m, battled on dourly, no match for winner.
Snagged back to 1 off near rear, switched 3 deep 600m, smooth progress into stretch, not clear run until shaken up150m, closed late.
Good break, taken back to 1 off with cover fore of midfield, shifted out 400m & driven, led 340m, emptied 200m & headed, faded to wire.
Broke well, snagged to sit 3 wide with cover midfield, wide & driven 420m, boxed on evenly centre track.
Tardy start, raced rail behind midfield, driven turning in & shifted out, stayed on evenly.
Smart break, snagged back & caught 4 deep no cover fore of midfield, ridden 820m, pressed front rank home turn, all out 300m & tapered.
Slow start, raced rail near rear, shifted 1 off 600m, driven 430m, plugged on moderately.
Smart start, trapped wide & snagged back 1400m, sat 3 wide with cover near rear, 4 wide & driven 600m, very wide into stretch & soon emptied.
Broke well, pace to race handy but caught 3 wide no cover, ridden to press front rank 500m, all out 400m, struggled in run home.
Broke with others, snagged to stalk 1 back on rail, driven turning in & every chance, switched off heels 300m, faded weakly thereafter.
Smart start, dropped in to midfield 1 off, niggled 550m, driven & shifted out turning in, one paced, crowded & checked 230m, eased.
Outpaced & rousted at break, niggled at tail on inner, driven along turning in, found nothing & eased late.
Broke well with others, keen on rail & led 1500m, set steady tempo, under pressure & joined 500m, headed turning in, emptied 300m & eased thereafter.
Hard ridden forward, 3.5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Settled in midfield, 5Ls off the good pace 2 wide, progressed steadily 300M for 2nd, just missed by a short head.
Pushed forward, 2Ls off the good pace 2 wide, closed off strongly for 3rd.
Eased midfield, 6Ls off the good pace along the rails, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear, just missed win by a narrow margin.
Settled in box seat, ran on well to the line.
Hard ridden early but not muster, 5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide, made ground 300M, run ended 100M.
Eased midfield, 6Ls off the good pace 2 wide, made steady ground 250M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 4Ls off the good pace on the fence, lack room 400M, made some ground 200M.
At back, 7Ls off the good pace along the fence, blocked most straight, ran on ok.
At back, 7.5Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, ran on ok.
At back, 7.5Ls off the good pace, trapped 3-4 wide, ran on fairly.
Very slow away, 7Ls off the good pace 2 wide, no dash.
Took rail and led easily by 2Ls at good pace, out of fuel 250M.
Slow away, never a factor.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, setting good pace while being challenged throughout. Found extra to pull away in final stages.
Hard ridden to stay outside and eyeball leader. Continued to battle strongly in straight, losing only in final strides.
Bumped start, ridden along but unable match early speed, settling three-back in a one-off position. Turned in behind horses, got run 320m, finished off nicely.
Began well, not pushed, settling between horses four-back from leader. Got inside run in straight and ran on steadily under hard riding.
Allowed to stride forward from outside draw but held three-wide in second tier behind leader around turn. Battled on gamely.
Ridden along between horses to maintain forward position before settling one-back, one-off. Kept on fairly under pressure in straight.
No early speed, taken in behind horses to rail but then switched out around turn. Widest in straight and kept on steadily.
Ridden along early to hold midfield position but taken wide 900m. Kept on one-paced in straight.
Pressed forward from inside draw settling three-back from leader. Took closer order around turn but soon tired.
Bumped start, taken across behind runners but held in one-off position. Never competitive.
Ridden along early to hold midfield position. Unbalanced when hit rail 700m and lost position. Flattened final stages.
Jumped OK but outpaced and soon last. Never competitive. (Unacceptable performance).
Strode forward as expected, led uncontested to 500M, found plenty in reserves when driven out 350M, kept on gamely final stages to hold off pursuing rivals.
From wide draw shifted across behind runners, held up at the rear 7Ls off the good pace, shaken up 400M and took a while to get going, made good progress to get within 0.8L of winner.
Began awkwardly, stayed close enough to the pace, 2Ls to make up on eventual winner passing 400M, ran on well to go 2nd 150M but always held by winner, beaten to 3rd just before line.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settled near the rear 5-6Ls behind leader, waited with until passing 300M, closed off well to be nearest at the finish. (Jockey and Trainer questioned.)
Given a waiting ride as usual, 5-6Ls off the pace turning for home, guided to outside of field and finished off well.
Dropped back and held up at the rear of the field, 6Ls behind leader and still last at 400M, made stealthy headway between runners for a never nearer 6th.
Settled in mid-division along the 3-path, soon into clear on straightening, made good initial progress but turned one pace final 150M.
Settled just behind the pace, advanced to press leader 600M, loomed a threat but kept on at same pace only when driven, lost 2nd 150M and was swamped final 50M.
Held up 2-wide in midfield, hung in entering straight and proved difficult to ride at times, ran on same pace, no threat to main rivals.
Guided to a midfield position along the rails, lacked immediate response when driven early straight, checked 300M, stayed on without threat final 200M.
Held up behind mid-division, found less than expected passing 400M and not able to quicken with main rivals, never a serious threat. (Heart Irregularity)
Never far off from leaders, had a smooth run along the fence but unable to muster a challenge turning in, soon outpaced.
Stayed within striking distance always, driven along 400M but gave no further response, weakened 300M out.
In touch but unable to cross from 12, caught 3-wide no cover throughout the race, gave way passing 400M.
Allowed to stride forward at own pace settling three-wide in midfield but with cover. Began forward move 500m, widest into straight, kept on strongly to win on the line.
Eased, taken in gradually to sit in one-off position at rear. No run top of straight, got split 250m, powered through to just miss out.
Ridden to maintain forward position two-back from leader along rail. Popped off fence 450m, got run 350m, took over lead 200m, run down final strides.
Bumped start, outpaced, dropping to rear in one-off position. Taken out turning for home and finished strongly down centre track.
Outpaced, settling behind midfield in one-off position. Switched out on straightening and ran on fairly to be closest at finish.
Bumped start, taken across behind runners from wide draw and last on settling. Still last into straight before finishing off nicely down centre track.
Ridden to maintain forward position, three-back from leader in one-off position. Took closer order turn, looked chance 200m, no extra final.
Began OK, ridden along behind midfield in one-off position. Raced tight making turn, got inside run in straight, kept on fairly.
Steadied shortly after start, but held rail behind midfield. Came off fence 500m. no clear run top of straight, ran on fairly when clear passing 200m.
Pressed forward from outside draw to lead after 1000m. Crossed to fence around turn, joined up front 200m, kept on unit swamped final 50m.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside early leader, easing to one-off, one-back before turn. Still in contention top of straight before tiring.
Began well, led to 1000m before taking box seat around turn. Began to give ground from 300m.
Began well, pushed forward but kept wide without cover from 900m. Gave ground soon after straightening.
Jumped with field, ridden along 4-back from leader along rail. Gave ground soon after entering straight.
Began well from a tricky gate, showed early speed to race 2 wide in 3rd, enjoyed the slow sectionals, 2nd on turn, dueled from 250M, stayed on strongly to gain upper hand inside 150M.
Moderately away from gate 13, sent forward to take the lead and set a slow tempo, easy lead to turn, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner final 150M.
Jumped with them, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, difficult to settle near 1300M, same position turning, finished off mildly in straight to get 3rd without posing any threat to the first two.
Slightly slowly away, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, slightly improved on turn, made good progress in straight to make frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7-8 lengths back at tail, not suited by the slow tempo, still 5 lengths back on turn, finished off strongly in straight to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Jumped well, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run to turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Out well, unable to slot in, raced 3 wide and without cover in 4th, difficult to settle early, still no cover on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Slowly away, raced 4 lengths back on rail behind midfield, difficult to settle throughout, steadied near 600M, finished off evenly in straight.
Out in line, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3 lengths back, same position turning, finished off one-paced in straight.
Average to begin, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths or so back behind midfield, similar position turning, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced 3 wide with cover, 6 lengths back at rear, improved on turn but failed to close off in straight.
Began well from a wide draw, taken back to race 2 wide, 6 lengths back at rear, angled out after turning in, finished off one-paced.
Jumped well, showed early speed to race in a length behind the leader in 2nd, easy run throughout, failed to close off in straight. (See racing incident)
Slow to begin, raced 5-6 lengths back on rail at rear, same position turning, showed response after turning in, eased final 100M, never competitive.
