Soon taken back from the widest gate travelling on the rails, continued to save ground turning in, rattled home to assert authority inside final 100 metres.
Vied for lead from a tricky gate, obtained rails run passing the Rock, unable to sustain effort and worn down inside final 100 metres.
Settled 3-wide in midfield or slightly worse, ran on under pressure in straight to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly from the one draw, settled in midfield early before improving to one-back position coming out of far side, one-paced under pressure in the run home.
Jumped moderately, niggled along in last few, made headway along rails coming out of far side, continued to save ground entering straight, only kept on at the same pace down the inside of straight.
Midfield early, lost position past the Rock, behind midfield rounding home bend and into straight, made moderate progress near the centre of the track without threatening.
Settled towards the rear, wide into straight, made moderate progress near the centre of the straight but never threatening.
Broke well, ridden along to hold place settling 3-wide in a prominent position, made short-lived effort early in straight, no extra closing stages. (Lame)
Wide throughout, soon in rear, never seen with a chance.
Began moderately, soon picked up to better than midfield, gave ground steadily after straightening.
Always well behind.
Amongst leaders and wide far side, obtained 2-wide position nearer the rails approaching home bend, weakened under pressure in straight. (Lame next day)
Rolled forward settling just off the pace, 3 deep facing the breeze. Found an extra gear at the 150m and drew clear.
Drifted back early settling 3rd from the rear on the rails with cover.. Came with wider on the home turn, ranged up and looked likely at the furlong but couldn't sustain its run.
Camped midfield, 1 off with cover. Swung deep on the home turn and closed off steadily.
Parked in last position on the paint with cover. Peeled out early in the home straight and worked home soundly.
Led early before handing up and box seating. Copped some tightening early in the straight, faded over the last 100m.
Parked handy with cover, 1 off. Was on paced down the running.
Ridden along but couldn't go the early speed of the race settling midfield the fence. Stayed to the inside in the straight, gave ground over the concluding stages.
Raced behind midfield on the rails with cover. Never really quickened in the run home.
Raced wide in the early stages then was allowed to improve to race outside the leader, 1 off near the 1100m. Weakened over the final 100m.
Missed the start, settling worse than midfield, 2 wide with cover. Made no impression in the home stretch.
Settled 2nd last, 1off with cover. Failed to close off.
Travelled 2nd early before taking up leading duties on the fence passing the 1100m. Was running on empty passing the furlong.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, dashed on strongly to score impressively by 3Ls.
Take back to rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast pace, worked home nicely to get 2nd.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by fast sectionals, hung on well until final 100M for 3rd.
Eased to settle worse than midfield, 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast tempo, ran on well.
Eased to midfield, 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast pace, ran on steadily.
Midfield early, gradually moved forward from 600M, harmed by the fast sectionals, kept on until final 100M weakened.
Pushed forward to obtain the box seat, harmed by the fast tempo, found no extra after straightening.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the fast sectionals, flattened over the last furlong.
Midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite benefited by the fast pace, never ran on.
Rolled forward to settle 1.5Ls outside the leader, harmed by the fast tempo, soon flattened after straightening.
Taken back from the wide barrier, despite benefited by the fast tempo, never looked likely.
Trapped wide without cover throughout, flattened badly soon after straightening.
Jumped with field, ridden along 3-wide at rear before finding cover back stretch. Began forward move 500m, wide into straight, powered home to win drawing clear.
Ridden along to hold forward position one-back, one-off. Awkward turn, rolled forward 500m, hit from 200m but run down lose line.
Began well, pressed forward inside leaders to hold box seat by turn. Got inside run on straightening, kept on well till swamped final stages.
Allowed to settle behind midfield in one-off position. Rolled from 400m, wide into straight, kept on steadily to line.
Began OK, settling three-back the fence. Had clear run entering straight, looked chance 200m, one paced final stages.
Shifted across behind runners settling last but away from fence. Began forward move from 500m, widest into straight, ran on steadily. Closest at finish.
Jumped well, led to 1300m when passed on the inside. Drew level 350m, kept on steadily till running on empty from 100m. Wound left hind.
Slow into in stride, recovered, ridden behind midfield on fence. Caught flat-footed when field speedy up 400m and one-paced in straight.
Shifted across behind runners to sit in last pair along fence. Clear last entering straight, ran past beaten horses.
Pressed forward inside leader to take over running from 1300m. Set slow pace to 350m when headed, giving ground streakily from 200m.
Ridden along early to hold forward position three-back, one-off. Put under pressure from 500m but found nothing and faded gradually.
Ridden to hold forward position two back from leader. Switched off fence 450m, picked up momentum final 200m to win close home.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead on settling. Kicked clear top of straight, looked winner 200m, run down on line.
Hard ridden early to sit in slipstream of leader. Pulled out 450m to make run but unable close gap.
Outpaced, dropping to near rear in one-off position. Taken 3-wide turning for home, taken wider in straight and kept on well to be closest at finish.
Outpaced, dropping to clear last and becoming detached. Caught up to field top of straight and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit one-back, one-off. Lost position turn, stayed on rail and ran on steadily in straight.
Crowded out start dropping to near last. Lay out turn, awkward on heels 500m, switched out in straight and kept on steadily.
Began OK, settling behind midfield along rail. Stayed on rail around turn and ran on fairly in straight without looking dangerous.
Taken closer to fence and ridden along early but reluctant to stride out. Switched out turn but one-paced. (Rider reported reluctant to stride out among horses)
Bumped start, ridden along to hold rail in midfield, Taken out 350m to make run but only one-paced.
Hard ridden early but not enough speed and caught wide without cover. Taken to one-off position 600m but came off bridle and lost interest. (Unacceptable performance)
Ridden along early to maintain forward position but held wide without cover. Gave ground turning for home and faded.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, held up 300M, dashed strongly when clear and scored only by a short head.
Awkward away, 5.5Ls off the leaders 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 200M whilst hanging in, just beaten by narrow margin in 2nd.
Pushed to occupy box seat, raced keenly and checked 900M, benefited by the slow pace, led 300M, just beaten in 3rd.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leaders 2 wide, dashed well 250M despite not suited by the slow pace, on heels just prior to the line.
At back, 5.5Ls off the leaders along the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 200M.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, little dash.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the slow pace along the fence, just held ground in straight.
Behind midfield, 4.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack turn of foot.
Pushed early, trapped 3 wide, steadily went forward, shared the lead at slow sectionals 2 wide, reduced 200M.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, soon weakened 300M.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead at slow sectionals, soon out of fuel 250M.
Midfield, 4Ls off the leaders on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, emptied 200M.
Ridden along early settling three-back, one-off before turn. Taken wider entering straight and finished off strongly to win pulling clear.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader passing 1300m. Put under pressure 350m, looked chance 200m, unable to match winner.
Hard ridden early to hold position one-off, one-back first turn. Pressed forward entering straight but unable to match first two.
Shifted across behind runners but held in one-off position towards rear. Began forward move passing 500m, kept on steadily to be closest at finish.
Pressed forward from good draw to be clear leader on settling. Led field to 200m before running on empty from 100m.
Fractious before start and began only fairly, then crowded for room. Held in one-off position at midfield to straight and kept on fairly.
Pressed forward, grabbing box seat behind leader into first turn. Looked chance top of straight but only one-paced.
Ridden but failed to muster, slipping behind midfield close to rail. Lost position final turn and one-paced straight. (Jockey reported reluctant to stretch out)
Restrained early and taken in to one-off position towards rear. Taken out entering straight but did not respond under hard riding.
Shifted across behind runners from wide draw and travelled well towards rear until 400m when came of bridle and hung in. Did not close off.
Began well, ridden along to hold forward position three-back from leader. Kept on fairly in straight until tiring final 200m.
Outpaced and soon last, trailing field from start to finish. Never competitive.
Settled nicely in midfield, moved to contention passing 500M, quickened well to lead 100M out, kept on well to the finish under determined riding.
Began awkwardly, crossed to the front 1100M, enjoyed an easy lead, kept grinding away when urged inside 250M, headed 100M out but fought on gamely to hold 2nd.
Tracked leader in a slowly run race, kept up the chase final 300M and stayed on well for 3rd in a pleasing Happy Valley debut.
In mid-division 5-6Ls off leader in a slowly run race, peeled off the fence near 400M, closed off steadily, had to shift out for clear running 100M and got up for 4th near line.
Never far off from leader, 4th going into home turn, advanced 3-wide, stayed on same pace over final 200M, hung in under pressure and was difficult to ride.
Tracked leaders along the fence, stayed on inside entering straight, kept on evenly final 300M but always held by leaders.
In touch with leaders along the fence, kept on steadily behind leaders, not much room final stages but would have made little difference to the results.
Travelled 5-6Ls off the pace and had cover behind midfield, niggled along 400M, ran on moderately and only held his ground over final 150M.
Reserved near the rear, well off the pace in early and middle stages, fanned wide into straight, stayed on only fairly and not getting to leaders.
Shifted across behind runners after the start, settled near last 8-9Ls behind leader in a slowly run race, lost his chance when checked 300M.
Taken back from 12, raced in last 9Ls off the pace in a slowly run race, proved difficult to settle middle stages, shaken up near 400M but making no real progress, eased.
Settled towards the rear, not quickened passing 400M, soon left behind by main rivals.

Waited with, commenced move approaching home turn, ran on under pressure to assert authority over 150 metres out.
Settled in midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, did not find much room early in straight, ran on inside final 200 metres to be nearest at finish.
Jumped fairly from the one draw, settled better than midfield within 3L of pace, shifted off rails and obtained a run over 350 metres out, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
From a wide gate, soon taken well back for rails run, angled out for a run entering straight, made up good ground to be nearest at finish.
Began well, amongst leaders early, gradually shifted back to one-out-one-back position in 4th approaching home bend, hit the front momentarily 200 metres out but soon swamped.
Settled wide in rear of midfield, slightly worse rounding home bend, made steady headway early in straight but run not sustained nearing finish.
Broke well from the middle gate, held narrow lead most of way to the 200 metres when found no extra.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, travelled well behind before making headway down the centre of the track after straightening, never nearer.
Jumped well from a poor draw, pressed on to share the pace travelling outside the leader around home bend, kept on before finding no extra inside final 200 metres. (Lame next day)
Jumped fairly, niggled along to gain rails run in 3rd or 4th just 1L off the lead, baulked for a run early in straight, unable to sustain effort inside final 200 metres.
Settled in midfield, gave ground soon after straightening.
3-wide in midfield, found nothing in straight.
Slow to begin, travelled just worse than midfield, made no impression in straight.
Broke well from a poor draw, raced very wide prominently, folded up quickly upon straightening.
Made every post winner after leading on the fence, setting slow fractions. Straightened with a healthy margin and drew clear in the run to the line.
Parked in 2nd position, 1 off no cover. Held on gamely down the running.
Settled towards the rear, 1 off with cover. Took some time to wind up after shifting out approaching the 300m, ran on nicely.
Posted 3 deep without cover for most of the trip, travelling in 3rd position. Finished off gamely.
Enjoyed a nice run in the race, box seating. Finished off one paced.
Crowded at the start, travelling 1 off with cover in midfield. Ran on steadily.
Coursed wide early before racing with cover, 3 deep on the circle, close to midfield. Was dour in the straight.
Had every possible hope after settling 1 out 1 back. Struck interference near the 300m, never recovered.
Travelled behind midfield the fence, had cover. Was a beaten horse at the 400m, after being placed under pressure before the home turn.
Settled last, 1 off with cover, and was inclined to hang in during the early stages. Was never a factor finishing well back.
Raced midfield, 3 deep with cover after being checked near the 800m. . Made no impression in the run home.
Travelled worse than midfield, 3 deep with cover. Failed to close off.
Settled midfield the fence, had cover. Struggled in the home stretch.
Prominent, travelled 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the slow tempo, finished off strongly to score comfortably by 1-3/4Ls.
Rolled forward to park outside the leader, benefited by the slow pace, kept on strongly until final 150M headed by the impressive winner.
Midfield, travelled 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slow tempo, ran on well for 3rd.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1/2L at slow sectionals, kept on steadily until 150M weakened.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, despite benefited by the slow pace, kept on one pace to the line.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, hampered by the slow pace, one paced home.
Midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader, not suited by the slow sectionals, made no impression in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow tempo, never ran on.
Eased back, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow sectionals, kept on one pace to the line.
Taken back from wide drawn, settled 6Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, hung out badly rounding the Home Turn, never looked likely.
Hard ridden forward, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, flattened badly 300M.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Eased to midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, not suited by the slow sectionals, well beaten 300M, tailed out. (Questioned for performance, see incident report)
Ridden along early from wide draw to settle three-back, one-off. Started forward move turning for home, hit front 100m, held off late challenge to win on line.
Began fairly, then crowded out. Forced to steady 900m, settling 4-back from leader. Switched out on straighten and finished strongly down centre track to just fail.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead though kept away from fence. Kicked ahead entering straight, led to 100m when no extra.
Involved in early battle for lead before dropping into box seat. Rolled forward top of straight to look a chance 200m before turning one-paced.
Allowed to stride forward own speed settling 3-back from leader close to rails. Taken out turning for home and made ground gradually to be closest at finish.
Hampered on jumping, dropping to rear but kept away from fence. Three-wide entering straight, taken to centre track and ran on steadily.
Pressed forward to settle fourth but unable to find cover and kept wide thereafter. Kept on well till 200m before running on empty.
Taken in from wide draw but still held three-wide towards the rear. Made some ground early in straight before turning one-paced.
Began OK, ridden along three-back, one-off to straight. Made some ground initially before turning one-paced.
Bumped start, dropping to rear, then crowded for room 700m and taken further out. Found little under pressure.
Began well and involved in early tussle for lead before steadied 900m and dropping back to 5th. Faded under pressure soon after straightening.
Taken cross behind runners from wide draw, dropping to rear and becoming detached turn. Ran past beaten horses in straight.
Hard ridden from inside draw to hold 2nd inside leader to straight. Came under pressure passing 350m and faded. Declared a "roarer."
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling last close to fence. Improved position turn but found nothing in straight.
Reared and lost ground start, taken across behind runners settling in last pair along rails. Came off fence 500m, taken to centre-track and finished strongly to win puling clear.
First out, leading to 1200m when passed on the inside. Kept outside leader around turn though racing keenly. Battled strongly in straight to get 2nd on line.
Pressed forward to lead from 1200m. Set steady pace. Was still in front 150m, swamped.
Ridden along from wide draw and held three-wide, three back from leader. Lay out turn, urged forward and looked chance 200m, no extra close home.
Pressed forward to sit one-back, one-off on settling. Took closer order on straightening and looked chance 200m before turning one-paced.
Outpaced, dropping to near rear along rails. Switched out for clear running 400m and ran on strongly till blocked 75m and restrained. Not properly tested.
Ridden along to maintain forward position, settling in box seat before turn. Urged forward top of straight but flat from 200m.
Began fairly, ridden along before awkward on heels 1000m. Took closer order turn, wide into straight, kept on one-paced.
Jumped OK, ridden along three-back from leader before shuffled back turn. Came off fence 400m and kept on fairly.
Ridden along between horses to hold forward position but got close to heels and unbalanced 800m. Kept on steadily in straight.
Was leaning on stall when gate opened and began awkwardly, settling worse than midfield along rail. Made forward move around turn but only one-paced in straight.
Taking in from wide draw shortly after start but kept away from fence towards rear. Taken wide in straight but only one-paced.
No speed, dropping to last pair but away from fence. Clear last into straight, found nothing.
Pressed forward from wide draw, racing three and four wide without cover in midfield. Kept on early in straight before tiring and dropping back.
Pushed to take rail and shared lead at advantageous slow sectionals, dominated from 400M.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on well for 2nd.
Eased at start, took rail, hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot, 4Ls off the leaders, lack room 400M, bumped 300M, little dash when clear.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, dashed well 300M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in midfield, 3Ls off the leaders, not suited by the slow tempo, lack room 400M, bumped 300M, little dash 200M.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leaders 2 wide, favoured by the slow tempo, emptied 200M.
Eased to rear, 6.5Ls off the leaders on the rails, harmed by the slow pace, held up whole straight, never tested.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leaders on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, blocked most straight, no dash when clear.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the slow pace, blocked whole straight, never tested.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow tempo, dashed fairly.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, weakened 250M.
Pushed early, trapped 3-4 wide throughout just off the leaders, out of fuel 250M.
Pushed forward, trapped 4 wide first bend, share lead 2 wide at slow sectionals, soon reduced 400M, bumped and unbalanced badly.
Bumped start, pressed forward three and four wide without cover to and around turn. Taken to centre-track 400m and stormed home for smart win.
Ridden along three wide in midfield. Crowded for room turn, blocked for run, taken wide entering straight and finished strongly.
Began OK, ridden along behind midfield in one-off position. Taken out turning for home and ran on steadily to be closest at finish.
No early pace, settling at rear along rail, Popped off fence 400m but unable get run until 250m. Finished strongly.
Crowded out start, ridden to hold forward position three-back from leader. Badly held up for run in straight but finished off nicely when clear 200m.
Began well, racing inside leader before getting box seat around turn. Came off fence 400m, bumped and unbalance 350m, boxed on gamely.
Outpaced, dropping to clear last. Taken wide top of straight and ran on steadily.
Pressed forward to lead on settling and then allowed to set own pace. Collared 200m out and faded gradually.
Outpaced, racing at rear but away from fence. Taken wide on straightening but found little under hard riding.
No speed, dropping to rear along rails. Stayed on rails around turn and in straight, but only one-paced.
Hard ridden to sit outside leader to turn. Rolled forward top of straight before turning one-paced from 200m.
Not much pace, racing between horses towards the rear. No clear run over the final 300m and not properly tested.
Bumped start, pressed forward from wide draw to sit two-back, one-off till entering straight. Gave ground gradually from 200m. (Inquiry into restricted action in stable before race)
Began well, sitting two back from leader on settling. Unbalanced when attempting inside run 350m, checked 250m when attempting to get run, checked again 150m and 100m.
Restrained to race in midfield 4-5Ls off the pace, cruised into contention inside 400M, powered to the front 200M out under minimal urging, drew away and won with authority.
In touch, had a smooth trip along the rails, no match for winner's acceleration passing 350M, shifted out inside 200M and stayed on to go 2nd 50M out under a 5lb penalty.
Settled in midfield along the fence, kept to the inside turning home, lay in early straight, momentarily held up 250M, ran on well to go 3rd near 50M but no chance with runaway winner.
In 2nd place 2Ls behind leader, quickened to lead 300M out, brushed aside by ABLE FRIEND inside 200M, faded late stages and lost 2 placing near 50M.
Held up towards the rear, still 5Ls to make up 400M, ran on steadily for a non-threatening 5th.
Reserved in a rearward position 5-6Ls off the pace, driven 450M, stayed on mildly and never a threat to leaders.
Emerged to lead from 1200M, had uncontested lead, kept on same pace under pressure, headed 300M out, weakened towards finish.
Never far off from the pace, under pressure passing 500M, soon outpaced by leaders early straight, weakened out of contention.
Settled at the rear 8Ls off the pace, pushed wide 500M, found nothing when asked and soon beaten.
Held up at the rear, proved difficult to settle from 1300M, shifted out from rails 500M, never going the pace to challenge, eased 200M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance)
Jumped with field, settling midfield in a one-off position. Improved position around turn despite racing wide, picked up momentum from 300m to win in bob of the heads.
Taken forward from start, settling two back from leader. Made forward move from 450m, hit front 250m, run down close to line.
Not pushed, settling midfield close to rail. Took closer order around turn, looked a chance 200m, kept on well to line.
Ridden along early to hold rail, three-back from leader. Took closer order around turn, loomed as a possibility 200m, kept on well.
Well back early. Began forward move 600m, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to be closest at the finish.
Ridden along early to sit outside leader before taking box seat around turn. Rolled forward top of straight to lead momentarily before swamped final stages.
Outpaced, settling at rear close to rail. Taken wide entering straight and ran on steadily without looking dangerous.
Began well, but proved difficult to settle, racing three-back one off. Put under pressure on straightening and battled well till closing stages.
Fractious in gates, began awkwardly, losing ground. Stayed on rail around turn but found little under pressure in the straight.
Pressed forward to lead on settling, pulling clear back stretch and final turn. Tried to kick 400m, collared 250m, faded.
Began fairly, raced between horses worse than midfield, started forward move turning for home but effort was short lived. Faded.
Taken across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. Never likely. (Lame left front fetlock).
Slowly away, recovered to race 3-4 lengths back on rail in midfield, 2 wide turning, finished off very strongly to score narrowly.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in early, sent forward to take the lead near 1100M, travelled well on turn, kicked clear in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late, just missed.
Fast into stride, raced 2 wide in front of midfield, travelled well on turn, closed off evenly in straight without threatening to get 3rd.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 2 wide at rear, 6 lengths back, 3 wide with cover turning, no daylight early in straight, closed off well when clear to make frame.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 5 lengths back, similar position turning, angled out in straight and made some headway, just missed frame.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 4 lengths back, under pressure turning in, finished off evenly in straight without threatening. (Blood in the horse's trachea.)
Average to begin, raced 3 wide with cover, 5 lengths back behind midfield, similar position turning, took widest in straight and closed off evenly.

Moderately away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide with no cover throughout, 4 wide turning, made some headway early in straight, emptied 200M and dropped off gradually thereafter.
Crowded out start, positioned 2 lengths or so back on rail, saved ground to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, sent forward to race prominently in 3rd, 3 wide no cover on turn, weakened gradually after turning in.
Jumped with them, raced 8 lengths back at rear, well-back on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, raced at tail throughout, still well back on turn, made minor progress after turning in, steadied near 150M, eased thereafter.
Crowded out start, sent forward to race in 2nd on rail, outside the leader on turn, emptied early in straight and dropped off gradually.
Slow to begin, raced on rail, 5-6 lengths back at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept on evenly before steadied near 150M, finished last.
Crowded out start, raced 1 out 1 back, same position on turn, bumped near 300M, closed off well and found extra to overhaul rival late stages.

Crowded out start, raced 2-3 lengths back in midfield, there to turn, no daylight early in straight and bumped near 300M, closed off well and looked a strong chance 150M, was outbattled closing stages.
Began well, raced 2 wide at rear in 10th, same position turning, no clear running until 200M, made late headway to get 3rd.
Jumped with them, raced 4 lengths back at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, no daylight at any stage in the straight, finished full of running.
Began well from the widest draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide with no cover, improved on turn, took the lead early in straight, headed and weakened final 100M. (See racing incident)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 6 lengths back at rear, 3 wide turning, made reasonable headway in straight but never looked lively.
Away with them, raced 7 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, kept to inside in straight and got traffic, made some headway when clear final 100M.
Moderately away, raced 3 wide in 5th, got cover on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.
Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back to race 4-5 lengths back at rear, similar position turning, made only minor progress in straight.
Began well, sent forward to race outside leader in 2nd, shared lead on turn, headed near 300M and weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide in midfield, 2 lengths or so back, same position turning, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped with them, positioned a length back on rail, easy run to turn, no daylight in straight until near 100M, not ridden out thereafter.
Average to begin, showed early speed to take the lead, travelled well throughout, headed after turning in, emptied near 200M and eased thereafter.
Slightly slow out from a wide draw, difficult to settle near 900M, raced 3 wide with cover until 600M, made no progress after turning in, never a factor. (See racing incident)

Settled 2 back in 5th on rails, made steady headway after straightening before switched out for a clear run over 150 metres out, sustained effort to just get up on line.

Always well there racing 2-wide, came to challenge under pressure entering straight, gained upper hand inside final 200 metres but hanging and a difficult ride and caught by the eventual winner final stride.
Settled in 4th one-out-one-back, fought on steadily to be nearest at finish.
Soon took up running setting a steady pace, narrowly worn down under pressure inside 200 metres.
Settled behind midfield to straight, finished off race well.
Jumped well, settled one back on rails, failed to quicken after straightening.
Jumped okay but failed to muster and had to settle in rear of midfield on rails, remained similar turning for home, ran home one-paced.
Slowly away, settled behind, ran past well-beaten horses under pressure in straight.
Settled in midfield, faded in straight.
Never seen with a chance.
Always well behind, made no impression in the run home.
Travelled 3-wide behind midfield to straight, soon weakened.
Ridden to take the lead. Held advantage turning in and stayed on well to the line.
Raced outside the leader most of the way. 1/2L off turning in, kept on well but unable to find extra to catch winner.
Slow out. Settled on the fence at midfield. 2Ls off the lead turning for home. Ran on well for a minor placing.
Managed to get to 2-wide midfield from widest draw. Kept on fairly in the straight.
Jumped fairly and hard ridden to race along the rails behind the leader. Stayed on one pace in the straight.
Settled in rear section and raced greenly. Made up some ground in the straight despite hanging in.
Jumped well and had the lead briefly. 3-wide behind leaders turning for home and kept same pace thereafter.
Settled in rear section and last to turn for home, ran on without threatening.
2-wide behind midfield. Ran on same pace in the straight.
2-wide better than midfield. 2 to 3Ls off the lead turning in but found nothing in the straight.
Ridden along early to keep pace behind midfield. Hugged the rails turning for home but found nothing thereafter.
Soon at the rear and trailed field till 500M. Widest turning for home and never picked up in the straight.
Eased back, settled 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, finished off strongly to score by 1/2L.
Rolled forward to take the lead along the fence at fast tempo, hung on well until final 30M headed by the winner.
Ridden forward to settle 1L behind outside the leader, despite harmed by the fast pace, kept on nicely for 3rd.
Eased to settle in front of midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the fast sectionals, ran on steadily for 4th.
Prominent, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, stayed on until final 150M weakened.
Camped handy, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the fast pace, weakened soon after straightening.
Midfield, settled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the fast pace, never ran on.
At rear, travelled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the fast sectionals, made no impression in straight.
Showed no early pace, travelled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast tempo, never ran on.
At rear throughout, never a factor. (Heart Irregularity, retired)
Pushed to occupy the box seat, raced greenly throughout, eased down soon after straightening. ( Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
Outpaced early, settling in last pair. Began forward move 800m, looped field to sit 3rd but wide 500m, came again in the straight to win close come.
Began awkwardly, recovered, ridden to hold box seat first turn. Stayed on rail turning for home, got inside run, hit front momentarily before run down.
Pressed forward from wide draw before getting cover passing 1400m. Improved position turn, wide into straight, ran on strongly.
Taken straight to rail on settling, 3-back from leader. No clear run top of straight, taken in 300m, switched in 250m to find run but checked. Kept on.
Began well, rolled forward alongside leader to first turn before easing one-back, one-off. Looked chance entering straight before checked heels 300m. No extra.
Fractious before start, removed from gate, then replaced. Rolled forward to lead on settling, setting steady quarters. Was still in front 150m before swamped.
Outpaced, soon at rear along fence. Hampered 1400m, still well back turning for home, made some ground in straight.
Began well, rolled forward sitting one-back, one-off. Kept on steadily until tiring final 200m.
No pace, settling four-back, one-off. Raced tight around turn, losing position. One-paced in straight.
Outpaced and soon clear last. Tagged onto field top of straight and ran past tired horses.
Ridden along to maintain forward position and held wide without cover for most of the trip. Gave ground soon after entering straight.
Began fairly before clipping heels and blundering 1600m, dropping to near rear. Never a factor.
Began well, settling three-back the rails. Took closer order around turn, got clear run 300m and bolted through for easy win.
Allowed to stride forward at own pace settling 3-back one-off at turn. Improved position around turn, ran on steadily in straight without threatening winner.
Ridden long between horses in midfield. Popped off fence 400m to make run, loomed 200m, no extra close home.
Began OK, held on rail behind midfield, saved ground turn, got inside run in straight making ground to 200m before one-paced.
Began best, lead for a few strides before being eased into box seat. Improved position around turn to look a chance 350m. Awkwardly placed and not tested final stages.
Crowded out start, shifted across behind runners from wide draw, settling last. Caught up to field 400m, taken wide and ran on steadily.
Steadied from heels soon after start and then shifted in behind horses from wide draw, settling towards rear. One-paced in straight.
Crowded out start, dropping to near last close to rail. Made forward move approaching home straight but soon tired.
Pressed forward from wide draw to lead before being eye-balled and passed by another 1200m Retook lead but tired soon after straightening.
Ridden along early to hold forward position but held wide without cover. Lost position around turn and weekend further in straight.
Pressed forward to sit one-back, one-off to turn. Looked chance top of straight before fading.
Began well, racing outside leader initially before taken over 1200m. Raced fiercely and refused to settle after 1000m, giving ground quickly in straight.
Hard ridden to maintain the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, closed off strongly to score.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the slow tempo 2 wide, dashed well 300M, run ended 100M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 200M for 3rd.
Eased at start, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, dashed strongly 300M despite not suited by the slow pace, however badly held up 100M.
Eased back, took rail, 6Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well but without threats.
Pushed to sit midfield, checked first bend, 4Ls off the leader on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, held up 4-2, little dash.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow tempo, out of fuel 200M.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leaders 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, just held ground in straight.
Pushed to take the rail and led by 1.5Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, soon reduced 250M.
At back, 6Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Pressed forward from inside draw to lead on settling. Set quick quarters to straight, kicked clear 350m, never challenged.
Began well, holding box seat. Scraped paint around turn, kept on steadily in straight but unable close gap to winner.
Ridden among to hold forward position two-back, one-off. Taken a little wide in straight but boxed on gamely to just miss the quinella.
Ridden along from wide draw and raced three and four wide around turn. Widest into straight but kept on gamely to be closest at the finish.
Jumped best before settling one-back, one-off behind leader to straight. Made forward move 350m but effort was short lived. One-paced.
Slow into stride, taken to fence and quickly made up ground to settle 4-back from leader. Stayed on fence around turn and kept on fairly in straight.
Bumped start, ridden along to hold rail 3-back from leader. Not much room in straight and held for clear running final stages. Not properly tested.
Shifted across early, racing between horses towards the rear. Not much room top of straight but only one-paced when clear.
Began only fairly and then severely checked, dropping to clear last. Crowded 550 when attempting to improve. One-paced.
Got off well but crowed out 950m and then difficult to settle in midfield. Hung out final stages when giving ground.
Ridden along early to hold midfield position but kept wide without cover. Lost position around turn and never likely.
Eased back to the rear after the start, travelled 5Ls off the pace in middle stages, picked up strongly inside 250M, driven to lead 80M from home, lengthened away.
Settled towards the rear but never far off from leaders in a compact field, switched back to inner for clear run in straight, ran on well to go 2nd close home without matching winner.
Settled 2-wide in the group chasing leaders, had every chance on straightening, briefly went 2nd nearing 50M, not pace of first 2 final stages.
In touch behind leaders, 3-wide for much of the way, moved up to challenge nearing 400M, quickened to the front 150M but turned one pace final stages.
Held up 3-wide behind mid-division, driven along near 400M, stayed on mildly for non-threatening 5th.
Strode forward from wide barrier, shared lead on outside, emerged as sole leader 600M, led to 150M, no extra towards finish.
Settled midfield 3Ls behind leaders, held up rounding the home turn and early straight, stayed on only fairly when clear, not reached leaders.
Tracked leaders along the rails, had to switch out when hampered by weakening rival near 400M, shifted back to inside rails for clear run passing 250M but failed to close off.
Taken across behind runners. Settled in last pair 5Ls off the pace, still in last 300M, hampered 150M, made some progress late but never going the pace to seriously challenge.
Unable to slot in, caught 3-wide no cover just off pace, strode to race outside leaders 600M, lacked further response in straight, weakened and eased 200M.
Bounded in the air and lost ground at the start, settled behind midfield 3-4Ls off the pace in a compact field, unable to quicken with leaders 400M, soon left behind.
Shared the lead along the fence, set good pace middle stages but came under serious pressure home turn, dropped out rapidly 400M.

Began well from a poor draw, niggled at before settling in 5th within 3L of pace, commenced move turning in, responded well to assert authority over 200 metres out.
Travelled keenly just worse than midfield, similar turning in, obtained clear run passing the 300 metres, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Travelled wide down far side after beginning from a wide gate, improving from midfield early to join the leader rounding home bend, kept on one pace in the run home.
Soon in last few, saved ground turning in, ran on without threatening.
Jumped moderately, settled in midfield, switched wide for a run entering straight, ran home at the one pace.
Soon taken back from the widest gate, remained well behind to straight, ran on. (Tactic questioned.)
Jumped fairly, towards rear early in far side, gained midfield along rails rounding home bend, did not find much rom early in straight, kept on.
Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace on rails, badly baulked for a run upon straightening, kept on before fading inside final 200 metres.
Jumped fairly, taken back towards the rear off the rails, ran home one-paced.
Midfield, wide into straight, ran home one-paced.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, recovered steadily to midfield on rails, saved ground turning in, faded gradually.
Well there to 200 metres, faded.
Given reminders early, soon led, headed when weakened over 250 metres out.
Jumped fairly, soon dropped well behind.
Box-seated behind the leader. Switched out turning in and responded well when asked. Kicked away for an easy win.
Settle 2-wide at midfield. Ran on well in the straight but never a threat to winner.
Taken back early and raced 3-wide behind midfield. Widest turning in and closed off well for a minor placing.
Raced outside the lead till home straight. Found enough to make the frame.
Dropped back from wide draw to be closer to rail. Ran on well and made up some ground in the straight.
Settled on fence behind midfield. Ran on fairly but never a threat.
Slowly away and was hard ridden to make up ground. Settled on the rails and 2Ls off the lead. Stayed same pace in the straight.
Ridden hard early to race behind the pace. A length off the lead turning for home. Unable to quicken and stayed same pace.
3-wide better than midfield. Ran on same pace in the straight.
Raced wide at midfield. Ran on without threatening.
2-wide better than midfield. Pressured rounding home turn but unable to quicken in the straight.
Settled at rear. Near last turning in and ran on fairly. Struck traffic 200M and only one-paced thereafter.
Led until home straight but tired final 400M and dropped out.
Raced in rear section. Trailed field into home straight and made no impression thereafter.
Camped handy, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, suited by the slightly slow sectionals, ran on well to score by a neck.
Sent forward to take the fence and led by 1L at slightly slow tempo, kept on strongly until final 50M headed by the winner.
Eased to settle midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, despite harmed by the slightly slow tempo, closed to the line strongly.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, despite benefited by the slightly slow sectionals, one paced home.
Midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slightly slow tempo, ran on steadily.
Taken back to rear from the outside gate, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow pace, made some ground late.
Rolled forward to settle 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide without cover, despite benefited by the slightly slow sectionals, failed to make any impression when asked.
Settled worse than midfield 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the slightly slow tempo, ran on only fairly.
Settled worse than midfield 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slightly slow tempo, kept on one paced to the line.
Midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, soon weakened after straightening. (Questioned trainer for riding, see incident report)
Prominent, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite suited by the slightly slow pace, faded 300M.
Never a factor.
Bumped at the start. Hung out 900m after being checked. Balanced, then travelled midfield closer to stands' side. Ridden 450m & ran on to win going away.
Jumped well. Travelled. Under pump at 450m. No room at 300m. Kept up a good gallop under riding when in clear.
Beaten for speed. Travelled midfield, switched to the grandstand rail at 130m. Closed off well. Good ride.
Jumped cleanly. Led at 600m. Challenged by runner-up at 400m. Battled on well.
Not a clean jump. Shared lead at 550m. Kept battling under the whip.
Ridden to be in touch with the leaders after getting a bump at the start. Under riding throughout and never a factor.
Jumped well but checked. Ridden out stands' side well back, no room 450m and changed course, held up at 170m and switched again. Not ridden out. Unlucky runner.
Slow start. Well back at 500m on stands' side & ridden along. Difficult ride at 420m after being checked, switched to the wrong part of the track at 220m. Made minor ground.
Jumped well. Travelled mid track. Had enough at 300m.
Bit slow. Took cover on the mid part, went far out at 350m after laying in. Found nothing under the whip.
Poor start. Travelled on the worst part of the track. Never a factor.
Shifted out at the start. Tracked the leaders in mid part of track. No room at 250m. Weakened.
Jumped well. Travelled strongly stands' side, unbalanced and shifted out 500m. Found nil.
Jumped cleanly. Ridden to share lead 700m. Kept up a strong gallop to win after being headed by the runner-up at the 130m.
Jumped well. Followed the winner, came off the fence at 330m, challenged the winner at 130m. Game in defeat.
Jumped well. 3-wide without cover midfield at 700m, hung in after turning for home. Ran on well.
Jumped well. Sat fairly handy, drifted to midfield after losing ground at 800m. Wide on turn and came up short.
Jumped and sat deep early. Took hold to sit handy one-off the fence. One-paced under the whip.
Jumped well. Drifted back 950m, under pressure before the home turn and kept grinding away out wide.
Jumped cleanly. Travelled fairly handy on the rails. Kept grinding away under riding.
Crowded at start. Improved to sit 4 back on fence 850m. Came off rail on home turn. Switched inside for clear running at 300m & made a bit of ground. Improved effort.
Jumped well. Lost ground after being hampered at 900m & was erratic. No room at 200m & no extra.
Restrained after the start. A difficult ride before the home turn. Went out wide & never a factor. Blood in trachea after race.
Jumped & under riding out wide to share lead with winner. No extra final 300m after tough run.
Slow start. Under drive at rear, glued to the rail. Gone before home turn.
Settled in front of midfield, 3Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, closed off strongly 300M to score.
Behind midfield, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 250M for 2nd.
Hard ridden forward to cross, 2Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast sectionals, ran on strongly for 3rd.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast tempo, made steady ground 350M.
Hard ridden to hold the rail in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the fast pace, lack room 400M, made ground when clear but without threats.
Pushed forward, box seat, not suited by the fast pace, ran on until 100M flattened.
8Ls off the leader along the fence, checked 850M, benefited by the fast tempo, progressed steadily 300M.
Hard ridden forward, 3Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3 wide, just held ground in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 9Ls off the leader, checked 850M, favoured by the fast tempo, made ground 200M.
Pushed early but not muster, 6.5Ls off the leader along the fence, checked 850M, benefited by the fast pace, made steady ground 200M.
Midfield, 5Ls off the leader on the fence, favoured by the fast tempo, no progress.
Took rail easily and led by 0.5L at fast sectionals, hung on until 250M out of fuel.
Bumped start, pushed forward, sat outside the lead, not suited by the fast tempo, emptied 300M.
Bumped start, hard ridden but not muster, 7Ls off the leader 3 wide, suited by the fast pace, but never progressed.
Slow out as usual. Always well back, travelled well throughout, widest on turn, ran on strongly hands & heels.
Jumped well. Shared lead, headed by 3rd place getter at the 120m before battling on well under riding. Winner too strong.
Jumped well, restrained & fired up a bit, midfield at the 1200m, no room on the home turn, raced to the lead at the 120m but one-paced close to the line. Winner too good.
Restrained after jumping. Travelled at the back, turn out wide and closed off well.
Jumped well. Led at the 1200m, challenged by runner-up on home turn & kept battling away.
Bit slow. Improved to sit 5 back on the fence 950m, travelled well. One-paced.
Jumped well. 3-wide throughout outside eventual 3rd. No room at the 1200m. Never a factor & one-paced.
Broke well, taken back & glued to rail. Came off the fence on the home turn and had every chance.
Jumped well. Fired up at the 1200m, then settled, followed the runner-up. No extra final 260m.
Caught 3-wide no cover early stages, strode forward to be one out one back, travelled strongly into straight, driven to lead inside 200M, continued on willingly to line.
Settled 2-wide ahead of mid-division and never far off the pace, driven to chase leaders from 400M, did best work final 200M, got up for 2nd just in time.
Sent forward, emerged as sole leader 1200M, soon pressed by eventual winner turning in, headed inside 200M but rallied on along the fence, lost 2nd close home.
Dropped back and guided to the fence soon after the jump, travelled behind midfield 6Ls off the pace, kept to inside in straight, made steady progress without getting to top 3.
Along the 2-path about 5Ls off leader, soon into clear on straightening, briefly threatened with a strong looking challenge but turned one pace passing 150M.
Ridden more forward than usual, travelled well behind leader, kept up the chase early straight and held 3rd position until 200M, faded towards the finish.
Position 3Ls off the pace and ahead of mid-division, stayed on mildly not reaching leaders.
Settled behind midfield along the 2-path, 4Ls off leader at 400M, ran on evenly but not making progress on leaders.
Dropped back to a rearward position 6-7Ls off the pace, shifted out into clear nearing 400M, stayed on fairly and never reached contention.
Taken back to last 8-9Ls off the pace in early stages, saved ground along the fence, closed off the race fairly inside 400M and lacked the necessary response.
Raced a shade keen in midfield, 3-wide no cover from 1100M, kept on same pace on straightening, never threatened.
Slow to begin, held up in midfield along the fence, not pace to challenge leaders, weakened 200M.
Restrained after the start, settled near the rear 8-9Ls off the pace, switched out 500M to challenge but soon outpaced, never involved.
Checked on jumping, attempted to slot in for cover but unable to do so, caught wide at the back, came under pressure 600M out, first to be beaten.
Jumped cleanly. Sat fairly handy 1 off the fence, challenged leaders at 250m, headed by runner-up at 130m & prevailed under riding on the line.
Jumped fairly. Not rushed. 3-wide without cover, improved to sit midfield at 950m, challenged winner at 130m hands & heels. Game in defeat. Lost hind plate mid-race.
Jumped well & handed up to sit fairly handy 4th on fence. Ran on under hard riding.
Jumped OK. Followed runner up 3-wide with cover, kept on one pace.
Jumped fairly. Sat 8 behind the leader 2 off the fence, hampered at 900m, shifted out 220m, closed off well under the whip.
Jumped well from wide gate. Led at 1200m, travelled, beaten at 350m.
Jumped well. Restrained to take box seat, travelled loose rein, no room 230m and shifted for clear running, battled on one pace.
Jumped cleanly. Ran up out wide from poor gate to sit outside the leader, challenged the leader at 350m, nothing at the finish.
Jumped fairly and restrained to sit 2nd-last, improved position, hampered at 500m. Closed off OK.
Jumped well, restrained to sit last. Shifted slightly inside at 400m. Battled on.
Ridden after jump. Sat one-off the fence in midfield. Niggled. Driven turning in. No extra & eased final 100m.
Jumped with the field. Sat 5 back the fence, followed 3rd place-getter, shifted back to rails at 300m. One-paced at finish.
Poor start & ridden. Checked at 930m and drifted well back. Ordinary.
Jumped well. Not rushed, hampered at 900m and drifted to 6 back on the fence. Nothing under the whip.
Moderately away, positioned 1 out 1 back, similar position turning, finished off strongly in straight to score easily.
Fast into stride, raced in 2nd throughout, 2 wide on turn, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner final 100M.
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, shared lead on turn, headed after 200M but still kept on well for 3rd.
Jumped well, positioned nicely in 3rd, easy run throughout, finished off evenly in straight.
Fairly away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5-6 lengths back, same position turning, finished off well in straight to be nearest on line.
Began awkwardly, raced 2 wide, 4 lengths back in midfield, there to turn, closed off evenly in straight without threatening.
Crowded out start, recovered to race 3 lengths back in 5th, saved ground on turn, finished off evenly in straight. (Jockey dropped his whip at the 150M)
Jumped well from a tricky gate, taken back to race 2 wide at rear, 5-6 lengths back, similar position on turn, shifted in from heels near 200M, closed off evenly in straight. (See racing incidents)
Crowded out start, raced 5 lengths or so back on rail behind midfield, saved ground throughout, finished off evenly in straight.
Began well, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, same position on turn, made minor headway in straight.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7 lengths back on rail at rear, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept to inside in straight, finished off one-paced.
Moderately away from the widest gate, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover, 7 lengths back at rear, found cover on turn, failed to close off in straight. (See racing incidents)
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 9-10 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Average to begin, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide without cover in midfield, still no cover on turn, emptied early in straight when hard run took effect.

Began from the widest gate, with leaders early gradually shifting across towards the rails, took rails run in front at the Rock, just held on to the line.
Jumped fairly, dropped steadily back to worse than midfield, saved ground on inside turning in, ran on to just fail to get up on line.
Began moderately, settled better than midfield in 5th within 3L of the pace, ran on under pressure down the centre of the straight to miss narrowly.
Broke well from a tricky gate, soon taken back to race 3 wide in rear of midfield, hampered 200 metres out, ran on to be nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately, niggled at early before settling in midfield on rails, kept on one pace in the run home.
From a middle draw, settled 3-wide in a prominent position, improved to 2-wide in 2nd spot rounding home bend, found nothing under pressure after straightening.
Settled towards the rear after beginning from gate 11 travelling wide most of way, ran home one-paced.
Jumped fairly, niggled along to hold prominent position on rails, remained one back in 3rd on rails into straight, soon faded under pressure.
Well there early, ceded advantage going up the Rock, came under pressure approaching home turn, found nothing.
Reared and lost ground at start, remained well behind throughout, never nearer.
Jumped moderately, soon dropped to the rear, never a danger.
Jumped with others but failed to muster early dropping to last few, made no impression thereafter.
Ridden and had early lead. Settled nicely behind the pace 1200M. Switched out turning for home and responded nicely. Took the lead inside 200M and held off a late charging rival.
Taken back from wide draw. Trailed field until home straight. Charged through others strongly and just failed to catch winner.
Jumped awkward and raced in rear section. Switched wide and was near last turning in. Ran on strongly for a minor placing.
Caught 3-wide without cover. Midfield back straight and advanced to the lead 500M. Took advantage into home straight but was headed 150M. Found just enough to make the frame.
Hard ridden early to be closer to pace. No worse than midfield backstraight. Hugged rails and 2 to 3Ls off the lead home turn. Ran on steadily in the straight.
Caught wide into 1st turn and then settled 2-wide behind the pace. Unable to find extra gear after straightening.
Settled 2-wide at midfield. Switched out 3-wide to improve 700M out without making much ground. Ran on same pace in the straight.
Ridden early but showed no speed. Settled towards the rear. Swung wide and last into straight. Made up some late ground.
2-wide behind midfield. Ridden along home turn and kept on only fairly in the straight. No clear run final stages.
Settled 2-wide and no more than 3Ls off the lead. Ridden along to keep pace 600M out and stayed on fairly. Checked 200M out and faded thereafter.
Pushed along from wide draw and took the lead 1200M out. Headed 600M and struggled to keep up. Weakened on straightening.
On the fence and no better than midfield. Kept on after straightening but raced ended after being striking interference at 200M.
Settled worse than midfield about 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, switched wide turning in, closed off strongly to score by 1/2 L.
Prominent, settled 1L off the leader 2-3 wide without cover, finished off well for 2nd.
Pushed to midfield, travelled 2Ls behind the leader on the fence, stayed inside, ran on steadily for 3rd.
Sent forward to take a seat behind the leader along the fence, kept on one pace to the line without threatening.
Slow to muster despite ridden along, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground late.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, soon weakened after straightening.
Slow to muster despite niggled along, never looked likely.
Began well, parked 5th behind speed in one-off position. Improved 600m, 5-wide into straight, rolled forward to lead 150m, held off late challenge.
Crowded out start, urged ahead settling midfield away from fence. Peeled out turning for home and finish off strongly to just miss.
Hard ridden from wide draw but failed to muster and shifted in from 1100m to find cover at rear but still wide. Under pressure from 400m, picked up from 200m and finished off strongly.
Shifted across behind runners from outside draw, settling last. Picked up momentum entering straight, shifted out 200m for clear running, finished off nicely.
Ridden to maintain forward position settling one-off, one-back. Rolled forward entering straight, looked chance 200m, no extra close home.
Bumped start, ridden along 3-back from leader along rail. Tightened around turn, kept on steadily in straight but raced greenly from 100m.
Ridden along to hold box seat. Caught flat-footed top of straight when leader kicked. Ran on steadily to 200m before turning one-paced.
Bumped unbalanced start, pressed forward to lead passing 650m. Collared soon after straightening and weakened steadily.
Bumped start, not much speed settling at rear along fence. Still well back turning for home and ran past tired horses in straight.
Hard ridden from wide draw to lead on settling, crossing to fence 900m. Passed 650m, retook lead 200, but soon under pressure and weakened badly.
No speed, soon at rear, losing contact with field before the turn. Never likely. (Unacceptable performance)
Erratic start. Ridden hard. Sat 4 back off the leader on the fence, drifted to 2nd last at 730m, mid track on home turn. Ridden out to win well.
Jumped & restrained to sit handy. Followed the leader, one-paced at 150m, responded under drive to finish close 2nd.
Jumped well. Led at 950m, kept up a good gallop but weak in the finish.
Restrained after jump. Sat 4 off leader at 850m, stayed glued to the fence. Ran on nicely along the rails.
Jumped and ridden to share the lead early, headed to sit handy at 940m 3-wide, bumped at 850m. Kept grinding away.
Jumped cleanly. Sat midfield 1 off the fence, wide home turn & plugged on. Still green.
Restrained after jumping from wide gate. Last at 900m, held up in run at 210m and kept on in an improved effort.
Jumped cleanly & 2nd last early stages, held up 490m, checked 250m & shifted back to inside. Ran on but not a factor.
Jumped well and bumped soon after. Shared lead early stages, restrained to box seat at 850m after getting a bump. Bit keen before home turn & plugged on.
Not rushed at the start. Bit keen early, on heels at 700m, 4-wide before the final turn, nothing under the whip in closing stages.
Jumped to race 5-wide early, niggled home turn & under the whip. No finish.
Handy but 6-wide early, covered ground 3-wide throughout and weakened right out.
Hard ridden to take a midfield spot, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, made early move 800M to take advantages from the slow tempo, ran on strongly to score by a neck.
Pressed forward, 1L off the leader, trapped 3 wide throughout but favoured by the slow tempo, closed off strongly 300M, just beaten by narrow margin in 2nd.
Settled in box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, just held ground for 3rd.
Pushed early but not muster, 3.5Ls off the leader along the fence, harmed by the slow tempo, blocked 300M, dashed well when clear.
Hard ridden forward, sat 2 wide, shuffled back to 3.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, little dash in straight.
Eased at start, took rail at rear, 7.5Ls off the leader, dashed well 200M despite not suited by the slow pace.
Eased back, 5.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, held up 4-2, dashed well when clear.
Slow away, at rear, 7Ls off the leader along the fence, not suited by the slow pace, no dash.
Slow away, 5.5Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, bumped 300M, lack turn of foot.
Hard ridden forward, took rail, led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, soon emptied 250M.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, sat just off the lead 2 wide, suited by the slow tempo, however reduced quickly 350M.
Raced 2nd last. Followed the runner-up, took off wide at 950m, shared lead with runner-up at 680m & fought on to win.
Crowded start. 6 back at 1200m 1 off the fence, took off with the winner at 950m and shared the lead outside the winner at 680m. Fought on gamely.
Not rushed at start. Sat handy at 1700m on the fence, Found himself 6 behind the leader 700m. Closed to heels home turn, shifted inside and plugged on.
Jumped & held up at 1700m, fairly handy 2 off the fence, checked and became awkward after shifting out. Lay in after turning for home & ran on under whip.
Last from outside gate, took off with winner & runner-up at 950m, sat 3-wide behind the lead 600m. Kept on one-paced.
Jumped well. Sat 4 behind lead on fence. Steadied 1900m and 900m. Second last at 800m and ridden out, shifted inside at 200m. One-paced.
Jumped and sat midfield 1 off the fence, followed with the mid-race movers, wide on turn. Battled on evenly.
Jumped to 3-wide without cover, improved position to sit behind the leader without cover 1440m, found cover 650m, shifted inside at 250m but found nothing.
Jumped and ridden to lead at 1700m. Handy on fence 700m, tight for room at 600m. Weakened out.
Jumped well. Handy 2 wide no cover, travelled but found little when needed.
Jumped to lead. Headed 1700m, travelled but found nothing. Tired in run.
Sat 6 behind the leader at 1650m on rail, last at 800m, driven but not a factor.
Settled in mid-division 4-5Ls off the pace, saved ground on the inside, ran on steadily under mainly hands and heels riding, led close home.
Soon led, pressed by rival 700M, kicked 1.5L clear 200M from home, caught by winner final stages.
Checked at the start, 6Ls off the pace in middle stages, had to swerve his way through, closed off fastest, nearest finish.
Settled ahead of midfield in 6th, fanned widest into straight, stayed on moderately for 4th.
Urged forward, chased leaders, advanced to 2nd 250M, faded final 100M and beaten to 5th.
Began only fairly, moved closer to leaders nearing home turn, switched away from fence 600M, stayed on mildly and not getting to leaders.
Eased back from wide barrier and soon taken across to the rails, well off the pace early stages, still plenty to do 400M, ran on well down outside.
Ahead of midfield early stages, rolled forward to track leaders nearing home turn, kept on same pace in straight, faded 150M.
Held up in midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, had no clear run early straight, checked 200M and lost every chance.
Taken across behind runners, settled 8Ls towards the rear, came under pressure home turn, never involved.
Nudged along after the start, pressed leader from 800M, soon no extra turning home, faded 250M.
Switched off to last over 10Ls behind leaders, didn't respond to urging 500M out, never factored.
