Jumped nicely from the one gate, led or disputed lead under restrain to straight, gained upper hand over 200 metres out.
Always prominent, one-back on rails into straight, switched out for a run turning in, ran on late without threatening.
Disputed lead far side, renewed effort to tackle for lead upon straightening but unable to sustain run inside final 200 metres.
Sluggish at start settling in midfield on rails, fought on steadily under pressure but without quickening.
Travelled well behind to straight, ran on between runners to be nearest at finish.
Jumped moderately, settled wide behind midfield, produced moderate late impression closing stages.
Jumped fairly settling 2-wide in midfield, kept on steadily under pressure.
Jumped fairly, travelling in last few when badly checked and lost ground on top of home bend, kept on at the one pace in straight.
Never better than midfield, ran home one-paced.
Broke well, with leaders early before settling 3-wide in midfield, similar in midfield turning for home, found no extra in straight.
Ridden along from the widest gate, improved to a prominent position but wide without cover, folded up quickly shortly after straightening.
Always well behind, never seen with a chance.
Jumped awkwardly from widest draw and dropped to rear section. Last few to turn in and staged a strong rally. Swept to the lead 50M and won comfortably.
Contested for the early lead before settling behind the pace. Hard pressed and was 3Ls off turning for home. Kept on strongly but unable to hold off a late charging rival.
Niggled to be in a disputed lead. Behind the speed making the turn. Switched out home turn and regained lead 300M out. Unable to hold off late challengers final stages.
Jumped well wide draw but can't keep pace with early leaders. Gradually slipped to midfield. Wide turning for home and ran on well to make the frame.
Dropped back from wide draw and raced behind midfield. Niggled along rounding the turn. Kept on fairly in the straight.
Niggled along and no worse than midfield. 3 to 4Ls off rounding home turn. Ran on steadily in the straight.
Hard ridden early and raced at midfield. Hugged rails rounding the turn but unable to turn up a notch in the straight.
Towards the rear early and middle stages. Closed the race off fairly.
Outpaced and soon at the back. Some lengths off the main field at the turn. Made up late ground in the straight.
Jumped well and had the early lead. 2-wide behind the pace into turn. Faded gradually in the straight.
Only fair jump but ridden and took lead 800M. A length in front into home straight but gradually dropped out thereafter.
Jumped awkwardly and ridden along. Never better than midfield. Continued to be ridden at the turn. Same pace and race ended after checking 100M out.
Jumped slowly, travelled 4Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast tempo, dashed well to score by 1L.
Eased back, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast pace, ran on strongly to get 2nd but never match with the winner.
Taken back from wide gate, travelled 6.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, benefited by the fast sectionals, ran on well for 3rd.
Rolled to occupy the box seat, despite harmed by the fast pace, kept on nicely to get 4th.
Sent forward to park outside the leader at fast tempo, kept on steadily.
Midfield, travelled 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, despite benefited by the fast sectionals, ran on fairly.
Ridden forward to take the fence and led at fast tempo, hung on until final 150M weakened.
At rear, settled 8Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one pace until final furlong weakened.
Pushed to midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace until 300M weakened.
Raced midfield, settled 4Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, under pressure rounding the Home Turn, never looked likely.
Midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, soon weakened after straightening, tailed out.
Raced midfield, however trapped 4 wide without cover throughout, weakened rounding the Home Turn, tailed out.
Camped handy, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, harmed by the fast tempo, flattened badly 350M, tailed out.
Jumped well. Stalked the pace on the fence, bumped the running rail at 700m. Ridden after home turn. Ran on to win well.
Took a sit 5 off leader on the fence. Shifted out from rails at 1000m. Under the pump before the turn and ran on under ridding out wide.
Poor jump and caught wide early and pushed on at 1130m to lead at 970m. Gave way in closing stages.
Back as usual and out wide with cover after a bump start. Went further wide after a check at 1000m. Kept grinding away to the line.
Jumped well. Handy and took a sit one off the fence. Ridden before the turn and battled on OK.
Jumped well and 3 off leader early, drifted 5 back on fence. Made little ground along the rails.
Last, 9 off leader, wide with cover, ran on out wide without making an impression.
Ridden out early, settled, well back 8 off leader, then ridden out again. Never a factor under the whip.
Slow out. Ridden to sit 6 off leader on the fence. Always under the pump, drifted to last at 480m. Ran on along the rails.
Restrained as usual at the start. Hugged the rails, shifted out at 800m to sit one off fence second last. Made minor ground pass beaten runners when in clear.
Bit keen out wide early on, settled, held up at 1,400m. Kept on one-paced.
Jumped and shared the lead early on, gave up the lead at 880m. Box seated, beaten before the home turn.
Ridden to share the lead early on. Took a sit at 840m one off the fence. Weakened out after home turn.
Caught 4 wide near the speed early on. Struggled before the turn and weakened out.
Jumped and hugged the rails. Last and 8 off the leader at 990m, ridden, shifted out from the fence at 230m. Burst through horses to win on line.
Jumped and crowded at the start. Rear at 1,300m, checked at 500m, came out wide at home turn. Closed off well.
Slow start. Improved along the rails to sit midfield at 750m. Came off fence after turning in, bumped at 50m, Closed off under riding.
Jumped very well. Ridden to share the lead at 1300m along the fence. Took control at the 550m. Kept up a good gallop. Collard late.
Jumped sat handy one off fence, drifted at 810m and 3 wide without cover, improved at 480m. Kept on one paced.
Jumped well. 3 wide with cover at the back. Ran on under the whip.
Jumped and sat behind the leaders along the fence. Had every chance.
4 wide throughout and never in the hunt.
Taken back at the jump, took off at 460m, hung out at home turn. No finish.
Steadied at 1,400m, sat 5 off leader and 2 off the fence, drifted further back at 780m. No finish.
Jumped and sat handy one off the fence, came off the bridle at 780m and never travelled.
Caught 3 wide with cover 5 off the leader, ridden to improve position at 460m. Strong one pace in the stretch.
Shared lead early on, then handed up at 1,000m, gradually gave ground at 790m.
Caught wide early on and surge forward to share the lead at 1000m and gone at 430m.
Pushed to sit in midfield, 3Ls off the leader 3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, dashed well 400M to score by a narrow margin.
At back, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3 wide, dashed strongly 300M for 2nd despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 3Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow pace, lack room 400M, dashed strongly for 3rd.
Hard ridden to obtain the box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, ran on well to the line.
Eased back, 5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow tempo, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 250M whilst hanging out.
At rear, 6.5Ls off the leader along the fence, lack room 4-2, dashed strongly despite not suited by the slow pace.
Pushed forward early but shuffled back to midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, lack room 4-2, little dash when clear.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, lack room 400M, just held ground when clear.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the slow pace, out of fuel 200M.
Pressed forward, took rail, led by 1L at advantageous slow sectionals, ran on until 200M emptied.
At back, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Eased back, harmed by the slow pace, never progressed.
Never competitive at rear.
Eased early but trapped wide, allowed to stride forward 1000M, 2Ls off the slow pace 3 wide, faded 400M.
Not rushed after a bump start. Box seated, travelled, and ran on well to win.
Jumped and wide early on. Restrained to sit 3 wide with cover 2nd last. Turn out wide and closed off well.
Jumped cleanly. Led comfortably. Challenged by the winner at 130m. Run came to an end.
Handy 3-wide throughout, turn widest out and kept grinding away.
Handy 2 off the fence. Travelled, one-paced to the line. Sustained a minor cut to the right front leg.
Sat midfield, 2 off the fence, ridden. Made minor ground under whip. Sustained wounds over the left hind leg.
Jumped poorly and took left turn. Sat last, travelled, held up at 180m. Kept coming.
Poor start. Ridden to improve to sit 5 off leader on fence. held up at 530m. Ran on along the fence. Blinkers not a good idea.
Second last. Drifted further back when held up at 560m. Came out wide on home turn. Never a factor.
Jumped well. Handy on the fence. Ridden. Shifted out on home turn. Never likely under the whip.
Bumped start and ridden to share the lead at 810m and gone after turning in.
Head up on jumping. 5 wide early on, drifted to 3rd last at 620m. Never travelled. Irregular heart rhythm.
Began well, always prominent, tracked leaders going into the bend, taken out 400M and quickened smoothly to lead 200M out, had enough to hold off a late challenge final stages.
Chased leaders in 4th place, tracked the path of eventual winner turning home, ran on well to get within 0.5L of winner.
Gradually moved forward to race outside leader, stayed on for clear 3rd but not matched finishing pace of first 2 final 100M.
Towards rear 8Ls off the pace, plenty to do turning in, stayed on well to go 4th near line but not reached leaders.
In 5th place about 4Ls off the pace, kept on same speed final 400M, never a serious threat to leaders.
Soon led, all out passing 300M, headed nearing 200M, faded towards the finish.
In mid-division, stayed on same pace in straight, never threatened.
Held up 4Ls back in midfield, plodded on final 300M and not making headway on leaders.
Settled 6-7Ls behind leader, still had plenty to make up 400M, never going the pace to challenge.
Towards the rear, found nothing when pressed nearing 400M, soon out of contention.
Travelled behind midfield, came under pressure mid-stages, weakened 300M, well beaten.
Slow to begin, outpaced and detached in last over 10Ls off the pace, never involved.
Ridden to share the lead at 400m outside the front runner, took control at 300. Won well.
Went back and near the grands stand, shifted course to far side 200m, close off nicely under the whip
Not rushed, sat fairly handy with cover, shifted in at 340m to face breeze, shifted out sharply at 100m. Kept on OK.
Jumped well and sat midpack closer to the grands stand. Held up at 200m after shifting inside, shifted to far side for clear running at 120m. One paced.
Not rushed. Parked in between horses. Held up at 700m, and kept coming when in clear.
Jumped and led on the grands stand, challenged by the winner at 400m. Weakened as usual.
Sat fairly handy, travelled, held up at 120m and checked at 100m. Kept on OK.
Jumped and stalked the leaders, ridden out and checked at 120m. Gave ground after.
Jumped, midfield, shifted out at 700m, travelled on the worst part of the track, checked at 120m. Kept on. Bad ride.
Not rushed after a hampered start, travelled back, checked at 700m, improved position but had nowhere to go.
Shifted in at start. Travelled fairly handy on grads' stand, Shifted in for clear running at 320m. held up badly in closing stages. Unlucky runner and lame after the race.
Handy on the grands' stand. Checked at 150m and then no room in closing stages. Had excuses.
Checked at start. Well back, shifted to far side. Never a factor.
Mid pack early and gradually gave ground.
Jumped well, showed early speed to race in 2nd, easy run to turn, finished off strongly in straight to score with a little to spare.
Began well from a wide draw, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead on turn, kept on well until headed near 200M, just held on for 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 2-3 lengths back in midfield, similar position on turn, angled out in straight and finished off strongly, just missed 2nd.
Fast into stride, raced 2-3 lengths back on rail, easy run to turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening the first few to make frame.

Moderately away from a tricky gate, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover in midfield, 4 lengths back, still no cover turning, didn't have extra gear to feature but held ground evenly.
Jumped well, raced 2 lengths back in 3rd, no cover on turn, kept on evenly until 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Began well, raced 6-7 lengths back on rail in 9th, 2 wide on turn, made minor headway in straight.
Slightly slowly away, raced 10 lengths or so back at rear, still well back on turn, set too much to do and could only made some headway in straight.
Taken back from the widest draw, positioned 5 lengths back behind midfield, 3 wide with cover, similar position turning, closed off evenly in straight. (Bled from both nostrils)
Moderately away, taken back to race 8 lengths back at rear, 3 wide with cover on turn, taken widest in straight but only finished with one-paced.
Slowly away, raced 11 lengths back at tail, still last turning, set too much to do and could only pass a tired horse in straight.
Jumped with them, raced 6 lengths back on rail behind midfield, similar position turning, showed no response early in straight and dropped out gradually.
Moderately away, positioned 2-3 lengths back on rail in midfield, easy run to turn, closed off well to score by a neck.
Began well, raced a length behind the leader on rail, easy run throughout, kept on well in straight but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 lengths or so back in 5th, bumped near 1200M, similar position on turn, kept on well in straight to get 3rd.
Taken back from gate 12, raced 7-8 lengths back at rear, gradually improved on turn, taken wide in straight and finished off strongly to make frame.
Fairly away, raced 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position turning, made reasonable progress in straight, just missed frame.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 5 lengths or so back on rail behind midfield, saved ground on turn, angled out in straight and made some progress.
Began well, raced 3 wide with cover in 6th, 2-3 lengths back, similar position on turn, made some headway early in straight, weakened gradually after 150M.
Average to begin, sent forward to take the lead, easy lead until turning in, headed near 250M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Away with them, positioned 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back, improved on turn, showed no progress early in straight and eased thereafter.
Jumped with them, raced 2 wide at rear, 5-6 lengths back, similar position on turn, taken widest in straight but finished with only one-paced.
Began well from the widest gate, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, same position turning, emptied early in straight and dropped out gradually.
Taken back from a wide gate, raced at tail throughout, 9-10 lengths back, still well back on turn, finished off one-paced, never a threat.
Moderately away, 6-7 lengths back at rear, similar position turning, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
Began fairly, sent forward to race 3 wide with cover in 4th, no cover on turn, emptied early in straight and dropped out tamely.

Jumped fairly, settled just off the pace on rails, obtained a split inside 200 metres, ran on to prevail narrowly.
Settled towards the rear on rails, saved ground turning in, finished off race strongly to just fail to get up on line.
Began well from the one draw, disputed lead early stages before kicking 1L clear on top of the Rock, maintained a similar break after straightening but soon flattered can caught close to home.
Prominent early after beginning from a wide gate, gradually settled in midfield far side, came closer entering straight, kept on steadily without quickening.
Soon taken back from a wide gate, took closer order around the bend, sustained progress in straight, did best work late.
Very slowly away, remained well behind on rails to straight, produced good late impression in the run home.
Close up early, gradually settled wide towards the rear, baulked for a run early in straight, finished off race well inside final 200 metres.
Began moderately, dropped steadily to last approaching home bend, fought on steadily under pressure in the straight, never nearer.
Jumped fairly, settled in midfield on rails, did not find much room most of the way in straight, not properly tested.
Ridden along amongst leaders early, remained in a prominent position to straight, soon weakened.
Jumped fairly, gradually settled 3-wide in midfield, wider turning for home, ran on steadily without threatening.
Never far off when wide far side after beginning from the widest gate, dropped away quickly in straight.
Raced outside the lead. Responded well when asked on straightening and took over final 150M.
Ridden out of the gates to take up a forward spot. One out one back in backstraight and home turn. Ran on well but never a threat to winner.
Niggled to the lead. Held a ½L advantage into home straight. Headed 150M out and held on for a minor placing.
2-wide midfield. Switched out and made up ground rounding the turn. Ran on fairly to make the frame.
Settled on fence at midfield. Switched out 500M turn and 3Ls off turning for home. Ran on fairly in the straight.
Lacked early speed and raced 3-wide behind midfield. Wide and towards rear turning for home. Ran on without threatening.
Box-seated behind the pace. Hard ridden to keep up at home turn and remained same pace in the straight.
Outpaced early and raced towards the rear. Near last turning for home. Ran on and made up some late ground.
Blew start and raced on fence in rear section. Blundered at 500M. Ran into traffic a few times in the straight and not able to show ability.
Crowded on jumping. 2-wide and no better than midfield backstraight. Lacked response when asked and same pace to line.
3-wide in rear section. Last to enter home straight Only ran past a tired runner.
Soon at the rear. Remained in rear section turning for home and never picked up.
Settled in front of midfield about 3Ls off the leader 2 wide with cover, suited by the fast tempo, demonstrated strong finishing to take the victory by 1.5Ls.
Eased back as usual, settled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, dashed well for 2nd.
Prominent, travelled 1L behind the leader 2 wide with cover, despite harmed by the fast pace, kept on well to the line to get 3rd.
Pushed forward to take the fence and shared the lead at fast tempo, hung on well until final 100M headed by the winner.
Raced midfield, settled 4.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, benefited by the fast sectionals, ran on steadily.
Pushed forward to occupy the box seat, harmed by the fast pace, kept on fairly to the line.
Raced midfield, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, one paced home.
Hard ridden forward to park outside the leader at fast sectionals, faded over the last furlong.
Settled worse than midfield about 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast pace, ran on fairly.
Failed to muster pace, settled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast tempo, never ran on.
Pushed to midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite suited by the fast sectionals, never ran on.
At rear throughout, never a factor.
Jumped well. Sat 3 back off the leader after a check, always travelled, lengthened nicely to win.
Four back the fence, ridden out before the turn, kept up a good gallop out wide.
Jumped and wide early on. Stalked the leader on the fence, challenged the front runner just after the turn. Kept on well.
Erratic start, improved to settle 6 off the leader on fence at 1,000m, and closed off under riding.
Slow and third last on the fence, ridden out at 650m, and closed off along the fence.
Held his position 4 off the leader on the fence after a clean jump, shifted one off fence at 1000m. Ran on in a much-improved effort.
Went straight to the front after the jump. Challenged by the 3rd place getter at 320m. Beaten at 220m.
7 off the leader, one off the fence, turn the widest out. Closed off OK.
Jumped well. Sat midpack, one off the fence, bumped at 950m and drifted further back. Never a factor. Blood in the trachea and lost his left front plate.
Well back early after a poor jump, tight at 1,100m, improved to sit 4 wide at 850m, under ridden and never a factor.
Jumped well to go forward, then restrained to sit 4 off, 3 wide at 850m, had cover at 600m. No finish.
Always at the rear. Never a factor.
Jumped well to lead from a middle gate, kept up a good gallop under riding to win.
Ridden out after losing early position, sat 4 off leader, one off the fence at 420m. Bit erratic on turn, settled, then closed off strongly out wide.
Jumped well to sit midpack earl on, travelled, ran on well out wide.
Fast break, bustled to race handy 1 off, driven 350m, 3rd turning in, boxed on evenly to wire.
Followed the winner along the fence. Weak in finish.
Jumped and sat 6 back the fence, travelled, tight at 550m. Closed off in an improved effort.
Jumped a bit slow. Ridden to sit 3 off leader on the fence. Very one-paced.
Poor start. Ridden, improved position, always ridden, battled on. Bled and heart irregularity.
Beaten for speed, sat 4 back 2 off fence. Held up before the turn, shifted in at 200m. Never a chance out wide.
Not rushed. Travelled wide early on, second last turning for home. Ordinary.
Ridden early on, always at the rear, and never travelled.
Always wide, couldn't handle the turn and weakened.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the leader 2- 3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Eased back, 7.5Ls off the leader 1-2 wide, benefited by the fast tempo, made steady ground 250M for 2nd.
Eased to sit in midfield, 4Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made early move 500M, led 300M, overhauled 150M, ran on for 3rd.
Eased back, 6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 300M, run ended 100M.
Slow away, 5.5Ls off the leader on the fence, favoured by the fast pace, checked 500M, made steady ground 250M.
Pushed forward, sat just off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast tempo, flattened 200M.
Settled in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the fast pace along the fence, held up 5-3, just held ground in straight.
Eased back, took rail, 6.5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, made ground when clear.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the fast pace 2 wide, lack room 400M, flattened 200M.
Pushed early but not muster, trapped 3 wide in midfield, continued forward 1000M to share the lead at fast pace, out of fuel 300M.
Pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 4Ls off the leader, suited by the fast tempo, checked 500M, no progress.
Hard ridden to take rail and shared the lead at fast pace, soon emptied 300M.
Box seated, always travelled, challenged leader at 170m before running on well to win.
Ridden after the jump, well back one-off the fence. Ridden at 480m and finished off well to get 2nd. Blood in the trachea.
Sat 4 off the leaders one off the fence, travelled, held up at 600m, 400m and 220m before running on under the whip out wide.
Jumped and took the lead at 1140m, challenged by 450m, running on empty under riding.
Not rushed. Sat midpack on the fence, ridden at 520m, stayed glued to the fence. One-paced.
Rear early, improved at 860m to sit 3 wide with cover, 4 wide at 500m. Widest out turning for home and kept plugging away.
Poked his head to lead early on from middle gate, sat one-off the fence behind the leader at 1040m. Challenged the leader at 450m & tired 150m.
Sat 5 off the leader one-off the fence at 1,020m, ridden out at 470m & plugged on out wide.
Well back on the fence, improved to sit 6 back off the leader, stayed glued to the rails, held up a bit at 230m.
Rear early on, held up & head up at 550m, checked badly at 200m, shifted inside for clear running. One-paced.
Jumped to go forward but caught 4 wide and was weakening.
Handy early on and then 3 wide. Ordinary.
Patiently ridden in a midfield position, 5Ls off the pace along the inside, switched back to inside for clear run 200M, found his best stride late, led near 50M.
Vied for lead on the inside, driven out 400M, unable to hold off winner passing 100M, kept on well enough for 2nd.
Began awkwardly, held up 2-wide in midfield, stayed on moderately to go 3rd 100M but not a serious threat to first two.
Crossed to a 2-wide position near the rear, well off the pace early stages but crept closer passing 600M, put in some late good work, got up for 4th close home.
Held up behind midfield 6-7Ls off leaders, waited with till 350M, stayed on but not making impression on first two.
In 5th never far off from leaders, had his chance turning home, outpaced by leaders final 200M.
Chased leaders and more prominent than usual, ran on same pace final 300M.
Switched off to last over 10Ls off the pace in early stages, crept closer as the pace slackened in middle stages, taken wide 350M, stayed on but never a threat to leaders.
Slow to begin, settled near last, still more than 7Ls to make up 400M, driven out 300M, ran past weakening rivals mainly.
Vied for the lead on outside, set good pace early stage, kept on to 200M, weakened rapidly thereafter.
Guided to the fence tracking leading pair, found little on straightening, beaten passing 200M.
Patiently ridden, 6Ls near the rear making home turn, hung early straight, never picked up the pace.
Jumped cleanly and box seated. Came off the fence at 900m, challenged the leader at 230m and kicked clear.
Sat 2nd last one-off the fence, bit keen early on, turn widest and ran on strongly.
Jumped well, sat five off the leader one-off the fence, held up at 280m, shifted out for clear running before running on nicely.
Ridden and 3 wide without cover at 880m. Plodded on.
Jumped well, sat handy 3 deep without cover and fired up. Settled and sat with cover behind the winner and kept on one-paced.
Sat 4 back the fence, always travelled. Nowhere to go in closing stages along the paint. Unlucky runner.
Jumped poorly, ridden to sit behind the leaders on the fence, found nothing & never a factor.
Jumped and led easily, challenged by the winner at 230m, weakened in closing stages.
Bumped after the start. Sat 7 off one-off the fence. Bit keen before the turn. Didn't make much of an impression.
Third last on the fence early after jumping fairly, bit tight after turning in and no room in closing stages.
Very poor start and always at rear. Never a factor.
6 back off leader and 3 wide with cover. Fading turning for home.

Slightly slow out, settled just over 2L off the slow pace in 4th, held similar position into straight, responded well to win readily.
Settled in 3rd within 2L of the slow pace, box-seated entering straight, did not find much room until late when quickened well inside final 150 metres.
Jumped fairly, settled at the rear of the small field about 3L off the slow pace, came under pressure soon after straightening, produced only moderate progress in the run home.
Broke well, settled 2-wide just off the slow pace, took the lead from the tiring leader 200 metres out but short-lived, finished off tamely.
Began well from the one draw, set a sedate pace to straight, led until finding no extra inside final 200 metres. (Questioned for disappointing performance)
Soon taken back to the rear of the field, one-paced under pressure in the run home.
3-wide towards the rear. Asked to improve position at 600M turn and was a length off turning in. Kept on strongly and kicked away final 200M.
Jumped well from wide draw and allowed to drift back to rear section. Saved ground making turn and ran on well in the straight.
Missed the kick and was wide facing the breeze behind midfield. Gradually improved after 1100M and was 3-wide among leaders home turn. Kept on well for a minor placing.
Gradually dropped back to rear section. Wide turn home and showed a nice rally in the straight.
Behind midfield early and middle stages. Last to enter home straight. Found trouble 400M out but rallied impressively thereafter.
3-wide better than midfield. 4-wide among leaders turning for home. Remained in contention 300M out but unable to find extra gear thereafter.
Slowly away. Raced along the rails at midfield. Quicken on straightening but lost momentum when crowded 250M out. Ran on only fairly thereafter.
Ridden along early and took the lead 1400M. Maintained advantage turning in but faded shortly after.
Nicely box-seated behind the pace. Failed to quicken when asked on straightening. Same pace to finish.
3-wide at midfield. Made up ground at the turn and was 5-wide among leaders turning for home. Faded gradually final 300M.
Settled on fence behind midfield. Ran on without threatening in the straight.
Settled 2-wide at midfield. Wide turn home and never picked up in the straight.
Early lead and then settle behind the pace 1200M. Lacked response when asked before checking at home turn. Dropped out thereafter (bled).
Niggled along and eventually settling outside the lead. Disputed lead turning for home but struck itself, became badly unbalanced and dropped out.
Rolled forward to settle 1L off outside the leader, ran on well to score by 1/2L.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, could not find a day night until final furlong, dashed strongly thereafter to get 2nd.
Eased back from the outside barrier, settled 4.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, ran on nicely for 3rd.
Pushed forward to obtain the box seat, kept on one pace to the line.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran on steadily.
At last, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, swung wide turning in, dashed well.
Pushed forward to settle in midfield, 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, kept on one pace until 100M weakened.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, never ran on.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on until 300M weakened.
Settled worse than midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never ran on.
Settled worse than midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader on the fence, never looked likely.
At rear, travelled 6Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, rider's stirrup leather broken 350M, because of that not able to ride out thereafter.
Rolled forward to settle 2Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on until 250M flattened.
Sent forward, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, soon flattened after straightening.
Settled 1 off with cover behind midfield, strong traveller, fanned wide home turn & driven, quickened impressively to lead 200m, hung in a touch, held on at wire.
Taken back to near tail 1 off with cover, overraced early, strong traveller & driven 430m, shifted wide 400m, quickened in pursuit, closing at line.
Smart break, soon led, to rail 1650m & set steady pace, shaken up 850m, pressed turning in, all out & headed 200m, battled on to wire.
Snagged to race rail behind midfield, driven 420m & shifted 1 off, good progress & back to fence 260m, kept on evenly closing stages.
Broke well, raced easily in 4th 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide 900m & moved upside leader 800m, pressed lead into stretch, peaked 250m & tapered.
Broke OK, raced 1 off with cover midfield, shifted 3 wide 800m, hard-ridden turning in, outpaced but stayed on gamely.
Broke well, keen early, covered up midfield on rail, shifted 1 off & niggled 800m, hard-ridden 400m & outpaced, kept on evenly.
Missed break & detached, soon closed to race at tail 3 wide with cover, travelled easily until driven 400m, tapped for toe, plugged on one pace.
Sharp start to dispute early lead, soon settled 3rd 1 off with cover, ridden 700m & under pressure, all out turning in, faded in run.
Slow start, 3 wide no cover near rail, niggled 900m, driven 800m, widest into stretch, emptied tamely.
Smart break, overraced early, settled 1 back on rail, overraced 1350m, hard-ridden 450m, found nothing & weakened, eased in run.
Speed to lead, crossed to rail 1000m, set solid tempo, pressed turning in, waited with until shaken up 330m, kicked on & battled home under strong drive.
Broke well, settled 1 off 1 back, smooth traveller, shifted 3 wide & driven in 3rd 400m, quickened to 2nd 250m, pressed lead but always held.
Broke OK, worked from wide gate to sit 1 off with cover fore of midfield, shifted wide & driven 430m, quickened to 3rd 200m, held but battled on.
Broke OK, bustled early to race rail fore of midfield, driven turning in, ran on soundly.
Broke well wide, taken back to 3 wide near tail, driven centre track 420m, quickened & closed doggedly for solid inroads.
Fast break, raced outside lead in close 2nd, vied for lead turning in, driven 370m, outpaced & tapered to wire.
Smart start wide, snagged to 1 off near tail, ridden 430m, & ran home well centre track for minor late gains.
Tardy start, raced at tail 1 off, switched 3 wide 600m, widest turning in, driven 350m, quickened & ran on centre track for minor headway.
Snagged back to 3 wide with cover midfield, ill-at-ease on turn, pushed widest turning & driven, kept on evenly, never a threat.
Sharp start, soon outpaced & backpedalled, scrubbed along midfield 1 off, wide home turn & driven, one-paced & tapered out.
Pace at break, sat 1 back on rail, every chance when driven 430m but found nothing & weakened tamely.
Bustled early to race handy 3 wide no cover, progress to 3rd on turn, driven 420m, soon emptied & wilted.
Awkward start, settled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, ridden 420m, outpaced & struggled in run.
Tardy start, raced rail behind midfield, shifted out & driven 420m, found nothing & eased 250m.
Settled in midfield, 5.5Ls off the good pace along the fence, progressed steadily 300M to score.
Occupied a comparatively more prominent spot in front, 2Ls off the good pace 2 wide, led 300M, ran on well until 100M overhauled.
Eased at start, took cover at rear, 8Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the good pace 2-3 wide, made steady ground 300M but lack of its usual strong finishing efforts.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the good pace on the fence, lack room 4-2, made steady ground when clear.
Settled 4Ls off the good pace along the rails, made some ground 200M.
Eased to sit in front of midfield, 3Ls off the good pace 2 wide, no dash in straight.
Settled 2.5Ls off the good pace along the fence, lack turn of foot, flattened 200M.
Pushed to take rail and led by 2Ls at good pace, hung on until 300M emptied.
Eased back, 6Ls off the good pace 2-4 wide, no progress.
Hard ridden forward, 2Ls off the good pace, trapped 3 wide no cover, reduced quickly 400M.
Very slow away, never improved at rear.
Very slow away, never a factor.
Began well but eased back from wide draw and shut off at rear. Switched in and boxed top of straight but got clear 300m and powered way to easy victory.
Bumped start but quickly in front and set good pace. Temporarily headed 400m but fought back strongly to hold second on the line.
Ridden along to maintain forward position 3-back from leader but wide. Battled on gamely in straight to just miss the quinella.
Crowded out start, taken to fence behind midfield. Steadied 700m, improved position turn, not much room in straight, lay out under pressure from 200m, raced tight closing stages.
Began well, settling 3rd about 3L from leader. Took closer order turning for home. Hit front passing 200m, one-paced final stages.
Began fairly, ridden along 4-back from leader in one-off position. Kept on steadily in straight without looking dangerous.
Crowded out start dropping towards rear but away from fence. Lost position turn, ran past tired horses closing stages.
Jumped OK, settling midfield 5L from leader. Lost position around turn and one-paced in straight.
Ridden along early, settling 2L behind leader. Rolled forward around turn to join leader 400m, but gave ground quickly after passing 200m.
Outpaced and soon last. Never competitive.

Patiently held up at the rear 7Ls off the pace, wide bid nearing 600M, swung widest into straight, chased home Military Attack, kept giving under strong drive, dug deep final stages to prevail in a pulsating finish.
Settled behind midfield 5-6Ls off the pace, travelled smoothly to straight, picked up well 400M, hit lead 50M only to be caught by winner last few strides. Ran huge in defeat.
Tracked leader, responded well when driven 350M, hit lead inside 300M and looked a strong chance, caught by first 2 nearing 50M, held on for 3rd.
Held up in mid-division, moved out to a striking spot 450M, not finishing pace of first two but stayed on well to claim 4th.
Soon taken across the fence after a sluggish start, travelled towards the rear 5-6Ls off the pace, switched out for his challenge 400M, ran on well for a career best performance.
Never far off from the pace, kept on chasing leaders early straight, outdashed final 150M.
Settled in midfield, saved ground on inside, driven 350M, stayed on moderately and never a serious threat.
Dropped back to the rear over 8Ls behind leaders, crept closer home turn, stayed on mildly and not reached leaders.
Soon led, set slow pace first 800M, quickened up mid-stages, headed inside 300M, weakened and no extra passing 150M.
Sat handily just behind leader, driven out near 400M but had little to offer, soon outpaced by much higher rated rivals, eased final 100M.
Shifted across behind runners, raced in a 3-wide position for much of the way, came under pressure 500M, not quickened entering straight.
Caught 3-wide without cover from draw 12, still in touch rounding the home turn but first to be beaten turning in. (Lame next day)
Began well, eased, settling towards rear in one-off position. Began forward move 4-wide from 600m, coasted to the front 200m and pulled clear for easy win.
Began fairly, pushed along to sit 5th in one-off position before turn. Tightened passing 800m, no run early in straight, blundered 350m when crossed. Finished strongly when clear 150m.
Began fairly, allowed to roll forward but three-wide to sit 4th 800m. Improved position around turn, joint leader from 300m to 200m, ran out of steam final strides.
Ridden along between horses to maintain forward position about 2L behind leader. Raced tightly around turn, 4-wide into straight, kept on steadily.
Pressed forward to lead on settling. Joined up front 300m, kept on to 200m before giving ground gradually.
Crowded out start, settling between horses towards the rear. Took turn a little wide and kept on one-paced in straight.
Began well and allowed to settle outside leader. Remained in contention till passing 300m when gave ground gradually.
Taken across behind horses from wide draw, settling at rear but away from fence. Taken wide entering straight and kept on one-paced.
Beaten for speed, settling at rear in one-off position. Switched out 400m for clear running but only one-paced.
Began OK, not much speed, settling behind midfield along fence. Found little in straight under hard riding.
Ridden along to maintain forward position, settling one-back, one-off before turn. Found little soon after straightening and faded.
Outpaced and soon last long fence. Ran past beaten horses final stages.
Ridden forward from wide draw and held in midfield without cover for most of the trip. Faded final 200m.
First out but unable maintain speed and eased into box seat 3L behind leader. Still in contention entering straight but gave ground quickly from 250m. Unacceptable performance.
Moderately away from a tricky gate, positioned 5 lengths or so back in 10th, slightly improved along the rail on turn, kept to inside after straightening, finished off well to score.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 7-8 lengths back at rear, 3 wide with cover on turn, closed off well to get 2nd.
Began fairly from the widest gate, raced 10 lengths back at tail, still well back on turn, taken widest in straight and finished off strongly, just missed 2nd.
Average to begin, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, same position on turn, angled out in straight and made reasonable headway to make frame.
Began awkwardly and blundered, raced 8 lengths back on rail at rear, similar position turning, no clear running early in straight, found daylight 150M and kept on well thereafter.
Began fairly, positioned 2 lengths back on rail in 5th, bumped near 900M and steadied 500M, finished off evenly in straight.
Away with them, raced 3 wide with some cover, 5 lengths back behind midfield, still 3 wide on turn, finished off evenly in straight without threatening.

Fast into stride, positioned 2 wide in 4th, a length or so back, bumped near 900M, similar position on turn, improved briefly after turning in, but peaked at near 200M and just held ground thereafter.
Bumped start, raced 3-4 lengths back on rail, gradually improved along the rail on turn, made some headway early in straight, peaked at near 200M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Jumped with them, positioned 2 wide in 6th, 3 lengths back, hampered near 800M, similar margin back on turn, closed off one-paced.
Jumped nicely from gate 1, raced in 2nd, sat outside the leader on turn, kept on evenly until 200M, weakened thereafter. (See racing incidents)
Jumped well, sent forward to race prominently in 3rd, similar position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 7 lengths back, 2 wide turning, failed to close off in straight.
Began well, unable to slot in and difficult to settle early, took the lead near 1200M, emptied after turning in, never competitive.

Broke well from the one draw, settled just off the pace on rails mainly in 4th, hit the front under pressure 200 metres out.
Taken back to settle in midfield on rails, continued to save ground turning in, fought on steadily without threatening.

Jumped well from the widest gate, soon taken back to race at the rear, angled off rails for a run turning in but did not find much room early on, switched back to inside to make up good ground inside final 200 metres.
Jumped well from a wide draw, taken back across for rails run behind midfield, ran on down the centre of the straight, did best work late.
Not far off to straight, inconvenienced a few times in straight, kept on steadily under pressure.
Began fairly, wide in midfield early before settling in 10th, made modest headway without threatening in straight.
Jumped fairly, pressed on to take up running coming onto stables bend, led the field until overhauled over 200 metres out.
In front early, ceded advantage to settle 2-wide in 2nd far side, soon faded in straight. (Mucus)
Settled in midfield, came under pressure entering straight, found nothing.
Taken back to race in rear, remained well behind to straight, made no impression down the centre of the track.
Jumped awkwardly losing ground, worked his way up to travel in better than midfield but wide without cover, took closer order to prominent 3rd far side, weakened after straightening.
Missed the break, settled in midfield, widest turning in, run soon ended. (Lame next day)
Jumped well and raced one out one back. Quickened well and took the lead 200M out. Stayed on well to deny a late challenge.
Nicely box-seated behind the pace. Quickened well but had to alter course when gap closed 200M out. Charged home strongly and just failed to catch winner.
Niggled and took the lead near 1000M. Held a slight advantage into home straight. Failed to hold off top pair final stages.
Jumped well and better than midfield backstraight. 2Ls off the lead home turn but never threatened placegetters.
On the rails and better than midfield. 2Ls off turning for home but unable to turn up a notch in the straight.
Settled 3-wide behind midfield. Ran on steadily in the straight.
Off slowly and trailed field until home straight. Made up a bit of ground in the straight despite being hampered 200M out.
Raced 2-wide and no better than midfield. Ran home without quickening.
Jumped well but was outpaced. Checked 1000M out and gradually slipped back to rear section. Saved ground making home turn but found nothing in the straight.
Awkward jump and raced in rear section. Near last turning for home and remained same pace to finish.
Wide without cover mostly. No impression in the straight.
Jumped awkwardly and raced in rear section. Wide no cover back straight and just behind midfield 500M out. Widest and last few turning in. No impression thereafter.
Pushed forward to race outside the lead, benefited by the slow tempo, ran on well to score by 3/4L.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 3/4L at slow sectionals, hung on strongly until final 150M headed by the winner.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover suited by the slow pace, ran on gradually for 3rd.
Rolled forward to obtain the box seat, despite benefited by the slow tempo, kept on one pace only without threatening.
Crowded start, then settled 6.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, despite harmed by the slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader 3 wide without cover, not suited by the slow pace, ran home one paced.
At rear, settled 7Ls behind the leader on the fence, harmed by slow sectionals, made some ground in straight.
Settled worse than midfield, 5.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, not suited by the slow tempo, ran on only fairly.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, not suited by the slow pace, never ran on.
At rear, never responded despite ridden along throughout, dropped off rounding the Home Turn. (Questioned for disappointing performance, see incident report)
Raced midfield, travelled 4Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, never looked competitive.
Settled worse than midfield about 5.5Ls behind the leader 3 wide with cover, hampered by the slow pace, never looked likely.
Broke well, sat handy 1 off with cover, switched 3 deep 950m & advanced to lead 850m, soon crossed to rail, shaken up 400m, kept finding to wire.
Tardy start & bustled, settled handy on rail, shifted 3 deep 600m & driven to 3rd 500m, boxed on to 2nd turning in, closed to press leader in run but held.
Moderate start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, forced 3 wide 570m, very wide into stretch & driven 300m, closing run to claim 3rd.
Tardy break, settled behind midfield 1 off, switched 4 wide & advanced 570m, hard-ridden 450m, kept on evenly centre track.
Slow start, rousted early to race midfield, switched 1 off 570m & ridden for progress, hard driven 400m, boxed on dourly.
Broke OK, rousted to dispute early lead, soon overraced & snagged to sit handy on rail, shuffled back 850m, to 1 off 460m & driven, stayed on evenly.
Slow start, sat 1 off with cover near rear, switched 3 deep & ridden for progress 450m, widest into stretch, ran on for minor inroads.
Missed break, settled rail near rear, shoved along 670m, under pressure turning in, emptied 150m & no extra.
Sluggish break, camped last place 1 off, niggled 720m, switched wide & driven 570m, outpaced & found little, plugged on tepidly.
Slow start, raced rail last pair, scrubbed along 720m, to tail 570m, & driven, struggled in run home.
Sharp break wide, raced in 2nd 1 off no cover, driven under pressure 450m, outpaced & emptied 300m, faded thereafter.
Fast start, soon led & to rail, headed 850m & raced 1 back on inner, ridden but backpedalled 500m, weakened tamely & eased in stretch.
Dropped in at break, raced 3 wide with cover near tail, shifted out 750m & rapid advance to slim lead 640m, slotted 1 off, shaken up 300m & drew well clear.
Smart start, camped 1 back on rail, shaken up & shifted out turning in, ran on to 2nd but well held by winner.
Bustled to lead 1260m & snagged rail, set steady tempo, headed 640m & driven, all out & vied for lead final turn, tapered final 200m.
Fast start & rousted, settled back on rail midfield, driven turning in, kept on without threatening.
Broke OK, taken back to race last pair 1 off with cover, driven 550m & wide into stretch, closed centre track for late gains.
Moderate start, raced rail behind midfield, scrubbed along 550m, all out turning in, kept on evenly.
Broke well, slotted 1 off with cover behind midfield, ridden along 550m, shifted wide 400m, stayed on centre track for moderate inroads.
Fast start wide & soon led, headed 1260m & parked close 2nd 1 off no cover, shuffled to 3rd 1 back & scrubbed 600m, all out turning in, one-paced & tapered.
Broke OK, settled midfield 1 off with cover, outpaced & niggled 400m, ridden final turn, found little in tame stretch run.
Taken back at start, sat 3 wide no cover behind midfield, advanced a spot 850m, driven 400m, plugged on tamely.
Slow start, raced rail at tail, travelled well until driven turning in, plodded on same speed.
Sharp break, slotted 1 back 1 off, niggled 600m & shuffled back, under pump 450m, wilted in run home.
Eased to sit in midfield, traveled well, dashed strongly 250M and scored with some in hand.
Pushed forward, 1.5Ls off the slow pace 2 wide, lack room 300M, dashed well when clear for 2nd.
Settled in box seat, enjoyed the slow sectionals, just held ground in straight for 3rd.
Pushed to share the lead 2 wide, benefited by the slow sectionals, ran on until 150M flattened.
Slow away, 4Ls off the leaders 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, little dash 200M.
Took rail easily and shared the lead at advantageous slow sectionals, however soon weakened 250M.
Hard ridden forward, trapped 3 wide no cover throughout, out of fuel 250M.
Eased back, 4.5Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide, not suited by the slow pace, ran on ok despite all negative racing situations.
Back and wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, ran on fairly, on heels 100M.
Slow away, pushed to hold the rail in midfield, 3Ls off the leaders, unbalanced 600M, harmed by the slow pace, no progress.
Eased to rear, harmed by the slow tempo, never a factor.
Midfield, 3Ls off the leaders, trapped 3 wide throughout, harmed by the slow pace, reduced 300M.
Jumped with field, ridden along early to hold fence behind leader. Temporarily pocketed turning for home, switched off fence 300m for clear running and powered home for smart win.
Began well but eased back towards the rear in one-off position. Took closer order passing 500m, taken wide into straight, finished strongly.
Crowded out start, ridden along to hold midfield position, tightened and unbalanced 600m. Got inside run in straight and finished off nicely.
Crowded out start, no pace, dropping to rear. Got close to heels turning for home. Took inside run in straight, tightened 100m, kept on well.
Began awkwardly, ridden along to hold forward position 3-back from leader. Ran on steadily in straight though raced tight passing 100m.
Lifted leg at start and lost ground, dropping to last pair but away from fence. Last into straight, taken out for clear running but only one-paced.
Began OK, settling behind midfield along fence. Stayed on fence around turn but one-paced in straight.
Crowded out start, ridden to obtain forward position, struck heels and blundered 1000m, allowed to roll forward to share lead from 550m. Still in contention 200m before fading.
Pressed forward racing 3-wide first turn before settling one-off, one-back. Hung out badly home turn, very wide in straight, not properly tested. Racing behaviour unacceptable.
Hard ridden to lead on settling though wide, cutting to fence passing 850m. Joined up front 550m, first into straight before fading.
Tracked leaders 2-wide, driven forward 600M to chase breakaway leader, wrestled the lead inside 200M under strong handling, fended off late challenges to score.
Held up in mid-division 4Ls off the pace, saved ground on the inside, stayed on well up the fence to make a late impression, went 2nd 50M from home.
Fractious in stalls and slowly away, settled towards the rear 6Ls off the pace, nudged along 500M, did best work final 200M, nearest finish.
Lost ground at the start, held up behind midfield 4-5Ls behind leader, closed off steadily when driven out 400M, made good late impression.
Chased leaders along the fence, shuffled back a bit nearing home turn, loomed a place hope 150M, turned one pace final stages.
In last pair early stages, made mid-race move back-straight, strolled to lead before home turn, kept on effort to 200M, headed and weakened out of contention.
Soon taken across to the fence, settled at the rear 7-8Ls back, waited with until 350M, closed off well.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, driven 450M, gave limited response, never reached contention.
Eased to a 2-wide spot towards the rear, came under pressure home turn, took time to pick up, ran past beaten rivals closing stages.
Crossed to the lead 1300M, led slowly first half, relinquished lead near home turn, had little to offer on straightening.
Caught wide early stages, strode forward to race outside the pace, driven to chase breakaway leaders home turn, run ended 200M, eased when no chance.
Behind mid-division and travelled 3-wide for much of the way, not helped by the slow pace first 800M, struggled to keep up 500M, first to be beaten.

Slowly into stride, recovered but raced keenly in the early stages, took the lead near 300M, ran on well to score.
Bumped start, raced 1-2 lengths back in midfield, ridden near 400M, finished off well to get 2nd.
Fast into stride, showed early speed to take the lead near to the stands' side, headed near 300M but still stayed on for 3rd.
Jumped with them, raced at rear, finished off strongly to make frame to be nearest on line.
Jumped well from a good draw, raced in midfield on the near side, made reasonable headway final furlong to be nearest on line, just missed frame.
Moderately away, raced about 4 off the stands rail, finished off evenly without threatening.
Bumped start, raced prominently on the stands rail, kept on at the same pace in the run to the post.
Began awkwardly, raced about 4 lengths back at tail, made some headway final 400M.
Moderately away from a poor draw, raced prominently, about 6 off the stands rail, stayed on until final 200M, weakened thereafter.
Jumped well from a poor draw, raced towards the middle of the course, no cover, weakened gradually after 300M.
Bumped start, raced near side, always at rear, emptied near 200M, never competitive.
Ridden early down centre track to maintain forward position until 400m when gave ground quickly.
Jumped with them, raced 3 off the stands rail at rear, was under pressure after the 500m, but failed to respond and finished well back.
Jumped with them, raced near side with cover in midfield, weakened sharply after 300M, finished tailed out. (Bled from both nostrils)
2-wide better than midfield. 2Ls off turning for home. Gradually picked up and took the lead final 200M. Kept on well to the line.
Trailed field from 1200M onwards. Caught in traffic for some time after straightening. Found daylight near 200M and charged home strongly.
On the rails at midfield. Stuck in traffic for some time after straightening. Closed the race off well once finding daylight.
Ridden along from wide draw and took lead 1000M out. Took a length's advantage into home straight but unable to hold off placegetters final 200M.
Settled in rear section. Last few to turn in and held up briefly early straight. Closed off well.
Among early leaders. Settled 2-wide behind pace 1000M. Kept on fairly in the straight.
Settled in rear section. Last on straightening and was checked 350M. Made up ground in the closing stages.
Wide at midfield early. 4-wide and near last turning for home. Made up ground after straightening but unable to sustain effort final stages.
Urged along early but left wide no cover. Allowed to go closer to the pace after 1000M. 3-wide turning for home. Kept on fairly before fading final 200M.
2-wide and no better than midfield. No clear run in early part of the straight. Ran on without threatening once in the clear.
3-wide and no better than midfield. Widest turning in and stayed same pace to finish.
Crowded shortly after start and then dropped to rear section. Made a ground saving trip rounding the bend. Ran on same pace in the straight.
Hard ridden to a forward position. Box-seated behind the leader making the turn. Faded gradually final 300M.
3-wide better than midfield. Never quickened and weakened shortly after straightening.
Pushed forward, settled 1L off outside the leader, dashed strongly to score by a nose.
Hard ridden forward to take the fence and led by 1L, kept on strongly to the line, just beaten by a nose.
Raced midfield, travelled 3.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, processed steadily for 3rd.
Midfield, travelled 5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, ran home gradually.
Prominent, travelled 2.5Ls behind the leader 2 wide with cover, kept on one paced to the line.
Jumped awkwardly, then travelled 9Ls behind the leader, ran home nicely despite raced very wide without cover throughout.
At rear section, settled 6Ls behind the leader on the fence, made some ground in straight.
Raced midfield, travelled 3Ls behind the leader on the fence, ran on fairly.
Pushed to occupy the box seat, kept on one pace until final 150M weakened. (Twisted plate during the race)
Always at rear section, never looked likely.
Raced midfield, travelled 5.5Ls behind the leader on the fence, made no impression in straight.
Sent forward, however trapped 3 wide without cover throughout, dropped off soon after straightening.
Broke ok, settled rail midfield, switched 1 off 400m & shaken up, checked 330m, driven 260m & burst well clear, eased at wire.
Fast start wide, sat 2nd 1 off no cover, joined leader 420m, shaken up to lead 350m, all out & headed 200m, tapered to wire.
Smart start, dropped in 1 off fore of midfield, switched 3 wide for progress 680m every chance when shaken up 420m, boxed on to snag 3rd.
Sharp break, rousted initially to race 1 back on rail, in pocket turning in, shaken up 350m, one paced in run.
Fast break, slotted handy 1 off with cover, every chance & driven 420m, outpaced, kept on evenly.
Missed break, raced rail behind midfield, stoked up 350m & shifted out, kept on for moderate inroads.
Tardy start, bustled early, settled 3 wide with cover behind midfield, niggled 600m, driven 430m, one paced in run.
Taken to tail from widest gate, sat 1 off, taken widest into stretch, shaken up 400m, closed off centre track for minor inroads.
Slow start, sat 1 off with cover behind midfield, hard ridden turning in, shifted out 360m, plugged on under pressure.
Missed break & bustled initially to sit 2nd last on fence, switched out & driven final turn, plugged on past fading rivals.
Snagged back from wide to race near tail 1 off, shifted wide home turn & driven 420m, found little in tame run home.
Fast start & soon led, to rail 1300m, 1L clear & driven 430m, all out & headed 350m, edged off rail, weakened tamely.
Broke well out wide, slotted back 5th 1 off with cover, 3 wide progress 1050m to sit handy no cover, faded in stretch.
Awkward start & bustled, caught wide no cover fore of midfield, cover from 950m, niggled 850m, driven 620m, faded out.
Fast start to lead out wide, headed 1100m, snagged back 900m to 3rd 1 off 1 back, shifted out 400m & cruised to 2nd, shaken up 300m & quickened to lead 260m, drew clear.
Broke with others, camped rail midfield, shifted 1 off 720m, wide turning in, driven 400m, closed centre track to 2nd 250m, no match for winner.
Fast start to dispute lead, soon snagged back to midfield 1 off, to rail 760m, shifted out & driven 450m, stayed on to 3rd 200m, battled dourly to wire.
Missed break, ridden to race rail behind midfield, niggled throughout & progress on turn, driven 400m, stayed on dourly to just miss frame.
Broke OK, soon 1 off behind midfield, off heels 900m & lost spot, 3rd last & driven wide turning in, closed off centre track for minor gains.
Broke with others, raced 4th on rail, driven & shifted out turning in, plugged on one pace.
Sharp break & rousted to dispute early lead, settled 1 off in 5th, ridden in 4th 420m, outpaced & tapered.
Taken back at break to race tail on rail, driven 400m, stayed on for minor inroads.
Awkward start, raced 3 wide near rear, wide on turn, bumped 430m & 400m, driven but plugged on tepidly.
Broke OK, bustled to narrow lead 1100m & snared rail, 1L clear 700m, shaken up 400m, all out & headed 260m, faded out.
Snagged back from wide gate, settled 2nd last 1 off, niggled 720m, under pump 600m, wide home turn, plugged on tamely.
Tardy start, found a spot on rail near rear, overraced 750m, hard-ridden 400m, struggled in stretch run.
Good break, bustled early to race 1 off behind midfield, crowded & bumped 430m, driven 400m & bumped, soon emptied & eased.
Broke well from widest, vied for lead, caught 3 wide until slotted 1 off 890m & sat 2nd, driven 440m, soon emptied & faded.
Pushed forward, took a considerable distance to cross and obtain the lead, drifted away 400M, hung on well to win despite not suited by the fast sectionals.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, benefited by the fast pace, progressed steadily 400M for 2nd.
Very slow away, 5Ls off the leader along the fence, suited by the fast tempo, lack room 400M, progressed steadily when clear.
Eased back, 6.5Ls off the leader, benefited by the fast pace but trapped 3-4 wide throughout, made steady ground 200M.
Eased at start, 7.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, favoured by the fast pace, made some ground 200M.
Settled in midfield, 4Ls off the fast tempo 2 wide, lack turn of foot in straight.
At back, 6Ls off the leader along the fence, benefited by the fast pace, held up 4-2, ran on only fairly when clear.
Hard ridden forward to hold the rail, 2.5Ls off the leader, harmed by the fast pace, gave ground 300M.
Hard ridden forward, 2.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the fast pace, emptied 350M.
Eased to sit in midfield, 5Ls off the fast pace, trapped 3-4 wide, weakened 300M.
Hard ridden to sit in front of midfield, 2.5Ls off the leader, not suited by the fast pace and trapped 3 wide, out of fuel 300M.
Hard ridden to take box seat, harmed by the fast sectionals, reduced rapidly 400M.
Slow away, hard ridden forward, 1L off the leader 2 wide, burnt out by the fast pace, exhausted badly 400M.

Placing: TNP
Comment: Reared at the start and did not jump out from the stalls.
Pressed forward from middle draw, three-away from outside fence before making forward move entering course proper. Took over 150m and pulled clear.
Began OK, taken to outside fence settling three back from leader. Switched in for clear running passing 400m and finished off strongly while laying in.
Began well, pressed forward, settling inside leader until course proper. Kept on steadily under hard riding.
Began best and soon clear leader on stands end setting slow pace. Collared 300m out but kept on well to just miss a placing.
Hard ridden from inside draw to go forward while edging toward stands rail. Shifted out and bumped 500m, kept on well.
Bumped shortly after start, pressed forward to sit behind pace to course proper, but only one-paced under hard riding final 300m.
Began fairly, taken to outside rail but uncomfortable with slow pace. Became unbalanced 600m, put under pressure 400m, finished fairly.
Began well, racing between horses behind the pace. Bumped 500m out but only one-paced final stages.
Ridden along early to maintain forward position one-away from outer fence. Tightened and unbalanced 400m, kept on one-paced.
Crowded out start, recovered settling behind midfield. Shifted in 500m to find clear running but only one-paced.
Jumped OK, taken to outside fence settling behind midfield. One-paced under pressure entering course proper and tired final stages.
Began fairly, crowded, dropping to rear. Never competitive.
Ridden early but outpaced, dropping to rear down centre track. Never competitive.
Began awkwardly, bumped, hard ridden but failed to respond, gradually losing touch with rest of the field. (Jockey reported horses did not stretch out at any stage).
Driven forward and crossed to the lead before the turn, continued on well when urged mid-straight, had enough to hold off late challenge of 2nd.
Well placed behind leaders, picked on well on straightening, chased leader strongly final 200M, held by a diminishing neck.
Took early lead, restrained nearing home turn and held up just off the pace, ridden to chase leader 300M but always held.
Travelled in midfield 3-wide, driven out 350M but not pace to challenge leaders, stayed on for non-threatening 4th.
Switched off to the rear 7Ls off the pace, waited with until 300M, closed off well when let down.
Failed to muster speed, travelled 4-wide without cover, hung out on the turn, finished off only fairly, never reached contention.
Slotted into a spot behind midfield, had 6Ls to make up 400M, ran on fairly making no real progress.
In touch, 3-wide swinging for home and travelled well enough, found disappointingly little however over final 300M.
Prominently placed as expected, not picked up on straightening and soon weakened.
Settled in midfield along the fence, came under serious pressure 500M, no extra mid-straight.
Slow to begin, urged along and got back to race in mid-division, had little to offer turning in, soon left behind.
Towards the rear, lost touch and falling behind inside 500M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance)

Began well, not pushed, settling toward rear in one-off position. Checked, unbalanced 1100m, edged closer turn, widest into straight, rolled to the front 200m, pulled clear under hands and heels riding.
Shifted in from wide draw after start but still caught 3-wide mostly. Urged forward from 600m, wide into straight, kept on well.
Began awkwardly, dropping back but holding rail. Popped off fence 500m to get clear run, finished strongly between horses to be closest at finish.

Pressed forward from awkward draw, racing 3-wide before settling outside leader back stretch. Hit front soon after straightening and kept on well until flattened final strides. Lay out under pressure.
Ridden along to hold position four-back from leader close to fence. Switched out at turn to get clear running and boxed on gamely in straight.
Ridden along to hold forward position along rail 3-back from leader. Took closer order around turn, kept on well early in straight before turning one paced.
Shifted across from wide draw and improved position close to rail. Left the fence back stretch, wide into turn but only one-paced.
First out before taking sit on leader then easing into one-back, one-off position. Edged closer around turn, looked chance 200m, one-paced.
Taken back from awkward draw and soon last. Tightened 600m when making forward move but only one-paced, running past beaten horses.
Began OK, ridden along between horses but checked and lost ground 1100m, dropping to last. Put under pressure from 600m and made some late ground.
Hard ridden from wide draw but didn't muster and caught wide in midfield without cover. Switched in passing 1100m but left wide again from 900m. Gave ground steadily in straight.
Jumped with field but lacked speed and drifted back towards rear along rail. Put under pressure turning for home but found little.
Began OK, ridden along to hold forward position behind the pace. Lay in passing 900m, unbalanced and lost ground when brushed rail 700m. Never likely thereafter.
Pressed forward to lead on setting, setting steady sections. Collared soon after straightening for home and faded quickly. Substantial amount of mucopus in trachea.
Taken back from gate 10, raced at tail throughout, still well back on turn, no clear running early in straight, angled out into clear and finished off very strongly to score.
Began fairly from a wide draw, sent forward to race prominently in 2nd, 2-3 lengths back on turn, matched leader most straight and took the lead near 100M, but couldn't hold off the winner late.
Bumped start, raced 2 wide behind midfield, 6-7 lengths back, improved on turn, finished off well in straight to get 3rd.
Slightly slowly away, raced 2 wide at rear, 8-9 lengths back, improved on turn, finished off strongly in straight to make frame.
Fast into stride, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, matched rival to 100M but couldn't find any extra at business end.
Jumped well, raced 4 lengths back on rail in 4th, saved ground on turn, closed off evenly in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 2 wide in 3rd, similar position on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Moderately away, raced 6 lengths or so back on rail in midfield, easy run to turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began well, raced 2 wide in midfield, 6 lengths back, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Began awkwardly, raced on rail at rear, 9 lengths back, slightly improved along the rail on turn, finished off one-paced in straight.
Began well from the widest gate, showed no early speed, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide with no cover in midfield throughout, weakened gradually in straight.
Crowded out start, raced 10 lengths back at rear, slightly improved on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Moderately away, taken back to race 3 wide with cover at rear, still at rear on turn, failed to close off in straight. (Blood in the horse's trachea)
Jumped with them, raced behind midfield, 3-4 wide turning, failed to close off in straight.
