Gear: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Comment: Comments on Running is not available for this race.
Crowded at start dropping to the rear and waited with, commenced move entering straight, ran on well down the centre of the straight to assert close to home.
Jumped fairly from the middle gate settling in forward of midfield, soon came to challenge upon straightening, ran on to hold some chance but winner too good.
Soon took up running maintaining a slender lead to straight, driven 2L clear on straightening but soon flattered, headed 200 metres out.
Crowded to the rear at start, remained well behind to straight, finished off race strongly.
Settled in forward of midfield, saved ground on rails turning in, baulked for a run early in straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Taken back after jump settling just worse than midfield on rails, made steady progress in straight.
Soon shifted back to the rear from the widest gate trailing the field to straight, ran on steadily without threatening.
Began fairly, never far off to straight, found no extra inside final 200 metres.
Settled in rear of midfield, ran home one-paced. (Lame)
Pressed on from a wide gate, remained wide without cover in a prominent position most of way to 400 metres, weakened under pressure.
Disputed the lead to straight, folded up quickly after straightening.
Settled in midfield on rails, gave ground from around home bend.
Driven along from the start, had to settle for a position towards the rear, widest runner turning in, found nothing.
Given reminders to maintain prominent positions early, ridden along mainly 3-wide in 2L 5th far side, dropped out under pressure upon straightening.
Ridden along to take the lead. Held a ½L margin turning in, shook off pursuers and opened up a 2L advantage near 200M. Kept on well final stages to preserve win.
Jumped well and was among early leaders. Settled behind the pace around the turn. Quickened gradually but unable to catch winner.
Jumped awkwardly and crowded shortly after. Niggled along to get back to midfield. Saved ground making the turn. Kept on well in the straight for a minor placing.
Settled at midfield. Behind midfield making the turn. Switched out on straightening and rallied to make the frame.
Rear section. On the rails and trailed field making the turn. Closed off well and made up ground in the straight.
Settled towards the rear. Near last turning for home and had to switch out for daylight. Steadily made up ground in the straight.
Taken back from wide draw and raced in rear section. Ran on fairly and made up some late ground.
Settled on the rails and no better than midfield. Ground saving trip behind midfield around the turn. Ran on fairly in the straight.
Niggled along from wide draw and was in lead or disputed lead until home straight. Failed to keep pace and faded final 300M.
Hard ridden from wide draw but not able to muster speed. Improved gradually and was 2-wide behind leaders making home turn. Faded final 200M.
2-wide behind midfield. Taken wider making home turn and never quickened in the straight.
Hard ridden, behind leaders 1000M out. Soon outpaced and slipped back to behind midfield. Wide and last turning in. Only ran past a tired runner.
Contested for the early lead. Better than midfield 800M and 3Ls off turning for home. Dropped out after straightening.
Prominent, tracked nicely behind the leader, ran on strongly to score comfortably by 1-3/4Ls.
Raced midfield, settled 2Ls behind the leader, unable to find a clear run from 350M out, ran on nicely for 2nd when clear over the concluding stages. (Bled)
Sent forward to share the lead along the outer fence, kept on well until final 180M headed by the winner.
Slow to begin, then eased to settle 3Ls behind the leader, ran on gradually for 4th.
Rolled forward to take the lead, kept on one paced until 300M weakened.
Camped handy, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader, kept on one pace until over the concluding stages weakened.
Taken back, settled 5Ls behind the leader, checked 250M, made some late ground thereafter.
Raced midfield, settled 3Ls behind the leader in the middle of the track, never ran on.
Prominent, travelled 1.5Ls behind the leader, made no impression when placed under pressure 400M.
At rear, travelled 11Ls behind the leader, never a factor. (Questioned for riding, see incident report)
Camped handy early, however weakened badly when place under pressure 300M.
Always at rear, never looked competitive.
Showed some early pace to settle 2Ls behind the leader in the middle of the track, flattened badly 400M. (Lame left fore)
Began very awkwardly and lost a considerable amount of ground, tailed out.
Broke well, rolled to lead 1350m, to rail 1100m, dictated tempo & shaken up 350m, drew clear, all out & tapered closing stages, just held on.
Smart start, ridden to vie for early lead, soon settled 1 back on rail, shifted out home turn & driven 420m, closed determinedly under strong drive, just failed.
Broke well & bustled wide to settle 2nd on leader's flank, under pump 500m, outpaced by winner turning in, all out 250m & lost 2nd, boxed on evenly.
Tardy start, raced midfield 1 off with cover, shifted 3 wide 500m, driven centre track & closed soundly without threatening.
Good start but outpaced & driven midfield, niggled for 3 wide progress to rank 4th at 1000m, under pressure 600m & driven, plugged on moderately.
Moderate break, rolled to sit rail fore of midfield, switched to outer 420m & driven, plodded on one pace.
Steady break, taken back to 1 off with cover near rear, shifted out 500m & driven, ducked back towards inner 380m, plugged home tamely.
Missed break, settled rail near rear, ridden a touch 730m, under pump 480m, plodded on same speed.
Taken back from wide gate, caught 3 deep & soon in rear rank, ridden 600m in attempted advance, soon under pressure, kept on tepidly.
Missed break & niggled to race rail at tail, driven 680m, plugged on tamely past fading rivals.
Speed to lead at break, soon headed & slid back to 1 off with cover fore of midfield, driven 500m, slight check 420m, found nothing & faded.
Broke OK & rousted to settle midfield on rail, shifted 1 off home turn, driven 400m, found nothing & wilted.
Sluggish start, soon in rear 1 off with cover, ridden 580m, found nothing in weakening run.
Broke OK, snagged to sit rail behind midfield, edged 3 deep with cover 1200m, wide progress on turn, driven 340m, closed centre track to lead 70m.
Tardy start, mustered on rail to lead 1620m, set tempo & 0.5L advantage turning in, shaken up 350m, soon all out, tapered & caught late.
Moderate start, bustled to 1 off with cover midfield, shifted out home turn, outpaced & driven 340m, stayed on dourly to 3rd & battled to wire.
Sluggish start & bustled, sat rail near rear, niggled 1400m & minor progress 1 off, driven wide home turn, closed to vie for 3rd final 100m.
Slow break & bustled wide to sit 3 wide with cover midfield, driven wide home turn, boxed to 3rd 240m, emptied 200m & faded.
Taken behind at start & raced at tail, niggled 900m & advanced on inner, ridden 500m, stayed on one pace.
Slow break & rousted, raced wide last pair, niggled for progress 1200m, back to last pair 750m, hard-ridden 450m, plugged on tepidly.
Driven from gate, settled 1 back on fence, every chance when clipped heels & stumbled turning in, soon hard-driven, plugged on one pace.
Broke well, slotted 1 off 1 back, well-placed & driven 480m, outpaced & plodded on evenly.
Broke well, shuffled back to 1 off with cover behind midfield, pushed 4 deep no cover 1200m & shuffled back, ridden 540m, last turning in, kept on centre track.
Broke well to lead, headed 1620m, raced 1 off no cover in 2nd, niggled 900m, emptied 250m & faded out.
Smart start, soon outpaced & settled rail midfield, under pump 700m, no extra turning in & weakened out.
Broke OK, driven wide to slot 1 off near rear, shuffled back to tail 870m & niggled, driven 500m, wilted tamely.
Rousted from gate, trapped 3 wide no cover handy, under pump 500m, emptied 350m & backpedalled.
Pushed to sit in front of midfield, 3.5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide no cover, dashed well 300M to score despite all negative racing situations.
Pushed to obtain the box seat, benefited by the slow sectionals, led 400M, hung on well until 150M overhauled, ran on for 2nd.
Eased to sit behind midfield, 5Ls off the leader, trapped 3-4 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 300M.
6Ls off the leader 2-3 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, demonstrated strong finishing efforts 300M.
Slow away, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, dashed well 250M.
Midfield, 4.5Ls off the leader 2 wide, little dash 200m despite not suited by the slow pace.
Slow away, hard ridden to obtain a midfield spot along the fence, 3.5Ls off the slow pace, made early move 600M, ran on until 200M flattened.
Settled in midfield, 3Ls off the leader 2 wide, not suited by the slow tempo, just held ground in straight.
Hard ridden to take rail and led by 1.5Ls at advantageous slow sectionals, however soon emptied 350M.
Slow away, struggled to keep up at rear, 9Ls off the slow pace on the fence, harmed by the slow pace, little dash 200M.
Eased back, 8Ls off the leader 2 wide, harmed by the slow pace, no turn of foot.
Hard ridden to hold the rail behind midfield, 6Ls off the leader, not suited by the slow tempo, no dash.
Not suited by the slow pace, never competitive at back.
Settled in front, enjoyed the slow tempo, but reduced quickly 400M.
Began well but allowed to drift back in 3-wide position settling at rear. Made forward move passing 700m, widest into straight, finished strongly to just get there.
Allowed to find feet behind midfield in one-off position. Took closer order around turn, shifted out 400m for clear running, finished strongly inside eventual winner.
Eased back after start, dropping to clear last back stretch. Saved ground around turn by hugging rails, switched out 350m for clear running, flashed home final 200m.
Ridden to hold forward position behind the pace in one-off position. Three-wide entering straight, rolled forward to hit front 300m, kept on well till swamped final stages.
Began well but eased into slipstream of leader approaching turn. Came off fence 500m, rolled forward to look chance 300m, kept on well till flattened final 50m.
Hard ridden early to hold rail, settling two-back from leader passing 1000m. Stayed on rail around turn, shifted out 400m for run but bumped another, kept on well till 100m when one-paced.
Outpaced early, then crowded for room 950m. Steadied and lost ground 850m. Made steady progress between horses final 400m.
Jumped with field, allowed to settle midfield in one-off position. Cut to rail around turn, looked for inside run in straight but only one paced.
Ridden forward but held three-wide mostly, settling in midfield. Switched out approaching straight and put under pressure but only limited response.
Slow into stride, cut in to rail and quickly made ground to sit 4-back from leader. Stayed on rail entering straight but only one-paced when put under pressure.
Ridden along three and four wide back stretch, settling behind midfield. Switched wide turning for home but only one-paced under hard riding. (Substantial blood in trachea)
Difficult to load. Pressed forward to lead on settling, cutting to fence. Joined 900m, retook lead entering straight but condition ran out 350m.
Used up early to go forward from wide draw, racing outside leader from 900m to 300m. Gave ground quickly final stages.

Kicked rail before start but passed fit to run. Pressed forward from wide draw to race alongside leaders to 800m. Lost position rapidly turning for home and tailed off in straight. (Unacceptable performance)
Restrained to a 2-wide position towards the rear, well suited to the quick pace middle stages, had 8Ls to make up turning in, quickened up smartly to lead 150M, won going away.
Shifted across behind runners early stages, not hurried over 10Ls behind runaway leader, had plenty to make up 400M, closed off strongly and got up for 2nd near line.
Settled in 4th 4-5Ls behind runaway leader, made steady headway inside 400M, not finishing pace of winner final 150M, lost 2nd near line.
Held up behind mid-division, 8Ls behind runaway leader 400M, took time to get going, did best work final 200M.
Travelled in midfield 6-7Ls behind breakaway leader, kept on evenly down the inside rail over final 400M.
Held up 2-wide in mid-division, driven 450M, went 4th 150M, peaked 100M and faded towards finish.
Driven to the lead, set fast pace 2nd quarter and opened up a 3-4Ls lead, run ended 250M, weakened and swamped final 150M. (See Racing Incidents.)
Settled behind mid-division, over 7Ls to make up 400M, made some progress early straight but flattened out final stages. (Lame left front leg)
Travelled in midfield, 7Ls off the pace in middle stages, could only make limited progress inside 400M, never reached contention.
Up with early pace, settled 3Ls behind breakaway leader in middle stages, driven out 500M, made good initial progress but couldn't sustain run passing 200M, no extra late.
Held up towards the rear, 10Ls behind leader in a strongly run race, ran on only fairly entering straight, never involved.
Soon pushed along to obtain a forward position, settled in 2nd about 3Ls behind runaway leader, failed to keep up with pursuers from 300M, weakened towards finish.
Began awkwardly, raced greenly early and middle stages, reluctant to maintain position 900M and shuffled back to rear, failed to respond to riding 500M, soon out of contention.
Sluggish away, dropped back to the rear well off the pace, lost touch 500M, finished tailed out. (Unacceptable Performance)
Slow into stride, dropping to last. Popped off fence at first turn and made ground between horses though still towards rear. Switched in 400m and ran home strongly to just make it.
Began well, slipping into box seat behind leader. Raced a little keenly, switched out 400m to make run, hit front 50m but caught on line.
Pressed forward from wide draw to sit outside leader around first turn. Looked chance on straightening but unable hold off first two.
Began well, pressed forward to hold position one-back, one-off to straight. Looked chance 300m but run down final stages.
Ridden along three and four wide behind leading pack to first turn. Kept on steadily in straight under hard riding but unable close gap.
Began well, quickly on rail 3-back from leader. Switched out 400m to make run but only one-paced under hard riding.
Restrained early, dropping to behind midfield in a one-off position. Bumped when shifted out 500m to make run but only one-paced.
Hard ridden early but unable get cover, racing three-back and three-wide mostly. Very wide into straight and one-paced final 300m.
Steadied soon after start and shifted in behind horses from wide draw, settling at rear. Taken out turning for home and ran past tired horses.
Ridden along three and four wide towards the rear but failed to muster. Bumped passing 500m and one-paced in straight. (Lame right front, poor action in both hind legs)
Quickly on rail, holding position four-back from leader. Stayed on rail turning for home but only one-paced in straight.
Began OK but soon outpaced dropping to last. Never competitive.
Pressed forward to lead, setting muddling pace. Collared just before straightening for home and faded quickly.
Restrained and taken in from wide draw but held 3-wide at rear. Bumped and unbalanced 500m put under pressure 400m but no response. (Continuous epiglottic entrapment)
Jumped with them, raced 3 to 4 lengths back in midfield, easy run on turn, finished off strongly in straight to score narrowly.
Began well from a tricky gate, raced 2 wide in 5th, 2 to 3 lengths back, same position turning, finished off well in straight but always held by the winner.
Average to begin, positioned 2 lengths behind the leader on rail, easy run on turn, closed off well but just couldn't hold off the first two late.
Began fairly, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 5 lengths back, bumped near 900M, similar position turning, no clear running in early straight, finished off strongly thereafter to make frame.
Jumped well, raced prominently next to the leader, half lengths back on turn, kept on evenly in straight.
Slowly away, raced 7 lengths back at rear, 2 wide on turn, angled out in straight and finished well to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, difficult to settle after 1000M and severely checked near 900M, 8 lengths back at tail, well back on turn, made good progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Jumped well, sent forward to take the lead, still leading turning in, headed near 100M, weakened gradually thereafter.
Moderately away from the widest draw, raced 2-3 wide in midfield, 3 wide turning, finished off one-paced.
Slightly slow out, raced 4 or so back behind midfield on rail, bumped near 1000M and 900M, similar position on turn, finished off evenly in straight.
Slightly slow out, difficult to settle early, positioned 5-6 lengths back at rear, still travel keenly on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Jumped well from a wide draw, unable to slot in, raced 4 wide without cover at rear, 7-8 lengths back, emptied after turning in, never a threat.
Slightly slow out from a wide draw, raced 7-8 lengths back at rear, saved ground to turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide with no cover throughout, gave ground soon after entering straight, finishing tailed off. (Irregular heart rhythm)
Began well, sent forward to take the lead, enjoyed the easy lead throughout, kicked clear after turning in, won comfortably.
Slightly slow out, recovered to race 1-2 lengths back on rail in 4th, easy run on turn, finished off well without threatening the winner.
Jumped well from the widest gate, raced 3 wide with cover in midfield, 2-3 lengths back, same position turning, finished off well in straight to get 3rd.
Fast into stride, positioned 2 wide in 5th, 2 lengths back, same position on turn, no daylight early in straight, closed off well when clear to make frame.
Began with them, raced 3-4 lengths back on rail in midfield, saved ground turning, kept to inside after straightening and finished off evenly.
Slightly slowly away, positioned 2 wide in midfield, 3-4 lengths back, similar position turning, finished off evenly in straight.
Slowly away, raced 7 lengths back at rear, still well back on turn, make some progress in straight to be nearest on line.
Bumped start, unable to slot in, travelled 3 wide and without cover throughout, failed to quicken in straight, just stayed on one-paced.
Jumped well, positioned 2 wide behind midfield, 6 lengths back, similar position throughout, finished off one-paced.
Slowly away, raced 6 lengths back on rail in 11th, easy run along the rail, made no progress after turning in, never a threat.
Broke nicely, raced prominently in 2nd, easy run throughout, showed no response after turning in and weakened gradually.
Jumped well from a wide draw, raced 3 wide with cover behind midfield, 4 lengths back, same position on turn, failed to close off in straight.
Bumped start, raced 3 wide with cover at rear, 5-6 lengths back, travelled keenly for some distance near 1100M, still 3 wide on turn, showed no response in straight, never a threat.
Taken back from a wide draw, raced 8 lengths back at tail, angled out turning in, failed to close off in straight, never competitive.
